  <string name="$Item.Story.HalfDozercane01.Tooltip">GingerDozer\'s candy cane, broken in half. Hurry and rescue GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.Sugarcoin.Tooltip">An essential item for entering the auction. It\'s so shiny! Don\'t ask why, but it also tastes very sweet!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.BraveMaidcloth.Tooltip">GingerBrave donned this uniform while temporarily aiding the staff of the Grand Cabinet Hotel. Not a single speck of dust could be found after GingerBrave helped with cleaning!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.BrightBellboycloth.Tooltip">GingerBright donned this uniform while temporarily aiding the staff of the Grand Cabinet Hotel. A bright smile to greet the guests is always a sign of great service!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.WizardShefhat.Tooltip">Cleanliness is key when cooking! Not a single hair or speck of dust is allowed! This chef\'s toque is both practical and very fashionable.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.StrawberryMaidcloth.Tooltip">Strawberry Cookie donned this uniform while temporarily aiding the staff of the Grand Cabinet Hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.Goldenkey.Return.Tooltip">A golden key that was retrieved from bandits. It\'s so shiny!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.Oliveoil.Tooltip">Top quality olive oil. Its aroma is so strong that it penetrates the cap.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.Babypowder.Tooltip">This powder is softer and finer than snow. But watch out! If you drop the bottle, it\'ll get everywhere! The hotel staff uses this after waxing the floors.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.Rope.Tooltip">A sturdy rope that can tie anything. A twist here, a pull there, and BAM! Mission accomplished.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.LegendCompass.Tooltip">A compass said to have been left behind by an explorer who reached the end of the world. Legend has it that this compass will guide you to your heart\'s true desires without fail.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Story.BlokenLegendCompass.Tooltip">This magical compass is no longer working. Luckily, the needle pointed towards GingerDozer\'s location just before it malfunctioned. Broken compass or not, nothing will stop the Cookies from rescuing their friend.</string>
