  <string name="$Neighbor.0001.Story">Such a clever mouse, and a good friend!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0002.Story">Such a brave mouse, and a good friend!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0003.Story">Skittish and timid, but friendly!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0004.Story">Always tired and sleepy, but never lazy!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0005.Story">Always hungry, but never overeats!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0006.Story">Always seems to know many secrets, but never gossips!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0007.Story">A blazing hot, but friendly, Ember. No one knows where it came from...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0008.Story">A scorching hot, but friendly, Ember. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0009.Story">A flaming hot, but friendly, Ember. It seems they\'ve been here a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0010.Story">A moldy Cheese on the run. No one knows how long they\'ve been running.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0011.Story">A ripe Cheese on the run. Will you be their new partner in crime?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0012.Story">A disguised Cheese on the run. No one knows where they came from...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0013.Story">A cute Black Sesame Fuzzball. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0014.Story">An adorable Cheese Fuzzball. It seems they\'ve been here a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0015.Story">A cuddly Tabby Fuzzball. No one knows where they came from...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0016.Story">"Blue cheese is notoriously difficult to make and store, but not at Cheesehaven! It\'s been a favorite dish of the tavern for years on end. You absolutely must try this rare and distinguished delicacy!\" -Interview Excerpt from \"Micedom Fromagers Society"</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0017.Story">"You can never go wrong with a classic cheddar cheese. But Cheesehaven has found a way to make it more scrumptious and savory than anywhere else! It\'s been a favorite dish of the tavern for years on end. Of course, rare delicacies are welcome, but there\'s something comforting about a sharp and sweet cheddar!\" -Interview Excerpt from \"Micedom Fromagers Society"</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0018.Story">"If your palate desires something refined and creamy, look no further! Cheesehaven\'s selection of brie is smooth and rich as can be. It\'s been a favorite dish of the tavern for years on end and will definitely bring a smile to your face.\" -Interview Excerpt from \"Micedom Fromagers Society"</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0019.Story">If you visit an establishment with 3 Squeakchelin Stars, you\'re guaranteed to experience an amazing night of fine dining, and maybe run into this particular Squeakchelin Inspector. Renown for writing both scathing critique and poetic praise, this critic seeks only the epitome of exquisite cuisine. Traveling via the halls and chambers may be dangerous, but that doesn\'t stop this eccentric, and somewhat nervous, fellow from discovering all sorts of flavors and aromas at renowned restaurants throughout the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0020.Story">A brand-new staff member of the Grand Cabinet Hotel. So friendly!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0021.Story">A proud staff member of the Grand Cabinet Hotel. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0022.Story">A veteran staff member of the Grand Cabinet Hotel. It seems they\'ve been here a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0023.Story">A bellhop who dreams of becoming a manager. So friendly!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0024.Story">A bellhop who strives to be the kindest member of the staff. So caring!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0025.Story">A bellhop who hopes to become Employee of the Year. So punctual!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0026.Story">Detective Gumdrop, currently investigating undercover. The disguise could use a little work.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0027.Story">A burglar trying to keep a low profile. The disguise is rather genius, actually.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0028.Story">A spy performing some field work. The disguise kind of sticks out.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0029.Story">While caring for his wife\'s quills, he accidentally pricked himself. Luckily, the injury doesn\'t seem too bad.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0030.Story">While caring for his wife\'s quills, he accidentally pricked himself. Luckily, it seems there are more bandages than needed.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0031.Story">While caring for his wife\'s quills, he accidentally pricked himself. Luckily, it seems that first-aid care was delivered swiftly and... very-thoroughly.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0032.Story">Done with a perfect quill perm and ready for a brand-new day! What sort of fun awaits us today, darling?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0033.Story">Well-rested and ready for a new brand-new day! What sort of fun awaits us today, darling?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0034.Story">Refreshed, relaxed, and ready for a new brand-new day! What sort of fun awaits us today, darling?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0035.Story">The first son of the proud Stag family. What a gentleman!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0036.Story">The second son of the proud Stag family. So down-to-earth!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0037.Story">The youngest son of the proud Stag family. So friendly!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0038.Story">A perfectionist chef of great tenacity. Everything must be perfect, from ingredients, to measurements, and exact timing!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0039.Story">A precisionist chef of great skill. Everything must be precise, from savoriness, to sweetness, and tinges of acidity!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0040.Story">A maximalist chef of great vision. Everything must be considered for maximal flavor, from oil temperature, to stirring, and hefty plating!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0041.Story">The backbone of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, Walnut. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0042.Story">A captain of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, Walnut. They seem familiar...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0043.Story">The fashionista of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, Walnut. No one knows where they came from...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0044.Story">The frontrunner of the Apricot Jam Syndicate. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0045.Story">The cackling jokester of the Apricot Jam Syndicate. It seems they\'ve been here a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0046.Story">The head ruffian of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, who really doesn\'t like the color purple... Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0047.Story">The cutester of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, Cashew. Will you be their new best friend?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0048.Story">The amateur mage of the Apricot Jam Syndicate. It seems they\'ve been here a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0049.Story">The greatest trendsetter of the Apricot Jam Syndicate, who really loves the color purple. No one knows how long they\'ve been here.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0050.Story">Have you met the greatest, reputable, and very talkative host in the witch\'s castle? Everyone who has met this silver-tongued parrot claims that his comments and persuasive tones can auction off the priciest of jewels to the grubbiest of dishrags! In recognition of his skills, an endless number of events and establishments are asking for his presence. He\'s always wearing his sunglasses though, but no one knows exactly why.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0051.Story">\"The Grand Cabinet Hotel has been in this family for three generations, and it shall not be the last!\" This esteemed hotelier manages the Grand Cabinet Hotel as strictly as he grooms his mustache, prioritizing cleanliness, precision, and perfection. And there\'s nothing wrong with looking amazingly sharp while doing so! Under his strict management, the hotel has not received any formal complaints, none whatsoever! But at the cost of some whining from the staff, of course... Regardless, nary a soul doubts the managerial skills of Hotelier Rabbit III, whose grandfather first managed this majestic hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Floor.001.Story">Nothing like a hot bowl of stew to warm yourself up! This stew has a long history of providing sustenance and comfort to many Cookies of ages past, when song and laughter filled these halls.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Floor.002.Story">A cauldron that\'s been sitting here for quite a while. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Floor.003.Story">A wood-burning stove for roasting Jellies. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Wall.001.Story">A boiling kettle atop a cozy fire. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Ceil.001.Story">An aromatic bundle of herbs. Let\'s put it to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Ceil.002.Story">A cut of ham that\'s been cured, smoked, and aged. Looks scrumptious!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.WP.001.Story">Sandstone bricks with a hazel hue. Try decorating the walls with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.TooHotKitchen.Deck.001.Story">Sandstone tiles with a hazel hue. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.001.Story">An old-fashioned lantern that provides both light and warmth. It will definitely help ward off the cold!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.002.Story">An old-fashioned lantern that provides both light and warmth. It will definitely help light up any room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.003.Story">An antique candlestick. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.004.Story">A simple, but hearty meal of stew and roasted Jellies. Looks scrumptious!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.005.Story">An old-fashioned candelabrum. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.006.Story">An ingenious method of roasting some food with a simple candle! Hungry yet?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Floor.007.Story">A haphazardly crafted canopy made with a fork. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Wall.001.Story">It\'s not much to look at, but it serves its purpose! It\'s a start to making a lovely home!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.WP.001.Story">Simple panels that are perfect for any room or home. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WarmShelter.Deck.001.Story">Simple panels that are perfect for any room or home. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.001.Story">This curious plant always seems to hungry. But hungry for what? Water? Better soil? Sunlight? No... Hungry for Cookies! Who would plant such a ferocious thing and leave it in the castle?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.002.Story">A dusty jar filled with old, stale Cookies. Looks like someone was practicing their baking skills...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.003.Story">A jar of syrup for creating... some interesting looking candy. It\'ll probably look good somewhere...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.004.Story">A tiny Cookievorous plant. It might seem homely to certain folks...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.005.Story">An old, purple candle. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Floor.006.Story">One of the hardest candies in existence. It\'s rather ironic that it\'s shaped like a tooth too...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Wall.001.Story">A simple window adorned with vines. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Ceil.001.Story">A string of onions set out to dry. These will look great wherever you decide to put them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Ceil.002.Story">A cut of cured ham that\'s still being aged. Looks scrumptious... maybe...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Rug.001.Story">A pile of old, stained parchments. These will look great wherever you decide to place them... maybe.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.WP.001.Story">Damp stone bricks that are a bit slippery. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WhisperingWarehouse.Deck.001.Story">Damp stone tiles that are a bit slippery. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Floor.001.Story">An ancient grimoire that contains an entire chapter devoted to the study and creation of Life Potions. The recipe can only be understood by those astute in the magical arts.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Floor.002.Story">A telescope used to observe the stars. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Floor.003.Story">A stool made from juniper wood. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Floor.004.Story">An hourglass that was filled with sand measured with pinpoint accuracy, added grain by grain. It\'ll look good where you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Floor.006.Story">An inkwell filled to the brim with Life Potion! Let\'s definitely put this to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Ceil.001.Story">A delicately crafted mooncatcher. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Ceil.002.Story">A hanging planter. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Wall.001.Story">A window frame adorned with a crescent moon. Everyone will love it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Wall.002.Story">A round window with a star shape within. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Hanger.001.Story">A blue valence adorned with a star. Everyone will love it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.WP.001.Story">A lovely shade of purple wallpaper. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.LifePotionLab.Deck.001.Story">Plain and simple stone tiles. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.001.Story">Some poorly wrapped cheese. Let\'s place it somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.002.Story">Perfectly aged blue cheese that seems to radiate with a golden glow. Its strong flavor loved by Cheesehaven\'s regulars.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.003.Story">Perfectly aged blue cheese that seems to shine with a shade of ivory. Procuring this cheese from the witch\'s cupboard took a particularly daring and roguish adventure.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.004.Story">A wooden pantry. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.005.Story">Two wheels of cheese. These will look great wherever you decide to put them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.006.Story">A pair of oak barrels for all your juice storage needs. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Floor.007.Story">A hand trolley to move cheese more efficiently. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Wall.001.Story">Excess humidity can ruin cheese. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Ceil.001.Story">Sausage Jellies linked together. Looks scrumptious!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.WP.001.Story">Homely earthen walls. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CheeseStorage.Deck.001.Story">Sturdy hardwood tiles. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.001.Story">A few blades of grass with fresh drops of dew. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.002.Story">Have you ever seen such a snug and plushy bed? Everyone will love it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.003.Story">It\'s a rocking chair. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.004.Story">A cozy, decorative lamp. Everyone will love it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.005.Story">Only you can prevent castle fires! But not to worry, these lost matches were used to light a safe and cozy campfire. So come and take a seat! Gaze into the flickering flames and listen to it crackle... So relaxing.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.006.Story">Someone\'s preparing a campfire with some crooked matchsticks. Be careful!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.007.Story">A pair of spotted mushrooms. Are they edible...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.008.Story">A trio of inkcap mushrooms. They don\'t seem edible...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.009.Story">Though it may look a bit shabby on the outside, it\'s a warm and cozy shelter. Inside, the aroma of fresh bread still permeates the air. Many a weary traveler has made camp in this shelter, shielded from the horrors of the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Floor.010.Story">A stalk of giant broccoli. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Wall.001.Story">Seems like this fan hasn\'t been used for a long time. Let\'s put this to good use... if it still works, that is.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Hanger.001.Story">The bulbs on these ivies are glowing! These will look great wherever you decide to put them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Hanger.002.Story">An ivy leaf with fresh drops of dew. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Ceil.001.Story">A spider\'s web that\'s been sitting here for ages. Everyone will love it... maybe...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.WP.001.Story">Wooden boards that are illuminated by the moon. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumbleRoom.Deck.001.Story">Floor tiles that are illuminated by the moon. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.WP.001.Story">Panels of lovely redwood. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Deck.001.Story">An adorable carpet featuring strawberries and flowers. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.001.Story">A sleeper sofa made from a pristine strawberry sandwich. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.002.Story">A sleeper sofa made from a pristine strawberry sandwich. WITH UPGRADES: an armrest, better shade, and a basket of snacks! Your cozy and peaceful gaming session with the Pocket Strawberry begins now!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.003.Story">A sleeper sofa made from a pristine strawberry sandwich, alongside an armrest, fancy shade, and a basket of snacks. Your cozy and relaxing weekend filled with naps begins now!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.004.Story">A toolbox for all sorts of magical devices. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.005.Story">A jar full of strawberry jam. Everyone loves strawberries!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.006.Story">A jar full of raspberry syrup. Everyone loves raspberries!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Floor.007.Story">A blob of jam. Should it really be stored outside...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Hanger.001.Story">A poster featuring a tasty, ripe strawberry. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Hanger.002.Story">A set of stickers featuring strawberries and jam. Let\'s put them to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Hanger.003.Story">These light bulbs give off a warm, radiating glow. Just looking at them makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Hanger.001.Story">This badge has been polished beyond your typical mirror shine. This dazzling and glistening prize of honor is the reason why Sheriff Whiskerton keeps a zealous watch over the kitchen.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Hanger.002.Story">A deep investigation of a crime network? Or an attempt to untangle a conspiracy? Anyhow, let\'s hang it up somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.001.Story">Disturbance of the peace? Vandalism of castle property? Not in this sheriff\'s kitchen...! If you break the law, then you\'ll be confined right here with a rickety stool and broken TV.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.002.Story">A refined and perfect scratch sofa. It\'ll look good wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.003.Story">It\'s a mini stool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.004.Story">Ooh, catnip! It must be meow lucky day!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.005.Story">An old pile of \"Best Kitty\" badges. What a collection!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Floor.006.Story">A mini stack table for all your snacking needs. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Rug.001.Story">A perfect rug for scratching. Everyone will love it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.WP.001.Story">Sturdy and solid stone tiles. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CatSheriffOffice.Deck.001.Story">Sturdy and solid stone tiles. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Floor.001.Story">Hm, what\'s that? You think this apparatus is someone\'s tea, brewing away? Nonsense! Close your eyes and relax. The burbling sound of water is so relaxing, don\'t you think?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Floor.002.Story">These Jellies seem to glisten just like the stars in the night sky. Rumor has it that this globe will tell you when your tea is perfect and ready for consumption.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Floor.003.Story">A table with high-quality, well-trimmed herbs. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Floor.004.Story">A stool made from rosewood. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Floor.005.Story">A jar that used to store some aged juice. It\'ll look good wherever you decide to put it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Ceil.001.Story">A basket for storing herbs. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Wall.001.Story">The sun has set and twilight is upon us. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.StrangeSauna.Wall.002.Story">The sun has set and twilight is upon us. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
