Dert herts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_10">OH! I\'m so sorry!
I didn\'t know you were there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_11">But... why\'re you talking all... weird?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0001_12">Mer merth ith hrozen.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_13">Erm... Oh?!
Your mouth is frozen!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0001_14">Ned to thurw.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_15">Thaw?
But how?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0001_16">See thert roo?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_17">A room?
That frozen room?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0001_18">Irf yu culd hert urp thert roo,
ir\'d ee urch appeciaterd.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_19">AH! So you want me to heat up that room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_20">Okay, I\'ll do whatever it takes to help you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_21">Time to heat this place up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_1">HAHA!
If two witches were watching two batches, which witch would watch which batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_2">Ah, finally! To speak with such ease!
Your assistance is most appreciated, young Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_3">Hehe, it\'s good to hear your actual voice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_4">Ah yes, absolutely sublime. The warmth of ages past has been rekindled.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_5">Ages past?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_6">These halls were once filled with the aroma of scrumptious feasts and jubilant music.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_7">Before denizens escaped from the witch. Before the moonlight itself froze over.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_8">This warmth is undeniably a welcome sensation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_9">I shall allow you to pass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_10">Awesome! Now I can get to that window!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_11">Eh? What\'s that?
A window?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_12">There\'s a window that\'s way, way up there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_13">I\'m going to use it to escape to a place with no witches!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_14">*Grunt, cough, grumble*
Escape?! It\'s dangerous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_15">No one has ever managed to leave this castle\'s premises!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_16">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_17">No, but I have to!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_18">Whatever happens, whatever gets in my way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_19">I will find a way out of this castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_20">HAHA! You certainly possess a strange, unique form of bravery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_21">The Witch\'s Castle is teeming with mysteries, with danger lurking around every corner.
But your bravery may just...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0001_22">Go forth, young Cookie.
Step gingerly yet bravely!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_23">Gingerly... Bravely...
GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">I think that\'ll be my name!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_CUT2_Cookie.0001_25">I\'m gonna be the bravest Cookie ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_CUT2_Cookie.0001_26">The window!
I\'m almost there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ3_CUT2_Cookie.0001_27">I need to find a way up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">It\'s getting dark...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">There has to be a path I can follow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">That voice...?
A Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">I\'ll ask them for directions!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">What\'s happening...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">I feel... so weak...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_7">Crunchy, crunchy makes me happy!
Happy, happy makes me cheery!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">I found a new carpet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_10">Wait?!
You\'re a Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_11">Deary, deary me...
You look so tired and crumbly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_12">Wakey, wakey!
Rise and shine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Hey you!
You\'re finally awake, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Oh? Did you...?
Wow, thanks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">My name\'s GingerBright! What\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Heeheehee!
What an easy name to remember!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">So\'s yours, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Erm, GingerBright?
What did you use to wake me up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">I felt so tired and weak... But now it\'s like I\'m full of energy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_9">Heehee, I gave you a Life Potion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Cookies like us need Life Potions handy at all times.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">If we don\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_12">We\'ll get all stale and icky!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_13">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_14">Becoming stale looks so scary...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_15">Yup, yup, yup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_16">But don\'t worry.
Once you take a good look...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_17">being stale doesn\'t seem so bad.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_18">Eeeeugh, no thank you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_19">Life Potions are key...!
I\'ll remember that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_20">Let\'s go looking for
some potions together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_21">Oh! Great idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_22">I know just the place!
It\'s over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_23">Ta-da!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_24">Oh! There\'s gotta be something here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_25">Right?
Something exciting awaits us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1PQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_26">Let\'s bust through that wall!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Oooh!
What a pretty flower!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">That\'s not a flower!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">Look! It\'s smiling!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">IT\'S TERRIFYING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_5">Hey, GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_6">I think sticking with
you will lead to all
sorts of fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Likewise... but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">Wanna stay here in
this part of the
castle with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">We can have so
much fun,
just like now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">Sorry, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">I\'m heading to the
highest window.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_12">Oh? Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">I\'m gonna escape
from this castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Outside and free!
And far away from
the witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">Outside and free?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_16">Hmm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_18">FUN!!! Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">Let me tag along,
GingerBrave!
Pleeease?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">Really?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_21">Yeah! It will be
so much fun together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_22">Haha, alrighty then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_23">We\'ll make a great team,
GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_24">We\'ll be the
bestest team ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_25">I think I know the
window you\'re
talking about.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_26">Follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_27">GingerBright and me,
a team!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_28">I can feel the power of
friendship already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_29">We made it up
another floor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_30">Oh? There\'s a broken
Life Potion vial here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_31">I wonder
what happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_32">What was that noise?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_33">Let\'s go check it out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">The noise came from this way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Look over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">A Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">We heard a big noise!
Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">I... There\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Nothing to see here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_7">No need for concern.
Go about your business!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">OOOH!
It\'s a talking chest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_9">No, it\'s erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">Strawberry Cookie!
I am NOT trapped!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_12">Watch and learn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">AHEM!
Watch and learn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_14">He\'s been saying
that since yesterday...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">Don\'t worry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_16">We\'ll help your trapped friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_17">I am NOT trapped!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_INT1_Cookie.0001_18">Let\'s shake it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_19">If you\'d just given me a few more minutes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">Anyhow, pleased to meet you.
My name is Wizard Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">I\'m GingerBrave! And this is my friend, GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_22">Hello!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_23">I\'m... I\'m Strawberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">How\'d you get trapped in that chest, Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">First off, I\'ll have you know that I am an expert at escape magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_27">Second, I didn\'t want to waste my magic on such a trivial box.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_28">Which is why I was biding my time to make an escape.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">Sure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_30">I was checking the chest for magical artifacts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_31">The artifacts are required for a magical experiment of mine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_32">A magical experiment?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_33">The ultimate spell of a lifetime!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_34">A spell to conjure Life Potions!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">That sounds so cool! Is that really possible?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_36">I\'ll soon be able to verify my hypothesis.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_37">Good luck, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_38">We need to take this artifact back to my laboratory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_39">A laboratory? Where is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_40">Well, I must admit that I\'ve never had any visitors other than Strawberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_41">But you seem like trustworthy Cookies. You are cordially invited to visit my laboratory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_42">Follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_43">A laboratory! This is all so exciting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">This is the moment...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">The day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">I create a Life Potion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Magic circle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">Oooh!
It\'s started!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Creatio Potionus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">A Life Potion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_10">You did it, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">Thank you!
I knew that\'d work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_12">IT WORKED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">IT WORKED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_14">IT WOOORKED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">Wizard Cookie...!
Be careful!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Huh?
OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">The potion is spilling everywhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">My pristine robes are drenched...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Yippee! Looks like we won\'t have to worry about finding Life Potions anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">Well, yes, that is, if it doesn\'t keep spilling onto the floor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">We should find something to store the potion in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">Ah, there should be a few empty vials scattered around the laboratory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_23">Find them quickly! We need to hurry before we lose more of the potion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">Alrighty! Let\'s find those vials.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_25">Let... let me help too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">We did it! The potion has been stored in all the vials we found!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">And not a moment too soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Erm... thanks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">No, no! Thank YOU!
Now we have all the Life Potions we\'ll ever need!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">So... full...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">If you want, you can take the remaining vials.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Huh? But what about you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">I have enough potions stored within my robes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">After all, a wizard must travel light at all times.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Huh? Travel?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">I may have succeeded in creating a Life Potion...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">But I must continue in my journey for magical knowledge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">There are more magical artifacts to be found.
And ancient spells of legend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">And I won\'t be able to find them stuck here!
So I must depart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">You should come with us then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Pardon?
With you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Yeah, with us!
Together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">We\'re heading for the highest window!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">The highest window...?
Isn\'t that... really high up, and dangerous?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">Sounds exciting, doesn\'t it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">Very well then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">So you\'re coming with us then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_24">Ah, yes, well, for the time being.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">At least until I find another magical artifact!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_26">Together, we may be able to find artifacts much more quickly and efficiently.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">Teehee! Welp!
Whatever the reason, welcome aboard, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_28">How about you, Strawberry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">I... well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">C\'mon, Strawberry Cookie!
Let\'s go, together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_31">I may still be a freshly-baked Cookie,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_32">but I already know that with friends by your side, nothing\'s impossible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_33">... OKAY.
I\'ll go too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_34">Hooray!
We\'ll make an awesome team!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_35">Ahem.
A temporary team.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_36">An awesome, temporary team!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_37">Heehee!
This is gonna be amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_38">Then off we go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_39">It\'s a bit rowdy but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_40">I feel all
warm and
fuzzy inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_41">This floor feels so cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_42">\"Chilly\" is the correct term.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_43">Wait...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_44">What\'re those things...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_45">EW! It stinks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_46">Who left these here???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_47">An enormous someone, I assume.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_48">Everything\'s spoiled...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_49">Perhaps a quick tidying-up spell?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_50">We should get these out of our way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_51">Clean-up, clean-up,
everybody, everywhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">It looks so soft!
What\'s it feel like?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">I\'ve seen this in a book...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">A long and
elegant tail...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Soft, glistening fur...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_7">This thing is a...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_8">A CAT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Event.0001_9">WAAAH!
GO AWAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">Over there!
A small Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0003_11">You\'re under arrest, ageless Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0003_12">The meowstress has eagerly been searching for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0003_13">You will be given as tribute to the meowstress. And I shall receive a reward... a badge...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">The cat is toying with that Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">It\'s so dangerous, it\'s exciting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Alright. I have a plan.
We\'ll have to–</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">LEAVE HIM ALONE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Npc.0003_18">Mrawr?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.0025_19">I said I had a plan...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_1">Rogue Cookies!
Skittering about in the meowstress\' kitchen?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_2">You\'re all under arrest, mrawr!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0001_3">We need to save that Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0002_4">But... the cat is too big...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0025_5">We\'ll need something big and bold to succeed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0003_6">Hey! What about those old cans?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0001_7">Great idea, GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0003_8">Okiedokie then, here it comes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0002_9">She... she threw that like it was nothing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_10">MRAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_11">Is that all you\'ve got?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_12">HISS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_13">Outlaws!
All of you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_14">There\'s no escape!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_15">MEOUCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0003_16">It worked!
Now\'s our chance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_17">HISS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_18">Pests... all of you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_19">MRAWRRR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_20">Play time is over!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_21">GIVE UP NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_22">You pesky doughrats!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_23">MEOWRRR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_24">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0003_25">You\'ll be sorry,
you batterbrains!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">He\'s awake!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">How\'re you feeling?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Event.0001_3">Wa... WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Oh, he\'s crying...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Event.0001_5">My candy caaane!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_6">Maybe he lost it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">A truly terrible loss...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_8">Let\'s take a look around.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">Don\'t worry, little friend!
We\'ll find it for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ1_CUT1_Event.0001_10">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">I FOUND IT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_2">My candy cane! Thanks...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">What a lovely smile!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">What\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_5">I\'m... GingerDozer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_6">I was fast asleep... and dreaming... but then I woke up and saw that HUGE cat!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">It was a close call... Sounded like that cat wanted to take you to the witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_8">Witch...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_9">WITCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_10">Is the witch back?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">He\'s... smiling at the thought of the witch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">Maybe he thinks he\'s still dreaming...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">He looks so lonely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">Where do you live? Do you have any friends?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Event.0001_16">I... don\'t know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">We can\'t just leave a Cookie here on their own. It\'s not right.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">Hey, GingerDozer. Do you want to come with us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_20">I mean... 
If you wanna...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Event.0001_21">I\'ll go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_22">We\'re going to a window...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Event.0001_23">I\'ll GOOO!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_24">It might be dangerous...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Event.0001_25">I\'ll GOOO!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0003_26">Looks like we made
a new friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0002_27">You two look
oddly similar too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_28">I guess I\'m really good at
making friends, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_29">Alright! Let\'s get to
that window, together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">So... hungry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">Hey, is there a spell
to make food?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0025_3">There is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0025_4">But I can\'t cast it on
an empty stomach.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Event.0001_5">Something smells good!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">Something smells good!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">It\'s not coming from here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0003_8">OOOH!
GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0003_9">The aroma is coming
from back there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_10">OH-HOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_11">Let\'s move this
outta the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Event.0001_12">Let\'s! Let\'s!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">I smell food!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">But there\'s no handle...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">How do we get inside?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">We could try knocking?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Event.0001_5">Oooh!
Me too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">That\'s... quite a knock...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_7">W-w-wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">This is
a puzzle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">A puzzle?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_10">It looks like
an old tavern!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_11">There\'s no one here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0002_12">Over there...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_13">Hello!
We\'re hungry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0004_14">I would give my
whiskers to serve you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0004_15">But alas....
My Cheesehaven is no more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0004_16">On orders of
Sheriff Whiskerton,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0004_17">my Squeakchelin Star
tavern is closed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_18">What?!
Nooo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">Closed? But why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_20">I, the Cheesemaster, have committed an infinite number of crimes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">Huh... You don\'t seem like a criminal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">What sort of... crimes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_23">By the plucking of my whiskers, many a wicked deed has been birthed in this tavern of mine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_24">The crime of preparing a cheese sandwich sans a catnip garnish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_25">The transgression of failing to accommodate the proper granules of sand in the facilities.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_26">The grave dereliction of duty for not providing a proper grooming service before the meal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">Those don\'t sound like rules at all!
They sound like kitty litter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_28">Bad kitty...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_29">The witch has left the kitchen in the care of Sheriff Whiskerton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_30">And since that fateful day, I am not within the Sheriff\'s good books.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_31">The fault, my good friends, is not in the stars, but within my own self...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_32">I wouldn\'t be too worried about it. We made the bad kitty go away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_33">Woe is me for I–
Eh? Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_34">Yup! The cat\'s gone! You can reopen your tavern!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_35">I can... save... my Cheesehaven?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_36">We\'ll help you reopen! What can we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_37">Yeah, we\'re happy to help in any way we can...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0004_38">I have no words to express my gratitude...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Npc.0004_39">First! These fiendish parchments
must be discarded!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Npc.0004_40">These foul wanted posters
drove off my customers...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Cookie.0025_41">Doesn\'t sound too difficult.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Cookie.0003_42">The tavern could use a
little cleaning too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Npc.0004_43">My despair has
caused such shame...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Cookie.0001_44">Let\'s get to work!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Cookie.0001_45">Cheesehaven is gonna be
back in business!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Npc.0004_46">Fortune smiles upon me
once again...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ1_CUT3_Npc.0004_47">I am most grateful,
young Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0004_1">Splendid!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0004_2">Cheesehaven\'s glory has
returned tenfold!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0004_3">The tavern shines
once again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">So... When\'ll the customers
start rolling in?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">It\'s almost evening...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_6">Wizard Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0004_7">Ah, you have much to learn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0004_8">Micedom comes to life
after sunset!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">The Cheesehaven is packed to the brim with guests!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Oooh, I didn\'t know mice were nocturnal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">It, erm... seems so. My books positively did not mention anything of the sort!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Everyone?! PLEASE! Er... wait your turn, please!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_13">HAHA! Be not afraid of such a bustling night of business!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_14">For this is an unusually quiet night for my Squeakchelin Star tavern!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">There\'s so many orders coming in all at once!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_16">Okay, so that\'s one strawberry cheesecake, one cream cheese sherbet, and one strawberry cheeseburger. Sorry, three strawberry cheeseburgers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">GingerBrave! Hustle! HUSTLE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">*Huff puff*
I thought I was a good runner, but this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_19">Feast your ears upon their lively chatter... Immerse yourself in the nutty and savory aromas of cheese!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_20">This is all thanks to you, Cookies. My gratitude reaches beyond the stars themselves!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_21">We\'re glad we could help...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">Cleaning this place up has certainly brought some amazing results.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_23">Come now, my friends. Rest your weary bodies and take a seat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0004_24">I shall prepare a feast of cheese that you will reminisce on \'til the end of time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">Finally! Hooray!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_26">I\'m famished!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Event.0001_27">Thank you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_28">Hehe, look at GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0002_29">He must\'ve been really tired...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Npc.0004_30">The room upstairs should
suffice for a restful sleep.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Npc.0004_31">But it too
remains in disarray.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_32">No worries!
We\'ll clean it up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_33">C\'mon, friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0003_34">Wow, this room is enormous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0025_35">And definitely needs cleaning...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0002_36">And some furniture too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_37">Let\'s fix up this room,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_38">so GingerDozer can sleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0025_39">Alright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Event.0001_1">Whoa...
So pretty...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">GingerDozer, are you cold?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Event.0001_3">No, I\'m okay...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">The fire\'s gone out...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">I\'ll bring it back to life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Looks like GingerDozer\'s fast asleep again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">As he should be! He had a really rough day, especially because of that no-good kitty cat!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Now that I think about it, SO MUCH has happened!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">We\'ll reach our destination quite soon. What do you plan to do once we get there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Huh? OH! I haven\'t told you yet, have I?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">I\'m gonna use that window to escape!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">*GASP*
You\'re going to... WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_13">Escape...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">You heard me! I\'m going to run and live far, far away from the witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Wanna come with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">I... Well, I er... There remain much too many tasks for me to do here and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">My search for magical artifacts has yet to be concluded...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">I\'m gonna find all the fun things in the world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">I... I don\'t know... I haven\'t thought about it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Haha! I\'m sure every one of us has their own idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_22">Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_23">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_24">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">You\'re all so cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">When we take our separate paths, I\'ll be rooting for everyone all the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">After all, we\'ve made a pretty good team and some good memories!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_28">Me too! I\'ll be rooting for you both!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">I will too...! Thanks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_30">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_31">As will I.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_32">We should rest up
as much as we can.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0003_33">Sweet dreams, everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0002_34">Good night...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_35">GINGERDOZER?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_36">GINGERDOZER IS GONE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0003_37">What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0002_38">I... I didn\'t hear anything...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0025_39">Let\'s hurry and find him!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0002_40">Not here either...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0003_41">He couldn\'t have gotten far...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Event.0001_42">GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_43">GINGERDOZER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Event.0001_44">GINGERBRAAAVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_45">He must be in between
those bottles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_46">Let\'s clear a path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">GINGERDOZER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_2">GingerBraaave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">He\'s back there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Leave this to me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">Byebyeus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2006_6">MYAHA!
What a show!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2006_7">Never thought they\'d
make it this far!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_8">Achoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">GINGERDOZER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_10">There you are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">We thought you disappeared!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_12">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_13">This powder...
It\'s not tasty...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">That\'s...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_15">GingerBrave...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_16">The window!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_17">So we\'re finally here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_18">We made it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">Hooray for us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_20">I wanna see too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Event.0001_21">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_22">... The witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0009_23">Interesting.
You are far too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0009_24">Small.
Weak.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0009_25">Hmph.
Ugly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0009_26">I hope you are at least tasty,
stale one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_27">STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0009_28">Ah, there you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_29">GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_30">Urgh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_31">PULL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_32">PUUULLL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_33">P-p-pull!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_34">PULL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0003_35">Yoohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_36">AGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_37">NOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0003_38">Time for a random search, myahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_1">Do we have any cans left to throw?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0003_2">Yup! SPECIAL DELIVERY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_3">Pesky outlaws!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_4">Criminal Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_5">It\'s like he was expecting that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_6">I don\'t see any weak spots either!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0003_7">Hey, these things are...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0002_8">Pepper shakers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_9">Yes! I remember now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_10">CATS HATE SPICY, PEPPERY THINGS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_11">Let\'s try throwing some pepper!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_12">F-FREEZE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_13">Stop right there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_14">Surrender peacefully...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_15">Or face the consequences!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_16">We don\'t have much time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_17">We need that pepper, and quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_18">GingerDozer must be rescued!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0003_19">We can do this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_20">I knew that would work!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0002_21">It worked...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_22">You\'re hopeless!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_23">Give up while you still can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_24">MRAWR?! My eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_25">MRAWR?!
Spicy, icky powder!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_26">You doughbrains!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_27">SURRENDER MEOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_28">HISS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_29">MRAWRRR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_30">Not spicy anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_31">What now?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0002_32">We might need more pepper...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_33">We\'re gonna need a bigger bottle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_34">ENLARGIO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_35">MRAAACK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_36">Almost there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_37">Don\'t mess with us Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_38">A splendid performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_39">I\'ll myash you into crumbs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_40">Pfft pfft! PFFFT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_41">ACHOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_42">MROWR! Get it away!
AWAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_43">MRAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_44">We did it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0003_45">MROOOWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Npc.0003_1">GRRR...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">AGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Npc.0003_3">HISS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_4">Stand back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Npc.0003_5">MROAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_6">Where is he?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP1CH1BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_7">The small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">We need to save GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Hang in there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2001_3">I believe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2001_4">Your adventure ends here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">No! Outta the way!
We need to rescue GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_6">A freshly-baked Cookie such as yourself will stand no match against the witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_7">And the one who was captured is of the First Batch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">The First Batch? What\'s that supposed to mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_9">The witch seeks the Cookies of the First Batch... for within, they contain the most ancient of secrets.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_10">The witch\'s vast legion of minions will keep a close eye on that Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">I\'ll find a way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">You? You could barely handle that domesticated feline.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_14">Look behind you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_16">I know why you are here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">You wish to escape from this castle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_18">And here you are. Few Cookies have made it this far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_19">Now... run.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_20">Your life did not begin in the oven... It begins now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2001_21">You\'ve done enough, freshdough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_22">Erm... what\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_23">... First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_24">My name\'s GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_25">And I\'m not gonna run away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_26">!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0002_27">Oh wow...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0003_28">See, I knew he was fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0025_29">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_30">I may still be a Cookie fresh out of the oven...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0003_31">Quite literally too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_32">And I may not be the smartest Cookie around.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0002_33">That\'s also true...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_34">But I know one thing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_35">I don\'t leave my friends behind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_36">And GingerDozer... is my friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_37">A lone Cookie such as yourself has no chance of–</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0025_38">He\'s not alone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0025_39">There\'s a wizard by his side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_40">Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0003_41">And me too! GingerDozer is my friend as well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_42">GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0002_43">I\'m with you too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_44">Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_45">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_46">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_47">GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_48">Er, yeah?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_49">Do you see that faraway light?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_50">Yeah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_51">The source of that light is a hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_52">What\'s a \"hotel\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_53">... Go there and seek out the Compass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_54">It will aid in your quest to rescue your companion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0025_55">Wait! What\'s with the sudden change of demeanor?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_56">You remind me of a certain past... a past of joy and happiness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_57">A past where the laughter of Cookies could be heard throughout the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_58">A past... when life itself seemed to be composed of sweets.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_59">You have friends too, don\'t you? So you understand?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_60">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_61">Go. Before it is too late.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_62">Wait, don\'t go! Come with us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_63">Perhaps the heat of the oven still radiates from within your dough... For your heart is full of warmth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.2001_64">We shall meet again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_POR2_Cookie.0001_65">Thank you very much, First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0001_66">Alrighty then!
Off we go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0003_67">TEEHEE!
This\'ll be fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0002_68">I\'m so nervous...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0001_69">Awesome, Temporary
Adventure Team! Forwa-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0025_70">Temporary is no longer necessa–</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.0002_71">FORWARD MARCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.2001_72">A Cookie without fear...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.2001_73">Perhaps he truly can
save the First Batch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.2001_74">And you will be one step closer
to your wish, will you not?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH2_SQ5_CUT3_Cookie.2001_75">My Mistress...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">Oh ho!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">So this is the hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0002_3">It\'s so big...
Almost too big...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_4">The compass is
somewhere here, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_5">If it really exists at all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">Let\'s trust First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">We should start
looking for it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_8">Maybe someone here
knows about the compass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_9">IF anyone\'s here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_10">Well then...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_11">We\'ll find them too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_12">GingerBright, what was that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0002_13">My ears are ringing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0011_14">Yes, yes, on my w- GAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_15">Oh my...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0011_16">Ow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_17">Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0011_18">I\'m okay, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0011_19">Oh dear, the luggage!
What a mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_20">We wanted to ask
you something...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0002_21">Do you need a hand?
We can help...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_22">Yeah!
Let\'s clean up the mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">HUP!
That\'s the last one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0011_1">Thank you very much!
You\'re a lifesaver!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Don\'t mention it, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Oh, you dropped- HUH?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">\"A compass... to aid our quest...\"
Is that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">This is it!
This is what First Cream Cookie told us to find!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">I suspect that this is no ordinary compass! It just might lead the way to GingerDozer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">And we found it so quickly! But... where exactly is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_2">Ah, you\'ve taken an interest in the compass? It will be auctioned later and- OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_3">Oh, I SEE!
You\'re here for the auction!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">The auction...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_4">Our luxurious Grand Cabinet Hotel hosts a variety of auctions for our esteemed clients.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Erm... So how does an auction work...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_5">Oh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0011_6">You can ask our manager,
right over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">Excuse me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_1">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_2">Ah, I see we\'ve new guests.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_2">We\'re not exactly guests...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_3">Everyone is a guest of
the Grand Cabinet Hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_4">This hotel is filled with
history and tradition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_5">I guarantee your stay
will be most excellent.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_6">Our hotel is truly one-of-a-kind,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_7">and the best in the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_8">And I do hope you will be able to
attend tonight\'s special auction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_9">We\'ve quite a collection
prepared this evening.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_10">I wish you luck in your bids,
good guests.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Npc.0012_11">Now, if you\'ll excuse me...
Please enjoy your stay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">WAIT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_1">Have you no manners?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">COMPASS! AUCTION!
GINGERDOZER!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">... Sure, just keep
blabbering like that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">We\'re looking for our lost friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">And we need that compass, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_2">Unfortunately, 
it is not for individual sale.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_3">And frankly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_4">I doubt you can afford it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">We\'ll do ANYTHING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">If we knew how...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_5">Have you any Sugar Coins on hand?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">No we don\'t!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_6">Oh my...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_7">I surmised that you
didn\'t have any.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_8">They are used
for the auction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_9">Without them,
you cannot bid.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">There must be a way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_10">Hmmm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_11">There ARE openings
for staff positions...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_12">Come.
Chop, chop.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">What exactly are you thinking?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_13">You must work
to earn Sugar Coins!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_4">Oooh!
Are we hired?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0012_14">An astute observation!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">This is my calling!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0013_1">You remember the plan...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0014_1">Well duh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0014_2">After the auction starts, we-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0015_2">SSSHHH!
Someone\'s coming...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0013_3">HEY! GET OUT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Whoopsies...!
Didn\'t see them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Guess I\'ll 
move on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0016_1">What is this mess?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Peeling potatoes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">With magic it\'s e-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0016_2">Magic. IS NOT. Cooking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0016_3">You must get to
know your ingredients!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0016_4">Cooking is about love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">I... Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0016_5">No magic in MY kitchen!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0025_4">So... exhausting...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0025_5">But also quite fun...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT2_Npc.0016_6">Well done.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT2_Npc.0016_7">You\'ve real potential.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0025_6">This is nothing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Welcome! Hello there!
Can I help you with your bags?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_1">Get your filthy hands away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Has your ego blinded you
from basic manners?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_2">I am not the one who
showed such audacity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">Would it not be wiser
to offer an apology rather
than an accusation?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_3">You of all Cookies speak
to me about apologies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_4">The nerve...
You truly are a piece of work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_3">I beg your pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_5">You heard me.
And you know of what I speak.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2003_6">Now remove yourself
from my sight. I\'ve no time
for trifles such as you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_4">Hmph... That nasty,
no-good, ill-mannered...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Looks like those two aren\'t
happy to see each other...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">Okay... I got this...
I got this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_1">Oh! Just leave it there, please.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_2">Just a moment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_3">A gentleman I fancy
will attend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_4">Will he ask me
for a dance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_5">Or... Or should I ask him first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_6">What should I do...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">It sounds...
complicated.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">But you gotta
be brave!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_7">YES!
Love waits for no one!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_8">Thank you so, so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_9">This is for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">*GASP*
I\'m... rich...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">How\'d everyone do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Same!
Quite a haul!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">I love my job!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Strawberry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Are you hiding something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">So many coins!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">This should be
more than enough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">This place is awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">Looks like we need
tickets to go in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0011_1">No, oh no, no!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_2">The rules are clear, sir...!
They clearly state that-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">This sword is a symbol of my family\'s heritage. It is more precious to me than life itself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_3">But sir, please! The rules state that all weapons of decorative or practical use are not permitted in the auction house...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">So this is my fate... None wish to partake in conversation with a fallen noble.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_4">I- eh? No sir, that\'s not it. I-I-I didn\'t mean... I am just stating the-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Oh, cruel world and fickle fate...
Am I truly so lost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Very well. I will no longer loiter and I shall capitulate to your rules. My sword will remain here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Please keep it safe, with utmost care.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_5">Of course, I-
OH! This is... VERY... HEAVY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Cookie.0001_5">That looks really heavy...
Do you need a hand, friend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Npc.0011_6">*PHEW!*
It\'s perfectly... fine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Npc.0011_7">Oh... OH!
I remember you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Cookie.0001_6">Yup, it\'s us! We got us some
Sugar Coins. Can we go inside now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Npc.0011_8">Of course!
Here\'s your ticket!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Cookie.0025_3">We\'re supposed to leave everything here, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Npc.0011_9">Oh, candy canes and
sticks are allowed, sir.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Cookie.0025_4">\"Stick\"?
I\'ll have you know this \"STICK\" is-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_POR2_Cookie.0003_4">Thanks very much!
We\'ll be going on in then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT3_Npc.0011_10">Enjoy the auc-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT3_Npc.0011_11">OH NO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT3_Npc.0011_12">This always happens...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT3_Cookie.0025_5">Quite the tumble...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT3_Cookie.0002_1">We still have some time...
Let\'s help...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0011_1">You\'re lifesavers!
Lifesavers, I say!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0011_2">Thank you very much...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Haha, we didn\'t do much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Indeed.
It was a simple task.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0011_3">If you need anything,
just let me know!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0011_4">The auction is about to start!
You should hurry inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">See you later, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0017_1">AH! Our most esteemed,
honored guest is here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Huh?
We\'re honored guests?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">Preposterous. Know your station, simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">This seat belongs to me. Now sweep yourselves aside like the crumbs you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Whoa... that Cookie\'s got a LOT of friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Oh! That\'s the Cookie who doesn\'t like others touching her things.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I... what? Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">The entire auction is visible from here! Such a seat is only suited for one such as myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">Don\'t you agree, Clemens?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Hmph. Whoever that is... their demeanor just screams of Sugar Coins and wealth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">They must\'ve worked extra hard, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">I don\'t think \"work\" has anything to do with it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Oh? Look, there\'s someone else coming.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">He\'s the Cookie we saw at the lobby! He was carrying an awesome sword...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">He looks scary... and really serious...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0018_1">Over there... is that...?
You know, from the House of Danish?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0019_1">Well, I\'ll be...
Even after what happened, he looks as noble as ever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Seems like he\'s well-known around here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">No time to think about it now! Let\'s get settled in before the auction starts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_6">So, so many items...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">But where\'s the compass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_2">Now, for the pièce de résistance!
The highlight of the auction!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">Is it?!
IS THAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_4">It is!
We need to bid!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_8">Okay! Here we-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_1">3,000 Sugar Coins.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_7">Looks like
we\'ve got competition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_2">Ah, a bidding war?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_3">Beware, for I will not yield.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_5">We won\'t either!
3,500 Sugar Coins!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_3">3,500!
We got 3,500!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_4">4,000!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_4">We have 4,000!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_5">5,500!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0025_8">6,500!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_6">... What?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_5">6,500 going once!
Going twice...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_7">Hmph...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_8">8,000 SUGAR COINS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0003_6">8,000?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_9">This war is over.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0002_3">10,000 SUGAR COINS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_9">Wizard Cookie...!
Do we even have that many...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_6">We have the highest bid tonight!
Any more bidders?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2002_10">This can\'t be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_7">Alright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_8">GOING ONCE...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.0001_10">Huh?
What\'s going on?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0017_9">GAAAWK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Huh... Where am... I...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_1">We meet again, freshdough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_2">Why are you on
the floor THIS TIME?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_3">Is taste-testing the
floor a hobby?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">No, it\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">The auction house
went dark and then-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_4">I know, floordough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_5">The Apricot Jam Syndicate
strikes again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Who\'re they...???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_6">D\'oh! Silly me...! Of course, you don\'t know the Syndicate. They\'re crafty, fearsome bandits who know how to make an entrance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_7">Wherever there\'s word of precious treasure, you can expect the Apricot Jam Syndicate to pounce! Not even a speck of flour is left in their wake!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_8">They used to be a ragtag band of misfits... but lately, they got really good at stealing things.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_9">Anyway, listen to me and hightail it outta here. You don\'t wanna mess with the Syndicate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Whoa, you really know a lotta things about the castle, don\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">So, like, have you been hiding in the castle in sort of a safe place, all this time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_10">Myehehe... wha?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_11">Hiding? Does it really look I\'m hiding to you?! The name\'s Witchberry Cookie, not Hidingberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Huh? No, no, I just thought that it\'s really cool that you know so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Oh, and thanks for waking me up, Witchberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_12">Oh? Erm... Well then...
Ahem.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_13">Anyways...
Your friends are tied up over there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_14">You might wanna run and see if they\'re alright, freshdough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">*GASP!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.0001_10">Thanks, Witchberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.2006_15">So that\'s that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.2006_16">What sorta mess\'ll
he cook up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.2006_17">Wish I had
some popcorn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.0001_11">Hey, you guys!
Where are you!?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.0001_12">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT2_Cookie.0001_13">Better untie them, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">Thanks, Gingerbrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Were we knocked out...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Somehow, we were
all tied up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">And our Sugar Coins
are gone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">At least GingerBrave wasn\'t tied up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Witchberry Cookie helped me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Berry... Who...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">She\'s right there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">There\'s... No one there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">Were you dreaming,
GingerBrave?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Huh?!
I could\'ve sworn...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">Sure, sure...
Anyway, we should find the others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">She was here!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_4">We found someone already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Marble Danish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">We\'ll untie you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">This is one heck of a knot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">It\'s an enchanted rope. It will not unravel with normal means.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Then what should we do...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">My sword. If only I had my sword... It could cut through this rope in a blink of an eye.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">The heavy sword you were carrying earlier?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">But a normal sword shouldn\'t be capable of cutting through an enchanted object.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">*Tsk*
It is not a \"normal\" sword.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">It is a saber crafted from a specialized glaze of sugar, handed down through generations and generations of my family. It will cut through this rope like a hot knife through butter.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Sounds like we need to get that sword!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">You?
You would do this... for me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Yup! After all, you can\'t move because you\'re all tied up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">Do... do you know where it is right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I am quite certain that an employee must have taken it to the Vault.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">Okay! Sit tight!
We\'ll be right back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Where else would I go...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Npc.0020_1">T-t-thank you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Npc.0020_2">Everything\'s... a blur...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">We\'re here to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Luckily, no one\'s injured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Have you seen Marble Danish Cookie\'s sword?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Npc.0020_3">A sword...? Aaahhh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT1_Npc.0020_4">Let\'s see here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR1_Npc.0020_5">Are you looking for this oddly-shaped and heavy blade? This blade is so unique, it\'s hard to forget.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">That\'s it!
We found it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Hooray!
That was easier than I thought!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">We should get back to the auction...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.2002_1">So you\'ve found the blade!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0001_3">It\'s so heavy...!
You must be really strong
to carry this all the time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.2002_2">Strength alone cannot
wield this blade.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.2002_3">Only those of great
honor and responsi-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0025_3">Pardon the interruption,
but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT2_Cookie.0025_4">Let\'s get you untied first.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.2002_4">Thanks to you,
I have been freed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0001_4">Don\'t mention it! It was the right thing to do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0025_5">Now that things have quieted down here, I suggest we make a run for it. Who knows when those bandits might return?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0001_5">That\'s right! The bandits!
They\'ve taken over the entire hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.2002_5">... Bandits?
Are you perhaps referring to the Syndicate?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0002_2">D-d-do you know something about the... *gulp*
Apricot Jam Syndicate?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.2002_6">No, I do not know anything about them specifically...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.2002_7">But this... Syndicate is infamous for terrorizing this neighborhood.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0003_3">Does that mean the other guests might be in trouble too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_POR2_Cookie.0001_6">Maybe...
We can\'t let them get away with this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT3_Npc.0008_1">How...?!
How\'d they get loose?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT3_Npc.0008_2">Don\'t just stand there!
Grab\'em!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT3_Cookie.2002_8">Fortuitous timing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ11_CUT3_Cookie.2002_9">Begone, you whelps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0008_1">We ain\'t got nothing to be afraid of!
We outnumber them!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.0001_1">Yikes! We\'re surrounded!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.2002_1">\"Nothing to be afraid of?\"
I beg to differ... You will learn to be very, very afraid.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.2002_2">Are you ready for a lesson in fear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0008_2">H-H-Hey! These Cookies are stronger than they look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Npc.0008_3">Surround them properly this time!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_BQ1_Cookie.2002_3">It makes no difference how many of you there are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0008_1">You\'ll be sorry...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Whoa! You\'re really
strong and tough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">I have been honing my skills ever since that day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">To never...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_3">be bested
by scoundrels!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_1">Is everyone uninjured?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Are you okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_2">I\'m fine...
Those no-good bandits...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_3">Oh...? There\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_4">No bandits here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">We took care of them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_5">You must be quite formidable?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH1BQ1_CUT1_Npc.0012_6">Then, I have a special
request for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_CUT1_Npc.0012_1">Please...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_CUT1_Npc.0012_2">Please save our hotel...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Npc.0012_3">This hotel is the life\'s work of our staff and myself...! We\'ve tried to make everything perfect!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Npc.0012_4">If word got out that we cannot keep our guests safe...
It\'d be disastrous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Npc.0012_5">Our Grand Cabinet Hotel would be ruined!
Ruined, I say!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">... GingerBrave, was it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Let us call a truce on our bidding war for the compass.
I believe we have, how do you say... Bigger fish to fry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">The compass is with Sachertorte Cookie, so we\'ll have to confront her one way or the other.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Will you and your friends help me save the Grand Cabinet Hotel?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">This place is... precious to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I do not wish to see turmoil and despair haunt this place ever again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Seems like there\'s a long story involved...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Yeah...
We don\'t know the whole picture but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">We\'ll help you save the hotel! And make these bandits think twice before causing more trouble!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">L-L-Let\'s do this!
I like this hotel too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">And don\'t forget the compass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I- Ahem... Well, I too need the compass but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Let us cross that bridge when we come to it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Okay! Let\'s do this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">I thought it was an enemy attack... But it\'s only a piece of paper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">What is it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">A wanted poster.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Whoa... check out the bounty...!
It\'s really high!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Does that mean the bandits who sacked the hotel are really, really dangerous?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Is there a quicker way around the hotel? We need to hurry up and search for the other hostages!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Hm... I have a plan.
Come, follow me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_3">It\'s so slippery and sticky...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_2">Ewww...
Slippery AND sticky?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_2">Is that... apricot jam?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2002_3">A fine mess...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2002_4">This chaos prevents us
from finding what we need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_4">This sounds like
a job fooor...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_5">HOUSEKEEPING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_3">Am I seeing things...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">This gunk won\'t
come off easily...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Syndicate scoundrels...
This is unforgivable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">We can\'t just leave it like this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Let\'s try scrubbing it a bit more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">We did it! The painting\'s smiling again, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">A child? A very... wealthy child, it seems.
I wonder who it might be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">This hotel is... Well, there\'s no simpler way to put it.
The Grand Cabinet Hotel is my childhood home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Most of the decor, the antiques, the furniture you see here today belonged to my family.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Wait, so you used to live here? Were you in charge of decorating? Or cleaning?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">No, no, look at the portrait. Anyone with a portrait must have been rich. Or his parents must\'ve been the owners of the hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">... Wrong on all accounts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">This grand hotel was once the House of Danish\'s-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">What I meant was... my family\'s manor was refurbished to become this hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">What happened? Why did your family home become a hotel?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">A great many things happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">But now is not the time to share this tale.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">Now, if we shift this portrait aside...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_11">Voila. A secret passage.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Are those voices at the end of the passage?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0025_3">Huh? That voice!
It\'s the chef!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0002_3">Sounds like he\'s in trouble...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_5">*Sniff sniff*
Something smells awful!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">Ruining food is unforgivable!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0003_4">There\'s another voice...
The bellhop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.2002_12">They sound distressed...
And out of breath.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">Do they need water?!
We need to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0002_4">The barbershop...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0002_5">It\'s Miss Scarab\'s voice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0003_5">She sounds really frightened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.2002_13">... Or, perhaps, threatened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_8">We need to hurry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.2002_14">Where should we go first...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_9">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0003_6">Hmmm???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ2_CUT2_Cookie.0001_10">Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0015_1">Ooopen wiiide!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0016_1">For the love of
all cuisine... STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Hold it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_2">Hm? You\'re interrupting my mint chocolate battered fried ham with salted licorice glaze taste-test!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_3">Wait, I know you. Yeah, the boss hates your guts.
Mar... Mar... Wait, wait-wait- I know you, hang on...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_4">I wanna say... Marshmallow Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">It\'s Marble Danish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">I am the heir to... Eh? Ahem!
Release these employees at once!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_5">Yap yappity yap yap yap...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">I beg your pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_6">You\'re interrupting an important taste-testing session here, pal! Ya think you can beat me? ME?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">I will vanquish you with ease. En garde, you scoundrel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_7">Eh? En garde? NAW, nuh-uh! I\'m talkin \'bout a cooking contest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">A contest...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0015_8">A fair and square contest of skill! And what\'s the first step in cooking, hm? Gathering ingredients!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0002_1">Oh... oh...! What should we make?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0003_1">Any ideas, Marble Danish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0025_1">Yeah, you probably know a lot of dishes and desserts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.2002_7">I... erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.2002_8">I have no knowledge of cooking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0002_2">Eh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.2002_9">I\'ve tasted many dishes before... But I\'ve never made any of them myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.2002_10">If it were an eating contest, oh, I could probably...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0002_3">What do we do?
None of us know how to cook either!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0025_2">Step aside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0001_1">Huh? Are you going somewhere? I\'m pretty sure we should stay and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0025_3">No, silly!
I meant that I know how to cook!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0025_4">I\'ll take up the mantle and win this competition!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ3_POR2_Cookie.0025_5">After all, I have first-hand experience as a part-time chef! Let\'s find some ingredients to work with!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_1">There\'s no such thing as a
\"part-time\" chef! Being a chef is
about devoting your life to cuisine...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_2">I\'ve already won before you\'ve even started, hehe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0003_1">Oooh...! Are you gonna just stand there and take that, Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_1">Well... that taunt contains an inkling of truth. There is quite a significant lack of ingredients available.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_1">It seems that mostly everything was used in that awful slush...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_2">Are those... gourmet wafers? Is there a way you can use those in a dish?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_2">I see you\'ve a fine eye for ingredients!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_3">Alrighty then! I need as many wafers as we can get!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_4">Yes, yes... These will do nicely. But I can\'t cook up a gourmet dish with just wafers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_1">What sorta dish are ya thinking, Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_5">I was thinking along the lines of a potently sweet dessert.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_3">What about those...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_4">Pumpkin candies, a fine snack on their own. Their flavor may complement the wafers we\'ve just collected.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_6">I concur! Pumpkin candies, everyone! Get to it, chop chop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_7">Well... I think we\'re really out of options now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_5">I too do not see anything useful remaining.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_3">After all that hustling and bustling, heehee...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_4">You\'ll lose. Then you\'ll cry.
... I wonder what Cookie tears taste like?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_8">I didn\'t want to resort to this but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_9">I have no choice but to cast a spell to conjure some fresh ingredients!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0016_1">NO MAGIC IN MY KITCHEN!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0003_2">.........
What the...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0002_1">GingerBright... be nice...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_6">But... What the...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0016_2">This slop is
exponentially worse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_10">Hey! I poured my
heart and soul into-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_5">This...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_11">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_6">You\'re a culinary genius!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0025_12">... Eh???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_7">Savory, sweet,
crunchy, chewy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0015_8">THIS IS
UNFETTERED GENIUS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.0001_2">This is
too weird...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Npc.0016_3">Extremely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ1_Cookie.2002_7">... Weird.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">I DID IT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">I mean...
I knew I\'d win!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Npc.0015_1">This isn\'t fair!
Grrr... I\'m gonna have to call in
some reinforcements...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">There is nowhere to run.
No one to call.
Surrender now, and quietly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Npc.0015_2">Grrr...!
You think you\'re really all that,
Margarine Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">It\'s Marble Danish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Hey! We won, right?!
We all did a great- AGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">You should be more careful when
moving around in the kitchen.
You\'re lucky it\'s just a cutting board that fell.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Oh, it\'s gotten dirty...
We should probably clean
this place up a bit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Leave the dishwashing to me.
I can handle the porcelain and
silverware with care and ease.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Sounds like Wizard Cookie
should be a full-time chef!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Cooking is just like magic.
It requires meticulous research
and strict measurements!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Guys... This cutting board.
It\'s getting dirtier the more I wipe it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Hey, what\'s that...?
Do you see that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">It\'s...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">A picture?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Whoa, there\'s a lot of Cookies in this picture!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">They\'re all wearing something like... uniforms?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">They are indeed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">These are the Cookies who were once in the service of House Danish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">From your name... Am I correct to assume that you too are part of this \"House Danish?\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Indeed, but my family has fallen so low that it can no longer regain its former glory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I... Oh...
I think I hit a nerve...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">In the past, the House of Danish had amassed much wealth and authority. The entirety of the witch\'s cabinet was once the family manor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">*Sigh*
Was once... Hmph.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">W-what happened...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">Bandits pilfered our collection of treasures, relics, and family heirlooms. No one was hurt, but the family lost everything, and our employees had no choice but to leave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Oh... At least no one was hurt...?
... Hey, doesn\'t this Cookie here seem a bit familiar?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">Hm...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Perhaps one day, you will be able to meet these Cookies... Those who have left the manor...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">So this is why you\'ve such strong resentment for bandits... And rightly so, I would say.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">We can\'t let them get away with this! C\'mon, let\'s keep moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0011_1">No more!
Pleaaase!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0013_7">Run, run as fast as you can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0011_2">*Huff puff*
I can\'t feel my legs...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0011_3">Please!
NO MOOORE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0013_1">Work those muscles!
WOOORK THEM, HAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Cease this madness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0013_2">Eh? Who\'re you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0011_4">HEEELP ME!
GAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">You heinous fiend! How could you do such a thing?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0013_3">Well, it was really easy. And... because I can! Wanna see what else I can do?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">I will not sit idly by as you inflict pain upon innocents, you scoundrel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0013_4">Hoho? Such big words! Or are you just all bark and no bite?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0013_5">How about a contest of strength, eh? A deadlift contest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0013_6">Stand in front of those barbells!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">A test of strength! A big Cookie like Marble Danish Cookie has got this in the bag!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">... Hm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">What\'s the matter Marble Danish Cookie? Is something wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">... Dirty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Hm? What was that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">The barbell is absolutely filthy. I dare not touch such a foul object.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">... Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I have never seen such a horrendous object.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">This barbell has more dust on it than a swarming sandstorm. And I\'ve been in a sandstorm... A mask is vital for survival.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">It looks like Marble Danish Cookie is confused!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">He\'s become rather... talkative.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">What do we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Simple! We just find a clean barbell!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">But that\'s not all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Not all?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">I have never heard of this \"deadlift.\" Nor have I performed such a deed before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Do you even lift, bro?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">Uh oh... We\'re in real trouble now, aren\'t we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Oh, is that all?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Then I can do it!
It seems so fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Will you be alright, GingerBright? It looks really heavy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Teehee! I\'ll be fine!
Let\'s find something sturdier than this flimsy thing though!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_1">You? Against me?
BWAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_2">You\'re in for a world of pain!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_3">Keep adding choco weights until one of us gives up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_4">Or do you wanna just save us some time and give up now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Cookie.0003_1">So, only that one rule then? Just keep adding weights? Okay then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Cookie.0001_1">Those weights look super heavy!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Cookie.0002_1">GingerBright\'s gonna be... okay, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_5">BWAHAHA, the fun\'s just getting started! Time to add more weights!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_6">HA!
Is that all you\'ve got?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_7">Impossible...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_8">How?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ2_Npc.0013_9">Fine.
You win!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Shall we keep moving?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Did something break...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">Something\'s stuck...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Let\'s see what it is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Hm, what\'s this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">What an awesome painting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">The sword in this painting... It looks like Marble Danish Cookie\'s sword...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">You are correct. Painted in this portrait are the three greatest heirlooms of House Danish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">The Blessed Vase is broken and long gone... The other is the very sword I wield today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">And the last one is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">The compass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Yes, the compass, and the reason for which I attended the auction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">If only I could afford it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I would have bid on every single family heirloom being sold at the auction... Not just the compass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">The compass must be a really important treasure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">A truly important and priceless treasure that may perhaps revitalize our family\'s standing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Hm... Sounds like that compass is really, really important then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Now is not the time to dwell on such thoughts. We must rescue the hostages without fail.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Agreed. Let\'s get moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0006_1">Save me, someone!
Anyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">STOP!
Don\'t hurt them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_1">Hurt? Me...?
I would never do such a thing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">What do you think
you\'re up to, you liar?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_2">Well, the hotel...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_3">We took it over because...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_4">Sachertorte Cookie was
hurt by someone evil...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_5">And now? I\'m waiting for
that evil Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_6">But these guests kept
talking about a ball...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0014_7">So I\'m decorating the place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Erm... This has taken
a strange turn.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Why does it feel like we\'re
talking to Strawberry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">OOH, OOH! I know why!
It\'s because they\'re both shy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_8">But you\'re here now... And you seem... evil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_9">Sachertorte Cookie doesn\'t like evildoers... You are bad, bad Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_10">So erm... I\'ll erm... Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">... I take it back.
You\'re nothing like Strawberry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">I agree! Strawberry Cookie is much cuter and much nicer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Erm... This is all a bit embarrassing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_11">... Cute?
Nice...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">I... wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_12">I see it now... You\'re a bit... like me? You\'re shy too... and the way you talk is cute, like me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_13">But... your cuteness is no match... for mine...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_14">You, in the pink hoodie... I erm... I... I\'m the cutest! And I\'ll prove it to you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">Wha...? Me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_15">You aren\'t allowed to be cuter than me...! You\'re evil...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_16">Let\'s settle this the right way... By out-cuting the other!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">What does that even mean... \"Out-cuting\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_17">SSSHHH! It means what it means... We\'ll need a mirror... and accessories.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0014_18">Bring them. Now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Looks like we have a cuteness competition!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Will you be alright, Strawberry Cookie? You don\'t have to do this if you don\'t want to.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">We\'re here with you, okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">Thanks, GingerBrave... But I think... I can do this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">We need to save the guests...! Let\'s find that mirror!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_1">If Pink Hoodie Cookie here is cuter than me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_2">Which isn\'t true... but if she is... I will leave, quietly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_3">But if I\'m cuter...
And if I win, hehe... teehee... HEEHEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0025_1">I really don\'t want to hear the end of that sentence... We better win, no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_1">But... but... I\'m not cute...! I\'m not cute at all...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_2">If I lose... then everyone will...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0001_1">It\'s alright, Strawberry Cookie! Just remember, we\'ve got your back, okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0025_2">We\'re with you all the way! Here, let me conjure up some encouraging courage charms in these bottles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0003_1">That\'s a good plan! Let\'s gather up some extra bottles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_4">How can... such a shy Cookie... prove she\'s... cuter than me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_5">Oh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_6">What are you doing with these bottles... Hmmm? No more bottles for you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_7">Hehe... hehehe... HEHEHE...
I win... I know I\'ll win...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0001_2">Not on our watch!
We need to untie those bottles, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_8">My knots...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_9">Stop it...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0003_2">We\'re ready!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0001_3">You got this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_3">I can do this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_4">I can do this...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_5">I CAN DO THIS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_6">I CAN\'T DO THIS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0006_1">EEEeeep, she\'s sooo cute!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0003_3">You\'re the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0003_4">ADORABLE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Cookie.0002_7">T-T-Thanks, everyone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_10">Lies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_11">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_12">How can you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_13">Not fair...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_BQ3_Npc.0014_14">NoT fAiR!!!
*Sob*</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">You\'re so awesome, Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">No, I don\'t think I am... I was really, really nervous...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">I just wanted to help and keep the guests safe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">And... GingerBrave...
Thanks for believing in me... </string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">You helped me be brave, just like you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">What\'re friends for?
We\'ve got your back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">An excellent display of courage! Now, shall we continue on our way?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">AGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Teehee! Silly Wizard Cookie, you\'re not supposed to break mirrors! It\'s bad luck!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">I wasn\'t trying to break it, I almost accidentally bumped into it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Something fell out from behind the mirror...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">If the mirror is damaged... then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">It\'s not damaged!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">A painting fell out from behind the mirror is all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">I swear, it\'s not-
Wait... a painting?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Oh! It really is a painting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH2BQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Another painting?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Hey, check this out!
This is a really cool picture!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">If I\'m not mistaken... Is that smaller Cookie you, Marble Danish Cookie? And there\'s another Cookie too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">Our family\'s Treasure Keeper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">What\'s a Treasure Keeper?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Relics and heirlooms are quite difficult to manage. Sometimes they are damaged, or victim to forgeries.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Therefore, only the most discerning and clever of Cookies could manage the family\'s treasures.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Oh, I see!
So... were you best friends with this Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">As a young Cookie, I often attempted to play with the relics. I admit, back then, I whined and begged to see them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">But the Treasure Keeper would always give me some candy, with a warm smile.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I confess, I was the one who broke the Blessed Vase and feared a harsh scolding. But the Treasure Keeper kept this a secret.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">With a warm smile, I was advised that I myself should tell my parents of what happened and ask for forgiveness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">So, what happened when you told your parents?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">I... I, erm... I completely forgot to tell them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">This is the burden I bear... I was so afraid of being scolded, I did not confess the truth to my parents...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Sounds like this Treasure Keeper Cookie was a very kindhearted and wise Cookie who thought highly of you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Does this remind of you someone...? I feel like we\'ve seen...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Well, it is Marble Danish Cookie in the painting, but it\'s when he was a child.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">No, never mind... I must be mistaken...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">That was an interesting history lesson, but we should keep moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_1">You did it!
You saved our hotel...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_2">I have no idea where to begin in thanking you for your hard work and effort...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">It\'s okay!
We\'re just really glad that no one got hurt!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_3">But... but... I really must insist on giving you some form of compensation and reward.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_4">You\'ve saved the Grand Cabinet Hotel, our guests and staff, in addition to tidying up the mess around here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_5">How can we ever repay your splendid, noble deeds...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">There is no need for compensation. Having saved this place is reward enough for me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_6">No! I truly insist!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Gyah...?!
Calm down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_7">This hotel has been passed down from my grandfather, to my father, to myself! It is a place of great history and very dear to my heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_8">Moreover, we rabbits NEVER FORGET!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_9">I refuse to accept your refusal of a just reward! I cannot possibly let heroes such as yourself leave empty-handed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_10">I won\'t be able to sleep if I can\'t express my gratitude...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">He... He\'s really insistent...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Welp! I guess we\'ve got no choice but to accept a reward with big, bright smiles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">SO!
Whatcha got?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_11">I- Oh... Well, ahem!
Yes, yes, I\'ve just the thing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_12">Yes, there is definitely something in here of extraordinary value that I can present to you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_13">But I... I seem to have misplaced it, somewhere...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Npc.0012_14">If you don\'t mind, would you please assist in my search for it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">The only way we\'re going to receive a reward... is to look for the reward? How interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">TEEHEE! It\'s like hide-and-seek!
C\'mon, let\'s find it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Nothing here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Nope.
There\'s nothing but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">WANTED POSTERS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Any luck over there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">We found...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">Something here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">This is... a key?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_1">Ah, you\'ve found it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_2">You have found the piece of irrefutable proof that certifies the Grand Cabinet Hotel as the greatest there is.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_3">Only the finest of establishments are bestowed such a trophy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_4">The Golden Key!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Gold? Wait, so this is like, real gold?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Wizard Cookie... calm down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Wizard Cookie must really like shiny, valuable things, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">No! It\'s fascinating! Gold is one of the primary catalysts used in many wizarding spells and formulas!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_5">Yes, it is indeed pure gold. In normal circumstances, this Golden Key would remain in my office...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0012_6">But as the saviors of our hotel, I would like to present this to you as a gift of gratitude.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">OH WOW! Thank y-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2003_1">Tut, tut, tut! Things are
just starting to get fun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_2">You...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_2">Your hospitality is quite lacking. So uncouth and undignified.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_3">Of course, such traits are somewhat necessary for survival. But I do not condone such delinquency upon my colleagues.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_4">Move aside before you get hurt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_5">Or does the heir of the house wish for some harsh reprimanding like the one he received in the past?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_3">The past...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.0002_3">Oh! OOOH! I remembered something!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.0001_3">What is it, Strawberry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.0002_4">One of the portraits...!
Sachertorte Cookie was in one of the portraits!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_4">You... you were...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_5">Our family\'s Treasure Keeper...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_6">You always had such a dull memory. But bravo, bravo. You\'ve finally remembered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_7">Yes, in the past, I was once known as the Treasure Keeper for the House of Danish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_8">But did you know... I was also the one who successfully procured your family\'s treasures from the vault, with some help from my friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_6">Wretched fiend...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_7">Then that means you were...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_8">You...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_9">FOUL VILLAIN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2002_10">Your betrayal has kneaded chaos and ruin into the very dough of my family!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_9">Oh, I\'m absolutely quivering from fear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_10">Alas, I am not here for such a barbaric altercation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_POR2_Cookie.2003_11">Because, you see... I\'ve bought just enough time for my Syndicate to escape!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.2002_11">NO!
She escaped?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0001_4">The bandits are gone too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0025_5">And the Golden Key...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0025_6">GAH! The compass has
been stolen as well!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0002_5">W-w-what do we do?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0001_5">We need to go after them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0001_6">We can\'t just stand here...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0001_7">It\'s time to put an end to this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.2002_12">Such brave words.
I too shall follow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.2002_13">My family\'s honor is at stake...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0003_4">Okie-dokie then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0003_5">Time to get that compass
and key back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH2_SQ10_CUT3_Cookie.0001_8">Off we go, running once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Ow, ow, ow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Apologies for the sudden halt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">But our path is blocked.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Is there a way around?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Everyone!
Let\'s get to work!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Here we go again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">We should keep moving and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2003_1">My, my, my...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2003_2">You\'re 17 minutes late.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2003_3">Perhaps I\'ve overestimated you lot.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">There you are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">AAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">We\'re gonna end up
as crumbs for sure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Nooo! I don\'t wanna
become crumbs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Hang on!
I\'ll try and slow us down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT2_Cookie.0025_2">Ow, ow...! That was a bit of a
rougher landing than expected...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT2_Cookie.0025_3">Is everyone alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT2_Cookie.0002_1">Phew...!
You saved us, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT2_Cookie.0001_4">Haha! We\'re all okay!
That was amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT2_Cookie.0001_5">But... where are we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">By the looks of it...
I believe we have arrived at the lounge, on the sixth floor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">And to think, the Syndicate was within our grasp...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Everything\'s gonna be okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Now that we know where we are, we just need to keep moving forward and find them again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Yes... Your optimism is not unfounded.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">But I must say, you are a rather odd one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">I... huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">Pursuit after pursuit, we\'ve failed to properly apprehend these bandits.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">Yet your bravery and optimism gives me hope.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">I dare say that you are-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">Well, well. It seems I\'ve stumbled upon an interesting and heartfelt conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_POR1_Cookie.2003_5">I wonder what\'ll happen if the young master\'s new friend is suddenly... removed from the equation?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.0001_9">What are you- AGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.0003_2">GingerBraaave!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.0002_2">Sachertorte Cookie just...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.0025_4">What do we do?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.2002_9">Remain calm!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_Q3_CUT3_Cookie.2002_10">We shall rescue
GingerBrave at all costs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">She\'s... run off...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">At least GingerBrave is safe...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">Yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2002_3">Are you uninjured?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Thanks to you, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">But Sachertorte Cookie managed to get away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">If only I was more careful... I\'m sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Why are you apologizing...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">It wouldn\'t be honorable to ignore a Cookie in need of aid, especially when that Cookie and I have traveled this far together for a common goal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I guess what I am trying to say is...
We are friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">If I had been captured, then you would have done the same.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Of course!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">So there is no need to apologize. Come, we must continue our pursuit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Alrighty! Let\'s head out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Waaait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Huh? What\'s wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Shouldn\'t we come up with a plan? We can\'t let the bandits keep escaping.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">And guess what?
I\'ve got a plan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">What sort of plan...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">It\'s-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">*ACHOO!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">As I was saying, it\'s-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">*AAACHOO!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Come to think of it, this place is very du-duh-ACHOO-dusty... This conversation isn\'t going anywh-wh-ACHOO-where!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">Perhaps we should tidy up before continuing this conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Alright sneezies!
Now listen up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">The bandits keep escaping from us because...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">We aren\'t fast enough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Aaand your point is...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">We need to be super fast and catch all the bandits in one fell swoop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Tada! That\'s the plan!
What do you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">Hm, I am quite fond of that plan.
After all, the best defense is a good offense.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Whoa, that phrase is really cool!
Okay then! We\'ve got a plan-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2006_1">NOOOOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0025_2">Did you hear that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0002_1">A... g-g-ghost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">Was that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.0001_3">That voice was...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2002_2">Someone\'s here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2002_3">Let us search the area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2006_1">Myaha! It\'s time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2006_2">Time for me to
make an appearance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Oh, we\'ve a tiny visitor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2006_3">A tiny visitor?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2006_4">Hmph! Speak for yourself,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2006_5">shortstuff! Myehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Shortstuff?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">... And you are?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">AH! WITCHBERRY COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_6">Myahaha! That\'s me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_7">Tis I, Witchberry Cookie, the resident expert on everything about the Witch\'s Castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_8">I\'ve been eavesdropping on your conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_9">And I have one thing to ask. Do ALL of you have crumbs for brains?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">So, the Cookie that helped GingerBrave was... really real?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">REALLY REAL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_10">Not everything is about speed, you slowpokes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Oh? Then what is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_11">Myahaha...ha...
*Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_12">MYA! \"Eh, what is it?\"
PFFT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_13">The leader of the Apricot Jam Syndicate is using a rope, but not just any rope!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_14">It\'s so sticky, that unless you\'ve got nothing but butter in your dough, you\'ll be caught by it no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Oh???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_15">If you really want to catch those bandits off guard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_16">Then you need a secret weapon of your own!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_17">Use something! Sprinkle baby powder in the air to blind them. SOMETHING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_18">And after you catch them? Well, you OBVIOUSLY need to tie them up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">I see...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2006_19">How did none of you think up any sort of plan for catching the bandits?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0001_3">Witchberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_20">Erm... perhaps I should\'ve remained calm and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0001_4">YOU\'RE A GENIUS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_21">... Myeh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0001_5">We should do as
Witchberry Cookie said!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0003_2">Let\'s find what we need!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0025_5">We should split up to save time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0002_2">O-O-OK! Let\'s do this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_22">And they\'re off...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_23">Maybe I should have just, erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_24">told them from the beginning...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2006_25">Well, at least they\'ve got an idea now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_1">OH! The heroes who saved our hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_2">Are... you perhaps looking for something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">BABY POWDER!
We\'re looking for baby powder, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">We\'re gonna dust ourselves with it so that we can catch the bandits!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">... No.
We\'re not looking for baby powder. We\'re searching for oil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">It pains me to even consider using such a precious and important element of cooking for such a purpose...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_3">Hm, I\'ve no clue as to what sort of plan you\'ve got cooking up in your heads...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_4">But if it is oil you seek, we recently received a shipment of the finest olive oil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Olive oil! It\'s perfect!
Thank you very much, chef!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_5">Do not mention it, my friend. Once you\'re done with the Syndicate, how about I treat you all to a full-course, gourmet dinner?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Gosh, that sounds SO AMAZING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">But we can\'t stay! We need to keep moving right after we\'ve caught the bandits.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">We\'re currently searching for our lost friend, GingerDozer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_6">Alas, what a shame!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_7">Then let\'s make a deal. Once you\'ve found your friend, make your way back here for a proper meal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Now THAT sounds like a deal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">An excellent deal! Thanks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0016_8">Until then, stay safe, Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Indeed we shall!
We\'ll return one day, I promise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Thanks for the olive oil!
See ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_1">Oh! The hero! My hero!
The Cookie who saved me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_1">Oh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Teeheehee! You still remember me?
I\'m so embarrassed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_2">Of course I do!
May I assist you with something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Do you have baby powder? Because we need some baby powder. We\'re gonna use it to capture the Syndicate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_2">Baby powder...?
Huh, there should be some... but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_3">Well- the manager uses baby powder to trim and shape his mustache... I can\'t just, you know, give it away, like, what if I get fired or...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_3">Oh...
Erm, but when you think about it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_4">This Cookie and her friends saved the hotel and the manager might get mad if we don\'t help these heroes... Who, you know, saved the hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_4">Huh...
Maybe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_5">What do you mean, \"maybe\"? The manager gave the Golden Key as a gift! Do you know what that means?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_5">*GASP*
The Golden Key?! Then that means...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0020_6">HERE! Take the baby powder! This is all the baby powder we have stored here! Take it for your good cause...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Hooray! Thank you so very much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Npc.0011_6">No need to thank us...!
We\'re just doing our part! And please do be careful!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Awww, how nice and sweet, hehe!
Stay safe now, and bye-bye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_1">Oooh, you\'re still here!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Oh, hello...
Yeah, we sort of... erm... lost the bandits.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">We have returned in search of a rope or some form of cordage to apprehend the Syndicate. But it is not an easy thing to find in such an establishment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_2">Perhaps I can be of some assistance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Oh...!
Yes, please...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_3">I may not look it, but I am quite strong and my pincers were just manicured! If I cut that barrier, perhaps it can provide some length of rope?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">A marvelous idea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">You\'d do that...?
For us...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_4">Of course!
Stay here, it\'ll be just a moment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_5">There!
Will this suffice for your needs?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">Yes...!!!
Thank you so, so much...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_6">I am glad I was able to help. After all, I should be the one thanking you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0006_7">Now go get those nasty bandits!
And do be careful, sweetie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">Thank you, and yes, I promise...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Is something the matter, Marble Danish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">No, it\'s nothing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Well... It\'s just... It feels good to see someone grateful and appreciative of my deeds. It has been a long, long time since I\'ve felt this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">But I digress.
Let us linger no more and make haste.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_1">Got everything ya need?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2006_2">Guess you\'re good at something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Okiedokie, time to use this oil!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">I feel funny.
Like I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">You\'re so slippery!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">I\'m quite confident that Sachertorte Cookie\'s rope won\'t be able to bind any of us anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2006_3">See? Now you\'re gettin\' somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Is something on your mind, GingerBrave?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">I just started thinking... Why are Marble Danish Cookie and Sachertorte Cookie fighting in the first place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">They used to be good friends, right? Sharing candy, keeping each other\'s secrets...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">There\'s just something I can\'t wrap my head around...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">What, exactly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">I... Well, I don\'t understand how such good friends can end up fighting like this... It makes me feel sad.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">Maybe if we knew the reason, the two of you could just talk and be friends again?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Hm...
Unfortunately, I do not know why either.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">But I do remember one thing, very clearly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">The manor was empty. Only I remained, as I was feeling ill.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">That day, a band of thieves entered my family\'s vault.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I tried to fend them off with a sword...
But the bandits merely belittled and mocked my effort.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">And thus, here we are today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Stealing\'s bad, but...
That\'s just mean...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Grrr... We need to teach them a lesson!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">If that\'s really the case...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">We should hurry and finish this!
The chase is back on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">Hey, Witchberry Cookie!
Wanna tag along?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Huh???
She\'s gone! Where\'d she go?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Fascinating... Even I did not notice her absence.
She\'s disappeared without a trace.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ9_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">I get the feeling we\'ll bump into her again down the road. For now, we\'ve got some bandits to apprehend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Excellent. They\'re all in one place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Wizard Cookie!
You\'re up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Alright.
Watch and learn, folks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">Okay. You got this.
Just throw it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Just throw it, and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">POWDERIO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT1_Npc.0013_1">GAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0013_2">They found us...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0014_1">Those pesky doughbrains!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Npc.0015_1">Sachertorte Cookie! Make a run for it! We\'ll buy you some time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">You go first. I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">... have something to finish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">You should have fled when you had the chance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">And leave my colleagues behind? Unlike you, we look out for each other.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Thick as thieves... The saying must be true then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_5">Is it not natural to never abandon your friends and colleagues?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_6">Ah, you wouldn\'t know, would you? You would rather accuse and blame instead of choosing the virtuous path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">... Explain yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_7">Aww, poor thing. You don\'t remember, do you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_POR1_Cookie.2003_8">It matters not. All you need to remember is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2003_9">I am always one step ahead!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2002_4">This can\'t be...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0025_6">Don\'t blame yourself.
You were trying to protect us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2003_10">Hmph. You truly are a
masterpiece of absurdity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2003_11">Give up. You will achieve
nothing in your pursuit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.2003_12">Let us depart,
my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0002_1">Oh... We messed up again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">Yeah...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">But we can\'t give up now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">That olive oil really helped, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">I don\'t trust
Witchberry Cookie just yet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">Still, it was a good idea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">We should say thanks
next time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Alas...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Despite having a plan... the Syndicate has managed to wriggle free from our grasp once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">Sachertorte Cookie is really smart... and tough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I beg to differ. I think Marble Danish Cookie is much more skilled and tougher.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Things could\'ve ended up a lot worse if you didn\'t cover us when the smoke hit, Marble Danish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Marble Danish Cookie would\'ve won all by himself, even without us here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Perhaps... but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Without you, I would not have made it this far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">So do not fret.
After all,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">friends must have each other\'s backs, no?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">Hehe...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">You know, I\'ll be honest... At first, I thought you were nothing but a strangely stubborn, snobbish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">But you\'re not so bad, are ya, you big softy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">Shall we continue our pursuit and finally put an end to this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">We\'re with you, Marble Danish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">I bet the rope that Witchberry Cookie told us to pack can get us out here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">But the ceiling\'s really high up there...
What do we do...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ11_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Leave it to me.
After all, you just considered me to be, \"very tough.\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Alright! Onwards!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">Yes, and this time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">We will succeed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Over there!
It\'s Sachertorte Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">But... where are the others???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">If you\'re curious as to the whereabouts of my colleagues... I sent them off to pack up our valuables and belongings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">Aaand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">I believe it is finally time to put an end to this little game of cat and mouse now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">Here\'s how things will proceed, listen closely, little ones.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_5">I will make you stop this incessant pursuit. Then, I shall return to my friends. As simple as one, two, three.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I\'m guessing that the compass is part of your so-called \"belongings\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">It might be a better idea for us to just ignore her and go straight for the compass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_6">Speak up; it\'s not manners to mumble.
As for the compass... Do you mean this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">The compass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_7">How very astute of you!
I have the compass right here, and I will be keeping you busy until my crew is done packing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_8">Now, tell me...
Shall we engage in a little fun?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">How arrogant and pompous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Do you truly believe you can stop me, all by yourself?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_9">In the end? Maybe I can, maybe I cannot.
But to answer your question, yes, I do believe I can.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I won\'t give you the satisfaction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_10">As much as I am lividly enjoying this conversation...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_11">I must point out that everything you wished for is right here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_POR1_Cookie.2003_12">And since we have everything we need, and all parties are present... Let us enjoy this night, slowly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT2_Cookie.2002_7">You are stalling for time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT2_Cookie.2002_8">But you won\'t escape.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT2_Cookie.2002_9">And neither will your Syndicate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT2_Cookie.2002_10">Let\'s put an end to this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ12_CUT2_Cookie.2003_13">... Well then.
Prove it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_1">You will...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_10">Regret this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_2">How arrogant can you be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_3">Shall I reveal the truth?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_4">There was once a young master,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_5">who broke a vase...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_6">After breaking it,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_7">the boy thought
his parents would be angry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_8">The child told the
Treasure Keeper,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_9">I will tell my parents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_10">Please keep it a secret until then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_11">Can you guess how the story goes?
Did the young master tell his parents the truth?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_2">He did.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_3">He didn\'t.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_12">What fate fell upon the Treasure Keeper when the boy\'s parents found out?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_4">She was banished.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_5">Nothing happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_13">What happened to the Treasure Keeper after that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_6">Lived happily ever after.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_7">Plotted revenge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_14">You still don\'t see the error of your ways?
Begone, whelp.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_15">Play time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2003_16">IS OVER.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_8">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_BQ1_Cookie.2002_9">For once, I agree!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Marble Danish Cookie!
You did it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">Haha! I knew you had it in you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_1">I did not win alone.
We won, together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_2">You have given me
strength and courage.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2002_3">And...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">What you said before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Is it all true?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">Still avoiding the truth, are we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">My parents... They told me you faced a difficult burden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">That you had no choice but to leave far, far away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">In my search for you, with tears in my eyes, they told me this tale. To not be concerned with your whereabouts. I remember it clearly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">Aw, such \"wonderful\" parents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">Had you managed to confess the truth, my opinion of them may have remained unchanged.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">I... erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">I trusted you. I trusted you... and waited for you. I waited until the day I was banished.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_5">No... Even after my shameful banishment, I kept waiting, every day and night.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_6">"He\'ll come around and explain the truth to everyone! He\'ll make things right and apologize. The young master will say he\'s sorry."</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_7">Ah, the yesteryears of living in naïveté and ignorance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_8">And you? You buried every memory and lived life without a single worry or regret.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_9">The Syndicate took me under their wing, became my new family. And you, oh good heir and young master of the family...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2003_10">I am not through with you yet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2003_11">What are you doing...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2002_11">The right thing to do.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2002_12">I have caught you...
from falling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2003_12">You\'re a fool if you think
this serves as penance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2002_13">No, I am just...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP2CH3BQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">We need to help
those two, pronto!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">... I am sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">W... What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">You heard correct. I am sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">My immaturity as a youth has caused you much pain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">The fact that I had no recollection of such events has only magnified your pain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">To make matters worse, I resented you without recognizing my own mistakes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">And for that... I am truly, deeply sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">Hm. Time has passed far too long for your apology to hold any merit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I am not asking for your forgiveness. Nor am I asking for you to forgive my family.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">I wished to convey, no... I needed to say it. I needed to say it a long, long time ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">You are entitled to reject it, but... My apology has been long overdue.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">... Long overdue, indeed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">You never were the punctual sort.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.2003_5">Did you know,
young master...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.2003_6">I used to be quite
fond of you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.2003_7">Though you\'ve grown up
to be quite despicable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.2003_8">Let us part ways.
Eternally, if possible.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">Huh? What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">The compass?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_3">Look! Sacher... Sach...torte Cookie left the compass behind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0025_1">Or maybe... she forgot to take it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0002_1">Or maybeee! Maybe she finally forgave Marble Danish Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0003_1">She has such a weird way of showing forgiveness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_4">It doesn\'t matter. We found the compass!
And... well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_5">Here, Marble Danish Cookie.
You should keep it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_10">Pardon? But... your quest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_6">I\'m pretty sure we can find GingerDozer on our own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_7">I don\'t know why... but I just feel like we can and will!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_8">Besides, this compass means a lot to you and your family!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_11">... I cannot accept.
You need this compass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.0001_9">But why? It belongs to your family! Without it, House Danish is-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_12">House Danish has sullied its name by clinging onto relics and treasures, while hurting those close to the family. I will not let history repeat itself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_13">Even without treasures and riches, I, as a member of House Danish, can still offer aid and assistance to those in need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_14">Which is the path I am taking now.
Take the compass. Save your friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_15">You helped me through my turbulent quest.
Let me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_POR2_Cookie.2002_16">Let me help yours.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT3_Cookie.0001_10">Wow, thanks,
Marble Danish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT3_Cookie.0025_2">Well then!
Shall we take a look
at the compass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ13_CUT3_Npc.0012_1">WAIT! Excuse me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT1_Npc.0012_1">Phew, just in time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Is that... THE GOLDEN KEY?! Where did you find it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Npc.0012_2">Well, I must say, that it\'s quite a conundrum!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Npc.0012_3">The Syndicate has left a hefty sum of Coins with a note saying, \"Fees and expenditures for an exquisite and entertaining stay\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">... Hmph. Interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Hooray! So everything\'s worked out in the end!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">So we can... finally use the compass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Yeah! Let\'s take a look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">But er... how does this thing work?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Ah, I forgot to mention.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">Hold the compass tight and imagine where you wish to go.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Then, with a heart full of hope, ask the compass to show you the path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Oh? That sounds easy enough...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.0001_4">Please! Tell us where
GingerDozer is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.0001_5">HUH?!
I-I-It\'s glowing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.0002_2">The needle\'s moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.0003_2">It\'s pointing that way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.2002_5">That direction is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT2_Cookie.2002_6">The... the Syrup Garden?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0001_6">What\'s the matter?
Is the Syrup Garden a scary place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_7">There are dangers lurking around every corner near the garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0003_3">MEH!
We\'ve met worse! Probably, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_8">I know not what creatures you will meet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_9">But the tales of that place... They send shivers down my spine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_10">Are you sure you will venture towards such danger?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0001_7">Of course!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0001_8">No matter how scary or dangerous, our friend needs us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_11">... You are, indeed, a rather odd Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_12">Here. Take this with you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0001_9">What\'s this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_13">My next destination.
If you are in danger... Send word to this location.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_14">Do not hesitate to ask for help.
I shall answer the call immediately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0025_2">Well, well.
That was quite a speech.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0003_4">So trustworthy too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0002_3">Thanks... Marble Danish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.0001_10">Welp. I guess this is it!
Goodbye, Marble Danish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_15">Goodbye, my friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_POR2_Cookie.2002_16">May your dough remain crispy and fresh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT3_Npc.0012_4">The Syrup Garden...
A ghastly place...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT3_Cookie.2002_17">Ghastly...?
No, far worse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT3_Cookie.2002_18">I hope they stay safe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT3_Npc.0012_5">... Likewise.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ14_CUT3_Npc.0012_6">Though... their journey
won\'t be easy.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.TooHotKitchen.Story">This kitchen is always ready to welcome guests! And something smells delicious! Just a whiff of the aromas from this kitchen is enough to warm the heart. Today\'s menu? A steaming hot bowl of mushroom soup with a side of fire-grilled Jellies.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.WarmShelter.Story">This toasty shelter ensures that chilly Cookies that have stayed in the cool kitchen for too long will regain their freshness and sweet, fragrant aroma after a good night\'s rest.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.WhisperingWarehouse.Story">This storeroom doesn\'t contain the typical sort of things you\'d see in storage. Who left these strange and eerie things in here?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.LifePotionLab.Story">Cookies need Life Potions in order to stay crispy and fresh. This laboratory seems to have been made for researching methods to create Life Potions.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.StrawberryFlavorHideout.Story">The fragrant strawberry scent makes it easy to figure out which room the Cookie stayed in!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Basic.CatSheriffOffice.Story">The diligent but sometimes zealous Sheriff Whiskerton\'s office. The sheriff is determined to maintain order in the kitchen. Judging from the pile of badges and commendations, the sheriff has been very, very busy.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.CheeseStorage.Story">The secret behind the exquisite cheese dishes of Cheesehaven lies within this very cellar! All types of cheeses are well-preserved in this homely storeroom. Sometimes, it seems like small pieces of cheese magically come to life and make a break for it.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.HumbleRoom.Story">Though humble and a bit untidy, this cozy guestroom is enough to provide comfort and relaxation for the weary traveler. The creaky floorboards are an extra bonus, for they\'re noisy enough to drown out the pesky meowing from outside.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep01.Blueprint.StrangeSauna.Story">It\'s best not to linger too long in the sauna... especially this one.  This particular sauna features a root of ginseng in a hot water bath that looks eerily similar to a teapot. It looks happy to be in the sauna though, right?</string>
