  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.ManagersGoldenKeyOffice.Story">This office is decorated with the prestigious Golden Key that is awarded to only the best hotels. But rumor has it that the one in the office is a fake, and the real one is hidden away somewhere for security reasons... could it be true?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.SafeDepository.Story">Boasting round-the-clock, impenetrable security, the Treasure Vault stores precious items, costly gems, and rare artifacts of all sorts. Some say the Vault contains more treasures than the auction can handle.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.Room201.Story">A guest wearing a mysterious chocolate mask stayed in this room. The guest refused to let the employees help with his strange bag, that leaked apricot jam onto the floor and made it sticky.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.Room202.Story">A lively yet elegant guest stayed in this room. As for room service, they often requested Scarab Jellies.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.Room203.Story">The Grand Cabinet Hotel contains many luxurious rooms, but the Deluxe Room really takes the cake. It\'s so comfortable that guests are unable to settle for just a single visit.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.PassionKitchen.Story">A bustling kitchen with chefs tirelessly igniting their passion and stoves. Chop with efficiency! Sear with zeal! Bark orders loud and clear! Not a single gram of passion is to be spared when preparing meals for the esteemed guests!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.BarbershopOfPride.Story">If your icing has become messy and unkempt after a long journey, why not pay a visit to Butter &amp; Icing Parlor? This proud establishment uses only the finest of cream shampoos followed by professional drying and styling that\'s hotter than any oven. A single visit here will have you looking, and feeling, like a freshly baked Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.BluemarlinRestaurant.Story">A fine-dining restaurant established in homage to the chef\'s hometown. This place has everything! From enchanting music to a mystifying ambiance, and to top it all off, a plethora of mindblowing dishes for every palate. No visit to the Grand Cabinet Hotel is complete without dining at Le Maquereau Bleu!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.CabinetFitness.Story">Do you want to toughen up your dough? Come to Cabinet Fitness! Using their wide array of exercise equipment, anyone can become a tough Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.DustyPortraitRoom.Story">This room hasn\'t been open to guests for a long time, and now a thick layer of dust has gathered on every surface. However, it\'s full of objects from the time when The Grand Cabinet Hotel served as the residence for a very powerful family.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.OldPortraitRoom.Story">A room that has been locked away from guests for years and years. It might be old and dilapidated, but it\'s filled with all kinds of treasures. Sometimes the manager stops by and opens the door of the old wardrobe inside... what could be hidden in there?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Blueprint.PurpleJuiceBar.Story">A juice bar where you can taste a variety of aged fruit juice, from sweet to tangy, to extremely inventive. Come on in and take a seat! Listen to the mellow music and soak in the atmosphere as your week-long exhaustion melts away.</string>
