  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.IconTouch.Cookie.2006_1">Purrfect!\nI see you have what it takes, mya!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.IconTouch.Cookie.2006_2">Now tap on the Draw button!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_1">In the Witch\'s Castle,\nyou can obtain ANYTHING with these magical dice!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_2">Huh? You need to try it out?\nNya... Fine. I\'ll let you roll the dice\nfor free this time!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_3">Tap the button to roll the dice! Let\'s go, myah!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_4">Let\'s see...
Depending on the results, you can fill the score gauge!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_5">Each symbol represents Gift Boxes, Decors
Cookies, Residents, and Treasure Chests!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.RollButtonTouch.Cookie.2006_6">Once you fill the gauge for every symbol,\nyou can earn a pawsitively mya-rvelous reward!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.TripleMatch.Cookie.2006_1">Oh, let\'s try again!\nRoll the dice again!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.TripleMatch.Cookie.2006_2">Oh?!\nTry to get three of the same picture!\nYou\'ll get an even better reward!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.Roulette.Cookie.2006_1">A-mya-zing!
Now turn the wheel and get your reward!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.Roulette.Cookie.0035_1">Huh, this castle is pretty neat...
Like a glass of fine grape juice.
See ya later!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.End.Cookie.2006_1">Here are some celebratory Coins.\nRoll the dice again! Myah!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.Bonustime.Cookie.2006_1">You reached Bonus Time! A-mya-zing!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.Bonustime.Cookie.2006_2">If you fill the Alphabet Gauge within the time limit, a veeery special reward awaits!</string>
  <string name="$Gacha.Tutorial.Bonustime.Cookie.2006_3">I\'m \"feline\" good about this!
Now, let\'s roll the dice! Right meow!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.SocialIcon.Cookie.2006_1">Good, good!
You are now ready to meet the 
other Castle Masters! Follow meow!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Team.Cookie.2006_1">Ever needed some help in
your journey? Then join a team of
Castle Masters to help each other!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Team.Cookie.2006_2">You can also create
your own team too!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Team.Cookie.2006_3">Oh, and let me tell you about friends...</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Friends.Cookie.2006_1">You can help friends even if
they\'re on different teams!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Friends.Cookie.2006_2">And lastly, I\'ll show you how to check the rank of your castle!</string>
  <string name="$Social.Tutorial.Ranking.Cookie.2006_1">The more you try, the greater your castle will become! Myaha!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Tutorial.IconTouch.Cookie.2006_1">Oooh! Collections are available!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Tutorial.Popup.Cookie.2006_1">What\'s this shiny light? Tap it!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Tutorial.Popup.Cookie.2006_2">What a purrrty card, mya!
If you collect multiple copies, you can upgrade
your cards and earn Collection Points!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Tutorial.Popup.Cookie.2006_3">Wanna see what happens when
you earn a lot of Collection Points?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Tutorial.Popup.Cookie.2006_4">Look at all these amazing rewards!
Complete other Collections and get your rewards!</string>
  <string name="$Movein.Tutorial.Cookie.2006_1">Hmm... Since you already explored other areas of the castle,
why don\'t we invite the Cookies over?</string>
  <string name="$Movein.Tutorial.Cookie.2006_2">Now select a room!</string>
  <string name="$Movein.Tutorial.Cookie.2006_3">And select a Cookie you\'d like to invite!
Rent is paid in Coins, myah.</string>
  <string name="$Movein.Tutorial.Cookie.2006_4">Cookies that moved in can get deliveries through Mole Shipping!
Look at all these unclaimed packages... All yours!</string>
  <string name="$Delivery.Tutorial.IconTouch.Npc.0002_1">A new customer!
Welcome to Mole Shipping!</string>
  <string name="$Delivery.Tutorial.Popup.Npc.0002_1">Thank you for visiting Mole Shipping!</string>
  <string name="$Delivery.Tutorial.Popup.Npc.0002_2">The Witch\'s Castle is kinda hazardous, so we have some
conditions if you want to order.
Complete our missions and then we\'ll talk!</string>
  <string name="$Delivery.Tutorial.Popup.Npc.0002_3">You can earn 1 or 2 Mission Points depending on the difficulty.</string>
  <string name="$Delivery.Tutorial.Popup.Npc.0002_4">Once you have 3 Mission Points, your package will be delivered!
Now let\'s complete those missions!</string>
  <string name="$Readyitem.Tutorial.Cookie.2006_1">Now you can start the level with powerful Boosters!
Try it out, myahaha!</string>
  <string name="$GameStart.Tutorial.ChangeCookie.Cookie.0003_1">Whoops! Not enough energy I guess!
But I can keep going!</string>
