  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.001">Choco Drop Plushie</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.001.Story">A plushie in the shape of Choco Drop. It looks so huggable! And look at its adorable smile!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.002">Precision Pastry Bag</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.002.Story">It\'s said that an extra layer of icing can make anyone feel better!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.003">GingerBrave\'s Spare Button</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0001.003.Story">A spare skull-shaped button kept in pristine condition. It\'s just in case a button goes missing!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.001">Cheese Drop Plushie</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.001.Story">A plushie in the shape of Cheese Drop. It looks so cuddly! And look at those adorable eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.002">Carefully Wrapped Lollipop</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.002.Story">Do you know how many swings it takes to break a lollipop? Regardless, it\'s always a good idea to keep a spare lollipop around! Many, many spares...!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.003">Lollipop Shards</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0003.003.Story">It appears that a lollipop has been shattered into many pieces. Some say that Cookievorous Plants love these things.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.001">Hardened Strawberry Jelly</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.001.Story">A piece of strawberry jelly that has become a solid chunk. It looks like it might\'ve been a part of Strawberry Cookie\'s bag at one point.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.002">Ultra Pocket Strawberry</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.002.Story">A portable gaming device that has all the latest games, now with increased resolution, graphics, and storage! Say goodbye to boredom!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.003">Sentimental Failed Potion</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0002.003.Story">A vial of Life Potion that failed because, well, there\'s no Life in it. Strawberry Cookie couldn\'t bear to throw away Wizard Cookie\'s first experiment. After all, failures can also serve as precious memories.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.001">Vanilla Cream Scarf</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.001.Story">Wizard Cookie always wears this scarf so that others can\'t see him practicing spells in silence. Many mistake this scarf as a beard, but it\'s still unknown if Wizard Cookie wants it to be seen as a beard.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.002">Popping Candy</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.002.Story">This particular candy is said to give you a shocking bolt of inspiration once you pop it into your mouth! The side effects of eating too many of these are unknown, so proceed with caution!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.003">Wizard Cookie\'s Secret Notebook</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0025.003.Story">Wizard Cookie has learned so many spells that it\'s a bit difficult to keep track of all of them. He secretly began writing them down to prevent forgetting about them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.001">Clemens, the Aberrant Parasol</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.001.Story">The parasol known only as Clemens was separated from its fellow umbrellas. Scared and alone, Clemens was rescued by Sachertorte Cookie. The two are now an inseparable pair.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.002">Blessed Vase Fragment</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.002.Story">This seemingly innocent shard of ceramic used to be a reminder and symbol of revenge for Sachertorte Cookie. After hearing Marble Danish Cookie\'s heartfelt apology, Sachertorte Cookie no longer feels anger when looking upon this fragment.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.003">Syndicate Brooch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2003.003.Story">A brooch crafted when the Apricot Jam Syndicate was first formed. Sachertorte Cookie only wears this on extremely special occasions.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.001">Blessed Feather</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.001.Story">Feathers that seem to have an angelic nature to them. Just looking at them fills you with a serene calm.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.002">Winged Painted Eggs</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.002.Story">Perhaps the witch who baked Angel Cookie also enjoyed painting eggs. It looks like the eggs grew wings of their own, but just like Angel Cookie, they can only float a tiny bit above the ground.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.003">Young Angel\'s Trumpet</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0012.003.Story">Want to grow up to become an archangel? Then you should never neglect trumpet practice! Keep practicing and learn to play it like... well, an angel!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.001">Sticky Bottle Cap</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.001.Story">This sticky bottle cap is one of Devil Cookie\'s favorite items. Why? Because it smells like cola, of course!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.002">Fizzy Cola Jelly</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.002.Story">This particular Jelly will open your eyes to a new world of extreme flavors! A fizzy start to a syrupy cola finish, it\'s everyone\'s favorite.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.003">Well-Baked Spectral Jelly</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0023.003.Story">Spectral Jellies seem to follow Devil Cookie everywhere. Some say that Devil Cookie transforms into a monstrous Super Devil after munching on a handful of these... How terrifying!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.001">Avocado Goggles</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.001.Story">Always remember... SAFETY FIRST! A pair of industrial-grade protective goggles like these will protect your eyes from the forge\'s light and heat!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.002">Pristine Weapon Oil</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.002.Story">Oil extracted from the ripest of avocados. This rich and aromatic oil is said to help keep weapons from rusting and corroding.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.003">Avocado Sword</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0113.003.Story">Avocado Cookie has crafted an entire arsenal\'s worth of blades, but this one takes the cake! This sword boasts the sharpest of edges with a perfectly balanced weight, extremely useful for getting rid of pathblocking obstacles!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.001">Gardening Gloves</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.001.Story">Gloves are a must for keeping the syrup garden in tip-top shape! No more ouches and owies from stinging thorns or pesky vines!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.002">Complaint Form</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.002.Story">Residents and visitors run to Rosemary Cookie when they wish to file an official complaint. As a responsible gardenkeeper, Rosemary Cookie files each and every complaint in an orderly fashion.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.003">Cute, Tiny Scissors</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2005.003.Story">Rosemary Cookie strived to be the greatest gardener since her early childhood. She keeps this pair of tiny scissors as a reminder of her past ambitions and memories.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.001">Berrytailed Toy Mouse</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.001.Story">Witchberry Cookie\'s favorite toy. The berry at the end of its tail fills the room with a fruity and sweet aroma.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.002">Spare Witch\'s Hat</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.002.Story">You can\'t call yourself a witch without a pointy hat! It\'s like rule number one on how to be a witch! Witchberry Cookie always keeps a spare at home, just in case something happens.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.003">Witchberry Cookie\'s Pendant</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2006.003.Story">A pendant that can hold a small, miniscule item within. Witchberry Cookie seems to sneak a few peeks at whatever\'s inside from time to time, but no one has ever found out what\'s inside.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.001">First Performance Sheet Music</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.001.Story">Sheet music from Mint Choco Cookie\'s very first performance on stage. These pages are filled with memories of excitement and nervousness, which he will cherish for years to come.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.002">Violin Polishing Cloth</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.002.Story">Mint Choco Cookie never leaves home without this polishing cloth. A few wipes with this cloth always leaves his violin looking better than new!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.003">Musical Cocoa Mug</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0046.003.Story">A mug given to Mint Choco Cookie as a gift by a certain fan. On cold days, he enjoys a cup of hot cocoa with extra marshmallows. And he always remembers to use this mug every time!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2002.001">Pure Cotton Cloth</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2002.001.Story">Any Cookie devoted to swordsmanship knows the importance of keeping a high-quality cotton cloth close by at all times. After training, you must never forget to polish your blade!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2002.002">House Danish Cuffs</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2002.002.Story">Cuffs delicately engraved with the family crest of House Danish. Marble Danish Cookie wears these as a way to remember his family\'s proud and honorable past.</string>
