  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_1">So... thirsty...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">Ugh... Why\'s this
garden so dry...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_3">Not a drop of syrup in sight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0025_4">This garden is bone dry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0025_5">Almost as dry as the oven...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0002_6">... OH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0002_7">My bag! Oh, my bag!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0002_8">The bellhop packed us
some snacks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_9">Oooh...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0025_10">What\'re we waiting for?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_11">OOOH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0025_12">What is it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_13">JUICE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_14">Crusty... bread...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0002_15">Yup... bread...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0025_16">Anything else?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_17">OH HOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_18">Juice...!
JUICE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_19">Ha... ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_20">What else...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0003_21">I\'m goin\' back to the hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Npc.0037_22">GingerBright, wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_23">We can\'t just sit around.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_24">There\'s gotta be something here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH3_SQ15_CUT2_Cookie.0001_25">Let\'s search the area!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_1">WHOA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_2">SYRUP!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">Oh- STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">What\'sa matter?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">Not a step further!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">That...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_7">is a trap!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">A trap?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_9">I\'ve read about such things
in a book about survival
and camping.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">A camping book?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">There\'s the bait...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_12">Then the camouflage...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">And a suspicious
someone nearby...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_14">Yes... This is definitely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_15">A DELIBERATE TRAP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_16">Oh ho...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_17">The book I read
didn\'t say that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_18">Eh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">My book said
stuff like this is safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">The book I read
said that too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_21">And the title of
that book was...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_22">"Safe Food..."</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_23">...
\"Found on the Ground!\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_24">ARE YOU KIDDING ME?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_25">Let\'s go for it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_26">YIPPEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_27">He he he...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_28">I warned ya
to stay away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_29">I, Radish Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_30">Will always protect
this garden!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_31">Who\'ll I meet today?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_32">Is that you, Churro Golem?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_33">COOKIES?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_34">We come in peace!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_35">So do we...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_36">Cookies?!
Here in the garden?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_37">Quickly, follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_38">We can talk over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_39">Okay, just give us
a moment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_1">Sorry about that
back there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">I thought you
were intruders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_3">Y\'all triggered an
alarm on the system!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">You can see the
entire garden from here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_5">Yup!
Fancy, eh?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">Built it all myself from scraps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_7">All this... on your own?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_8">Exactamundo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_9">Everything was made
by yours truly</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_10">with these here pliers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_11">Oooh, a tinkerer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0002_12">That\'s so cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_13">These skills of mine are needed</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">to keep the Syrup Garden
safe and secure, all by myself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">The \"Syrup\" Garden???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0025_16">It\'s a rather... arid garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_17">It wasn\'t always!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_18">Fresh syrup used to
flow everywhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_19">The garden was always
teeming with life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">That is... before the
Churro Golem...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_21">Who\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_22">The Churro Golem\'s
been here for a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_23">He used to be
rather quiet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_24">But then the main
faucet went faulty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_25">That faucet was a vital
piece of equipment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_26">Since then, the garden
has dried out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_27">All the residents fled to...
somewhere...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_28">And now, here I am, all alone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_29">That golem will pay!
I swear it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_30">Are y\'all... thirsty?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_31">Syrup\'s a bit too scarce.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_32">So I can\'t just give it to ya.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_33">Buuut...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_34">I know just the spot to visit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_35">It has enough syrup
for everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_36">That sounds great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0003_37">This is the best news ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_38">Alrighty then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2004_39">Follow me, and stick close!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">Feast your eyes on a magical engineering marvel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">This faucet supplies the garden with fresh syrup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Er, Radish Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">This thing\'s completely broken...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">That\'s exactly why we\'re here! We can fix it! After all, I am a skilled engineer and tinkerer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Oh ho! Syrup, here we come!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">Hm... You mentioned the Churro Golem before. Did the golem break this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">Correctomundo! We\'ve been repeating history forever...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">I fix it, the Churro Golem breaks it, again and again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">That lunk of dough and sugar is really strong! And a quick runner too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_11">There are so many broken faucets around the garden... And I\'m just one engineer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">You must\'ve been so lonely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">But then y\'all showed up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">If you\'re willing to help, I\'m 100% sure we can fix up this faucet in a jiffy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_15">And once it\'s fixed, y\'all can have a proper drink to quench that thirst!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Okay! We\'re in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">Just like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">Yes, just like that, it seems.
Well... we are very thirsty too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Hooray! Let\'s hurry up and start fixing things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_20">Alrighty then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">So... what do we need to do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_22">Fixin\' something this big calls for bigger tools!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_23">The witch should\'ve left behind a bunch of things nearby.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_24">Oh, there\'s a big winding, handle thingy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_25">Yup, and looks like it\'ll be perfect for the faucet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_26">There\'s a cork too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_27">It\'ll be perfect for sealing a leak!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_28">This is awesome! I haven\'t felt this excited in a long time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_29">If you can bring me the stuff, I\'ll be able to fix the faucet in no time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">Alrighty! Let\'s work together to fix that faucet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_31">Together...?
Fix???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_32">Those are two of my most favorite words!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_1">Three...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_2">Two...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_3">One...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_4">WOOOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_5">AWESOME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">Would you look at that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_7">This is all thanks to you, friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">So this is what the garden
was supposed to look like...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">SYRUP!
IT\'S SYRUP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_10">YIPPEE!
FINALLY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">HAHA!
Drink up, friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_12">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">OH! What\'s that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">That\'s...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">Whatcha doin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_16">Gotta pull...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_17">before it\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_18">too late...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_19">OH! Are you okay?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0028_20">RADISH COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_21">It\'s been a while, hasn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0028_22">You... Then does that mean...
The garden?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_23">These new friends of mine helped!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0028_24">Thank you!
THANK YOU!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_25">We\'re happy to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_26">Let\'s save the hello\'s for later!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_27">We need to help the others!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_28">Right with ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0028_29">Hurrah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_1">Everyone\'s awake! Thanks for helpin out once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Hehe... We\'re glad to be of help...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Erm, excuse me...? Why was everyone sleeping in the ground?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_4">Ya heard about how the garden dried up once the faucets broke?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_5">Well, we can\'t live in such a dry spot. So we decided to hide underground, where the dirt was still kinda wet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">It\'s all because of that Churro Golem...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_7">I\'d bet a whole bushel of crops that the other residents are deep underground too. But thanks to y\'all, we\'re back on top!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Hehe, it was all Radish Cookie. We just helped a bit is all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_9">There\'s an ole sayin\' in these here parts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_10">If ya receive a helpin\' hand, ya gotta pay back with BOTH hands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_11">If it\'s okay with ya, I\'d like to repay ya somehow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">We appreciate it, but it\'s quite unnecessary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_13">Ya sure? Shucks, I should at least treat ya to a lil snack at least, but if you insis-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">-Well, if you insist!!! We are extremely grateful to accept!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_15">Harhar! Right this way then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0028_16">There should be some preserved snacks stored in the mill.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">Wooow! Do y\'all know what this means?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_18">The farmers don\'t just let anyone into the mill!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">It took me years to get invited to the mill! This means y\'all\'re already friends, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Oh really?
Wow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">Off we go! Off we go!
La dee da da de!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">*Gulp gulp*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">*Gulp gulp*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">*Gulp gulp*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">AAAAAAH! That hits the spot...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">Wow, y\'all must\'ve been really parched!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_6">Here, try some candy powder as well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">What is it? Crushed candies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">This here candy powder is the signature crop of the Syrup Garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_9">It\'s made from the sweetest candies that grow deep in the syrup-soaked soil! Go ahead, try some!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">This... THIS... THIS IS AMAZING!
It tastes like pure magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">Yummy! Is this what snow tastes like???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_12">If you don\'t mind my askin\', how\'d y\'all end up here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_13">I dunno how long it\'s been since we\'ve had outsiders come to these here parts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">We\'re looking for a friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">He was... taken by the witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">The witch?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Our friend\'s name is GingerDozer. He\'s always sleepy and sorta cries a lot...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">We think he was taken somewhere along this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">Hmmm...
My security system didn\'t pick up anything outta the ordinary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_20">Ain\'t seen anything either. After all, we been sleepin\' in the ground for who knows how long.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">... Oh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_22">Hey, I\'ve got an idea. Why don\'t y\'all ask Rosemary Cookie for help?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_23">She knows the Syrup Garden\'s in\'s and out\'s!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_24">Who\'s that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_25">Oh boy, where do I begin with Rosemary Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_26">Welp... She\'s the gardener of this place, a real trustworthy and hardworkin\' Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_27">Rosemary Cookie leads the garden and our community, smart and wise that one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_28">And more importantly...
She\'s my sister! HAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">... OOOH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">So that\'s why you know so much about this garden! Because you know the gardener!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_31">Where can we find Rosemary Cookie? Can you show us the way?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_32">We can ask her if she knows anything about GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_33">Well.... That\'s the thing. You can\'t really meet her right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_34">How come?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_35">When the Churro Golem made the garden dry up, Rosemary Cookie also dried up a bit too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_36">Oh... Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_37">So... if the garden isn\'t dry anymore, we could meet Rosemary Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_38">And Rosemary Cookie is why you were so determined to fix the faucets, right, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_39">Exactamundo. I\'m gonna do whatever it takes to bring this garden back to life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_40">And I\'m gonna see Rosemary Cookie again, no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_41">Hold up a moment...
Do y\'all hear that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0028_42">What in tarnation?!
The tap is broken! HOW?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_43">Huh? We literally just fixed it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_44">Did something happen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_45">Don\'t worry! I\'m sure Radish Cookie\'ll be able to fix it up again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_46">Right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_47">Of course I can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_48">The repairin\' wasn\'t faulty or anything...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_49">Nothing breaks this fast... Unless...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_50">You\'re around here somewhere, ain\'t ya, Churro Golem?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0028_1">Well, I\'ll be...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0028_2">You fixed that in a jiffy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Easy peasy, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">That doesn\'t sound good!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">Everything\'s shaking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_6">Churrro!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_7">CHURRR-OH OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_8">No, not now...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_9">CHURRR-OH OH OOOH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_10">... WHAT\'S THAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">M-m-monster!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_12">CHURRR-OH OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_13">CHURRRRRRGH...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">GAH!
He looks angry...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_15">It\'s cuz we fixed the faucet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_16">Get back, you!
GO AWAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_17">We literally JUST fixed this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_18">Don\'t break it!
DOOON\'T!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_19">Ch-ch-churro!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">You won\'t scare us that easily!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_21">We won\'t let you hurt anyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_22">This is your home too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_23">Why are you trying to ruin it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_24">Y\'all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_25">Ch-URRRGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_26">We need to stop him!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_27">I\'ve got just the thing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">FACE MY MA-geh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_29">Face my lollipop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_30">Woohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_31">Hup hup HUP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_32">Ch? Ro? Ro? Rooo?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_33">Woohoot! Hup hup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_34">Woohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_35">Teeheehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_36">Teeheehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_37">Chur-chur-chur!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0034_38">CHRAAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_39">It worked!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_40">I can\'t believe THAT worked?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_41">Why did I ever learn magic...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_42">What a show...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_43">Y\'all\'re like...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_44">REALLY STRONG!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">This is really all thanks to you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">You woke up the residents, you fixed the faucet, you even taught the Churro Golem a lesson!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">I never imagined getting so much done in such a short time was possible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Haha, we make a pretty good team, don\'t we? Nothing beats teamwork!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">... Teamwork!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">You mentioned that you were looking for a friend of yours, right? GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Rosemary Cookie knows everything. She\'ll know where GingerDozer is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">I\'ll take you to meet Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">That sounds great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">But, I\'ll need your help once more. We need to wake her up first!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">How do we wake her up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">The Sweet Heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">I... me? Sweetheart?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">It\'s a magic thingamabob apparatus in the middle of the garden that\'s been enchanted to create syrup.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">A conjuration spell? Or perhaps evocation? Regardless, it\'s one of the most advanced forms of magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">Before the Sweet Heart malfunctioned, there was enough syrup to keep the garden in tip-top shape with no hassle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">Rosemary Cookie and I kept an eye on it at all times to maintain peak efficiency.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_18">If we can get the Sweet Heart fired up, the entire garden might be able to return to its former glory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">And Rosemary Cookie will be restored to her cheerful self!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">And then she\'ll help us find out where GingerDozer is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_21">Of course!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">Alright, Radish Cookie! We\'ll help you fix the Sweet Heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_23">For Rosemary Cookie and the Syrup Garden! Woohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">And for GingerDozer! Woohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Hey look! There\'s some syrup on that broken pipe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">It\'s the Churro Golem...
He must\'ve run past here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">The Churro Golem should apologize for breaking that faucet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">This place is still sorta dry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">The Syrup Garden won\'t come back with just a single faucet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Only the Sweet Heart is powerful enough to revitalize the entire garden, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Correctamundo. But we can\'t just leave this pipe broken like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">There\'s gotta be a broken faucet nearby. Let\'s handle that before we move on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">Sounds like a plan! Just tell us what to do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_1">Three...!</string>
