  <string name="$Neighbor.0071.Story">A small kitten was snooping around a kitchen full of fragrant teas and delicious desserts when it stumbled across a block of crumbly cheese. By looking at its face and body covered in powdered cheese, one can tell that this curious feline is quite the messy eater. It\'s difficult to tell whether this friendly critter is a cat or a cheese ball. Either way, LOOK AT THAT SMILE! So adorbs.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0072.Story">Neither the fearsome Sheriff or the daunting difficulties that come with developing an all new assortment of gourmet cheese platters can stand in the way of the Cheesemaster\'s passion! This master bartender and chef is always working hard to provide new and delicious dishes to the customers of his Squeakchelin star tavern, the Cheesehaven!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0001.Story">A simple room decorated by GingerBrave after he escaped from the oven. It may not be fancy, but it\'s filled with the lovely scent of freshly baked Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0002.Story">Are you worried about Strawberry Cookie never leaving her room? You may think it\'s because of her timid nature, but once you see her cool game room full of all her favorite items, you\'ll change your mind!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0003.Story">This room is full of GingerBright\'s favorite candies. Want to pay her a visit? A smile from GingerBright and a piece of delectable candy is sure to brighten up your day!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0012.Story">If you want to know what heaven looks like, pay Angel Cookie a visit! Cozy feather beds, heavenly light from above, and the sweet sound of trumpets... Ah, what a blessing!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0013.Story">Did you hear the floor creak just now? Urgh... Did you hear that strange groan? Don\'t be scared! It\'s just the sound of Zombie Cookie waking up from its nap.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0023.Story">Suspicious cackling can be heard from Devil Cookie\'s room every night. If you take a peek inside, you\'ll see Devil Cookie scribbling on a certain Cookie\'s poster... apparently this is how the Cookie maintains its characteristic fizz.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0025.Story">Potion recipes, a new magic circle, and a shocking magic enhancement formula. This room, full of books and documents on complex and mysterious magical formulas, must be a paradise to Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0028.Story">If you\'re tired of your boring day-to-day life, try visiting Cherry Cookie\'s Room! This Cookie definitely knows how to have fun. I mean, once you find a little cherry bomb hidden in the corner of this adorable room... you won\'t be bored anymore, right?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0030.Story">A room full of snow, sugar, and ice that looks super chilly but somehow comfortable. Perhaps it\'s thanks to their wonderful friends that Snow Sugar Cookie doesn\'t feel cold at all anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0034.Story">Alchemist Cookie\'s room is where she has the freedom to experiment with combining substances according to her own formulas. But be careful, even a slight mistake can lead to drastically different results!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0035.Story">The moment you enter this room, you\'ll be greeted with the rich aroma of grape juice! The fragrant scent and Vampire Cookie telling you to just take it easy will have you feeling sleepy in no time, so watch out.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0037.Story">Cheesecake Cookie\'s room is not just a room, but a PARTY! This place is full of flashing lights, upbeat music, and even sparkles! Just look at the countless, colorful party supplies; this party never stops!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0038.Story">Judging from all the exploration memorabilia around the room, it\'s clear to see this room belongs to Adventurer Cookie. But it\'ll be tough to actually meet him, since he\'s always running off on a new journey!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0042.Story">Blackberry Cookie usually manages everything in the mansion, but when she rests in her own room, her mysterious energy somehow becomes even stronger?! Every item in the room seems to put itself back into place... mysterious indeed.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0044.Story">Werewolf Cookie fears nothing more than unintentionally hurting someone, which is why he chose a room in such a secluded place. Even if you try to visit the pepper-scented room, all you\'ll see is a furry little thing scurrying away to hide, yet wagging his tail.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0045.Story">If you follow that sweet, mellow scent, you\'ll soon find yourself in Cocoa Cookie\'s room! She always has a mug of hot cocoa topped with marshmallows ready, so you can have one whenever you\'d like. Cocoa is just the best!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0046.Story">Perhaps it\'s because he spent so many years off the stage, but despite being hailed as a musical genius, Mint Choco Cookie still deeply cherishes the stage. He never misses a day of violin practice, so wonderful music can always be heard from his room.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0058.Story">An adorable room that seems to be decorated with smaller Cookies in mind. As you approach Onion Cookie who\'s playing alone with her toys, tears start streaming down her face. Could it be the onion juice? Or maybe it\'s because she can\'t leave this room...</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0111.Story">There\'s been more than a few Cookies that have fallen for Sparkling Cookie\'s deadly charm! He always offers a drink with a polite smile. Maybe that\'s why his cocktail bar is full again today!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0113.Story">Don\'t be surprised if you feel the heat from this room before you even enter! In Avocado Cookie\'s room, there are always new weapons and ideas coming to life. The fire in this room won\'t go out today, tomorrow, or... well, ever!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0157.Story">Cream Unicorn Cookie\'s Room is graced by a beautiful rainbow both day and night. This room sparkles like an everlasting dream, evoking good memories for everyone who visits.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2002.Story">Marble Danish Cookie\'s room is where all the family treasures are kept. Look inside to get a glimpse of the once majestic Danish family!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2003.Story">Carefully selected sparkling jewelry, well-made furniture, and luxurious desserts... Sachertorte Cookie\'s room really has everything. But wait! Isn\'t that the jewelry piece that was lost a some mansion part not long ago?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2004.Story">Anything that\'s broken is fixed in a jiffy! Tightening screws, polishing, and re-connecting broken wires... it\'s no wonder Radish Cookie\'s room is always so messy and noisy! This room is overflowing with passion!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2005.Story">A room full of Rosemary Cookie\'s favorite things. A beautiful flower planter, a gardening guide, a fragrant bouquet garni, and a chair gifted to her by a certain Cookie! Even the usually poker-faced Rosemary Cookie can\'t hide her smile when she enters this room.</string>
