  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0034.001.Stroy">The culmination of countless hours of research and intricate calculations! This concoction is made using fresh grapes, said to be the fruit of the gods, but what could its purpose be?</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0034.002.Stroy">Curious about the secrets of alchemy? Give this journal a read! It is filled with meticulous records for each experiment, successful or not, Alchemist Cookie carried out so far.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0034.003.Stroy">Explosions are a common occurrence in the alchemical laboratory. That\'s why glasses made to withstand spontaneous exothermic reactions are a must!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0028.001.Stroy">This cupcake is sure to burst with sweetness in your mouth! You can count on Cherry Cookie to bring it when going to picnics with a certain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0028.002.Stroy">A cute ribbon dyed with sweet and sour cherry syrup. It is attached to Cherry Cookie\'s cloak at all times.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0028.003.Stroy">Don\'t underestimate these just because they\'re smaller than cherry bombs! This bundle of adorable firecrackers is easy to carry around for when you want to have a blast.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0038.001.Stroy">Adventurer Cookie\'s trusty old friend. No matter how risk-filled the adventure—with this rope at hand the Cookie has nothing to fear!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0038.002.Stroy">A compass is essential when going to explore lands far and wide! As a veteran among veterans, Adventurer Cookie always keeps this at his side.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0038.003.Stroy">A treasure map so old that it might just crumble by a careless touch. What could the missing part of the map have shown? Adventurer Cookie\'s eyes sparkle with excitement as he plans his next excursion.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0013.001.Stroy">A large bone carried by Zombie Cookie. Maybe it\'s best not to ask why it\'s covered in strawberry jam...</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0013.002.Stroy">A flower decorating Zombie Cookie\'s bedside. It has a ribbon tied to it, but who could have put it there?</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0013.003.Stroy">This patched-up plushie has been through a lot. The colors have faded, and it might not look like it once used to, but maybe it just wants to resemble a dear friend!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0157.001.Stroy">A glass dome containing sparkling memories. Although the memories inside may have been forgotten by their original owner, Cream Unicorn Cookie will always remember.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0157.002.Stroy">A unicorn doll that\'s sure to bring back happy memories. It was left behind by a young Cookie after playing with Cream Unicorn Cookie, but even that has become a precious memory.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0157.003.Stroy">A music box, from which beautiful melodies of never-ending dreams can be heard. If you stay a while and listen, you will be reminded of old memories, gleaming like jewels.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0045.001.Stroy">A beautifully designed invitation to a concert. Just opening it up makes you hear beautiful melodies in your head. Cocoa Cookie was overjoyed when she received this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0045.002.Stroy">Knitting with yarn in colors that would suit a certain Cookie well makes Cocoa Cookie\'s heart feel warmer just as much as a steaming cup of cocoa on a snowy winter night.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0045.003.Stroy">A cup of hot cocoa, that Cocoa Cookie always seems to be carrying around using both hands. Nothing quite makes a cold winter day like your favorite hot cocoa in your favorite cup!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0063.001.Stroy">A watering can, filled to the brim of energy from a warm summer day\'s sunlight. Use this on any soil, and sprouts will start popping up in no time!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0063.002.Stroy">The essentials of gardening! Add these hand-made nutrients to your soil and healthy, green sprouts will grow in no time!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0063.003.Stroy">The secret to making barren soil fertile in a second! How it\'s made, you ask? Well... You\'ll have to ask Herb Cookie himself!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0111.001.Stroy">This set of glasses is reserved for Sparkling Cookie\'s finest guests. Their long, round shape is said to truly bring out the refreshing aroma of any drink poured in them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0111.002.Stroy">A fine bottle given to Sparkling Cookie by a Cookie who loves to party. Filled with fresh and delicious sparkling juice, this bottle is only brought out by Sparkling Cookie on very special occasions for a sip or two.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0111.003.Stroy">The cork belonging to the very first bottle opened at the bar. It holds a great amount of sentimental value to Sparkling Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0044.001.Stroy">A must-have for dealing with tangled fur after a long night\'s sleep. This quality brush tidies up even the nastiest tangles with ease!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0044.002.Stroy">A necklace given by a certain someone to Werewolf Cookie, as he left his village. It is filled with a desire to grow stronger.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0044.003.Stroy">A leather choker with spikes, made for someone who wishes to highlight their fierce nature. Werewolf Cookie often considers using it to keep others away but always ends up putting it back down. Maybe deep down,  he wants someone to come close.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0035.001.Stroy">The juice inside this glass gives off a captivating aroma. How about a sip? It is said to greatly improve your mood.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0035.002.Stroy">Grape juice extracted from nothing but the freshest, sweetest, and tastiest of grapes. Even Vampire Cookie saves this vintage for very special occasions.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0035.003.Stroy">With this, you can make grape juice in your own room! This all-purpose extractor takes care of everything from the ripening to juice extraction, as long as you put the grapes inside first. You don\'t need to ask—of course Vampire Cookie has one of these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0042.001.Stroy">Late at night, Blackberry Cookie walks down the long, dark corridors, holding this candle to light up the surroundings.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0042.002.Stroy">A notebook with every page filled from edge to edge with minuscule memos of things to do. Most appear to have been completed, except one of the oldest entries that still seems to be unfinished.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0042.003.Stroy">What good is a notebook without a quill and ink to write things in it! Blackberry Cookie uses these to jot down tomorrow\'s tasks before going to bed.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0058.001.Stroy">Onion Cookie\'s favorite doll. Hugging it makes you feel cozy and warm inside.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0058.002.Stroy">Doors open on their own, clocks turn backwards, and strange noises echo throughout the hallways. Onion Cookie buries her face in the pillow, hoping for it all to stop. Even going close to this soaked pillow is enough to make any Cookie tear up themselves.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0058.003.Stroy">Onion Cookie tried hard to fold her pajamas neatly. Although the result is a bit disheveled, we all know she did her best, and that\'s more than enough!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0037.001.Stroy">An opulent, decadent cheesecake-scented perfume. It is the fragrance of choice for Cheesecake Cookie when she goes to parties.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0037.002.Stroy">A cheesecake-shaped jewelry box. This is where Cheesecake Cookie keeps her most cherished necklace.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0037.003.Stroy">A purse belonging to Cheesecake Cookie, for whom lack of Coins has never been a problem. It feels like the purse itself might be worth more than the Coins it is made to contain.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0030.001.Stroy">These cute earmuffs are warmer than they seem, and they make you feel better when you\'re lonely. Snow Sugar Cookie always wears a pair.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0030.002.Stroy">One flick of the magic wand, and a myriad of beautiful snowflakes fill the air! This never-melting snowflake is said to be one of Snow Sugar Cookie\'s personal keepsakes. Just looking at it makes you feel at ease.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0030.003.Stroy">A snow globe with a tiny Snow King inside. There are few things more precious than a tiny copy of your dearest friend!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2004.001.Stroy">A band used to keep Radish Cookie\'s unruly hair in place. It makes sure that no hair gets in the way while doing repairs.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2004.002.Stroy">Potpourri, given to Radish Cookie by a special Cookie. The aroma makes everyone nearby relaxed and comfortable.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2004.003.Stroy">A pack filled with Radish Cookie\'s most well-used tools. The marks left on some of them show how much effort the Cookie puts into her work.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.AuctionRoom001.Title">100 Carat Chandelier</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.AuctionRoom001.Info">This chandelier is made from the purest, brilliant jewel ring, that reflects light around the auction house in the most beautiful pattern. It might just be even more valuable than any other items in the auction house...</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.AuctionRoom002.Info">This stage kind of looks like a box.
Could it be a jewelry case?</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.AuctionRoom003.Info">Wait up! That pattern we saw earlier
is here as well!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.AuctionRoom004.Info">It\'s too damaged to see the face.
Who could it be?</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.Penthouse001.Title">Cozy Den</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.Penthouse001.Info">A cozy resting spot with soft pillows. It seems like Sachertorte Cookie was here, reading a book as she waited for someone.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.Penthouse002.Info">It\'s a piece of sheet music
belonging to a violinist
who visited the
hotel a long time ago!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.Penthouse003.Info">Mhm! There\'s tasty
juice everywhere!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep02.Penthouse004.Info">This black tea... is still warm...</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep03.SweetHeart001.Title">No Entry Sign</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep03.SweetHeart001.Info">There\'s a small warning sign that says no entry except for Rosemary Cookie and Radish Cookie. Seeing how shiny the screw handle is from use, you can imagine how often the two Cookies have been in and out of this room.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep03.SweetHeart002.Info">There\'s a wonderful vanilla scent
coming from the flowers...!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep03.SweetHeart003.Info">You can measure sweetness?
That\'s so cool!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep03.SweetHeart004.Info">All the Witch\'s stuff is so huge!</string>
