  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.001.Story">A lollipop-style hot air balloon with a muffin basket. Just a bit more hot air and it could probably take off to the skies!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.002.Story">A table filled with snacks prepared by GingerBright! Look at all those jelly beans!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.003.Story">A swing installed on a branch of a hardcandy tree. Anyone riding this would end up smiling brightly!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.004.Story">A puffy muffin chair. Sitting on this is bound to let you completely relax.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Hanger.005.Story">Fluffy cotton candy bushes. Let\'s give a room a softer vibe with these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.006.Story">A bush made from cotton candy with sprinkles in it. It\'s so fluffy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.007.Story">A candy snail with a spiral pattern on its shell. Let\'s give it a place to live comfortably.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Floor.008.Story">This little bear is always invited to GingerBright\'s snack time. After all, a tasty treat is better enjoyed together with friends!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Ceil.001.Story">A piñata in the shape of a candy. Who wouldn\'t like to have this?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Ceil.002.Story">A chandelier in the shape of a lollipop. It will surely suit any room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Wall.001.Story">A cloud with a rainbow to decorate rooms with. Where should we place this?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Wall.002.Story">A miniature hot air balloon! While a bit too small to ride, it\'d make for a nice decoration piece in one of the rooms.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Rug.001.Story">A pretty carpet with edges of soft cream and tiny lollipop decorations on top.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.WP.001.Story">This wallpaper is sure to brighten anyone\'s mood as they enter the room. You feel energized just looking at it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0003.Deck.001.Story">Lovely pink grass grows on this carpet. Now you can jump around without hurting your feet!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Floor.001.Story">A book of notes kept by Wizard Cookie. It contains details on countless experiments studying potions... but it is way too difficult to comprehend.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Floor.002.Story">A pile of books and scrolls containing research on powerful magicks. However, they need to be deciphered, as the texts are written in the wizards\' language.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Floor.003.Story">A mystical tome. The runes inscribed within are foreign to you, yet somehow you feel like you can understand what they say. Flipping through the pages, you feel like you learn new things about potionbrewing.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Floor.004.Story">An inkwell imbued with a handy enchantment, causing it to never run out of ink!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Floor.005.Story">A magical candy, used as an arcane focus for Wizard Cookie\'s wand.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Ceil.001.Story">A suncatcher shaped like a star. Hang this in a room to give it a more magical feel!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Ceil.002.Story">A ceiling lamp shaped like a planet. If you look closer, you can make out surprisingly intricate details!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Wall.001.Story">Protection spells have been engraved onto this bookcase, most likely to guard ancient secrets from nosy onlookers.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Wall.002.Story">A window with a view of falling stars on a night sky. Looking out through this is one of Wizard Cookie\'s methods of choice to relax after a long day spent studying.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Wall.003.Story">Traces of thaumaturgical research. Putting these on your wall is sure to impress other Cookies with your superior intellect!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Wall.004.Story">A hat belonging to Wizard Cookie. If you ask nicely, maybe you get to try it on!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Rug.001.Story">Magic circles, drawn on the floor with chalk. They draw magical energy from nearby leylines, allowing for the practice and studying of more powerful spells.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Hanger.001.Story">A star-filled piece of decoration that might once have adorned a witch\'s wrist. For a Cookie, though, it works perfect as a garland!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper featuring the Milky Way. Enchanted with astrological magic, the constellations match those seen in the night sky above where it is located.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0025.Deck.001.Story">A magical flooring with a star pattern.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.001.Story">A bed that\'s fluffy, soft, and even perfect for hiding from the outside world! I could stay in this forever!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.002.Story">While a bit too large to carry around like a regular Game Berry console, the large screen makes it easier to play together with a friend.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.003.Story">A fridge colored like strawberry milk. Better keep one around to keep your favorite drinks refrigerated.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.004.Story">A strawberry lollipop, repurposed into a floor lamp. Perfect for when you want to give a room a sweeter atmosphere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.005.Story">A cute strawberry sofa, perfect for resting in any room you place it in.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.006.Story">A small chair. Simple, yet does exactly what it\'s supposed to.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.007.Story">A large keyboard, with keys so large it takes some effort to push the keys down!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Floor.008.Story">A large strawberry-themed mouse, that now functions as a decorative piece.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Wall.001.Story">A window with a great view of the lush strawberry vines outside. Strawberry Cookie likes to leave the curtains open at all times.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Wall.002.Story">An old diskette, filled with all the classics! This one has been decorated with stickers and put in a place where everyone can see.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Wall.003.Story">A cute shelf to display all your favorite things!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Hanger.001.Story">A garland with spring flowers. Who wouldn\'t like this hanging on their wall?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Rug.001.Story">This carpet feels like walking on clouds!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper with small strawberries painted on it. The sweet spring scent is positively mouth-watering!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0002.Deck.001.Story">Walk on this sunkissed floor, and you will feel the grass tickle your toes!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.001.Story">An imposing office desk that has been passed down through generations. It now belongs to Marble Danish Cookie, who uses it for work.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.002.Story">An aviary companion that has accompanied Marble Danish Cookie since a young age. Just how old could it be...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.003.Story">A white chocolate chess piece designed in traditional House Danish style. This one can move across the board by jumping over other pieces.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.004.Story">A dark chocolate chess piece designed in traditional House Danish style. This one can move across the board in an L-shape.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.005.Story">Armor belonging to a valorous knight. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.006.Story">A flag bearing the insignia of House Danish.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Floor.007.Story">This one is bound to contain treasure! ... If only we had a key to open it with.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Wall.001.Story">A decorative piece, containing a shield bearing the House Danish family crest. The shield\'s condition is pristine, as it has never actually been worn in combat.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Wall.002.Story">A display of various swords commissioned by a master blacksmith. You can tell by their gleam that someone is taking good care of them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Wall.003.Story">A medal symbolizing service to House Danish. Hang it up with pride!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Wall.004.Story">Round picture frames containing portraits of Cookies. Let\'s hang them up somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Wall.005.Story">A beautiful picture frame. It probably looks great no matter where you place it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Rug.001.Story">A carpet with the insignia of House Danish embroidered onto it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.Deck.001.Story">A floor giving a visual definition of \"elegance.\" This can give any room a dignified feel.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2002.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper with a subtle gold leaf pattern. It feels like it would suit the mansion of an old-fashioned aristocratic family.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.001.Story">An enchanting canopy bed. A very cherished piece of furniture for Sachertorte Cookie, it\'s hard not to look fancy lying down in this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.002.Story">A spiral staircase with elegant curves. Make sure to watch your step as you use it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.003.Story">A luxuriously decorated chocolate table. With this at the party, it might just become the center of attention!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.004.Story">A floor lamp that looks like a muffin impaled on a golden fork. Everyone would like to have one of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.005.Story">An expensive-looking umbrella stand. This will make any guest impressed!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.006.Story">An atmospheric lamp. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.007.Story">A chair shaped like an upside-down muffin cup. What a find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.008.Story">A vase containing beautiful flowers. This will look great wherever you put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Floor.009.Story">A place to put your finest shoes. Now everyone can admire your fashion even when you\'re not wearing them!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Ceil.001.Story">A chandelier smelling faintly of apricot jam. The soft light gives any room a sophisticated atmosphere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Wall.001.Story">A well-hidden safe. Rumors say that Sachertorte Cookie is storing something very valuable inside.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Wall.002.Story">A place used to \"store\" golden daggers. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Rug.001.Story">A soft fur carpet. It feels amazing to walk on!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.Deck.001.Story">A beautiful red floor. It\'s easy to lose track of time staring at the intricate pattern.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2003.WP.001.Story">A wall with red flowers embroidered onto it. If you get closer, you can smell a faint scent of apricot jam.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.001.Story">A bed within an intricately designed egg. After a good night\'s sleep on top of the feathers inside, you\'ll feel like you\'ve been baked again!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.002.Story">This statue is calmly waiting for something. I wonder what that something could be!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.003.Story">These gates, surprisingly not made out of candy pearls, are said to open up to any Cookie with a pure and kind heart.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.004.Story">A statue of an angel tooting a horn. With this around, any Cookie would feel welcome!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.005.Story">A statue of an angel holding a star. With this around, any Cookie would feel blessed!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.006.Story">A pillar with a burning flame on top. It brings both comfortable warmth and pleasant light!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Floor.007.Story">Feathers of an angel. These are said to bring great luck to anyone holding them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Wall.001.Story">A portal that only can be entered by Cookies who have opened the gates of heaven. If you look closely, you can see blessed light shining in the distance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Wall.002.Story">There\'s no better place to rest and absorb sunlight than on top of the clouds.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Wall.003.Story">The soft, fluffy clouds make the long wait for the next game of fetch bearable.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Ceil.001.Story">A winged Bear Jelly. It both watches over you and judges your deeds, so you better not do anything naughty!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Ceil.002.Story">A ceiling light designed to look like a cloud. You could position it so that the sun rays give emphasis to your favorite belongings!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Rug.001.Story">A circular carpet with a star in the middle. Let\'s find a place for it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper with feathers floating in the wind. Maybe one of them belongs to Angel Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0012.Deck.001.Story">Angel Cookie prepared a special kind of floor, to let you find out how it feels to literally walk on a cloud!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.001.Story">Devil Cookie\'s carefully constructed bottle rocket. It\'s decorated with the Cookie\'s favorite stickers!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.002.Story">A magnificent chair, worthy of an archdevil. How could Devil Cookie settle for anything less?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.003.Story">An imp statue featuring a large dice. Let the dies be cast!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.004.Story">An imp statue featuring dessert sculptures. It makes you feel a bit peckish.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.005.Story">A piñata with its contents spilled out. Seems like you missed out on all the fun!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.006.Story">A fallen-over candle. Just make sure the fire doesn\'t spread!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.007.Story">A candle with an ever-burning flame. Perfect for long nights spent reading books in the dark.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Floor.008.Story">Crayons and paper to draw on, for when you want an outlet for your sudden bursts of inspiration.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Wall.001.Story">A dartboard made out of a large bottle cap. It makes a satisfying sound when you hit the mark.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Wall.002.Story">A poster featuring Angel Cookie, with some... \"creative touch-ups\" by Devil Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Ceil.001.Story">A chandelier modeled after Devil Cookie\'s devil form. The crimson flames seem to never go out!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Ceil.002.Story">A bass guitar able to produce cool, dark tunes. Is someone practicing to perform in a band...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Rug.001.Story">A carpet that is specially made to go with burning decors.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.WP.001.Story">Being surrounded by flames is a must to make a devil feel at home! This wallpaper has a zigzag pattern to accommodate such desires.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0023.Deck.001.Story">While it looks extremely hot, the floor isn\'t actually lava!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.001.Story">A beautiful flower tree, growing out of a teapot filled with sweet syrup. It was lovingly grown from a weak sapling by Rosemary Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.002.Story">If you try to watch all the different mystical species of plants in the garden, you\'ll end up losing track of time.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.003.Story">A table used by Rosemary Cookie to trim messy leaves from the garden plants. This one looks very pleased with the result!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.004.Story">A chair that was given as a gift by a certain Cookie. Let\'s find a fitting place for it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.005.Story">A slightly overgrown bookshelf, filled with plants and books filled with information on said plants.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.006.Story">This watering can has a sprout growing out of it. If that isn\'t a sign of effectiveness, I\'m not sure what is.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Floor.007.Story">A book detailing various interesting botany facts. I can\'t wait to start reading this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Ceil.001.Story">A ceiling light with leaf-shaped crystals. It makes you feel like sunlight is shining down through tree crowns above.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Ceil.002.Story">A garland with dried flowers hanging from it. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Wall.001.Story">A large window that opens to a beautiful view of the Syrup Garden, giving you peace of mind.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Wall.002.Story">Shears used for trimming plants and greenery. Maybe someone will put these to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Wall.003.Story">Shelves decorated with seedlings. Let\'s put this up someplace nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Rug.001.Story">A round rug made out of rattan. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.Deck.001.Story">The unprocessed stones used as floor tiles gives the room a more natural look.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2005.WP.001.Story">A wood wall painted in the color of fresh spring grass. It makes you feel like you\'re in the middle of a tranquil garden.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.001.Story">A telescope that has been modified and altered multiple times. It is now used to watch over every corner of the Syrup Garden.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.002.Story">A workbench used by Radish Cookie to draw blueprints and make plans. Does that Cookie ever rest?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.003.Story">A large tea cup decorated with a rosemary pattern.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.004.Story">Why have a toolbox when a can does the trick just as well?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.005.Story">A seamless blend of balance, style, and performance. Climbing this feels like ascending into the clouds.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.006.Story">A chair made out of half a radish. Anyone would love to have one of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Floor.007.Story">A hanger that makes a funny noise when you adjust the angle.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Wall.001.Story">This giant belt was discovered by Radish Cookie during a daily walk through the garden.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Wall.002.Story">A window giving easy access to view the garden outside. With this, nothing will go unnoticed!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Hanger.001.Story">Multiple notes filled with possibilities. So much to do, but so little time!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Hanger.002.Story">A set of differently-sized wrenches. Let\'s put these somewhere they come to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Ceil.001.Story">A ceiling light made from half of a radish. It is perfect for making a room feel closer to nature.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Rug.001.Story">A miniature garden with plants from the Syrup Garden. It is maintained by an automatic system giving the plants nutritious syrup at regular intervals.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.WP.001.Story">This wall is perfect for hanging things on. The slight amount of rust does not seem to have affected its sturdiness.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2004.Deck.001.Story">A floor that can take heavy tools being dropped on it. Because of that, I recommend placing it in the room of a hard-working Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.001.Story">A movable stage, custom-made for Mint Choco Cookie. It even has soundproofing included!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.002.Story">A table with a portrait of Cocoa Cookie on it. Just looking at it gives a warm feeling inside, not quite unlike a warm cup of cocoa.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.003.Story">A violin case with a letter from a fan inside. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.004.Story">A table with two cups. It seems someone was invited for some warm drinks.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.005.Story">A beautiful music stand. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Floor.006.Story">A small cupcake-shaped stool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Ceil.001.Story">Gorgeous curtains, seemingly transported from a concert hall. With these, even practice sessions feel like the real thing!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Wall.001.Story">A cabinet containing some of Mint Choco Cookie\'s happiest memories. Let\'s help make some more.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Wall.002.Story">A window with a view of beautiful melodies. But Mint Choco Cookie\'s music outshines even the brightest stars in the sky.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Wall.003.Story">A box seat from a concert hall. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Wall.004.Story">The bow of a violin. Let\'s hang it somewhere as decoration.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Rug.001.Story">A carpet created with soft down. Who wouldn\'t like this in their room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Hanger.001.Story">Curtains frequently used as stage decoration. But now, you can place them wherever you want!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.Deck.001.Story">Floor with a sprinkle pattern. The mint fragrance coming from it feels fresh as you breathe in!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0046.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper with stripes resembling musical staves and notes. What happens if we play those notes?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.001.Story">A forge used for creating weapons. The blazing flames melt down any materials put inside, creating incredible weaponry.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.002.Story">An anvil that can be used to shape steel. This has been used by Avocado Cookie to make equipment for countless Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.003.Story">A tank used to cool down hot metals. It is coated with a special oil and is resistant to extreme heat.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.004.Story">A display of crafted equipment. One day, these may come to good use in the hands of a brave adventurer!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.005.Story">A wooden barrel used to store crafted weapons. If you want one, just pull it out without breaking the barrel.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.006.Story">A simple chair to rest on. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Floor.007.Story">A pile of roll cake logs. They have been kept dry, so they are easy to use as fuel for any fire.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Ceil.001.Story">Heavy iron chains. What a find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Ceil.002.Story">A hook, hanging from the ceiling by a chain.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Wall.001.Story">Too heavy for most Cookies to even lift. I wonder what happens if worn by someone strong enough to even snap their fingers?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Wall.002.Story">A window lit up with the light of forge fires. It seems someone is hard at work.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Wall.003.Story">A simple torch. Put it on a wall to light up the dark.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Rug.001.Story">A sturdy carpet made out of avocado skin. The material is so durable that it\'s sometimes used for reinforcing armor.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.WP.001.Story">A wall that has been exposed to the heat of a furnace for a long time. Be careful, touching it might result in burns!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0113.Deck.001.Story">This floor has turned yellow by the heat of the forge. Watch out for sudden sparks flying around!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.001.Story">Your mouth will explode with sweetness with just a single bite! ... Hopefully not in that way though.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.002.Story">Turn the handle on the side and receive a startling surprise! I hope you aren\'t disappointed it didn\'t explode.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.003.Story">If you fled seeing the lit fuse, you are a victim of Cherry Cookie\'s prank! It\'s just for show!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.004.Story">A drawer with a cherry bomb on top. Is it purely decorative, or is it a very effective morning alarm? Only one way to find out!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.005.Story">A pile of firecrackers. Putting them in a room is sure to make it a bit more festive! Just keep it away from open flames.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.006.Story">Confetti from firecrackers. Throw these into the air over and over again, and the party never stops!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Floor.007.Story">Solid fences made out of candy. Suited for keeping things out (or in).</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Ceil.001.Story">This used to be a bouquet of balloons, but most seem to have popped.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Ceil.002.Story">A bouquet of balloons, tied to a star candy so that they don\'t fly away.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Wall.001.Story">A broken window. Maybe all those cherry firecrackers warrant using sturdier glass.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Wall.002.Story">A picture frame with broken glass. Let\'s be a bit careful when tossing bombs around indoors!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Wall.003.Story">Pictures capturing some of Cherry Cookie\'s fondest memories. Let\'s hang these up somewhere they can easily be seen!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Hanger.001.Story">A decorative ribbon. All Cookies would like to have this hanging in their room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.WP.001.Story">A cute wallpaper made to resemble cherry firecrackers exploding!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0028.Deck.001.Story">A cute, pink floor with a star pattern.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.001.Story">With this table, you don\'t need to worry about friends suddenly showing up. It comes prepared with delicious cocktails and finger food for everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.002.Story">A bucket that keeps your bottles at the optimal temperature. You just need to fill it with ice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.003.Story">An award given only to the best of the best in the bartending industry.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.004.Story">A neat table reserved for fine guests. Now all that\'s left is someone to invite!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.005.Story">A nice chair with a footrest. What a nice find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.006.Story">A green jelly chair. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.007.Story">A lamp shaped like a glass of lime juice. It can bring any room refreshing light!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.008.Story">A lamp shaped like a glass of lemon juice. It can bring any room refreshing light!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Floor.009.Story">A stylish pot. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Ceil.001.Story">A high-class chandelier. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Ceil.002.Story">A yellow neon sign. Just looking at it makes your mouth tingle.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Wall.001.Story">A large shelf with fancy bottles containing a wide assortment of beverages. With all these to choose from, there\'s no doubt you can get your favorite cocktail made!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Wall.002.Story">A bright yellow window. If you look closely, you can see bubbles slowly moving to the top.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.WP.001.Story">To no one\'s surprise, Sparkling Cookie went for simplicity when selecting wallpaper. After all, your focus should be on the glass in front of you, and especially the drink within it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0111.Deck.001.Story">This floor carpet is so soft you\'ll feel less tired with each step you take. With this, you will definitely be able to have a great time.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.001.Story">A bed made out of a candlestick once used by the witches. It is now where Blackberry Cookie sleeps.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.002.Story">While very old, this closet does not show any signs of wear or tear. Inside are multiples of the same outfit.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.003.Story">A neat table, perfect for tea time.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.004.Story">A purple chair with laces as decoration. It looks neat, yet comfortable at the same time.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.005.Story">Blackberry Cookie\'s preferred means of avoiding direct sunlight.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.006.Story">A mood light giving off a comfortable amount of light when turned on. Any Cookie would like to have this in their room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Floor.007.Story">A lantern containing a blue flame. Let\'s place it somewhere fitting!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Ceil.001.Story">A candle-filled chandelier with soft blue flames. It doesn\'t seem to be ordinary fire.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Wall.001.Story">The silver moonlight shines through this window, making it a perfect spot to wonder about the whereabouts of a certain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Wall.002.Story">A photograph capturing an old memory. If only...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Wall.003.Story">A picture of a young Cookie. How time has passed...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Wall.004.Story">Small portraits placed on top of a shelf. Let\'s put this somewhere it can be seen!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Rug.001.Story">A beautiful lace-trimmed carpet. Simply putting it in a room makes it look more elegant.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.WP.001.Story">A wall that probably could make the messiest room look orderly. *Ahem* N-not that I would know anything about that.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0042.Deck.001.Story">A floor with an antique pattern giving the room an impression of being neat and organized.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.001.Story">A bed with Onion Rabbit quietly sleeping in it. Here even Cookies afraid of the dark can rest at night without worries.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.002.Story">How strange... This kind of wardrobe isn\'t supposed to have automatic doors. But why are the doors open again every morning...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.003.Story">An in-progress book about a timid Cookie. Onion Cookie says it\'s her favorite story.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.004.Story">A drawer with a teddy bear and an onion lamp. This lamp stays lit at night, just in case.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.005.Story">Blocks to play with. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.006.Story">A secret dairy. Let\'s keep it in its owner\'s room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.007.Story">Fairy tale books that seem to have been read many times.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Floor.008.Story">A small chair, shaped like a macaron. What a nice find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Ceil.001.Story">Cute toys hanging from the ceiling. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Wall.001.Story">An old and worn portrait. The tear makes it unclear whom it depicts, but the remaining fragments bear some resemblance to a certain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Wall.002.Story">A window decorated with transparent curtains. Let\'s find a room to put this in!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Wall.003.Story">Star-shaped stickers that glow in the dark. Put them on the wall or in the ceiling and watch them when you go to bed!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Rug.001.Story">A round carpet. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.WP.001.Story">A purple wallpaper with a teardrop pattern. It sounds like Onion Cookie is sobbing nearby, maybe we should go console her.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0058.Deck.001.Story">This pattern was popular for flooring a very long time ago... but how did it end up in Onion Cookie\'s room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.001.Story">What was once a merry-go-round, bringing joy to children, is now a comfy bed to sleep in after a long day of playing.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.002.Story">A pretty unicorn in pastel colors. When you ride it, you feel like you\'re soaring through the sky.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.003.Story">A cute teddy bear holding balloons. Maybe it wants to give them to friends!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.004.Story">A carefully painted panel that looks like something you might have seen at the amusement park as a child.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.005.Story">Pastel-colored balloons. Everyone likes these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.007.Story">A pointy street light. It goes well wherever you place it, even indoors!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Floor.008.Story">A star-shaped rainbow seat. If you scooch hard enough, you might fit five Cookies at once!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Ceil.001.Story">A decorative mobile with a cloud, moons and stars. Looking at it makes you feel a bit drowsy.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Ceil.002.Story">Sugar butterfly decorations, hanging from the ceiling on strings. Where should we put these?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Ceil.003.Story">A pretty pastel curtain. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Wall.001.Story">A comet with a rainbow tail. Let\'s make a wish!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Wall.002.Story">A rainbow with a double arc, somewhat resembling a heart. Maybe the pot of gold is behind the star!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Wall.003.Story">A decorative purple cloud. Who wouldn\'t want a cloud in their room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.Deck.001.Story">A floor with clouds, and stars gleaming in between. Looking at it somehow makes you think back to distant memories.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0157.WP.001.Story">A wall depicting the night sky and all its stars. Happy and bright memories come to mind, making you stare at the wallpaper as you get carried away by nostalgia.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.001.Story">A pot full of warm cocoa and fluffy marshmallows bobbing inside. Amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.002.Story">A fireside filled with memories together with a certain Cookie. Every single one brings a smile to Cocoa Cookie\'s face.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.003.Story">A chair made out of a marshmallow. It is perfect for lengthy knitting sessions.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.004.Story">A set with yarn and knitting needles. With this you can create anything, especially if that something is a sweater.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.005.Story">A tree as white as snow. Anyone would like this... at least until they have to clean up all the needles falling on the floor.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.006.Story">A roll cake with a winter holiday theme. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.007.Story">A boiling teapot. Let\'s put it to good use, but be careful it doesn\'t burn anyone!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Floor.008.Story">A stool shaped like a sugar cube. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Ceil.001.Story">A simple wreath with snowflakes. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Wall.001.Story">Some winter landscapes have a warm feeling. Just like watching the snow fall outside while sipping on some hot cocoa.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Wall.002.Story">A reindeer with a glowing nose. It shines bright enough to light up a dark winter night!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Wall.003.Story">A hanger with a scarf and a Snow Rabbit resting on top. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Hanger.001.Story">A cute bell with a ribbon. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.Deck.001.Story">A floor decorated with vivid colors and a snowflake pattern. It gives off a very warm feeling.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0045.WP.001.Story">A wall made out of dark wood logs. They completely block out the winter winds!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.001.Story">A playground slide made to resemble the Snow King. It takes some effort to climb up, but the joy of sliding down makes the climb worth it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.002.Story">An igloo with what seems like a half-melted Snow Cone on top. Surely it\'s not the real thing...?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.003.Story">A snowman made to look like Snow Sugar Cookie. You can tell someone put in a lot of effort into making it, but who could it be?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.004.Story">A sprinkle meringue tree. Place this somewhere for a more wintery mood!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.005.Story">A snowman made out triple-stacked ice cream scoops. They are sure to lighten the mood in any room they are placed in.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.006.Story">A large blue snowflake, stuck inside a pile of snow. What could have caused this one to grow so large?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.007.Story">A small stool covered in snow. Sitting on this will quickly wake you up, no matter how sleepy you were.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Floor.008.Story">A barricade made out of fluffy meringue. Since you can easily walk between them, it\'s mostly for decoration.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Ceil.001.Story">A snowflake attached to a piece of string. It doesn\'t seem to melt, so it is safe to hang up as an indoor decoration.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Ceil.002.Story">A heap of cozily piled-up snow. It doesn\'t seem to melt, so no need to worry about walking through puddles of water if you place it in a room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Wall.001.Story">When the fierce blizzard subsides, and the surroundings quiet down, the skies fill with a mesmerizing aurora. Maybe it is a gift to those who endured?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Wall.002.Story">A path through a winter landscape. Where could it lead?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Rug.001.Story">A pile of snow with small footprints on it. What kind of adorable creature could have left those?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.Deck.001.Story">Snowy floor with a path plowed through the middle. Thanks to someone clearing the snow, everyone can walk through without worrying about slipping and falling.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0030.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper giving your room permanent snowfall. The snowflakes drawn on it are incredibly realistic, making you almost feel the cold winter breeze.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.001.Story">A magical portal that only activates once the riddle is solved. Where could it lead, I wonder?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.002.Story">A mysterious coffin that no one could open before Adventurer Cookie found a way. How much gold could have been kept inside?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.003.Story">A structure from mysterious ruins. Adventurer Cookie will definitely be able to find out what secrets they hide!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.004.Story">A pillar with a depiction of a cheesebird. This would fit well in a ruin-themed room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.005.Story">A low pillar with gold-tipped arrows lodged in it. Try as you like to pull them out, they won\'t budge.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Floor.006.Story">A rock with various symbols etched onto it. We should probably ask Adventurer Cookie about what they mean.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Ceil.001.Story">Leaf hammocks with a pair of cheesebirds resting inside. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Ceil.002.Story">Purely decorative, this medieval-style contraption has had its sharp blades dulled down to prevent accidents.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Ceil.003.Story">Swing from these like you rule the jungle!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Wall.001.Story">Pull the lever. Not that lever!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Wall.002.Story">An entrance to hidden ruins. These stairs don\'t show up in any of our maps, so keep an eye out for traps!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Wall.003.Story">This will show your way through the dark, abandoned ruins. If you are lucky, it might also be the key to a locked-away treasure!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Rug.001.Story">Watch your step!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.Deck.001.Story">Ground filled with bushes, vines, and traps. Watch your step!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0038.WP.001.Story">A wall designed after actual ruins somewhere in the world. There are no secrets behind the cracks, so don\'t get any ideas!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.001.Story">A sofa adorned with giant feathers. Rumor has it the feathers were part of a fan belonging to a witch who loved to party.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.002.Story">A gramophone shaped like a flower. It prefers to play springtime tunes!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.003.Story">A crescent-shaped chair with a disco ball attached. The cheese it is made of does not actually come from the moon.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.004.Story">A perfume bottle with feathers attached as decoration. The pleasant fragrance is sure to attract the attention of nearby Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.005.Story">Pendants repurposed into a coat hanger. But even without coats, it makes for a beautiful decor in any room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.006.Story">Fluffy Cheese Cat\'s favorite sofa. If you decide to use it, be ready to get up to give Fluffy Cheese Cat its favorite spot by the armrest.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.007.Story">A fancy drink mixer. With this, any sparkling cocktail you could imagine is just a shake and a stir away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.008.Story">A soft stool made from a slice of cheesecake. Let\'s put it somewhere right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Floor.009.Story">A soft stool made from a slice of basque cheesecake. Let\'s put it somewhere right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Wall.001.Story">The highlight of the party—watching the coin fireworks from the terrace! It never fails to amaze!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Hanger.001.Story">A golden curtain. It can be pulled down to give the guests an easier time to focus on the party in front of them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Ceil.001.Story">A chandelier made out of slices of high-quality emmental cheese. When lit, it fills the room with a cheesy aroma.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Rug.001.Story">A yellow carpet. Let\'s place it somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper with a design created by a world-renowned artist.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0037.Deck.001.Story">These floors are so polished they double as mirrors!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.001.Story">While most Cookies would be unable to sleep here, Zombie Cookie looks surprisingly comfortable in this bed.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.002.Story">An old tree, vaguely resembling a witch\'s crooked hand. Try to resist the temptation of grabbing one of the jellies dangling from the spider web.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.003.Story">A truly spooky atmosphere needs some thick mist! Just make sure to turn it off after a while, or you\'ll end up all soggy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.004.Story">A carefully decorated grave for someone\'s best friend.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.005.Story">A table made out of a stone slab. It looks quite heavy, but hopefully some Cookie can help out with bringing it to the room you want to decorate with it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Floor.006.Story">A chair created out of gravestones. It seems quite old, judging by the amount of moss growing on it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Wall.001.Story">A stairway leading somewhere. The only Cookie who returned after entering is Zombie Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Wall.002.Story">A diagram showing the basic anatomy of a Cookie. I wonder who this belonged to!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Wall.003.Story">A crack in the wall. You can feel a breeze of cool air coming out of it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Hanger.001.Story">Spider web picked from a cemetery. You can\'t see the spider that made it, but surely it\'s somewhere nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Ceil.001.Story">A lantern often found near graves. It gives off an eerie light.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Ceil.002.Story">A small graveyard lantern. Hang this in a room to give it a spookier vibe.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Rug.001.Story">A soaked carpet. It makes squishy noises when you walk on it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.WP.001.Story">The horrible colors and patterns of this wallpaper makes it an unpopular choice among Cookies. Zombie Cookie, however, seems to enjoy it greatly.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0013.Deck.001.Story">The hard-packed earth and pebbles makes it rough to walk on, but Zombie Cookie seems to enjoy it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.001.Story">A bed made of furs and leather, designed to completely block out the cold. It gives a very wild vibe.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.002.Story">Meat Jelly filled with delicious nutrients and protein. Cooked over an open fire, and herbs sprinkled on top for enhanced flavor.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.003.Story">The lair of a dangerous (but small and fluffy) beast. Only the bravest adventurers dare venture close, even fewer still try taking the yarn ball placed next to the bed.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.004.Story">A table containing the essence of the wild. No table manners are required when you dine by this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.005.Story">A bucket filled with a bunch of treats for a well-behaved companion.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Floor.006.Story">A coat hanger made out of a suitably shaped stick.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Wall.001.Story">A window where you can often find Werewolf Cookie looking out into the distance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Hanger.001.Story">A fur ornament where flowers have started to grow. Let\'s hang it up somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Hanger.002.Story">A banner with marks, kept around to never forget.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Ceil.001.Story">A huge collar once worn by a ferocious beast. It is sturdy enough to withstand someone sleeping on it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Ceil.002.Story">These snacks have been tied up with a rope as storage. Their size make them entire meals for ordinary Cookies, though.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Ceil.003.Story">A light wrapped in rough cloth. It efficiently lights up any room it is installed in.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Rug.001.Story">A rough carpet. Not the most comfortable to walk on, but it does what it\'s supposed to.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.WP.001.Story">A cold stone wall. You can feel cold air seeping through the gaps.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0044.Deck.001.Story">This stone floor can feel rough at first, but stays cool even during hot summers.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.001.Story">Round vials filled with simmering liquids of various colors. It will likely result in a strong potion, only for the strongest of adventurers.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.002.Story">A quietly boiling pot of a newly invented substance! It seems even the cauldron itself is looking forward to seeing the results.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.003.Story">An accurate set of scales is invaluable to an alchemist, to whom the craft revolves around the law of equivalent exchange.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.004.Story">A chalkboard filled with complex formulae. In the corner someone has written \"DO NOT ERASE\" in large letters, so we better let it be.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.005.Story">Various materials for studying. With this, you have everything needed for absorbing knowledge!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.006.Story">A step stool used to assist Cookies administering reagents during scientific research.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.007.Story">A pestle filled with medicine. While slightly bitter, it will likely make you feel better in no time!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.008.Story">This bad boy can get you across the laboratory in 2.5 seconds!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Floor.009.Story">A note written in a hurry. Someone must be busy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Wall.001.Story">An old and extremely fragile source of information on alchemy. Make sure a certain juice-loving Cookie doesn\'t get too close.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Ceil.001.Story">A pair of test tubes and litmus paper: the very basics (or acidics, depending on the results) of chemical tests.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Ceil.002.Story">A light bulb with a less-than-stable source of electricity. It should still work for most illumination-based purposes.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Rug.001.Story">A carpet decorated with a distinct symbol. Whom—or what—it belongs to, remains a mystery.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.WP.001.Story">A wall filled with shelves containing various medicinal herbs. It is said every great alchemist owns a wall like this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0034.Deck.001.Story">Flooring designed by a geometry aficionado. The pattern is quite complicated, but the symmetry makes it nice to look at.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.001.Story">A glass of juice made out of only the ripest grapes. Just the aroma is enough to make you slightly drowsy.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.002.Story">Vampire Cookie\'s favorite lounge chair for relaxing. It has a bottle of grape juice within arm\'s reach.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.003.Story">A coffin that will dispel any prejudice about coffins being uncomfortable. Close the lid, and enjoy deep sleep, safe from any sunlight!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.004.Story">Boxes of grape juice perfect for on the go. It is one of the few ways to convince Vampire Cookie to go somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.005.Story">A cut gemstone with a grape-like purple hue. It looks very valuable!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.006.Story">A place to store multiple bottles of grape juice in a way that make them great conversation pieces at the same time.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Floor.007.Story">Why bother hanging it up when you\'re going to wear it later anyway?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Wall.001.Story">A view of bats flying in a star-filled night sky. The landscape outside the window contains everything Vampire Cookie could ever ask for... aside from a glass of grape juice, of course.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Wall.002.Story">A window showing the starry night sky outside. Looking out through it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Hanger.001.Story">A furled curtain. Pull it down to bring an aura of mystery to what might hide behind it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Hanger.002.Story">A curtain tied with a neat knot. Basic, yet sophisticated.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Ceil.001.Story">A ceiling-mounted hanger for juice cups. Now you can store more juice in your cupboards!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Rug.001.Story">A carpet with a fang-shaped pattern.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.WP.001.Story">A grape-colored wall. Taking a closer look, it seems like there are fangs too...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0035.Deck.001.Story">A floor giving off a distinct smell of grapes. Was it intended, or did someone spill a cup...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.001.Story">Turn this mood light on, and you will instantly feel like you\'re floating among the stars.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.002.Story">A witchberry mousetrap. Let\'s avoid placing this in a cheese-loving Cookie\'s room, just in case!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.003.Story">A stick with a long feather at the end. Who could resist doing everything they can to catch the feather? Not Witchberry Cookie, that\'s for sure!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Wall.002.Story">A long window showing the night sky outside. Who wouldn\'t like an amazing view like that from their room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.005.Story">Stained glass in the shape of a cat\'s paw. Who wouldn\'t love to have this in their room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.006.Story">A table with a bowl of crispy snacks. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.007.Story">A cauldron of freshly brewed snacks. Let\'s hope we get to taste test soon!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Ceil.001.Story">A hat filled with stars and moons. I wonder what they can be used for!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Wall.001.Story">A set of windows showing the night sky outside. Who wouldn\'t like an amazing view like that from their room?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Floor.004.Story">A cute black cat doll. Some Cookies claim to have seen its tail move, but that can\'t be true... right?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Wall.003.Story">Stained glass, depicting a cat sitting quietly underneath the moonlight.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Ceil.003.Story">The stars hanging from this look so real they might as well have been picked straight from the night sky!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Ceil.004.Story">A curtain swaying in the wind, not quite unlike that of a playful cat. This is perfect for hiding items in a corner!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper showing constellations of the night sky. It is said this wallpaper changes with the seasons.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Deck.001.Story">Brick flooring that resembles the paved pathways of the City of Wizards. Just walking on this makes your magic grow stronger!</string>
  <string name="$Error.Popup.Purchase.Fail.Title">Purchase Error</string>
  <string name="$Error.Popup.Purchase.Fail.Text">Purchase unsuccessful.
Please try again later.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.01">Homemade Guard Post</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.02">Candy Mill</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.03">Sugar Beats Plaza</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.04">Twin Parlor</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.05">Faucet Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.01.Story">A surveillance monitor made out of discarded cans, a phone made using yarn and rubber bands! This guard station, built from scratch by Radish Cookie, really shows the Cookie\'s desire to reunite with someone very special.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.02.Story">A mill that finely grinds syrupy candy into sweet candy powder. Spend an entire day working here, and you will have to spend ages to wipe candy powder off your clothes!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.03.Story">A place for green residents to let loose to a healthy groove! Take a sip of sweet syrup and feel your body get carried away by the pleasant rhythm until the morning sunlight starts shining through the canopy above.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.04.Story">Twin windows! Twin sofas! Even the teapots come as a pair! This luxuriously furnished room was tailored to the taste of the Twin Cherry Ladies. Just make sure you bring someone with you, otherwise it\'s easy to get lonely.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.05.Story">An overgrown room with a faucet. All the syrup nourishing the garden comes from here! Let\'s fix it quickly and wake the garden up!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0073.Season">Taro Purée Phantom Cat</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0074.Season">Castella Spirit Cat</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0075.Season">Strawberry Donut Ghost Cat</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0076.Season">Magic Maestro Berry Owl</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0077.Season">Dessert Doctor Caramel Owl</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0078.Season">Machine Maven Mint Owl</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0073.Season.Story">A ghastly feline that has been around for a very, very long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0074.Season.Story">Perhaps this adorably spooky cat is looking for new friends?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0075.Season.Story">A very amicable cat apparition.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0076.Season.Story">An owl who has watched over the witches from the old wooden beams of the Witch\'s Castle. Confident in most schools of magic—all learned by watching the witches at work—this owl might even have surpassed their teachers in proficiency over time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0077.Season.Story">This owl, whose wing flaps leave a sweet caramel scent in the air, has spent ages studying all kinds of dessert creatures born in the Witch\'s Castle. Although confident there are no more creatures that have yet to be studied, it is not a rare occurrence that this owl melts with excitement when they learn of a new discovery!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0078.Season.Story">An owl who prefers the ingenuity of mechanical gadgets over the witches\' magic, perhaps because of being so coolheaded due to a strong affinity with mint. Flying across the entirety of Earthbread is nothing if there is new piece of technology waiting to be studied. Are the rumors of a place, where magic disappeared and technology rules, true?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2006">Witchberry Cookie\'s Room of Magical Mysteries</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2006.Story">Witchberry Cookie\'s room is filled with sparkling starlight and all kinds of mysterious tools. At first glance, the room looks like a witch\'s abode, with enchanted brooms and bubbling pots... but after a closer look it seems they are just cat toys? Let\'s pretend we didn\'t notice.</string>
