  <string name="$Room.Ep02.HotelRoom.Story">A room where you can truly enjoy the star-class service that the Grand Cabinet Hotel is known for. Comfortable sleep, exquisite interiors, and 24-hour room service! What more could one wish for when looking for proper rest and relaxation?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.PortraitRoom.Story">A hidden room that hasn\'t seen visitors for a very long time. It is filled with traces of a family lineage... What other secrets might this room hold?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2006.Ceil.002.Story">A broom, decorated with a ribbon. Anyone would like this!</string>
