a place of mysteries and adventures.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">I\'m gonna need some Life Potions! You need Life Potions to wake up sleepy Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_14">Hmm, I wonder where this Cookie came from... What could their name be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">Ooh, I just feel like something fun is going to happen! I\'m sure of it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_1">I fixed it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_2">This is great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP1_CH1_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001.BraveJust_3">Window, here I come!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0015_1">Aaand... We\'re back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0014_1">So tired... My feet hurt... I don\'t feel cute at all right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0013_1">STOP! I\'ve had it up to HERE with all the weaksauce griping!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0014_2">But... All that hard work has gone to waste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_cookie2003_1">\"Gone to waste?\"
I beg to differ, my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_cookie2003_2">I only returned the compass.
As for the other valuables...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0008_1">We\'ve got\'em right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0013_2">And lookee here! I swiped a pearl egg too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0015_2">Since we\'re being honest and all... I managed to get my hands on a lovely ring.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0014_3">Oh, so we\'re being honest then? I, erm... brought a jewelled mirror, hehe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_cookie2003_3">As per usual, our Apricot Jam Syndicate has succeeded once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_cookie2003_4">Shall we celebrate our latest success? After all, our hard work has truly paid off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0014_4">A grand idea, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ1_POR1_npc0013_3">Then let\'s clean up the place first! Can\'t have a celebration if there\'s a mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0015_1">Now that the cleaning\'s done... It\'s time to roll up my sleeves and put my culinary skills to work!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_1">Perhaps, our dear Cashew wouldn\'t mind help setting the table. You\'re, erm... finesse is needed for such an occasion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_1">Erm, yeah. The boss has a point!
I can cook for us today!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0015_2">OW! No need to push and shove! I\'m supposed to cook today, and the gift needs to be wrapped too and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_2">I beg your pardon?
A gift...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_2">Gift? Nah, nope, nuh-uh.
N-n-no one said anything about a gift, hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_3">Anyway, at least we don\'t have to experience Cashew\'s signature Choco Cucumber Pizza once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_3">Yes, Cashew\'s cooking is certainly... unique.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_4">I often reminisce on the time I was lost and hungry... You were the only souls who offered me a warm meal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_4">Back then, we were still calling ourselves the Looting Legumes... A ragtag band of failed misfits, always hungry, always miserable...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_5">Even so, we couldn\'t leave someone like us to wander about and starve!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_5">The soup you offered that night was the most horrendous thing I\'ve ever tasted... But it truly warmed my heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_6">Sachertorte Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_cookie2003_6">I am done dwelling on the past for tonight. Perhaps I shall check up on the others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ2_POR1_npc0013_7">Of course!
I\'ll get dinner ready, boss.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_1">It needs to be perfect... and pretty... and cute... like me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0008_1">Er... Like this?
Or... like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_2">It\'s still missing something... Something as grand as our gift...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_cookie2003_1">A gift...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_3">GAH?! Sachertorte Cookie?!
N-n-no, we were just talking about erm... decorating the hideout!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_cookie2003_2">Ah, I see. How about placing our syndicate\'s emblem somewhere well-seen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_4">Perfect! You\'re a genius, boss...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_cookie2003_3">Much better. I remember when we first designed our emblem together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_5">An unforgettable day...! The day the Looting Legumes were reborn as the Apricot Jam Syndicate...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_6">When you, Sachertorte Cookie, became our boss...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_7">Walnut wasn\'t so bad as the leader, but... Poor cute me... So much nagging...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_cookie2003_4">*Chuckle*
I\'m sure it wasn\'t anything personal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_cookie2003_5">I shall continue on my way then. I trust that you can manage the decorations on your own?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0014_8">No sweat, boss...
We got this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ3_POR1_npc0008_2">Leave it to us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0014_1">The party\'s ready to get started but... Where\'s Sachertorte Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0015_1">*GASP!*
Did Mar... Marsh... March... What\'s-His-Name Cookie kidnap the boss?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0013_1">Nonsense! The boss is at least a hundred times stronger than all of us combined!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0015_2">Hmph! You\'re just a big bully, Walnut... You know that? And you\'re a windbag of yappity yap yap yaps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0014_2">A nagger who doesn\'t... acknowledge just how... adorable I really am...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0013_2">Why I oughta...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_cookie2003_1">My, oh my.
What sort of shenanigans have erupted today, I wonder?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0015_3">SACHERTORTE COOKIE?!
Where were you? We were so worried!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_cookie2003_2">Ah, forgive me, friends. I needed to procure something for the party. Shall we begin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0013_3">Before we start...!
We got you a special gift!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_cookie2003_3">A gift...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0014_3">Erm... Well...
We know what that hotel used to be... And what it meant to you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0015_4">But it\'s a thing of your past! History, gone, bye-bye, toodeloo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0014_4">This gift... we hope it helps you move forward...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0013_4">Ya see, boss? We care about you just as much as you care about us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_cookie2003_4">My friends... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ4_POR1_npc0015_5">Alrighty then!
Let\'s get this party started!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_npc0015_1">This party doesn\'t feel complete without my cooking... But it\'s going pretty well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_cookie2003_1">It is quite the party already. But I\'ve just the thing to add a little... festivity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_npc0014_1">Oh... I bet Walnut forgot to bring something...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_cookie2003_2">Not at all, my friend. The party is wonderful. But... What sort of party is it without cake?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_npc0013_1">A cake?! And not just any cake...!
It looks amazing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_npc0014_2">It\'s so pretty... It\'s like looking in a mirror...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_cookie2003_3">I am glad to see that all of you are pleased. Shall we continue with our merry celebration?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_cookie2003_4">And, I know in my heart, that this party will be a memory most cherished.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS2_SQ5_POR1_npc0008_1">Let the fun begin and last all night! WOOHOO!</string>
