  <string name="$Event.0001.Story">The Witch of Light loved the world and all living things in it. She added all the ingredients necessary for life as she baked the First Batch. GingerDozer, one among the Cookies of the First Batch, was filled with peaceful, sweet sleepiness. The Cookie\'s simple appearance is a testament to the fact that even the Witches had to learn to bake by practice... But even so, this Cookie was created with just as much love as all the others.</string>
