  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">Heehee! What a funny hairdo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0031_5">Let\'s brocca-locka-rooock!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Wow! This place is amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_8">Another success, thanks to you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0025_10">Radish Cookie!
Can you give us a hand?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_22">We fixed the faucet, remember?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_23">The ground around here is
flowing with syrup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_24">This\'ll be enough to end
the party on a high note!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_30">Told ya there\'d be enough
for everyone, hahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_31">Let\'s see who can
collect the most!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0033_5">Finally!
A fellow Fruit Resident!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0033_9">I was just so excited to
meet someone like family...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">Something\'s constricting
the Heart...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_7">These pesky Churro Vines
are stopping</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_8">the production and
flow of fresh syrup.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_19">I\'ve already tried everything
I can think of.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">These vines are practically
impervious to everything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_21">No matter what
I throw at them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_22">they just...
won\'t come loose...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_23">But not today!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_25">Just say the word,
Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_29">First, we need to whack away
these awful Churro Vines.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_30">But they\'re really
tough and sturdy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_32">These vines become much more
pliable when exposed to syrup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_35">If you split up and manage
to fix all four at once,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_36">the incoming flow of syrup should
be enough to weaken the vines!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_37">And then you can cut
them away, easy-peasy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_1">The Sugar Heart is free!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_15">We need to get
her out of there!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_16">She\'ll get too soggy
if we don\'t save her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_24">He looks really
angry right now...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_26">Leave the Sweet Heart alone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_27">Leave Rosemary Cookie alone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_33">before Rosemary Cookie
gets too soggy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_35">You won\'t get through us,
Churro Golem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">Yeah!
What a touching reunion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">Yup! It\'s all thanks to
Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_31">Or something more is going on
underneath the surface...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_32">Let\'s follow them! We need to
know what\'s going on!</string>
