  <string name="$Cookie.0001.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of GingerBrave\'s soul. It fills you with boundless bravery.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0002.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Strawberry Cookie\'s soul. Holding it in your hands, you feel a bit more timid than before.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0003.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of GingerBright\'s soul. Holding it makes you want to burst into cheerful laughter.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0012.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Angel Cookie\'s soul. Its light fills you with confidence in your abilities.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0013.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Zombie Cookie\'s soul. It fills you with the endurance to just keep going, no matter how tough things get!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0023.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Devil Cookie\'s soul. Suddenly you feel an urge to play a prank on someone.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0025.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Wizard Cookie\'s soul. It radiates with a dim arcane light.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0028.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cherry Cookie\'s soul. Be careful, it looks like it\'s about to explode!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0030.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Snow Sugar Cookie\'s soul. It looks cold as snow, but is quite warm to the touch.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0034.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Alchemist Cookie\'s soul.
It radiates with curiosity and a spirit of inquiry.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0035.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Vampire Cookie\'s soul. It has a rather relaxed aura.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0037.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cheesecake Cookie\'s soul. Maybe it\'s time to plan an amazing party?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0038.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Adventurer Cookie\'s soul.
It fills you with the desire to hit the road and go exploring faraway places.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0042.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Blackberry Cookie\'s soul. It fills you with the desire to respect order and loathe mess.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0044.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Werewolf Cookie\'s soul. Holding it in your hands, you can hear a lone wolf\'s howl.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0045.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cocoa Cookie\'s soul. The pleasantly rich aroma of cocoa makes you want to get a hot cup yourself!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0046.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Mint Choco Cookie\'s soul. It hums with pure passion for music.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0058.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Onion Cookie\'s soul. It looks like it doesn\'t want to remain alone.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0063.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Herb Cookie\'s soul. When warmed under direct sunlight, it smells like fields of grass.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0111.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Sparkling Cookie\'s soul. You can make out exquisite golden bubbles rising inside.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0113.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Avocado Cookie\'s soul. Holding it in your hands, you start getting great ideas for funny jokes.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0157.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cream Unicorn Cookie\'s soul. It resonates with a quiet melody from a merry-go-round—endearing, yet for some reason forgotten.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2001.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Cream Cookie\'s soul. You can feel a cold, yet sweet aura emanating from it.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2002.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Marble Danish Cookie\'s soul. It radiates with pride, no matter the circumstances.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2003.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Sachertorte Cookie\'s soul. You can feel the prying eyes of the Syndicate watching from the shadows.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2004.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Radish Cookie\'s soul. You can hear cheerful laughter coming from within.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2005.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Rosemary Cookie\'s soul. It gives off a fragrance that soothes your mind.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2006.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Witchberry Cookie\'s soul. Myahaha! I might help, if you say purr-ty please!</string>
