  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.01.Story">This adorable truck travels alongside the first light of dawn to quickly deliver groceries that the Cookies have ordered. Few have seen this swift truck as it only travels while everyone is asleep.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.02.Story">A box that is ready to go on a journey to its destined recipient. Who receives it? That\'s up to you!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.03.Story">This fruit box is fresh and sweet, almost as fresh as the fruit picked from the Syrup Garden!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.04.Story">No need to worry about the menu when you\'ve got Kurly around! The menu goes into great detail to let you know about all the ingredients, their flavors, and even how they all blend together in culinary perfection! If you\'re a Cookie who knows your stuff, this is definitely something to refer to.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.05.Story">The morning stars shining bright, an owl resting on a branch... This decoration has a bit of all the things one would consider part of a mystical early-morning landscape.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Kurly.06.Story">A round carpet with a \"Kurly\" print in the middle. It could give any room a more sophisticated feel to it.</string>
