  <string name="$Item.Deco.Prereservation.Floor.001.Story">While there exist many unidentified objects within the Witch\'s Castle, this orb is among the most mysterious. If you feel yourself remember long-forgotten memories, the brilliant glass sphere shows a moment where a certain witch completely changed the world. It seems the world itself does not forget easily.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Prereservation.Floor.002.Story">Its tip might be crooked and its brim split, but this old witch\'s hat still makes an excellent hideout for a Cookie looking to rest their dough after a hectic day. But who might have been the owner of this hat? Be careful—they might come back looking for it any day!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Prereservation.Floor.003.Story">Something incredible happened after someone poured this toxic potion into the teacup...! Fortunately, the living foam doesn\'t seem to be able to escape its porcelain confines. Still, it\'s better not to take the witch\'s belongings lightly!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Prereservation.Floor.004.Story">This marshmallow meowgician has roasted to perfection and is now enjoying the pleasure of sound sleep atop their wisdom\'s cushion. It is highly advised not to get ahead of yourself when getting to know this meowjestic pundit, for they will only reveal their most roasty-toasty belly to someone they trust!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Prereservation.Hanger.001.Story">An animated bat replica made by a certain skilled resident. It likes to be placed in spacious, empty rooms. Every now and then, a certain mischievous Cookie places it in empty hallways, but let\'s keep that to a minimum so that the timid mice don\'t flee.</string>
