  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0006_10">There\'s a party tonight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">I got lots!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP2_CH1_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Ah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP0_CH1_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2006_38">Such bravado!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_1">Greetings.
My name is Sparkling Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_1">My, my! When I heard the Juice Bar\'s bartender called in sick,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_2">I never imagined the esteemed Sparkling Party\'s very own Sparkling Cookie would be aiding today as well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_2">You\'re much too kind, sir.
After all, the Cheesehaven is a much more esteemed establishment than my own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_3">Nonsense! Though I must admit, my guests are quite fond of my latest Squeakalicious Soda, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_3">Haha, perhaps those particular patrons of yours have yet to taste my signature Sparkling Juice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_4">Throngs of guests have traveled beyond the Cat Tower to sample my Squeakalicious Soda.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_4">I\'ve hosted customers who have claimed they escaped the oven just to taste my Sparkling Juice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_npc0004_6">Shall we... erm... prepare for opening?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ1_POR1_cookie0111_6">A splendid idea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_npc0004_1">Now then! Shall we finish what we\'ve started?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_cookie0111_1">I believe an outside opinion is needed to wrap things up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_npc0004_2">Hm, yes, yes... Then we must...
OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_cookie0035_1">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_npc0004_3">Why don\'t we have our latest guest be the judge of our little debate?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_cookie0111_2">I agree! Vampire Cookie is a frequent guest of mine. I am sure he will provide some valuable insight.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_cookie0035_2">Huh? Who...?
Me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_npc0004_4">Then let us make haste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ2_POR1_cookie0035_3">Oh, c\'mon... Can\'t we all just relax and chill...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_1">So, lemme get this straight. You want me to try this juice made from a full bunch of grapes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0111_1">Yes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_2">And then try this creamy, grape soda...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_npc0004_1">Yes...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_3">And tell you which one\'s better?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_4">OK...
Hmmm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_5">They\'re both really tasty...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_6">I think I need another sip of each...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_npc0004_2">Well...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0111_2">Well...???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_7">Can\'t rush something like this, fellas...
I need another sip or five.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_8">Cheers, to both of you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0111_3">I guess... erm... we should prepare a few extras for his consideration.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_cookie0035_9">That\'s the best thing I\'ve heard all day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0111_1">I look forward to your final verdict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0035_1">Do I really have to choose just one...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0035_2">Meh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0035_3">Nah, I think I still need to taste both a bit more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_npc0004_1">By my gouda and halloumi, our concoctions must be equally matched if he\'s deliberating this much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0111_2">Yes, it appears so, doesn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0111_3">Your ideas and recipes are exquisite, good Cheesemaster.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_npc0004_2">And I too am just as impressed at your finesse, good Sparkling Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0111_4">What would you say to a... collaboration of sorts? A special recipe to commend this momentous occasion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_npc0004_3">It would be a great honor to do so, my friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ4_POR1_cookie0035_4">Oh wow, I can\'t wait to see what you two will come up with!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0035_1">WOW! That\'s the best thing I\'ve ever tasted!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0111_1">Haha! I\'m glad you enjoyed it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_npc0004_1">Ah, a fine compliment for a fine drink!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0035_2">Buuut...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0035_3">I\'m feeling a bit...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0035_4">ZZZzzz... *Snore*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_npc0004_2">He has... fallen asleep?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0111_2">Perhaps he\'s indulged a bit too much...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0035_5">Huh... Wha-?
Oh, I\'m not done forming my full opinion just yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_npc0004_3">Wait... Have we...
Did we just partake in a grand scheme?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0111_3">Ha... haha...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_cookie0111_4">Perhaps we should call for Alchemist Cookie to handle this situation?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ5_POR1_npc0004_4">Yes! I believe a good nagging is well deserved for our taste-testing patron!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_1">YUP! This should do it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_2">Angel Cookie\'s gonna freak out when they see this mess! HAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_3">Oh, maybe one more finishing touch...
A poster here and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0012_1">Oh dear... What a mess.
What has happened to my room?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_4">GAH?!
A-A-Angel Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0012_2">What happened to my room...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_5">(I can\'t let Angel Cookie know it was me...!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_6">Huh? What?
I erm... I just got here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_7">And erm... I was... I was about to clean this all up for you. Yeah! Cleaning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0012_3">Really?
But... cleaning up is such a virtuous act.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0012_4">I\'m so grateful and happy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0012_5">We should clean together...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ1_POR1_cookie0023_8">Er... Yeah...?
Sure, I guess?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_1">(This plan\'s going terribly... I just wanted to prank Angel Cookie!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_2">(Why am I CLEANING?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0012_1">Cleaning is such fun, isn\'t it?
Doesn\'t it make you feel all warm and proud?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_3">NOPE!
This is boring!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0012_2">Cleaning is not boring...
It\'s a first step to becoming a good Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_4">It\'s boring because it\'s not my vibe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0012_3">We should move on to our next act of kindness...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_5">Are you even listening to me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_6">(I should\'ve just come clean at the very beginning...!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_7">(Wait a minute... Honesty is an act of kindness too, isn\'t it?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ2_POR1_cookie0023_8">(PFFFT! I don\'t care anymore... I\'m gonna make a run for it!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0012_1">Devil Cookie...?
Why are you pretending to be a statue...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_1">Er...
It looked fun, that\'s all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_2">(There\'s nowhere to hide in this room! BAH!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_3">(What do I do?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0012_2">If you want to be just like the angel statues...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0012_3">Then it must mean you\'re ready to be a kinder Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0012_4">I can help you become a kinder Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0012_5">Here... Let\'s go... Follow me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_4">(Why is there a portal here?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_5">(NO! I CAN\'T GO IN THERE! NOOO!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ3_POR1_cookie0023_6">(I NEED TO GET OUT OF HERE!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0012_1">We\'re ready...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0012_2">We can open the portal now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0012_3">Come, Devil Cookie... It\'s time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0023_1">(Ain\'t no way I\'m gonna go through that door! That portal\'s unnatural!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0023_2">(What do I do? WHAT DO I DO?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0023_3">OW! OUCH!
Oh, my stomach! My tummy! OH NO! ThE pAiN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0012_4">Oh dear...
Have you fallen ill...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0012_5">Stay still, Devil Cookie...
I will go get some medicine for you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0023_4">(YES! Angel Cookie\'s finally gone!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ4_POR1_cookie0023_5">(Time to hide behind that statue!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_1">Haha! Angel Cookie\'ll never find me...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0012_1">There\'s no way they\'ll find me-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_2">GAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0012_2">Devil Cookie... Were you trying to do something bad...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0012_3">Bad things make me cry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_3">(That face! Those eyes?! THAT STARE!
I need to come up with an excuse, QUICK!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_4">No, you\'ve got it all wrong!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_5">Er... I feel so nice and kind because of all the things we did today...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_6">And look at the time! It\'s time for nice and kind Cookies to go to bed and sleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_7">It\'s important to sleep on time!!!
So I\'ll go in that portal with you next time, OK?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0012_4">Ah...! Yes, sleep is very important...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0012_5">OK... I will take you next time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_8">Haha... haha... Yeah, next time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_9">(PHEW...!
That was a close one...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_10">(I should put up this poster before I leave... quickly!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS6_SQ5_POR1_cookie0023_11">(Just you wait, Angel Cookie...!
I won\'t forget this!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_3">One...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_4">WOOOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">Wohoo! Another layer turned green!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">This is quite satisfying!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_7">... Someone sprung up again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">Who aaare you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">I\'m so curious!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">Let\'s pull\'em out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">HAHA! The Vegetable Residents!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">They\'re the happiest, cheeriest folks in the entire garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_3">Radish Cookie!
Are you the one who woke us up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">Not just me, but these other Cookies too!
They helped a ton!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_5">New Cookies! New friends!
Nice to meet you, nice to meet you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">We\'re happy to meet you, too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0031_7">Nice to meet yaaa, such beautiful greetings!
Oooh yeah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">... Er, what\'s with the singing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0031_9">A syrup shooower!
Awaken the garden flower powerrr!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">Really? Is that the best rhyme you could come up with...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_11">This is the Vegetable Residents\' beloved performer,
the legend himself, B. Rock\'n 51!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">He\'s always strumming his guitar and sings instead of talking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">Why...? How come...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_14">Eeeek! B. Rock\'n 51 is looking good!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0031_15">Yeeeah! I could barely survive, all that time underground where I couldn\'t thrive!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_16">He\'s so cool! He\'s so cool! His lyrics are amazing as ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0031_18">Radish Cookie, got a question for yooou!
How looong were we underground? Please give us a cluuue!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">I tried to pay attention to the time at first, but now I have no idea how long it\'s been.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_20">Eeek! Then we better stretch our stiff bodies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_21">Let\'s party! Party till the morning dew! Eeek!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_22">... You JUST woke up minutes ago...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_23">Haha! See? I told ya they\'re the most fun-lovin\' folks in the garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0030_24">Let\'s go straight to the Sugar Beats Plaza!
We\'re gonna dance to B. Rock\'n 51\'s music!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0031_25">Using my music to dance?
You better not miss this chance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">Wohoo! Should we go as well?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_27">We have to go fix the Sweet Heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_28">That\'s alright! The theater is on the way anyway, so we\'ll make a quick stop.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_29">Hehe! I think that\'s a wonderful idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">To the Sugar Beats Plaza!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_1">The Sugar Beats Plaza is a total mess...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_2">The stage is gone! And all the lights are broken...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">Seems like it all dried up and wilted away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0031_4">Crushed are my dreams of a show!
And no dancing for all my veggie fans, no no no!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Don\'t look so sad! We can build a new theater!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">Now that everyone has awoken from their sleep, you can all work together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_7">Ah... so you\'re all just going to leave...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_8">Okay then... everyone is leaving...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Erm... This is awkward...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_10">It\'s not like we have to do the whole festival thing anyway...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_11">It\'s fine... just go...
We get it, you\'re busy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">Oh, oh...
We can\'t just go now...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0031_13">Thought you were a frieeend, all cool and nice!
But your heart\'s as cold as ice, ice, ice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">He\'s really not giving up on the rhyming, is he...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Uhm... Well this doesn\'t feel great...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">So, should we take off?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Radish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_18">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">Let\'s help them before we go.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0030_20">Eeeek!! So cool, so nice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0031_21">That Cookie must be freshly baked!
His heart is still so toasty, warm;
what a friend, so great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">You just said we have hearts of ice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_23">Hahaha! If that\'s what you want, then why not!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_24">Let\'s work together to rebuild the Sugar Beats Plaza!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0031_1">Wave your cabbages
in the AIRRR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_2">YEEEAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0031_3">Are you ready to
PHOTOSYNTHESIZE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_4">YEEEAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_6">YEEAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_9">The Sugar Beats Plaza is
back in action!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">Sure, what\'s up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0025_12">We ain\'t got enough drops!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">Er, drops?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">There\'s a tradition of drinking</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_15">syrup drops after a grand party.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0025_16">Our stock\'s literally run dry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0025_17">With the garden in
such rough shape,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0025_18">we couldn\'t find any in time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">Oh no! It\'d be a shame to end
a party without syrup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">Not to worry!
Lookie here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_21">WOOOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_25">That\'s so cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_26">I want to try that too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_27">Oh, me too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">Absolutely fascinating!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_29">Hehe, I did it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_32">Alright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Wow! Look at how many syrup drops we collected in such a short time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Everyone looks so happy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">I\'m really glad we helped...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">I can\'t believe we\'re gathered all in one place once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">I\'ve been dreaming of this for the longest time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">Every time I fell asleep in the corner of the garden, all by myself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Every time I fixed the faucet all by myself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">I dreamed of this reunion...</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">And now everything is back to how it\'s supposed to be!
Thanks to you all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">We\'re happy to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">Seeing everyone so happy makes us happy too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Npc.0029_12">Help! Help! HEEELP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">What\'s going on???</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Npc.0029_15">My- my little sister!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">Calm down and tell us what happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Npc.0029_17">My little sister is stuck in the ground over there! We have to get her out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_18">Looks like there are more residents that need our help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Don\'t worry, we\'ll help you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">We\'re getting super good at pulling up residents from the ground now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP3CH2PQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">Yay! Let\'s go meet the new resident!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0033_1">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0033_2">What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">Long time no see, Cheery Cherry Tomato!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_2">Radish Cookie? What\'s happening?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">You\'ve woken up from your sleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">We\'re fixing up the garden, you see!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">You can thank us later. You must be feeling a bit dazed, still.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_6">What did you say?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_7">Who told you to wake us up?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Wha- What\'s wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">Calm down, Cheery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_10">I see how it is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_11">Was it you, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_12">You can\'t just wake us up because you selfishly wanted to!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">I... huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Wait a second, didn\'t everyone want to wake up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_15">Ha! Ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_16">That\'s what the Vegetable Residents told you, huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_17">But WE Fruit Residents think differently!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_18">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_19">You\'re a vegetable, Cheery...
A cherry tomato, to be precise.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_20">Pffft!
Stay out of this, big brother.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_21">I\'m really sorry Cheery, but it\'s true.
You are one of the Vegetable Residents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_22">EXCUSE ME! Can\'t you see I\'m a fragrant little fruit?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_23">It\'s even in my name! Cheery CHERRY Tomato, you see?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_24">*Sigh*
Alright. \"Cherry\" Tomato.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_25">UGH! You\'re all so annoying!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_26">She\'s just woken up, but here we go again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_27">That\'s it! I don\'t wanna talk to any of you anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0033_28">I\'m going to find the Fruit Residents!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_29">Cheery! Where are you going?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_30">Let\'s follow her, quickly!
Before she gets lost!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_31">Why can\'t we just be a normal family...
*Groan*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_32">This is really becoming a big problem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_33">Hey, no need to get upset, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_34">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_35">Every family\'s got their own problems. But family\'s about sharing worries together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0026_1">Emergency supplies
are packed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0026_2">We are ready to evacuate.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_3">Let us evacuate at once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_4">Yes, at once, we must evacuate.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_6">Gosh, you gave us a fright.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_7">Please lower your voice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0033_8">Oh, sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_10">Someone like...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0032_11">Family...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0033_12">Ah, what I mean is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_1">Radish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_2">It\'s been a while.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">Nice to see you again! I\'m glad to see you\'re safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_4">Well, we were but... now we\'re not so sure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_5">Unfortunately, someone decided to wake up the whole garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0033_6">It was them! Radish Cookie and a bunch of Cookies I\'ve never seen before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_7">Unbelievable...! Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_8">Are the words of this vegetable true?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">They are, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_10">This is simply too much! Why would you do such a thing, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_11">Why would a Cookie such as yourself proceed with such reckless behavior?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">I just...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_13">Explain yourself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_14">Let\'s hear it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_15">I wanted to see everyone again, like old times!
So we could all work together...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_16">Wait, what did you say?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_17">Was that your only motivation?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">I can\'t help but ask, but why is it that you mustn\'t wake up the garden?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">I want to know too! After all, all the Vegetable Residents seemed happy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_20">The Vegetable Residents... Hmph.
They have never known sweetness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_21">They couldn\'t possibly understand our point of view.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0026_22">Ladies, there\'s no time.
We must evacuate at once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">Wait! Tell us why you mustn\'t wake up the garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_24">We do not have time to explain such a thing to those who are unaware of the long history of this garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_25">But if we were to give you a piece of advice...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_26">... You, the sweet smelling Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_27">... Huh, Me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_28">Your strawberry scent is so sweet and fragrant, so be careful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_29">To be sweet in this garden is to be cursed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_30">Wh-what?
What do you mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_31">Well then, we must be on our way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0032_32">Yes, on our way we must be.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0033_33">Wait, let me come with you! I\'m a fruit too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0029_34">Cheery!!! WAIT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">They all left.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_36">Radish Cookie, should we follow...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_37">... Erm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_38">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_39">Is something the matter, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_40">I... Well...
Was I wrong to wake up the garden...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_41">Of course not! Everyone was happy to wake up again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_42">Well, not all of them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_43">Well, those two just now had a different opinion is all...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_44">What would Rosemary Cookie have done in this situation...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_45">I have no idea what she\'d say if she could see me now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_46">Rosemary Cookie would be proud of you, I\'m sure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_47">But you don\'t know anything about my big sister at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_48">True, I\'ve never met her, and I don\'t know a lot about her...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_49">But I know that you\'re a great repair-Cookie that does her best for the Syrup Garden and all its Residents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_50">And Cookies can\'t help but root for those who put their heart into helping others!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_51">You sound so well-spoken for once, saying things like that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_52">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_53">You\'re right, GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_54">There\'s one reason I keep fixing this garden! To wake everyone up! To save everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_55">Everyone who understands can\'t help but agree, right? Even the Fruit Residents! And, I\'m sure that Rosemary Cookie will too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_56">That\'s the spirit! Keep your chin up and stand strong, Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_57">... So cool...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_58">Alrighty then! Let\'s pull ourselves together and head to the Sweet Heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_59">We\'re almost there, so buckle up and follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_1">This is it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">The Sweet Heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">Looks like it\'s been
broken for ages.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">This place is creepy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">*Tsk*
The Churro Golem\'s work...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_9">But... but why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">There\'s someone in there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">That Cookie is... She\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_12">The Gardener. Our leader.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_13">Rosemary Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">She\'s... my sister.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">Rosemary Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_16">We need to help her...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">Not a moment to lose!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_18">It\'s no use...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_24">Cuz y\'all\'re with me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_26">We\'re with you all the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_27">We\'ll find a way, together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">Where shall we begin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_31">Yeah, but I have an idea...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_33">So we\'ll need to fix
another faucet nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_34">Yup! There are four faucets in the area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_38">Haha! Sounds like a plan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_39">It\'s time to split up
and fix the faucets!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_40">Just hang on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_41">I\'ll save you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">Hahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_3">Y\'all\'re miracle workers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_4">Now let\'s wake up
the Sweet Heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_5">And save Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">Let\'s do this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Huuup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_8">The Sweet Heart is working!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_9">It\'s making syrup already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_10">Wow...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">It\'s too fast!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_12">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_13">ROSEMARY COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">WAKE UP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">GAH! OKAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_18">Chuuur... CHURR...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_19">That noise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">Not now...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_21">Chuuur... Chuuu!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_22">Chuuur... Chuuu!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_23">Chuuur... Chuuu!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_25">No more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_28">Chuuur!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0034_29">Chuuurrrgh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_30">We won\'t let you hurt
Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_31">Bad golem! Shoo!
Go away!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_32">We need to stop him,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_34">Let\'s do this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_1">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">ROSEMARY COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_3">Radish... Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_4">Radish Cookie...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_5">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">I thought I\'d lost you forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_7">I\'m OK... It\'s OK...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">I\'m glad she\'s OK...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_10">Wait...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_11">Our Syrup Garden is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_12">is awakened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_14">She defeated the Churro Golem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0002_15">And restored the garden too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_16">You did... all this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_17">You... the garden...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_18">Haha! It\'s a fresh new start!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_19">Now that everyone\'s up and awake,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">we can all get back to work and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_21">You...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_22">How could you be
so FOOLISH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_23">No...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_24">Nooo...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_25">NOOO!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_26">The Syrup Garden...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2005_27">Must not be awakened!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2004_28">Rosemary Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_29">Why is Rosemary Cookie so angry?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_30">Something doesn\'t feel right...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_33">They might need our help
once more! I can feel it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">RADISH COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0002_3">I don\'t think they\'re here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0025_4">They can\'t have gotten far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0025_5">We were right on their tails.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0003_6">This syrup pipe is broken...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0003_7">Was it the naughty
Churro Golem again?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_8">If we leave the broken
pipes as they are,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_9">all that precious syrup
will go to waste.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH2_SQ10_CUT2_Cookie.0001_10">Let\'s fix it up and
go find those two!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0004_3">From his reaction... It seems we are at a draw.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_1">"Excuse me. You must vacate the premises!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_2">No, that sounds a bit too mean...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_3">"You\'ve yet to pay your expenses and are no longer welcome at..."</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_4">Hm, that\'s sounds a bit too... cold?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Pardon for the interruption. But may I ask why you are mumbling in front of my room?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_6">AH?! Ah! Oh yes, hello there, sir.
Er... How long have you been standing there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I believe you started with, \"Away with you! Out! BEGONE!\" I must admit that I was quite fond of that one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_8">I, erm... Hehe... Well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">I will be honest with you. I am no longer in a stable enough financial position to pay for my stay at the hotel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">If permitted, may I have a few minutes to pack my belongings? Just a few family heirlooms is all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_11">Family heirlooms, sir...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_12">Heirlooms!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_13">I beg your pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_14">Heirlooms are always a part of the Grand Cabinet Hotel\'s auction! And there\'s an auction very soon, sir!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_15">Maybe... well, I mean... if you\'re willing, these heirlooms could be featured at the auction...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_16">The revered treasures of House Danish... in an auction?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_17">Well, it\'s just an idea, sir. They might be enough to cover your expenses? And that means I won\'t have to kick, ahem, send you away?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_18">Interesting.
Yes... A very interesting idea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0011_19">O-O-Oh, but of course, that\'s only if you\'d a-a-allow me to assist! Perhaps I can take a look at them first? A quick evaluation?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2002_20">Very well then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0011_1">Sir! What about this wonderful, illustrious antique desk?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0011_2">Such a fine specimen may fetch a good price, enough to cover your stay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">... Have you no discretion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0011_4">I... I\'m... Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">That desk belonged to the very Cookie who first discovered the Witch\'s Cabinet! The one who designed this very hotel before it was even a hotel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">The illustrious... Grandfather Danish!
He designed the manor of House Danish on that very desk, years and years ago!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">No! I refuse to put up a piece of history to some auction! The very thought puts a stain on my honor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0011_8">I, erm, well... Hehe... Oh...
I didn\'t mean anything by it, sir.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0011_9">Let\'s look for something else, perhaps?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0011_1">Oh, these look interesting!
Sir, what about these chess pieces?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">You\'d dare insult Great Grandmother Danish with such a blasphemous suggestion?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0011_3">GAH! No, I just...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Great Grandmother Danish risked her life to bring the chess set from the deadly and treacherous witch\'s study...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Alas, I cannot part with such an heirloom just to hear the clinking of Sugar Coins.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0011_6">(Oh... I think I should call the Manager...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">The chess set is not for sale.
Pick another.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0011_1">Oooh... Well... Maybe...
I dunno... This old picture?
No, don\'t say anything. It\'s not for sale, I presume?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">On the contrary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0011_3">REALLY?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">NO, have you no respect for one\'s family elders?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">This masterpiece of a painting, \"Likeness of Lordly Little Lad\", is a timeless work of art by the legendary artist, Brushed Danish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">This piece is so priceless, if it were ever sold at an auction, I could stay in this room forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">No, I could buy the entire floor of this hotel...
Nay, I could buy the entire Grand Cabinet Hotel itself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0011_8">I... I didn\'t really think... erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">But I shall not put it up for auction. As the heir of House Danish, I cannot commit myself to such financial greed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0011_10">But sir! You must come to a decision!
Check-out time is nearing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">And so... This is my fate. To squander in the back alley of the hotel. But alas, I... I cannot give up such prized family relics.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_2">Sir! Sir!
Come this way, sir!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">You?
How did you know I was...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_4">Good news, sir! I looked over the books and there\'s a few vacant rooms available until the day of the auction!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_5">I\'ve reported this directly to the Manager! He has personally arranged for a temporarily extended stay for you, sir.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">You... The warmth of your heart fills me with gratitude. Thank you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_7">But... It\'s only until the auction, sir.
There are no vacancies on the day of the auction!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">This auction must be quite the popular occasion...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_9">Yes, there are many relics and rare finds featured at the auction. This year will feature the \"Pathfinder\'s Last Compass\"!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">What? Did I hear you just correctly?
The Pathfinder\'s Last Compass? Are you certain?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_11">Have you... heard of it, sir?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_12">... Of course I\'ve heard of it, for it too is part of House Danish\'s lineage and history.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0011_13">How many family treasures are there?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS5_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2002_14">Please inform me of when exactly the auction will be held. It looks like I must extend my stay up until the very day of the auction!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">There are so many wonderful places inside the castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Lookie, lookie!
Isn\'t this place MARVELOUS?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Oh? Yeah, I guess, haha?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">\"Marvelous\" isn\'t quite the word I\'d use...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">La dee da de de!
I just want to store all sorts of cute things here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">GingerBrave! Let\'s decorate this place together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_7">OH...! That sounds pretty fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">(Wait a second... Things that are cute? Things that... GingerBright thinks... are cute...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">(... WAIT! Then that means?! That monster plant from last time!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">(Oh no, no, no! This can\'t end well!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">Ahem. I\'m gonna go find some things we\'ll need then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">I-I-I\'ll go with you, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_13">Then I\'ll help GingerBright then...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_14">Then let\'s do this! We can start with this wall first!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">UWAH?!
Erm... GingerBright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_16">There\'s something a bit weird here...
What should we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">OH! Those are just stale Cookies who didn\'t drink enough Life Potions!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">EEP!
So that\'s what happens when there\'s no Life Potions... That\'s really scary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Aw, it\'s not so bad when you take a closer look.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">You can tell they were all baked by the same witch! They all look pretty similar, don\'t they? Teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_21">...
\"Not so bad?\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_22">Aaand, if you look really close at them for a long time...
they blink, heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_23">OH! I\'ve got a wonderful idea just now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_24">Strawberry Cookie!
Let\'s leave this jar of stale Cookies where it is.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_25">And let\'s decorate the jar to make it prettier!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_26">I\'m sure the stale Cookies will feel all nice and warm!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_27">Oh... Is that... Really?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_28">C\'mon, it\'ll be fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_29">The jar will liven this place up SO MUCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_30">WE DID IT!
It\'s so pretty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_31">I don\'t think \"cute\" really describes this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_32">It seems closer to... creepy...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_33">Erm... It\'s not so bad?
Ha... haha...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_34">Really? But look at them, all inside!
They look so happy and cheery!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_35">I... guess so?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_36">We should keep up the pace!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_37">OK...!
Maybe we can put up some cozy lights...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_38">Good lighting is important when playing video games... Hehe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_39">What an awesome idea, Strawberry Cookie!
And maybe some curtains too?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_40">Curtains\'ll give a sense of privacy from prying eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_41">LIKE THIS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_42">...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_43">Hmm!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_44">I think...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_45">This room is getting better and better!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_46">It\'s... getting somewhere for sure, hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_47">Buuut... There\'s still something missing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_48">I wonder...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_49">OF COURSE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_50">We\'re missing a nice, pretty flower!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_51">Oh...!
I like flowers, hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_52">Did you know that, before we met you and Wizard Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_53">GingerBrave and I found the bestest and prettiest flower out in the hallways!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_54">We should give that flower a new home!
Right here, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_55">A flower from the castle hallways...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_56">That doesn\'t sound very...
Erm, I mean... is it safe?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_57">Don\'t you worry, Strawberry Cookie!
I\'ll bring it right now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_58">I\'m so excited! This place needs a bit of color to brighten up the place. That flower\'s gonna be perfect!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_59">Oh...
This isn\'t going to end well, is it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_60">GingerBrave! Wizard Cookie!
Welcome back, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_61">We\'re done decorating!
Sooo? What do you think?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_62">What in the name of wizard\'s beards and ice cream...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_63">Hey, Wizard Cookie... GingerBrave...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_64">What happened to you?!
You look so exhausted!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_65">I\'m... fine, I think...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_66">GAH?!
THAT FLOWER!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_67">Saying hello to an old friend, GingerBrave? TEEHEE!
I knew you\'d recognize this cutie pie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_68">I thought it\'d look perfect in this room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_69">Look at these ribbons too!
So fancy, hehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_70">(This is DEFINITELY not fancy!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_71">(No thank you...! I\'d rather lock myself in a treasure chest than staying another minute here!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_72">(Note to self, for all our sakes. \"If GingerBright thinks something\'s cute, RUN.\")</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_73">OOOH!
And last but not least!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_74">To help the flower grow all healthy and strong,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_75">we should leave lollipops right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_76">This flower really loves lollipops, hehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_77">(AGH!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_78">(Note to self... NEVER FORGET!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_79">(Note to self... NEVER FORGET! If GingerBright thinks something\'s cute...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_80">(RUN!!!)</string>
