  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.001.Story">When the sun sets, you can hear the sound of wheels turning in the distance, hinting at the start of a fun festival! This mobile stage is carved out of a large pumpkin, and is perfect for simple plays.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.002.Story">A place to store good luck gifts! I\'m sure anyone would love having one of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.003.Story">A storage for neatly keeping all concert outfits in one place. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.004.Story">A cart filled with sweet syrup droplets. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.005.Story">A cabbage dressed up for party! Having one of these around will definitely raise the mood of everyone around!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.006.Story">A tomato street light decorated for a festival. Even so, it\'d probably look good anywhere you place it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.007.Story">A table made for simple events. Let\'s find a good spot for it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Floor.008.Story">A small seat made out of a bottle cap. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Ceil.001.Story">A bunch of leaves tied together with a light source. Let\'s hang it up right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper portraying fireflies in the night sky. While the wallpaper does glow at night, it\'s not bright enough to disturb a good night\'s sleep.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SugarRushTheater.Deck.001.Story">Oh no, there\'s been an accident! Let\'s place it somewhere and pretend we didn\'t see it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.001">Repaired Syrup Faucet</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.002">Turn-around Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.003">Rusty Old Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.004">Tightly Blocked Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.005">Wild Weeds</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.006">Syrup-starved Grasslet</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.007">Timeworn Warning</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Wall.001">Twisty-turny Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Wall.002">Multi-way Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Ceil.001">Metered Pipe</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Ceil.002">Freely-grown Ivy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.WP.001">Dense Bush Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Deck.001">Parched Dirt Floor</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.001.Story">A faucet, fixed using things thrown away by the witches. You can truly feel Radish Cookie\'s determination radiating from it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.002.Story">A pipe that doesn\'t seem to be able to decide for a direction. I\'m sure we can find a place for it, still!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.003.Story">A pipe in a fairly rough shape. Let\'s find a place where it can shine!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.004.Story">A pipe that has been sealed by someone. I\'m sure there\'s a wall somewhere that could use this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.005.Story">Weeds growing freely from the ground. It\'s certain to bring any room closer to nature!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.006.Story">A small patch of grass that desperately needs more syrup to grow. Let\'s place it somewhere it can reach the skies!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Floor.007.Story">A warning sign that has faded with time. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Wall.001.Story">A strangely twisting pipe. Let\'s find a good place for it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Wall.002.Story">This pipe goes this way and that way too! Let\'s put it somewhere it can be of good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Ceil.001.Story">A pipe with a gadget attached for metering. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Ceil.002.Story">Ivy that grows however it pleases! One look away and the whole wall will be overgrown with it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper that makes you feel like you\'re in the middle of the forest. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FaucetRoom.Deck.001.Story">Basic floor made from dry dirt. It\'s not much, but it has a certain rustic charm.</string>
