  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep01.16.Story">The Witch\'s Castle is full of unexpected dangers. Will you really be able to escape out through the window?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.04.Story">The compass is being sold at the Grand Cabinet Hotel auction. It was fun working a brief part-time job at the hotel to get this!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.05.Story">The Cookies went through the hotel looking for captured guests and staff. Phew! That was a doozy!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.06.Story">Some memories fade with time. Will the two Cookies be able to resolve their complicated relationship?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.07.Story">GingerBrave has never cleaned before, but he seems to be doing well! The uniform fits like a glove too!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.08.Story">An encounter with the syndicate as they raid the auction! It was scary as they attacked in a group, but our friends have made it through together.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.09.Story">The first deadlift competition! It was far from an easy, but thanks to GingerBright, the Cookies have won!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.10.Story">What even is a cuteness contest...? No one is sure, but Strawberry Cookie was the perfect choice as competitor!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.11.Story">Wizard Cookie shocked everyone with the dish he presented for the contest. But it impressed Cashew, so... A win is a win!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep02.12.Story">The time has come to put an end to a long, bad relationship. Perhaps today\'s showdown was destined from the beginning.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.01.Story">The residents feel the groove again at the Sugar Beats Plaza! This is the moment Radish Cookie has been looking forward to while rejuvenating the barren garden!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.02.Story">The day when the Reaper harvested all the sweet residents of the Syrup Garden... This event is likely the reason for Rosemary Cookie\'s cold demeanor.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.03.Story">Rosemary Cookie realized as soon as she heard Radish Cookie\'s cry! Radish Cookie is no longer a half-baked Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.04.Story">Bright red eyes shining through the faded bushes! Our heroes\' first encounter with Radish Cookie started with a small misunderstanding!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.05.Story">Our friends helped Radish Cookie wake the garden up by soaking the soil in syrup! Is it just me, or can you still smell that sweet fragrance?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.06.Story">Our heroes engaged in a bout with the Churro Golem in front of the Sweet Heart! Why is he so angry?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.07.Story">Just sticking a straw in the ground makes syrup well up?! GingerBrave and friends completely lost track of time watching the amazing sight!</string>
