  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_4">The residents in there are...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">Are they hurt...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_6">An ambush?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0025_7">What happened?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_8">They\'re... naked!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Npc.0037_9">EEEK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">What\'s wrong with that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">The spa broke down
while they were inside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_12">And their clothes are gone too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.2004_13">We need to
fix up the spa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_14">We\'ll help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">Woohoo! It\'s fixin\' time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">We\'ve looked everywhere... but it looks like your hat isn\'t here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0024_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">Maybe we could take another look...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0024_4">But... I\'ve already looked everywhere I could think of...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_6">Hey, Radish Cookie? Could you ask Rosemary Cookie if she\'s seen our friend\'s hat?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Huh? Rosemary Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_8">The thing is... Well... Rosemary Cookie\'s the one who ruined the spa...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">WHAT?! There\'s no way she\'d do that! She loves taking care of the garden and everyone here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Um... What exactly happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_11">We were relaxin\' and chillin\' here after we called it a day, but then Rosemary Cookie showed up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_12">Mind you, we hadn\'t seen her in forever! So we called out to her, to say hi and stuff!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_13">"Hey, Rosemary Cookie! The spa\'s back in business!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_14">She took one look at the spa and all the hot syrup... and got all angry and frustrated!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_15">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_16">She flew into a rampage, I tell ya! Started to pour out the syrup all over the floor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_17">The place was ruined in the blink of an eye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">Huh... Why\'d she do that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0024_19">Was it a distraction to steal my hat?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">All that for a farmer\'s hat? If she were after MY hat, I\'d understand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0028_21">Anyways... y\'all should probably find her, and quick. Can\'t shake the feelin\' that something big\'s gonna go down soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_22">Don\'t worry! I\'ll find her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">Don\'t worry, Radish Cookie! We\'ll help you look for her.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_24">Maybe Rosemary Cookie\'s confused or something...? She\'s been sleeping for a long time, hasn\'t she?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_25">Thanks, y\'all. I\'m really glad y\'all are here with me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">We\'re happy to help! Now let\'s keep moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">Rosemary Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Huh? What\'s this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">There\'s a distinct fragrance...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">This aroma... it\'s so relaxing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">This is...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">One of Rosemary Cookie\'s hairs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Oh???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">The aroma is still fresh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">Which means she can\'t be far!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Hey, look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">There\'s more over there...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">Which means she must\'ve gone that way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">C\'mon! We should follow her trail!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">Let\'s move!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">Over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Found ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">W-w-w-wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">LOOK...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_5">The Churro Golem...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">Here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Rosemary Cookie\'s in danger!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">We need to save her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_9">Pipe down!
Look...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0034_10">Churrr...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_11">Stay still.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_12">You\'re too
injured and brittle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0034_13">Ch-ch-churr...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_14">Think before
barging into a fight.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_15">Running away is
always an option.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0034_16">Churro churr...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_17">No, I am not
disappointed in you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_18">You were just trying
to keep our promise...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_19">Our promise to keep the
garden dry and barren...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_20">Where everyone would
slumber peacefully, forever...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">Calm down, Churro Golem.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">... How could you do this to me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">How could you do that to our garden?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">WHAT SORT OF GARDENER ABANDONS HER GARDEN!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_11">Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">Afraid? Afraid of what? TELL ME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">Have... Have you forgotten?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">What\'s a \"Reaper\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0038_17">*SHRIEK!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">W-w-who was that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_19">It can\'t be...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_20">Churro Golem, follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0034_21">CHUR CHUUU!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">What\'s going on?! What\'s happening?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2004_1">No, I haven\'t
forgotten at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2004_2">The Reaper...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT2_Cookie.2004_3">I hate the Reaper!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0035_1">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_2">It\'s OK.
I\'m here now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0035_3">*Sniffle*
Rosemary... Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_4">Are you hurt...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0035_5">We were running...
We tripped...
I got separated and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_6">Running from what?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0035_7">S-S-S-S-SHE\'S BACK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_8">... No!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0035_9">THE REAPER IS BACK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0026_10">AAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_11">Mushy, mush!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_12">It\'s been a whiiile!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_13">Fresh, syrupy
muddy mud mud!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0037_14">EEEK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_15">Swingity, swing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_16">Scythe goes
slash and fwing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_17">Come now, into
the bags you go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0031_18">THE REEEAPER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_19">Ahhh, the smell of
fresh dirt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_20">The garden
has awakened!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_21">Whooo has fixed
the faucets???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_22">I LOOOVE you for it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_23">You\'d be great in
a glass of juice!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0027_24">MWAHAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0028_25">AAAAAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_26">Snap out of it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_27">Pay attention!
We must flee, immediately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_28">But we must get this
resident to safety first.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_29">Let me help.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_30">Me too!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_31">As for the others, you-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0029_32">HEEELP! HEEELP!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_33">Bookworm Tomato?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_1">*Huff puff*
I need... your help...! There are... others... trapped... up there...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Let us help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">Me too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">It\'s already begun... The garden is in danger once more...! But this is too soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">Churro Golem! Find out where the Reaper has gone. And tell everyone to get to safety!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0034_7">Chur-chuuu-churr!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">We need to stop running!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">We can fight back! The residents are healthier than ever! We\'ve got new friends who can help! We can do this, TOGETHER!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Is that really all you can think of?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">Together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">Wizard Cookie. GingerBright. With me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_15">The more time is wasted, the more lives are at risk.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">URRGH! That coward...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">I\'m sorry, kiddo. I... You didn\'t need to see that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_18">It\'s... It\'s alright.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">Lead the way, sport! We\'re here to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0029_20">Y-y-yeah! Follow me...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_1">This won\'t hurt... will it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Don\'t worry, it\'s a simple and quick procedure. You\'ll be snug inside the pod in no time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_3">Okay... I believe you. But I\'m still nervous...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">This\'ll be our first time helping with something like this! But everything\'ll be alright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_5">Oh... I, erm... I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_6">Wait... WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">If I may interject? I\'ve no hands-on, practical experience, but trust me when I say I am familiar with the procedure thanks to my extensive reading.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_8">\"A Beginner\'s Guide to Gardening\"...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_9">ROSEMARY COOKIE! NO SURGERY! NO SURGERRRYYY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">Rest assured, I will be the only one performing the procedure. You\'re in good hands... These Cookies are here to aid me with minor tasks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_11">No! I don\'t trust them!
CALL IT OFF!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">I think your... enthusiasm... was a bit too much for her.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">We, erm... We just wanted to reassure her that everything\'ll be fine...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">Here, take some of my hair and scatter it around our friend. It should calm her down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">Oh? Like this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_16">Ahhh... So aromatic... So fragrant...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_17">So soothing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_18">Now\'s our chance! Pull from both ends of the pod and don\'t let go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0035_19">Eh? Rosemary Cookie? Rosemary Cookie! ROSEMARY COOKIE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Npc.0030_1">A-one! And a-two! AND A-THREE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Npc.0030_2">We\'re back together again! Thanks, Rosemary Cookie. You\'re the best gardener ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_3">I couldn\'t have done it without the help of these two.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_4">Thank you, GingerBright and Wizard Cookie. I meant it when I said I couldn\'t have done it without you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_5">You\'re really good at gardening and taking care of the residents!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_6">I try... But it\'s always better if no one gets hurt in the first place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_7">If only Radish Cookie hadn\'t restored the garden...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_8">But everything Radish Cookie\'s done so far was to help the garden, wasn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_9">Pardon me for asking so bluntly but... Why mustn\'t the Syrup Garden be awakened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_11">You\'ve seen much of the garden already, haven\'t you? And you\'re familiar with how verdant it can truly be.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_12">The flow of sweet syrup, the rich soil, the heartiest of residents... Everything within the garden is fragrant and aromatic, healthy and robust.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_13">You probably think it\'s the sweetest of blessings, don\'t you? But you\'re wrong. In reality, it\'s the bitterest of curses.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_14">A curse? But why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Npc.0030_15">The witch knows that our garden is special. That we\'re special. And because of the syrup... we taste special.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_16">Wait... Then you mean...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_17">We\'ve always tried to avoid the witch\'s attention, hiding and lying low. The sweetest of residents must always take extra care.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_18">Everyone was quite skilled in hiding amongst the leaves and bushes, but we lived in peace. That is... until the Reaper appeared.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_19">I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_20">The witch offered rewards for our capture. Raiders and hunters swarmed the garden in droves to offer us to the witch. And the Reaper was the worst of them all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_21">Many of our friends were captured and sacrificed to the witch. Foul rumors and horror stories soon reached our ears, of how the witch enjoyed her meals...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_22">That\'s horrible...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_23">Radish Cookie wanted to resist, fight off the invaders. She built all sorts of gadgets in her attempt to keep them and the Reaper at bay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_24">But I knew it was futile... With each passing day, we lost more and more of our closest friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_25">Then one day, Radish Cookie left the garden, claiming that the answer to defeating the Reaper might be out there somewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_26">As she ran off into the distance, I told the Churro Golem my plan. Something that I had been thinking over for a very long time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_27">That\'s when you asked the Churro Golem to break all the faucets, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_28">Hmm... Making the garden a dry and barren place and removing the Syrup Garden from the Reaper\'s sights.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_29">Yes. I thought it was the only way to ensure our survival... The garden, the residents, myself,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_30">and Radish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_31">You knew she wouldn\'t dare face the Reaper alone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_32">It was a solid plan, and it worked. But I did not take into account one major variable...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_33">Which was...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_34">I knew Radish Cookie was persistent and stubborn. But I didn\'t know that her persistence would succeed in restoring the garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_35">She is- Wait, did you hear that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0001_36">Rosemary Cookie!!!
ROSEMARY COOKIE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_37">It\'s...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0003_38">It is! It\'s GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0001_39">Rosemary Cookie!
Where are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0001_40">Rosemary Cookie!!!
We need your help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.0025_41">Something\'s definitely wrong! We should find him quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_42">*GASP*
Radish Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ6_POR2_Cookie.2005_43">Enough chatter! Come, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_1">The residents...
Where are they?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Huh, I don\'t see anyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_3">... I swear they
were right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_4">Maybe they\'re
hiding in there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_5">Are you sure this is
the right place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0037_6">*GASP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_7">You said to b-b-b-bring
sweet ones here so I did!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_8">NOW LET MY SISTER GO!
DON\'T HURT HER!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_9">SHE\'S NOT A FRUIT,
SHE\'S A VEGETABLE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0033_10">I... AM... FRUIT...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_11">That\'s the worst thing
you could say right now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_12">HAHA! What a brave
tomato you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_13">But not very smart, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_14">I... wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_15">Think outside the box!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_16">"If I bathed in sugar,
sprinkle sprinkle!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_17">"I\'d be sweet no
matter who I am!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0033_18">She\'s got a point!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0029_19">WAAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_20">Let them go!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_21">Oooh!
YOUUU!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_22">You smell like lovely lil\' ssstrawwwberries!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0027_23">The Witch will
enjoy tasting you!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_24">The... WITCH...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_25">Uwa... WAAAH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_26">STRAWBERRY COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_27">G-G-G-GINGERBRAAAVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_28">Wait GingerBrave, I\'ll go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_29">I know the paths
and shortcuts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_30">I\'ll go too!
I\'m a pretty good runner!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_31">No, you need to
find Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_32">Tell her what happened and
she\'ll know what to do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_33">I won\'t run away from fear!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2004_34">Hang in there,
Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_35">Rosemary Cookie!
Where are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_36">Rosemary Cookie!!!
We need your help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">GingerBrave!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">What happened?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_4">He\'s wandered the brush.
His dough is scratched.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">The Reaper...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">THE REAPER HAS
STRAWBERRY COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0037_7">Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_8">Where\'s Radish Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_9">I\'m here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_10">Radish Cookie...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_11">I used every shortcut
I knew but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_12">The Reaper...
She got away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">Then Strawberry
Cookie is...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_14">This can\'t be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_15">I\'m not giving up!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_16">The Reaper can\'t
have gotten too far...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2004_17">We can do this if we
fight together and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_18">Stop that rambling
nonsense about fighting!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_19">You haven\'t
changed at all...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0035_20">WAAAH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0025_21">HEEELP!
Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_22">I can\'t... I can\'t lose any
more of my friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_23">I need to find a way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_24">Where no one gets hurt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_25">I must save everyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_26">No matter the cost...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_27">This is the way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_28">The greenhouse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_29">Oh? What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_30">There\'s a secret greenhouse
built in the garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_31">Within that greenhouse...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_32">is an answer
to saving everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_33">Urgh...
Then let\'s get moving...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_34">Uhm, are you
sure you\'re OK???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_35">If we can...
save Strawberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_36">a few broken crumbs
won\'t stop me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_37">Come.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_38">Follow me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_39">I won\'t lose anyone again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2005_40">Never again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">Where...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">The R-R-Reaper...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">I got... captured...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">What...
What\'s going on?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">*GASP!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_1">Something smells sweeter and riper than ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0026_2">Please! Fear will only make me age and rot faster!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0026_3">I will turn into browned mush! There\'s no reason to take me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0026_4">You cannot offer such a pathetic, rotten specimen as I to the witch, can you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_5">Oh ho ho? That only means produce such as yourself must be disposed of more quickly and efficiently!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0026_6">I- No, that\'s... Oh dear...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_7">What else have we got here... Ah! A vegetable!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0031_8">A fair warning! No one likes broccoli!
I\'m no use, I should go free, no one likes fresh broccoli like me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_9">But fresh broccoli is scrrrumptious in all types of stir-fry! Kehehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0031_10">Cruuuel faaate...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">She\'s taking the residents somewhere else...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_12">In you go! Nice and quietly, one by one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0029_13">Where are you taking us...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_14">OH!!! Well, you asked and you shall receive... You\'re going to Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">Mount St. Crème...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_16">Such a lovely place! Where eternal frost keeps everyone ripe and fresh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_17">Aw, don\'t make that face, little tasty! You should feel blessed to call Mount St. Crème your new home!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_18">Well, technically speaking, a temporary home... Because your final destination is the witch\'s dining table!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">*GASP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_20">So many recipes, so many appetizers and entrées! I wonder where you\'ll end up?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_21">Maybe you\'ll all be part of a hearty stew served with Cookies for dessert?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0026_22">Nooo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_23">Or maybe as a healthy snack for the witch\'s minions?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0029_24">No-o-o-o!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_25">Or if you\'re super lucky, you might end up as part of the greatest supper with that sleepy Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_26">Oooh, I heard that Cookie\'s a special one too... So tasty, ripened dough... But very sleepy apparently.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_27">A sleepy Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_28">GingerDozer! She\'s talking about GingerDozer!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">I need to get out of here and find everyone! We need to save GingerDozer from the witch!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_30">Just gotta find a way out of here first and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_31">GAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_32">You know, talking to yourself can often bring unwanted attention, sweet little Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_33">W-w-where did you come from?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_34">Were you thinking about whether you\'d be a snack or dessert?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_35">Maybe with tea? Or with coffee?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_36">NO! NONE OF THE ABOVE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0025_1">*Huff... puff...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0003_2">We\'ve been
running forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2004_3">There\'s a greenhouse
this far out...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2004_4">Even the hardiest of residents
couldn\'t make it this far...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.2005_5">Just a bit further.
We\'re almost there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_6">We can\'t give up!
Strawberry Cookie\'s counting on us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ1_CUT2_Cookie.0001_7">Let\'s clear this outta
the way and keep moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">The greenhouse is just ahead.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Finally!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">I\'m quite curious as to what this greenhouse contains...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Something the matter, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">Something smells funny...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">*Sniff sniff*
Oh, is that me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">No... Something else... I don\'t know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">It\'s an unfamiliar smell... Acrid, stinging...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">Normally, wherever Rosemary Cookie goes, there\'s an aromatic scent of herbs left in her wake... But this scent is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Come, let us head inside. Time is of the essence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Looks like the path is blocked.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">Which means it\'s another job for teamwork!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">*Sniff sniff*
Hmmm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0037_1">Whoa...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">WOW! This place is amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">What\'s that?
It\'s emitting a
strange light!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_4">Denatonium Hedera.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">Dinner-toe-um... Hedro?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_6">I\'ve been preparing
for this day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_7">Everything here,
I\'ve grown from seeds...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_8">All by yourself?
That\'s amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_9">This plant may not
seem like much,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_10">but it will open the path
to our garden\'s salvation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">Anything with the word \"nium\"
is usually powerful magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_12">It\'s quite common knowledge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_13">Here.
Give me your hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Whoa...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_15">You must plant
this in the garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2005_16">The fate of the Syrup Garden
is in your hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">Dinner-tonion Hairdo.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_18">Protect the Syrup Garden
and all its residents!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0037_20">AAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_21">Wh-What\'s happening?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_22">It\'s growing everywhere?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_23">*Gasp!*
The ground is...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0036_24">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_25">The soil and syrup are
getting contaminated!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_26">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_27">ROSEMARY COOKIE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">WAAAGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_29">Wizard Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_30">It\'ll be OK!
Hang in there, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2004_31">We need to get rid of
the denatonium vines, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_32">Got it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_33">HEEELP ME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0036_1">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_2">*Huff puff*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Did we kill it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0037_4">Don\'t use THAT word!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0036_5">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">Up there!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_7">EEEK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0036_8">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0036_9">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_10">It\'s growing at
an alarming rate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">Oh jeez...
Did I anger it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_12">Did we kill it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_13">At this rate, the garden\'ll
end up a wasteland!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_14">And it just came
back to life...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">Over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_16">Rosemary Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2004_17">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0036_18">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_19">Don\'t give up!
These vines won\'t stop us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">We need to find
Rosemary Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_1">There\'s no end...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_2">But I won\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_4">You guys!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0036_5">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_6">No... I won\'t give up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_7">I will... protect...
this garden!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2005_8">Radish Cookie.
Stop.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2004_9">Rosemary... Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">The Denatonioum Hedera was nurtured with one of the witch\'s potions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">It will grow exponentially, and won\'t stop until all of the garden\'s syrup is transformed into the bitterest of concoctions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">NOT ON MY WATCH! I\'ll keep fighting!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">The garden we remember is gone! And nothing can ever bring it back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">This garden! The residents! You and me! We can never go back!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">You...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Why are you doing this?! Why won\'t you protect the garden and our friends?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_8">I AM PROTECTING THEM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">How many friends have we lost... We were helpless, useless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Our garden... A stomping grounds for evil and death.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">And you... Reckless and thoughtless as ever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">I am protecting everything we loved. I am saving them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">The garden we knew will be gone forever, but no one will ever hurt us again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2005_15">As long as everyone remains unharmed... I will do anything it takes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">Rosemary Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0027_17">MWAHAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_1">MWAHAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_2">Sorry for interrupting
your moment, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_3">Watching puny things like you
being all serious was too much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_4">First a haul of fresh produce,
and now some Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_5">Ah! What an
amazing harvest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0034_6">Chur CHUUUR
CHUR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0027_7">Oooh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_8">Churro Golem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0034_9">Chur, CHUR CHUR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_10">Are you crazy...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_11">NO!
I won\'t leave you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0034_12">CHUR!
CHUUUR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2004_13">Churro Golem!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_14">It\'s keeping our promise...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_15">To protect the Syrup Garden...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Npc.0036_16">*Rustle rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2004_17">LOOK OUT!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2005_18">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.2004_19">We need to get
her out of here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0001_20">OK! A couple more
vines won\'t stop us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ5_CUT2_Cookie.0003_21">IT\'S GARDENING TIIIME!
Teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">We\'re surrounded...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">It\'s no use...
I\'m out of magic...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2004_3">Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0027_4">MWAHAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_1">I\'ll remember this harvest for AGES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_2">Fresh produce, Cookies, and even a Churro Golem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_3">My sweet, sweet, Syrup Garden, how I\'ve missed you sooo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">Radish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">Take the others... and get away from here, as far as you can.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_7">And this time... don\'t look back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">What\'re you saying? Snap out of it!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">My leg is broken, I felt it crumble... You and I both know that all of us can\'t make it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">I won\'t give up! C\'mon, sis!
The garden, our friends... They\'re all counting on us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Just listen to me for once! The Denatonium Hedera will take over the entire garden and there\'s no way to stop it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">Once the garden is desiccated, no one will gaze upon us. The witch, the Reaper... No more harm will befall our friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">The residents who have failed to flee the garden will burrow into the ground... forever hibernating, forever hidden and safe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">Everyone will be perpetually unharmed... And more importantly, alive.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_15">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">Safe? Unharmed? ALIVE?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">You think the residents will be thankful for being stuck in the ground, away from everyone they love? You think this is the answer to staying safe?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_18">You have no right to force such cruel isolation upon any of them, on ME! I\'ve been alone, I\'ve been isolated, I KNOW WHAT IT\'S LIKE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_19">You crumbskull!!!
That isn\'t protecting life, it\'s living in fear!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_20">Sure, life can suck and be full of bruises and falling down, but it\'s also about getting back up and keeping at it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_21">Having your friends backs! Giving a helping hand! Cheering each other on! Living free to chase dreams and hope for a better future!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_22">That\'s the real meaning of life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2004_23">You call yourself old and wise? BAH! You\'re just... just a selfish coward!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_24">*GASP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2005_25">... I... Radish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_26">BWAHAHA! Give this Cookie a ROUND. OF. APPLAUSE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_27">Splennndid! Maaarvelous! What an inspiring, insightful speech from our lovely flourbrain here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_28">Oh, I do so wish to hear the rest of your fire-spitting debate...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0027_29">But tut, tut, tut... We have an appointment to keep... at the witch\'s dining table!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0027_1">What on...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2004_2">Huh...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2004_3">The mushroom farmers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2004_4">The sweet peas!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2004_5">Even the Cherry Twins?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_6">They\'re all taking a stand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_7">To protect the garden...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_8">To protect each other...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_9">To live and be free...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0028_10">We\'re with you,
Rosemary Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0030_11">You\'re not alone
in this fight!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0025_12">We\'re done
running in fear!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0032_13">Rise up,
Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0032_14">For our garden!
For our home!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0034_15">CHURRR!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0028_16">We\'re with you to the
bitter end, so get up!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0028_17">Or Radish Cookie won\'t
let you forget this day, ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_18">More nagging from HER...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_19">I\'ve had enough
for a lifetime.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.0001_20">Looks like Rosemary
Cookie\'s made a decision!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.0003_21">With a bright and
lovely smile too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0027_22">EEEWWW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Npc.0027_23">STICKY AND GOOEY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.0003_24">The Reaper\'s slowed down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.0025_25">Syrup\'s our ticket
out of this mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.0001_26">Hang on, Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2005_27">It\'s time for a lesson!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT2_Cookie.2004_28">You raggedy pumpkin face!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">GingerBrave!
Over here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">We need to save
Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">Let\'s throw some syrup
to slow the Reaper down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">That should gimme
enough time to free everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_4">Oooh, so you have a plan, eh?
SO DO I!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Npc.0027_5">IT\'S HARVEST TIME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_1">STICKY!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_2">What?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_3">Cheeky!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_4">URGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_5">Oh?
Straws, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_6">Say BYE-BYE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0001_7">She cut the straws!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.2005_8">Don\'t panic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_9">Taaake...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_10">THIS! HEEHEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_11">I seeeee youuu!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_12">HAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_13">I can do this all day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_14">HEEHEEHEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_15">Still wriggling?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0027_16">Take this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0027_1">Cheeky pipsqueaks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0027_2">You\'ll regret that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_CUT2_Npc.0027_1">Eugh... Eugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0001_1">The Reaper\'s slowed down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0003_2">Now\'s our chance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.2005_3">Ready, Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.2004_4">HAHA!
Of course I am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Npc.0027_1">Can\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">G-g-guys...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0037_2">You\'re OK! WOOHOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">Can\'t... breathe...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">OH, OHHH, OHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">GINGERDOZER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">GingerDozer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">What about GingerDozer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">When I was captured...! The Reaper said something about GingerDozer and where he might be!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Oooh!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">But... I don\'t remember the exact name of the place... I was too scared and couldn\'t concentrate clearly but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">The Reaper definitely said... It sounded like Mount? Mont? Mountain?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_7">Was it perhaps... Mount St. Crème?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_8">YEAH! That\'s it! Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Hm, I\'m not familiar with that area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">Soils have mercy...
If your friend is truly at Mount St. Crème, he doesn\'t have much time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Not enough time? Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">The entirety of Mount St. Crème was regarded as sacred ground. It\'s existed for ages, considered ancient even before Radish Cookie and I were baked.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">It\'s said that those on the verge of spoil and rot... were able to exist in a state of freshest youth for all eternity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Eternal freshness...? Is such a thing possible?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">It sounds wonderful! That means GingerDozer is all fresh and comfy, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">If it were the old Mount St. Crème we\'re talking about, then yeah... But nowadays...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_17">No longer is it considered sacred. It has been corrupted... a place of misery and doom.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">Nooo...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_19">Mount St. Crème is now a perpetually frozen prison, where all become one with the frost or until...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_20">Until they meet their fate upon the witch\'s dining table as a meal for the witch herself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">That sounds horrible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">If GingerDozer is really at Mount St. Crème, then it must mean...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2005_23">Your friend, GingerDozer, may potentially be offered to the witch upon the dining table.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_24">Nooo! GingerDozer...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_25">Hey! Hey now!
Don\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_27">You said it yourselves.
There\'s nothing that you can\'t do as a team!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.2004_28">And if I know y\'all, you\'ll definitely find a way to save your friend no matter the odds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">... Radish Cookie\'s right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0025_30">I- well... I must admit, despite the odds, we have had a remarkable winning streak so far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0003_31">We can do anything! Together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_32">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_33">We can do this! WE GOT THIS! I know we do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_POR1_Cookie.0001_34">Thanks, Radish Cookie!
Thanks, Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT2_Cookie.0001_1">Let\'s head out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT2_Cookie.0001_2">To Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ7_CUT2_Npc.0037_3">And save GingerDozer!</string>
