  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.06.Story">A small spa in the garden filled with the sweetest and most aromatic of steam! The syrup is heated to the perfect temperature over a long period of time. When relaxing in the tub, you can almost feel your stress melting away.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.07.Story">A sturdy hut built with deep-fried dough and bolstered with thick, hardened chocolate. As a finishing touch, the Churro Golem sprinkled cinnamon around the entire hut to truly make it a cozy home.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.08.Story">Lost a twig? Leaves withering? Stem feeling weak? Then you might be in need of medical care! The residents of the Syrup Garden visit this clinic for all their health issues and needs. From surgical equipment to syrup medicine, this clinic has everything that\'s needed to provide top-notch care!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.09.Story">Who would force two siblings to share a room... It\'s a recipe for disaster! Luckily, the two tomatoes have negotiated somewhat of a deal by splitting the room exactly in half.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.10.Story">The Reaper\'s warehouse for storing equipment. Everything about this place is creepy, no doubt about it. What\'s that thing used for? What\'s this? Why does something like that exist?! Let\'s get out of here before we\'re offered up to the Witch\'s Table!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.11.Story">If you look carefully around the dark greenhouse, you\'ll find some strange seedlings growing peacefully... Sure, they look harmless enough, but they\'re giving off a weird vibe.</string>
