  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest01.Summary">Our heroes find Radish Cookie in front of a broken spa. Is there anyone inside? \"EEEK! Don\'t come inside!\"</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest02.Summary">The Cookies have fixed the spa, but learn that it was Rosemary Cookie who broke it. Why would she do such a thing?</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest03.Summary">Our friends find one of Rosemary Cookie\'s leafy hairs leading somewhere. C\'mon, let\'s follow the trail!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest04.Summary">A shocking discovery! The Cookies learn that it was Rosemary Cookie who forced the garden to become dry! Radish Cookie angrily asks her why she would do such a horrendous thing.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest05.Summary">The Reaper has returned to the Syrup Garden and is kidnapping the residents. Our friends decide to help protect the garden!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest06.Summary">We learn that Rosemary Cookie forced the garden to become dry in order to protect the garden and ensure the survival of the residents and Radish Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest07.Summary">While trying to save the residents, the Cookies walk into a trap. OH NO! Strawberry Cookie has been kidnapped by the Reaper!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch03.SQuest08.Summary">Rosemary Cookie helplessly looks at the ensuing chaos and is struck with fear... She forms a plan to save the garden from the Reaper, once and for all.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest01.Summary">Strawberry Cookie is held prisoner somewhere by the Reaper. But she overhears something about GingerDozer\'s whereabouts!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest02.Summary">Our friends follow Rosemary Cookie to a secret greenhouse. Radish Cookie feels uneasy, with an unexplained sense of foreboding.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest03.Summary">Rosemary Cookie asks the Cookies to plant a type of vine into the ground, a Denatonium Hedera seedling. But the vines grow out of control and begin to pollute the garden with frightening speed!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest04.Summary">Our heroes try to weed out the vines and prevent it from growing any further. The garden was just restored!!! We can\'t lose it again!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest05.Summary">Rosemary Cookie is determined to stop the Reaper from appearing in the garden, even if it means ruining the garden. Radish Cookie is heartbroken at Rosemary Cookie\'s desperation.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest06.Summary">The group believes that all hope is lost... but garden\'s residents appear to resist the Reaper\'s harvesting! Get up, Rosemary Cookie! Fight with us! Fight for our home!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep03.Ch04.SQuest07.Summary">Our heroes have defeated the Reaper. Strawberry Cookie tells the group about GingerDozer\'s whereabouts, a place called Mount St. Crème.</string>
