  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Floor.001.Story">Feel like your strength is withering? Try resting a while in hot, bubbly syrup! In no time, you\'ll find yourself up and jumping, even sweeter than before!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Floor.002.Story">A plain syrup pump. It doesn\'t seem to have been used in a while.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Floor.003.Story">A shallow tub, a perfectly safe alternative for veggies with little legs.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Floor.004.Story">A well-wiped chair. Sit on this for a more comfortable time washing!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Wall.001.Story">A plate enchanted with fog-repelling magic. A perfect fit for a hot, steamy bathroom.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Wall.002.Story">A half-transparent window with an intricate zig-zag pattern. Let\'s place it somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Ceil.001.Story">An elegant chandelier. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Rug.001.Story">A surprisingly soft mat made out of sedimentary rock. It feels great to walk on, so let\'s place it somewhere right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.WP.001.Story">Wall panels made out of gleaming, sugary syrup. Who wouldn\'t want to bedazzle their room like this?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.HumidSpa.Deck.001.Story">Shiny jade floor tiles. Let\'s decorate a room with these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Floor.001.Story">This scale has been redesign to quickly tend to scratches and other serious injuries that the residents of the garden may suffer. May every resident lying down on this scale have a speedy recovery!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Floor.002.Story">A light fixture powered by small, hard-working fireflies. With this, no procedure will ever have to be done with bad visibility!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Floor.003.Story">A medical sickbed for giving injured leeks and green onions comfortable rest. We should keep one around for emergencies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Floor.004.Story">A medical sickbed for giving unwell apples comfortable rest. We should keep one around for emergencies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Floor.005.Story">It\'s important for plant health to spray them regularly with syrup. This bottle also contains a herb to bring the fragrance to the next level.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Wall.001.Story">A roll of leaves that do a decent job at blocking sunlight out. Let\'s hang it up somewhere right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Ceil.001.Story">A hanging light made out of a turquoise pendant. Let\'s put it in a room to lighten it up!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Ceil.002.Story">A hammock made for the comfort of soft and frail fruits. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Ceil.003.Story">A syrup filled with sweet, sticky syrup. Let\'s hang it somewhere it can be reached in an emergency.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Hanger.001.Story">A rope where you can hang emergency packs of syrup. Let\'s hang them up somewhere they can easily be accessed!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.WP.001.Story">Tent cloth that has been carefully stitched together to not let anything through. We should be able to find a good place to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FreshClinic.Deck.001.Story">A floor covered in band aids. Maybe it got hurt after someone stepped too hard on it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.001.Story">Lie on top of the cherry pie, looking at the cherry-topped drink above, and fall asleep to the pleasant cherry fragrance. This piece is a must-have for all the cherry lovers out there!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.002.Story">The mere thought of that unfinished book below is enough to get rid of all your sleepiness! Now it\'s up to you—5 more minutes in bed, or getting up to find out what happens in the next chapter!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.003.Story">These fruits have been polished to the point where they positively sparkle! ... Or are they just replicas?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.004.Story">These cherry lights give off a comfy red light. Let\'s place them somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.005.Story">A seat made out of a wood stump and a leaf. Let\'s use it to give a room a more natural vibe!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.006.Story">A wood stump with a cute strawberry seat cover. Let\'s place it somewhere right away!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.007.Story">These color crayons are enough to bring your wildest imaginations to the real world! Let\'s give them to someone who\'ll make good use of them.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.008.Story">A box filled with bright-red tomatoes. Just looking at them makes you feel a bit peckish!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Floor.009.Story">A planter where small tomatoes—dreaming of one day becoming large and tasty—grow. Let\'s help them achieve those dreams, and place them somewhere with loads of sunlight!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Wall.001.Story">A collection of small pictures to hang up on a wall. Let\'s find a nice place for them!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Wall.002.Story">A drawing of two cherries. Even from this rough depiction, you can tell they are a match made in heaven!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.WP.001.Story">A wall made of wooden planks, painted in a soothing turquoise color. Put this up in a room to give it a natural, yet stylish feel!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BubbleBedroom.Deck.001.Story">Mix and match these tiles to create the floor pattern you want!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Floor.001.Story">A special canopy that keeps the cinnamon fragrance inside thanks to the roof covered in thick chocolate sauce. In the Churro Golem\'s language, a structure like this is called \"CHUR-OH-CHUR!!!\" Just make sure to put a rising inflection on the final syllable, as anything else obviously would cause a fight to break out.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Floor.002.Story">Various items that seems to have been part of a butler\'s belongings. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Floor.003.Story">A planter of churros, growing nice and healthy. Let\'s take good care of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Wall.001.Story">A lovely, heart-shaped cabinet. This would make a great gift to any Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Ceil.001.Story">Pieces of churro that seemingly were about to be eaten. Instead, now they get to be decoration!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Ceil.002.Story">A churro hanging from the ceiling. It seems to be used to practice strange combat techniques.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Rug.001.Story">A rug made out of oil paper. Someone might like having this in their room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.Deck.001.Story">This floor may be a bit unpleasant to walk on, but it is great at keeping the room warm even on cold days!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WellFriedHut.WP.001.Story">The very solid wall of a hut. What a lucky find!</string>
