  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.FreshClinic.Story">Lost a twig? Leaves withering? Stem feeling weak? Then you might be in need of medical care! The residents of the Syrup Garden visit this clinic for all their health issues and needs. From surgical equipment to syrup medicine, this clinic has everything that\'s needed to provide top-notch care!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.BubbleBedroom.Story">Who would force two siblings to share a room... It\'s a recipe for disaster! Luckily, the two tomatoes have negotiated somewhat of a deal by splitting the room exactly in half.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.WellFriedHut.Story">A sturdy hut built with deep-fried dough and bolstered with thick, hardened chocolate. As a finishing touch, the Churro Golem sprinkled cinnamon around the entire hut to truly make it a cozy home.</string>
