  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2005_22">Radish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0034_23">Chuuur...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">The Churro Golem breaking the faucets... making the garden go bone dry. That was all your doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">Days and nights alone, trying to wake up you and the residents. My endless failures to irrigate the garden with nothing but scrappy old parts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">And all that time... It was you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0034_5">Chu-CHUR CHUUUR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">... A cowardly gardener.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">I was afraid, Radish Cookie.
I was afraid...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2005_15">The Reaper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ6_CUT1_Npc.0034_5">Churr... Rrro...</string>
