  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0518.001.Story">A headset hand-crafted by Strawberry Crepe Cookie. It rumbles threateningly if you get too close... Maybe it\'s more than just a head ornament?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0518.002.Story">A special piece of equipment that can analyze structural composition and ingredients of Cookies. According to Strawberry Crepe Cookie, it is still an early prototype, so it can only measure powder levels up to 9000.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0518.003.Story">This little friend was made by Strawberry Crepe Cookie using discarded parts. But as can be seen with this pupper, even unwanted parts combined can make a dear friend!</string>
