  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.13">Secret Greenhouse</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.12.Story">The Reaper\'s warehouse for storing equipment. Everything about this place is creepy, no doubt about it. What\'s that thing used for? What\'s this? Why does something like that exist?! Let\'s get out of here before we\'re offered up to the Witch\'s Table!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep03.Blueprint.13.Story">If you look carefully around the dark greenhouse, you\'ll find some strange seedlings growing peacefully... Sure, they look harmless enough, but they\'re giving off a weird vibe.</string>
