  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Floor.001.Story">A makeshift prison made from a hollowed-out pumpkin. The dim red color and the putrid pumpkin stench can make a softie out of even the toughest of Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Floor.002.Story">A pumpkin that happened to be in the wrong place at the wrong time when someone could no longer contain their frustration.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Floor.003.Story">A trap that seems to have its best days behind it. The teeth still look sharp, so better not take any chances!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Wall.001.Story">A door from which a sweet, fruity scent emanates. You can place it in any room, but it somehow always leads to the same place.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Wall.002.Story">A place to hang gardening tools. Let\'s place it somewhere it comes to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Ceil.001.Story">A ceiling-mounted fixture for storing fruit. Every room needs fruit, so let\'s find a good place for it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Ceil.002.Story">Or is it half-emptied? Every Cookie in the castle seems to have a different perspective.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Rug.001.Story">A rug made out of hay raked together to form a nice circle. Let\'s make good use of it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.Deck.001.Story">Old, wooden floor panels that give away your presence when you walk on them. While not optimal for someone who likes to go for discreet late-night snacks, they are surprisingly effective for alerting you about intruders!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.BroodingFarmShed.WP.001.Story">A wall made of less-than-sturdy planks. Don\'t lean on them, unless you\'re looking for a quick way to create an extra entrance.</string>
