  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.001.Story">A giant Wafflebot undergoing research by Strawberry Crepe Cookie. It won\'t be long before we have adorable giant Wafflebot dogs running around the place, happily wagging their tails!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.002.Story">Manually control Wafflebots from this elevated seat! It\'s made with a fluffy strawberry crepe cushion, so your feet will be fine even after multiple hours of use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.003.Story">One of Strawberry Crepe Cookie\'s more advanced creations—a data processing device capable of complex calculations using data from all the Cookie\'s other machines. With this, you can find out everything from the exact density of a Wafflebot to its optimal temperature and suitable toppings! The ultimate Wafflebot is within reach!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.004.Story">A handy tool used for fixing broken waffle machinery. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.005.Story">A control panel for various mechanical devices. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Floor.006.Story">A soft footrest made from a cone of strawberry cream. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Wall.001.Story">A schematic for creating a giant Wafflebot puppy. The \"Version 618\" at the bottom shows how much effort has been put into creating the perfect companion.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Wall.002.Story">A display showing the vitals of a nearby Wafflebot. We should probably put it somewhere in sight.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Wall.003.Story">A monitor detailing the science of Cookie anatomy. I had no clue all of this was inside me!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Wall.004.Story">A mechanical fan providing air circulation to a room. Strawberry Crepe Cookie says the added spiky edges make any room at least 7.8% cooler.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Ceil.001.Story">A lamp made from a waffle cone and strawberry cream. It gives off a smooth light that keeps your eyes from straining, even after hours of research.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Ceil.002.Story">Fluorescent lights with modules to control resistivity, so that you can research under optimally controlled conditions.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Rug.001.Story">A floor-mounted glass pane with a sturdy crepe frame. It gives the room a high-tech, yet clean look!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.WP.001.Story">A wall filled with circuits, lighting up as they activate. The very essence of the curious mind of Strawberry Crepe Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0518.Deck.001.Story">The more mechanical devices in a lab, the more neatly the lab needs to be maintained! That\'s the reason Strawberry Crepe Cookie keeps this floor free from even a single speck of dust.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Floor.001.Story">A beautiful fountain, endlessly spouting syrup. All year round, it seems to be surrounded by pretty flowers and butterflies, drawn by the sweet fragrance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Floor.002.Story">A fountain with fresh water pouring out of it. The sound of water flowing down through flower pots, forgotten in time, bring peace of mind for nearby Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Floor.003.Story">A single tulip, leaves adorned with little drops of dew.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Floor.004.Story">A transient abode for plants looking for someplace new to live.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Floor.005.Story">A table for replanting Candy Flowers. Perfect for simple gardening needs!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Wall.001.Story">Stained glass depicting a flower bud just about to bloom. It must have taken a lot of effort for it to get this far.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Wall.002.Story">Stained glass depicting a bud sprouting through the earth. You may have a long way to go, but I\'ll be there cherring you on throughout your journey!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Wall.003.Story">Stained glass depicting seeds planted deep in the ground. It serves as a reminder that even the most beautiful flower once grew silently in the darkness of the soil.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Hanger.001.Story">A basket filled with large leaves. Just imagine a relaxed afternoon spent resting in this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Hanger.002.Story">A hand-made ladder that can do a bit of everything. Let\'s place it somewhere easy to reach.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Hanger.003.Story">A leafy curtain that blocks out unwanted sunlight. If you leave the window open to let the wind in, you\'ll find the room is filled with a pleasant fragrance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Ceil.001.Story">A ceiling lamp made from a fully-bloomed daisy flower. It\'s sure to bring your room both light as well as a sense of elegance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Ceil.002.Story">Shh... Even as little seedlings, Cookievorous plants tend to have quite the temper if they don\'t get enough sleep.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Ceil.003.Story">A planter hanging from the ceiling, adorned with a cute ribbon. Let\'s put it somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Ceil.004.Story">A coconut in need of some more rest. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice and quiet.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.WP.001.Story">This herb wallpaper gives a fresh, spring-like feeling to any room it\'s placed in!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0063.Deck.001.Story">Spring blooms, even in the tiniest of cracks! These stone tiles have pretty flowers and greenery growing in between them.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0063">Herb Cookie\'s Room of Herbal Tranquility</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0063.Story">Herb Cookie\'s peaceful room is filled with the fragrant scent of herbs and the faint rustling of grass. All concerns and anxieties are washed away as you enter this tranquil haven.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.Herb.Limited.Floor.001">Herb Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.Herb.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy with a design capturing the characteristics of Herb Cookie perfectly. When you hug it, the faint herbal scent will help make you relax.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0079.Season">Floating Fluffy Seedpuff</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0080.Season">Drifting Fluffy Seedpuff</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0081.Season">Hovering Fluffy Seedpuff</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0082.Season">Verdant Spring Topibeary Gardener</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0083.Season">Abundant Autumn Topibeary Gardener</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0084.Season">Frigid Winter Topibeary Gardener</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0079.Season.Story">This Floating Fluffy Seedpuff has seen many corners of the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0080.Season.Story">No one knows how long this Drifting Fluffy Seedpuff has been in the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0081.Season.Story">This Hovering Fluffy Seedpuff is a great friend to have around.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0082.Season.Story">This adorable gardener loves sowing seeds at midday while basking in the sunlight. Our hard-working, green-thumbed friend here has an uncanny ability to choose the best plots of land for flowers to grow.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0083.Season.Story">This handsome gardener loves harvesting syrup reeds and berries while watching the sun rise upon the horizon. Our warm-hearted, green-thumbed friend here takes extra care to harvest fruits without damaging a single twig.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0084.Season.Story">This hearty gardener knows that a productive winter will bring an abundant spring. Our diligent and fast-working friend here ensures that the soil doesn\'t freeze solid, allowing the roots to continue growing throughout the winter.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0518">Strawberry Crepe Cookie\'s Wafflebot Workshop</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0518.Story">Welcome to Strawberry Crepe Cookie\'s bustling hub of robotics research and maintenance, a state-of-the-art facility used to repair and create highly advanced Wafflebots. This workshop is filled with bright flashing screens, intricately tangled wires, and topped off with the occasional shower of sparks.</string>
  <string name="$UX.NewCookie.Popup.Text1">Meet the new Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.NewCookie.Popup.Text2">Meet new Cookies, decors, and curious by visiting the
Premium Dice Gacha, Mole Shipping, and via Collection Level rewards!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Seasonpass.Purchase.Popup.Text5">Stay at Stage 1 even
if you fail a puzzle!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.09">Two Cookies, One Dream</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.10">A Harvest for the Ages!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.09.Story">It seemed as if differing opinions wouldn\'t end... But the residents of the garden stood up to protect their home, helping the two Cookies come to an agreement.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.10.Story">The battle for the fate of the Syrup Garden has begun! Begone, Reaper! You\'re not welcome here, any longer!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.11">Mount St. Crème Awaits</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep03.11.Story">Though far away, it seems the chilling winds of Mount St. Crème can be felt already. But our heroes can\'t be stopped by a bit of cold weather!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.001">Hopeful Terrarium</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.002">Suspicious Gardener Desk</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.003">Dreamwood Flower Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.004">Potent Sprout Salve</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Wall.001">Deep Green Window</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Wall.002">Earnest Research Notes</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Hanger.001">Lovely Herb Shelf</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Hanger.002">Carefully Collected Essence</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Ceil.001">Glowing Seed Light Bulb</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Rug.001">Cultivation Glass Hatch</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.WP.001">Thoughtful Gardener\'s Wall</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Deck.001">Thoughtful Gardener\'s Flooring</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.001.Story">A terrarium with cute seedlings healthily growing. I wonder how they\'ll look once they bloom? Perhaps friendly trees with branches casting comforting shadows on hot summer days, or maybe beautiful flowers putting smiles on everyone\'s faces?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.002.Story">A desk belonging to a certain gardener. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.003.Story">A flowerbed full of dreamwood flowers. Let\'s put them somewhere they can grow and flourish!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Floor.004.Story">A bowl filled with carefully mixed sprouts and herbs. Looks like it might be used for some medicinal purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Wall.001.Story">A large window that somehow feels important. Let\'s pick a good spot to place it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Wall.002.Story">Documents containing research data. It looks important, so let\'s hang them up somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Hanger.001.Story">A shelf filled with herbs and traces of nature. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Hanger.002.Story">Various liquids hanging from a sturdy branch. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Ceil.001.Story">A glass bulb containing a self-luminescent seed. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Rug.001.Story">A hatch to an indoor cultivation patch. It lets you grow your favorite plants but not have to worry about walking on them!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.WP.001.Story">A wall belonging to someone truly passionate about gardening. Let\'s fill its room with greenery!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RosemarySecretGarden.Deck.001.Story">The floor of someone truly passionate about gardening. Let\'s fill its room with plants!</string>
