  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">This place is yucky.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">And it sorta stinks too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_1">A very stark contrast to how it was described.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Far from \"perpetually frozen\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">Nothing seems fresh at all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_1">Is GingerDozer really here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">Or did we make a wrong turn?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">If only we could ask for directions...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0002_3">Rosemary Cookie did say
this is a place of
misery and doom...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">It sure fits the description...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Ooof!
Hey? What gives?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0001_2">I thought I heard something!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">Stop with that nonsense!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">This place is creepy enough already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">Y-y-y-you
guys!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0039_1">EEEK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">It\'s a m-m-monster! And it\'s attacking someone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">THAT\'S NOT VERY NICE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">What is that?! Why\'s it... WHAT IS THAT THING?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">I\'ve never seen such a thing before,
but I know it\'s angry!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">We need to drive the monster away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_7">But... how\'re we gonna do that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Erm... Uhhhh-ohhhh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">Did that...? Oh, I thiiink it sawww us...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0039_2">RRRUUUNNN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_8">It\'s... it\'s coming towards us...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">What do we do?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">Stop being silly, GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">We need to....</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_9">RRRUUUNNN!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_1">Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Npc.0040_1">I... I think so!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_2">Flee now. And do not look back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_3">Just beyond is the Crème Refuge...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_4">I must hold the line or
it will be engulfed in chaos.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_5">You shall not pass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_6">You\'ve been warned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_7">Begone, or face my blade.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_8">I gladly forfeit my dough
to protect the innocent.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_9">And I\'ll take you with me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_10">As I was commanded.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2001_1">Not today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2007_11">First Cream... Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2001_2">It has been a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2001_3">You\'ve done well in my absence,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP3_CH4_SQ8_CUT2_Cookie.2001_4">Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_5">Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_12">First Cream Cookie...! Is it really you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_6">Yes. It is I, in the dough. Are you injured?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_13">I remain in one piece...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_14">Know that I am still eager to serve, regardless of the dangers set before me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_7">Though I would very much like to hear
of your endeavors... There is a more
pressing matter I wish to discuss.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_8">What has happened to Mount St. Crème?
I must assess the situation in full.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_9">I\'ve heard it has not fared well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_10">But to see it for myself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_15">Of course, My Lady.
Shortly after your departure from Mount St. Crème,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_16">the temperature controller malfunctioned without warning.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_11">How could that be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">Such an apparatus has withstood
the test of time for ages.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_17">Alas, I know not how it happened...
but despair rapidly descended upon the land.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_18">Once the winds changed, Mount St. Crème was
already upon the precipice of ruin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_19">It was already too late...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_20">The frosted grounds condensed into muddy sludge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_21">Even the glaciers have subsided...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_22">The landscape itself has melted away,
with mold and decay creeping further
with each passing day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_23">My desire to repair the controller has brought me to this area...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_24">But, so far, my efforts to restore it have only resulted in failure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_13">You are not at fault, my friend.
I am confident that you made a valiant effort
each step of the way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_14">And I am truly glad to see your resolve is unwavered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_25">First Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_26">Oh! My Lady...!
I almost forgot to mention.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_27">I\'ve received a report that may also be of interest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_28">There has been a sighting of an unknown, small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_15">A \"small Cookie\"?
Could it be...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_29">Yes... I believe so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_30">I shall continue to keep watch over this area.
You should make haste and investigate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_16">Onyx Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">Thank you for bringing this to my attention.
It does merit further investigation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_18">Though I wish to discuss a great many things with you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_19">My calling lies elsewhere at the moment.
Let us continue our conversation at a later time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_20">Onyx Cream Cookie, please ensure the temperature controller is repaired...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_21">I must ask that you bring Mount St. Crème back to its former glory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_22">Please... do this for me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_31">You need not ask, Your Radiance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_32">I shall do as you command.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_33">No matter the cost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Phew... Oh yeah, that was definitely quite a run...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">How long were we running?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">And seriously, what WAS that thing? I\'ve never seen anything so ferocious!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">I wonder if the other fella made it to safety...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">I don\'t know... I hope they\'re okay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">We could look for them?
But... where would we start looking?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Yeah, we don\'t know much about this place yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">Is GingerDozer really somewhere here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">*Sigh*
If only we could use the compass once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">It\'d make our lives SO much easier...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">Do you think we can fix it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">At this moment? No...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">Hey, hold on...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Huh? What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">Over there...! Voices!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Where?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Hm, I think I hear it too...
Just beyond that lump of cream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_13">Yeah, I definitely heard something...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">We should investigate.
Let\'s see if there\'s a way arou-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Let\'s clear a path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">Haha! My favorite thing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">Um... Okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">*Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">I\'m honestly surprised he didn\'t say
that catchphrase of his earlier...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">So the voices were coming from around here, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0041_1">Eugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0040_2">Urmph...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">Oh... Everyone looks like they\'re in bad shape.
Are they okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Hm... They appear to be suffering from sort of malady.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">It might be wise to help them first before asking for directions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0039_4">Ugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Oh! You\'re the one who the monster was
about to attack!!! Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">You\'re in really rough shape...
Is there anything we can do to help?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0039_5">GWAAAH! No, no stay back! Don\'t touch me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0039_6">The mold will... it\'ll infect you too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Mold? What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_14">Get to it, Wizard Cookie!
You know you wanna say it, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">I- wha- You make me sound like a know-it-all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_19">But yes... How did you know I was about to explain?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">Anyway... Mold is a type of fungal growth that can
form in environments saturated with moisture.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Hm, yes, I think I\'ve heard of these words before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">Ahem... Speaking plainly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">It\'s something bad and can cause rot and decay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">That sounds really bad! And painful!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0041_2">It does hurt, yeah...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0040_3">It kinda really hurts... Eugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0039_7">I got away from the monster, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0039_8">In the end... it infected me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_23">So that thing was a monstrous manifestation of mold...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0041_3">It\'s really bad... if all of us get infected...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0041_4">First Cream Cookie will be so sad when she gets back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0041_5">After so many years of waiting for her return...
she\'ll be so disappointed in us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">First Cream Cookie??? You know her?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0040_4">Urgh... Ow, ow, ow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">I think we should let them rest...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_24">The mold is definitely detrimental to their health.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">Can\'t we do something? Is there a way to get rid of mold?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Is there a way, Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">Eh? Why\'re all of you looking at me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">Well... \'cuz you\'re a wizard! You know things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_26">Y-y-you\'re not wrong there but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_27">C\'mon, think, think, think!
Search your mind! Find the answer...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_28">AH-HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">OH! You got an idea?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_29">Baking soda! That\'s the answer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_30">It\'s an effective cleaning agent
that can neutralize mold!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_16">But where\'ll we find baking soda?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">I get the feeling we\'ll be able to find some nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">That\'s the spirit, GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">And you\'ve saved the day once more, Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_31">Well, I, erm... thank you.
Now come, let\'s find some baking soda and get to work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">It worked! Are you feeling any better?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_9">It\'s... I can... Oh wow! I feel so... normal!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_10">Thank you very much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_11">Oh, and I should thank you for before too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_12">I wouldn\'t be here if you didn\'t lure the monster away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_32">We wouldn\'t be here if that thing caught us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_5">Thank you for the temporary cure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">Huh? What do you mean by temporary?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_6">Mount St. Crème\'s temperature controller is broken... We\'ll end up moldy once more...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_33">A temperature controller? Is that what I think it is...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_6">Hey now! You can\'t say something so depressing in front of the Cookies who just helped us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_7">Oh? Then can I say it behind them...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_7">NO! That\'s even worse!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_13">Er... hehe... Pay them no mind.
They\'re always in a bickering match.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_34">Pardon me, but your friend just mentioned
something about a temperature controller?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_8">Oh, allow me to explain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_9">It\'s the thing that makes Mount St. Crème so chilly
and keeps everything fresh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_8">And it\'s broken...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_35">I get it now! Without the chilled air from
the temperature controller, this entire region
is subject to mold and decay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">Hey, a while back you mentioned First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">Do you know her?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_14">Of course we do! Everyone living in Mount St. Crème knows First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">OH! Hehe, we know her too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_28">We\'re friends with First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_17">She\'d know what to do...
We could really use her help again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_10">First Cream Cookie?
She helped you? She talked to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">Yeah, she helped us find our way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">We\'re looking for a friend of ours!
His name\'s GingerDozer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">And First Cream Cookie told us how to find him!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_15">Oooh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">Do you know anything about GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_16">No, the name\'s not familiar... Sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_17">But someone at the refuge might\'ve
heard something about your friend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_18">There\'s lots of folks there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_9">And it\'s somewhere we can\'t go...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_11">Cut it out! Stop moping!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_22">Why can\'t you go there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_10">Because we\'re moldy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_11">They call us Moldizens... and if we go...
the mold might spread and infect the others...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">But... the baking soda worked.
You should be able to go, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_12">Mold is inevitable... We\'ll be drowning in it soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_12">HEY! Zip it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_19">Well... It\'s true that we can\'t go there,
but we can show you the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_13">*Sigh*
You\'d have to travel past the controller...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_14">And there\'s definitely gonna be more monsters there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_20">That reminds me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_21">Onyx Cream Cookie might still be there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_23">Who\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">Monsters, huh? I think we\'ll be okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_31">After all, I\'d say we\'re preeetty good at
running away from things now, hehe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_22">Okay then. But you really should be
more careful from now on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_20">Oh boy...
This place is way too creepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_37">And there\'s something
foul and rancid in the air...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_21">*GASP*
Everyone freeze...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_33">Huh? What\'s wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_22">I heard something... but... I dunno...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_34">Huh? I didn\'t hear any-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0042_1">Fffsssttt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_35">I HEARD IT!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_36">What\'re those things?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_25">Hi there, cute little thingamajigs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_37">SERIOUSLY?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_23">Are those things gonna hurt us...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_38">If so, we\'d better get out of here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0042_2">Fffsssttt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_38">EVERYBODY RUN FOR IT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_39">They\'re gone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_26">We\'re saved! But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_24">I don\'t think we\'re safe just yet...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_35">It seems there was more</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_36">than only spores here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_40">WAAAIT! Wait-wait-wait!
WE\'RE COOKIES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_27">We\'re too cute to get crumbled!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_37">You\'re... Cookies...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_38">You don\'t belong here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_39">This area is dangerous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_41">We\'re looking for our friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_28">We heard about some
sort of refuge ahead.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_29">Someone there might
know our friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_42">Um, if you\'re from around here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_43">You must know First Cream C-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_40">The temperature controller!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_41">This conversation must wait.
I must fix it with haste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_25">By yourself...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_42">Hmph.
Who else is here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_43">Alas, my efforts have
been fruitless...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_44">No matter how often it\'s fixed,
it\'ll never be the same.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_45">Now, scurry away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_46">Mind yourselves and
try to keep your distance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_39">Wait.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_40">We can-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_44">We\'ll help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2007_47">You...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_26">We\'ve managed to
fix a big machine before...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_48">This is the temperature controller.
It has seen much, much better days...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_49">In order to return the controller
to a fully functioning state,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_50">we must collect the required
potions of the matching color shown.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_41">I see...! So essentially, this thing
requires potions to power itself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_51">You offered to help, and I accept. Shall we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_1">*CLANG*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_2">*Whirrr*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_3">*CLUNK*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_4">*BEEP BEEP BEEP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_5">*FFFSSSHHH*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_45">GAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_42">Is it working?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_6">*BEEP BEEP BEEP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_7">*FFFSSSHHH*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_52">Excellent!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_27">Huuup...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_8">*BEEP BEEP BEEP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0047_9">*FFFSSSHHH*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0001_46">I think we\'re getting the hang of it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.2007_53">The air is getting cooler!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0025_43">The airflow is being blocked...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0047_10">*Clank, clunk, clank, clunk*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0047_11">*Cllluuunnnkkk, WHAP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0001_47">The temperature\'s changing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0002_28">It\'s working...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.2007_54">Will our efforts succeed...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0003_30">We can\'t stop now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0001_49">Haha! We did it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0002_29">Hooray! It worked!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_55">I appreciate your assistance.
It was, without a doubt, extremely invaluable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_56">Apologies for the late introduction,
but my name is Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_50">And I\'m GingerBrave! This is GingerBright,
Strawberry Cookie, and Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_31">You must do a lot of amazing stuff with that sword!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_57">Hmph. I would not say that my deeds are
anywhere close to \"amazing\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_58">Before we proceed any further, you mentioned
something about Madam First Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_51">So you do know First Cream Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_59">This insolent whelp dares to speak of
Madam First Cream Cookie as an equal?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_60">How dare he...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_61">Yes, Madam First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_32">The folks we ran into a while back knew her too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_33">She must be really famous around here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_62">Madam First Cream Cookie is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_63">She is the wise and respected
leader of Mount St. Crème.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_64">She is the Guardian Mother, our protector and savior.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_52">What? A grandmother?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_44">Dude... Seriously.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_65">I may have judged this Cookie a bit too quickly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_66">Perhaps he is just... simple.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_67">Her Radiance has left for the frozen lands
to uphold her call.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_68">I... remained behind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_34">So... What now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_30">Wait! Did you say she went to the frozen lands?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_31">Is that where the prison is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_69">How is it that an outsider knows of the prison?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_70">Hmph. It matters not.
Yes, it is where the sinister prison is located.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_71">The once pristine frozen lands have
become a monolith of dread and misery...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_53">Then that\'s where we might find GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_72">Ginger... Dozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_35">He\'s our friend! A small, tiny, and cute Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_73">A small Cookie...? Does that mean...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_74">Wait. The small Cookie from the reports?
Was their name... GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_75">I will show you the way to the refuge.
They will be able to tell you more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_54">You\'re not gonna come with us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_45">Oh, by the way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_46">Do you know if we can find a way
to repair this compass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_32">It\'s really important...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_33">If we can fix it, it might tell us
exactly where GingerDozer is.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_76">Alas, I am afraid I cannot help you there.
But... Madam First Cream Cookie may be
able to shed some light on it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_1">Open up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_2">THEY\'RE COMING! MONSTERS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0044_1">ARGH! We can\'t just leave them out there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0045_1">DO NOT OPEN THAT GATE! Or we\'ll all get infected!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0044_2">My friend is out there...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0044_3">We\'ve known each other for ages!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0046_1">*RAAAWWWR*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_3">WAAAHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0044_4">No... I just can\'t...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0045_2">WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0044_5">C\'mon... PLEASE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0046_2">*RAAAWWWR*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_4">NNNOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_25">Stand aside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0046_3">*RAAAWWWR*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_5">The monster is defeated!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_6">She\'s... she\'s back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_7">SHE\'S RETURNED!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0043_8">FIRST CREAM COOKIE IS BACK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_26">... I must open these gates.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_27">The gate is colder than a frozen heart...
closed shut and impervious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_28">It will take immense power to force it open.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_29">I must collect Light Shards to unleash my power...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.2001_30">Excellent!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.2001_31">I will need more shards!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.2001_32">Ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.2001_33">Light, come forth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Npc.0043_9">YAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Npc.0043_10">YAAAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_BQ2_PLAY1_Npc.0043_11">YAAAY!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ2_POR1_Npc.0043_12">All hail First Cream Cookie!!! Our savior!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ2_POR1_Npc.0044_6">There are truly no limits to her power...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_34">Let it be known...!
This land is Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH1BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_35">A sanctuary for all!
A haven for all to remain fresh and pristine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_1">Flour. Salt. Sugar...
Hmph. Nothing special.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Event.0001_1">WAH!
WAAAHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_2">A flimsy hat...
Nothing special, again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Event.0001_2">WAAAH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_3">Noisy...
And annoying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Event.0001_3">WAAAAAAHHHHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_4">Noisy. Noisy. Noisy. Noisy.
NOISY. NOISY. NOISY. NOISY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_5">ZIP IT ALREADY!
You cacophonous, lump of dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Event.0001_4">I\'m scared! Someone help me!
*SOB*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_1">Mrawr, what\'s all this racket...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_6">Where\'s that hammer...?
Maybe you\'ll pipe down
with an itty-bitty smash or two.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_2">Looks like the Meowstress is very, very upset...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_3">That small Cookie doesn\'t seem SO loud, even to my keen sense of hearing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_4">Perhaps the Meowstress\' research isn\'t coming along?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_5">The last time her research didn\'t work as planned, she threw such a tantrum. Broke so many things, so much hissing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_7">When will you stop crying, you good-for-nothing, stale blob?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_6">Mmmyes, just like now...
Her desk is so messy again... So angry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_7">But wait! Mayyybe this is a chance to earn favor with the Meowstress?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_8">Meowstress! There\'s no need to be so angry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_8">I am NOT in the mood for games!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_9">Please, Meowstress, hear meowt! I can silence this Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0009_9">You?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0003_10">Of course! You can count on meee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_11">Meowstress! See what I\'ve done with the desk? It\'s all clean again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_12">And I found this dirty old, useless picture in the corner. It looks like a waste of space!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_10">Hm? This is a picture from ages ago, of my grandmother and I. I wasn\'t aware that it was still here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_13">MYAH?! Of course, a family picture! I KNEW it was a very, very important picture the moment I laid eyes upon it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_14">May I ask, Meowstress, about this shabby house? It looks like it reeks of rotten cheese...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_11">It\'s my grandmother\'s bakery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_15">And a LOVELY bakery it is, myehehe! It looks so homely and sturdy!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_12">The business failed.
Miserably.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_16">Ungrateful human scum! How dare they bring ruin upon such a special place?! How could they not appreciate your grandmother\'s baking?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_13">Unappreciative?
Hmph, that\'s actually partially true.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_14">The bakery was immensely popular in the beginning. But the villagers believed its success was due to witchcraft.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_15">My grandmother passed without the chance to redeem her bakery\'s standing. It was soon abandoned and left to ruin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_17">How despicable! Those rude and foolish humans!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_16">Yes. They were utterly despicable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_17">Such oafs did not deserve my grandmother\'s baking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_18">I have no intention of letting such filth poison the world. I already have a plan to-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Event.0001_5">GINGERBRAVE! HEEELP!
WAAAHHH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_19">I thought you promised to take care of the incessantly, earsplitting crying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_18">EEP! Y-y-yes, of course I shall, Meowstress! I haven\'t forgot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_19">If you return to focusing on your research, I shall get to calming down the loud one soon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_20">Very well. But... have you seen my goggles?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_21">I seem to have misplaced them after the ugly one distracted me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_20">Mrawrm... you probably lost them when you threw that tantrum...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0009_22">Well? What are you waiting for?
MY GOGGLES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0003_21">Right away, Meowstress!
Your goggles! I will find them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_22">Meowstress! I have found your goggles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_23">But this a strange looking thing. It reminds me of pesky crows.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_23">Strange?
How dare you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_24">These were made with cutting-edge technology, truly state-of-the-art! The only good thing to come from halfwits who dare to call themselves scientists.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_25">The olfactory sensors can detect even the most minute ingredients, and the lenses are capable of zooming in on the tiniest of granular inconsistencies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_24">There she goes again...
The Meowstress can never stop talking about such topics.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_26">Are you listening?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_25">O-O-Of course! Such a splendid contraption! Now, if you\'ll excuse me, I shall put an end to the incessant noise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Event.0001_6">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_26">Hello there, Ageless Cookie! It\'s me, a cute kitty cat! Look at me smile! Don\'t you want to smile after looking at such a fine specimen as I?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_27">Everyone likes cats! This Cookie will be in awe of me and stop crying, which means more badges from the Meowstress!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Event.0001_7">WAAAHHH!!!
I REMEMBER YOU! YOU\'RE THE SCARY CAT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Event.0001_8">PLEASE DON\'T EAT ME!
GO AWAY!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_27">This is the opposite of quiet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Event.0001_9">GAAAH?! A GIANT CROW?! SCARY GOGGLES! A GIANT CAT! HEEELP ME!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_28">The weird goggles are making him cry even louder. At least he was quiet when he first saw my smile...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_29">This stale Cookie is scared of everything! There\'s no way to stop his crying! This is a disaster!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_28">... What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_30">I-I- What I meant was... Ahem! I didn\'t mean to say that out loud- I mean... DOH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_29">Did you say... \"Disaster\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0003_31">Uh-oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_30">Okay, you useless furball. I\'ll tell you exactly how to silence this rascal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0009_31">Watch... and learn...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Event.0001_10">GINGERBRAVE!
Where are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_32">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_32">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_33">The Cookie keeps crying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_33">I can see AND hear that he\'s crying. Just let me think for a moment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_34">I thought all brats liked toys and snacks... It was a surefire plan. Where did my calculations go wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_35">Wrong...? No, it wasn\'t the plan that was wrong.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_36">There\'s something wrong with this Cookie! This ugly one is the cause of all this mess, my failed experiments!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_37">Let\'s be realistic here... I don\'t need a whole Cookie to analyze the ingredients. I just need some crumbs. Perhaps the plan with the hammer is still viable?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_38">Then you\'ll be quiet, and then I\'ll be able to conduct my research on baking more Cookies in peace... Yes, yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_39">YES! I will smash you into smithereens! It\'s an ideal solution to all my troubles!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_34">She\'s plotting sinister things again. Her meticulous notes are slowly becoming a mess...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_35">She can be so impulsive sometimes, but this is on a whole new level!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_36">I should stop her before she regrets it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_37">Meowstress? Before we crush this noisy doughrat, how about you consult your favorite book first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_40">Which book?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_38">You know... THE book! The book that helped you find this castle? Your grandmother\'s precious book?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_41">The tome? Perhaps you have a point. It may contain some sort of answer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_42">Let me see here...
Ahaaa? Interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_43">You.
I have a job for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_39">Yes! Reporting for duty! I will do anything and everything you ask!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_44">Put this crying lump of dough in the refrigerator.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_40">Right away! I shall do as you command!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_41">Does this mean this humble servant will receive a badge? It\'s been sooo long since the Meowstress has bestowed praise upon me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0009_45">Hmph. Fine.
Make it quick and I will consider giving you ten badges.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0003_42">Ten! TEN?!
I will clean this entire room for such a reward!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_43">The cleaning\'s done and the fridge is here but... Ew, it\'s quite dirty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_44">Come to think of it... Why must this Cookie be put in the refrigerator?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0009_46">Yes, this is definitely... I remember now. I think... Hm, no? Maybe? Was it? Or could it be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_45">I dare not ask the Meowstress right now... She\'s too focused on her research.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_46">If I disturb her, she won\'t give me the praise I deserve!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_47">Best not to think too much... Let\'s get rid of this frost and open the door, and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_48">IN YOU GO, you pesky Cookie! Say hello to your temporary home!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Event.0001_11">WAAAH!
NOOOooo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0003_49">Resistance is futile, doughrat!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Event.0001_12">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0009_48">Crying once more, are we...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0009_49">No matter. Keep sobbing, little one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS7_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0009_50">Your own tears will aid in seasoning your dough. A little salt can go a long way in preserving desserts such as you.</string>
