  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.01.Story">Everyone needs to wait here in an orderly fashion until it is their turn to undergo the expiration inspection. Ages ago, when everything was fresh and preserved, the waiting room was filled with travelers greetings each other with smiles and laughter. Nowadays, the ambience of this room is filled only with groans and winces of pain caused by mold infection...</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.02.Story">Mount St. Crème\'s arid yet chilled temperatures are possible thanks to its temperature controller. Such an environment was perfect for prolonging freshness for all residents. But with the controller gone haywire, Mount St. Crème has become abysmally dreary and miserable...</string>
