  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Floor.001.Story">A device that lets out a cool breeze when the coolant and antifreeze levels are identical. However, it is extremely difficult to achieve this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Floor.002.Story">An old flashlight that has become home to a colony of fungi. Let\'s give them a nice, dark, and damp home!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Floor.003.Story">A chunk of ice containing vials of antifreeze liquid that\'s used to keep stable temperatures. It seems like the liquid\'s effects doesn\'t extend outside the vials.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Floor.004.Story">A shattered vial somewhat containing liquid coolant. In a way, it\'ll make your room a bit cooler.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Wall.001.Story">A hole in the wall, giving the room a beautiful view of the moonlit sky outside.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Wall.002.Story">A softly illuminated cave passage. Mysteries and adventures are sure to wait those who walk through!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Ceil.001.Story">Tiny icicles. Make sure to watch your head if you place these in a room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Ceil.002.Story">Long icicles that won\'t melt even if you place them indoors. Just remember to watch your head!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Ceil.003.Story">Pretty crystals hanging from the ceiling. Let\'s make a room positively shining!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.WP.001.Story">With these walls in your room, you\'ll feel like every day is a spelunking adventure!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Thermostat.Deck.001.Story">A floor made out of beautiful, yet mysterious blue stone. Perfect for when you\'re looking for that magical cave aesthetic.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.001.Story">A sofa made out of a moldy piece of meat. Now this is a... rare sight!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.002.Story">A sofa made out of a moldy piece of bread. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.003.Story">A sofa made out of a moldy egg carton. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.004.Story">A moldy suitcase that lost its owner a long time ago. Like this, it\'s easily recognizable when going traveling!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.005.Story">A group of self-luminescent fungus flowers. Plant it in a room and it fulfills the roles of both vegetation and lighting!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Floor.006.Story">A self-luminescent fungus flower. While not yet fully grown, you can plant it in a room and it will be a reliable source of light for many years ahead!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Wall.001.Story">Stained glass, that is also stained with patches of mold! How ironic.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Ceil.001.Story">Want to know the temperature on Mount St. Crème? While the device used to be redundant for the mountain and its permanently freezing state, it ended up breaking just as it gained a purpose when the controller stopped working.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Ceil.002.Story">A ceiling-mounted lamp made out of ice cream. It\'s slowly melting, so better place it somewhere nice and refrigerated!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Hanger.001.Story">A wall decoration made out of ice. The rising temperatures have caused it to melt, so it definitely has seen better days. Still, let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Hanger.002.Story">A self-luminescent fungus flower. Plant this on a wall in any room for some convenient lighting!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.WP.001.Story">A wallpaper covered with mold. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.WaitingRoom.Deck.001.Story">A floor mat consisting of soft blue mold. Who wouldn\'t want this in their room?!</string>
