  <string name="$Neighbor.0088.Story">A soft-hearted Cream Guard who always tries to look out for their friends.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0089.Story">A soft-hearted Cream Guard who always tries to make new friends.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0090.Story">A soft-hearted Cream Guard who always tries to keep their promises.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0091.Story">A resident of Mount St. Crème. They are always talking about the importance of strong bones.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0092.Story">A resident of Mount St. Crème. They are always talking about the importance of laughter.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0093.Story">A resident of Mount St. Crème. They are always talking about the importance of kindness.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0094.Story">Your typical, average Butterbar. They\'re always so serious for some reason.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0095.Story">Your ordinary, mediocre Butterbar. They\'re always concerned about work for some reason.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0096.Story">Your undistinguished, unexcited Butterbar. It looks like they\'d be able to sleep until sunrise at any given moment.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0097.Story">Happy and healthy Breadan, a long-time resident of Mount St. Crème.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0098.Story">Jovial and giggly Breadan, a friend who\'s always willing to listen to your stories.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0099.Story">Down-to-earth Breadan, an admirer of Mount St. Crème\'s scenery.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0100.Story">Happy and healthy Jammy, who needs some time to warm-up to new friends.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0101.Story">Sour and tarty Jammy, who always seems to have a sarcastic joke ready.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0102.Story">Hardy and mellow Jammy, who tends to listen rather than talk.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0103.Story">Cream Cake is very proud of their hairdo, which is actually a hearty scoop of the freshest cream in the neighborhood. They may spend a bit too much time on styling, but everyone loves to converse about hair products and fashion with this amazingly charming resident.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0104.Story">Cream Cake is very proud of their bold fashion sense, especially today\'s selection of red and pink hues. They may spend a bit too much time on selecting their outfit for the day, but everyone loves to converse about colors and fashion with this wonderfully chipper resident.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0105.Story">Cream Cake is very proud of their chic fashion sense, especially today\'s selection of casual chocolate. They may spend a bit too much time talking about breakout fashion trends, but everyone loves to converse about the latest news with this cheerful and kindhearted resident.</string>
