  <string name="$Neighbor.0108.Season.Story">A jiggly Rice Cake Bunny. It seems like the perfect friend to call on any occasion!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0109.Season.Story">This species of bird only lives in the coldest and freshest of environments where the temperature hovers near-freezing. When they are in a good mood, they will chirp the happiest of tunes.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0110.Season.Story">This species of bird only lives in the coldest and freshest of environments where the temperature hovers near-freezing. When they are in an excited mood, they will flap their wings as if applauding, causing a minty aroma to spread across the area.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0111.Season.Story">This species of bird only lives in the coldest and freshest of environments where the temperature hovers near-freezing. When they feel unsafe or nervous, they will breathe in as much air as they can to look large and intimidating. Unfortunately, it just looks cuter!</string>
