  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2001">First Cream Cookie\'s Radiant Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2001.Story">Tales of old claim that the chilled winds of Mount St. Crème could restore freshness and stave off all signs of staleness. You can find the heart of this premise represented within First Cream Cookie\'s room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.001">Whisk of Determination</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.002">Cone of Fresh Memories</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.003">Light-filled Brooch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.001.Story">A divine whisk, once used by the Witch who baked the First Batch. It radiates with the will to make all things sweet.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.002.Story">A thin, crisply baked ceremonial hat. Even as time passes, First Cream Cookie\'s memories of that dearly missed someone only grows clearer.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2001.003.Story">An elegant brooch, once a treasured keepsake of nobility. The golden light, still brilliant, seems to reminisce those glory days of yore.</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.FirstCream.Tooltip">Onyx Coins resembling the darkest of cocoa powder. These can only be obtained during the Onyx Cream Season!</string>
