  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.01.Story">Mount St. Crème has fallen from grace. There is nothing but lukewarm, humid air and an unwanted layer of built-up frost now.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.02.Story">Our friends have encountered an unknown, ferocious creature of some kind! WHAT IS THAT THING?!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.03.Story">Everyone who calls Mount St. Crème their home trust and follow her guidance.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.04.Story">When the gates opened, the residents were overjoyed to see First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.05.Story">The temperature controller for Mount St. Crème has been fixed! Let the cold and arid winds wash over the region once more!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.06.Story">Only the brightest and strongest of light could open such a cold and frozen gate.</string>
