  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0001.Title.01.Summary">Onion Cookie is afraid of many things, and she wants to learn how to be brave like GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0001.Title.02.Summary">Onion Cookie is struggling to shout WOOT like GingerBrave. It\'s harder than it looks...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0001.Title.03.Summary">Why is GingerBrave always so excited about things?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2006.Title.01.Summary">Witchberry Cookie is very fond of her treasures. But she\'s decided to show off her hoard to... Sachertorte Cookie, the leader of the Apricot Jam Syndicate?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2006.Title.02.Summary">Sachertorte Cookie has finally laid eyes upon Witchberry\'s trove of... \"treasures.\"</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2006.Title.03.Summary">The Apricot Jam Syndicate has no choice but to spend all day \"admiring\" Witchberry Cookie\'s \"treasures.\"</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2001.Title.01.Summary">A visitor has come to First Cream Cookie\'s room: an old friend, Zombie Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2001.Title.02.Summary">After a long adventure throughout the castle, Zombie Cookie excitedly tells First Cream Cookie of everything that was experienced.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2001.Title.03.Summary">Unfortunately, during Zombie Cookie\'s tale, First Cream Cookie had to leave to fulfill her destined duty. Poor Zombie Cookie was confused at her sudden departure.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0028.Title.01.Summary">Lately, Avocado Cookie\'s been worried about her forge\'s low temperatures. Cherry Cookie to the rescue! Wait... Cherry Cookie?! Oh no...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0028.Title.02.Summary">The forge\'s heat isn\'t getting any higher, despite Cherry Cookie\'s batch of firecrackers. Maybe it needs something stronger! Like a cannon!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0028.Title.03.Summary">Despite Cherry Cookie\'s efforts, the forge\'s temperature isn\'t improving. Maybe this calls for a RADICAL IDEA! Warning: A large explosion will definitely occur.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0035.Title.01.Summary">Vampire Cookie has been waiting for the greatest batch of aged grape juice for a long, long time. Unfortunately, he\'s greeted by... bitter, green juice.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0035.Title.02.Summary">Herb Cookie wants to see Vampire Cookie take better care of his health, hence the green juice. Vampire Cookie is quick to hide himself from sight...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0035.Title.03.Summary">Herb Cookie, unable to find Vampire Cookie, is sad that his green juice will be untasted... until something happens!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0002.Title.01.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie is visiting Strawberry Cookie\'s room. Why? To learn how to play some games, and maybe become a gaming champion?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0002.Title.02.Summary">The road to becoming a champion is long and arduous! Strawberry Crepe Cookie was utterly defeated by another player. Strawberry Cookie decides to step forward...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0002.Title.03.Summary">It turns out, the champion was Strawberry Cookie all along! Strawberry Crepe Cookie\'s eyes light up when realizing this amazing fact!</string>
