  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_01">This is a tale from ages past...</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_02">A tale of a princess from a faraway land,</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_03">the radiant and inspiring Witch of Light.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_04">Ignorance and greed corrupted
the fabric of the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_05">Despite facing such despair,</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_06">she knew there was still
hope for the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_07">Twelve witches bowed before her,
sharing her wish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_08">To serve a greater purpose and
cleanse the world from darkness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_09">They gathered Life, attempting to
harness its very essence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_10">But a single heart, poisoned with pride
was enough to ruin it all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_11">Their bodies crumbled to powder,
their souls adrift in the wind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_12">The Witch of Light, desperate to
save her companions,</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_13">placed their souls into Cookies,
fueled by her very own Life Essence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_14">"This will not be the end."</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_15">And it was not, for the prideful witch
managed to capture her radiant essence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_16">The witches slumbered
within the castle, as Cookies,</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_17">their essence scattered across the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_18">In its wake, new civilizations flourished.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_19">A world of desserts,
born from the Witch of Light\'s wishes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_20">These living Cookies were proof of the
greatest form of magic to grace the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_21">Now, a seeker of the truth has
entered the castle\'s abandoned halls.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_22">And one by one,
the slumbering Cookies awakened...</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mcinematic_23">What other secrets lie
dormant in the Witch\'s Castle?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_1">Hello?
Erm... GingerBrave...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">OOOH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_3">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">OH! I didn\'t mean to frighten you. Sorry about that, Onion Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_5">H-H-Hi, GingerBrave... I\'m here because... I want to learn something from you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">From me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_7">Erm... Well... I want to... You see...
I want to be brave like you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_8">I\'m scared of lots of things... I\'m scared of ghosts, scare to sleep alone at night, scared of all sorts of noises and shadows...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie0058_9">Even talking about it is making me scared again...!
*SNIFFLE*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Hm... Learning how to be brave?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">OK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_1_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Don\'t worry, Onion Cookie! I\'ll try and teach you how to be brave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Woot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_2">Woo... woo...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Try it like this...
Www... WOOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_4">Www... woo...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">You\'re getting there! Just a bit more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_6">Woo... woo... WAAAH!
I can\'t stop crying...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">I... I guess it\'s a bit difficult when you\'re crying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Maybe there\'s another way?
Let me see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">I know! Why don\'t you try saying it while swinging this candy cane? It might help you feel braver!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_10">*Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Let\'s take a short break, Onion Cookie. Your dough might get soggy from all those tears.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Try sitting here by the fireplace. It\'ll dry up your dough and make you feel all nice and toasty inside too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_13">*Sniffle*
I want to be like you so much, GingerBrave...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_14">You\'re not afraid of anything... And you\'re always happy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Er...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Not really.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">I\'m afraid of things too, you know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_2_POR1_Cookie0058_18">Really...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Really! It\'s not like I\'m NOT afraid of everything! There\'re things that scare me too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_2">Like what...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">It\'s a secret but... When I\'m running, I\'m afraid that one my skull buttons might fall off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">And here\'s another one. I\'m scared that my friends may not want to be friends with me anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_5">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Once in a while, while I\'m staring at the fireplace, I remember the day I escaped the oven. I was so scared that day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_7">... But, if you were so scared, why didn\'t you cry...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">WOOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_9">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Sometimes, an energetic shout is
all you need! WOOT! And it\'s all
about believing in yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">It doesn\'t make the scary part go entirely away,</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">but it\'s the start to gathering up some courage!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">It also works super well when my friends shout along with me, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_14">...
I... I want to try practicing again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">You sure?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie0058_16">Yes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Alrighty then!
Remember, try imagining the shout coming from every inch of your dough and open your mouth to say...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0001_3_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">WOOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2003_1">This is Witchberry Cookie\'s designated location... And yet, where-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2006_2">MYAHA! Sooo, you actually found your way here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2006_3">Welcome to my myeowsterious and myarvelous room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2003_4">Oh my goodness, how awfully nice it is see you! You seem to be in the brightest of moods today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2006_5">Of course I am! Today\'s the chance to show off-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2006_6">I mean, show you my amazing treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2003_7">And I am looking quite forward to it! After all, you mentioned that you\'ve been carefully collecting them for such a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2003_8">I\'ve been waiting for quite some time to finally lay eyes upon your esteemed collection.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_1_POR1_Cookie2006_9">Myahaha! You won\'t be disappointed!
Come in, come in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_1">Welcome to Witchberry Cookie\'s epic treasure hoard of wonders!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2003_2">Marvelous! Simply marvelous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2003_3">Now then, where oh where are the treasures you spoke so highly of?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_4">Myeh? Everything you see here ARE my treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2003_5">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_6">Look at this feather on a stick!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_7">I can stare at this thing all day long! It moves with such grace, such finesse, and with such enticing colors! Nothing compares to this fine masterpiece!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_8">And that adorable snack table in the corner! Don\'t you just wanna curl up underneath it and take a nice nap?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_9">I wouldn\'t trade that table for the... the... the entire castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2003_10">I see. I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2003_11">So... You\'ve invited me all this way here to... show me these \"treasures\" of yours?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_2_POR1_Cookie2006_12">Myahahaha! I can tell you\'re quivering with excitement!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2006_1">Now moving on! This here soft and cushy- Eh? Who\'s there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Npc0015_2">Oh... We\'ve been caught...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Npc0014_3">We\'re erm... We\'re part of Sachertorte Cookie\'s crew...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Npc0013_4">The infamous Apricot Jam Synd-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2003_5">My friends! They are my friends! And they\'re just as excited as I am to see your treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2006_6">You dooon\'t saaay...? Do you like treasures too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2006_7">Then why\'re you hiding there! Come over here and get a GOOD LOOK, myahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2006_8">There\'s still LOADS of stuff to see! And I promise to show your EVERYTHING!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2006_3_POR1_Cookie2006_9">Myahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_1">I felt... a presence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_2">Who\'s there? Reveal yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie0013_3">Graaah...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_4">Zombie Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie0013_5">First Cream... Cookie...
Long... time...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_6">Yes, it has been quite a while since we\'ve last met. Come, my friend, have a seat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie0013_7">Me... Passing by...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_8">I see. Pray tell, how have you been faring? Have you seen much of the castle?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie0013_9">Eeergggh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_1_POR1_Cookie2001_10">Take your time. There\'s no need to rush.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie0013_1">Fence... Climb.
Find... cemetery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie2001_2">Fascinating. The castle is quite large, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie0013_3">Find friend... Brain Gum...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie2001_4">How interesting! I did not know that such a thing exists.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie0013_5">Party... Jam... Dancing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie2001_6">It seems that you\'ve enjoyed quite a bit of traveling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie0013_7">First Cream Cookie... Still here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie2001_8">Yes, my friend. I remain here, keeping watch over Mount St. Crème.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie2001_9">However, there is a high possibility that I must depart on my own travels soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_2_POR1_Cookie0013_10">Grah...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie0013_1">Where...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie2001_2">Where? I am still uncertain.
And as for why...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie2001_3">I still do not understand it fully, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie2001_4">I believe the time is nigh... for me to follow destiny.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie0013_5">Destiny... new word... No understand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie2001_6">Haha, apologies, my friend. I did not want to bring up my burdens to one who has been traveling so long.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie2001_7">Ah, but where are my manners? Please, make yourself comfortable and help yourself to these fresh Jellies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie0013_8">Fresh... Jellies...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2001_3_POR1_Cookie0013_9">Me no like... fresh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0113_1">So lemme get this straight. There\'s stuff here that can make my forge burn hotter?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0113_2">Welp! I\'m definitely curious! After all, fire and heat are key. Ya might say that they\'re the keys to my smashing success, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0113_3">But... I don\'t see anything here to help stoke the flames.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0028_4">Hehe...! Never judge a bomb by its warning label!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0028_5">For example... CHERRY FIRECRACKERS!
Pow, pow, pow! Watch them go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0028_6">Wuddya think? They\'re perfect for your forge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0113_7">Hm, nah. The forge needs something stronger and it definitely needs to last longer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_1_POR1_Cookie0028_8">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0028_1">I\'ve got just the thing then!
Feast your eyes on THIS: A cherry cannon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0113_2">We-he-ll! Now you\'ve go my attention!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0028_3">HAHAHA! Get ready for my favorite sounds in
3... 2... 1...! GO, CANNON, GO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0113_4">Huh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0028_5">THAT WAS AWESOME, wasn\'t it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0113_6">I dunno... It kinda felt like the normal amount of heat to me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0113_7">But that\'s okay! I can work with that if that\'s the best we\'ve got!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0028_8">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_2_POR1_Cookie0028_9">NOPE! Just you wait, I\'ll find something! Something BIG! Bigger and biggest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0028_1">TADA!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_2">That\'s... Oh...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0028_3">The bestest thing I\'ve ever made! Say hello to the Cherry Cupcake! It\'s got everything I\'ve ever made inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_4">Now THIS is gonna interesting!
Cherry Cookie, you\'ve really outdone yourself this time and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_5">You lit the fuse already?!
GAAAH! The shockwave is MASSIVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0028_6">BWAHAHAHA! Did you feel that?!
The shockwave and heat just passing through your dough?! There\'s nothing like it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_7">Oooh... Either I\'m seeing stars, or you\'ve really just sent us into space...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0028_8">Well? WELL?!
How awesome was THAT explosion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_9">It was awesome!
... But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_10">An explosion of this magnitude will destroy, not only my forge, but probably my entire shop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0028_11">I\'ll take that as yes!
I can make another and blow it up too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0028_3_POR1_Cookie0113_12">Huh? Wait, no! STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0035_1">*Yawn*
Where is he...? Sparkling Cookie said he\'d show up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0035_2">AH! Someone\'s at the door.
Finally... my aged grape juice is here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0035_3">Lemme just make some room here and get a glass ready and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0063_4">Greetings!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0035_5">Eh?
Herb Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0063_6">Let\'s see... There was an order placed for a special batch of Green Juice, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0063_7">Ah! I made it to the right place!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_1_POR1_Cookie0035_8">Eh? Me? What?
Green Juice? Wait...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0035_1">There\'s gotta be some mistake.
I\'ve never ordered something with herbs, let alone anything that\'s green...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0063_2">Oh? But it says right here that I\'m supposed to deliver this to Vampire Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0063_3">It also says I need to make sure you drink some...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0035_4">Ah?!
Who would...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0035_5">Oooh... Of course.
Alchemist Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0035_6">Look, I don\'t think... Erm, actually, let\'s start over.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0035_7">I\'m not drinking that stuff!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_2_POR1_Cookie0063_8">Oh! Vampire Cookie! Wait!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_1">Oh dear, where did he go?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_2">He\'s not under the chair, not behind the curtains...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_3">Maybe he\'s in this coffin...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0035_4">EEP!
Don\'t... move... a muscle...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_5">Hm, it won\'t open.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0035_6">Phew...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_7">Oh well. I\'ll just pour out some of my fresh herbal juice into all of his empty glasses.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_8">Then he\'ll have to drink some! Hehe, he\'s going to be so healthy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0035_9">NNNOOO! I don\'t want that green gunk anywhere NEAR my glasses!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_10">There you are, Vampire Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0063_11">Shall we try some healthy, green juice together then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0035_3_POR1_Cookie0035_12">EWWW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_1">Oh cool! It\'s the famous Retro Game Berry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_2">I\'ve heard it\'s always online so you can play against anyone, anywhere, anytime!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_3">And it\'s got a leaderboard system where only one champion can reign supreme!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">It sounds like you know everything about this already, Strawberry Crepe Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_4">Of course! I\'ve played it before, but I\'ve never been able to become the champion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Oh wow... You were faster than any speedrunner just now...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Haha, see, I told\'ya I\'ve played this before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_1_POR1_Cookie0518_6">What\'s this...? A new challenger has appeared? AWESOME! Keep bringing me challengers! I\'ll beat\'em all and finally face the champion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Oh, looks like you lost...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie0518_2">GRRR!
This one\'s got some serious skills!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">They used sort of a cheap move on you too. Just an endless hit and run, rinse and repeat sort of strategy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">So tacky...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Eh? What was that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Oh, nothing...
Erm, Strawberry Crepe Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_7">Could I... give it a try?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie0518_8">Huh? You?
I doubt you can beat my score, but okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_2_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Yeah, I-I\'ll try to do my best...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_1">WHOA! HOW DID YOU DO THAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">I just... I just thought this move would work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_3">No, I mean... How? HUH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_4">WAIT A SECOND! That plushie is... That\'s a prize given only to Cookies who become champion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_5">YOU\'RE the champion?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Erm... Well, I didn\'t mean to keep it a secret...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_7">DO IT AGAIN! Show me how you did that! I wanna learn!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie0518_8">Should I record the screen? Or should I learn from you daily? Or maybe I should analyze your reflexes...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0002_3_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Erm...
Let\'s take things one step at a time... Please?</string>
