  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_1">"Preparations are complete. It has taken me all winter, but my latest experimental elixir is finally ready for the real test."</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_2">"Fortune favors the bold!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_3">Aaand... that\'s that! Research notes are completed and now, it\'s finally time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_4">If my calculations are correct, this elixir should provide me with enhanced intelligence!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_5">*Gulp, gulp, gulp*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_6">... Hmmm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_7">... Hmmm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_8">HMMM?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_9">What\'s this...? I feel so... heavy, drowsy. It\'s like my dough is melting onto the floor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_10">Something\'s wrong... The formula, the calculations were all precise! Or could it be... cross contamination?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_11">Waaait... Why is there a half-empty glass of grape juice on my workstation?! Grrr... VAMPIRE COOKIE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_12">The antidote! I need to find the back-up antidote I made! Buuut... It\'s like the whole world is slowing down...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_13">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_14">Meh...
Who needs an antidote.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0034_15">*Yawn*
I\'ll just take a nap or something, I guess.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_1">C\'mon, spill the beans.
What happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0034_2">Whaaat...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_3">You\'re being weird. Usually, you\'d be sticking your nose in your research journal, or experimenting, but... you haven\'t moved a muscle all day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_4">You\'re just lying down and staring off into space. How many glasses of my grape juice did you have?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0034_5">So what...?
What\'s your point...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_6">So what? SO WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_7">Is this is my life now...?
Cuz it\'s great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_8">You\'re not so bad nowadays, ya know? The lazy talking, the blank staring.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_9">Looks like you\'ve finally opened your eyes to the bliss of a slow, relaxing life. Not bad, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0034_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_11">Hey. Yo.
You awake?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0034_12">Quit yapping away... I\'m too tired to talk right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_13">Yapping away?!
You astound me, Alchemist Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0035_14">That\'s the best thing I\'ve heard from you, ever! You\'re the greatest sister a Cookie could have, I tell ya.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_1">Alchemist Cookie...?
I think you\'d better get up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0034_2">Whyyy...?
Just leave me be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_3">Look outside the window...!
There\'re a bunch of Cookies asking for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0028_4">ALCHEMIST COOKIE!
You promised to make me the most awesomest cherry bomb!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0038_5">I thought you were going to analyze the gems I found from my latest adventure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Hmph, I knew it! I KNEW IT!
I\'ll just have to research the method of creating Life Potions all on my own!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_7">Everyone out there looks a bit... well, really angry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0034_8">Staaahp...
So much nagging... PSSSH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_9">Ugh! You stink of grape juice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0034_10">*Yawn*
*Smacks lips*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">You know what? Let\'s just go... It looks like Alchemist Cookie has given up on her pursuit for knowledge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_12">H-h-hey, wait!
No she hasn\'t!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_13">... This is bad! All those years Alchemist Cookie spent getting smart and doing research will end up in crumbs if she doesn\'t snap out of... whatever this is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0035_14">I\'m the lazy one in the family, not her! She needs to better than me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_1">Wizard Cookie!
Wizard Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Nope. I told you last time, I\'m not using magic to conjure up some grape juice for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_3">Huh?
No, that\'s not-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">And also, another nope. I\'ve never tasted grape juice that the ancient wizards made.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_5">No, seriously!
I need your help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Go on...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_7">Magic! Magic is the only way to bring Alchemist Cookie back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Huh?
What\'re you talking about?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_9">Alchemist Cookie drank some experimental elixir and became weird! She\'s been drinking grape juice all day, not moving a muscle, and nothing else!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">So... just like you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_11">YES! Just like me!
We can\'t let Alchemist Cookie\'s research and efforts go to waste.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Hm, I see.
Well, if we are to proceed, I just need to check one thing first.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_13">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">How much grape juice have YOU had today...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0035_15">Not a single drop!
Alchemist Cookie drank everything!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_1">Heeey... Staaahp...
I don\'t wanna get up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_2">Sure, sure, we know.
But just stand up straight, just for a moment. And don\'t move.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_3">NOW, WIZARD COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Here we go!
Juicio dehydratus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_5">Cast a spell that makes you go away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_6">PLEASE...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_7">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_8">So annoying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_9">No!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_10">So annoying... TO HAVE TO KEEP NAGGING YOU TO STAY OUT OF MY ROOM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_11">...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_12">And I told you a million times to clean up after yourself!!! What\'s with all the grape juice stains around here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">That\'s... all on you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_14">... Alchemist Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_15">And why didn\'t you air this place out? It reeks of grape juice in here! What sort of slob have you become to live in an environment like this?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_16">She\'s back!
Alchemist Cookie, you\'re back!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_17">My little sister...! Always so serious and angry! The one who\'d always make my juice taste like vinegar with her nagging... SHE\'S BACK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0034_18">... Huh?
Why do I get the feeling that I\'m missing something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_19">This is the stuff...
The noise. The cacophony. The clamorous ambience...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_20">I\'ll never say this out loud, but... You give my laziness meaning, little sis.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS8_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0035_21">Welcome back, Alchemist Cookie!
I should have a glass of grape juice to celebrate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Welcome to my room, Cream Unicorn Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0157_2">Thank you for inviting me. It\'s such a lovely place, filled with joy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">No, thank YOU!
I\'ve always wanted to be friends with you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Besides, it\'s hard to meet Cookies who want to talk about all sorts of things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0157_5">Hehe, I like listening to all sorts of stories and memories.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0157_6">Memories are like stars in the night sky, there are so many...! And I want to hear them all...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_1_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">Then you\'ve come to the right place! I\'ve got all sorts of stories to share!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Do you know how I met GingerBrave? I found him flat on the floor, in a dark room all by himself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">He woke up after I gave him some Life Potions. But he didn\'t know ANYTHING about the castle. And then we decided look for more potions together, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_3">It sounds like a such a fun memory. What happened next-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Speaking of Life Potions, it reminds me of those stale and spoiled Cookies outside the Castle. They kinda look like Zombie Cookie, but they act a lot different.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_5">I... Pardon-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">But then it\'s only natural that everyone\'s different right? Like, look at Vampire Cookie and Alchemist Cookie. They\'re family, but they talk and act totally differently!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_7">... Oh, the topic\'s changed again-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">I\'ve never seen a Cookie who loves grape juice as much as Vampire Cookie! Speaking of juice, have you met Sparkling Cookie? He knows how to make all sorts of juice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_9">I... This is... Wait-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Have you been to the Sparkling Party? It\'s such a fun place! Oh, do you wanna hear some jokes? I met Avocado Cookie there, and she taught me some really funny ones!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">What do you call a fish with no eye? Teehee, take a guess! I wonder if you can get the answer? It\'s very funny and it\'s a lot simpler than you think!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_12">So... dizzy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0157_13">This feels like... riding a really, really fast merry-go-round.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_2_POR1_Cookie.0003_14">The answer is... FSH! Heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">There was this one time that Strawberry Cookie wanted to ride the swings, but it was a bit shaky and made a weird noise. She held onto the rope so tightly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">When it was time to get off, she still wouldn\'t let go! I kept telling her to get off, but we ended up staying there for hours! It was okay though, since we had so much fun there and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_3">... Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">... Where are you going?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_5">Oh, I... erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">Are you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">Do you want to see the stars? Is that where you\'re going? That sounds like a perfect idea! You\'re amazing! Let\'s go outside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">Did you know that Wizard Cookie once taught me how to find constellations? It\'s really easy. You see those stars? They make a giant dipper and those make an hourglass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0003_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_9">It sounds like you have so many interesting memories, GingerBright... So, so many...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.0012_1">May sweet blessings be upon you, Rosemary Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">May sweet blessings be upon us all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_3">I somehow feel... calmer and much more confident than before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">The journey here was worth it. Thank you, Angel Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.0012_5">I\'m happy for you, Rosemary Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">Feel free to visit any time...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_7">You are too kind. Well then, I shall now take my leave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_8">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">Angel Cookie?
If I may, can I ask you a small favor?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.0012_1">A small favor...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">I, well... No, it may not be a small favor after all. Never mind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.0012_3">No, it\'s okay... You can ask...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">Well... I was wondering if you\'d be willing to bless the residents of the Syrup Garden as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">They are my dearest friends and family. But their recent efforts to restore and protect the garden have taken a toll on them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">I know it\'s unreasonable for me to ask, but-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.0012_7">Of course! Everyone must be blessed...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_8">Will you be alright? You do not have to push yourself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">The Syrup Garden is home to many, many residents, after all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.0012_10">It\'s okay...! It\'s only one garden...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.0012_11">Bring as many as you wish, Rosemary Cookie... The more blessings to share, the better...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">Angel Cookie... You truly have a heart of gold...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">Calm down, everyone! Please form a line! Everyone will be blessed, so please remain in line!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0029_2">She\'s right! There\'s no need for chaos! Everyone stand behind me and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0033_3">OUTTA MY WAAAY!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0029_4">WAAAGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0030_5">Me first! Me first! Me first!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0031_6">Angel Cookie\'s passing blessings out! Everyone scream, cheer, and shout!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0032_7">Who shoved me?! STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Npc.0032_8">OW! Did you just push me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.0012_9">Two hundred twenty-one...
Two hundred twenty-two...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.0012_10">Rosemary Cookie...! Are these...? Are they all... residents of the Syrup Garden?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Not everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.0012_12">I see... Then that means...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">The ones gathered here are only about a third of the garden\'s population!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0012_3_POR1_Cookie.0012_14">Oh no...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">I\'m certain it\'s somewhere here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">YEOWCH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_3">Ha. Ha. HA...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_4">GOT YA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_5">I knew there was someone secretly reading my research notes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_6">And to catch you... I set a trap!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_7">Now... Let\'s see who you are, thief!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Aaah...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_9">...
Wizard Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">*Sigh*
Yes, yes. It\'s me... Now let me go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie0034_11">You... You\'ve finally abandoned magic and decided to steal my insights into alchemy, haven\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">No!
Why would I want to steal your research?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie0034_2">I dunno. Maybe you\'ve finally admitted to alchemy being superior to some wand-waving wizarding!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Huh...? My name is Wizard Cookie!
I have no interest in alchemy, thank you very much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">If you must know...
The candy from my staff has somehow fallen off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">I\'m looking everywhere I can for it!
For MY MAGICAL research!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie0034_6">Hm. Doesn\'t sound like you\'re lying or anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie0034_7">... But can you prove you\'re not lying?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Just take a look by the stairs you use for storing reagents! It\'ll probably be around there somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie0034_9">Hmmm...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_2_POR1_Cookie0034_10">Well I\'ll be...
You weren\'t lying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">See! I told you so!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_2">Then who has been messing with my research logs?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">How would I know?!
You and I have the same goal—seeking knowledge! Albeit, our methods are vastly different...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">You may be annoying, but I still consider you a peer when it comes to the pursuit of knowledge! I wouldn\'t steal anything of yours!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_5">Well, okay... I think so too, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0035_6">Hm, hmm, hmmm!
There\'s no one here at this hour as usual?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0035_7">Alriiight then...! Now... where are you...? There has to be some sort of alchemical formula for making grape...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0035_8">... juice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Hey, Alchemist Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_10">Yeah, Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">I think we found your so-called thief.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_12">I think I can see that too, obviously.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_13">And very... clearly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0035_14">Oh? Is this a bad time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0034_15">GET HIM!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Lightning ssstrike!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0034_3_POR1_Cookie0035_17">AGH!
Time to make my exit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_1">So, essentially, you\'re going to host a party?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Yes, to commemorate the return of several of my family\'s treasures.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_3">However, as it has been quite some time since I\'ve hosted such an event, I am unsure I\'ll be able to pull it off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Hence, the reason for requesting your aid.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_5">And an excellent reason! I\'ll make sure your party goes well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0111_6">I too shall do my best to create the finest blend of juices for your party.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_7">First things first. Have you chosen a theme for your party?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_9">A theme! You need to decorate for the party with a clear concept in mind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_11">...
Then I\'ve already decided.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_12">That was quick!
Well, what is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.2002_13">Simple.
\"Fight to the crumbs.\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_14">Well, that\'s quite...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0037_15">Marvelous!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_1_POR1_Cookie.0111_16">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">Think about it. Every guest will each wield a sword.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">Then, they will all engage in a spectacular display of swordsmanship.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.0037_3">It\'s such a unique idea!
I can\'t wait to be part of it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.0111_4">No, wait, but...
What if someone gets injured and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">I jest.
The swords you see here are all a part of my family\'s collection.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_6">I dare not risk damaging them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_7">I shall think about the theme later. For now, let us address the issue of invitations.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">Have you any advice to provide?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.0037_9">Writing invitations is so easy!
Think of it like writing a short letter. Say what you wish to the Cookie you\'re going to invite.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_10">I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.2002_11">Then the first invitation I write will be to a Cookie I wish to duel, in full armor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.0037_12">A duel! How exhilarating!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_2_POR1_Cookie.0111_13">The two of you realize this is a PARTY, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_1">Again, I jest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_2">I shall now sit at my desk, the most significant treasure in my family\'s entire history. From there, I shall write my first invitations.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0037_3">Oooh, you\'ve already thought of a Cookie you want to invite?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_4">Of course I have.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_5">Here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0037_6">Do I know the Cookie you\'re giving this invitation to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0111_7">Do you want us to deliver it to someone?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_8">No. These invitations are for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_9">Is it not customary to first invite those who have aided in the party\'s preparations?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0037_10">I\'m very touched, Marble Danish Cookie! I promise to help make this party one for the history books!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0111_11">It did, erm, almost go off the rails...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.0111_12">But, nonetheless, I will do my best to help you prepare as well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2002_3_POR1_Cookie.2002_13">Thank you, both. Now then, shall we begin with the preparations?</string>
