  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0003.Title.01.Summary">Cream Unicorn Cookie is paying a visit to GingerBright\'s room. GingerBright is overjoyed to have a visitor!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0003.Title.02.Summary">An over-excited GingerBright is more than happy to share her tales and stories... A dizzying amount of stories...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0003.Title.03.Summary">Sensing that the conversation has somehow gone off the rails, Cream Unicorn Cookie tries to make an escape...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0012.Title.01.Summary">After receiving a blessing from Angel Cookie, Rosemary Cookie asks for a small favor...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0012.Title.02.Summary">Rosemary Cookie asks if Angel Cookie can share blessings with the residents of the Syrup Garden. Angel Cookie happily agrees!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0012.Title.03.Summary">The residents of the Syrup Garden have come to visit Angel Cookie for blessings! And there\'s a LOT of residents...! A LOT!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0034.Title.01.Summary">Someone has been tampering with Alchemist Cookie\'s research! She\'s set a trap for the culprit, who turns out to be... Wizard Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0034.Title.02.Summary">Wizard Cookie claims he\'s innocent! He tries to prove he\'s not the culprit.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0034.Title.03.Summary">Having been proven innocent, Alchemist Cookie and Wizard Cookie discover the identity of the true culprit...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2002.Title.01.Summary">Marble Danish Cookie, after procuring several of his family\'s heirlooms and treasures, has decided to host a party. He\'s asked Cheesecake Cookie and Sparkling Cookie to provide some expert advice!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2002.Title.02.Summary">Marble Danish Cookie has an... interesting theme for the party, which Cheesecake Cookie finds fascinating. The only thing stopping them from this strange plan is Sparkling Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2002.Title.03.Summary">Having figured out the big picture for the party, Marble Danish Cookie writes the first pair of party invitations. Which two Cookies will he be inviting first?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.08">What Happened to My Sister?!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.08.Story">Though a welcome phenomenon at first, Vampire Cookie misses his sister\'s usual self. Get back to normal, Alchemist Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SpeciaInteraction.Limited.Floor.001">Cozy Candytree Shelter</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SpeciaInteraction.Limited.Floor.001.Story">There was once a lonely street with but a single candy cane tree. At some point, a passerby decided to hang a sturdy swing from the tree, and another passerby placed a beautiful cushion. Having become a cozy shelter for all, this place brings comfort and joy to every visitor.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0012">Angel Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0003">GingerBright Bear Jelly Toy</string>
