  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0012.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Angel Cookie. The fuzzy hair is especially soft and makes the toy extra cuddle-worthy.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.2002.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Marble Danish Cookie. Made from a total of 128 layers of the finest cloth, this toy is the epitome of luxurious quality.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0003.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles GingerBright. The toy\'s face is beaming with the brightest and cheeriest of smiles. If you listen carefully, you can almost make out a faint but excited giggle.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRun15th.JellyBear.107200">Strawberry Shortcake Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRun15th.JellyBear.107200.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Strawberry Shortcake Cookie. Even a single glance at this toy seemingly tells you that it\'ll always stay by your side as a friend and companion.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRun15th.Limited.Floor.001">Festive Strawberry Shortcake</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRun15th.Limited.Floor.001.Story">FIFTEEN YEARS! That\'s no small feat! A sweet and tangy strawberry shortcake has been prepared to celebrate the fun-filled years of running! All the Cookies have been running with hearts burning with courage, thanks to you! And you! AND YOU!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02">Crème Refuge</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch01.SQuest08.Summary">The guards of the Crème Refuge endlessly debate the true definition of freshness and where to draw the line. Meanwhile, our friends help Onyx Cream Cookie with his mold infection.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest01.Summary">Onyx Cream Cookie, having reassured the guards that the Temperature Controller has been repaired, requests entry into the refuge and vouches for our friends. But something about the refuge seems... off.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest02.Summary">First Cream Cookie has returned to the Crème Refuge! The residents are ecstatic! They cheer and welcome her return...!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest03.Summary">The Crème Refuge has been engulfed in disorder due to Fizzy Soda\'s antics! But just before our heroes could dish out some justice, a monster appears!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest04.Summary">Onyx Cream Cookie easily defeats the moldy monstrosity. The inhabitants of the refuge peek out from their hiding spots, welcoming them. Our friends are eager to learn about the Crème Refuge\'s situation.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest05.Summary">The climate of the refuge has been growing warmer and warmer, leaving the residents no choice but to rely on ice packs. But Fizzy has wrested control and monopolized the ice packs!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest06.Summary">The group learns that a cabal of sodas has been overseeing the icy prison and growing in strength! Onyx Cream Cookie cannot stand by and tolerate such injustice.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest07.Summary">GingerBrave and friends have brought much needed ice packs to the refuge! They then head off into the frozen lands to rescue GingerDozer!</string>
