  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_1">Stop right there! You\'re not going anywhere until you\'ve undergone the expiration inspection!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0051_1">No, wait! Hear me out! I\'m only a single day past expiration...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0052_1">And I\'m entirely brined. Expiration doesn\'t really, usually apply to me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_2">Everyone must adhere to the inspection!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_3">All travelers past expiration will not be allowed entry! No exceptions, no exemptions, and no excuses!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0044_1">Hold on a moment. They seem fresh enough...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0044_2">It can\'t hurt to let them inside, can it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_4">I said NO EXCEPTIONS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_5">This is no time for leniency! The refuge doesn\'t have enough ice packs to go around.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0044_3">Yeah, but, well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_6">Is the temperature getting to your head?! We\'re already in enough of a pickle because of Fizzy\'s antics...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0045_7">Letting these folks in would only make things worse!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0051_2">Please!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0051_3">I\'m still fresh! I swear I am! Believe me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Npc.0052_2">You won\'t be in a bigger pickle cuz of me, I promise. My expiration date is just a suggestion after all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">What\'re they talking about? What\'s expiration mean...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Ahem. The concept of an expiration date is often used for determining the maximum duration of freshness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Do Cookies have an expiration date too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Hm! I\'ve never heard of this expiration thing before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Hm, now that I think about it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">I\'ve not come across any notion of Cookies such as ourselves being tied to the very concept.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">If that\'s the case...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">What if we\'re not allowed in \"just because\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_1">*Sigh*
Expiration...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_2">There was a time when such a concept held no meaning in Mount St. Crème...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_3">If I may? I\'m confident that you will be granted entry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_4">Please, send my regards to those in the refuge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_5">I... truly miss them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Onyx Cream Cookie, wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Why don\'t you tag along with us then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Yeah, after all, it\'s always nice to say hello!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_6">... I cannot.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2007_7">My exposure to warmer temperatures has... adversely affected my dough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">*GASP*
Then does that mean...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">If you\'re infected, are you in pain right now?! Just like the Moldizens from before?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Hold on a moment! We helped the Moldizens from before with baking soda and it\'s proved effective!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH1_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Let\'s use the rest of it, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0045_8">Stop! Please hold for an expiration inspection!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_4">Huh...? Hey, these folks are Cookies.
Erm, do you have anything to declare? All of you... fresh and crunchy, I assume?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Of course! We\'re quite fresh, crunchy, and very much lively, thank you very much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">AAAnd we\'re cute too! Heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0045_9">Hmmm... YOU THERE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_5">WAIT! Is that... *GASP*
Sir Onyx Cream Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Wow, looks like Onyx Cream Cookie is famous around here too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_8">Greetings, old friends. It is good to see you again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_9">It seems that, with the passing of time, much has changed here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_6">We thought we\'d never see you again! Everyone has missed you so, so much, Sir Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_10">Though it has taken much time, the temperature controller is back in working order.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_11">So I implore you to grant all of us entry. I will vouch for everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_12">After all, they seem quite fresh and worthy of entry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0051_4">*GASP*
THANK YOU...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0052_3">Yes, yes! We\'re still fresh! We promise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0045_10">The temperature controller... Is it really fixed?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">Indeed! We personally had a stake in its repair.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_7">It\'s a miracle...! It\'s just what we\'ve been waiting for!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">They look so happy at the news!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_8">Everyone will be overjoyed at your return, Sir Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0044_9">It\'s been so... Well, the refuge... something happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Hey! Do you hear that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Sounds like some sort of commotion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">I hope it\'s nothing bad...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">It definitely sounds like this Crème Refuge is quite populated!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">C\'mon! Let\'s take a look for ourselves!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_13">Apologies, but we must depart with haste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0045_11">Wait! Sir Onyx Cream Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0055_1">Hurrah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0055_2">Hurrah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0055_3">First Cream Cookie
has returned!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0039_1">EEEP!
FIRST CREAM COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_1">Hear me, my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_2">It seems much has
happened during my absence...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_3">But for now, that beast
will harm you no more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_4">Our very own
Onyx Cream Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_5">is tending to the
temperature controller.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_6">The winds will be
chilled once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0041_1">Hear, hear!
Woot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_7">Unwelcomed frost has
built up on these lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_8">But I shall personally
look into it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_9">Do not fall
into despair!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ2_CUT1_Npc.0054_1">Hmph...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0002_6">Is that the
refuge over there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0002_7">But it\'s...
Something seems wrong.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_14">Hm, the conversation
at the inspection post... </string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_15">Am I missing something...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0045_12">Sir Onyx Cream Cookie!
Wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_16">Impeccable timing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_17">I suspected you wished
to address something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_18">Tell me,
what has transpired here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_10">The truth is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_11">Things may have
been bad out there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_12">but the refuge hasn\'t
fared well either.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_6">Did something happen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_7">This place is a bit, well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">Something just
feels wrong here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0025_9">And it feels rather
unsafe and uneasy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_13">Well... The thing is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0045_13">It\'s Fizzy Soda.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_19">Fizzy?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">Erm, who\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_20">The frail one who always
put his own wellbeing first...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_21">Am I recalling correctly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_14">*Sigh*
Yes, sir. It\'s him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0045_14">He\'s taken control
of the refuge,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0045_15">and his posse has grown
greedy and reckless...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0045_16">The Crème Refuge has become as lawless as-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_2">BWAHAHA!
Lawless, eh?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_3">Psssh! That just hurts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_4">I\'m only doin\' ma part</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_5">to provide this dump
some fresh ice packs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_6">And that\'s the thanks I get?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_22">What have you been scheming
in my absence, you fiend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_7">WE-HE-EEELL! It\'s the one and
only Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">HE\'S HUGE AND SCARY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_8">And you two piles of scraps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_9">I told you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_10">No one gets inside</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_11">WITHOUT MY PERMISSION!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">I\'m scared...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0044_15">W-w-we\'re s-s-s-sorry, Fizzy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_23">I will not allow such injustice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0051_5">MONSTER! MOOONSTER!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0052_4">WE\'RE DONE FOR!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_12">HAHA! Looks like you\'ve got bigger fish to fry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_13">I\'ll get rid of that holier-than-thou stench of yours!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_14">Welcome back, Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0054_15">And good riddance! FWAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Npc.0046_">*Roar*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ3_CUT1_Cookie.2007_24">Meet your end, foul creature!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">That was awesome, Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">You really showed that monster who\'s boss!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">Such prowess in combat deserves high praise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">The only thing WE seem to be doing when facing such a monstrosity is, well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Just screaming and running away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Thanks, Onyx Cream Cookie... You saved us again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2007_25">No need for such flattery. I am only doing what is required.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_9">So this is the Crème Refuge, huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Is it just me or is it a bit too quiet...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">All that noise we heard before... It\'s like it never happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_1">Oh... Oh...? OH...?
Did you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_2">You DID...! You defeated the monster...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">Hello there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Onyx Cream Cookie took care of everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_3">Onyx Cream Cookie???</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_4">ONYX CREAM COOKIE! It really is you!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Everyone we\'ve met so far is super happy to see Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">I\'m glad we were able to come this far, together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Hehe! You can say that again, GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_5">So much has happened while you were away, sir...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_6">The greedy have wrestled control of the refuge and we-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_7">*GASP*
Wait... Is Fizzy around? He\'s not listening, is he...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">Nah, he\'s probably not around!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">He ran off when the monster showed up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2007_26">Just how much chaos has been wrought upon the refuge...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_8">It\'s... It\'s a long story!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_9">Quickly, over here...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">Oh no... Everyone looks really tired and sick...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_10">When everything started warming up,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_11">everyone in the refuge managed to stay fresh with ice packs.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">So ice packs can keep everyone fresh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">That sounds really smart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">But... why does everyone look so tired...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_12">Well, we used to harvest ice packs found in the chilled alcove.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_13">The cold, dry winds there were perfect for keeping them nice and frosty...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_14">We used to bring back as many as we could to the refuge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_15">And once an ice pack became too warm, it could be refrozen in the alcove, good as new.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_16">But Fizzy... he started to... He just decided...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_17">*WAIL*
He forcefully took over the alcove and refused to share the ice packs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0053_18">Without those ice packs, most of us are just days away from expiring...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">So that\'s why the refuge seems so gloomy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_27">It\'s obvious that Fizzy Soda\'s greed has wrought much havoc...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_28">This dire crisis must be resolved.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_29">Despite having repaired the controller,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_30">it will take precious time for temperatures to return to normal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_31">I must make haste and bring an end to Fizzy\'s tyranny, ensuring that ice packs are available for all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">We won\'t let you go alone, Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">Hehe. Right on cue, as always, GingerBrave.
And now... cue GingerBright.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">He\'s right! We\'re going with you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Well then, let\'s get moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_16">Well, well, WELL!
You lot are tougher than I thought!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_32">You foul villain!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_33">What has happened to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_34">How is it that you\'ve changed so drastically?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_35">It\'s as if you weren\'t affected by mold, but by something far worse!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_14">YEAH! And it\'s not nice being a big, mean, selfish bully!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_17">Hey, come on now! No need for such hurtful words!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_18">The old me is gone, and good riddance, I say!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_19">I used to be a weak worrywart, always concerned about losing the last of my bubbles.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_20">But once the frost started to build up, so did my strength!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_21">It happened to all of us sodas! We\'re taller! We\'re stronger! WE\'RE BULKED UP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">Bulked up? I guess that\'s... one way to put it. But, something\'s awfully... lumpy about him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">I knew something was off! Yeah, he definitely looks a bit weird!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">It seems the carbonation within him has burst out rather than bulked up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_22">Bubbles, shmubbles! Gains are gains, ya hear?! I\'m still stronger than I\'ve ever been!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_23">Us sodas are never gonna let the old days come back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_24">Resist all you want! You\'re gonna end up like everyone else here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Npc.0054_25">As permanent residents of Mount St. Crème and its Icy Prison, with us as your wardens! PAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_36">I cannot permit this madness to continue.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2007_37">Your reign of terror ends now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_38">His hardened ice must be shaved away to reveal his weakness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_39">At any given chance, we must not hesitate to strike!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_40">Let us lower our stance and bring the swords to the bottom, striking from below!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">Sounds like a plan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_41">Let us bring an end to his tyranny!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_26">Yeowch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_27">Grrr...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_28">It hurts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_29">That pesky sword!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_30">Take this...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.2007_42">Hmph... That pest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0001_24">We can\'t give up now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_31">Stay still, you scraps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0054_32">TAKE THAT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0001_25">GAH?! Oh no! LOOK OUT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0003_15">That was amazing, Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0002_13">So he DOES have a weak spot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_MINI1_Cookie.2007_43">It is an opportune
time to strike!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_33">Cut it out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_34">I HATE COOKIES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_35">That stings!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_36">Grrr...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_37">I\'ll show you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_38">Grrr, take this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Cookie.0001_26">SO unfair!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Cookie.2007_44">Is that all?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_39">Stop wasting my time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0054_40">You\'re scraps!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0001_27">He\'s fizzling out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0025_16">It\'s now or never, Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0002_14">You can do it...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_MINI2_Cookie.2007_45">Let\'s finish this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.2007_46">What\'s done is done.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0001_28">You did it, Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">Looks like he\'s definitely down for the count!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH2BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">And now we can deliver fresh ice packs to the Crème Refuge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_30">Tada! Ice packs for
everyone who needs\'em!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_17">Onyx Cream Cookie taught
Fizzy a good lesson!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_18">There\'s nothing to
worry about!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0053_19">*GASP*
Thank you! Thank you so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_31">Thanks for letting us know
where the Icy Prison is too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_17">Though I get the feeling
it won\'t be smooth sailing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_15">And... thanks for joining us,
Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_16">You\'re so awesome...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_47">The cabal of sodas
still control the prison.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_48">Their corruption must
come to an end.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_49">And it shall, for justice
will be delivered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_50">Ah! And we may also find a way
to repair that compass of yours.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">Oh? How?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_51">On the path to the
prison is a secret hollow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_52">Traces of ancient magic
and baking are within.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_53">A thorough search may
reveal something useful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_20">Oooh! I love secrets!
They\'re always fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_32">Alright!
Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Seasonpass.Purchase.Popup.Text6">Upgrade the Season Pass
for awesome benefits!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Seasonpass.Purchase.Popup.Text7">Upgrade the Season Pass
for awesome benefits!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Seasonpass.Purchase.Popup.Text8">Upgrade</string>
  <string name="$UX..CookiePuzzleChallenge.Title">Cookie Challenge</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.08.SQuest1.Summary">Alchemist Cookie decided to test her newest elixir... by drinking it herself! But it was contaminated with a drop of grape juice?! The results... have turned the world upside down.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.08.SQuest2.Summary">Vampire Cookie loves the way Alchemist Cookie has changed. It\'s awesome having such a laid-back younger sister!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.08.SQuest3.Summary">It seems that Alchemist Cookie\'s newfound laziness is causing a stir... Other Cookies are eager for Alchemist Cookie to continue her research, but she\'s not moving a muscle. Vampire Cookie realizes that she can\'t stay this way any longer.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.08.SQuest4.Summary">Vampire Cookie hurriedly asks Wizard Cookie for a favor: a magic spell to return Alchemist Cookie to her normal self. What\'ll happen next?!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.08.SQuest5.Summary">It worked! Vampire Cookie welcomes the annoying nagging from his sister to its fullest. With everything back to normal, he decides to enjoy a glass of grape juice with Alchemist Cookie\'s rant continuing in the background.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.1002">Twisted Donut Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.1002.Profile">Twisted Donut Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.1002.Story">\"Leave everything about running the Star Coal Express to me!\" 

Twisted Donut Cookie and his trusty Coco Drop helpers comb every inch of the train to make sure it\'s in proper shape for a safe trip to the next destination.

With this dynamic team at work, no dough marks nor spots can be found when it\'s time for new passengers to board, and the train keeps its almost glittering shine at all times!</string>
