  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.001.Story">Whoever stacked these pancakes in such a precarious way was surely an adventurous sort! This delicious stack of flapjacks can only be found in the Star Coal Express\' very own dining carriage. You\'re going to need a stomach that\'s ready for adventuring to wolf down this dish!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.002.Story">Sturdy bags to keep your things safe on all of your adventures! It\'s always a good idea to prepare for the unknown, but don\'t forget to leave some extra space for all the stuff you might find during the journey!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.003.Story">Down! Down, boy, down! You greedy little, adorable thing, you! This chest is always hungry for all sorts of items, but it loves to scarf down all sorts of adventuring gear and necessities!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.004.Story">A pristine, well-maintained train seat. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.005.Story">Ssshhh, do not disturb! Loafykins is sleeping!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.006.Story">There\'s no doubt whose luggage this is! Let\'s keep it in a nice and safe place.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.007.Story">A simple potted plant. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Floor.008.Story">Super useful and colorful Star Coal! Who wouldn\'t like to have this?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Wall.001.Story">A single glance out this window fills your mind with curiosity and wonder. Your heart begins to pound with excitement and, before you know it, you\'re ready for an epic adventure and you won\'t give up until you\'ve completed it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Wall.002.Story">Stickers used to decorate the passenger carriages. Let\'s put these to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Hanger.001.Story">Does this really gauge steam? Maybe it measures excitement? Or maybe it\'s for something else?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Hanger.002.Story">A simple yet sturdy lamp. Let\'s put it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Ceil.001.Story">Seems like this hammock is already in use. Let\'s place it somewhere carefully so the occupant doesn\'t wake up!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.WP.001.Story">Wallpaper used to decorate the interior of a certain train\'s passenger carriages. They look and smell amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie1002.Deck.001.Story">Wooden flooring used to decorate the interior of a certain train\'s passenger carriages. They seem to creak and sing as the train chugs along.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.001">Ice Pick Rapier</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.002">Crystallized Ice Clasp</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.003">Onyx Eye Patch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.001.Story">A rapier that is sharp enough to slice through solid ice with a single swing. The worn handle is evidence of a rigorous training regimen.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.002.Story">Deep within Mount St. Crème, water droplets from icy stalactites dripped down to create gleaming crystals of ice. Onyx Cream Cookie decided to create this clasp as a reminder of Mount St. Crème\'s once pristine beauty and chilled climate.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2007.003.Story">After discovering that he too was infected with mold, Onyx Cream Cookie wore an eyepatch to conceal his ailment for a brief period of time. It was not shame that made him wear it, but a strong desire to prevent unnecessary worries and concerns.</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.OnyxCream.Tooltip">Onyx Coins resembling the darkest of cocoa powder. These can only be obtained during the Onyx Cream Season!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.OnyxCream.Limited.Floor.001">Onyx Cream Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.OnyxCream.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Onyx Cream Cookie. The toy seems to radiate an aura of loyalty and commitment.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SeasonComplete.OnyxCream.Story">Proof of completing the Onyx Cream Collection. Always remember to never give up in the face of adversity!</string>
  <string name="$EP4.CH02.Profile">Profile obtained by completing the \"Crème Refuge\" Chapter</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0112.Season.Profile">Creamy Wolf</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0115.Season.Profile">Pretzel Reindeer</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Story">This stalwart defender\'s dough was created by blending diligently churned cream with substantial portions of cocoa powder resembling onyxes as dark as the night sky.

Onyx Cream Cookie perseveres to uphold his skill with a sword and protect the residents of Mount St. Crème, fueled by a profound loyalty to a certain radiant and noble Cookie. Many recognize his unwavering love for Mount St. Crème, as can be seen through their trust and confidence in his name alone.

Will his efforts to restore Mount St. Crème to its former glory succeed? And, if successful, will he be able to reunite with the Cookie to whom he has pledged an oath of loyalty?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Get">I shall heed your command.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Random.01">I gladly forfeit my dough
to protect the innocent.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Random.02">How may I aid you?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Random.03">I shall protect these sacred lands.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Random.04">I can do this...
I will protect our home.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Random.05">This place is unsafe.
Keep your distance.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Skill.Name">Finishing Slash</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.LifeZero.01">I cannot...
fall here...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2007.Ceil.999">Onyx Cream Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2007.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Snow Stormed Night Onyx Cream Cookie\'s Room!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2007">Snow Stormed Night Onyx Cream Cookie\'s Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2007.Story">The lands of Mount St. Crème would be engulfed by howling gales and fierce blizzards every time the refrigerator was opened. Despite the icy winds peltering the window, Onyx Cream Cookie\'s room always gives off a sense of calm, just like the Cookie himself.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Onyx Cream Cookie\'s soul. It looks like it can withstand anything.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0112.Season">Onyx Crème Wolf</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0113.Season">Butter Crème Wolf</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0114.Season">Berry Crème Wolf</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0115.Season">Crème Pretzel Reindeer</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0116.Season">Matcha Pretzel Reindeer</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0117.Season">Mint Pretzel Reindeer</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0112.Season.Story">Onyx Crème Wolf are fiercely territorial and will pursue anyone who dares to trespass on their grounds. Their usual method of hunting is to hide and meld into the shadows, lurking silently until the opportune moment to strike arrives. However, they are also extremely loyal to those they consider family.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0113.Season.Story">The lush, glistening coats of Butter Crème Wolves can be spotted from long distances away. They are very particular about keeping their fur pristine and well-kept. Perhaps this is why they are rather relaxed and less aggressive than most wolves.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0114.Season.Story">Berry Crème Wolves naturally carry a distinct scent of berries and cream. This odor attracts nearby rabbits, who flee after finding a pack of wolves instead a patch of berries. But in reality, the wolves use this natural scent of theirs in hopes of meeting new friends... not for hunting.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0115.Season.Story">A wild Crème Pretzel Reindeer. It seems friendly and calm.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0116.Season.Story">A wild Matcha Pretzel Reindeer. It seems to have called this place home for a very long time.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0117.Season.Story">A wild Mint Pretzel Reindeer. No one knows where they came from...</string>
