  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2001_1">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0039_2">Look...! It\'s really her!
The Cookie that keeps Mount St. Crème fresh and chilly!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0039_3">She\'s sooo cool!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0040_4">Quiet...! She\'s sleeping...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0040_5">And speaking of...
Shouldn\'t we like... NOT be here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0040_6">What if Onyx Cream Cookie shows up? He might get angry and scold us and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0040_7">Worst case scenario... he might crush us into smithereens...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0041_8">Hehe, I can see it now. He\'d probably say something like...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0041_9">"Who dares to trespass in this sacred chamber?!"</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_10">I couldn\'t have said it better myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0039_11">GYAAAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_12">And yet, despite knowing this, you still made the decision to trespass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_13">Haha.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_14">Hahaha!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0041_15">Erm... er...
Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0040_16">This isn\'t the time to laugh!
We\'re doomed, I tell ya, doomed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0039_17">Let\'s make a run for it, quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Npc0041_18">W-w-wait for me!
Don\'t leave me heeere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_19">*Sigh*
Youths.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2001_20">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_21">While I understand their curiosity...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_22">If anything were to go wrong...
The blessing upon Mount St. Crème may become lost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2001_23">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_24">Though, I must admit, I too am curious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_25">Legend has it that you descended from the clouds, shining with radiance... all that time ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2001_26">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_27">You, the slumbering Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ1_POR1_Cookie2007_28">...
I should patrol the area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_1">No signs of suspicious activity or trespassers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2001_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_3">Strange... How long will she remain asleep?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_4">...
Everyone is curious about you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_5">We believe that you are the one who has blessed Mount St. Crème with eternal freshness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2001_6">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_7">*Sigh*
What am I doing? Talking to a Cookie who probably cannot hear me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_8">And yet, I want to know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_9">Who are you, truly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_10">What mystical energy and strength flows in your dough?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_11">And why do you slumber in these chilled lands?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_12">In the very least...
If only I could learn your name.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2001_13">I am...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2007_14">!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ2_POR1_Cookie2001_15">First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_1">Am I... dreaming?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_2">Where... am I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_3">This is... You\'re in Mount St Crème.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_4">Mount St. Crème...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_5">A sacred land regarded as a safe and fresh haven for all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_6">It has been considered so ever since your arrival,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_7">as Mount St. Crème has remained in a perpetual state of chilled freshness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_8">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_9">It seems like I am not getting through to her all...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_10">I did...? Me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_11">I cannot... remember anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_12">Could it be... amnesia?
What may have caused such a thing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_13">Do not fear. Rest assured, you are quite safe here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_14">And I am certain that your presence alone has blessed this land.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_15">Everyone is eager to meet you, if you are willing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_16">There are many who wish to show their appreciation, First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_17">They have been waiting patiently for quite a long time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_18">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_19">Ah! Pardon me for springing such a request without warning...! If you do not wish to-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_20">No, it\'s just...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_21">I do not know your name. What should I call you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2007_22">Where are my manners! My name is Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_23">I see.
Thank you, Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ3_POR1_Cookie2001_24">I assume that I have been asleep for a long time... and you and the residents of this place have kept me safe during my slumber.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_1">Hup...! Hyah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_2">You train so eagerly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_3">Madam First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_4">I\'ve heard that this is where you train.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_5">Your swordsmanship skills are already well-honed, and yet you continue to train. Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_6">Though Mount St. Crème is peaceful and remains fresh,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_7">I must not grow complacent.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_8">One can never be too prepared for a crisis.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Npc0041_9">Hehe, that\'s Onyx Cream Cookie for ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Npc0040_10">Or maybe he just wants to impress First Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_11">You rascal...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Npc0040_12">AGH!
Run for it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_13">Stop right there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_14">*Chuckle*
You seem to get along well with everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_15">Though it\'s true that I am training to prepare for the unknown...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_16">I am also training in the hopes to aid you, Madam First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_17">To help you regain your memories...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2007_18">If I am to help you, then I must be diligent in my training.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_19">Come, everyone.
I\'ve prepared some refreshments for us all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Cookie2001_20">Shall we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Npc0039_21">Woohoo! You\'re the best, First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ4_POR1_Npc0041_22">Awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_1">Are you truly departing...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_2">Yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_3">Permit me to go with you! I am certain that I can aid you in your quest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_4">Onyx Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_5">Or would I... just be getting your way?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_6">...
I know what I am.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_7">I am weak, and no matter how much I try, I will never measure up to your strength.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_8">No, my friend. That is not the case.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_9">You have kept watch over Mount St. Crème for many winters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_10">If you were to leave Mount St. Crème with me,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_11">the residents who look up to you would fall into despair and lose hope.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_12">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_13">So I must ask of you... Will you and the residents of Mount St. Crème wait patiently for my return?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_14">I will return.
I promise.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_15">... Yes, My Lady!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2001_16">Thank you.
I will be back soon, Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_17">We shall await your safe return, Madam First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_18">... May your every step shine brightly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_19">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_20">And just like that... You departed from these lands, as if you would return soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_21">And yet, you did not.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_22">Nevertheless... I will continue to protect our home,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_23">for I firmly believe in your promise to return.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS9_SQ5_POR1_Cookie2007_24">Always.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_1">Oh dear...
I think I am definitely lost. Where am I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_2">Oh...? Is that... It is!
It\'s a crooked claw tree!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_3">It looks lonely all by itself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_4">Maybe I should plant some seeds around it, to give it some friends?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_5">Yes! Let\'s make the world green!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0013_6">Who... there...?
Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0013_7">Doing something...?
What... doing...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0063_8">I hope everyone grows big and strong!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0013_9">Throwing... things...
Cookie... throwing... seeds? Seeds?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_1_POR1_Cookie0013_10">No seeds!
Plants... scaaary!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_1">This should suffice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_2">Oh, hello little sprouts! You\'re already growing, I see!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0013_3">Growing... fast... too fast...
Scary... plants...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0013_4">Scary... no... don\'t like...
Home... gone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_5">Hm?
Hello? Is someone there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_6">Oh! Hello, Zombie Cookie! It\'s been-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0013_7">PLAAANTS!
NO LIKE... PLANTS! GRAAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_8">Oh... Did I do something wrong...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_9">Wait, is Zombie Cookie afraid of plants...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_2_POR1_Cookie0063_10">Hm... AH!
I\'ve got a perfect idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0013_1">Grah... No more plants near... Good...
No scary... anymore...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_2">There you are, Zombie Cookie!
I\'ve been looking for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_3">Grah? Plant... Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_4">I have a gift for you! Here!
It\'s a special, damp carpet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_5">It looks like moss and algae, but it\'s just a regular carpet! It\'s not a real plant, see?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0013_6">Graaah...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_7">I didn\'t know that I was planting seeds in your room. I\'m really, really sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_8">Would you like to take a closer look at it? It\'s a rather splendid shade of-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0013_9">Plant...!!! Walking?!
WALKING PLANT! GURAAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_10">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_11">Oh dear...
Why is Zombie Cookie running away from me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0013_3_POR1_Cookie0063_12">Wait, Zombie Cookie!
You forgot to take your present!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_1">Welcome! Thank you for visiting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_2">You said that you were interested in trying something new?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_3">What sort of flavors would you prefer? Is there anything that comes to mind?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0045_4">Hm, I think... I\'m looking for something that tastes like cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_5">I see. Anything else?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0045_6">Oh? Cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_7">... You\'ve mentioned that just now. What I meant is, anything other than that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0045_8">Hmmm, no. I really think cocoa is the way to go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_9">Ah, haha...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_1_POR1_Cookie0111_10">Oh dear. This will be quite a difficult evening...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_1">Here we are! How does that taste?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0045_2">Hmmm... I think the flavor of cocoa is a bit watered down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_3">Erm, if I were to add more cocoa into this drink... It would just be hot cocoa.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0045_4">But I really think it could use some more deep, rich cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_5">This is, by far, turning out to be the most interesting night I\'ve ever experienced.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_6">Aaand... there we go!
What do you think? It\'s a special glass of juice with a touch of cocoa aroma blended in-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0045_7">Oh! I know what this is missing. It\'s missing the authentic aroma of cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_8">What have I done to experience such an ordeal...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_9">No, let\'s calm down. This is a lesson! I can learn from this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_10">I will make a brand new drink that is so great, even Cocoa Cookie won\'t be able to resist trying it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_2_POR1_Cookie0111_11">I swear it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_1">This is it!
Time for the coup de grâce!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_2">Behold! I call it, \"mint chocolate sparkling juice!\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0045_3">Interesting... I don\'t think I can taste enough cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_4">... Alas, is this my fate?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_5">Okay then... THIS is truly the last and final glass!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_6">I call it...
The \"cocoa on cocoa atop of cocoa.\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_7">Three plentiful portions of cocoa with a mere half-drop of sparkling juice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0045_8">*GASP*
This is it! This is amazing! I LOVE COCOA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_9">In the end, Cocoa Cookie did not need my help in discovering this drink. After all, it\'s practically just pure cocoa.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0045_10">This is wonderful, Sparkling Cookie!!! I couldn\'t have discovered this amazing glass of cocoa without your help! You really are the best bartender ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_11">But... How can I remain disappointed tonight after seeing such a bright and warm smile?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0111_3_POR1_Cookie0111_12">I\'m glad she\'s pleased with the results, which makes my job ever more satisfying!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie0038_1">Thanks for inviting me here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_2">Do not mention it. After all, it seemed that you needed a place to rest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_3">This Cookie... You can almost smell the money on him. I wonder just how wealthy he really is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_4">Now, to pick up where we left off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_5">You mentioned how lovely your home was. If it\'s so lovely, why are you out here, wandering the castle?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie0038_6">Ha! It\'s simple!
To find new lands and explore the unknown!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie0038_7">I\'d escape and leave the house to explore the world without a second thought!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_8">Oh? So you ran away from home?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_9">Oh dear, oh dear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_1_POR1_Cookie2003_10">...
How immature and reckless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_1">Is it just me or... is she making a really scary face right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_2">I am quite curious about something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_3">Do you perhaps have someone at home who takes care of things, or helps you on a daily basis?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_4">Hm? Oh yeah, she\'s the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_5">She\'s always on top of things, day in and day out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_6">She manages the whole mansion and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_7">And am I correct to assume that she is always trying to find out where you are?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_8">Haha! You\'re absolutely right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie0038_9">Oh, and by the way, if you ever run into Blackberry Cookie, keep my whereabouts a secret! This meeting is just between us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_10">Ah, I see.
Hmmm... Blackberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_11">Pardon me, but I must step outside for a brief moment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_2_POR1_Cookie2003_12">Wait here and make yourself comfortable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_1">I apologize for my absence.
Have you been waiting long?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0038_2">You\'re back! I thought I\'d have to leave without saying thanks and goodbye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_3">Oh? Were you planning on leaving? You must be quite the impatient and restless Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_4">I\'ve returned with someone who is
quite eager to meet you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_5">You absolutely should stay for just a
few more moments and say hello.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0038_6">Oh? Someone wants to meet me-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0045_7">It is time to return home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0038_8">Bl-Bla-Blackberry Cookie?!
What... How... When...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0045_9">You have my thanks. It is thanks to you that I can finally bring him home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_10">Oh, do not mention it. After all, you and I have much in common and it\'s only natural to extend a helping hand, is it not?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0045_11">\"Much in common?\"
Are you employed by a family as well?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_12">Yes, but not anymore. Long ago, I used to keep a watchful eye over a certain young and adorable Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_13">But I digress. You have no need to repay me for this. Getting a chance to witness this entire amusing situation is enough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie0045_14">Thank you.
I hope our paths cross again some day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2003_3_POR1_Cookie2003_15">Yes, and do be careful, dear.
As for you, Adventurer Cookie, you really must learn to grow up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Hm, it seems like that thing on top of the igloo is just plain ice cream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Yup, it\'s just ice cream.
Rest assured, it\'s not your friend Snow Cone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_3">Thank goodness! I was so worried...
You\'re the best, Wizard Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_4">I thought Snow Cone had tripped and fallen onto the igloo...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_5">Oh, but where are my manners! I should at least give you a few snacks to thank you for coming...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_6">What would you like? I have frozen rice cakes, some icy sugar candies, and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">If I may...? I actually have a better idea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_8">Oh? Perhaps a warm cup of tea?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">I would very much appreciate the opportunity to inspect your Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_1_POR1_Cookie0030_10">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">I\'ve always been curious about your wand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I want to learn how it works! How it manages to summon snow and ice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">So, if it\'s okay with you, I\'d like to take it and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_4">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_6">I won\'t let you take the Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_7">I won\'t let you take my friends away!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Er, I think there\'s some sort of misunderstanding... I don\'t want to take the wand away from you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">I merely wish to take a closer look at it...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_10">Really? Is that it? Is he lying? Can I trust him...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_11">No! NO! He\'s lying!
His eyes have a funny look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_12">His eyes are glittering with excitement! Excitement at the thought of stealing my wand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie0030_13">No! Never!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">UWAAAGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_2_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">Hey! There\'s no need to summon the Snow King?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie0030_1">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Stop glaring at me like that!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">I really, really am not going to steal your wand!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">GAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">I\'m not getting through to Snow Sugar Cookie at all! I need to get out of here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Okay! OKAY!
I\'ll just drop everything and go! I\'m leaving peacefully and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">AAAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">I said I\'m leaving! Why\'d you do that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie0030_9">You\'re trying to trick me! I saw you still looking at my Snow Sugar Wand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">Ugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">I am DEFINITELY not interested in the Snow Sugar Wand anymore! I\'m leaving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie0030_12">Oh?! You mean...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie0030_13">Oh no!!! I\'m so sorry, Wizard Cookie! It was all just a misunderstanding...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">And now we\'ve come full circle to experience a misunderstanding about a misunderstanding!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">*Sigh*
In any case... I\'ll remember to never even mention any word of wands or snow next time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0030_3_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">NEVER!</string>
