  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.Main">Zombies vs. Plants</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.01">Plants, Invasion, SCARED!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.02">Sprout... Uh-Oh.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.03">Walking Plants...?! GRAAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.01.Summary">Herb Cookie, lost and alone, has stumbled upon an empty field. He decides to spruce up the place by sowing some seeds, but it turns out this is Zombie Cookie\'s room!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.02.Summary">The seeds that were planted have sprouted! Zombie Cookie becomes distraught and flees the area...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Title.03.Summary">Herb Cookie learns that Zombie Cookie is deathly afraid of plants. He tries to apologize with a small gift... but Zombie Cookie\'s reaction is not what Herb Cookie expected!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.Main">A New Item on the Menu</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.01">Cocoa! Cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.02">A Sweet Mystery</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.03">Cocoa is the BEST</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.01.Summary">Sparkling Cookie attempts to make a drink for Cocoa Cookie, but it turns out the only drink she wants is hot cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.02.Summary">Sparkling Cookie wants to introduce Cocoa Cookie to new flavors and varieties of juice. But, once again, Cocoa Cookie only wants a cup of hot cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Title.03.Summary">In the end, Sparkling Cookie prepares a mug of rich cocoa for his visitor. He may have failed in convincing her to try something new, but her beaming, warm smile is enough to stave off the bitter taste of failure.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.Main">Such a Difficult Cookie</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.01">Troublemaker</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.02">Immature and Reckless</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.03">A Memory of Days Past</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.01.Summary">Adventurer Cookie has been invited to visit Sachertorte Cookie\'s lavishly furnished room. Just as a nefarious plot begins to form, her attitude suddenly changes once she learns that he has run away from home!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.02.Summary">Adventurer Cookie claims that he\'s being chased. But by whom? Sachertorte Cookie asks the name of his so-called pursuer. Just what is she planning?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Title.03.Summary">Sachertorte Cookie has leaked the current location of Adventurer Cookie to... Blackberry Cookie?! She looks upon the pair with a faint but warm smile while she reminisces on an old memory.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.Main">Not the Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.01">You Want WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.02">Again, Not the Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.03">Definitely Not the Snow Sugar Wand</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.01.Summary">Wizard Cookie has been asked to inspect a strange igloo in Snow Sugar Cookie\'s room. Snow Sugar Cookie offers some snacks as thanks, but Wizard Cookie makes a counter-offer—the chance to study the Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.02.Summary">Upon hearing the counter-offer, Snow Sugar Cookie believes that Wizard Cookie is attempting to steal the wand. Snow Sugar Cookie summons the Snow King to fend off Wizard Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Title.03.Summary">Wizard Cookie, flabbergasted at the idea that he wants to steal the Snow Sugar Wand, fails to convince his host that he\'s not trying to pilfer it, but things go awry once more!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest1">Where the Light Sleeps</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest2">Rising like the Sun</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest3">Eyes of Radiance</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest4">Allow Me to Aid You</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest5">May Every Step be Blessed by Light</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.Title">Reverence and Duty</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest1.Summary">All the residents of Mount St. Crème believe that the region\'s chilled, dry environment, where everyone remains eternally fresh, is thanks to the presence of this mysterious, slumbering Cookie. A few youngsters have snuck into the chamber to get a glimpse of this radiant Cookie, only to run into a stern-faced Onyx Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest2.Summary">Where did she come from? Who is she? What is her name? Onyx Cream Cookie ponders these thoughts to himself... only to see that she has woken up...!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest3.Summary">First Cream Cookie has awakened, but with no memories. Nevertheless, her presence alone is enough to win the hearts of all the residents of Mount St. Crème.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest4.Summary">Onyx Cream Cookie trains diligently, day and night, in order to be of aid to First Cream Cookie. Though all is peaceful, he continues to train in preparation for the worst.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.09.SQuest5.Summary">Onyx Cream Cookie is shocked to find out that First Cream Cookie is planning to leave Mount St. Crème. She promises that she will return... but asks him for a promise as well.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Illust.Dialog.01">WALKING PLANT!
GURAAAGH!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0013.Illust.Dialog.02">Oh dear...
Why is Zombie Cookie
running away from me?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Illust.Dialog.01">Hmmm, no. I really think
cocoa is the way to go!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0111.Illust.Dialog.02">Oh dear. This will be
quite a difficult evening...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Illust.Dialog.01">Thank you.
I hope our paths
cross again some day.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2003.Illust.Dialog.02">Do be careful, dear.
As for you, Adventurer Cookie,
you really must learn to grow up!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Illust.Dialog.01">I would very much appreciate
the opportunity to inspect
your Snow Sugar Wand!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0030.Illust.Dialog.02">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.09">Fresh and Divine Radiance</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.09.Story">The name of the Cookie that everyone has grown to love and revere has been revealed to be First Cream Cookie! All the residents of Mount St. Crème rejoiced when she finally
woke up from her deep slumber.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0001.Monologue.Greeting">Hey there, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Let\'s do something awesome and fun!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0002.Monologue.Greeting">Hi, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;...
Do you want to play a game with me...?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0003.Monologue.Greeting">Meeting you has made
my day even brighter, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0012.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;...
I have been waiting for you.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0013.Monologue.Greeting">Gruuugh... 
&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;... Grah...?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0023.Monologue.Greeting">PSSST! Hey, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Wanna pull a prank on someone?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0025.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
You are very much welcome here, my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0028.Monologue.Greeting">Hiya, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Wanna throw some cherry bombs with me?!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0030.Monologue.Greeting">It\'s nice to meet you, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
Will you be my friend?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0034.Monologue.Greeting">Oh, I was just about to get some air!
Wanna come with me, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0035.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;?
You\'re here, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0037.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
I have the most wonderful idea for a party!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0038.Monologue.Greeting">I was just getting bored, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Wanna go on an adventure?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0042.Monologue.Greeting">Welcome, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0044.Monologue.Greeting">Stay back, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;...
I don\'t want to hurt you.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0045.Monologue.Greeting">Hello, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
I\'ve got a cup of cocoa with your name on it!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0046.Monologue.Greeting">Ah, welcome, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
Would you like to hear my latest composition?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0058.Monologue.Greeting">WAAAH! Who... Who\'s there...?
Oh, is that you, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0063.Monologue.Greeting">Hello there! The weather\'s so
nice today, isn\'t it, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0111.Monologue.Greeting">Ah! I\'ve been waiting for you,
&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0113.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
You\'re here to listen to one of my jokes, riiight? HAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0157.Monologue.Greeting">Greetings, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
It\'s so very nice to meet you.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0518.Monologue.Greeting">OH, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Wanna see my latest Wafflebot?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2001.Monologue.Greeting">Salutations and welcome, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
You have been missed very much.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2002.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
Pleased to make your acquaintance.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2003.Monologue.Greeting">What\'s that? You\'ve missed me, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;?
How amusing.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2004.Monologue.Greeting">Just in time, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
We\'ve got another faucet to fix!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2005.Monologue.Greeting">Hello, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
How have you fared?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2006.Monologue.Greeting">MYAHAHA! Lookie, lookie!
It\'s &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Wanna cause a ruckus like usual?!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2007.Monologue.Greeting">Salutations, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
Please, make yourself comfortable.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Greeting">... Oh, it\'s you, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
We\'ve been waiting.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Greeting">WOOOW! It\'s you!!! &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!!!
You\'re SO cool!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0013">Zombie Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.2003">Sachertorte Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0111">Sparkling Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0013.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy with a design capturing the characteristics of Zombie Cookie perfectly. Some say that it was made with authentic zombified dough.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.2003.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Sachertorte Cookie. This toy undeniably gives off an aura of sophistication and elegance that is hard to ignore.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RandomBox.JellyBear.0111.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that captures the handsome and charming nature of Sparkling Cookie. Its smile is so heartwarming that you feel like you\'re genuinely being welcomed with the cheeriest of greetings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_1">When have I last
set foot in this chamber?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_2">Every time I am here...
it\'s almost as if you\'re...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_3">You\'re here with me, Mistress...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_4">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_5">What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0010_1">... find...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Npc.0010_2">Find the small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_6">Mistress...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_7">It\'s clear that my choice
to return is warranted...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_8">But this feeling of unease is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_9">Are you there,
Snow Crystal Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2008_1">Yes, First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_10">Onyx Cream Cookie
mentioned the frozen lands...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_11">And a sighting of a
\"small Cookie\" in the area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2008_2">Yes, a very small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_12">Could it be...
the Cookie I\'ve been seeking?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_13">But something\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_14">wrong.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_15">Snow Crystal Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_16">I must find the small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_17">I will return soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_18">In the meantime, please
keep watch over this place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2001_19">None are to step foot in this
chamber during my absence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH2_SQ8_CUT1_Cookie.2008_3">Yes!
Of course, My Lady.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_1">Hey! Do you hear that? Someone\'s crying! Is it a ghost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">There\'s no such thing as ghosts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">You don\'t sound so confident, hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Well, I mean, they might... or not...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_1">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Someone\'s really crying though! And loudly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">There\'s a high chance that it\'s REALLY not a ghost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Erm... Hello? Are you okay? Why are you crying?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_2">*Sniffle, GASP*
INTRUDERS! INTRUDERS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_3">Don\'t move a muscle! I won\'t let you go any further! RAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Not to be rude, but I don\'t think you can really stop us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Are you sure you\'re okay? You look like you\'re frozen in place, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_4">S-s-stop making fun of me...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_1">Now I remember... You\'re Salty Cream Yeti, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_5">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_6">*GASP*
ONYX CREAM COOKIE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_2">Why are you stuck here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_7">AHEM! I\'ll have you know, I am NOT stuck.
*Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">But... you are...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_8">OKAY! I\'M STUUUCK...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_9">I was crying because I was so sad to see Mount St. Crème change like this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_10">And before I knew it, my tears had frozen solid and... and... I got myself stuck!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0056_11">BWAAAHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">Sounds like we have another job to do, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">You read my mind, GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_3">Wait...! Stop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_4">You\'re...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_4">Who are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_5">No, never mind. I don\'t really care who you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_6">Go away, outsiders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">But we just got here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Er, pardon me, but we must gain entry to the secret hollow. We\'re trying to repair this compass of ours.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">We didn\'t know this place was being guarded...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Maybe if we ask nicely...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">The mere fact you\'re here is suspicious enough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_8">Take one more step and you\'ll find out just how unwelcome you really are...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_5">Stop! Wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_6">Snow Crystal Cookie! It\'s you, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_9">Hm...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_7">It\'s me, Onyx Cream Cookie! Don\'t you recognize me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_8">I... I admit, it\'s been such a long time since we\'ve last met...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_9">I have suffered many trials and tribulations... and it seems you have experienced the same.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_10">You were always a stern one... Has time frozen your heart even further?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_10">Onyx Cream Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">You...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_12">Where have you been all this time, you sack of rancid milk?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Uh-oh! She sounds really angry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Wait, wait! Calm down, the two of you should talk-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_13">YOU KEEP YOUR TRAP SHUT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_11">Just hear me out, Snow Crystal Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_12">Repairing the temperature controller took much, much longer than expected! And I dared not return until it was fully functional once more...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_13">While I was out there... I was... I am... infected.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_14">YOU... WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2007_14">But these Cookies here! They helped repair the controller and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0056_12">Heeeeeey...! Sorry to interrupt but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0056_13">Can you continue the shouting match AFTER getting me out of this mess?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_15">Madam First Cream Cookie ordered me to keep outsiders away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_16">You may be outsiders... But since you\'ve met First Cream Cookie, I\'ll go easy on you for now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_14">Thank you! Thank you for freeing me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_15">Ahem! I am the guardian of this ancient hollow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_16">First Cream Cookie asked me to keep this place safe and secret! And I was, until I got stuck...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">But... but you just said you weren\'t stuck.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2007_15">You...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_17">... Hmph.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_17">Wowy, I haven\'t been in here for so looong!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_18">Let\'s get straight to it then. You want to fix that compass, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_19">Then go ahead and take a look! There should be something you can-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_18">Zip it, Salty Cream Yeti.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_20">Aw...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_19">Don\'t go moseying around and touching everything you see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">How\'re we gonna find what we need?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Hm, I think it\'d be wise for us to listen to Snow Crystal Cookie\'s warning...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">There\'s something in the air here... Something mystical, ominous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2007_16">It\'s said that everything in here once belonged to the witch... ages ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2007_17">Perhaps that is what your keen senses are detecting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">The witch, eh? I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Hey, check out this lump of dough! It looks pretty cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Do you think there might be something inside?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">... Yes, it may merit further investigation...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Wizard Cookie...! We don\'t even know what that thing is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">I know, but it can\'t hurt to check and see, right...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2007_18">Why don\'t you take out the compass first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">Oh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">The compass is glowing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Er, is it supposed be shaking like that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">Hold it steady! Don\'t let go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_20">It seems that this compass is fueled by magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Is that what\'s happening right now?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">It\'s... It\'s broken! The compass is totally broken!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">Ugh... I wanted to take a look at that room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Maybe I\'ll slip out to take a closer look later...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">What made the compass go crazy like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">I dunno... But it looks like we\'ll never get to use it again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_7">Marble Danish Cookie is going to be sad... We should apologize to him when we see him next time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">I have a theory as to why it\'s broken beyond repair.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">The hollow was saturated with strong, ancient magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">Exposing the compass to such raw power was too much for it to handle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">The compass may be gone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">But at least Snow Crystal Cookie got a good look at where it was pointing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">So I guess... that\'s where we\'re headed then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_8">And now we definitely know where it was pointing...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">It\'s leading us towards the icy prison for sure...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">And Salty Cream Yeti was so kind to offer help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_9">Since he\'s protecting the ancient hollow, Snow Crystal Cookie can join us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">And now we\'re here, all together! Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_21">Pipe down... We need to take caution from here on out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_22">Onyx Cream Cookie, you remember the sodas, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2007_19">Faintly. They slowly made their move as soon as the winds changed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2007_20">Making their way to the frozen lands, biding their time and gathering strength.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_23">Yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_24">The scoundrels do not wish for Madam First Cream Cookie\'s glorious return.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_25">And they will do everything in their power to keep our home from regaining its former glory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_26">The selfish fiends only care for themselves and that accursed, frozen prison.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_27">Forcefully bulking up their physical bodies with ice, becoming monstrous in size.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">But why...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">Why are they doing all of this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_28">Hmph...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_29">If you want an answer to that question,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_30">take a closer look here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">What\'s all this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_13">And why do these things look so familiar...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Hey! These things are-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Quiet! They\'ll hear us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">Whoops, sorry...! But seriously, look at this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">Hey, do these remind you of Sheriff Whiskerton\'s badges?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">They do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">And... I saw something like that back at the Syrup Garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">For a split second, I was reminded of the Reaper just now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">Why is all this stuff here with the sodas?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_31">Don\'t think too hard. Put two and two together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Does this mean...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">The minions of the witch! The ones that want to kidnap Cookies...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">They\'re here too? In Mount St. Crème?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_32">Minions of the witch would make regular visits here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_33">But they never stayed, as they don\'t call this place home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_34">The items you saw were given by the witch\'s minions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_35">Given to the ones who sold their souls to the witch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_36">Ones who used to call this place their home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2007_21">Then that means... the cabal of sodas...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_37">Exactly. They will do anything to keep themselves off the witch\'s table.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_38">The more they gather strength, the less likely they are to be sacrificed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_39">And as long as they can maintain their strength, and control of the prison...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_40">They will be entrusted by the witch\'s forces to keep a watchful eye on every prisoner within.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_41">Or should I say, every sacrifice to the witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_42">Within that icy prison...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_43">You will find your small Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_22">We should hurry...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_16">All the things
the Reaper said...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_17">Everything was true...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_18">The perpetual frost...
the witch\'s dining table...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0002_19">B-B-Becoming snacks and supper...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0003_13">I hope GingerDozer\'s okay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_20">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_21">Ice and frost,
everywhere...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_22">And yet,
I feel that I am close...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_23">Over there!
Is that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2008_44">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2007_22">You felt it too,
didn\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2007_23">There\'s something
over there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0003_14">Is it GingerDozer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_23">Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0025_18">Goodness....!
This prison is massive!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">Over there!
Is that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_24">My Mistress...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_25">I finally...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2001_26">Found... you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.0001_24">Found... you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ6_CUT1_Cookie.2010_1">Not today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_25">GingerDozer!
Wake up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_16">It\'s us, GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_26">C\'mon, buddy!
Wake up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_24">Stand back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_25">I will create a path of entry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_27">... Are you okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0002_20">Is something...
wrong with him?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0025_19">Hm... It\'s as if he can\'t
hear us at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0003_17">What do we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_26">May I take a look?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_27">So this is the Cookie
you sought...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_28">Snow Crystal Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2007_29">The small Cookie you saw long ago,
this isn\'t the one, is he?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_45">No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_46">I\'ve never seen this Cookie before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_47">This isn\'t the one Madam
First Cream Cookie was searching for.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_27">Found... you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_2">Not today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_28">Ah...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_29">I know of the one I seek,
but you... Who are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_3">First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_4">Why do you seek
this small Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_5">Do you even remember
their name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_30">It\'s... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_6">I will be taking this one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_7">As for you, try to remember</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_8">who we really are, if you dare.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_9">Remember all of us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_10">Until then,
fare thee well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_31">Wait!
No, please!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_32">Do not take them away...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2001_33">Nooo...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_28">Nooo...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.0001_29">He\'s not stale, is he?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_48">I doubt it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_49">It looks like he\'s been
chilled for too-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0057_1">Grrrufff!
Lookie here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0057_2">Unwanted pests!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0057_3">Grrr...
And they\'re playing with our food!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_50">Drat!
We\'ve been made...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2008_51">It\'s the cabal\'s ringleader,
Cokeberus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0057_4">This\'ll be your new home now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ7_CUT1_Npc.0057_5">You rotten little crumbwalkers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2007_30">You are no match for my blade!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_52">Wait! Cokeberus can\'t be defeated by normal means.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">Any ideas?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_53">He has a voracious appetite for sweet treats.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_54">And rumor has it, Cokeberus always falls asleep if he has a full belly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">Oooh! So all we have to do is give treats to the cute puppy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_21">Cute?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">C\'mere, cute puppy! We\'ve got treatsies!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0057_6">OOOH! A MUFFIN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0057_7">Nom, nom!
Yummy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY1_Npc.0057_8">Noooice...
Zzzzzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.2007_31">He\'s fallen asleep.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR2_Cookie.0003_20">We need more treats!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_9">Grrr...oh? Pudding!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_10">No, no... YES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_11">That\'s tasty...
Zzzzzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_12">Hur hur, ya thirsty?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_13">Let\'s quench that thirst!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Cookie.0025_20">Gah?! No, thank you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Cookie.2008_55">That mangey mutt...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_14">Grrr... Pudding...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY2_Npc.0057_15">Fresh Cookies...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0001_31">C\'mon, we can\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_POR3_Cookie.0003_21">Bad puppy! Bad, bad puppy!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_16">Rrrreally tasty!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_17">SO YUMMY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_18">Treats are... the best...
Zzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_19">Need... sleep...
Zzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_20">NO! Need to wake up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_21">You crumbly pests!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Cookie.0001_32">He\'s falling asleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Cookie.0002_22">We need more treats...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_22">So... full... and sleepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_23">I will squash you all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_24">Face our wrath!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_PLAY3_Npc.0057_25">HARHAR!
Pathetic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Npc.0057_26">Zzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0003_22">He\'s fallen asleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0001_33">Hooray! We did it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_34">Cokeberus is sleeping heavier than GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_CutOG_AfterEP4CH3BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_23">And it\'s time for us to wake GingerDozer up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">I think it\'s going to take something more to wake him up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">Should we take him somewhere warm? Would that work?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ8_POR1_Cookie.2001_34">May I have a look at him?</string>
