  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2008.003">Broken Hairpin</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2008.001.Story">An exquisite set of arrows crafted from the purest and clearest ice. Though fragile, Snow Crystal Cookie prefers these arrows due to their inconspicuous appearance. According to her, they are perfectly suitable for delivering a stern warning without firing a shot.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2008.002.Story">A brooch gifted by a certain Cookie who urged Snow Crystal Cookie to fasten her coat and keep warm. The cold never bothered her in the first place, but she seems to wear it at all times for sentimental reasons.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2008.003.Story">A hairpin that resembles a broken frost arrow. It holds Snow Crystal Cookie\'s hair firmly in place, making it an essential accessory for an archer such as herself!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Story">This Cookie was baked with a single snowflake perched atop a leaf from the witch\'s garden. Snow Crystal Cookie\'s eyes are as clear and serene as the dawn air, which help her keep watch for intruders and never miss her target.

The residents of Mount St. Crème admire her, but they often shrink back from her chilly demeanor. However, one Cookie, as bright and lively as a rainbow, is unfazed by Snow Crystal Cookie\'s frigid personality.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.IceCrystal.Limited.Floor.001">Snow Crystal Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.IceCrystal.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Snow Crystal Cookie, especially her cold gaze and icy demeanor.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Snow Crystal Cookie\'s soul. Holding it in your hands, you\'re reminded of snow gently falling on a dark, silent night.</string>
