  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.001.Story">The leftovers of a drink made with fresh fruit, sweeteners, and carbonated water. It looks like someone has quenched a rather strong thirst and left the fruit untouched...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.002.Story">A storage shelf made from recycled aluminum cans. Something\'s oddly familiar about the items being stored within...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.003.Story">An ice pack that has been confiscated from those who need it. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.004.Story">A simple, yet very large, straw. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.005.Story">A pile of old bottle caps, haphazardly stacked together. Anyone would love to have some of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.006.Story">A rather odd attempt to make a chair with broken glass and a bottle cap. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.007.Story">A sofa made from broken glass. At least the cushion seems soft... and safe. What an interesting find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Floor.008.Story">A shard of broken glass. Try decorating the room with it, carefully.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Wall.001.Story">One of the largest bottle caps ever seen! Anyone would love to have one of these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Ceil.001.Story">Recycled bottle caps tied together to make a set of lights. What an ingenious idea!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Ceil.002.Story">A hanging lamp made from a piece of shattered glass. This will look great wherever you decide to put it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.WP.001.Story">This vending machine gives off a dim and eerie glow. Try decorating the wall with this.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.FrozenSodaHideout.Deck.001.Story">Some sort of carbonated drink has been frozen to make a solid floor. Watch your step because there\'s ice sticking out of it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.001.Story">Ice crystals are usually beautiful, but they\'re rather intimidating in this case. This prison cell\'s bars are so sturdy, there\'s no way to escape without help from the outside.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.002.Story">A bottle of soda that has burst open due to the cold temperature. It goes well wherever you place it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.003.Story">A collection of ice cream cones that have been frozen solid. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.004.Story">The leftovers of a spiny fish. Does it serve a purpose...?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.005.Story">An ice candle that gives off a bluish glow. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Floor.006.Story">A piece of frozen candy that has grown ice spikes as sharp as knives. It goes well wherever you place it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Ceil.001.Story">A cage hanging from the ceiling. It serves its purpose a bit too well.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Ceil.002.Story">A collection of collars worn by Cokeberus. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Ceil.003.Story">An intimidating looking flail chain. Try placing it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Hanger.001.Story">This spiderweb has become frozen solid. It goes well wherever you place it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.WP.001.Story">A wall made from various foodstuffs that have been frozen over the years. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.IceJail.Deck.001.Story">A slippery floor made from solid ice. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Snow Crystal Cookie\'s Room of Frigid Solitude!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Get">You called?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Random.01">The cold never bothered me.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Random.02">The frost messes
with my aim...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Random.03">My eyes are as sharp as ever.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Random.04">I don\'t like
commotions.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.Random.05">Don\'t test your curiosity.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Monologue.LifeZero.01">I just need to
catch my breath.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2008.Skill.Name">Rain of Frost Arrows</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0119.Season">Salty Cream Fox</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0120.Season">Lemon Cream Fox</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0121.Season">Strawberry Cream Fox</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0122.Season">Shaved Ice Turtle</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0123.Season">Mango Ice Turtle</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0124.Season">Strawberry Ice Turtle</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0119.Season.Story">Salty Cream Foxes are easily recognized by their dense, firm fur. Their manes, in particular, are sturdy enough to remain intact even after a powerful sneeze. It\'s no wonder they take great pride in their coats.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0120.Season.Story">The fur of a Lemon Cream Fox has a rather tart and tangy aroma with a hint of sweet syrup. These foxes can often be found wrinkling their noses, as their cream fur is potentially too tart, even for themselves!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0121.Season.Story">The Strawberry Cream Fox covers itself in layers of strawberry cream and is friendly to all other breeds of foxes, from kits to adults. Strawberry Cream Foxes often sway their tails in a cheerful manner to win more friends.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0122.Season.Story">A wise Shaved Ice Turtle. They seem familiar somehow...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0123.Season.Story">A clever Mango Ice Turtle. Hopefully you\'ll get along!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0124.Season.Story">A prudent Strawberry Ice Turtle. Such an amazing friend!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2008">Snow Crystal Cookie\'s Room of Frigid Solitude</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2008.Story">It\'s clear that Snow Crystal Cookie\'s room was always chilly, even before unwanted frost and moisture fell upon Mount St. Crème. Her room is so quiet, you can almost hear the ice slowly freezing. This room is perfect for clearing your mind of worries and concern.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Special.SecretChamber">Secret Hollow</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.06">Frozen Sodas\' Hideout</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.07">Icy Prison</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep02.Special.01.Story">This ancient hollow, suffused with a mysterious light, contains traces of a certain witch who clearly baked many Cookies in the castle a long, long time ago. What sort of Cookies was this witch planning to bake with the leftover dough? But the bigger mystery is... where did the witch disappear to after preparing all these ingredients?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.06.Story">The nefarious gang of sodas keeps a stern eye on their captives within the icy prison. Within this small hideout of theirs, there are traces of the fearsome minions of the witch that GingerBrave and friends have encountered throughout the castle! Why is all this stuff here? What is going on?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.07.Story">The glittering shards of ice and clusters of frost seem beautiful until you realize this entire frozen complex is a massive prison! It\'s said that the witch\'s minions imprison their captives here until they are ready to be sacrificed to the witch\'s table... But not anymore!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Season.2008">Snow Crystal</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.2008">Snow Crystal Season Coins</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SeasonComplete.2008">Completed Snow Crystal Collection</string>
  <string name="$Season.2008.Complete.Profile">Completed Snow Crystal Collection</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep04.SecretChamber001.Title">Ancient Dough</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep04.SecretChamber001.Info">This mysterious lump of dough has been placed in the very center of the secret hollow. It is safe to assume that it was prepared for baking, but ultimately forgotten and too frozen to be useful. One question remains unanswered: who prepared this dough and why?</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep04.SecretChamber002.Info">Hey!
I might fit perfectly in that!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep04.SecretChamber003.Info">This doesn\'t seem like
ordinary flour...!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialRoom.Ep04.SecretChamber004.Info">Do you think this stuff can
be used to fix the compass?</string>
  <string name="$UX.Continue.Tutorial.01">Myah, what a shame!
But no need to feel sad!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Continue.Tutorial.02">There\'s always a way forward!
Tap the glowing button!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Continue.Tutorial.03">Don\'t forget...!
&lt;color=#337AFF&gt;Crystals&lt;/color&gt; are super important!
I got ya covered this time!</string>
