  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.01">Running Away is Awesome!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.02">Kindness is Bad!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.03">Revenge Will Be Mine!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.Main">Hoping to be Friendlier</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.01">Snow Crystal Cookie\'s Woes</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.02">Problem Solved?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.03">Problem Unsolved...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Illust.Dialog.01">RUN FOR IT!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Illust.Dialog.02">They\'re gone.
Perhaps they were too shy.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Illust.Dialog.01">Grrr...! I won\'t forgive you two!
I will have my revenge!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0157.Illust.Dialog.01">I know how to make your
bed spin just like a
real merry-go-round!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0157.Illust.Dialog.02">I... pardon...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_1">Thank you for coming all this way, Strawberry Crepe Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_2">WOW! I\'ve never seen a room like this before! Is that a real merry-go-round?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_3">Oh, sorry to disappoint you, but it\'s just a bed that looks like a merry-go-round.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_4">Eh? So it\'s just a boring piece of furniture that doesn\'t do anything?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_5">Well, yes, but it\'s shiny like the starry night sky...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_6">It\'s a happy room, just like an amusement park. Now, you said you wanted to share memories about-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_7">Hmmm... Maybe a simple rotation spell? The axis might be able to absorb mana and... Yeah, with enough centrifugal force it might work?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_8">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_9">Linear motion...? How much horsepower can it crank out after absorbing mana...? Or could it function on the same principles as my Wafflebots...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_10">Erm... Strawberry Crepe Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_11">Yeah, yeah! I can see it now...! It\'d definitely work!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0518_12">CREAM UNICORN COOKIE! I know how to make your bed spin just like a real merry-go-round!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_1_POR1_Cookie0157_13">I... pardon...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_1">At first glance, I thought it\'d be impossible to make your bed spin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_2">But thinking about it in terms of pure magichanical engineering was only limiting my approach! You get what I mean, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0157_3">Magichanical... engineering...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_4">I needed to think about it in an entirely different way! And that\'s when it hit me...! What if the design incorporated a little dessert magic?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Hear me out. If we add more sweetness to this bedpost here, it\'d be able to safely house all the mana-infused circuitry, which\'ll be needed to make it spin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0157_6">Circuitry...???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_7">Trust me! In principle, it\'s a similar design to my Wafflebots. And it\'s- Hey, what\'s with that face? Are you doing some calculations in your head?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0157_8">Erm... Strawberry Crepe Cookie? I thought you wanted to talk about memories...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_9">Yeah, yeah. But let\'s see if my theory for this new design works out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0518_10">If I\'m right, and I always am, this bed will spin like a real merry-go-round!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_2_POR1_Cookie0157_11">But... but it\'s MY bed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_1">The mana-infused circuitry is securely in place, and we\'re ready for the next step!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_2">Hey, Cream Unicorn Cookie? Do me a favor and press that green button on the control panel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_3">Hey! This isn\'t the time for a nap! We\'ve still got a lot of work to do!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_4">Pffft... Fine, I\'ll do it myself! All I need to do is press this button and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_5">HAHA! It works! It\'s spinning like a real merry-go-round!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_6">I knew it\'d work!
... It\'s a shame no one else is seeing this right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0518_7">Cream Unicorn Cookie!!!
Wake up! Why\'re you sleeping? You gotta see this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0157_8">Oh, Strawberry Crepe Cookie...
Why am I sleeping, you ask...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0157_9">Because all I see in my dreams are beautiful butterflies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0157_3_POR1_Cookie0157_10">It\'s a world without magichanical engineering... or circuits... or headaches...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_1">Look at all this stuff!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_2">So all this junk is the reason why you\'re running away from home?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0038_3">It\'s not running away, it\'s exploration and adventuring!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_4">Hehe, works for me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_5">Running away from home is bad, which means Adventurer Cookie is bad too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_6">Hehehe! He\'s my kind of Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_7">But... there\'s something weird about this room...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_8">What\'s this vibe I\'m feeling?
Is that... kindness?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_9">HEY! Adventurer Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0038_10">What\'s up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0023_11">These things here... How\'d you get your hands on them?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_1_POR1_Cookie0038_12">Good question! I\'ll tell you all about\'em!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_1">That\'s how the sphinx and I became best friends, and I was given this door as a gift!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_2">... Uh-oh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_3">This trap was given to me as a reward for ending a feud between two villages.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_4">They said they didn\'t need it anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_5">Adventurer Cookie is... nice?! Almost too nice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_6">And say hello to the Cheesebirds! I helped mend their injured wings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_7">They then followed me all the way home and made their nest here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_8">OH! This stone pillar is really special and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_9">Stop! STOP! STAAAHP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_10">Huh? Is something wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_11">Now that I think about it, you look a bit ill...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_12">Are you sick?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_13">No! Get away from me! I\'m leaving!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0038_14">Devil Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_15">No... no...! All that kindness...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_2_POR1_Cookie0023_16">I can\'t stand it!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_1">Eugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0038_2">Devil Cookie! Wake up!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_3">Urgh... What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0038_4">Oh no, looks like Devil Cookie\'s still groggy...
C\'mon, snap out of it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0012_5">Do not worry...
I am here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_6">That annoying voice is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_7">ANGEL COOKIE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0038_8">That was amazing, Angel Cookie!
You just walked in the room and suddenly Devil Cookie\'s cured!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0012_9">I am glad I could help... but we can\'t relax just yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0012_10">I will stay a bit longer and keep watch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_11">What?! NO THANKS!
I\'m getting outta here!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0038_12">Devil Cookie, stop! You need to lie down and rest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0012_13">Yes... rest...
Stay still...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_14">Huh...?! What\'s happening? I can\'t... move!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_15">This can\'t be happening!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0038_3_POR1_Cookie0023_16">Grrr...! I won\'t forgive you two!
I will have my revenge!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_1">So... you\'re worried that the other residents are scared of you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2008_2">Yes.
It\'s obvious they are afraid of me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_3">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_4">You usually stick around with the other Cookie, not me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2008_5">... Jealous?
Do you wish for us to be friends?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_6">... No, no. What I meant to say is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_7">The other Cookie is much more likely to provide more heartwarming advice than myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2008_8">Always busy, that one...
And very popular too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2008_9">And besides. You tend to be quite friendly with the other residents too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2008_10">Tell me... How do you do it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_11">How...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_1_POR1_Cookie2007_12">Hmmm... One thing comes to mind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_1">You are usually behind Madam First Cream Cookie, carrying out her orders and requests.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_2">You do not step forward into the light, hence the residents are unfamiliar with whom you really are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2008_3">So what you\'re saying is... I should interact with them more often?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_4">Yes. And you aren\'t the easiest Cookie to approach.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2008_5">Maybe I should smile and laugh more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_6">Correct. You should also try to appear majestic and helpful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2008_7">For example...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_8">Reach out to the residents first, especially to those who are in need of aid.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_9">Try doing what you are best at when it\'s needed most.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2008_10">Hm...
I think I understand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2007_11">Shall we put it to test?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_2_POR1_Cookie2008_12">Very well. I shall try it immediately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0040_1">My donut balloon is stuck in a tree...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0039_2">It\'s all Cream Cake\'s fault!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0040_3">My life is ruined... I will no longer be able to experience joy and happiness from this moment forward...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0041_4">Huh? That\'s a bit over-the-top, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_5">There is a resident who looks troubled.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_6">Onyx Cream Cookie said I should help residents in need...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_7">Yes... I just need to retrieve that balloon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_8">If I can hit the branch with an arrow, the string may become untangled.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0039_9">EEEK! An arrow came out of nowhere?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0041_10">What\'s happening?! Are we under attack?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0040_11">I... I think... I think that Cookie shot at us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_12">Everyone is looking at me now. Perhaps this is the perfect time to attempt a smile.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_13">Am I doing it? Is this what they call... smiling?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0040_14">What\'s with the creepy smile?!
Is... is she out to get us? Are we targets???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0041_15">Wait for me! Don\'t leave me heeere!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Npc0039_16">RUN FOR IT!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_17">Hm? What just happened...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_18">They\'re gone. Perhaps they were too shy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2008_3_POR1_Cookie2008_19">Although, I feel proud of myself for doing a good a deed. I should tell that Cookie about what happened.</string>
