  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.09">Warden of the Icy Prison, Cokeberus</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.10">GingerDozer &amp; the Prison</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.09.Story">The fearsome warden, Cokeberus, rules the icy prison with an iron paw! Rumor has it they fall asleep after eating snacks, but is this really the time to put it to the test?!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.10.Story">We found GingerDozer! Is he deep asleep?! Why isn\'t he waking up...?</string>
