  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.008.Story">A fluffy cotton chair. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Wall.004.Story">A small window shaped like a snowflake. Looking at it makes you feel calm.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.007.Story">A quiver for frost arrows. It\'s no wonder who this belongs to!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.006.Story">A giant beanbag made from the softest shaved ice. Anyone would love to have these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.003.Story">This fencing was crafted from sturdy ice crystals. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Wall.002.Story">A mount to store a bow. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Ceil.003.Story">A decorative branch of cotton. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Ceil.002.Story">A wind chime made from delicate ice. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Wall.003.Story">A shelf for storing many, many arrows. It serves its purpose very well!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.002.Story">This diffuser fills Snow Crystal Cookie\'s room with a gentle aroma. It almost makes you mistakenly feel something similar to warmth.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Wall.001.Story">You feel as if you\'re looking upon a beautiful painting when snow falls outside this snowflake engraved window. One could gaze out this window forever.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.004.Story">A table designed so that you can enjoy the view outside no matter where you sit. The tablecloth, which resembles flower petals, matches perfectly.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Ceil.001.Story">Designed in the shape of crystallized ice, this cozy spot is not only pretty but also spacious!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.005.Story">This cotton stool appears soft and fluffy, but it\'s surprisingly firm, allowing one to sit upright with proper posture. It\'s well-maintained to be neat and tidy, just how Snow Crystal Cookie likes things to be.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.WP.001.Story">When gazing at this wallpaper, many are reminded of silent winter nights where the only audible sound is the gentle piling of snow. Somehow, it makes you feel cool and refreshed even in the summer!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Deck.001.Story">This floor, with its mosaic pattern of different shades of ice, looks like it was made from hundreds of shards of frozen crystals. But don\'t worry, it\'s not slippery at all.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2008.Floor.001.Story">Though Snow Crystal Cookie doesn\'t mind the cold, someone must have wanted to add a touch of warmth and comfort to her room. When sunlight enters through the window, this diffuser blooms and releases a soft fragrance that can warm anyone\'s heart.</string>
