  <string name="$Script.Storyguide.SG_EP1_CH1_Q7_8_9">Okay! It should melt away now, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script.Storyguide.SG_EP1_CH1_Q14">Let\'s check out another wall too!</string>
  <string name="$Script.Storyguide.SG_EP1_CH1_Q17_18_19">What\'ll we find this time?</string>
  <string name="$Script.Storyguide.SG_EP1_CH1_Q21_22_23_24">Now we can find out what that noise is!</string>
  <string name="$Interactionguide_EP4_CH3_SQ2_INT1_01">Tap the ice to free Salty Cream Yeti!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0118">Salty Cream Yeti</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch02.SQuest08.Summary">Upon entering the secret hollow, First Cream Cookie receives a vision of the Witch of Light. She must find \"the small Cookie\"!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest01.Summary">GingerBrave and friends hear someone crying... The source is none other than Salty Cream Yeti, who claims they were crying out of sadness for Mount St. Crème\'s collapse.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest02.Summary">Believing the group to be intruders, Snow Crystal Cookie fires an arrow to ward them off! But thanks to Onyx Cream Cookie, the arrow is safely deflected. Interestingly, it seems these two know each other!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest03.Summary">The Cookies enter the hollow, hoping to repair the compass, but the unexpected happens! The mysterious energy within the chamber affects the compass, causing it to shine with a bright, blinding light.</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest04.Summary">The team manages to sneak into hostile territory, and they finally learn why the cabal of frozen sodas do not want Mount St. Crème to return to its former glory. Better tread carefully!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest05.Summary">The icy prison holds captives who will soon join the witch\'s table! GingerDozer is somewhere inside...!!! We have to find him before it\'s too late!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest06.Summary">GingerBrave and friends hurriedly rush deeper into the prison, as does First Cream Cookie. They finally discover the one they\'ve been seeking!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest07.Summary">It\'s GingerDozer! But he\'s not waking up? To make matters worse, the warden of the prison, Cokeberus, has appeared! And a mysterious Cookie has kidnapped the small Cookie away, right in front of First Cream Cookie\'s eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest08.Summary">Appearing before GingerBrave and friends is... First Cream Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.01.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie has paid Cream Unicorn Cookie a visit. Things go awry when Strawberry Crepe Cookie discovers a bed in the shape of a merry-go-round that doesn\'t spin!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.02.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie is excited to start a new magichanical engineering project. No one can stop this tinkering genius, not even the owner of the bed!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0038.Title.03.Summary">The upgrades to the merry-go-round bed are complete! Strawberry Crepe Cookie watches it spin, but Cream Unicorn Cookie is napping away the troubles in dreamland...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0157.Title.01.Summary">Running away from home to embark on a new adventure? It happens all the time! Devil Cookie admires Adventurer Cookie\'s daring and renegade attitude. But there\'s something else...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0157.Title.02.Summary">It turns out Adventurer Cookie is one of the nicest Cookies living in the castle! Devil Cookie, shocked by this discovery, faints with disappoints.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0157.Title.03.Summary">Devil Cookie wakes up to find Angel Cookie standing nearby!!! Being surrounded by such good and kind Cookies is too horrendous... The prankster vows to take revenge on them one day!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.01.Summary">Snow Crystal Cookie is aware that the residents of Mount St. Crème are somewhat intimidated by her. She asks Onyx Cream Cookie for some advice.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.02.Summary">Onyx Cream Cookie encourages Snow Crystal Cookie to interact with the residents and neighbors. Taking his advice to heart, she sets out to test this new approach!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2008.Title.03.Summary">Snow Crystal Cookie has helped the residents the best way she could. She\'s proud of her newest achievement! Alas, she seems unaware that this latest escapade hasn\'t delivered the desired effect...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0118.Season.Profile">Salty Cream Yeti</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0119.Season.Profile">Cream Fox</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0122.Season.Profile">Ice Turtle</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0118.Story">Salty Cream Yeti is one of the most iconic residents of Mount St. Crème, especially known for having a sweet and salty coat of cream fur, and matching personality—affectionate and endearing, but also tearful and sometimes irritating. This adorable yeti really must stop crying though, since adding moisture to an already chilly place will make the frost worse...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">First Cream Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">First Cream Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2007_3">First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2008_4">First Cream Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_5">GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_6">I knew we were
destined to meet again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_7">But I did not expect it
to be so soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">It\'s good to
see you again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_9">It seems you\'ve
fared well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">You\'re really popular,
First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">I had a feeling we\'d see
you here at some point!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0001_12">And like you said,
we found GingerDozer!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0002_13">But no matter what we do...
he won\'t wake up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_14">So this is the
small Cookie, GingerDozer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_15">He is in a
deep slumber...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_16">Fear not, for his life is
not in danger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_17">But we cannot
wake him here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_18">We should take him
somewhere safe, to the
Chamber of Freshest Cream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2007_19">My Lady!
How is it that you\'ve...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_20">Since departing Mount St. Crème,
my calling has been made clear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_21">And it has guided me
back here once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_22">Onyx Cream Cookie.
Snow Crystal Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_23">Before my departure,
I sensed the land\'s turmoil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_24">Having felt the winds of
change upon Mount St. Crème,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_25">I left behind my cherished
relic to prevent its downfall.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2008_26">Your relic...
It\'s here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_27">Yes. But it seems that
it was not enough
to save our-</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">GAH!
What was that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.0002_29">It... it sounded like the
temperature controller...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2007_30">It can\'t be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2007_31">Is the temperature controller
malfunctioning again...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_32">Remain calm,
my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_33">I believe the temperature
controller itself is not at fault,
but my relic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_34">If I am correct, the controller
will continue to malfunction,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_35">no matter how many
attempts are made
to repair it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_36">I must retrieve
my relic with haste.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_37">My friends...
I must ask for your aid once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2001_38">Onyx Cream Cookie, Snow Crystal Cookie.
I must ask that you handle the temperature
controller and keep watch over the residents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH3_SQ9_CUT1_Cookie.2007_39">As you command, Your Radiance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">What exactly did you leave behind, First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">I didn\'t want to interrupt earlier... hehe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">Honestly, I\'m curious too... But I\'m going to guess it\'s a powerful, magical artifact of some sort?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_4">It\'s... a relic that holds a portion of my magical essence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_5">It enables me to cast spells of greater magnitude and strength.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_6">This ancient land had always been capable of prolonging freshness for even the ill and spoiled...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_7">But I did not expect it would fall into despair due to my absence...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_8">Upon my previous return to Mount St. Crème, I could not believe my eyes at just how much it had changed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_9">I left a portion of my magical essence within the relic, and yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">When did things start going downhill in the first place...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">An astute question. Despite the artifact\'s presence, it still wasn\'t enough to stave off the spoilage...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">I have an idea of the root cause.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_13">But first, I must retrieve the relic to be sure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">If we find it, can we wake up GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_15">I believe we can.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_16">Not only can we wake him,</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">we may yet be able to restore Mount St. Crème to its former state.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">So we\'ll finally get to see the real Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Eeek! How exciting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">Mount St. Crème back to normal? Waking GingerDozer up? I can\'t handle the excitement!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">C\'mon! Onwards, to the Chamber of Freshest Cream!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">LOOK! There\'s a Cookie trapped in there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">Who could it be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_3">*Gasp*
Rainbow Sherbet Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Oh no! Is that Cookie a friend of yours?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_5">Her name is Rainbow Sherbet Cookie. Her, Snow Crystal Cookie, and Onyx Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_6">The three of them have called Mount St. Crème their home for many moons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Oh! We should get Rainbow Sherbet Cookie out of there!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Waaait! Not so fast.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Those bindings are not made of mere steel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Oh? What if I like, just... tap them to make sure?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">I... don\'t think that\'s a good idea...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie might get hurt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">Oh! You\'re right! Then what should we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Hold on. Let me take a closer look.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">Guh-AAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Wizard Cookie! Be careful!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">Everyone, keep your distance! I advise against making physical contact with these bindings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">But we can\'t just leave...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">Wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_20">Those things over there! They look kind of important...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_21">What if we get rid of them?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_22">Maybe that might do something...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">What a great idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_24">And so smart too! You\'re really cool, Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">Those things definitely do something important...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">I\'ve got it! I know exactly what we need do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Let\'s get to work, everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0001_1">Er, it\'s still moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0003_2">Ugh! It\'s even changed colors!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0025_3">No one said it\'d be easy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_PLAY1_Cookie.0002_4">But... But it IS slowing down a bit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0003_1">The bindings are gone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ1_CUT_CLEAR_Cookie.0001_2">Another job well done, everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_1">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_2">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie. Can you hear me? Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">You\'re not hurt, are you? Can you get up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_4">Wow, First Cream Cookie!
Wait... Am I dreaming? I am, aren\'t I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_5">If so, it\'s a really cool, life-like dream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">I think she\'s a bit confused...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_7">How long has she been sleeping?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Ahem! Greetings, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie. This is NOT a dream!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">We\'re friends with First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_10">*GAAASP*
So this is all... real?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_11">Yes, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">Why were you imprisoned here? Do you remember what happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_13">FIRST CREAM COOKIE...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_14">There was a Cookie from the outside! Someone who didn\'t belong in Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_15">I saw them sneak into the Chamber of Freshest Cream and followed them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_16">A Cookie from the outside... I have an idea of whom you speak.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">First Egg Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">Who\'s that...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Did that Cookie lock you up in here, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_20">I... I think so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_21">That Cookie was frantically looking for something in the Chamber of Freshest Cream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">A thief!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_23">Ah, I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_24">First Egg Cookie was more than likely seeking the relic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">So... your relic was stolen? What do we do now, First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_26">We can\'t restore this area back to normal without it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_27">And... it\'ll be impossible to wake GingerDozer up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2001_28">We are... at an impasse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_29">First Cream Cookie\'s relic?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_30">Oh! You mean...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_1">My Lady, I\'ve remembered everything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_2">The intruder was seeking your sacred relic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_3">I didn\'t know what the Cookie was truly up to...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_4">But I knew that they wanted to sabotage it... or worse!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_5">I had to do something! I had no choice but to charge in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_6">Such a reckless decision...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_7">Hehe...! At least the relic is safe, My Lady!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Whoa! What you did was really cool and brave, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_9">That\'s so awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_10">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_11">I am glad you are safe... But you should have known better.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">Your life may have been in danger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_13">But I... First Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">First Cream Cookie? Your relic is safe though, and it\'s all thanks to Rainbow Sherbet Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">I sorta get it though. It\'s only natural to be concerned!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Perhaps we should examine the relic and see if it\'s unharmed?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_17">This can\'t be... The relic is corrupted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_18">There is no doubt that this is First Egg Cookie\'s doing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_19">It all makes sense now. The temperature controller\'s constant malfunctioning...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_20">... is because the relic has been tampered with and sabotaged.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_21">Thus, Mount St. Crème has become...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_22">And Rainbow Sherbet Cookie was put in harm\'s way due to...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_23">I am the root cause for all this despair.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_24">If only I had disregarded First Egg Cookie\'s words, I would never had left Mount St. Crème.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">Hey, c\'mon, First Cream Cookie! It\'s not too late!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_26">Can\'t we try to undo whatever\'s been done to your relic?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">If we can pull that off, we can bring the old Mount St. Crème back, and even wake GingerDozer up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_28">He\'s right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_29">It might be a long shot... but we\'re willing to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_30">I... I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2001_31">Thank you. It will not be easy, but let us cleanse this corruption!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_1">First Cream Cookie...!
The relic is glowing red...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">And it\'s tied up in thorny vines!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">They\'re like the churro vines
in the Syrup Garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">Time to whack this weed away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.0025_1">It\'s shooting things at us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.2009_2">EEEK! Make\'em go away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_PLAY1_Cookie.0003_3">Thorny thing, you play nice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR2_Cookie.0001_1">We did it!
The vines are gone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_POR2_Cookie.0002_2">We can finally cleanse the relic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_1">This... this cannot be...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.2001_2">I cannot... keep... I am too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Npc.0010_3">This will not be the end.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Don\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">First Cream Cookie!!!
Don\'t give up now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">We can do this... together!
I know we can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Let\'s give it another shot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.0001_1">Hup!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.0003_2">Heeheehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.0025_3">Okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.0002_4">We got this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.2009_5">Woohoot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_BQ2_MINI1_Cookie.2001_6">Once more, together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2001_1">Thanks to you, the relic
has been cleansed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2001_2">Now, behold the true
form of Mount St. Crème
in its fullest glory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_3">This is so awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_4">The air itself is changing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">It feels so cool and fresh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2009_6">Our home is...
Mount St. Crème is back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0055_7">Yay...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0045_8">Mount St. Crème
has returned...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_10">Mount St. Crème.
Eternally cool and fresh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_11">So this is what it\'s
supposed to be like!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_12">Guys! GUYS!
GingerDozer...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">Huh... ?
GingerDozer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Event.0001_14">Yaaawn...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_16">GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_17">GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_18">GingerDozer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Event.0001_19">GingerBrave!
GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Event.0001_20">Hi! I missed you,
everyone. HUH?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_21">You\'re awake!
You\'re okay!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_1">Ah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_2">Whoaaa...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_3">You\'re back...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_4">YOU\'RE BACK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Oh? GingerDozer and First Cream Cookie know each other?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_6">First... Cream... Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2009_7">I\'ve never seen this little one in Mount St. Crème before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Aaah, First Cream Cookie knows who GingerDozer is though.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Didn\'t she say that he was a Cookie of the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Oh! I remember her saying that!
... What\'s a Cookie of the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_11">Cookies of the First Batch... are ones who were baked with Life Powder for the very first time in history.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_12">They were baked by the great Witch, thus their name.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_13">Great... Witch! Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_14">I have been tasked to seek and protect the Cookies of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_15">And I am still looking for them to this day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2009_16">Oooh...! Does that mean the small Cookie you were looking for...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2009_17">Is this Cookie here? GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_18">I am afraid not... I could not save that small Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_19">First Cream Cookie... Don\'t cry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_20">Don\'t cry... Be strong...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_21">What\'s... this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_22">Has the Mistress sent me a vision...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_23">A vision of the First Batch being baked into the world...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_24">Why have you shown me this vision, Mistress...? Are you assuring me that my path is correct...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Event.0001_25">Are you okay, First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_26">Yes, I am fine. But, my friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_27">You were seeking to escape the castle through the window, were you not?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_28">Oh yeah! Escape...! GingerBrave wanted to leave the castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">And I still do! I want to get far away from here, away from the witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_30">But... I\'m a bit worried about that small Cookie you\'re looking for, First Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_31">The one you said you couldn\'t save.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_32">Me too! We can\'t just stand around here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_33">Oh! Is the saboteur of your relic, the one called First Egg Cookie, somehow responsible for this missing Cookie as well?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_34">First Cream Cookie! How can we help?</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">I\'m still a freshly-baked Cookie, but I want to do what\'s right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_36">GingerBrave...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0003_37">Yippee! Another adventure! Let me help too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0025_38">Hm... I too shall aid you. After all, there\'s no better teacher than experiencing new things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0002_39">I... I want to help too...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_40">All of you... You are...
Thank you, and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_41">I... I wish to apologize for my demeanor when we first met in front of the window.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_42">If you wish to aid in my calling...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.2001_43">Please, help me protect the Cookies of the First Batch. Find them, so that I may fulfill my destiny and keep them safe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_44">You can count on us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_45">GingerBright! Wizard Cookie! Strawberry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ6_POR1_Cookie.0001_46">Forward MARCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_1">Oh me oh my...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_2">How amusing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_3">Shall I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_EP4_CH4_SQ7_CUT1_Cookie.2010_4">Make a move as well?</string>
