  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_1">Another quiet day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_2">As expected, there are no visitors or intruders... After all, barely anyone knows of this place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_3">Still, I must not let my guard down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_4">First Cream Cookie explicitly requested that no one is to enter this place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_5">And I will fulfill her wishes...
But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_6">What was that noise?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">Reveal yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_8">Could it be... First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_9">Madam First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2008_10">Hmph... Of course not.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_1">Hm... I\'ve managed to clear away the ice and debris to gain a clear line of sight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_2">But in doing so, this place has gotten quite messy and cluttered...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_3">So far, no Cookies or residents have made their way here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_4">The wall of ice outside actually helped with hiding the entrance to the hollow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_5">But now, it simply looks terrible.
Perhaps I should tidy things up a bit?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_6">The candlesticks have fallen,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">the glowing lights are ruined...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_8">Yes... I think I shall do some organizing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_9">Oh...? What\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_10">Has that bundle of fuzzy-looking fabric always been there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">What an odd object.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0056_12">WAAAHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_1">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_2">You...! You\'re... Salty Cream Yeti?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_3">What are you doing here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_4">WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_5">SNOW CRYSTAL COOKIE...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_6">I... *sniffle*
I didn\'t mean to scare you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">Calm down and answer my question. Why are you here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_8">Were you trying to sneak into the secret hollow?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_9">Because if you were, I cannot and will not allow it, no matter how well-known you are around these parts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_10">*Sniffle*
No, it\'s not that... It\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">Well? Spit it out. Why are you here? And since when?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_12">Well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_13">I was just standing around in front of the secret hollow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_14">And I saw First Cream Cookie go inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_15">I heard her talking and then... then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_16">I didn\'t mean to... but I heard everything thing she said!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_17">What did you hear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_18">*Sniffle*
First Cream Cookie said to keep this place safe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_19">And that no one was allowed to step foot in the chamber.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_20">Hmph... You\'re not lying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_21">And after hearing her say that, I, Salty Cream Yeti, a proud resident of Mount St. Crème...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0056_22">I decided to do what Madam First Cream Cookie asked!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2008_23">*Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_1">Ever since the unwanted frost showed up in Mount St. Crème, this area has grown chillier than usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_2">And because the ice is growing so thick, it\'s difficult to see what\'s inside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_3">Speaking of...
You, Salty Cream Yeti.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR4_Cookie.2008_4">You\'re the one who made this place a mess, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0056_5">I... I, erm...
WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0056_6">I wasn\'t trying to make a mess on purpose!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0056_7">It\'s just... This place was too quiet, and I was bored, and there was nothing to do...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR5_Npc.0056_8">And then I started looking around, and one thing led to another, and then... well... </string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_9">*Sigh...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_10">Fine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">Madam First Cream Cookie will return soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR6_Cookie.2008_12">We should clean up.
This place cannot be left in such a state.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0056_13">Okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_14">Yes... This is the perfect spot for the sculptures...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_15">This spot also serves as a strategic advantage, providing some good cover.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ1_POR7_Npc.0056_16">Where should we start?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_1">*Sniffle*
The entrance to the chamber is all cleaned up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_2">It\'s so magnificent!
Everything is back to the way it was!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_3">We should keep the snowball rolling and clean inside too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_4">No, we will not be going inside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_5">*Aw...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_6">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">There is no doubt that the winds of Mount St. Crème have changed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_8">Despite being deep within this hollow, I can still feel the chilled, damp air.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_9">*Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_10">I miss our home... I miss the old Mount St. Crème...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">...
Me too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_12">Salty Cream Yeti...
You\'d better not cry too often when it\'s this cold and damp.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_13">Your tears will freeze up immediately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_14">Like me, I know you aren\'t bothered by the cold...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_15">But you should consider joining the other residents elsewhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_16">I believe this place will get... quite lonesome over time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_17">*Sniffle*
But what about First Cream Cookie\'s request?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_18">...
I\'ll handle it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_19">...
Oh, okay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_20">But if I leave... Snow Crystal Cookie will be lonely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0056_21">No... I\'m gonna stay!
I\'ve got your back, Snow Crystal Cookie!!! You can trust me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_22">What\'re you thinking, Salty Cream Yeti?
I can\'t shake the feeling that you\'re not going to listen to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS10_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_23">...
I guess it\'ll be okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_1">Oh! You\'re here!
Hello, Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie2005_2">I came as soon as I could. You mentioned an overgrown plant that needs tending to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_3">They\'re on the table over here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_4">This candied flower and this one too, in the repotting pot.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie2005_5">These are very healthy flowers. I can tell that you\'ve taken care of them with lots of love.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_6">Hehe! I tried my best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_7">Will you start pruning them right away or-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie2005_8">Wait. Before I begin...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie2005_9">Is that a Cookievorous plant? How have you come across such a rare specimen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_1_POR1_Cookie0063_10">Oh! You know about Cookievorous plants? You can take a closer look if you\'d like!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_1">I\'ve never seen such a calm and docile Cookievorous plant before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_2">Do you have some sort of secret, personal method?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie0063_3">Nothing special! I just kept giving it nutrients and lots of water. Oh, and I played music for it too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_4">Fascinating. I will remember to jot those down in my journal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie0063_5">Oh? You have a journal?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_6">It is more like an observation and research log, for the plants in the Syrup Garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_7">I also write down notes about plants I\'ve learned about in my travels.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie0063_8">That\'s awesome! If it\'s okay, can I pay you a visit and read your notes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_9">Of course. I am happy to share such knowledge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_10">Shall we begin-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_11">Pardon me, but what is this fountain\'s purpose?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie0063_12">Oh! It\'s called the Fountain of Sweet Growth! Its waters contain all the nutrients that plants need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_13">And these fixtures here... They are made with luminous daisies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie0063_14">Wow! You really know your stuff!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_15">Of course. Now then, shall we commence with the-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_2_POR1_Cookie2005_16">No, sorry, I have one more question.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_1">This is... It\'s said to grow larger than any Cookie... It\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_2">Your hunch is right! It\'s a gigantigrow tulip!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_3">I didn\'t think you\'d recognize this one! You\'re amazing, Rosemary Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_4">I am very glad to have met you as well, someone who loves plants as much as I do.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_5">Well then, I shall begin pruning the-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_6">Before you start, I wanted to ask you something. What are your thoughts on this tillandsia coconut?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_7">!!!
I\'ve never seen such a large specimen!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_8">Hehe, like I said, I try my best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_9">I could spend all day talking about plants with you, Rosemary Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_10">I couldn\'t agree more.
Now then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_11">After I am done pruning, do you wish to come visit my room and talk some more?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_12">I can show you my observation journal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_13">That sounds awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_14">Oh! You should also take a look at these herb curtains!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_15">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie2005_16">Thank you for mentioning them first. I actually wanted to ask about them for a while now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0063_3_POR1_Cookie0063_17">Haha! By all means! We can take our time and talk all day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie0038_1">WOOOW!
Is that a giant telescope?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie0038_2">And that\'s...!
Is this what they call a computer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie2004_3">Yup! All of this stuff was made from scraps by yours truly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie2004_4">I used all sorts of parts and junk that I found throughout the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie0038_5">All this stuff was made from scraps?!
That\'s amazing, Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie2004_6">You said you were under-equipped for your last expedition. Isn\'t that dangerous?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie0038_7">Yeah. I set out to find some relics and treasures in the kitchen\'s cellar with nothing but a rope... I didn\'t find a single crumb!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie2004_8">That won\'t do! Which is why... I went ahead and made some gear that might be useful for ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie0038_9">Really?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_1_Cookie2004_10">HAHA! C\'mon, lemme show ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_1">Tada! I made a climbing hook out of binding wires!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_2">With this, you can climb almost any ledge or wall!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie0038_3">Oh wow! This\'ll come in handy when I\'m climbing bookshelves!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_4">And take a look at this!
A portable raft made from parts of a lightweight bottle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_5">Watch this...! You can fold it up to such a small size, it\'ll fit in any pack! But... it can get a bit noisy when you\'re trying to fold it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie0038_6">This is awesome! I won\'t have to worry about getting soggy and wet!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_7">Oh, this is a good one!
A shield! It\'s made from a sturdy, but lightweight piece of metal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_8">If you ever have to defend yourself from monsters, this shield\'ll keep ya safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie0038_9">Wow, I can\'t believe you made all this equipment from stuff that was just lying around the castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie2004_10">HAHA! I\'m happy to help!
Hopefully, these\'ll help ya in your expeditions!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie0038_11">This is all-
Wait, what was that noise?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_2_POR1_Cookie0038_12">*GASP!*
It\'s the witch! She\'s back!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Npc.0009_1">Gone. Gone... GONE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Npc.0009_2">How can this be?! I specifically remember leaving a paperclip on this very desk! And where is that bottle?! And... even the coin is missing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Npc.0009_3">Oh ho... This is getting very, very interesting indeed. Fine, let\'s play... Where oh where can you be hiding...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_4">The witch looks really angry! And she\'s looking for something!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_5">What\'s she up to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_6">...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_7">Waaait a second...
Radish Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_8">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_9">This climbing hook and raft... Is the witch looking for these???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_10">HA! No way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_11">You\'re sure that you made this gear with... stuff that was abandoned and just lying around, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_12">Well... No one was around when I picked\'em up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_13">So... yeah? Maybe? Possibly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_14">... Maybe? Possibly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_15">Adventurer Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie0038_16">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2004_3_POR1_Cookie2004_17">I think we should run!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">I cannot believe that our Syrup Garden has so many visitors.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_2">I am glad we decided to host a flower festival.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_3">Oh? There\'s some sort of commotion at the entrance...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie0028_4">Bang! Bang! Boom! Pow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_5">Explosions?!
Has the Reaper returned???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie0028_6">FIREWORKS! Everyone loves fireworks, sparkles, and explosions! BANG BANG!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_7">Cherry... Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie0028_8">HEEHEE! Everyone\'s waiting for a spectacular fireworks show!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_9">No...! No, please stop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_1_POR1_Cookie2005_10">This isn\'t the time for fireworks! Especially in our garden!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0029_1">Rosemary Cookie! ROSEMARY COOKIE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">What\'s happening?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0029_3">My entire wildflower encyclopedia collection was blasted away by Cherry Cookie\'s cherry bombs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0029_4">All my hard work... Gone.
And I never had the chance to show anyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0033_5">PFFFT!
I bet no one wanted to see it in the first place!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0032_6">Rosemary Cookie! Rosemary Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_7">Scarlet and Rose? What\'s wrong???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0032_8">We are flabbergasted at the number of explosions! And at a festival for flowers? The audacity!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0032_9">The audacity! We are extremely unsatisfied with this festival\'s chaotic and hectic atmosphere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">This festival is becoming a nightmare! We cannot let this chaos continue...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Churro Golem! Please help me stop Cherry Cookie\'s antics! We must save the festival!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_2_POR1_Npc.0034_12">CHUR CHUUU!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">Churro Golem? Where are you, Churro Golem???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">Oh! There you are! What are you doing here? I asked you to help me stop Cherry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Npc.0034_3">Chuuur... Chuur!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">Look up at the sky...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_6">!!!
What are those beautiful lights...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Npc.0028_7">Haha! This is amazing, Cherry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Npc.0025_8">I was unaware cherry bombs could make such beautiful fireworks. Marvelous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Npc.0030_9">More boom! More boom! More fireworks!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie0028_10">Teeheehee! There\'s still more!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Everyone is... having fun?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">*Chuckle*
I guess it doesn\'t matter whether it\'s a festival for flowers or fireworks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">What matters is... everyone is happy and enjoying themselves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_14">That\'s what you wanted me to see, right? Churro Golem?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2005_3_POR1_Npc.0034_15">Churchur!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.Main">Green Thumbs\' Daily Life</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.01">A Green Thumb\'s Invitation</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.02">A Fellow Green Thumb?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.03">Why Are We Here Again?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.01.Summary">Rosemary Cookie has come to visit Herb Cookie, who has requested her help in pruning some flowers. But before they can begin... the two of them engage in deep conversation.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.02.Summary">Both Cookies love talking about plants. Though there\'s work to be done, the two green thumbs seem to be enjoying the conversation.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Title.03.Summary">Rosemary Cookie, finally ready to begin pruning the flowers, is once more drawn into the conversation about rare plants! At this rate, the two will probably forget about pruning entirely!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.01.Main">Discarded Scraps or Not?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.01">I Need Equipment!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.02">Amazing Inventions</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.03">Maybe Possibly Abandoned Scraps...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.01.Summary">Adventurer Cookie decides to pay a visit to Radish Cookie, who has taken the liberty to craft some interesting adventuring gear! What sort of gadgets has Radish Cookie crafted?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.02.Summary">Adventurer Cookie is amazed at Radish Cookie\'s ability to create ingenious objects with nothing but abandoned scraps. But suddenly, the two Cookies spot the witch approaching fast!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Title.03.Summary">An extremely angry and ill-tempered Shadow Witch claims that several of her belongings have gone missing. Radish Cookie is somewhat possibly certain that her inventions were made from abandoned scraps...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.01.Main">An Explosive Flower Festival</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.01">Flowers vs. Fireworks</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.02">A Festival in Chaos</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.03">Fireworks Dancing in the Night Sky</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.01.Summary">The Syrup Garden is hosting a flower festival and many residents have come to enjoy the party... including Cherry Cookie and her seemingly endless supply of cherry bombs!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.02.Summary">Cherry Cookie\'s enthusiasm and excitement for explosions has wreaked havoc upon the festival. Rosemary Cookie asks the Churro Golem to help save the festival...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Title.03.Summary">Cherry Cookie\'s explosions have lit up the night sky with a wondrous display of fireworks. Rosemary Cookie is happy to see everyone enjoying themselves. She decides to join the festivities by gazing upon the dazzling show as well.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.Title">Waiting for Her Return</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest1">Intruder?!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest2">What Are You Doing Here?</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest3">First Cream Cookie\'s Request</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest4">The Culprit Revealed</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest5">Waiting for Her Return, Once More</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest1.Summary">Snow Crystal Cookie continues to keep watch over the secret hollow. The usual silence is suddenly interrupted by a rustle...</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest2.Summary">After removing a wall of ice, Snow Crystal Cookie discovers that the entrance to the ancient chamber is quite a mess. She decides to tidy up the area...</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest3.Summary">A mysterious lump of fabric turns out to be... Salty Cream Yeti? The little one claims they are keeping a promise made to First Cream Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest4.Summary">Knowing that First Cream Cookie could potentially arrive without warning, Snow Crystal Cookie decides to tidy up the place to its previous state. Salty Cream Yeti joins the effort.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.10.SQuest5.Summary">The winds of Mount St. Crème have irrefutably changed significantly. Snow Crystal Cookie urges Salty Cream Yeti to join the other residents somewhere safer than the hollow. But will they listen to her advice?</string>
