  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.cookie2005.Limited.Floor.001">Radish Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.cookie0157.Limited.Floor.001">Cream Unicorn Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.cookie2004.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Rosemary Cookie. This toy carries an aroma of fresh rosemaries, and looking into its eyes gives you a sense of comfort and relief.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.cookie2005.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Radish Cookie. The playful and cheerful smile makes you want to give this toy a giant hug.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.Season.cookie0157.Limited.Floor.001.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy with a design capturing the characteristics of Cream Unicorn Cookie perfectly. When you gaze into its eyes, you somehow know that your dreams will be magical.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Illust.Dialog.01">Is that a
Cookievorous plant?
Such a rare specimen!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0063.Illust.Dialog.02">You can take a closer
look if you\'d like!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Illust.Dialog.01">You\'re sure that you
made this gear with...
stuff that was abandoned?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2004.Illust.Dialog.02">Well... No one was around
when I picked\'em up...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Illust.Dialog.01">Everyone\'s waiting for a
spectacular fireworks show!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2005.Illust.Dialog.02">This isn\'t the time
for fireworks!</string>
  <string name="$UX.ExploreRuins.LastChance.Text2">Time left:</string>
  <string name="$UX.Competition.Start.Text">No need to wait for everyone!
You can start first and dive right in!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.10">Reminiscing on the Fresh Past</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.10.Story">The entrance to the secret hollow grows much colder than necessary by the day. Snow Crystal Cookie urges Salty Cream Yeti to join the other residents in the refuge, but it seems the little one thinks otherwise...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Illust.Dialog.01">What sort of break
was that?! It didn\'t
even last a second!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Illust.Dialog.02">But this is how I always
prepare for concerts.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Illust.Dialog.01">Make yourself comfortable.
I shall begin my recital,
just for you.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Illust.Dialog.02">Thank you so much,
Mint Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Illust.Dialog.01">I wasn\'t able to make a
real rainbow, but this is
SO MUCH BETTER!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Illust.Dialog.02">At least she\'s
happy, I guess?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Illust.Dialog.01">Here we go!
10... 9... 8...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Illust.Dialog.02">Huh?! WAIT!
I\'ll go hide,
just slow down!!!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch05.SQuest09.Summary">The Cookies finally meet First Cream Cookie! But before they could rejoice, the temperature controller has gone out of control again!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest01.Summary">In order to ensure Mount St. Crème remain fresh and chilled, First Cream Cookie left her sacred relic behind during her absence. Could it be that the region\'s temperature problems were caused by a problem with the relic?</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest02.Summary">The Cookies travel to the Chamber of Freshest Cream to retrieve First Cream Cookie\'s relic. They\'re surprised to discover Rainbow Sherbet Cookie, trapped in some sort of magical prison!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest03.Summary">Our friends succeed in freeing Rainbow Sherbet Cookie! She claims that an intruder was snooping around the chamber, looking for something. She reveals what the intruder was looking for...!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest04.Summary">Despite the potential danger, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie has safeguarded the relic. But somehow, it has been corrupted with some form of foul magic!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest05.Summary">Our friends have successfully purified the sacred relic! Immediately, First Cream Cookie wields its power to restore Mount St. Crème to its former glory and a chilled, fresh breeze begins to flow through the region. And what\'s this?! GingerDozer has awakened!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest06.Summary">Our heroes learn there are more Cookies of the First Batch! GingerBrave and friends decide to postpone their escape from the castle in order to help First Cream Cookie in her search for these mysterious Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch04.SQuest07.Summary">Meanwhile... First Egg Cookie has been watching everything from afar. A plan is brewing. A sinister plan...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.01.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie is eager to perform an experiment based on Piethagoras\' theory of harmony and suggests writing a concerto featuring a violin and hammers.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.02.Summary">Mint Choco Cookie believes a violin and hammer duet is an idea worth pursuing! The Cookies begin composing... for hours and hours on end!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.03.Summary">Strawbery Crepe Cookie presents all sorts of different ideas to buy some time and extend their break. However, nothing can stop Mint Choco Cookie\'s passion for creating music.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.01.Summary">Cocoa Cookie is getting ready to attend Mint Choco Cookie\'s recital... only to discover that her ticket is missing!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.02.Summary">Despite searching everywhere, Cocoa Cookie couldn\'t find her ticket. She hears a knock at the door, but is very surprised to see who it is!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.03.Summary">Mint Choco Cookie was worried when he didn\'t see Cocoa Cookie at his recital. After learning of Cocoa Cookie\'s stress-ridden day, he decides to perform a recital just for her.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.01.Summary">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie learns that real rainbows are created when sunlight meets water droplets in the air. She decides to try it out immediately... only to discover the water freezes too rapidly.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.02.Summary">Snow Crystal Cookie manages to rescue Rainbow Sherbet Cookie from the ice. The stoic archer points out it is near impossible to create rainbows with traditional methods in such a cold environment and, no less, indoors.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.03.Summary">Though failing to create rainbows using water, the colors reflecting off of the ice has created a dazzling display in its own right. Rainbow Sherbet Cookie is ecstatic to have discovered such a unique method of creating rainbows.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.01.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie, having grown bored of playing with the Wafflebots, aimlessly looks for something to do. Suddenly, Radish Cookie appears and asks to become Strawberry Crepe Cookie\'s apprentice!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.02.Summary">Strawberry Crepe Cookie decides to accept Radish Cookie as an apprentice. To demonstrate a sense of authority, the engineering genius tells Radish Cookie to run five meters. Is this what mentors really do?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.03.Summary">Radish Cookie has completed her task! And the next one, and the next one! Strawberry Crepe Cookie starts to feel bored again, but Radish Cookie has an ingenious solution.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.11.SQuest1.Summary">With a mixture of joy and curiosity, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie explores Mount St. Crème to see its restoration in full. She happens to find the Crème Refuge.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.11.SQuest2.Summary">Cherry Cream Muffin tells Rainbow Sherbet Cookie how the residents struggled to survive the lukewarm, moist air. Upon hearing this tale, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie decides to help create new, happier memories by hosting a party.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.11.SQuest3.Summary">The old supplies and ice packs are cleared away to make room for party decorations and fancy lights. But the party can\'t start without inviting guests!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.11.SQuest4.Summary">The Crème Refuge has transformed into a bright and lively party venue. Snow Crystal Cookie was also invited... but the other guests are rather unsure if she is enjoying the party or not.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.11.SQuest5.Summary">The party closes with many wishes for Mount St. Crème to stay fresh and chilled for a long, long time. Rainbow Sherbet Cookie adds in a last-minute prayer wishing for everyone\'s happiness and freshness.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Story">A Cookie as gentle and delightful as a scoop of brightly colored sherbet, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s lovely personality can turn even the smallest moments into joyous occasions. She\'s a magnet for good vibes and is adored by all the residents of Mount St. Crème!

Fearless in the face of change and danger, she often leaps into adventures and situations without a second thought. Luckily, she\'s friends with a calm and stoic Cookie who\'s always there to help her out of any bind!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Get">A fresh new day is here!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Random.01">Whoa...! So pretty!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Random.02">What a refreshing breeze!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Random.03">Wow! What\'s that lovely aroma?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Random.04">I\'m not scared at all! Heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.Random.05">You can call me for anything!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Let\'s try once more!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Skill.Name">Rainbow Beam</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s Dazzling Room of Colors!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.SeasonComplete.2009.Story">Proof of completing the Rainbow Sherbet Collection. There\'s no need to be afraid when you have an encouraging and supportive friend like Rainbow Sherbet Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s soul. Holding it fills you with a wave of wondrous joy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.JellyBear.0037">Cheesecake Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.JellyBear.0044">Werewolf Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.JellyBear.0113">Avocado Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.JellyBear.0044.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Werewolf Cookie. Surely this toy won\'t tell you to stay away... Perhaps it\'ll even let you touch the paw beans without growling! The intricate patterns and attention to detail are proof that this must have been made by a skilled craftsman!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.JellyBear.0113.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Avocado Cookie. The slight smirk on the toy\'s face makes it feel like an un-bear-ably hilarious joke is on the way! With such intricate stitches and attention to details, this must have been created by a skilled craftsman...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.2009.Tooltip">Rainbow Coins resembling the bright and dazzling colors of the rainbow. These can only be obtained during the Rainbow Sherbet Season!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2009">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s Dazzling Room of Colors</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2009.Story">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s room is filled with decorations and colors that remind you of sweet, refreshing ice cream. Just standing in the room, you feel like a magical wave of joy and excitement has washed away your concerns.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.001">Splendiferous Golden Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.002">Resplendent Pink Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.003">Sweet &amp; Smiley Parfait</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.004">Berry-Scented Chaise Lounge</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.005">Eclectic Hibiscus Bouquet</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.006">Ice Cream Scoop Beanbag</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.007">Beaded Ice Cream Table</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.008">Orange Sherbet Stool</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Wall.001">Rainbow Aurora Window</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Wall.002">Ice Cream Stained Glass</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Hanger.001">Iridescent Lace Curtains</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Hanger.002">Rainbow Cloud Curtains</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.001">Colorful Hanging Craft</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.002">Swirly Hanging Sculpture</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.003">Vibrant Candy Lamps</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.WP.001">Splotched Rainbow Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Deck.001">Splotched Rainbow Floor</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.001.Story">There\'s no better feeling than plopping onto this bed and sinking into its covers. As you lie down all snug and warm, you feel as if this bed\'s golden wings are shielding you from all the hardships of the day and the potential worries of tomorrow.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.002.Story">There\'s no better feeling than diving headfirst onto this snug and comfy bed. The moment you lie down, you feel as if you\'re going to have the happiest dream ever!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.003.Story">What\'s the recipe for a perfect parfait? Puréed fruit, Jellies, and dollops atop dollops of cream! Even the Bear Jelly is smiling at this culinary masterpiece!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.004.Story">A chaise lounge that emits an aroma of strawberries. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.005.Story">A collection of rare hibiscuses. It\'ll look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.006.Story">A beanbag resembling a scoop of ice cream. Yes, it looks scrumptious, but you can\'t eat furniture!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.007.Story">A table made from a cup containing beaded ice cream. Who wouldn\'t like to have this?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Floor.008.Story">A simple yet comfy stool that will bring some color to anyone\'s room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Wall.001.Story">A window with a view of a dazzling aurora. Looking out through it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Wall.002.Story">A colorful, stained-glass window. Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Hanger.001.Story">Even the harshest of sunlight is softened into a sparkling glow when passing through these curtains. It really adds some good vibes to any room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Hanger.002.Story">Colorful curtains that\'ll brighten any room! Where should we place this?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.001.Story">Fluffy marshmallow clouds and twinkling stars gently sway in the air with this hanging craft. It adds a touch of tranquility to your room!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.002.Story">A hanging sculpture that reminds you of a fresh swirl of sherbet. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.003.Story">Vibrant lamps hanging from the ceiling. Let\'s set them up here and there!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.WP.001.Story">These patterns and colors remind you of different flavors of ice cream. And there\'s a flavor for everyone! Do you want banana, strawberry, or chocolate?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Deck.001.Story">These patterns and colors make you feel as if you\'re walking on a rainbow. It seems the floor glistens with each step you take!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.001">Rainbow Sherbet Ice Cream Cup</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.002">Magic Rainbow Compact</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.003">Rainbow Ink Letter</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.001.Story">Have you ever experienced a summer so sweltering and blisteringly hot you forgot what day it was? Whenever you\'re faced with such heat, a mere spoonful of this fresh sherbet will make you feel refreshed from head to toe! It\'s okay if you want to have more than spoonful too!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.002.Story">What\'s that? You think this is some sort of magical artifact disguised as makeup and can transform the user into a magic-wielding hero? Nonsense!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2009.003.Story">This letter, written with rainbow-colored ink, seems to be addressed to a dear friend of the writer. It\'s somewhat easy to recognize who the writer and intended recipient are.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.08">Chamber of Freshest Cream</string>
  <string name="$Room.Ep04.Blueprint.08.Story">Legend has it that, long ago, a Cookie of mysterious origins brought eternal freshness to Mount St. Crème. The legend also states that this very chamber was where this Cookie awakened from a deep, enchanted slumber. Even when the winds of Mount St. Crème turned warm and humid, somehow, the serene beauty and temperature of this room remained unchanged.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.001">Mysterious Egg Spinner</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.002">First Cream Dais</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.003">Crème Resident Statue</string>
