  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.001.Story">This strange, rotating contraption emits a peculiar, golden glow. It appears as if this was used by the witches of ages past to scramble eggs within their shells... As you approach it, you are overwhelmed with a sense of foreboding.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.002.Story">At first glance, this dais resembles a golden crown. Upon taking a closer look, its breathtaking beauty irresistibly draws you in, and it is definitely not something one approaches lightly! Though its purpose is to store a brooch filled with power, the pedestal itself fills your heart with reverence and awe.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.003.Story">A statue of an unknown resident of Mount St. Crème from ages past. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.004.Story">A set of guardrails made from the freshest cream. It goes well wherever you place it!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.005.Story">Crème stanchions such as these are used to cordon off an area. Let\'s put them to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.006.Story">An elongated stool that brings a dash of elegance to any space!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Floor.007.Story">A soft, golden apricot. Everyone loves apricots!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Wall.001.Story">A stained-glass window that fills you with a sense of awe. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Wall.002.Story">A curved window that fills you with a sense of comfort. Let\'s put this to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Wall.003.Story">A narrow window that fills you with a sense of warmth. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Ceil.001.Story">An elegant chandelier that emits a warm, golden glow. Who wouldn\'t like to have this?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Ceil.002.Story">A simple chandelier that emits an unearthly yet comforting glow. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.WP.001.Story">This wallpaper\'s color reminds you of rich, pistachio cream. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.RoomOfFreshCream.Deck.001.Story">This flooring\'s color reminds you of soft vanilla and pistachio cream. Try decorating the floor with these.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0125.Season">Milk Cream Cloud</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0126.Season">Lemon Cream Cloud</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0127.Season">Strawberry Cream Cloud</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0128.Season">Tropical Sherbet Cone</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0129.Season">Citrus Sherbet Cone</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0130.Season">Very Berry Sherbet Cone</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0125.Season.Story">A tiny cloud made by gently whipping cream with a steady pace. It\'s so light and airy! This little one dreams of becoming a giant cloud in the sky. Perhaps the witch\'s magic can help it achieve this dream?</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0126.Season.Story">A small cloud made by gently pouring lemon juice into whipped cream. It\'s so silky and smooth! As you continue to pet this little one, you feel as if your concerns are melting away. And there\'s no need to worry about waking it up as it enjoys snoozing in your lap!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0127.Season.Story">A miniature cloud made by gently mixing strawberries into whipped cream. It\'s so soft and fluffy! This little one prides itself for having real strawberries within its cream. Absolutely no artificial flavoring!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0128.Season.Story">A tropical sherbet cone. They seem familiar somehow...</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0129.Season.Story">A citrus sherbet cone. Hopefully you\'ll get along!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0130.Season.Story">A very berry sherbet cone. They\'re a great friend to have around.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.11">GingerDozer\'s Awake!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.12">Cookie in a Bind</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.13">Corrupted Relic</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.14">Protect the Relic!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.15">A Certain Memory</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.11.Story">GingerDozer is awake! And... somehow, GingerDozer knows who First Cream Cookie is...?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.12.Story">A Cookie has been trapped by some form of foul magic. The conjured bindings need to be removed quickly.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.13.Story">First Cream Cookie\'s ancient relic has been corrupted. It must be purified to return Mount St. Crème to its former glory!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.14.Story">Within the Chamber of Freshest Cream, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie has protected the sacred relic from an unknown intruder!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Ep04.15.Story">After meeting GingerDozer, First Cream Cookie has received a vision. Perhaps it\'s a memory of the past, when the First Batch was baked? Why did she witness such a vision?</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.11">Ready to Party!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.11.Story">Can you believe this place used to be the Crème Refuge? To celebrate the return of Mount St. Crème, everyone gets together for a party!</string>
