  <string name="$Cookie.2009">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2009.Soulstone">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2009.Ceil.999">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_1">When sunlight meets water in the air, it forms a rainbow...?! WOW! You learn something new every day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_2">I wanna see a real rainbow!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_3">If I spray water into the air, that means I might be able to make one right here and right now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_4">Let\'s see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_5">Okay, and if I just turn on the water now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_6">HERE WE GO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_7">Eh...?
Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_8">The water\'s freezing?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_1_POR1_Cookie2009_9">I can\'t make rainbows with ice...!
Somebody haaalp!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_1">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie?
What happened???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_2">I don\'t want to know why or how you got trapped in all this ice, but hang on. I\'ll get you out of there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2009_3">PHEW!
Thanks, Snow Crystal Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2009_4">I sprayed water into the air because, you know, that\'s what rain is like.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2009_5">But all the water froze up so fast...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_6">You sprayed water... into the air...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_7">Indoors...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2009_8">Now, I know what you\'re gonna say, but I had a good reason. I wanted to show you a real rainbow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2009_9">But, well, things obviously didn\'t work out, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_10">Oh. I guess that explains it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_2_POR1_Cookie2008_11">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie. I believe it is practically impossible to see rainbows in cold environments.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_1">Oh... Really?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2008_2">Don\'t be too disappointed. Here, take a look at this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2008_3">The ice you made is glistening like crystals.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2008_4">And your colorful attire is reflecting off of the ice as well... Hence, you have succeeded in creating multiple rainbows.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_5">*GASP*
I MADE RAINBOWS?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_6">I made lots of pretty rainbows!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_7">I wasn\'t able to make a real one, but this is SO MUCH BETTER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_8">Thanks, Snow Crystal Cookie! I would\'ve never noticed this on my own!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_9">You just made my entire day! Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2009_10">I\'m still gonna find a way to make real rainbows though!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2008_11">You really shouldn\'t, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2009_3_POR1_Cookie2008_12">At least she\'s happy, I guess?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.Main">Shinier Than Any Rainbow</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.01">Time to Make Rainbows!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.02">Something\'s Gone Wrong...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2009.Title.03">Something Better Than Rainbows</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_1">Alright! Everyone\'s here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0113_2">That we are! But... why exactly are we here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0046_3">I was told there was an opportunity to for me to compose a new piece of music.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0046_4">I only thought it was natural to offer my room for the occasion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0113_5">That\'s what I heard too! I was told my hammer was needed to make some sort of experimental music!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_6">Exactly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_7">Hear me out! After reading some of Piethagoras\' works, I got an idea for an experiment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0046_8">Do go on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_9">As Piethagoras was walking past a blacksmith, he heard the sound of differently weighted hammers striking an anvil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_10">And that\'s how he came up with a hypothesis on the nature of harmony!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_11">I want to take it an extra step and create... a hammer and violin concerto!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0518_12">WITH SCIENCE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0113_13">Hammer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_1_POR1_Cookie0046_14">And violin concerto...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0113_1">HAHA! That\'s a good one...
You\'re kidding, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_2">Actually, I think it\'s a splendid idea worth exploring.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_3">Coincidentally, I recently pondered upon bringing some avant-garde themes to my next concert.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_4">I think our efforts will produce something magnificent.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0518_5">I know, right?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0113_6">If y\'all are excited, then so am I!
I\'m always ready to swing my hammer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0113_7">......
Five long hours have passed since I said that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0518_8">I... I didn\'t say... that I had to... do the hammering too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_9">But this melody seems to favor the smaller hammer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_10">Avocado Cookie\'s hammer produces a much heavier and robust sound.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0518_11">But my arms hurt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_12">Ah, then shall we take a brief respite?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0113_13">Just what I needed to hear!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0518_14">Yes! A break!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_15">Very well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0046_16">...
...
Shall we resume our efforts?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_2_POR1_Cookie0518_17">... Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_1">What sort of break was that?!
It didn\'t even last a second!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0046_2">But this is how I always prepare for concerts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0113_3">Wow, you\'re one tough Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0113_4">You\'re just like me when I\'m forging a new weapon, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Huh... I do the same when I\'m designing blueprints for a new Wafflebot...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_6">Which means...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_7">We\'re not going to stop hammering until we\'ve finished, are we....?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_8">No way! I can\'t keep this up!!! Who knows how long we\'re going to be stuck here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_9">Think, think, think...!
There has to be a way out of this mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_10">Say, Mint Choco Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0046_11">Yes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_12">What do you think about composing music with my Wafflebots?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0046_13">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_14">Hear me out! With the Wafflebots, you\'d be able to make something that\'s entirely new!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0046_15">What a novel idea! It may be an interesting endeavor with unique results!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_16">Right? Then I\'ll get the Wafflebots programmed and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0046_17">We should pursue that idea after we\'ve completed our current efforts with the hammers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_18">Eh? Wait, no, I meant-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0046_3_POR1_Cookie0518_19">NO! Things weren\'t supposed to happen like this!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.Main">Music! Devotion! Effort!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.01">Music, Never-Before-Heard!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.02">Music is Sincerity</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0046.Title.03">Practice Continues</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_1">It\'s finally here! Today is Mint Choco Cookie\'s violin recital!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_2">Cocoa to sip on during the performance? Check!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_3">Scarf that I spent so much time knitting? Check!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_4">Mint-colored mug to give as a gift? Check!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_5">Hehe! All set! And since there\'s still some time until the recital, I should have a cup of cocoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_6">Hm... Wait.
I feel like I\'m forgetting something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_7">Oh! I know what it is.
I don\'t see my recital ticket!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_8">I don\'t... see... my recital... ticket...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_1_POR1_Cookie0045_9">Oh no! Where is my ticket?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_1">It\'s not under the fondue pot...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_2">It\'s not under the bûche de noël plate...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_3">It\'s not near the window...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_4">Nooo!
I can\'t find my ticket...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_5">And my delicious cocoa got burnt while I was looking for it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_6">And look at the time!
Even if I manage to find my ticket, I\'m already too late...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_7">Now I\'m too sad to even drink cocoa. Today has turned out to be a terrible day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_8">Hm? Was that a knock at the door? Who could it be...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0046_9">Hello, Cocoa Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_2_POR1_Cookie0045_10">M-M-Mint Choco Cookie?!
Wh-Why?! Wh-What are you doing here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_1">So... You have lost your ticket?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_2">I grew concerned because I did not see you at the recital.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_3">I\'m sorry, Mint Choco Cookie.
You sent me an invitation, but I just missed your recital entirely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_4">Dearest Cocoa Cookie, there is no need for you to apologize.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_5">I am simply relieved to see you are healthy and well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_6">To think... I had almost assumed that you may have gotten hurt on your way to the recital.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_7">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_8">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_9">I am grateful that I am here with you now, for it means I can play my music for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_10">It is truly fortunate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0046_11">If you\'d please take a seat and make yourself comfortable... I shall begin my recital, just for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_12">*Gasp*
Oh, thank you so much, Mint Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_13">A cozy marshmallow chair, and a warm cup of cocoa... Double check!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_14">And Mint Choco Cookie\'s music...! Triple check!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0045_3_POR1_Cookie0045_15">Today turned out to be the best day ever...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.Main">A Recital for You</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.01">Missing Ticket!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.02">Even Cocoa Can\'t Save the Day</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0045.Title.03">In the End, the Best Day Ever</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_1">Wow...! I had a ton of fun today!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_2">I played tag with the Wafflebots, ran a race with the Wafflebots, trained the Wafflepup, and then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_3">Wait... Is that really all I did today...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_4">...
Okay, I\'m sick of playing with the Wafflebots now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Hmph...!
Hey, Wafflepup! Where are ya, buddy? C\'mon back! Time to-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie2004_6">HAHAHA!
I finally found you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_7">Waaah?!
Huh? What!? WHO ARE YOU?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie2004_8">I\'m Radish Cookie!
What\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_9">... Strawberry Crepe Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie2004_10">Okay, Strawberry Crepe Cookie. I have to ask! Did you make that robot?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_11">Yup, of course I did. All the Wafflebots here were designed and built by yours truly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie2004_12">Haha, I thought so!
Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie2004_13">I want to be your apprentice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_1_POR1_Cookie0518_14">... Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_1">I\'m very interested in inventing things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_2">And I really want to learn more about your Wafflebots!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_3">With robots like these, Rosemary Cookie can take care of the Syrup Garden much more efficiently!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_4">So how did you make them? How?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_5">Oh? This Radish Cookie recognizes my genius and how cool my Wafflebots are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_6">She doesn\'t seem so bad!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_7">But wait... She said she wanted to be my apprentice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_8">Which means... I\'d be her teacher and mentor, and I should act like one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_9">So you recognize the greatness of my Wafflebots? You\'re not so bad. Okay, you can be my apprentice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_10">Really?! Thank you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_11">Your first task is simple. Go outside and run five meters!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_12">A whole FIVE METERS?!
... But why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_13">Er... If you want to build robots, then you need to have the physical endurance to do so!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_14">Oooh! I get it!
So... you run five meters every day too then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie0518_15">O-O-Of course I do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_2_POR1_Cookie2004_16">Wow! That\'s amazing!
Okay, I\'ll be right back!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_1">Phew...!
That was quite a run, but I\'m back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_2">I wonder what\'s next?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_3">Your next task is to climb to the top of that tree and back, thirty times!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_4">Oooh! More endurance training, huh? Awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_5">I\'m... *huff puff*
I\'m back! What\'s next?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_6">The next step is...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_7">PHEW!
Okay, I\'m back! What\'s next?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_8">Erm, the next step is...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_9">I can\'t believe this Cookie keeps completing everything I say...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_10">And I can\'t think of any more things for her to do...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_11">Maybe I\'m not ready to call myself a teacher and mentor...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_12">There\'s... nothing left.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_13">Huh? What do you mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_14">This is getting boring. You should go now. It\'s time for me to play hide-and-seek with the Wafflebots.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_15">Hide-and-seek?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_16">Let me play too! After all, the more the merrier!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_17">After we\'re done playing hide-and-seek, can you teach me how to build a robot?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_18">I really, really want to learn how they work and make one for myself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_19">You... You\'re...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_20">Ahem! Okay then! This is my final task for you, my apprentice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_21">Play hide-and-seek with me and the Wafflebots every day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_22">HAHAHA! That sounds too fun to be a task!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_23">Okay then! Let\'s start playin\' hide-and-seek then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_24">Huh? Like... right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_25">You hide first!
I\'m gonna start counting to ten right now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie2004_26">Here we go!
10... 9... 8...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0518_3_POR1_Cookie0518_27">Huh?! WAIT! I\'ll go hide, just slow down!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.Main">Becoming an Apprentice</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.01">Teach Me!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.02">Grit and Discipline</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0518.Title.03">Just One Promise</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_1">Whoooa!
What is this place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_2">OH! I think this is the Crème Refuge that everyone\'s been telling me about!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_3">Wow... I must\'ve been stuck inside the Chamber of Freshest Cream for, like, a really long time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_4">It looks like all the residents stayed here in the refuge...? Wow, they\'re so hardy and tough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_5">I guess the frozen lands just kept getting colder while things here got warmer...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_6">What are these? They look like ice cubes and ice packs...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_7">How very interesting! But stuff like this won\'t be needed anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_8">To celebrate the restoration of Mount St. Crème, and for everyone to enjoy it to the max,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_9">I should clear out all the old stuff that\'ll remind folks of those warm and humid days!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2009_10">Okiedokes! Time for some cleaning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_1">*Gasp*
R-R-Rainbow Sherbet Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_2">Cherry Cream Muffin!!!
Hello!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_3">Have you been staying in the refuge too? How have you been, friend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_4">Things haven\'t been so great...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_5">I mean, sure, the refuge was a bit cooler than other places...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_6">And we didn\'t have to worry too much about moldy monsters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_7">But Fizzy and the cabal of sodas stirred up so much trouble...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_8">We were always desperate to find more ice packs...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_9">Yeah... It was pretty awful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_10">I... I don\'t ever want to see another ice pack again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_11">Huh? Wait a minute...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_12">There was a giant pile of ice packs and supplies here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_13">Where\'d they go? 
And when did this place become so clean?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_14">Heehee! Now that Mount St. Crème is back to normal, I decided to roll up my sleeves and do some cleaning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_15">The Crème Refuge doesn\'t need those supplies anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_16">And so... TA-DAAA!
Cleaning up was an amazing idea, wasn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_17">By the way, Cherry Cream Muffin...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_18">I was also thinking we should complete these changes to the refuge by holding a party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_19">Wanna help me with the party prep?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_20">Besides! No one said that this place needs to stay as a refuge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2009_21">We should make this a happy place! It\'ll be the opening of a new chapter for new memories!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0053_22">That sounds perfect, Rainbow Sherbet Cookie! It\'s just what this place needs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_1">Wooow...
This is... so... AWESOME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_2">It\'s hard to believe that this place was a refuge and shelter just moments ago!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_3">It\'s so colorful and shiny!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_4">Heehee! Quite the job well done, right?! I\'m glad you like it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_5">But we\'re not ready for the party to start juuust yet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_6">We\'re gonna need some bright lights...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_7">And maybe put up some more decorations near that empty space?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_8">OOOH! We should decorate that space with lots of rainbows!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_9">That sounds lovely!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_10">Once we\'re done with the decorations, we can start inviting everyone here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_11">Who do you want to invite first, Cherry Cream Muffin? Anyone come to mind?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_12">Well, there\'s Breadan, and then... Hmmm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2009_13">I\'m going to invite Snow Crystal Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0053_14">Aaah...? Snow Crystal Cookie...? Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_1">!!!
The refuge is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0041_2">Is this really the refuge?! It looks so different!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_3">Er, it kinda looks like the party hasn\'t started yet though...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_4">Haha! C\'mon in, friends! The refuge is almost unrecognizable, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_5">Oooh! Everyone\'s here!
Well...? What do you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_6">From now on, this place will no longer be remembered as a lukewarm shelter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_7">Rainbow Sherbet Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_8">OH! Hi there, Snow Crystal Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_9">I\'m so glad you\'re here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_10">Mount St. Crème is back to normal! It\'s time to celebrate!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_11">Sure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0039_12">Hehe... Take a look at Snow Crystal Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0040_13">I\'m not quite sure if Snow Crystal Cookie is happy or angry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_14">Teehee! Snow Crystal Cookie! I haven\'t seen you this happy in a long, long time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_15">Indeed. I am pleased that this place no longer needs to be considered a refuge.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2008_16">It is something worth celebrating.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0053_17">HAHAHA! Exactly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2009_18">What\'re we waiting for then? Let the party begin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2009_1">Wow... This really is the perfect party.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2009_2">I know what\'ll make it even more perfect. A cake and some candles! Oh, and a wish!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2009_3">I wish... for the blessing upon Mount St. Crème to last forever and ever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Npc.0039_4">And no more moldy monsters...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2008_5">May Madam First Cream Cookie\'s calling be fulfilled.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SS11_SQ5_POR1_Cookie.2009_6">I also wish for everyone in Mount St. Crème to be fresh, crispy, and happy!!!</string>
