  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Wow...! What is this place?
It\'s so awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">It appears to some sort of grand temple?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">There has to be a Cookie of the First Batch here... right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">*Sniff sniff*
Is it just me, or do I smell something yummy?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">Is someone cooking...? Maybe we can ask them about the First Batch...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">That sounds like a good idea! Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">Look! There\'s some sort of big group over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_8">There\'s so many of them...! And look at how much food there is too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">This certainly raises our chances of finding someone who knows about the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0061_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Hello there!
I\'m GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">We\'re looking for a Cookie of the First Batch! Can we ask you some questions?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0061_13">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">They\'re... really concentrating on eating.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">It almost feels rude to interrupt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">What do we do? Should we ask one more time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Erm... HELLO THERE! My name\'s GingerBrave! We\'re looking for a Cookie of the FIRST BATCH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0061_18">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_19">Wow... Not even a flinch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Erm... Should I keep asking until they listen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">I believe it\'d just be a waste of time. We should move elsewhere and ask-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_22">Deary, deary! What is the meaning of this commotion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_23">Who\'s that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_24">A Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">... Suspicious.
How very suspicious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">First Grain Cookie, allow me to take care of this. These outsiders may pose a threat and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_3">Deary, deary me.
There\'s no need, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">They do not seem to be bad Cookies or hiding any ill intentions. In fact, they may be wayward wanderers who have sought the wisdom of our temple.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Oh, my name\'s not Bad Cookie, it\'s GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">And these are my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">My name\'s GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">And I am Wizard Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">It\'s nice to meet you... I\'m... Strawberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_10">Greetings, everyone.
I am First Grain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_11">Welcome to the Temple of Abundance, my new friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">This is a temple? Of abundance? What\'s abundance...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">You are not familiar with the Temple of Abundance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_14">This grand temple and its lands are blessed with an eternal harvest, where grains and cereals flourish all year round!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_15">A sacred haven where hunger has been replaced with satiation!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">How could one be so unaware of this marvelous place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">Oooh! This place sounds a lot like Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">\"A land of eternal abundance\", eh?
This place sounds fascinating...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">Now, now. Let\'s not get too carried away here, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_20">Oh me oh my, where are my manners? You must be exhausted from your journey! Let us treat you to a warm and hearty meal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">Thank you, but before that, we must ask you something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">Oh! That\'s right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_23">Oh? What is it you wish to ask?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">We\'re looking for Cookies of the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Yeah! We need to find them to help a friend remember things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">So... If there\'s anything you know about the First Batch... It\'d really be helpful...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">The mood has... suddenly shifted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_8">Haha... Haaa...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_9">I knew this would happen.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_10">You foul, villainous worms!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">Huh...?! Wh-wh-what?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">We are done here, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">It is time for you to leave, outsiders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_14">Moletatoes! Toss out these scraps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0063_15">Toss\'em out! Toss\'em out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0064_16">Out! OUT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">Hey?! What\'s the big idea?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_18">Eeep! Stop pushing us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_1">... What just happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_2">We got... kicked out.
Did we say something wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_3">This is bad...! How are we going to find out
about the First Batch now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Hmmm... Oh, look!
Maybe we can ask that group over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">Let\'s go and ask them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0061_6">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Hello! Excuse me,
but have any of you heard of the First-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0061_8">Begone, pest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">GAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_10">GingerBrave! Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">I\'m fine, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0061_12">I grabbed it first!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0062_13">Hey! Hands off! I was eating that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0061_14">Get away from me!
This is MY food!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">They just started fighting...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_16">I don\'t think anyone can hear us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_17">There is something strange
about this so-called \"temple\"...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_18">It\'s like no one really wants to
talk or listen to us at all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_19">Could it be that... Maybe no one\'s heard of
the First Batch here at all...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_20">Hm... OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_21">Is something the matter, GingerBright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_22">There\'s someone
outside that window!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_23">A Cookie...?
Oh, and they are not eating any of the food either.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_24">I don\'t know what they\'re doing out there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_25">But I get the feeling that...
maybe we should ask them about the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_26">We\'ve got nothing to lose! Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_1">At this rate, the land is really gonna end up as... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Hello there! Whatcha doin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_3">\?!
Wh-Wh-Who are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">I\'m GingerBrave, and these are my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_5">Hi! I\'m GingerBright!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">And I\'m... Strawberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">I am... Wait, are we going to get kicked out once we\'re done introducing ourselves?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">Heehee, how silly! You should still say hello!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Well, yes, of course I will.
My name is Wizard Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">What\'s your name? And can we ask what you\'re doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_11">My name is Chickpea Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_12">I am attempting to preserve the soil\'s last traces of moisture.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_13">But, if I may, you mentioned something about being dismissed from somewhere?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">We were in the temple and asked the folks there if they knew anything about the Cookies of the First Batch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">But then they just started accusing us of being villains and kicked us out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_16">Ah? Haha, I presume it was Buckwheat Cookie who expelled you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_17">Well, I have not heard of this so-called \"First Batch\", but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">There is, without a doubt, a young Cookie who is not from these lands, residing in the temple.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_19">The Cookie is referred to as Yummers. Though rather average in appearance, the young one has a bottomless pit for a stomach! With quite an adorable demeanor as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_20">Maybe... this Yummers is...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">An average looking Cookie...? It\'s more than likely Yummers could belong to the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_22">Wait, so there IS a Cookie of the First Batch in the temple! But why\'d they kick us out?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_23">... Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_24">Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_25">The Temple of Abundance was once a grand community.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_26">All of us would work and toil the lands, but no matter how difficult and sweaty things were, the harvest was always worth it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_27">Alas, those days are now a memory of the past.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_28">The Temple of Abundance has changed, and not for the better.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">Why? What happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_30">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_31">Once again, because of Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Ah, so the one who scolded us is named Buckwheat Cookie, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Who is she...? Did she do something to the temple...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_3">We were originally... friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_4">As children, we were rather close. She would always be scheming a new prank to pull on the adults.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_5">We were caught and disciplined on many occasions, but we always ended up laughing together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_6">But one day, without warning, Buckwheat Cookie\'s demeanor changed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">How so?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_8">She used to be quiet and timid, but she slowly became more vibrant...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_9">Buckwheat Cookie then started to step forward and lead the others. Everything was fine until...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">Until...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_11">Her ambition. It slowly grew into something akin to greed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">What do you mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_13">First Grain Cookie has always cherished Yummers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_14">She was always fond of Cookies with a robust appetite. And Yummers is rather endearing, so much so that even we grew to adore him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_15">But I caught a glimpse of something in Buckwheat Cookie\'s eyes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_16">Originally, she did not give much thought to Yummers. But she suddenly spent more time with him and First Grain Cookie, almost every waking moment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_17">She then fell into a habit of suspicion and doubt, always on guard for something. Perhaps she had heard a rumor about Yummers being in danger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">And now... I believe that brings us here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_19">So her demeanor just changed like that? For what reason?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_20">I am at a loss for an answer. Though I\'ve tried to ask her directly, she simply refuses to meet with me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_21">But things were going rather well, which is why I dismissed my own concerns...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_22">What sort of concerns?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_23">Ever since Buckwheat Cookie took a more active role in managing the farms, the crops have been growing at an exponential rate.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_24">The harvest was bountiful beyond our wildest dreams. They grew so abundant that no one had to worry about working the farms ever again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">But that sounds like good news!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_26">I thought so too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_27">Until it became a reality... virtually everyone stopped working on the land.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_28">As a result, the land is dying... The soil\'s nutrients have all but dried out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_29">I\'ve tried on multiple occasions to warn the others of this perilous situation, but they brushed me aside. They\'ve become too accustomed to feasting day in and day out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_30">The Temple of Abundance is no longer the joyful and pleasant land I grew up in.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_31">It is now a den of greed and sloth...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_32">That\'s... a lot to take in.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_33">... How can we help?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_34">... Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_35">I... Wait, what?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">It\'s the right thing to do! You need help, and we\'re willing to lend you a hand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">And of course... right on cue, GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_3">If Yummers is the Cookie we\'re looking for, we\'d be helping each other, right...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Heehee! Admit it, Wizard Cookie! You wanted to say we\'d help before GingerBrave this time, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">What?! I don\'t- WHAT?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_6">What an odd bunch of Cookies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_7">We\'ve met just moments ago... I am still a stranger to them, yet they offer assistance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_8">And yet... I am truly, desperately in need of some help.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_9">... Thank you. I will strive to repay this debt as soon as I am able.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_10">If you\'re willing, shall we move elsewhere and discuss things in more detail?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Sure! So... where we goin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_12">... To find Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">So... The warning was true.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_14">Outsiders seek Yummers...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_15">Perhaps my own contribution to spreading rumors of hostile outsiders will serve useful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">This Cookie is mine... And they will pave my path to the top...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_17">Those pesky outsiders have been dealt with for now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_18">Which gives me the opportunity to begin...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">D-D-Did you hear that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_20">I had a rising suspicion Buckwheat Cookie was plotting something...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">Who was she referring to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">SSSHHH! Let\'s keep our eyes and ears open for now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">The concoction from Madam First Egg Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">It truly has served wonders... making the crops thrive and grow at a remarkable pace.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">And it only cost the next few years\' worth of the soil\'s nutrients.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_4">...!!!
It can\'t be... Buckwheat Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_5">I... I really hoped my suspicions were merely nonsense but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Did she say, \"First Egg Cookie\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">First Egg Cookie and Buckwheat Cookie... What\'re they up to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_8">These lands will become arid and barren in just a few days.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_9">And as soon as I can take Yummers away with this sigil from First Egg Cookie,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_10">I can finally be rid of that nuisance, Chickpea Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_11">Me? A nuisance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_12">Buckwheat Cookie... what have you become...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">Aaah, there you are, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_14">Madam First Grain Cookie?! Forgive me, I-I-I did not hear you approach.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_15">Time and time again I have heard from our neighbors that you\'ve taken a keen interest in caring for the crops.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_16">Such an endeavor must be a heavy burden for just one Cookie... which is why I\'ve come to aid you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_17">M-M-Milady, it is hardly a task which you-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_18">Deary, deary! Together, we can bring forth the most bountiful harvest in the history of the temple!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_19">I, but... It\'s such a menial task that I can perform without-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_20">No, Buckwheat Cookie. I simply wish to provide aid as I am very grateful for your hard work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_21">I have yearned to see my dream become a reality. A world absent of hunger, where everyone lives without concern.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_22">Oh me oh my! Buckwheat Cookie, what is that in your hand...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_23">OH! An insect!!! Haha, haha, haha...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2012_24">Crumbs... I will have to retrieve it later...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">Ow ow ow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_26">Are you alright, GingerBrave?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">Yeah, I\'ll be okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_28">I found that thing Buckwheat Cookie threw!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_29">What is this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_30">Isn\'t that the sigil she received from First Egg Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_1">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_2">This artifact does not
belong to First Grain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_3">It\'s somehow, similar to her presence...
but entirely different...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_4">Do you think... we should show this
to First Grain Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_5">Maybe she\'ll listen
to us this time...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Or she might scold us for
bringing it and kick us out again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">Well... What\'ve we got to lose?
We might as well try!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_8">Hey! The two of them
are starting to leave...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">And Buckwheat Cookie
is coming this way?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_10">We need to hide! HIDE NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_12">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_13">Chickpea Cookie!
We need to go... and quickly...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_14">... Okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_15">I wanted to believe you...
believe in you, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_16">Let us depart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_17">Odd... I am quite certain I threw it
in this direction, but it\'s not here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_18">And this is...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_19">Of course it\'s you again...
Chickpea Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_20">You\'ve become quite
the pest, haven\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_21">Very well.
Two can play at that game.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_22">Whatever it is you\'re planning,
I will put an end to it once and for all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH2_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2012_23">After all, I was always
the craftier of us two.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Phew... We made it out...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">And we didn\'t get caught!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">So... are we going to meet First Grain Cookie now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_4">Yes! Madam First Grain Cookie\'s chambers are just over there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_5">She should be there right now-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_6">Why, yes I am.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_7">I have just returned moments ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_8">But tell me, Chickpea Cookie, these strangers with you are...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_9">I distinctly remember they were dismissed from the temple grounds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Wait! You have to hear us out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_11">I \"have to\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">Perhaps you too wish to tell me that Yummers is in danger?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">Just as Buckwheat Cookie warned-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">No, you\'ve got it all wrong!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">It\'s Buckwheat Cookie herself! She\'s the one who\'s putting Yummers in danger!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_16">I beg your pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_17">Madam, I found it hard to believe myself. And I know that you will also refuse to believe it, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">This Cookie speaks the truth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">And am I to simply trust such an accusation on a whim?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">We have proof! LOOK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_1">What is it that I am looking at...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Buckwheat Cookie had this in her hands!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">We heard her say that she was going to take Yummers to First Egg Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">First... Egg Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_5">Yes. Apparently this item in question is what connects Buckwheat Cookie to First Egg Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_6">And the concoction she used on the fields... It saps nutrients from the soil. That too was given to her by the one called First Egg Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_7">... Is this true?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_8">And yet... There is no reason for Buckwheat Cookie to have known, let alone learned, of First Egg Cookie\'s existence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_9">And these outsiders do not seem like they are lying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_10">I shall admit... What you claim does seem feasible.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Really? You believe us?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">And yet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">I still see no true reason to trust you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_14">There is still the possibility that you are presenting me with false evidence. Or perhaps you\'ve forged this sigil to deceive me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">What? No, we wouldn\'t do-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_16">Buckwheat Cookie has diligently strived to bring a golden age to the Temple of Abundance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_17">To discard the trust I have in her, to dismiss her efforts so far, based on the claims of outsiders...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">Madam... Are you truly pleased with what you\'ve seen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">I beg your pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_20">Do you truly believe the Temple of Abundance is still the grand community it once was?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_21">To be frank, do you genuinely feel that our temple, our lands are faring well?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_22">No one is working the land! The ground itself has grown arid and bleak!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_23">We once shared our harvests, but now we squabble and bicker to fill our plates, going so far as to covet the food of others!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_24">Is this truly... what you wanted, milady?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_25">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_1">Droughts are unbearable, and hunger is exponentially worse, almost torturous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_2">Friends and colleagues, wincing from hunger today, may only tremble in silence tomorrow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_3">The masses will fall and the land will cry out in tears of anguish and misery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">In desperation, I cried out and begged to see a world absent of hunger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0061_5">BACK OFF! Get your filthy hands away from my plate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0062_6">Get off of me or I\'ll crunch you into a pile of crumbs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0061_7">I GRABBED IT FIRST! Don\'t even think about looking at it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0063_8">Another fight?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0064_9">Again they fight! Again! Again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0063_10">Don\'t just stand there! Stop them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0064_11">Stop them! No, no, NO! Take away the food!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">Have I made the wrong choice, yet again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">Just like... long ago...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_14">No... And I had no knowledge of such sentiment until now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_15">Why was I not made aware of such a blight upon our lands? I assumed Buckwheat Cookie was working for the better good...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_16">Despite her reassurances, I should have looked into everything personally...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_17">I have... failed. What have I done? Everything is my fault, once more...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">No, it\'s not!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">I...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">It\'s not your fault, First Grain Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">And, even if you think you made a mistake, you can still make things right starting now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_1">Please elaborate.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">We\'ve made a lot of friends along our way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Some of them became sad when their choices ended up putting a lot of folks in danger too, and they regretted every moment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">Ah! Rosemary Cookie and Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">There was also a big misunderstanding that just kept growing because of a mistake in the past.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">Marble Danish Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">And a Cookie who waited for a long, long time, enduring the pain of mold, waiting for his friend to return!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">I\'ve learned that everyone makes mistakes! And everyone struggles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">But you know what else I\'ve learned along the way? No one should ever give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Sometimes, the answer to fixing a mistake is simple! All it takes is reaching out and asking for help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">Words of wisdom, but will everything truly be amended, even if I were to ask for aid?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_13">Will assistance from you or anyone else restore the Temple of Abundance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">I don\'t know!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">But I won\'t stop helping until all of your friends are happy again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">He\'s absolutely right, hehe! It\'s up to you First Grain Cookie! Do you need a hand?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">We\'re here to help, if you need us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">So... I guess the speech is over. Wuddya say, First Grain Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">I... am unworthy of...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">Being worthy or unworthy doesn\'t matter when it comes to helping others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">And besides... That\'s not really GingerBrave\'s way of doing things.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_22">Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_23">Please... Aid me in my effort to restore balance and bring back the Temple of Abundance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_24">Please, help me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_25">Yes! We\'re happy to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_26">Our first step should be locating where Buckwheat Cookie is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_27">Do you know where she might be right now...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_28">At this time of day, it is most likely she is preparing a few snacks for Yummers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_29">Didn\'t Buckwheat Cookie say something about...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_30">You\'re right! Buckwheat Cookie is planning something about taking Yummers away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_31">Then we should make sure Yummers is safe first!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_32">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_33">So, er... Which way are we goin? Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_34">Never change, GingerBrave. Never change, my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_35">Follow me. Yummers is this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_1">Just a bit further.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_2">Yummers is currently residing
in my chambers. We will find him there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_3">And there is no doubt that
Buckwheat Cookie will also be present.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_4">Excuse me,
if I may ask a simple question?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_5">Of course.
What knowledge do you seek?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Earlier, you mentioned in passing that
you\'ve somehow made a mistake once more...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_7">I don\'t mean to pry, but did something
like this happen in the past before?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_8">Ah.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_9">Yes, there was.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_10">I was different than I am now when it happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_11">A prolonged drought
wrought havoc upon the lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_12">I employed my skills to alleviate
the pain of those who suffered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_13">At first, they were grateful. Their grimaces of pain
slowly changed into smiles of happiness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_14">As time passed, a group fueled by greed and ambition
wished to harness my powers for their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_15">The more their greed festered,
the more my life was put in danger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_16">I still remember their faces...
Corrupted and deformed by sheer greed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_17">That fearful memory made me keep my distance...
and ultimately delegate my own
responsibilities to Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_18">I feared that engaging directly with the denizens
of the temple would ultimately lead to chaos...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_19">Now, I realize that these were excuses.
The truth is... I was merely a coward.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_20">Milady... I... I had no idea...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_21">I hope I haven\'t rained down a depressing storm
upon your minds with my tale.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_22">Ah. We\'ve arrived to my chambers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_23">Let\'s go in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_24">STOP, BUCKWHEAT COOK-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_25">There\'s no one here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_26">There\'s no one here at all!
Where has Yummers gone?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_27">The place is empty...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_28">Melted ice cream! Did she somehow
figure out what we\'re planning?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_29">This is most concerning...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_30">Fret not, my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_31">Milady?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_32">I am First Grain Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_33">And I am the one who presides over this temple...
The Keeper of the Temple of Abundance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_34">And I welcome all those who
wish to enter our sacred lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_35">But I can also forbid those with
treacherous minds from leaving.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Event.0002_1">Brkwt Cookie, whr wu goin? (Buckwheat Cookie, where we going?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">Chew and swallow your food entirely before speaking...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">Little lumpy, doughy brat...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_4">It doesn\'t matter... You may attempt to chase me down, outsiders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">But I am one step ahead of everyone. Nothing can ruin my plans.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_6">Madam First Egg Cookie will be pleased with my results.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">I know she will! She will shower praise upon me, share the truth of how much she trusted in me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_8">Yes, there\'s no doubt about it. And once everything is over, that pesky Chickpea Cookie will never again-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Event.0002_9">Brkwt Cookie. (Buckwheat Cookie.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_10">What now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Event.0002_11">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_12">!!!
You\'ve got food all over your mouth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">Come here! Let me wipe it off for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Event.0002_14">Nr, luk ower der! Thw wah if blrcked! (No, look over there! The way is blocked!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_15">What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">What... What is the meaning of this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_17">Oh deary, deary. Precisely the perfect question to ask, my friend. What IS the meaning of this, hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_18">H-H-How...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">This ends here and now, Buckwheat Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">Let Yummers go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_21">Hmph... I dreaded resorting to this option but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_22">I will just have to get through all of you! No one will stop me from uniting with First Egg Cookie, with Yummers in tow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_23">Oooh? Deary, deary... Did you really think I was that much of a pushover?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2011_24">... Are you ready? Are you truly set on defying me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2012_25">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_26">Buckwheat Cookie, you were always the sly and crafty one... that is, until you always got caught.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2013_27">Looks like some things never change!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">*Huff puff*
No... It can\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">Is this... the taste of... defeat...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">First Egg Cookie... has forsaken me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">You believed First Egg Cookie would magically appear to aid you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_5">When in fact, she was using you as a mere means to an end.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_6">Perhaps, by now, you\'ve already realized that taking Yummers to her would not be rewarded with whatever she promised you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">No, but she... It can\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2011_8">You shall not see the next harvest. Guards!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_9">Madam First Grain Cookie! Wait, please!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_10">I wish to speak with Buckwheat Cookie! I must hear her own account!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_11">*Tsk* Taking the opportunity to finally gloat, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_12">... Far from it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_13">I wanted to ask you something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_14">Oh, I see you\'ve been hanging onto this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_15">I was wondering where I had left it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">Cut the small talk and ask your question, you big oaf.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_17">I didn\'t mean to spy on you, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">Do you... hate me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2012_19">Hate is all I have for you, you fool.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2013_20">Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">You... you haven\'t changed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">Whatever you had to do, you\'d succeed without breaking a sweat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">On the other hand, I had to endure buckets of sweat and tears to match a fraction of your success.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_4">You made things too easy, always smiling like some buffoon and bragging about how you did this and that and on and on, even when I was drowning in my own tears!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">... Everyone looked up to you, looked for you when they needed to. No one even mentioned me or recognized my efforts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_6">You don\'t know what that\'s like.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">I... I just wanted to be seen and heard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_8">... I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_9">My feelings for you haven\'t changed... I always liked you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_10">I always wanted to become a Cookie and friend that you could be proud of.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_11">I always wanted to be there with you, which made me work twice as hard to earn that spot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_12">... And that, old friend, is why I despise you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_13">It\'s okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_14">I\'ll always be there for you, no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_15">I know you\'ll have a change of heart. I don\'t know exactly when, but I know you will, and we can be close friends once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">You\'ll never be able to see that day... because I hate you. And I will keep hating you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_17">Are you sure about that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_18">Remember this bracelet? You made it for me, the very first thing you crafted with your own hands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_19">You said it\'s a gift, a sign of our friendship.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_20">I\'ve always cherished this bracelet, come rain or shine. It\'s my greatest treasure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_21">It\'s also a reminder of the memories we\'ve made.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_22">You still cherish those days to some extent, don\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_23">That\'s why you kept onto this. Deep down, you still remember the good times.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_24">Well, at least, that\'s what I think. And I believe in you, friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_25">Because, that\'s what we are, friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2012_26">*Scoff*
GUARDS! What\'re you doing? Hurry up and take me away from this nonsensical rabble!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0063_27">Take\'em away! Take\'em away! To the cell! To the cell!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0064_28">Cell! Cell! To the cell!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_29">I think we\'ve just witnessed something amazing beyond measure here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_30">That was a really touching conversation, Chickpea Cookie! From the heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2013_31">Ahem...! Well, we still have work left to do. We need to return the Temple of Abundance back to normal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_32">Oh ho! Then I have the perfect idea. Perhaps we should retrieve the old farming equipment?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_33">Look at all this DUST!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_34">My, oh my! Deary, deary! This equipment hasn\'t been used for far too long...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">*ACHOO!*
*Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_36">GingerBrave! Watch your step...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_37">You almost stepped onto and broke this... thing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_38">Oh? What is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_39">Obviously, I don\'t know either. We just got here moments ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_40">Some sort of slab with writing on it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_41">Well, well, well! This is quite the relic of the past!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_42">It is a stone tablet... which I personally carved and wrote in ages past.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_43">Cool! So this is your writing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_44">It is. I wrote it when I finally realized I had become a Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_45">I also knew that, somehow, my memory was fragmented with gaps in between...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_46">I wrote down as much as I could possibly remember.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_47">Wait... Did you just misspeak? You said, \"You became a Cookie\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_48">Oh, deary me, did I not say? Is my memory failing once more, hehe?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2011_49">I... was originally a Witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">A Witch?! What? First Grain Cookie... wait, what?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">Why am I getting goosebumps all of a sudden?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2013_3">Madam First Grain Cookie... Are you saying...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_4">It was far, far too long ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_5">Many of us witches had gathered from all corners of the world, each with our own purpose and motive.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_6">We began to bake living Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_7">They were... the Cookies of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_8">They were simple and honest to instinct, but instilled with immense portions of Life Energy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_9">They did not depend on Life Potions to move, talk, and think for themselves... just like our very own Yummers here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Event.0002_10">*Nom nom... nom?*
Me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">Then... GingerDozer is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_12">Yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">Amazing... Then it means that GingerDozer is not the young Cookie we thought him to be!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_14">Wait, so he\'s like... one of the oldest Cookies in the castle?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_15">Since the First Batch, we witches baked Cookies with passion and diligence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_16">We wanted to create a happy world of Cookies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_17">Cookies living of their own free will, strong and resolute.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_18">And, one day, a certain Cookie was baked and brought into the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_19">One of fiery courage and an iron-willed heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_20">Teehee! That kinda sounds like you, GingerBrave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_21">My memories seem to have dissipated like dust in the wind beyond that point.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_22">But I have a vague memory... of an incident.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_23">An incident where the witches, including myself, somehow became Cookies... and we\'ve been living alongside you ever since.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">Wow... But, why did that happen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2011_25">I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_1">My memories surrounding
that event is... hazy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_2">Whenever I try to remember, I am filled with
raw emotion, unpleasant and disturbing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_3">And the more I try to remember,
the more painful it becomes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_5">Then... I guess you just don\'t
try too hard to remember!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">Who knows? Maybe, one of these days,
while wandering the castle...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_7">You might remember
something out of the blue!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">I\'m pretty sure you\'ll remember things
if you give it time, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_9">Perhaps.
However, I cannot leave this place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_10">If I were to leave, the Temple of Abundance
and its surrounding lands would wither away
to nothing but dust and crumbs.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_11">Plus, I\'ve still much work to do...
I must restore the parched land and replenish the soil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_12">No longer must anyone suffer
due to my actions, or shall I say, my inaction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">I see... Perhaps it\'s something similar
to what happened to Mount St. Crème
when First Cream Cookie left.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Hmmm... There\'s gotta be
something we can... OH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">We can come back here and share
whatever we might\'ve learned with you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_16">I\'m sure we\'ll be able to
find something out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">After all, whatever we learn
just might help restore your memories,
First Grain Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_18">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_19">Deary, deary... Thank you, young one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_20">Yes... This Cookie is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_21">Then I shall propose an offer as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_22">Whenever you are weary and worn out,
you may return to recuperate your strength here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_23">I shall personally prepare
a feast in your honor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_24">Please, take Yummers with you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_25">And do return after your
adventures beyond the horizon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_26">Go, explore what life
has to offer by your own volition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_27">And most of all... be brave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_28">Haha! Thanks!
We\'ll be back one day! It\'s a promise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_29">Teehee!
Thanks, and see you again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_30">Take care of yourself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_31">We hope the temple...
will be restored soon...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_32">Goodbye... young ones.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_33">I hope we can meet again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_34">Well then... Deary, deary me,
we\'ve so much work to do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2011_35">Shall we begin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA01_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2013_36">Yes, Madam First Grain Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Journal.Ep04.Ch03.SQuest09.Summary">The Cookies finally meet First Cream Cookie! But before they could rejoice, the temperature controller has gone out of control again!</string>
