  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR1_Cookie0058_1">WAAAH! It\'s so scary!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR1_Cookie0042_2">Calm yourself, Onion Cookie. Tell me, what is troubling you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR1_Cookie0058_3">There\'s a voice...! There\'s a voice mumbling and humming out the window...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR2_Cookie0042_4">Fear not. It is appears to be Vampire Cookie, who seems to heading home in a cheery mood with grape juice in hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR3_Cookie0058_5">Then... then what\'s that other smaller voice out there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR4_Cookie0042_6">Ah, it seems that Strawberry Cookie is whispering to herself to muster up the courage to walk down the path during the night.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR5_Cookie0058_7">Oh... Erm, Blackberry Cookie? If I hear any more voices, can I ask you to check and see what it is again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_1_POR6_Cookie0042_8">Of course. My door is always open to you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0058_1">WAAAH! IT\'S SO SCARY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0042_2">Hush, Onion Cookie. It will be okay. What is troubling you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0058_3">Another voice...! It\'s roaring and yelling outside the window...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0042_4">Oh? Ah! Zombie Cookie is singing a tune in a very cheerful manner... yet highly out-of-tune.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0058_5">And there\'s another one... someone cackling over and over again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0042_6">It seems GingerBright is in very high spirits and is on her way to meet a friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0058_7">Oh... I guess everything\'s okay then. If I hear any more voices, can I come here again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_2_POR1_Cookie0042_8">Of course. My door is always open to you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_1">WAAAH! I\'m so scared...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_2">Do not fret, Onion Cookie. You are safe here. What is troubling you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_3">Did you hear something growling...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_4">No...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_5">Ah, perhaps some angered hissing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_6">No...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_7">I see. Then what has frightened you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_8">Blackberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_9">Yes, I am listening.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_10">No matter how much I cry... why does everyone pretend not to hear me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_11">...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_12">It\'s like... you\'re the only one who can hear me, Blackberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0058_13">That\'s what scared me this time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_14">Onion Cookie. If you are scared, you may sleep in my room tonight.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_15">*Sniffle*
Really...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0042_3_POR1_Cookie0042_16">Yes. This room should be quiet enough for you to sleep without hearing any strange voices.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_1">"And then, the scared Cookie wasn\'t scared anymore and lived happily ever after... The end."</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_2">Wow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_3">What a nice book... I wish I could be like the main character too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_4">Going on adventures... Being happy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_5">Making new friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_6">I... I guess I can try...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0058_7">I... I\'m going to go on an adventure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0023_8">Hehehe...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_1_POR1_Cookie0023_9">An adventure? Well, well! This oughta be fun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_1">I\'ve packed my Onion Rabbit... my book... and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_2">Oh, what else do I need...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_3">This is already so difficult...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0023_4">Pssst! Crayons to scribble on ancient temples!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_5">Oh, right... Crayons...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_6">Wait... w-w-who said that? What was that voice...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0023_7">Khehehe...! It was...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_8">G-G-G-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0058_9">GHOOOST!
WAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0023_10">A ghost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_2_POR1_Cookie0023_11">NO! I\'m not a ghost! I\'m Devil Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_1">GOOO AWAY! WAAAH! LEAVE ME ALONE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_2">GAH! Wait, will you just-
OW! Why does that Onion Rabbit doll hurt so much?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_3">GO AWAY!
I don\'t like adventures any more! I don\'t like ghooosts!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_4">WAAAHHH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_5">Aaand... she just ran to hide in the closet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_6">What was she talking about?! How can anyone mistake me, ME as a ghost? The nerve...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_7">And above all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_8">I\'m not the ghost here! The real ghost is in the closet! It\'s not me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0042_9">What is the meaning of all this noise? What is happening?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_10">*Sob, sob* There\'s a ghost! I heard and saw a ghost!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0042_11">A ghost? Excuse me, but allow me to check for myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_12">EEK! Someone\'s coming...! I gotta hide!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0042_13">Hm... I do not see anything out of the ordinary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0042_14">Just in case... I will hang this special poster from Angel Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0023_15">HMPH! That meddling Angel Cookie is ruining my plans again...! I need to get out of here, and quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0042_16">Do not worry, everything will be okay. You are safe here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_17">*Sob, sniffle*
Thank you, Blackberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_18">I didn\'t get to go on an adventure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0058_3_POR1_Cookie0058_19">But having Blackberry Cookie nearby makes me happier than any fairy tale...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2011_1">So... What do you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2005_2">It seems the soil has lost most of its nutrients...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2005_3">But it is not entirely lost. There is still a chance your crops, with proper rotations, can replenish the soil naturally.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2011_4">I am relieved at such good news... and I hope it comes to pass soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2005_5">Do not worry. I brought some syrup from our garden. If we spray it evenly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2011_6">Oh me oh my!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2011_7">What is this miracle concoction you\'ve brought? It\'s as if the earth itself has been rejuvenated in the blink of an eye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2005_8">Indeed. Here, take this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_1_POR1_Cookie2011_9">What is it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_1">It is a special type of enchanted syrup that can only be found in our garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_2">Its magical properties can replenish withered plants and rejuvenate any kind of soil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2011_3">Deary, deary me! I could not accept such a wondrous and overwhelming gift...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_4">It is a gift from me to you. After all, it is why I have traveled all this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2011_5">You have my deepest thanks, Rosemary Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2011_6">I absolutely must repay your kindness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_7">I... It\'s not really necessary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2011_8">No, I insist!
AH! Here, come this way! Follow me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_9">Erm... First Grain Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2011_10">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_2_POR1_Cookie2005_11">What is... all this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_1">My gift to you! These here are various loaves of bread, baked with flour made from the grains we\'ve harvested recently.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_2">And these are an eclectic collection of sweets made from our very own crops.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_3">Oh, and don\'t forget these amazing Fruit Jellies. And these Vegetable Jellies too! They\'re absolutely-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_4">T-T-This is too much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_5">I can\'t... I can\'t carry all of these wonderful things back to the Syrup Garden on my own...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_6">Oh deary, deary! But I simply cannot send you back home empty-handed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_7">You\'ve given me such an amazing gift, and I really must insist!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_8">Erm... then... I choose that. This will more than suffice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_9">Just a few sweets? Is that truly enough?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_10">Yes. My younger sister will enjoy these very much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_11">She will be extremely happy with this portion. Thank you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_12">Ah, you have a sister! You must be very close.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_13">Well, deary, if you or your sister ever need more snacks and sweets, do not hesitate to come visit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_14">Yes, we shall. And if you need more syrup, just let me know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2011_15">Of course! I shall you next time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2011_3_POR1_Cookie2005_16">Thank you. I shall take my leave now. Goodbye!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011">First Grain Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Story">Amidst a boundless field of wheat shimmering like a golden sea underneath, a humble and noble Cookie opened her eyes. As warm and generous as the autumn earth, this Cookie soon became adored by all who met her.

First Grain Cookie is especially attuned to the needs of the hungry, and she is never able to turn a blind eye to their plight. With a graceful wave of her Grainstalk Staff, young sprouts burst forth from even the most arid of soil, and with a second wave, they become crops filled with the promise of a bountiful harvest. 

In the presence of First Grain Cookie, no one has to live with the fear and misery of hunger ever again.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Get">Welcome to the Temple of Abundance!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Random.01">As long as I am present, no one shall go hungry.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Random.02">Come, let us enjoy this autumn\'s harvest!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Random.03">For a prosperous harvest...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Random.04">My goodness! Such a bountiful harvest!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Random.05">This reminds me of... when I first met...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Winter shall pass and the crops will grow once more.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Monologue.Greeting">Greetings, {0}. Have you had lunch yet?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Skill.Name">Harvest Time</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.001">Grainstalk Staff</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.002">Blessed Straw Hat</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.003">Arm Cuff of Abundance</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.001.Story">The staff wielded by First Grain Cookie wherever she goes. It is deceptively heavy, perhaps because of the tightly packed grains contained within. Many Cookies cannot budge this simple staff, let alone wield it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.002.Story">During the sunrise of a long forgotten morning of the past, a straw hat was woven with utmost care, blade by blade, each coated with the clearest of dew. Its fresh green scent radiates the calming, gentle spirit of the earth.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2011.003.Story">An arm cuff crafted to honor the vast wheat fields of the Temple of Abundance. It is said to be imbued with a heartfelt wish for none to ever go hungry for all eternity, and that all will live in a world of warm smiles and abundant harvests.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2011">First Grain Cookie\'s Chamber of Plenitude</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2011.Story">Soft, warm sunlight gently seeps into every corner of First Grain Cookie\'s chambers. As the room becomes a cozy temperature, the air is filled with the nutty aroma of toasted grains. No matter how weary or hungry one might be, they will find comfort, fulfillment, and happiness in this room.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to First Grain Cookie\'s Chamber of Plenitude!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Grain Cookie\'s soul. When holding it up to your ear, you can hear the autumn winds swimming across a field of wheat.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2011.TeddyBear">First Grain Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0035.TeddyBear">Vampire Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0058.TeddyBear">Onion Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0042.TeddyBear">Blackberry Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2011.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Grain Cookie. Its eyes reassure you that a bountiful harvest is just around the corner.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0035.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Vampire Cookie. The toy seems to give off an aroma of grape juice.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0058.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Onion Cookie. Standing close by makes you break into tears, but you can\'t help but give it a big hug!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0042.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Blackberry Cookie. When you gaze into its eyes, your concentration seems to grow exponentially.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0132.Season">Candy Apple Scarecrow</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0133.Season">Sour Apple Scarecrow</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0134.Season">Golden Apple Scarecrow</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0131.MissionBeginner">Fluffiest Cake Hound</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0132.Season.Story">This scarecrow emits a unique scent that can only be described as candy apples. Its sweet fragrance also contains a tinge of sourness to it, which is probably the reason why so many butterflies and sparrows flock to it. But why does the scarecrow smell so good in the first place? It\'s all due to the thin coat of caramel poured onto its apple head!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0133.Season.Story">This scarecrow\'s smile reminds you of late spring, when everything is looking forward to the warm summer. Despite having a sour apple for its head, there\'s no sign of any sourness to its demeanor! Somehow, its smile seems to grow with joy when it hears the laughter of children carried by the wind.</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0134.Season.Story">This scarecrow and its golden apple head seem to glisten under the midday light. If you listen closely, you can hear it snoozing as it basks in the warmth of the sun\'s rays. It\'s okay to take naps, friendly scarecrow, remember to take care! Your caramel coat might melt if you stay still for too long!</string>
  <string name="$Neighbor.0131.MissionBeginner.Story">This is the fluffiest Cake Hound you will ever find in your travels throughout the Witch\'s Castle. As it playfully wags its tail, followed by an endearing jump and skip, you can\'t help but want to give it the biggest hug you\'ve ever given. These adorable creatures usually roam the wilds, but can also be trained to live in harmony with Cookies. Perhaps this is why some can be found in certain corners of the Witch\'s Castle.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2011.Profile">First Grain Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Season.2011.SeasonComplete.Profile">Completed First Grain Collection</string>
  <string name="$Season.2011.SeasonComplete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the First Grain Collection. Thanks to your efforts, the Temple of Abundance has completed a record harvest that enriches, not just the belly, but the soul!</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch1_sq1.Summary">Our friends have traveled to the Temple of Abundance. They ask the whereabouts of a Cookie of the First Batch, but find no answers. Just then... a certain Cookie approaches them.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch1_sq2.Summary">First Grain Cookie seems to be a gentle and kind Cookie. GingerBrave and friends ask her if she knows anything about the Cookies of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch1_sq3.Summary">First Grain Cookie\'s demeanor turns cold and distant at the mention of the First Batch. Was it something we said?</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch1_sq4.Summary">Just like that, our friends were kicked out for no apparent reason. The Cookies begin to ask another group the same question, but everyone seems too preoccupied with eating... Then, in the distance, the Cookies spot someone who isn\'t eating!</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch2_sq1.Summary">Thanks to Chickpea Cookie, our friends learn that there is indeed a Cookie of the First Batch within the temple. They wish to learn more about the temple\'s history and happenings.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch2_sq2.Summary">It seems that the culprit behind the temple\'s recent changes is none other than Buckwheat Cookie. After hearing Chickpea Cookie\'s plight, our friends decide to bring peace back to the Temple of Abundance.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch2_sq3.Summary">The crew and Chickpea Cookie decide to eavesdrop on Buckwheat Cookie... and they figure out something dire and sinister indeed.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch2_sq4.Summary">Our heroes learn that Buckwheat Cookie has joined forces with First Egg Cookie! They manage to get their hands on a sigil supposedly belonging to First Egg Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch2_sq5.Summary">The Cookies scramble to escape before Buckwheat Cookie can discover them. But she soon realizes that someone has been spying on her...</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch3_sq1.Summary">First Grain Cookie grants a brief audience to GingerBrave and friends once more. They tell her the truth about Buckwheat Cookie, but it seems First Grain Cookie is hesitant to accept their testimony.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch3_sq2.Summary">Despite having been shown the sigil, First Grain Cookie still hesitates to accept our friends\' warnings. Then, Chickpea Cookie steps in and asks her how she truly feels about the Temple of Abundance\'s current state.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch3_sq3.Summary">Chickpea Cookie\'s words seem to have resonated with First Grain Cookie as she takes a closer look at the temple and its denizens. Seeing them fight for food helps her realize this is not what she wished for.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch3_sq4.Summary">GingerBrave, GingerBright, Strawberry Cookie, and Wizard Cookie are all willing to help First Grain Cookie restore peace to the Temple of Abundance. It\'s time to stop Buckwheat Cookie\'s schemes!</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch3_sq5.Summary">Our heroes are in hot pursuit of Buckwheat Cookie. On their way there, they listen to First Grain Cookie\'s tale... a recount of what happened in the past. A rather grim past...</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch4_sq1.Summary">The Cookies have finally found Buckwheat Cookie, who has also kidnapped Yummers! Have you no shame, Buckwheat Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch4_sq2.Summary">Buckwheat Cookie\'s sinister plot has been thwarted. Chickpea Cookie is eager to finally learn what drove her down such an evil path...</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch4_sq3.Summary">Chickpea Cookie is confident that Buckwheat Cookie can return to being the kind, gentle-hearted Cookie he remembers one day. Buckwheat Cookie departs and the Cookies must finally return the Temple of Abundance back to normal.</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch4_sq4.Summary">The Cookies find a tablet containing a memory of First Grain Cookie. They learn the true identity of First Grain Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$saga01_ch4_sq5.Summary">It\'s time to depart the Temple of Abundance. What else lies in wait in the quest to find more Cookies of the First Batch?!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.01">Temple Corridor</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.02">Vine-Choked Temple Corridor</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.03">Arid Field</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.04">Temple Warehouse</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.01.Story">Welcome to the Temple of Abundance, where the sun shines bright and the harvest is always plentiful! What new adventure await our friends here?!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.02.Story">The corridors of the temple have been blocked with strange vines! It looks like First Grain Cookie\'s powers are formidable!</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.03.Story">The land, once cared for and worked by all the temple\'s denizens, has become arid and drained of all nutrients. A certain Cookie prays earnestly for a way to save the soil.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.Saga01.04.Story">A warehouse used to store all sorts of farming equipment and valuables. Wait... Isn\'t it odd to house valuables in a warehouse? Nope! The equipment ARE the valuables!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.01">The Voice from Outside</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.02">The Voice Won\'t Stop</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.03">The Voice has Stopped</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.01.Summary">Onion Cookie is scared of the voices she hears outside her window. Blackberry Cookie reassures her that everything is fine.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.02.Summary">Onion Cookie has heard more voices this time! Blackberry Cookie manages to comfort Onion Cookie once more.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0042.Title.03.Summary">Onion Cookie returns to Blackberry Cookie, frightened by something else this time. And this time, it truly is a frightening thought...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.01">I\'m Going on an Adventure!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.02">Who Are You?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.03">Adventures are Scary!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.01.Summary">After reading a book and being inspired by its main character, Onion Cookie decides to depart on an adventure of her own! But someone is eavesdropping...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.02.Summary">Onion Cookie is startled by Devil Cookie\'s sudden appearance. Strangely, Devil Cookie is startled by Onion Cookie\'s sudden outburst of tears.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.03.Summary">Onion Cookie has mistaken Devil Cookie for a ghost. She asks Blackberry Cookie to check on things, just in case.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.01">Restoring the Soil</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.02">Rosemary Cookie\'s Gift</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.03">First Grain Cookie\'s Gift</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.01.Summary">On request, Rosemary Cookie has traveled to the Temple of Abundance. As a gift, she has brought a special vial of syrup to restore the soil\'s nutrients.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.02.Summary">First Grain Cookie is shocked at how effective Rosemary Cookie\'s syrup is. Insisting that she somehow repay this debt, she asks Rosemary Cookie to follow her.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2011.Title.03.Summary">First Grain Cookie tries to repay a gift with... too many gifts! Rosemary Cookie, surprised at First Grain Cookie\'s generosity, politely declines and just takes a single portion of snacks.</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.2011">First Grain Season Coins</string>
  <string name="$UX.Item.SeasonCoin.2011.Tooltip">Golden coins that resemble the grains of a bountiful harvest. These can only be obtained during the First Grain Season!</string>
  <string name="$Mailbox.S.BonusCoinMode.Title">Delivery of Missing BONUS Stage Coins</string>
  <string name="$Mailbox.S.BonusCoinMode.Desc">We apologize for the inconvenience.</string>
