  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.001">Sugary Cloud Canopy Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.002">Dreamy Galaxy Starchart</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.003">Conductor\'s Office Desk</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.004">Train Cabin Window</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.005">Meteor Shower Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.006">Galactic Stardust Flooring</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.007">Star &amp; Moon Clock</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.008">Train Cabin Seating</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.009">Sleepy Starry Cushion</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.010">Conductor\'s Coat Rack</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.011">Twinkling Garland</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.012">Luggage Shelf</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.013">Star Jelly Jar</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.014">Conductor\'s Certificates</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.015">Used Train Ticket Rug</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.001.Story">A bed as comfy as the softest sugar clouds. As you lie down, you can\'t help but feel as if you\'re floating in space, surrounded by a drape of twinkling stars. No matter how awake or tired, restless or exhausted, this bed is guaranteed to sweep you off to dreamland in a matter of seconds.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.002.Story">This panel has been engraved with all sorts of constellations and celestial bodies. It looks like someone has charted a very complex route through the stars and moons scattered throughout space. Where will this route take you?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.003.Story">A cup of tea, half-empty. A pile of old train tickets. A moonlight fountain pen with its lid open. The owner of this desk is either extremely busy or rather untidy... But today, it just looks like the conductor is lazing off and taking things slow...</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.004.Story">Open the curtains in your train compartment and you\'ll see a dazzling galaxy swimming in the void of space. With such a wondrous display of dancing stars and twinkling nebulae, a curtain to cover the window is certainly unnecessary!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.005.Story">It\'s a meteor shower! As an endless number of lights streak across the night sky, you can\'t help but wonder... Where are they going?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.006.Story">A floor that seems to magically contain the essence of an entire galaxy. If you stand on it, waves of light and stardust gently ripple out from your feet. This fantastic display of lights is so mesmerizing, you almost feel like you\'re floating in space!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.007.Story">A clock with four faces in the shape of stars and moons. What a nice find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.008.Story">Someone has ripped out the seating from a cabin! It\'s super comfy and classy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.009.Story">Someone is taking a deep, comfy nap on this cushion. Just looking at it makes you feel like you are home.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.010.Story">A coat rack that is already in use. It\'s no wonder who this belongs to!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.011.Story">A garland of stars, big and small. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.012.Story">A shelf with all sorts of luggage on it. Let\'s put this to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.013.Story">A jar full of Star Jellies! Yummy! Everyone loves Star Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.014.Story">An impressive collection of certificates and awards. What an amazing feat!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.015.Story">Is it an old rug or an old train ticket? Why not both? Let\'s put it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.001">Bountiful Hanging Patio Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.002">Autumn Hanging Patio Bed</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.003">Syrup Fairy Fountain</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.004">Golden Harvest Drawer</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.005">Two-Tiered Fruit Tray</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.006">Lotus Leaf Lamp</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.007">Wheat Stalk</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.008">Pile of Harvested Grains</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.009">Small Sunlit Window</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.010">Large Sunlit Window</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.011">Popped Corn Light</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.012">Rustic Popped Corn Light</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.013">Dried Wheatstalk Light</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.014">Lotus Leaf Pile</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.015">Sweet Syrup Bath</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.016">Wheatgrass Wall</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.017">Autumn Cloud Flooring</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.001.Story">Having been imbued with the blessing of abundance, this bed seems to emit a warm, golden glow. The fruits of labor and the gift of the harvest have been placed delicately nearby. It\'s said that, while lying down on this bed, a single bite of anything from the most recent harvest will satiate any hungry belly.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.002.Story">As you rest upon the bed and close your eyes, it begins to sway gently in the wind, as if by magic. Despite having a feast laid out before you, you feel as if leaving this bed will ruin your day.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.003.Story">The mythical syrup fairies are said to approach fertile lands and summon enchanted fountains of syrup. Inspired by such tales, this fountain has been crafted with the utmost care. The attention to details can be seen with the fairy\'s softly closed eyes, as if sleeping in eternal tranquility.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.004.Story">The inviting scene of freshly baked bread and the sweet aroma of popcorn is unbearably welcoming! No one can resist such amazing aromas! But the secret to these aromas can be found in First Grain Cookie\'s wheatgrass diffuser. Even so, try following your nose to the source of the fragrance and you might just discover a few hidden snacks here and there!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.005.Story">A lamp that also serves as a tray for fruit. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.006.Story">An old-fashioned lamp made with golden lotus leaves. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.007.Story">A decorative stalk of wheat. Let\'s put it somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.008.Story">A haphazard pile of grains from the recent harvest. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.009.Story">The sun\'s rays turn into a radiant golden glow as it passes through this window. Just looking at it makes you feel relaxed.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.010.Story">The sun\'s rays turn into a radiant golden glow as it passes through this window. Just sitting in front of it makes you feel cozy and comfy.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.011.Story">A ceiling light made from corn that was partially popped. It efficiently lights up any room it is installed in.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.012.Story">A ceiling light made from corn that was popped in the old-fashioned way. Looks scrumptious!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.013.Story">A ceiling made from decorative stalks of wheat. It\'s sure to bring your room a touch of rustic elegance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.014.Story">A pile of lotus leaves. Let\'s put it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.015.Story">A bath filled to the brim with syrup. Anyone would love to have one of these!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.016.Story">A wall designed to remember the bountiful harvests of the past. You can feel the warmth of the earth emitting from this wall.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2011.017.Story">Flooring with patterns of clouds that remind you of a sunset on an autumn day. The wave of clouds, scattered with the shape of grains here and there, remind you that your most recent harvest was made possible thanks to the blessing of abundance.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0573">Milky Way Cookie\'s Room of Stardust and Dreams</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0573.Story">Milky Way Cookie\'s room resembles the night sky, where stars and galaxies dance and glimmer in the void of space. When you enter, you hear the stars whisper and giggle. The room itself seems to beckon you to come join the fun in the world of dreams.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573">Milky Way Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Story">Take a handful of star powder gathered from all over the Milky Way Galaxy, illuminate it with delicate moonlight—and voila! Meet Milky Way Cookie, the Slumbering Moon\'s faithful servant and the conductor of the Sugarcloud Express that will take you to your sweetest dreams and back.

Don\'t be afraid and hop on: one sprinkle of Milky Way Cookie\'s star powder is enough for a colorful, vibrant dream-just like reality but better! Everything is possible in the World of Dreams, and accidents happen, too: every now and then, the train\'s floor disappears, and cars reshuffle randomly, leaving crowds of passengers in utter confusion. And right in the middle of the conductor\'s scheduled nap time! But professionalism never betrays, and there is no problem Milky Way Cookie can\'t sort out.

Colorful hair neatly tied with a Star Jelly, conductor\'s hat on, and choo choo! The Sugarcloud Express will deliver you to your dreamy destination according to the schedule. Just make a wish upon a twinkling star...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Random.01">Yawn... So where did I park my train...?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Random.02">Welcome aboard! Your dreams are waiting...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Random.03">What did you dream about last night?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Random.04">Mkay... Wanna go see the Milky Way?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Random.05">Let\'s go...! Somewhere no one has ever gone!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Get">Work\'s calling... To the World of Dreams!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Aw... I\'ve used up all my starshine!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0573.Monologue.Greeting">Yawn... Maybe YOU should drive the train today, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.Ceil.999">Milky Way Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0573.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Milky Way Cookie\'s Room of Stardust and Dreams!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.001">Ticket Punch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.002">Star Jelly Hairband</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.003">Starlight Whistle</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.001.Story">A punch used to verify passenger tickets. Wait a minute... is someone riding the train without a ticket?!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.002.Story">This special hairband was made by scooping up a handful of stardust and packing it tightly into the shape of a Star Jelly! It still twinkles and glows during the night!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0573.003.Story">A whistle imbued with a hint of starlight. You may think it sounds like a regular whistle, but it actually sounds like a whispering lullaby.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012">Buckwheat Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2013">Chickpea Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Npc.0061">Wheat Cleric</string>
  <string name="$Npc.0062">Barley Cleric</string>
  <string name="$Npc.0063">Moletato Captain</string>
  <string name="$Npc.0064">Moletato</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.Main">Fixing Up the Milky Way Express</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.01">A Broken Train and Troubled Conductor</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.02">Making Repairs</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.03">Once More Beyond the Stars</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.01.Summary">The Sugarcloud Express has broken down! Milky Way Cookie doesn\'t know where to start repairs, but the skilled(?) engineer, Radish Cookie, has an idea!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.02.Summary">Radish Cookie has, somehow, finally managed to fix the train. Though it took many twists and turns, Milky Way Cookie is ready to go... Huh? Where?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0573.Title.03.Summary">After exchanging a warm farewell, Milky Way Cookie departs! To where? To the World of Dreams, of course!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_1">Oh nooo... This is bad.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_2">I managed to escape those space pirates, but at what cost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_3">The train crashed and I have no idea where we are... I don\'t know if this place has enough scraps to help with repairs and... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">... Who\'re you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_7">My name\'s Milky Way Cookie. I\'m the conductor of the very, very special...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_8">Sugarcloud Express!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_9">Hm... Milky Way Cookie, huh? Doesn\'t seem like someone with ties to the Reaper...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">Lemme ask you this, Milky Way Cookie. Your train is broken down, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.0573_11">Yeah?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">HAHA! Then can I help fixing it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">Oh, where are my manners! My name\'s Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">I\'m an expert at inventing and repairing all sorts of things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_1">I... may have exaggerated my skills and expertise... This is more complicated than I thought!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_2">Yaaawn... How\'re the repairs going?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_3">GAH! They\'re going, erm, great! I\'m working at a good pace! Everything\'ll be done in no time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_4">EEP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_5">Heeey... You shouldn\'t just drop your pliers like that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">No, no, it was an accident... hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_7">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_8">Hmmm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_9">Oh! Was that the finishing touch? Everything seems to be working again?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">I think the pliers might have just dislodged some debris.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_11">And... that means...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">I fixed it! HAHA! I knew I could fix it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_13">Which means that I need to get moving! Thank you, Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">Don\'t mention it! It was a cinch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_2_POR1_Cookie.0573_15">But... where are you going?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_1">The World of Dreams, of course! This train was designed to travel between various dream worlds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">The World of Dreams?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_3">Yeah! It\'s quite a swell place, as long as you don\'t run into any pirates...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_4">But getting to travel and fly by the stars and galaxies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_5">There\'s nothing like it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">Wooow! That sounds AWESOME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_7">Maybe you\'ll get to ride along with me one day, Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_8">I promise to take you safely to your destination!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_9">Hope to see you soon! And if we can, let\'s meet up in the World of Dreams!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_10">Alright! Sounds like a plan! Take care of yourself, Milky Way Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_11">You too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.0573_12">Now then... CHOO CHOO! Off we go! Ready to depart all thanks to Radish Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_13">Wow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_14">That\'s a really fast train...! I can hardly see it now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_15">I wonder if Milky Way Cookie is driving past one of those stars up there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_16">Oh... I should\'ve asked where I can get my hands on a ticket for the Sugarcloud Express...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0573_3_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">Meh...! I\'ll figure it out someday, haha! After all, a promise is a promise!</string>
