  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.Main">A Grand Plan... In the Making</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.01">Organization of Thoughts</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.02">Why Are You Here?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.03">Just a Moment of Silence</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.01.Summary">Buckwheat Cookie\'s ambitions know no limits. She retreats to her room for some well-deserved peace and quiet, which she hopes will help her finalize her grand scheme.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.02.Summary">Yummers has suddenly ventured away from the Temple of Abundance on his own in order to visit Buckwheat Cookie... Why?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2012.Title.03.Summary">Yummers is hungry and asking for obscure, rare gourmet dishes and ingredients to snack on. Somehow, Buckwheat Cookie understands his demands, even when he\'s speaking with his mouth full...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.Main">Doon! Doon! Du-doa!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.01">Crash Landing in the Witch\'s Castle</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.02">Never Before Seen... Entity!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.03">Space Travel?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.01.Summary">Space Doughnut has crash-landed into... not an ocean, but a strange and eery castle! The space traveler is confused when suddenly...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.02.Summary">Witchberry Cookie, self-proclaimed expert on the Witch\'s Castle, has made contact with Space Doughnut! No, Witchberry Cookie, Space Doughnut is not a Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0106.Title.03.Summary">Witchberry Cookie, who has not traveled beyond the Witch\'s Castle, is fascinated by Space Doughnut\'s tales of space travel. And Space Doughnut is excited to explore the castle with Witchberry Cookie\'s help. The two make an odd pair, but it seems they\'ll get along just fine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">Hmph... What a mess. I could barely hear myself think back there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">... I will stop at nothing to fulfill my destiny.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">But I am finding it much too difficult to finalize my grand plan in such a dizzying environment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_4">The Temple of Abundance? Hmph! More like the Temple of Chaos.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">At least my room provides some solace and much needed silence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_6">I shall organize my thoughts and then-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">Hm? Is there someone outside my door?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Event.0002_8">Brkwt Cookie! (Buckwheat Cookie!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_9">Eh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Event.0002_10">Brkwt Cookie!!! (Buckwheat Cookie!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_11">It\'s that nuisance... Yummers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_12">*Sigh*
Never a dull moment...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_1_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">Yummers! Calm down, please! Stay still and I shall open the door.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">What does the small lump of dough want this time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_2">I swear, it\'s always something... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_3">Yummers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_4">Why are you here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">What happened to the Moletatoes? How come you\'re here alone?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Event.0002_6">Th Mrwltatus srd thr wrh bzy. (The Moletatoes said they were busy.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">Hold on. Yummers is an essential key to my plan.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_8">Yes... In the end, it may serve beneficial to become well acquainted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_9">I must ensure that Yummers learns to trust me without question.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_10">Besides... It will make the kidnapping go much more efficiently.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_11">Well... Now that you\'re here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Event.0002_12">I wnt spnch soop! (I want spinach soup!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">Eh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Event.0002_14">Frsh spnch soop!!! (Fresh spinach soup!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_15">Fresh... spinach soup.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_2_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">Now? Like, really, now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_1">Yummers... Do I look like the type of Cookie to have fresh spinach soup just lying around?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_2">Brkwt Cookie! (Buckwheat Cookie!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_3">Yer th onl wun whr rly undrstns me! (You\'re the only one who really understands me!!!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_4">Noh evrwun duz, hehe. (Not everyone does, hehe.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_5">You little... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_6">What are you eating right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_7">You should finish whatever it is you\'re having first. THEN, you can ask for something.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_8">And please remember... it is rude to speak with food in your mouth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_9">Have you not considered that\'s why everyone has a hard time understanding you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_10">Hehe, irf I der, werl yu gert mi srm spnch soop? (Hehe, if I do, will you get me some spinach soup?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_11">What? No, that\'s not the point...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_12">C\'mere, I can\'t stand to see your mouth covered in crumbs. Let me wipe them off for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_13">Spinach soup... *TSK*
Seriously? Spinach soup...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_14">Hehehe, thn haw bout... (Hehehe, then how about...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_15">Drmn Wrm Extr! (Dreaming Worm Extract!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_16">Dreaming... Worm... Extract...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_17">How did a little menace like you learn about such a gourmet ingredient...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_18">*Sigh*
I am cursed with a perpetual headache.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_19">Do I really need Yummers as part of my plan?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Event.0002_20">Brkwt Cookie! (Buckwheat Cookie!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2012_3_POR1_Cookie.2012_21">Please... Just a moment of silence is all I ask for!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_1">Fraka-kaki?! Du-doa?
(Huh?! Where am I?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_2">Du doa... don doo fraka-fraka-kri!
(I remember... crash landing into the ocean!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_3">Dou dou dooon?
(But... how did I end up here?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_4">Kyou-kya prrrp prrrp...?
(What is this place...?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_5">Doooo-biri-biri prrrp.
(It seems very old.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_6">Prrrp kyyu du-doa dddo dwoo da?!
(Just how old is this place...?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_7">Dooo dooo kyou-kya!
(It might be ancient, built before I began my trip!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_8">Kyou-kyyu...?
(And this chamber is...?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_9">Dooo-da?
(It\'s like it was prepared just for me?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_10">Kyou-kya-kya doa!
(I like it!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.2006_11">MYAH! What\'s going on here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.2006_12">I swear I saw something crash down from the sky...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.0106_13">Doo-da?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_1_POR1_Cookie.2006_14">EEEK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_1">W-W-Who are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_2">I\'ve been around the Witch\'s Castle FOREVER, but I\'ve never seen anything like you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_3">You... You... What are you?! Are you a Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_4">Fraka-ka-kaki du-do-a-a!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_5">MYAH?! What\'re you saying???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_6">Are they a Cookie? Or... something else?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_7">Bread? No, a cushion? Wait, a cushion with a mouth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_8">Who am I dealing with here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_9">Prrrprp turuturu dooo-da!
(What an interesting friend I\'ve just made!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_10">Du-doa biri-dduru dwooo-don!
(They seem really excited to meet me too!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_11">Hm... My name is Witchberry Cookie. And I am the resident expert on everything about the Witch\'s Castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_12">And according to my knowledge, you, Roundish-Circle Cookie... may not be a Cookie at all! So... what\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_13">Doooon... Doooonut!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_14">I still have no idea what you\'re saying...!!! What language are you speaking?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_15">Frrrrrrieeend...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_16">Doooonut! Doooonut!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_17">Friend? Doughnut? Myeh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.0106_18">Kyou kyu... kyou kyukyu! Ppu biri doa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_2_POR1_Cookie.2006_19">*GASP!*
Whoever this is, I think they can understand what I\'m saying!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_1">Prrrp-kyou-kya!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_2">I get it now! So... what you\'re saying is... you came from there, somewhere between the moon and the stars?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_3">KYOU!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_4">Hm, yes, fascinating...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_5">I\'ve been here a looong time, and I haven\'t been outside the Witch\'s Castle before but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_6">Ddooon-Doon! Doa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_7">What? NO! This castle is filled with all sorts of mysteries and fun stuff!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_8">No one ever gets bored here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_9">There\'s lots of crumbs and debris left in the castle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_10">And many, many minions of the witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_11">Oooh, and all sorts of funny Cookies running around, even ones that were freshly baked!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_12">With all that\'s going on here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_13">You might just end up staying here to experience it all!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_14">Kyou kyu... kyou kyukyu! Ppu! Biri! Doa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_15">Dduru du-doa! Dooonut!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_16">Myahaha! Of course I will! I\'ll show you around the entire castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_17">Dooonut...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_18">Du-doa prrrp-kya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_19">Is that so?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.2006_20">Well I\'ll look forward to hearing more about the sleepy moon and dancing stars! Keep\'em coming!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0106_3_POR1_Cookie.0106_21">Dooooon dooooooon dooogh!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.Title">It\'s Been a While!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest1">To Mount St. Crème!</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest2">A Happy, Yet Nostalgic Reunion</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest3">Remembering the Unforgettable</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest4">Cookies of the First Batch</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest5">Fare Thee Well</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest1.Summary">First Grain Cookie has been feeling down since Yummers\' departure. Chickpea Cookie suggests First Grain Cookie pay a visit to Mount St. Crème to cheer up.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest2.Summary">Upon arriving at Mount St. Crème, First Grain Cookie encounters someone she recognizes and is happy to meet once more.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest3.Summary">First Grain Cookie can barely contain her excitement to see First Cream Cookie, who has no recollection of her past. While engaging in conversation, they hear Yummers approach.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest4.Summary">First Cream Cookie and First Grain Cookie continue their conversation as they watch Yummers and GingerDozer get along. They both hope that First Cream Cookie can regain her memory.</string>
  <string name="$SpecialStory.12.SQuest5.Summary">First Grain Cookie departs for the Temple of Abundance, but before she does, the two new old friends wish each other the best.</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.12">A New Old Reunion</string>
  <string name="$Collection.Memory.Album.SpecialStory.12.Story">It has been ages since First Grain Cookie met First Cream Cookie, whose memories have faded. Perhaps the memories will come back soon. But for now, it\'s fare thee well.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Get">Kyou-kya!
Kyou-kya?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Random.01">Fraka-ka-kaki du-do-a-a!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Random.02">Ccoaght?
Ccuat?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Random.03">Kyou kyu... kyou kyukyu!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Random.04">Turuturu! Dua-dua!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Random.05">Kyou kyu... dua-do-dua?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Kyyu...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Monologue.Greeting">Ddooo-dua!</string>
