  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Profile">Buckwheat Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0106.Profile">Space Doughnut</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Story">Buckwheat Cookie was created using finely ground buckwheat flour, kneaded with warm water to create a fragrant and rich flavor. The method of carefully cooking at just the right time and temperature is the secret behind the Cookie\'s distinctive glossy shine.

However, despite the outward appearance, it is said that the Cookie lost her inner chewiness a long time ago... Even as she assists First Grain Cookie with helping the residents, Buckwheat Cookie\'s eyes occasionally reveal her true intentions.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Get">If there is anything you need, let me know... But only me.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Random.01">I\'ll make sure that nuisance Chickp...
Wh-what?! Stop eavesdropping!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Random.02">Like this... I\'ll be useful... right?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Random.03">Oh... Hoo hoo? No, that\'s a weird way to laugh...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Random.04">And so it begins... A new day...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Random.05">*Sigh*... It\'s okay. You\'re the best, Buckwheat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.LifeZero.01">No... This can\'t... Not like this...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Monologue.Greeting">Is there anything I can help with? Tell me, but no one else, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Skill.Name">Impeccable Chopstick Technique</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2012.Ceil.999">Buckwheat Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2012.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Buckwheat Cookie\'s Subtly Fragrant and Secret-filled Room!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Soulstone">Buckwheat Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2012.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Buckwheat Cookie\'s soul. It has a subtle scent of ambition. Mmm... Delicious ambition!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0106.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Space Doughnut. While it looks a bit different on the outside, it\'s just as sweet as every other Bear Jelly Toy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2012.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Buckwheat Cookie. The smile makes it seem like it\'s scheming something... But somehow it feels adorable?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0023.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Devil Cookie. How could anyone hate that adorable, yet mischievous grin?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0028.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Cherry Cookie. Every time you hug the toy it lets out a fresh, yet thrilling, scent.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0002.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Strawberry Cookie. How could you not hug it when it looks at you with those sparkling eyes?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0106.TeddyBear">Space Doughnut Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2012.TeddyBear">Buckwheat Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
