  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0106.002">Half-burned Meteor Fragment</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0106.003">Distant Planet Souvenir</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.001">Chopstick Bundle</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.002">Rattan Wristband</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.003">Headdress Collection</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0106.001.Story">Space Mini Ball was once the core of Space Doughnut. Truth be told, it is the brain of the duo—quite literally so, as the brain had been in the core of the dough. This ambitious extraterrestrial pet dreams of one day conquering the universe with Space Doughnut.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0106.002.Story">A space rock that originated from a planet where the inhabitants are anything but flat. The burned areas give off a sweet fragrance.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0106.003.Story">A colorful package hailing from a distant world. Could it be a specialty of Space Doughnut\'s home planet? No one knows for sure, but the contents of the package does resemble Space Doughnut.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.001.Story">The perfect tool for pointing to distant places, picking up things from the ground, or just for reaching things without needing to get out of your bed. Rumors speak of a mysterious fourth way of using chopsticks... but that is a well-kept secret.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.002.Story">A bracelet created as a symbol of friendship between two Cookies. The chickpea added onto it is the highlight of its design.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2012.003.Story">Every now and then, rumors travel throughout the temple about how many hair accessories Buckwheat Cookie has. Sliced onions, seaweed powder, pickled radish... the list goes on. What will she wear tomorrow? We\'ll have to wait and see.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2012">Buckwheat Cookie\'s Subtly Fragrant and Secret-filled Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2012.Story">When entering Buckwheat Cookie\'s room, you are instantly greeted by a savory fragrance. Among the neatly organized work logs relating to the Temple of Abundance, it is said a diary lies hidden, containing correspondence with a certain someone, filled with the Cookie\'s true feelings.</string>
