  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.001">Blueberry Syrup Flying Saucer</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.002">Strawberry Syrup Flying Saucer</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.WP.001">Sprinkly Syrupy Wall</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Deck.001">Sprinkly Syrupy Floor</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.004">Donut Dream Bar</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.001">Sugar Beats Neon Donut</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.003">Rainbow Donut Jukebox</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.002">Sweet Galaxy Porthole</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.007">Donut Stool</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.006">Mini Rocket Model</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Ceil.001">Standard Protocol Air Shower</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.005">Mini Donut Pot</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.003">Donut Porthole</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Rug.001">Giant Star Carpet</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Rug.002">Colorful Dancing Pad</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Ceil.002">Adorable Planet Mobile</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Hanger.001">Space Exploration Stickers</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.001.Story">This beyond-state-of-the-art flying saucer is filled with sweet blueberry syrup! It looks like the pilot took the extra time to make it cozy with lemon, blueberry, and raspberry candies. The spacecraft looks ready to blast off at a moment\'s notice with all sorts of flashy, rainbow lights!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.WP.001.Story">This beyond-state-of-the-art flying saucer is filled with strawberry syrup! Where did this spacecraft come from? Who is the pilot? Judging by the bright, blinking green light come from the lime candy, it looks like the spacecraft is preparing for launch?!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Deck.001.Story">A wall that resembles layers of cake from an unknown red planet. It looks incredibly tasty!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.004.Story">A floor that resembles layers of cake from an unknown red planet. It looks somewhat sticky?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.001.Story">Underneath the flashing neon lights, small aliens gather around to commune and spend some time together. It looks as if they are winding down for the day in each other\'s company, but there\'s also a fiery discussion on how to shoot donut beams... Let\'s leave them to their conversation for now, shall we?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.003.Story">These neon lights shine brighter than all the stars in the night sky. Standing beneath it, you can\'t help but feel overjoyed and cheerful!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.002.Story">Some time ago, this jukebox was discovered in a crash alien spacecraft. Aliens from unknown origins seem to enjoy this piece of musical machinery very, very much. But whenever Cookies try to enjoy its music, they are left puzzled because there is no audible sound coming from its speakers. Perhaps the music is emitted at an entirely different frequency...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.007.Story">Dua-do-dua-dododonut! Is this the remnants of an emergency landing? Or perhaps a monstrous space creature took large chomp? Whatever happened, the porthole seems damaged... but it\'s still sturdy enough to show just how large and vast outer space can be!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.006.Story">A small stool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Ceil.001.Story">A tiny model of a rocket. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.005.Story">Germs are bad. This will definitely help keep the place clean.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Wall.003.Story">A small pot. Let\'s put it to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Rug.001.Story">A donut porthole! What will we see outside?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Rug.002.Story">A large carpet in the shape of a star. Let\'s put it somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Ceil.002.Story">Flashy dancing pads for everyday entertainment needs! What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Hanger.001.Story">A hanging mobile of alien planets. Looks otherworldly!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0106.Floor.001.Story.Story">Stickers depicting all sorts of planets! Everyone loves these, especially since they glow in the dark!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2012.Hanger.001">Buckwheat Flower Folding Screen</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2012.Hanger.001.Story">A folding screen for some privacy. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
