  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.002.MintchocoTeddyBear">Mint Choco Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.001.CocoaTeddyBear">Cocoa Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.003.SnowSugarTeddyBear">Snow Sugar Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.001.PoinsettiaTeddyBear">Poinsettia Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.002.MintchocoTeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Mint Choco Cookie. You can faintly make out the graceful sound of a violin. And what a refreshing smile!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.001.CocoaTeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Cocoa Cookie. The warm smile makes you feel like you\'re able to withstand the cold winter nights with only a cup of cocoa.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.003.SnowSugarTeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy with a design capturing the characteristics of Snow Sugar Cookie perfectly. When you gaze into its eyes, you feel as if you\'ve just made a new best friend.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.Teddybear.Floor.001.PoinsettiaTeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Poinsettia Cookie. When holding it close, you feel as if it will sing a song that will make you feel all warm and fuzzy inside.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.001.XmasBubbleGreen">Green Bauble</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.002.XmasBubbleRed">Red Bauble</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.003.XmasCandycane">Wintry &amp; Minty Candy Cane</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.004.XmasSocks">Sleepy Dreamy Star</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.005.XmasTree">Creamy Tree Ornament</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.001.XmasBubbleGreen.Story">A green bauble used to decorate trees. Looking at it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.002.XmasBubbleRed.Story">A red bauble used to decorate trees. Looking at it makes you feel relaxed.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.003.XmasCandycane.Story">A decorative candy cane. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.004.XmasSocks.Story">An adorable star sleeping in a stocking. Ssshhh, don\'t wake them up!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2024Christmas.Ceil.005.XmasTree.Story">This beautiful ornament depicts an evergreen tree covered in heavy snow. The decorations and twinkling star on top remind you that even the coldest winters can bring the warmest of memories.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.Main">The Value of Siblings</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.01">Misunderstanding</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.02">Related?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.03">Will I Ever Find Such a Thing?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Illust.Dialog.01">I believe there
has been a
misunderstanding.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Illust.Dialog.02">... I am no villain.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.01.Summary">Stardust Cookie has landed in the Syrup Garden. Rosemary Cookie and Radish Cookie are wary of his sudden arrival. Stardust Cookie reassures them he is not a villain!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.02.Summary">With the misunderstanding cleared up, Stardust Cookie asks Rosemary Cookie about her sister, Radish Cookie. He learns that family is important and precious.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0574.Title.03.Summary">Rosemary Cookie cares for her sister immensely. Hearing this, Stardust Cookie wonders if the Wizards think the same of him. He continues his journey to seek answers, and to one day maybe find someone like family, important and precious.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.Main">Concert Partners!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.01">Would You Consider a Duet... Oops!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.02">Now\'s My Chance to Ask... Whoops!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.03">Shall We Perform a Concert Together?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Illust.Dialog.02">Would you be interested
in performing a duet for
the winter concert?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.01.Summary">The festive winter holidays are here, and Poinsettia Cookie is getting ready to plan the perfect concert! But something is needed to make it absolutely perfect... She thinks Mint Choco Cookie\'s serenading violin is the answer, but he\'s too busy engaging with his fans to ask!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.02.Summary">Poinsettia Cookie continues seeking a chance to ask Mint Choco Cookie to perform a concert together, but to no avail. In the end, she decides to just walk away...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2014.Title.03.Summary">Poinsettia Cookie is surprised to hear that Mint Choco Cookie has been searching for her. He pitches an idea to perform a duet together! Poinsettia Cookie eagerly agrees!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014">Poinsettia Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Story">On a wintry evening, when the end of the year was just around the corner, delicate poinsettia leaves were added to a batch of dough. This Cookie was baked just as the snow began to blanket the world and enchanting songs echoed throughout the streets. 

Poinsettia Cookie is known to be deeply shy, and many around her claim to have never heard her voice. The few who have are unanimous in their praise! Poinsettia Cookie\'s voice is so divine and heavenly, even the free-spirited, restless Cream Roll Birds take the time to listen to her songs.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Get">Will you... sing with me?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Random.01">Only practice... can make a performance perfect.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Random.02">AH! Nooo, you\'re not supposed to hear my song yet...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Random.03">I like the snow, especially when there\'s lots and lots.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Random.04">Gifts...? I think I like warm, kindhearted words more than gifts...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Random.05">I hope... that my singing can make the world a better place...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.LifeZero.01">I... lost my voice...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Monologue.Greeting">You make my heart feel so calm and warm, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Skill.Name">Blooming Melody</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2014">Poinsettia Cookie\'s Room of Holiday Melodies</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2014.Story">Poinsettia Cookie\'s room is decorated with sparkly, colorful, and vibrant ornaments of all shapes and sizes. The festive melodies that fill the room will have you jumping for joy!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.001">Ornamental Bead</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.002">Concert Sheet Music</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.003">Poinsettia Leaves</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.001.Story">Poinsettia Cookie never leaves home without this red and green bead in her hair. It resembles a holiday ornament used to decorate trees.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.002.Story">Sheet music prepared by Poinsettia Cookie. She carefully studies and practices her music in preparation for special holiday performances. The frayed corners and edges show her commitment and effort!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2014.003.Story">Poinsettia leaves, strikingly crimson and bright, are always a cute addition to Poinsettia Cookie\'s outfits.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Story">It is hard to say how long the lonesome speck of Cookie dough had been drifting in the vast emptiness of space before the radiance of nameless stars blessed it with the gift of life. Was it a mere coincidence...?

For Stardust Cookie, the warmth of many suns was the heat of the oven, and the distant planets were his only companions in his light-speed journey across galaxies. Beckoned by shapeless, fleeting nebulae, guided by the whispering of the stars, Stardust Cookie headed to the City of Wizards to uncover the secret of his birth. Was he trying to find his long-lost purpose, or, on the contrary, escape his predetermined fate...? 

With a glint of a stray shooting star, this lonesome voyager crosses someone\'s sky tonight, seeking a place to call home.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Get">My voyage... goes on.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Random.01">I wonder where my birthplace is...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Random.02">So many Cookies... gathered in one place...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Random.03">Have you ever seen the Sugar Swan in the night sky?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Random.04">Traveling through the vast emptiness of space is not for everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Random.05">I am but a grain of sand in an ocean of stars.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.LifeZero.01">All is futile...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Monologue.Greeting">The stars have led me to you, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0574.Skill.Name">Wrath of the Stars</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0574">Stardust Cookie\'s Starlight Sanctuary</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0574.Story">Stardust Cookie\'s room looks as if it\'s somewhere deep within the swirling galaxy, where the soft whispers of stars can be heard through the night. When you\'ve been seeking for, longing for that missing something... this place offers you respite and a soothing, cosmic embrace.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.001">Shining Stardust</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.002">Starkissed Cloak</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.003">Lost Meteor</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.001.Story">As Stardust Cookie speeds through the galaxy like a meteor, stardust dances and sparkles in his wake. The shimmering glow reminds you of Stardust Cookie himself.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.002.Story">The cloak worn by Stardust Cookie. It is said that, when even the moonlight fades to darkness, this cloak will shine brightly and illuminate the way forward.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0574.003.Story">A small portion of a meteor that orbits Stardust Cookie. Apparently, it is the last portion of a meteor that burned in anger.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Ceil.999">Stardust Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Stardust Cookie\'s Starlight Sanctuary!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_1">Hm... I seem to have ended up at the wrong destination.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_2">Where exactly am I...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_3">Stop.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_4">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">Who are you? What is the meaning of this intrusion? And did you really fall from the sky just now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_6">This stranger is wary of me. I must explain myself, quickly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_7">I am...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_8">Rosemary Cookie! Don\'t let your guard down!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">Radish Cookie? No! Stay back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_10">I\'m just...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_11">If you hurt my sister, you\'ll regret it! Ya hear me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_12">Stay away from my family!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">Radish Cookie! Get behind me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_14">... I believe there has been a misunderstanding.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_15">... I am no villain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2005_16">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.2004_17">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_1_POR1_Cookie.0574_18">Perhaps I should work on my first impression...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_1">... And that is how I have ended up here, simply at the wrong destination.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_2">So that\'s what happened, huh? Haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_3">My apologies. It seems there has been a misunderstanding on our part.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_4">No. Your mentioning of the Reaper explains your initial reaction. You were right to be wary of strangers such as myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_5">Welp, I\'m gonna take off! I\'ve got some gadgets that need fixin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2004_6">Oh! And welcome to the Syrup Garden! Hope ya can find some time to relax before you go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_7">Radish Cookie! Remember not to run too fast and please watch where you\'re going!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_8">These two seem to be very close friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_9">Rosemary Cookie, was it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_10">And the other, Radish Cookie. May I ask about the nature of your relationship...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">Radish Cookie is my younger sister.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_12">Ah, you are siblings. Then she must hold a special place in your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.2005_13">Yes, though her shenanigans have grown somewhat out of control lately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_14">How special is she to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_2_POR1_Cookie.0574_15">Siblings. Family.
Why are they so highly cherished?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_1">Though I don\'t quite understand why you\'ve suddenly asked such a question...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_2">I can tell you there is no one else like her in the world, and she is loved very much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_3">I guess you could say... I would do anything for her.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_4">I would wake up from the deepest slumber, I would face any danger for her...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_5">Radish Cookie is someone who I cannot imagine losing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_6">"Do anything..."</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_7">I wonder if my creators thought the same of me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_8">Am I special? Cherished?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_9">I do not know... But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_10">If it were me, I would.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_11">I cherish my sister, my family... I care about them so much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_12">There is no reason for me not to feel the same for a creation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_13">Perhaps.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_14">Thank you. I shall now take my leave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_15">I do not know what your journey entails...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.2005_16">But good luck, and I hope you find what you seek.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_17">Thank you. And farewell.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_18">Someone special and cherished... Do anything for them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_19">Will I ever meet them?
Hm... Yes, I will.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0574_3_POR1_Cookie.0574_20">Well then. My journey continues.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_1">Okie-dokie! The songs for the holiday concert are officially... DONE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_2">I can\'t shake the feeling that something\'s missing though...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_3">What is it? What could it be? Everyone\'s looking forward to this concert...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_4">AH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_5">An instrument! The concert will be so much better with the sweet melodies of a violin...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_6">Yes! It\'ll be perfect...! I should ask Mint Choco Cookie immediately!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0006_7">Hello, Mint Choco Cookie! Yet again, you\'ve delivered another amazing performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0032_8">It was so mesmerizing, I wish to see it once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0032_9">I could listen to your violin all day, for it is so enchanting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.0046_10">*Chuckle*
You are all much too kind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_11">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0006_12">May I please get your autograph?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_12">Erm... Hello...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0032_13">I would like to discuss many things about music with you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Npc.0032_14">I wish to engage in a deep conversation about music with you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_15">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.2014_16">I don\'t think I\'ll be able to get his attention right now... I\'ll approach him a bit later.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.0046_17">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_1_POR1_Cookie.0046_18">I felt someone\'s gaze upon me just now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_1">Oh! Mint Choco Cookie is alone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_2">Okay!!! Now\'s my chance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_3">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0031_4">What a wonderful show! You truly are a genius, an amazing maestro!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0031_5">How about a shared stage, a duet between classical and rock! Please consider, we can do it whenever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_6">A performance together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_7">What a wonderful idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_8">I... erm... Excuse me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0030_9">EEEK! This is so exciting! That performance will be a blast!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0030_10">Will it be a concert or a party?! OOOH! We should get some glow sticks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_11">Oh no...! I have to ask this time. This is my last chance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_12">Erm... Hello?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0012_13">Would you please consider holding a recital at our hotel one day?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0012_14">I am confident that our guests will be very happy to hear your performance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_15">Ah! If given the opportunity, it would be an honor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_16">He looks so busy again... Maybe it\'s rude of me to ask right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.2014_17">Okay. I guess I\'ll just have to it alone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_18">Ah, pardon me. I\'ve just noticed a Cookie with whom I can hold an amazing concert.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Npc.0012_19">Oh? There\'s no one there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_20">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_2_POR1_Cookie.0046_21">... Where have you gone?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_1">Practice! Just practice, practice, practice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_2">Mm-hmm ♪ ♬ La la de la da la ♩♬ ♪</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_3">Ah, there you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_4">*GASP*
Mint Choco Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_5">I have been seeking you, and just happened to hear your singing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_6">I knew it was you, Poinsettia Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_7">Why is Mint Choco Cookie here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_8">Wait! This is the perfect chance to ask him if he wants to join my concert!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_9">Poinsettia Cookie. I am here because I wish to ask for a favor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_10">A favor?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_11">Yes. I believe your voice and my violin can create a lovely harmony.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_12">Apologies for being so abrupt, but would you be interested in performing a duet for the winter concert?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_13">Your lovely voice will certainly be able to create a memorable experience for the audience.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_14">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.2014_15">Yes! Of course! This is so amazing...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2014_3_POR1_Cookie.0046_16">Lovely! Then let us create the perfect duet, together.</string>
