  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.008.Story">A collection of small gift boxes. Wrapped and ready!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Hanger.001.Story">Nothing like a poinsettia wreath to add some elegance to the holiday vibes.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Ceil.002.Story">A simple, but adorable garland with ornaments. Let\'s put it somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.009.Story">A comfy stool in the same color as poinsettias. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.005.Story">A collection of large gift boxes! Wrapped and ready!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.006.Story">Some sheet music for a holiday concert. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.007.Story">An expertly crafted wooden sofa. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Rug.001.Story">A carpet featuring a poinsettia in the center. Let\'s find a place for it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Wall.002.Story">Sunlight peeks in through this window. What an amazing view!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.002.Story">A gramophone playing a gentle, soothing melody that fills you with holiday cheer. Listening to it while eating cake by candlelight is an excellent way to spend a cozy, wintry night.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Ceil.001.Story">A garland decorated with bulbs and cute musical notes. When you gaze upon it, you feel as if there\'s a beautiful song whispering in your ear.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Wall.001.Story">A large window decorated with poinsettias. Even during the coldest of winters, the warm sunlight seeps in to bring the room to a toasty and cozy temperature.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.003.Story">A tablecloth decorated with holly, poinsettias, and candles. If you want to spruce up your room with some end-of-the-year holiday cheer, this is the only thing you\'ll need!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.004.Story">A bookshelf adorned in snowflakes. The starry lights on top have a warm glow that makes your heart flutter with holiday cheer.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.WP.001.Story">A wall decorated musical notes, ornaments, and lights. Not only does it add a dash of coziness to a room, it adds a ton of festive vibes as well.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Deck.001.Story">A soft floor with a central pattern resembling a poinsettia. Come relax, share stories, and sing with your friends as you reminisce on the year.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Floor.001.Story">A gramophone playing a soothing melody that reminds you of a quiet winter\'s night. You can imagine the streets are covered in snow and illuminated by warm, glowing lights, and in the air is the spirit of the holidays. Just listening to a few stanzas is enough to fill your heart with joy.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Ceil.999">Poinsettia Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2014.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Poinsettia Cookie\'s Room of Holiday Melodies!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Soulstone">Poinsettia Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2014.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Poinsettia Cookie\'s soul. It\'s cold to the touch and you can faintly hear singing from within.</string>
