  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.001.Story">A simple decoration depicting shooting stars. Just looking it makes you feel like you\'re home.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.002.Story">A floating piece of a star. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.003.Story">A notepad containing the archived whispers of the stars. Let\'s put it to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.004.Story">A sofa made from pure stardust. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.005.Story">A garland decorated with stars and planets. Looking at it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.006.Story">A simple light in the shape of a planet. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Floor.007.Story">A book to help pass the time. You should it read it someday.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Wall.001.Story">A carpet decorated to resemble the night sky. Simply putting it in a room makes it look more elegant.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Wall.002.Story">A strange flower from an uncharted planet. Just looking it makes you feel like you\'re home.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Wall.003.Story">A mysterious chair crafted from the roof of a spire in a city far, far away. It\'s a reminder of the city\'s once glorious past...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Hanger.001.Story">Armillary spheres can show you the approximate location of stars scattered across the vast universe. If you listen closely, you can almost hear the whispers and murmurs of lonely stars waiting to be found.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Hanger.002.Story">A bookshelf shaped like a spire. It has a magical and mysterious aura to it. It\'s said that a Cookie gazed upon this bookshelf repeatedly, always with a sense of loneliness upon their face.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Ceil.001.Story">A sparkling, planet-shaped ornament that makes you wonder just how long Stardust Cookie\'s travels must have been.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Ceil.002.Story">Curtains adorned with stars. The softly shining curtains remind you of just how dark and vast the universe can be.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Rug.001.Story">This wall makes you feel like you\'re gazing upon the vast night sky. It also makes you wonder if we\'re not alone in the universe...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.WP.001.Story">The floor makes you feel like you\'re floating through the vast night sky. You feel as if you\'ll be able to meet your destiny if you follow the starlight...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0574.Deck.001.Story">A chair made from the roof of an enchanted spire in a city far, far away. If you sit still, you can barely make out the encouraging and warm-hearted whispers of the stars.</string>
