  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">Eugh... It\'s so hot.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_2">It really is...! Each step feels heavier and heavier!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">And... this place is a bit... creepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">A hot and creepy place! What a change of scenery!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">... Dude, I wouldn\'t quite put it that way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">*Sigh...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_7">What\'s with the gloominess all of a sudden? Where\'s that signature enthusiasm of y-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">LOOK OVER THERE! It\'s a giant pile of chocolate!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_9">Ah, there\'s the enthusiasm... as usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">I get the feeling it might be less hot over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">Maybe it\'s something like Mount St. Crème... where First Cream Cookie is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">That means we might find a Cookie of the First Batch there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">Speaking of... I wonder what sorta place it is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Hm, I vaguely recognize it... Erm, what was it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_15">The Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">Ah! Yes, thank you. The Chocosseum! Where only the strongest of warriors-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">... Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_18">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_19">W-W-W-Where\'d she come from?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Who are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_1">First Choco Cookie! The next training session will commence soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_2">I shall join shortly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_3">Oh? And who might these Cookies be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_4">I do not know, but it appears they seek to enter the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_5">*Tsk tsk*
More whelps? This never ends well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_6">Excuse me, but you seem to be mistaking us for some random rabble of amateur adventurers...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_7">This is happening much more often of late, little Cookies trying to get into the Chocosseum...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">LITTLE?! Who are you calling \"little\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_9">It\'s a dangerous world out there, exponentially so in these lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_10">More and more whelps like you seek the Chocosseum in droves... and you lot are, well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">When entering the Chocosseum, you must be prepared to abide by its laws.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">What\'s that supposed to mean? What sort of laws?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_13">Ahem! To put it simply, whelps do not belong in the Chocosseum!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_14">Only those who have passed the Great Trial and proven their true strength can enter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_15">He seems very... smug.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">There\'s nothing wrong with a little confidence, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">We should take this trial too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">Hold your horses...! Don\'t forget, our primary task is to find Cookies of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_19">... The First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">Yeah! We\'re looking for Cookies of the First Batch! Do you know anything about them?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">I do not know why you seek the First Batch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_2">But I see no reason for me to tell you anything about them, especially to ones who are uninitiated.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Then could you tell us more about this Great Trial? We\'re allowed inside the Chocosseum if we pass it, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_4">Indeed! If you pass the trial, you are initiated as a warrior of the Chocosseum!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">So... What sort of trial is it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_6">Ha! Let me enlighten you, ragtag whelps. Back in my day, the trial was next level! A fierce battle with the notorious Choco Golem in the arena!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_7">Fighting to become the last warrior standing, victorious over all the other competitors...! What a rush!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">Enough about the details, just tell us how to start!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_9">Oh, did I not mention? You can\'t take the trial right now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_10">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_11">All slots have been filled! The trial is no longer accepting able-bodied contenders...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">Okay... So when\'s the next one gonna be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_13">The Choco Golem will need repairs after the trial ends, and that takes time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_14">To put it simply, you have no choice but to wait until the next full moon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">What?! That sounds like forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_16">Erm... Is there another way we could try?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_17">No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_18">You are left with only two choices.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_19">You can either wait patiently for the next trial to commence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_20">Or you can leave this place, quietly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_1">This conversation is over.
Begone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">And she\'s gone...
Just like that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">We can\'t just sit idly by
and wait around...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">Oh? Hey, check that out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0067_5">C\'mon! Walk faster,
you slowpoke!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2016_6">Pheeew...
But I\'m tiiired...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0067_7">We need to pick up
the pace and
find shelter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0067_8">The trial is tomorrow!
We can\'t be exposed
to danger until then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2016_9">*Huff puff*
Okay, okay, I\'m walking!
Don\'t puuush meee...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_10">They just mentioned
the trial...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_11">And they look
really tired too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_12">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_13">Before you say it...
Yes, we have some spare
Life Potions to share.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_15">Well... Knowing you
and your usual ideas...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_16">You were probably
thinking about lending
them a hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">Whoa... Wizard Cookie!
I didn\'t know
you were psychic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_18">No, stay back!
No hugs are necessary,
especially in this heat!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_19">Teehee, then it\'s settled!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_20">We should hurry and
catch up with them...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_21">And we should also ask
them about the trial too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_22">Okay!
Let\'s get moving!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Wow... Why\'s it so dark here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_2">It sounds like something is flowing beneath our feet... Watch your step, everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">And there\'s a cool breeze!!! It feels like the first time we all met!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">I\'m still quite certain that \"chilly\" is the correct term.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_5">Er, guys...? Where do you think those Cookies went...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Oh! Yeah... erm... well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Did we lose track of them?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_8">You might have lost track of us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">GAH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_10">... But we have not lost track of you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">H-H-He\'s pointing a spear at us...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Wait! We\'re not looking for a fight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_13">Then why are you following us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_14">No, nooo! Stop, Corn Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_15">It\'s baaad manners to threaten others with that spear of yours. We should hear them out fiiirst...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_16">But they might-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_17">Tut, tut, tut! Bad maaanners...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">This Cookie is... He\'s melting...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">Maybe this will help! Here, take it...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_20">A Life Potion? You\'re just... giving it away? To strangers like us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">Hurry and take it! It\'s okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_22">... Thanks.
Here, Melted Choco Cookie, drink up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_23">Pheeew! That hit the spot...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">It looks like it helped! Thank goodness! And there\'s no need to thank us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">We apologize for following you from afar. We were just a bit too eager to get this into your hands as quickly as possible.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">I kneeew it...! They\'re frieeendly...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_27">My name\'s Melted Choco Cookie, and this is Corn Choco Cookieee...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_28">Are you... warriors of the Chocosseum...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_29">Nooot yet... Corn Choco Cookie has the right to become a warrior...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_30">Not meee though... At least, not yet. This\'ll be my third tryyy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_31">Wow! You\'ve been through the trial three times?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_32">It\'s... it\'s also my last chaaance...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_33">Your last chance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">Yeeeah. Only the strongest warriors earn the right to enter the Chocosseum...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_2">Aaand if you can\'t pass the trial in three tries...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_3">You\'re forbidden from entering the Chocosseum, for all eternity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_5">Notice how these lands are harsh and scalding...? Our existence is all about survival.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Yeah... It\'s really, really hot here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">And it\'s not just the heeeat...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_8">There are scary Cookies that come out ooonly at niiight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_9">They aren\'t good talkers... or listeners, in fact... And did I mention they were very, veeery scary?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">*Shudder*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_11">Buuut the Chocosseum is different...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">And it\'s all thaaanks to First Choco Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_13">The Chocosseum is the only bastion of safety in this area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_14">Which is why so many of us seek entry... Perhaps too many.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_15">That\'s why the laws about the Great Trial were maaade.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_16">Ooonly the strongest warriors may enter the Chocosseum!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_17">These underground cacaocombs are also protected by First Choco Cookie\'s power.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_18">It\'s safer than most places, but we can\'t stay here for long.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_19">Especially... for this slowpoke.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_20">Then that means... we should really find a safer spot, and quickly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_21">It seems that entering the Chocosseum will prove more difficult than we initially thought.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_22">Oooh? You waaanna get into the Chocosseum too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">Yeah! We\'re helping a friend of ours in their search for the Cookies of the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_24">Maybe you can help us! Is there another way to get in the Chocosseum?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">We\'re desperate for any information. If there\'s anything you can tell us, we\'d greatly appreciate it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_26">If I knew of an alternative, this little rascal would already be inside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_27">So, that\'s a no...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_28">It\'s fiiine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_29">AAAll I have to do is pass the trial! Then I can help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_30">And I\'m quiiite sure that Corn Choco Cookie is willing to heeelp too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_31">Oh no! Melted Choco Cookie, you\'re starting to melt again...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_32">... You\'re in for a rough day tomorrow, so don\'t exhaust yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_33">Yeaaah... I guess you\'re right. I should get some rest.
*ZZZzzz...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_34">*Sigh*
Never a dull moment with this one...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_35">You two seem like best friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_36">We\'ve been friends for a long time now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0002_37">I hope he does well tomorrow... And if everything works out, maybe we can get inside too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_38">... I\'m pretty sure that\'s unlikely to happen.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_39">What do you mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_1">I still remember the day I passed the trial...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_2">It was Melted Choco Cookie who helped me succeed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_3">Just when I thought it was all over, he jumped in and saved my hide.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">He must be really tough! Maybe he won\'t have a problem tomorrow?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_5">... I doubt it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_6">I don\'t know how he survived... But it seemed like a one-time thing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_7">The truth is... Melted Choco Cookie is far too weak to pass the trial...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_8">But... He deserves entry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_9">I plan to approach First Choco Cookie with a petition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_10">It\'s Melted Choco Cookie who deserves to be in the Chocosseum, not me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_11">He\'s the one who protected me, and his sacrifice deserves recognition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_12">But that means... the two of you will be separated...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_13">Shh! Keep your voice down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_14">Whatever happens, only one of us will get to stay in the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_15">And whoever is granted entry, you\'ll still receive the help you need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_16">So... Let\'s pretend this conversation never happened, okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_18">That\'s enough for now. Keep an eye on him for me, will you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">Huh? Are you going somewhere?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_20">Like I said before, we aren\'t completely safe here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_21">I\'m going to scout the area. So stay with him until I get back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_22">... And he\'s gone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_23">What a sad story...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_24">Yeeeah, it is, isn\'t it...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">Indeed. We\'ve found ourselves in quite the sad and- Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">I kneeew this would happen... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_27">Eh?! Melted Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_28">W-W-Weren\'t you asleep...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">I couldn\'t sleep... Maybe it\'s because of the trial tooomorrow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_2">And I just... kept listening...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Melted Choco Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_4">Honestlyyy... I sortaaa knew this would happen...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_5">I know I\'m weeeak... And it\'s sad...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_6">But Corn Choco Cookie said... you protected him...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_7">Yeah! You might be stronger than you think!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_8">Naaah... I know who I am and what I can do...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_9">I just got lucky that tiiime... I mean, look at me. I can\'t even hold a weapon properlyyy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">Hey, c\'mon now! Don\'t say that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_11">Self-reproach is not the greatest of habits.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">But it\'s truuue... Only Cookies like me know what it\'s really like to be weeeak...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_13">My body is all wimpyyy... and meltyyy... I can\'t do-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">Stop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">Look at me! I\'m not strong either.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">I\'m not great at anything, and I don\'t have awesome abilities either!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_17">But there\'s one thing I\'ve learned. Even in the hardest situations...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">There\'s always the option to never give up, to keep going.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_19">And when you don\'t give up, you\'re always going to end up finding an answer sooner or later!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0025_20">Wise words to live by.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_21">Yup! And this sounds like a job for all of us! We\'ll think of something, together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_22">Yeah...! There has to be a way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_23">Reeeally...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_24">You reeeally think I have a shot...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_1">The thing is... I really do
wanna get strooonger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_2">Then Corn Choco Cookie
would stop worrying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_3">And we could get into
the Chocosseum together...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_4">Do you reeeally think
I have a shot...?
Really, reeeally?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0001_5">Yeah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0001_6">We can figure this out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_7">Okaaay...!!! Then I want
you to... HIT ME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0002_8">Wha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_9">The trial is tomorrooow...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_10">There\'s nooo time
to waaaste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_11">It\'s traaaining time...!
And every second maaatters!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0001_12">Haha!
That\'s the spirit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0003_13">Me too!
I wanna help too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_14">Okaaay!
Briiing it on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0001_15">Woot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0003_16">Teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.2016_17">Hyaaah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0025_18">We\'re going to
be okay, right...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH2_SQ5_Cookie.0002_19">Erm...
Hehe...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">Pheeew...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_2">What were you up to last night...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_3">Why is everyone so tired?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">Well... You see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_5">How\'re you going to fight if you\'re this exhausted?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_6">Hm... I can do this...! Leeet\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_7">Whoa... There\'s so many Cookies here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_8">I believe this is the first time we\'ve seen such a bustling crowd...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">So you need to be the last Cookie standing... to enter the Chocosseum...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_10">They all look tough and strong!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">It\'s okay! Melted Choco Cookie can handle it, no problem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">I... I think... Maybe I should quit whiiile I\'m ahead...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">You\'re starting to melt!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_14">Hey! Don\'t be a coward! Just relax and take a deep breath.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_15">Buuut...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_16">Whatever happens, everything\'ll be okay, got it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0067_17">So just get out there, don\'t get hurt, and come back in one piece!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_18">You can do it, Melted Choco Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">Give it your best! Just the way we practiced!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_20">If you have a goal in mind... No matter how scared you are...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">You should always give it your all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_22">Okaaay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_23">I\'ll be riiight back...! After winning...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_24">Woohoo! We\'ll be rooting for ya, all the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_25">... And here we are. Just moments ago, things seemed to almost lean in our favor for once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">*Siiigh...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Npc.0065_27">You! You\'re out!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">Halt. I believe we\'ve reached a conclusion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_2">Yes ma\'am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0068_3">Whirrr... PSSSHHH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_4">Ooooh... I tried my beeest... and my best wasn\'t even close to enough...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_5">It\'s okay. You tried.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_6">I\'ll take care of the rest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">Nooo... It\'s not riiight...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_8">I\'m not going alooone... And I never asked you to do this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0068_9">Whiiirrr...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_10">Huh? The Choco Golem... What\'s it doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0068_11">RAWR!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_12">Huh?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_13">Hey... Something\'s going on over there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_14">Why\'s this happening?! The Choco Golem has gone haywire!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_15">Urgh...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_16">Sounds like trouble!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">Look! The Choco Golem is acting weird!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0065_18">RUUUN! Run for your lives!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_19">Scorching crumbs...! Things are gonna get hot, so stay put and keep your heads down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_20">What about youuu...???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_21">I need to help the other warriors subdue the golem and evacuate the injured!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_22">And if things go well... I might get a chance to tell First Choco Cookie your story!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_23">Whaaat? If you\'re going, then I\'m goooing too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_24">It\'s too dangerous for you! Hurry up and get out of here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_25">Aaand... there he goes agaaain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">All I wanted to do was to heeelp... Why am I so weeeak...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_27">I\'m useless... I can\'t do anything...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_28">Melted Choco Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_29">Let\'s go help them! C\'mon, we got this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_30">Huuuh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">But... I\'ll just be getting in the waaay...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_2">I\'m toootally gonna mess things up...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_3">I mean... Look at meee. I\'m a mess...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_4">But if we give up now, nothing will change! And then it\'ll be too late to try again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">If there\'s something worth fighting for, then no matter what happens...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">You should never give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">Buuut I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_8">GingerBrave! We need to hurry and help the others!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">I\'ll... I\'ll help too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">I\'m with you too! Time to unleash some arcane magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_11">I\'m gonna go help them, Melted Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">And I hope you make a decision that you\'ll never regret!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_13">A decision I\'ll neeever regret...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_14">Gaaah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0068_15">RAAAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0065_16">Keep at it until we find a way to stop it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0068_17">RAAAWR!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_18">But... I\'m not a warrior...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_19">Watch it! Get out of there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0068_20">RAAAWR!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_21">Blast it...! Am I too late?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_22">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_23">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_24">What...? You...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_25">I\'m heeere! And I know now...! It\'s not about whether I caaan do it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">It\'s a question about wanting to...! I will help you! I will proootect you!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_27">I don\'t wanna see my friends get hurt!!! So get uuup, Corn Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0067_1">You crumbly slowpoke, I told you to get out of here...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_2">If I ran awaaay, you\'d be squashed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_3">And if you got hurt... Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_4">I would never forgive myself for not tryiiing to help...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Melted Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_6">I guess my melting body has one advantage... I can\'t feel any pain right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">But... I don\'t think I can keep this up for long...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0068_8">GRRR! RAAAWR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_9">Everyooone...! Get baaack!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_10">You too, Corn Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0067_11">Ugh...! I\'m not leaving you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">I\'ll hold the Choco Golem heeere...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_13">So listen to meee for once and get to safety!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0067_14">No, I\'m not going anywhere...!!! I need to stop the golem...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Npc.0068_15">ROOOAR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_16">Urf...!
Heeey, doesn\'t this remind you of when we first met?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_17">Do you remember? You fell to the ground, and I heeelped.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_18">And look at me nooow! I\'m... not... weeeak...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2016_19">So stop worrying about me... and run...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_20">C\'mon! We need to help those two!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2016_1">I... I think I\'ve hit
the limit... Oooh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0068_2">GRRR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0067_3">Crumbs...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">There\'s too much
rubble in the way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_5">Uh-oh...! We\'re in big trouble
if we can\'t clear a path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_6">Hang on!
I\'ll try casting a spell!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2016_7">Urrrgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">NO! STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_9">And stop it shall.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2016_10">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_11">Under my watchful gaze,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_12">no harm shall
befall anyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0068_13">Grrr...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_14">Hey! The golem just... stopped!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0002_15">And... in a single blow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_16">*Shudder*
Such... power...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0065_17">Hip, hip, hooray!
All hail, First Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0065_18">Looks like she helped
evacuate everyone to safety!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0065_19">And even had time to
deal with the golem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0065_20">All hail,
First Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Npc.0065_21">First Choco Cookie
saved the day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_22">Silence.
All of you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2016_23">Eh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2016_24">Eh? She\'s walking this way.
Why is she walking
this way...???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_25">You endured well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH3_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2015_26">Thanks to your efforts,
everyone made it to safety.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">What do you call yourself?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_2">Meh, Meh-meh, Meeeh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_3">Mehmehmehmeeeh? What a peculiar name.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_4">Wait, no, that\'s not... I mean...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_5">My naaame is Melted Choco Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_6">Ah.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_7">Melted Choco Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_8">On behalf of every warrior of Chocosseum, I would like to extend my gratitude.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_9">Thank you, brave warrior.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_10">Eeeeh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">Without your aid, many in the Chocosseum may have been severely injured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_12">I suspect the structure itself may have ended up a mess as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_13">And...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2016_14">\?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_15">Hm... I am suddenly reminded of my youth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_16">Despite knowing that I was a Witch, there were still those who accepted me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_17">And...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_18">Ultimately, I failed to protect them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_19">When I felt my will break beyond its limits...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_20">There was so much anguish... I was drowning in sadness. Such pain is a bitter reminder of why I resent the memory of losing everything I held dear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_21">From that point forth, I became obsessed with reaching the pinnacle of true strength.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_22">My obsession blinded me, for I did not see those who also had the will and strength to protect what is precious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_23">I did not see them for who they were...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_24">Were it not for your valor...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_25">I would have continued clinging onto my old ways, that all must become stronger no matter the cost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_26">I see now that I have been ignorant to the truth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_27">Melted Choco Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_28">Once again, I appreciate and commend your courage.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_29">Something still vexes me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_30">The Choco Golem has never malfunctioned in such a manner.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2015_31">Why now, all of a sudden?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">Hm... There is a strange apparatus within the golem.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_2">This... This cannot be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_3">First Choco Cookie...! May I speak?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Npc.0067_4">Does this mean... my friend has gained rightful entry into the Chocosseum?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_5">Such a request is unnecessary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_6">I shall investigate this matter at a later time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_7">First, I must address the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_8">All heroes who defend the Chocosseum, regardless of initiation, deserve to call this place home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_9">And...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_10">Hear me, warriors of the Chocosseum!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">Henceforth, the laws of the Chocosseum will be born anew!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_12">The Chocosseum will no longer cast out the uninitiated!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2015_13">To safeguard all that is truly precious, you must stand vigilant, together! For true strength can be found in each other!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">Woohoo! This is awesome!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_15">Wow! It\'s such good news!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_16">I... I... I\'ve been reeecognized by First Choco Cookie...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_17">Thanks so much, GingerBraaave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">Huh? Me? What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_19">It\'s just liiike you saaaid...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_20">You encouraged me to maaake the right choice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_21">A choice that I would neeever regret...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_22">So thank you! Thank you so very much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_23">Hehe! What\'re friends for?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_24">Which reminds meee...!!! First Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_25">GingerBrave saaaid he\'s looking for someone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2016_26">Can you help him, pleeease?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">Ah. I recall that you were seeking Cookies of the First Batch, correct?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Yeah! Do you know where we can find them?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_3">Hm... It seems they harbor no foul intentions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_4">And they appear to have aided in this debacle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_5">I ask you this. Why do you seek the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">If we find them, we might be able to help our friend recover her lost memories! Her name is First Cream Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_7">First Cream Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_8">Yeah! First Cream Cookie has to stay close to her home right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_9">So we decided to find them for her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_10">I see. First Cream Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">If she is involved in their quest... I suppose it is only natural for me to aid them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_12">Come. Follow me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_13">*GASP!*
So there is a Cookie of the First Batch in the Chocosseum?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_14">Yes. Due to certain circumstances, they are being sheltered in my chambers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">This is awesome! We found another one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_16">This is so exciting! I can\'t wait to meet them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0067_17">Huh? What happened here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_18">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_19">Agh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2016_20">They look huuurt...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_21">What has transpired here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_22">First Choco Cookie...! Something terrible has happened!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_23">A Cookie appeared from nowhere and... and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Npc.0066_24">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_25">Blast it all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_26">Hey! There\'s something on the ground here...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_27">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2015_28">We have no time to lose! Make haste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_1">The entire wall is broken...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_2">What a mess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_3">Where is the Cookie?
There\'s... no one here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_4">There\'s something on
the floor here too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_5">First Egg Cookie...
Must you resort to such...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_6">Wait, did you say,
\"First Egg Cookie\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_7">Rumors travel quickly. I knew she
was collecting the First Batch
for some nefarious purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_8">As a precaution, the Cookie
in question was kept close...
and well-guarded.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_9">Blast... I knew
something was amiss.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_10">There was no reason
for the Choco Golem
to malfunction...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_11">It is now confirmed.
It was merely a distraction
to kidnap the First Batcher.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0067_12">First Choco Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">... How can we help?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_14">Pardon me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_15">We\'re already looking
for Cookies of the
First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_16">And we still have a
lot more places
to search.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_17">At some point, we\'re
bound to run into
First Egg Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_18">The Cookie who was
kidnapped is someone
special to you, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_19">Then let us help!
We\'re more than willing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">We\'ll find them!
And we\'ll keep them safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_21">Perhaps this ragtag band is
far from feeble and fragile.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_22">The First Batcher is strong.
I am more concerned
for your safety.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_23">Even I struggle to
see myself besting
First Egg Cookie in combat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_24">We\'ll figure
something out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_25">We just want to
help everyone
we can...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_26">And as long as we don\'t
give up, we\'ll always be
able to find a way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_27">Heehee!
Another great speech!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_28">I see why First Cream Cookie
has placed her trust in them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_29">... Thank you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_30">Then I shall extend
a promise to you as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_31">Your journey will be
difficult and harrowing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_32">When you encounter an
impossible foe, call upon the
warriors of the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_33">We shall rush to your aid,
wherever you may be.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_34">I swear on my
name and honor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Npc.0067_35">And I promise to keep training!
I won\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2016_36">Meee too! I\'ll be muuuch
stronger the next time
we meet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_37">Haha! And we promise
to never give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_38">Hehe! All this talk is making me
feel all warm and toasty inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_39">I look forward to
meeting you again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_40">You too...!
And stay safe, everyone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_41">Go forth,
brave warriors.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA02_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2015_42">The bravest I have
witnessed thus far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_1">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_2">I sense... Ah-ha.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_3">Reveal yourself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.0044_4">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_5">Identify yourself, or face the consequences.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.0044_6">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_7">If you refuse to come out of your own volition, then I shall force you out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.0044_8">No! It\'s too dangerous... Get away, or you\'ll get hurt...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_9">You are gravely mistaken if you believe that I am the one in danger here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.0044_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_1_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">Is that a silent threat...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_1">I don\'t want to hurt you... It\'s too dangerous to be near me, so get as far away as you can.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_2">\"Hurt me\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_3">Interesting. No Cookie has ever said anything of the sort to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_4">Does this Cookie wield extraordinary power?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_5">How interesting indeed...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_6">What strength do you possess? Do you believe yourself to be powerful enough to become an initiate of the Chocosseum?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_7">Get away... Please, just go...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_8">There is a way to test your strength, to its very core and its furthest limits. Take the trial of the Chocosseum and prove your worth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_9">I said... stay back...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_10">Ah, how could I forget. The Choco Golem is still undergoing repairs. Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_11">I shall be your opponent then. Come, show me your strength, warrior.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_12">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_13">If you refuse to make the first move, then I shall.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_14">Is she even listening to me?! It\'s like talking to a wall...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_15">No...! If this goes on any longer... the monster within me will... I don\'t want to see anyone get hurt!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_16">I can\'t... I don\'t want to see anyone... get hurt...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.0044_17">Urgh...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_2_POR1_Cookie.2015_18">...!
Stop right there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.0044_1">Stop following me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.0044_2">I need to get as far away as I can! Away from her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.0044_3">That window over there! I can escape through it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_4">You cannot flee my grasp!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.0044_5">Argh...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_6">Blast it all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_7">I did not expect that Cookie to jump through the window.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_8">A Cookie who managed to evade me? HA! How VERY interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_9">I\'ve no doubt that Cookie is more than capable of becoming a strong warrior of the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_10">Is anyone out there? Guard! Hearken to me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Npc.0065_11">Yes, First Choco Cookie! What is your command?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_12">I must find a mysterious Cookie who was here moments ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Npc.0065_13">A Cookie? Who do you seek?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_14">A Cookie with gray, scruffy hair with a strong scent of pepper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_15">This Cookie has the makings of a great warrior. Find that Cookie at once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Npc.0065_16">Ah! I see a small patch of fur in that corner! Did it belong to the mystery Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Npc.0065_17">I shall heed your command and seek this Cookie! I will not fail!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_18">Good. Move out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_19">Just you wait, mysterious, scruffy Cookie of pepper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2015_3_POR1_Cookie.2015_20">I will not rest until you\'ve become a true warrior of the Chocosseum.</string>
