  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.Main">Danger? HA!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.01">A Dangerous(?) Cookie</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.02">Are You Worthy?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.03">Peppery, Gray Fur</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.01.Summary">An intruder has appeared in First Choco Cookie\'s room?! First Choco Cookie demands the intruder to reveal their identity, but the mysterious Cookie wants to avoid all contact. How intriguing...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.02.Summary">Werewolf Cookie is afraid that he might hurt First Choco Cookie. But his concern and demeanor only makes First Choco Cookie become more intrigued!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Title.03.Summary">Desperate to keep his distance, Werewolf Cookie makes a run for it. First Choco Cookie commands her guards to seek him out... She will not rest until he is made a true warrior of the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Illust.Dialog.01">Get away,
or you\'ll get hurt...!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2015.Illust.Dialog.02">You are gravely mistaken
if you believe that I am
the one in danger here.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2015.TeddyBear">First Choco Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2015.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Choco Cookie. Despite the fact that it\'s a toy, it\'s proving difficult to approach it. Maybe it\'s the icy steel gaze... Or the intimidating armor...</string>
  <string name="$Season.2015.Complete.Profile">Completed First Choco Collection</string>
  <string name="$Season.2015.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the First Choco Collection. Always remember to acknowledge individuality as sign of strength, not weakness.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2015">First Choco Cookie\'s Room of Absolute Strength</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2015.Story">The strongest of warriors never slack off. They give it their all in everything they do, from training to rest! First Choco Cookie\'s room exudes an aura of discipline and authority that overwhelms most ordinary Cookies. Even after the warriors of the Chocosseum have completed their training, you can hear the clashing of steel against wood as First Choco Cookie continues her training throughout night and day.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.001">Crown of the Victorious</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.002">Guardian\'s Brooch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.003">Swords of the Paragon</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.001.Story">A crown adorned with chocolate wings—a symbol of absolute victory. None dare to stand before this emblem without bowing their heads in reverence.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.002.Story">A brooch gleaming with the unyielding resolve of First Choco Cookie. It is a symbol of her conviction and vow to never lose anyone again.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2015.003.Story">A pair of colossal swords, said to have protected countless lives amidst an endless war. Only the mightiest of champions can wield these blades, as ordinary Cookies cannot even lift them.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015">First Choco Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Story">A lone cacao tree once stood amidst a forgotten battlefield. The flames of war provided it with light, and blades of steel nourished its roots. It was beneath this solitary tree where First Choco Cookie slowly opened her eyes for the first time.

Wielding enchanted blades that respond to her commanding voice and to her alone, this merciless warrior can cut through legions of enemies with ruthless precision and speed, leaving none in her wake. Her strength alone is enough to pummel enemy strongholds into gravel and graves.

Though her unflinching gaze and cold demeanor can send shivers down the spines of even the bravest Cookies, hidden beneath the cacao nib armor lies a sweet and tender heart.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016">Melted Choco Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Story">This Cookie\'s dough was made by mixing various flavors and types of chocolate, from sweet, melt-in-your-mouth to bitter and rich. But... perhaps the oven wasn\'t burning hot enough for a proper baking. Unlike most Cookies, whenever Melted Choco Cookie is exposed to even the slightest bit of warmth, he slowly melts into a soft, gooey mess.

As he often finds himself melting away and slouching down, he believes himself to be a feeble nobody... Not to worry though! He just hasn\'t realized his own incredible potential! Just like flowing water can take any form, having a body of melted chocolate means this Cookie\'s soft and oozy dough harbors limitless possibilities just waiting to be uncovered!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Random.01">The strong do not know
the meaning of defeat.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Random.02">Do you have something you wish
to protect with all your heart?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Random.03">Never give up.
Never surrender.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Random.04">My... past? I refuse to remember
that period of weakness...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Random.05">What time is it...?
Ah, time for the next training session.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Get">The last thing you will
see are my blades.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.LifeZero.01">... This will not be my end.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Monologue.Greeting">Get behind me, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;.
I shall be your guardian.</string>
