  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Soulstone">First Choco Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Soulstone">Melted Choco Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2015.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Choco Cookie\'s soul. It emanates an immeasurable amount of courage and charisma.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Melted Choco Cookie\'s soul. It\'s warm to the touch... and very cute and squishy too!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Ceil.999">First Choco Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to First Choco Cookie\'s Room of Absolute Strength</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_ch1_sq1.Summary">The Cookies have arrived to the fabled Chocosseum. What lies in store for them here? As they discuss their next move, a strange Cookie approaches them!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_ch1_sq2.Summary">Our friends have a hunch that there is a Cookie of the First Batch in the Chocosseum. But entry is only granted to those who have passed the Great Trial!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_ch1_sq3.Summary">The Cookies declare they want to participate in the Great Trial, but they can\'t! The next trial won\'t be held for several days... Is there no other way?</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_ch1_sq4.Summary">The Cookies, who are unable to participate in the trial, are disheartened. But they discover a pair of Cookies who are talking about the trial! The two look injured too... Time to lend them a hand!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch2_sq1.Summary">Our heroes share a Life Potion with their newly-met friend, Melted Choco Cookie. He tells them about the Chocosseum, the trial, and its laws as a gesture of thanks.</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch2_sq2.Summary">The Chocosseum is a safe haven within a harsh land and many are eager to enter. Melted Choco Cookie promises to help the Cookies enter the Chocosseum, provided he passes the trial first...</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch2_sq3.Summary">Corn Choco Cookie believes that Melted Choco Cookie will not be able to pass the trial and is willing to relinquish his spot in the Chocosseum...</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch2_sq4.Summary">Melted Choco Cookie is sad that Corn Choco Cookie is willing to sacrifice his hard-earned spot in the Chocosseum. Melted Choco Cookie blames his frail body for everything... But GingerBrave steps in with a few encouraging words!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch2_sq5.Summary">Melted Choco Cookie, invigorated by GingerBrave\'s words, is willing to try his best in tomorrow\'s trial. But until then... it\'s time for some last-minute training!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch3_sq1.Summary">The Great Trial of the Chocosseum has begun! Melted Choco Cookie enters the arena, head held high with confidence! But that confidence doesn\'t last long...</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch3_sq2.Summary">Melted Choco Cookie has been disqualified from the trial. Corn Choco Cookie is about to step in and sacrifice his spot... but the Choco Golem malfunctions and begins to spread havoc!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch3_sq3.Summary">Chaos erupts in the Chocolosseum as the Choco Golem goes berserk! Though he is convinced he is incapable of protecting or helping anyone, Melted Choco Cookie makes a decision. No matter what happens, he will try to protect his friends!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_ch4_sq4.Summary">It turns out that Melted Choco Cookie\'s soft and oozy body is the perfect defense against the Choco Golems attacks! But it looks like he won\'t be able to hold out any longer...!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch3_sq5.Summary">That was a close call! Just as Melted Choco Cookie was about to succumb to the Choco Golem\'s final strike, First Choco Cookie swoops in to save him! The day is saved...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch4_sq1.Summary">First Choco Cookie expresses her gratitude and respect for Melted Choco Cookie\'s selfless courage. As she looks upon him, she is reminded of her past...</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch4_sq2.Summary">First Choco Cookie discovers the Choco Golem has been tampered with... How nefarious! But before she begins a detailed investigation, she announces several changes to the laws of the Chocosseum.</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch4_sq3.Summary">GingerBrave and friends finally get the chance to meet another Cookie of the First Batch. But what\'s this? The guards in front of First Choco Cookie\'s chambers have been incapacitated?</string>
  <string name="$Saga02_Ch4_sq4.Summary">We\'re too late! The First Batcher has been kidnapped by First Egg Cookie...! Our friends make a promise to First Choco Cookie... A promise to find the missing Cookie!</string>
