  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.001.Story">A bed decorated to symbolize the golden achievement of victory. Somehow, it seems like the bed will only welcome those who have never lost in battle.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.002.Story">A bed decorated to symbolize victory. The sweet aroma of its covers are enough to melt away the fatigue of training all day.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Hanger.001.Story">A symbol of eternal conquest and triumph. May the swords of the Paragon carry you to victory!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Wall.001.Story">A window modeled after First Choco Cookie\'s helmet. Standing in front of the window makes you want to deliver a noble and uplifting speech.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Wall.002.Story">A crest forged from molten chocolate of many flavors. It is said that merely gazing upon this symbol is enough to strike terror into the hearts of your opponents.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Ceil.001.Story">A chandelier made from the same material as the Chocosseum\'s walls. How is it not melting...?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.WP.001.Story">Wallpaper made from thick panels of sturdy chocolate. These panels are durable and soundproof, providing a perfect environment for some intense training session!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Deck.001.Story">Flooring made from thick panels of sturdy chocolate. The patterns are simple and clean. They seem to reflect the owner\'s discipline and charisma.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Ceil.002.Story">A reminder of a hard-earned victory. Just looking at it fills your heart with pride.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Wall.003.Story">A symbol of a warrior\'s discipline. Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.003.Story">A collection of weapons, worn and battered due to many training sessions. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Hanger.002.Story">A garland that fills your heart with the pride of triumph. It goes well wherever you place it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Rug.001.Story">A clean carpet with crisp corners and edges. Simply putting it in a room makes it look more elegant.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.004.Story">A stool to use for a moment\'s rest. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.005.Story">A training dummy that has been used for many training sessions. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.006.Story">A small table with nutritious snacks. You can\'t train on an empty stomach!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2015.Floor.007.Story">Choco braziers lit with intense flames. How are they not melting?</string>
