  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">*Hum, hum, hum*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_2">What\'s with the humming? Something got you in a good mood?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_3">My training is finally paaaying off! I\'m getting strooonger and stronger!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_4">Haha! We\'re all training together, so of course you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_5">Nooo, that\'s not what I meant. After we\'re done traaaining at the Chocosseum, I go home and continue with some eeextra training!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_6">Huh? Training some more at home, eh? That\'s some serious dedication...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_7">You must be doing some intense training to be that confident in your strength!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_8">Hehehe, exactly! Aaand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_9">I\'m gonna show you my special traaaining regimen...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_10">Alright, I\'ll bite. Show me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_11">Hehe, preeepare to be amaaazed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">TADAAA! This is my training gear!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_13">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_1_POR1_Npc.0067_14">You can\'t be serious...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">Take a look at this! A fearsome, terrifying training dummy... Made from marshmallows!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_2">Marsh... mallows...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_3">Aaand these aren\'t nooormal marshmallows...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_4">Oookay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_5">They were roasted on top of a roooaring fire to make them extra tough and sturdy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_6">But roasting marshmallows just makes them... Never mind. Yeah, I guess they are quite... \"tough\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">I kneeew you\'d appreciate it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_8">AAAnd I\'m quite proud of this one: a chocolate target! It\'s for practicing with speeears like... THIS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_9">See? Doesn\'t it look really taaasty now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_10">This thing\'s even softer and mushier than the training dummy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_11">I use all this stuff every day for my extra traaaining...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_12">Well? Wuddya thiiink of my gear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_13">Yeah... I guess you could say I\'m... speechless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_14">I kneeew it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_15">Corn Choco Cookie! You can use my room for extra traaaining too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_16">C\'mon! Give it a try! Don\'t be shyyy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Npc.0067_17">Agh! I can\'t take this anymore!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_2_POR1_Cookie.2016_18">*GASP!*
You just... broooke my training dummy in one punch?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_1">Oooh... I spent days roasting those maaarshmallows...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_2">That training dummy was far from fearsome and terrifying...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_3">I barely put anything into that punch! That wasn\'t a dummy, it was practically a melting plushie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_4">Buuut... I roasted it peeerfectly... To make it tougher and sturdy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_5">Roasted marshmallows are still marshmallows! Roast them all you want, they\'ll just melt and burn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_6">And this target? It\'s too squishy! Look, I\'m barely touching it and it\'s about to fall over!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_7">Nooo...! I used that for taaarget practice...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_8">I can\'t believe this is what you\'ve been doing! Spending your free time to make all this shabby training gear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_9">I wondered why you were nodding off in our daily training sessions... And it looks like I\'ve found my answer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_10">Well, no more! Come with me! I\'m gonna teach you how to train properly myself, starting from the very basic of basics!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_11">Noooo! Don\'t draaag me away from my precious geeear...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Npc.0067_12">Nuh-uh! You\'re coming with me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_13">Nooo! My training geeear...! I won\'t leeeave you...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2016_3_POR1_Cookie.2016_14">I\'ll be baaack! I\'ll fiiix you soon...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Get">I want to get strooonger!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Random.01">Do you think I can
get strooonger...?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Random.02">The Chocosseum is awesome...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Random.03">I don\'t wanna be a burden
to my friends...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Random.04">I\'ll keep traaaining to
become a strong warrior!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Random.05">It\'s such a nice daaay!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Oh dear... I\'ve melted a bit too much...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Monologue.Greeting">Hellooo, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;! I\'ve been waiting for you!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2016.Skill.Name">Gooey Choco Punch</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2016">Melted Choco Cookie\'s Ooey Gooey Melty Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2016.Story">Melted Choco Cookie\'s room is decorated with many varieties of chocolate, both solid and gooey! Having a training dummy and ice cream target in his room makes one thing clear—Melted Choco Cookie\'s desire to grow stronger is as rich as the chocolate in his dough!</string>
