  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.001.Story">A towering choco cake topped with colorful fruits and even more chocolate. The cream is piled so high it looks like it might slide off at any moment. But worry not—it\'s sturdier than it looks. When you step inside, you\'re immediately wrapped in the comforting and tasty aroma of rich chocolate that seems to melt away all your problems.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.002.Story">A towering choco cake topped with even more chocolate. The cream is piled so high, it looks like it might slide off at any moment. But worry not—it\'s sturdier than it looks. When you step inside, you\'re immediately wrapped in the comforting and tasty aroma of rich chocolate that seems to melt away all your problems.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.003.Story">A thick, chocolate fondue fountain. Watching the silky chocolate trickle and flow down is mesmerizing. Resisting the urge to dip everything you can into the fountain is extremely difficult.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.004.Story">A practice target made of layered, gooey chocolate ice cream. It looks like it\'s already starting to melt... Better throw a spear and get some training in before it\'s completely gone!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.005.Story">A statue of a mighty warrior, carved from a single block of solid chocolate. Its glossy, polished surface almost seems to radiate strength and pride. Perhaps it\'s a reflection of one\'s deep desire to grow stronger.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Ceil.001.Story">A hanging mobile with various berries dipped in chocolate. It emits a fruity and sweet aroma that can make anyone drool...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Wallpaper.001.Story">A wall of simple squares of chocolate organized into an orderly pattern. It may look rigid and uninteresting at first glance, but a sweet, enticing aroma drifting through the air adds a smidgen of charm.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Deck.001.Story">A floor of flowing chocolate, layered in rich, gooey sweetness. Each color is said to be a different type and flavor of chocolate! And no, it\'s not weird if you have an urge to dip a spoon in it for a taste...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.006.Story">A training dummy that seems a bit too soft and flimsy... I guess it serves its purpose...?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.007.Story">A chair that\'s been... bitten? By whom? Regardless, it\'s actually quite comfy!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Ceil.002.Story">Curtains made from melting chocolate. Looking at it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Ceil.003.Story">A lamp decorated with dripping chocolate. This will look great wherever you decide to put it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Rug.001.Story">A rug made from chocolate waffles. Any room would look cozier with it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.008.Story">A fence made from tough chocolate wafers. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Wall.001.Story">Shields with simple patterns. Looking at it makes you feel strong.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Floor.009.Story">A marshmallow stool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2016.Hanger.001.Story">A collection of frames with symbols found in the Chocosseum. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.001">Marshmallow Sweater</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.002">Unhardened Choco Shield</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.003">Small Choco Spear</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.001.Story">A fluffy and cozy sweater made from the softest marshmallows. No matter how many times Melted Choco Cookie trips and falls or bumps into things, this super-soft and surprisingly durable sweater always cushions the blow!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.002.Story">A chocolate shield that hasn\'t been hardened or reinforced. It\'s still a bit too soft to withstand heavy blows... Despite its flaws, Melted Choco Cookie is proud to have created this shield himself in preparation for entering the Chocosseum!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2016.003.Story">A sharp chocolate spear tip attached to a wafer pole. It looks formidable and somewhat intimidating at first, but on closer inspection... Well, let\'s just say it probably won\'t be so useful after a few swings.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2016.TeddyBear">Melted Choco Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2016.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Melted Choco Cookie. When you give it a big, warm hug, it feels extra squishy and oh-so-soft!</string>
  <string name="$Season.2016.Complete.Profile">Completed Melted Choco Collection</string>
  <string name="$Season.2016.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the Melted Choco Collection. Even the gooiest and softest of Cookies can have a will stronger than iron!</string>
