  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2016.Title.01.Summary">Lately, Melted Choco Cookie has been training hard, growing stronger and brimming with newfound confidence. Curious about his training regimen, Corn Choco Cookie decides to visit Melted Choco Cookie\'s room!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2016.Title.02.Summary">Corn Choco Cookie witnesses Melted Choco Cookie\'s so-called \"training\" unfold... It\'s definitely not what he imagined. How is anyone supposed to become a strong warrior with such soft and squishy equipment?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2016.Title.03.Summary">Corn Choco Cookie points out ever flaw in Melted Choco Cookie\'s training regimen, one by one. It looks like the road to becoming a strong warrior is still going to be a long and arduous journey...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2016.Illust.Dialog.01">Come with me! I\'m gonna
teach you how to
train properly myself.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2016.Illust.Dialog.02">Noooo!
Don\'t draaag me away...!!!</string>
