  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Whoa! Look at THAT!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">It\'s a giant circus tent...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_3">A circus sounds like so much fun! We should go and watch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_4">With a crowd this big, there\'s bound to be a Cookie who knows about the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_5">Welcome, welcome! The show is about to begin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_6">The one and only, always hilarious and brilliantly entertaining First Sprinkle Cookie will perform an all-new act!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_7">Oh no! My drumstick! Someone please grab that runaway drumstick for me!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_event.0003_8">HEEHEE!!! I\'ll get it for ya, Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Oh...! There\'s a small Cookie over there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_10">Is it just me, or does that Cookie bear a striking resemblance to GingerDozer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_npc.0069_11">*GASP*
Sweet cinnamon swirls! IT\'S FIRST SPRINKLE COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_npc.0070_12">I\'VE SEEN EVERY ONE OF YOUR SHOWS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_13">Thank you, thank you! Just wait a bit and you\'ll get to see a circus show filled with nothing but glee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_14">Looks like we found First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">Everyone seems to love her...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_16">There you are, Giggles.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_17">Our super-duper important guest should be inside, not outside! C\'mon, let\'s head on in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_18">First Sprinkle Cookie! Wait a sec!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_19">Teehee! No time to delay! Our show\'s gonna be fun in the most thrilling of ways!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_1">She just blatantly ignored us...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_2">Greetings, wayfarers. My name is Ring Candy Cookie. Is this your first visit to our glorious circus?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">Yeah! We wanted to ask First Sprinkle Cookie something, but she just walked away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_4">Ah, so she\'s done it again it seems.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_5">Don\'t think too much about it. After all, the greatest show of all history awaits you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_6">This is a paradise of entertainment, the one-and-only Sprinkling-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_7">The genius performer and creator of laughter, the one-and-only First Sprinkle Cookie\'s \"Sprinkling Circus of Laughs\"!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_8">There\'s nothing she can\'t do! You name it, she\'s done it! The trapeze, ribbon dances, magic tricks, juggling stunts, and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_9">Yes, many, oh so many tricks and stunts. Everyone who was eager to watch her performances have gathered together to create this circus.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_10">But not everyone\'s able to put on an amazing show, hehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">Ain\'t that right, Cream Donut Cookie? All the little birdies are saying you lost your drumstick again, HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_12">I... I\'m squeezing in as much practice as I can...! I just need a bit more time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_13">Cease your hurtful taunting, Jelly Bean Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_14">Hehehe... Just jokin\' around with my favorite pal is all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_1">Hey, Ring Candy Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">About the Cookie who went inside the tent with First Sprinkle Cookie... Are they a Cookie of the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_3">Eh? I\'m not familiar with this so-called \"First Batch\"... But we call the little one \"Giggles\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_4">Everyone here is quite fond of her. There was an attempted kidnapping a while back, which is why the whole circus is taking extra precautions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_5">Giggles even laughs at Cream Donut Cookie\'s act!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_6">*Sigh*
Jelly Bean Cookie... What did I say about hurtful jokes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_7">Fine, fine! It\'s always me who gets nagged at... PFT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_8">I saw a giant shadow the day of the kidnapping... It looked like a bird with no beak or legs...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_9">I really hope nothing happens to Giggles...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_10">The situation is being handled. After all, we are all on the lookout for anything suspicious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_11">A failed kidnapping...? Do you think it might\'ve been, you know... First Egg Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">The failure works in our favor. We\'d better get Giggles out of here, and quickly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2020_1">Enough chattering!
The audience awaits us!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2018_2">Ah yes, it\'s already time
for the show.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2020_3">C\'mon, Cream Donut Cookie!
We still need you to
beat the drums!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_4">O-Okay!
Right behind you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2018_5">I should get going too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2018_6">Take a seat and enjoy
the show. I will introduce
you to Giggles after.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_7">Thanks,
Ring Candy Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_8">Welp!
Shall we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_9">Hooray!
This\'ll be so much fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_npc.0070_1">Ring Candy Cookie\'s trampoline act was amazing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_npc.0069_2">Did you see how majestic he looked up in the air? So shiny and dazzling!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_3">Look at that! A Banana Dolphin is juggling!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_4">WOW! They make it look so easy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">I particularly enjoyed the Giant Corn\'s feats of strength!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_6">Oh yeah! Me too! They lifted heavy candies like it was cotton candy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">Hold onto your popcorn! The real show\'s just begun!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_npc.0069_8">EEEK! IT\'S FIRST SPRINKLE COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_9">I\'ve been practicing my latest trick for AGES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_10">But, alas... Everyone\'s been having so much fun! It seems there\'s no need for my trick...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_11">Aw... Now I\'m sad... I don\'t have the strength to hang on...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">*GASP*
NOOO! HANG ON, FIRST SPRINKLE COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_13">She\'s gonna fall from the trapeze...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">I can\'t watch...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_15">HAAHAAHAA!
Worry not, folks! For I am First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_npc.0070_16">AMAZING! SIMPLY AMAZING!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_17">I... I knew she wasn\'t going to fall...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_18">I saw you cover your eyes, hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">I\'m in the mood for something more fun! I think I\'ll sit with the audience now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_2">Eh? Is the show over already?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_npc.0070_3">Haha, that\'s First Sprinkle Cookie for ya! So unpredictable!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_4">Well? What\'re y\'all waiting for? The show must go on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_5">Okie-dokie! It\'s time for ME to take the stage!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">Audience! I\'ve placed whoopee cushions under several of your seats, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_7">It\'s your job to guess which sounds came from whoopee cushions... and which sounds are real! TEEHEEHEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_8">Whaaat? That\'s all you\'ve got? BOOORING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_9">The cheeky trumpeting you let out in the break room yesterday was funny! Do THAT again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_npc.0069_10">HAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">Heeey, cut it out! You\'re just jealous that I\'ll steal your spotlight one day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_12">Everyone knows Giggles does all the work by starting the laughs and cheers! If I had Giggles for my act, then-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_13">That\'s quite enough, Jelly Bean Cookie. Let\'s step all the way over here... off-stage.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_14">*Muffled ranting*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_15">I guess that roasting routine was part of the show too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0025_16">That has to be scripted, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">If it is, they\'re really good actors! Everything felt so real!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_18">C\'mon! Isn\'t there a performer here who\'ll show us something new?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_19">Even First Yeast Cookie could put on a funnier show than whatever THAT was supposed to be.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_20">Hellooo? Anyone? Hurry up! I don\'t care what you do, as long as it\'s fun!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">No volunteers? Fine then... Cream Donut Cookie, you\'re up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_2">Huh?! M-M-M-Me? But... I\'m still drumming...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_3">Go on! Take the stage! You always wanted to give the audience a grand show!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_4">Give it up for our very own Cream Donut Cookie! He\'s gonna perform a tightrope walking, one-Cookie band show!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_npc.0070_5">WOOOW! WOOHOO! YEAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_6">W-W-Wait, First Sprinkle Cookie...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">Get out there! A true performer can make a mistake on stage become part of the act!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_8">O-O-Okay then... Here I g-g-gooo...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_9">Oh... OH...! AAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_10">GAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_npc.0069_11">Hahaha! Look at his face!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_npc.0070_12">He\'s hanging onto the rope like some upside-down snail, haha!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_13">C\'mon, Cream Donut Cookie! Get back on that rope! TEEHEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Wait a second... I don\'t think this is part of the act!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_15">Cream Donut Cookie\'s in trouble!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_16">My drum is... too heavy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2019_17">I\'m losing... my grip...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2018_1">Jelly Bean Cookie!
Conjure a balloon, now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2020_2">Oh, so now you need my help?
Fine, but I choose the balloon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_3">AAAGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_4">OOOF!!!
Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0069_5">HAHAHA! Was that the whoopee
cushion or did he just
really toot his own horn?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2017_6">HEEHEEHEE!
That was amazing,
Jelly Bean Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0070_7">I can\'t stop my laughing!
Oh, my stomach is gonna burst!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_8">This... doesn\'t feel right...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">HEY! Cream Donut Cookie
was in real danger and
could\'ve been hurt!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2017_10">EVERYONE! Let\'s give
Cream Donut Cookie
the biggest round of applause!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0069_11">AHAHA! Bravo,
Cream Donut Cookie, BRAVO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_12">Oh... Erm...
T-T-Thank y-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2018_13">Cream Donut Cookie.
Are you okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_14">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">Oh no! Cream Donut Cookie
just ran outside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_16">First Sprinkle Cookie!
This is all much too harsh!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2017_17">So what? He got the laughs!
That\'s all that matters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2017_18">It\'s what he always wanted:
making the audience laugh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_19">I\'m not getting
through at all, am I?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_20">C\'mon guys. Let\'s check up
on Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_1">*Sigh...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_2">Cream Donut Cookie? Are you alright?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_3">Oh, I\'m... No, I don\'t think so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_4">... First Sprinkle Cookie doesn\'t care how we feel. We\'re nothing more than just props for her to juggle and throw around!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_5">I... I love the circus. But I don\'t want to be a part of something so embarrassing and heartbreaking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_6">There you are, Cream Donut Cookie. You must have been terrified. I promise to stop such antics before they even begin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_7">First Sprinkle Cookie is well-versed in tricks and stunts, but not so much about the feelings of others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_8">I hope you can find it in your heart to move past this accident as well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_9">After all, you still admire First Sprinkle Cookie\'s performances and tricks, don\'t y-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_10">I... I don\'t wanna talk about it right now.
*Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_11">Wait, Cream Donut Cookie! And... he\'s gone once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0025_12">Wow... What a great, comforting speech. Kudos...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0002_13">What did you mean when you said First Sprinkle Cookie doesn\'t know much about feelings...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_14">*Sigh*
For First Sprinkle Cookie... fun is the only thing that matters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_15">Good or bad, right or wrong—such things do not reside in her mind. I try my best to talk things through, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_16">... In the end, I too am just a mere performer. My words do not carry much weight.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0003_17">Wait, a \"mere performer\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_18">Yes, but I cannot divulge any more information. This is First Sprinkle Cookie\'s story to share, not mine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_19">I have a favor to ask. I need to get ready for the next act... Could you find Cream Donut Cookie for me? For the circus?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_20">I shall keep my word and introduce you to Giggles after the next act.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_21">Of course! Don\'t worry—we\'ll find Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_1">That shifty, shady traveler was right. There\'s no way I\'ll ever become the star of the circus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_2">All I had to do was separate Giggles from the crowd... and First Sprinkle Cookie would be taught a lesson! But what now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_3">*Sob, sob*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_4">Cream Donut Cookie? Looking for a crying spot, are we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_5">*Sniffle*
Just leave me alone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">You little pipsqueak, I was here first. I oughta... Wait.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_7">... Cream Donut Cookie, I totally get how you\'re feeling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_8">Look, I had to send out that whoopee cushion to make the crowd laugh. But it wasn\'t like I WANTED to get them laugh AT you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">You\'ve noticed it too, right? How First Sprinkle Cookie treats us like crumbs and scraps, thrown out onto the stage whenever she feels like it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_10">Crumbs...? That\'s... going a bit too far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">C\'mon, you know what I\'m talking about here. She made a fool out of you!!! Don\'t ya wanna get even?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_12">Listen closely. I\'m gonna play a prank on First Sprinkle Cookie when she\'s on stage!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_13">All I need is for you to bring Giggles here and hide behind this pile of balloons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_14">If everything works out, we\'ll have the last laugh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_15">I... I don\'t think this is a good idea... What if-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_16">She wasn\'t laughing at our performance. She was laughing AT US! Now, it\'s her turn to feel what it\'s like.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2020_17">I\'m not asking ya to do anything super difficult, am I? All you need to do is get Giggles and keep her safe, right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_18">Okay... I-I-I\'m in...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">What the...? We need to start the next act! Where\'s Cream Donut Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_2">Hm... The travelers still haven\'t found him?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_npc.0070_3">What gives? Why isn\'t the next act starting?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_4">Wait—Giggles! Has anyone seen Giggles?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_5">Ring Candy Cookie! Just get the show started already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">Everyone! Ladies and gentlemen! The show begins... NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">Eh? Jelly Bean Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_npc.0070_8">What\'s that? Is that a feathered ball? Is this some sort of new balloon trick?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_npc.0069_9">Who cares! It\'s new! It\'s fresh! Hurry up and get on with the show! ENTERTAIN US, woohoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_10">....!
I\'ve... Where have I seen that before...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">Focus your eyes on this mysterious sphere, my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_12">My next act is called...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_13">rEvEnGe On FiRsT sPrInKlE cOoKiE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_14">NO, that\'s...!!!
Everyone, get off the stage! Get out of the tent! NOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_npc.0071_15">Find... Find...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ3_POR1_npc.0071_16">Find the Cookie of the First Batch—the one who possesses ancient strength...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_1">Are we playing hide-and-seek?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_2">Yeah, we are...
So we need to stay quiet, okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_3">Teeheehee! Okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_4">I wonder if the
prank\'s started...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_5">I bet the audience is mocking
First Sprinkle Cookie by now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_6">What\'s mocking?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_7">Oh... Mocking is like laughing,
but it\'s... something not nice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_8">Not nice? But I thought
laughing was a good thing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_9">Yeah, mostly. I guess you\'ve
never laughed at my tricks in
a bad way though.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_10">Yeah! I love your acts
and your music!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_11">Oh... Thanks. I like it
when you laugh, Giggles.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_12">Cream Donut Cookie.
Is that a new trick?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_13">What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0072_14">First... Batch...! 
Found! First! Batch!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_15">What is that thing?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_16">HEEELP! Ring Candy Cookie,
First Sprinkle Cookie! ANYONE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_event.0003_17">We\'re running now!
WHEEE! TEEHEEHEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0072_18">Subject matches
Jelly Bean Cookie\'s testimony...
RETRIEVE! RETRIEVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_19">Jelly Bean Cookie?
WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_20">I\'ve been tricked...!
How could I have
been so stupid?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_21">I should\'ve stayed with the troupe...!
Then, at least, Giggles would be safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0003_22">Found you,
Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.2019_23">You guys! HELP ME!
Those... egg things want to take Giggles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0001_24">Are they minions of
First Egg Cookie?!
Quick, protect Giggles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_npc.0072_25">Retrieve!
RETRIEVE!
RETRIEVE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0025_26">Back!
Back, you fiends!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_Cookie.0002_27">There\'s too many of\'em...!
We\'re doomed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">Who. Wrote. This. AWFUL. PERFORMANCE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_2">Who ruined our perfect circus?! Get out here, NOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.0001_3">First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_4">I\'ll smash your eggshells into smithereens and use the fragments to tile the circus\' kitchen floors!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_npc.0072_5">WARNING! WARNING! Major threat detected!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_6">UNFORGIVABLE! This is MY stage! This is MY circus! THIS IS MY TROUPE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_7">First Sprinkle Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_8">Why? Why are you doing this to me? After all the teasing and mocking, you\'re now helping me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_9">Do you want me to hate you or like you? I can\'t tell anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_event.0003_10">Cream Donut Cookie! The drums, teehee! Your drums!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_11">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_event.0003_12">First Sprinkle Cookie showing off some new tricks, teehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_event.0003_13">She needs music! Your music will make her tricks so much more fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_14">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_15">I\'ve been saving my powers for extreme acrobatics, but now I have to waste it on you PESTS?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2017_17">Is that... Cream Donut Cookie\'s drums?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2018_18">It\'s Cream Donut Cookie and Giggles! We found them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_19">Hang in there, First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ1_POR1_Cookie.2019_20">Let\'s put on a show they\'ll never forget!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0069_1">Do you hear... drums? Are they performing right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0070_2">I... I\'m not sure. It kinda sounds like they\'re fighting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_3">This isn\'t the time to play your drums, Cream Donut Cookie! Get yourself to safety!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_4">No! I... I\'m gonna keep playing... for First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_5">I still think she\'s super annoying and doesn\'t care about our feelings. And I hate heights. And I\'m bad at tricks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2019_6">But I still love watching First Sprinkle Cookie perform!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2018_7">Cream Donut Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_event.0003_8">TEEHEEHEE! Keep going, Cream Donut Cookie! You got this, First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0069_9">See, Giggles is laughing! It IS a performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0070_10">I guess so! But the fighting seems... so real!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0003_11">Look! Thanks to Giggles, the audience is starting to have fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.0001_12">Keep drumming, Cream Donut Cookie! Your drumbeat is what makes everything a real performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_13">Eh? Why\'s the audience coming back?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_14">Perfect! Cookies and critters, ladies and gentlemen! I\'ll give you the honor of becoming part of this brand-new show!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_15">HYAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0072_16">Warning. Warning. Difficulty of retrieval has increased exponentially. Retreat advised.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0071_17">You\'ll regret this... First Sprinkle Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_18">I dunno what sort of weird scheme you\'re planning. But go tell whoever sent you THIS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_19">If you show your face near my circus, or send your lackeys anywhere near my troupe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_20">I\'ll personally dunk you into rancid milk and knead you back into the rotten dough you were made from! Do you hear me, First Egg Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0071_21">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_22">...
Phew.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_Cookie.2017_23">And THAT, my friends, was the perfectly fun finale!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0069_24">*ROARING APPLAUSE*
WOO! THAT WAS AMAZING!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ2_POR1_npc.0070_25">It all seemed so real! That was the best performance ever! Bravo, Cream Donut Cookie! Brava, First Sprinkle Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_1">The audience is gone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_2">Where\'s Jelly Bean Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2020_3">*Muffled excuses*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_4">She was hiding out back. I shall venture a guess and say she did not expect such an... escalated level of turmoil.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_5">Let\'s, erm... Have her remain silent for now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_6">I don\'t get it! Why\'d you do this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">You joined our circus because you like fun! You like making others laugh! So why go out of your way to ruin everything?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2018_8">... Hm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0002_9">Erm, you know... Your circus is really fun. But sometimes, the troupe can get... you know, sad or tired...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0001_10">The circus might be precious, but so are your friends! You need to treasure them, cherish them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_11">Treasure...? Cherish...? What\'s that mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_12">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_13">Circus performers are supposed to feel sad and tired sometimes. It\'s all part of the deal, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0025_14">Wait, what are you talking about? You always look so happy and energetic when you\'re performing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_15">Because I have to! I\'m the ringmaster! I... I wasn\'t always like this when I was just a performer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_16">Nobody helped or said anything when I messed up. When I got scolded, when I got laughed at, and I didn\'t complain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_17">Because that\'s just how things were. Even if I was hurt after a show... even when I cried when no one was looking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_18">Whatever happened... The most important thing was that everyone had a good time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.0003_19">... Hm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ3_POR1_Cookie.2017_20">That\'s why, when I became a Cookie... When I finally got the chance to make my own circus, I thought it was the best thing in the world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">Now that I\'m ringmaster, I thought, no matter what happens, I\'d never let anything bring me down. No more boredom, sadness, or anger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_2">But when I look back... even when I thought I was happy, I was still sad. When every day was filled with laughter, my heart felt empty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_3">Is it because I don\'t understand the meaning of... cherishing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0002_4">First Sprinkle Cookie... Cookies can also feel boredom, sadness, and... even anger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0001_5">Those emotions are what help us find something precious to hold onto. And we work hard to protect it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.0003_6">When you realize something is truly precious, even when you\'re sad, you\'ll see that all the world is still one big, exciting stage with so many things waiting for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">All the world\'s... a stage...? Like, a circus?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_8">Someone told me something like that once. Who was it...? She was... a witch? Dressed in white? I don\'t remember...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_9">So, like, how do you make something precious? How do you treasure and cherish someone???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2018_10">... Cream Donut Cookie. I believe First Sprinkle Cookie is ready to listen to what\'s in your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2019_11">Erm... Right now?
... First Sprinkle Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2019_12">I love the circus. I love how happy it makes the audience. I love how happy it makes me and everyone in the troupe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2019_13">But... I don\'t want to perform if it\'s gonna be filled with sadness, anger, or embarrassment all the time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2019_14">This circus, Giggles, your performances and dazzling tricks...?  Everything is precious... I love everything and everyone here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2019_15">So, I guess what I\'m saying is... We adore and respect you, and we want you to think the same of us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_16">... I still don\'t really know what that means and I don\'t know how to do that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2017_17">But... I want to...
If you teach me, I\'ll learn and I\'ll try.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2018_18">And we are proud to join you in every step of the way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ4_POR1_Cookie.2018_19">Besides... When it comes to learning new tricks, you\'re a very fast learner.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2020_1">*Muffled ranting*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_2">Oh, we totally forgot about her.
Maybe we should let her speak now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2020_3">PWAHHH! I-I-I\'ll try too!
And I won\'t make fun of
Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2020_4">I swear I didn\'t know
things would get
THIS crazy and scary!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_5">*Sigh...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_6">If you pull off another stunt
like this, I\'ll tie you onto a
balloon and let it float away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2020_7">Okay! Okay!
It won\'t happen again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_8">Hey, erm... Shouldn\'t we ask about
taking Giggles somewhere safe?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_9">Actually, I think Giggles will be fine here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_10">If First Sprinkle Cookie learns
to treasure what\'s precious,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_11">even an entire army of
those Egg Golems
won\'t stand a chance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_12">Hey, you knew those golems
were lackeys of First Egg Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_13">Yup. You know
who she is too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0025_14">First Egg Cookie is
trying to kidnap all the
Cookies of the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_15">We\'re trying to find them
and make sure they\'re safe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_16">I don\'t remember everything...
But I know those golems
were created by First Egg Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_17">She uses them as her eyes and ears...
Oh, and as glorified microphones.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_18">She\'s a weird one. I asked her
how she made them, and she said
something about splitting souls...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_19">Anyway... If you\'re looking for
more Cookies of the First Batch,
you should be careful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_20">First Egg Cookie might look funny,
but she\'s a lot tougher than she looks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_21">My place is here, at the circus.
But if you need help, just say the word.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.2017_22">I\'ll help out if
I think it\'ll be fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0001_23">Thanks, First Sprinkle Cookie!
We\'ll let you know if there\'s
anything fun about to happen!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_Cookie.0003_24">Heehee! Thanks, everyone!
And goodbye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening01">Desserts and critters,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening02">ladies and gentlemen!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening03">Everyone\'s waiting for the perfect show.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening04">Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening05">I\'ll show you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening06">I\'ll make everyone laugh no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening07">Get ready,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening08">for the perfect laugh at</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA03_Opening09">the Sprinkling Circus!</string>
