  <string name="$SAGA.03.CinematicOpeningTitle">Sprinkling Circus</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_1">First Sprinkle Cookie...
Just you wait! One day, I\'m gonna be the star of this circus! ME! MEEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_2">But... and I hate to admit it...
She\'s too good! She\'s too perfect!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_3">What can I do to make her acts seem like child\'s play?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_4">Hm... She must be cheating! Or using tricks! Or some sort of secret technique!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_5">Oh, I know what to do! I\'ll sneak into her room and find out what she\'s hiding!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">This... is her room?
For crumbs\' sake... what a mess! This place is like a supply closet for props!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_7">Wait a minute...
Maybe one of these props is giving her the upper edge! Like some magical, secret weapon for perfect circus tricks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2017_8">\"A magical, secret weapon\"?
HA! I wish I had one of those!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">EEEK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">So you were sneaking around my room looking for some special secret to my circus acts?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_2">Yeah... I didn\'t mean... Well, I just wanted to... I just wanna be the best circus performer ever...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_3">Haha! Why didn\'t you say so?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_4">This is awesome! I never knew there was someone in our troupe who was so determined! So passionate! So driven!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_5">What do you wanna learn first?
No, wait... What do you wanna try first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">Wait... You\'re really just gonna... tell me stuff? Just like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">Yup, just like that.
What\'s there to not tell? It\'s all for making a better, funnier circus, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_8">Let\'s start here!
You see my bed?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">... It looks like our stage?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_10">Exactly! It\'s exactly like the stage! That way, I can practice new tricks and performances in my sleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_11">Sounds fun, doesn\'t it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_12">Erm... Er...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_13">You could also keep a mystery box filled with random props and take them out to practice whenever you have time and that way every chance you make for practice becomes a natural way to boost your improv skills!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_14">You should also think about stretching first thing in the morning and then hitting the gym to practice your acrobatics, jumps, and twirls. I recommend leaping through the rings first to improve your coordination and flexibility because those two go hand-in-hand for pretty much any-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_15">Hey! Are you listening, Jelly Bean Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_16">Erm... I... er...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_17">What\'s with all the yapping?! Are you really saying there isn\'t some super duper secret weapon you\'ve been using?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_1">All this stuff is like... for practicing your acts? That\'s it?! Just... practice?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2017_2">Of course! I practice when I sleep, I practice when I wake up, I practice after breakfast, I practice, practice, practice! And it\'s all for our circus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2017_3">Now, if you want me to go into details, I can-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2017_4">Eh? Jelly Bean Cookie? Where\'d you go?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_5">Ew, EW, EWWW! Practice?!
And all she ever thinks about is practice?! I could never do that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2017_6">Jelly Bean Cookie! Where aaare you? I haven\'t told you everything about practicing yet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_7">*GASP*
I need to hide! If First Sprinkle Cookie finds me, I\'ll be lectured until my dough turns dry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2019_8">Oh? Jelly Bean Cookie?
Are you... hiding from something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">Cream Donut Cookie!
Perfect timing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_10">First Sprinkle Cookie!!!
Cream Donut Cookie wants to learn your secrets!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2019_11">Eh? What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2017_12">Really?! That\'s amazing! Jelly Bean Cookie learned a thing or two from me just now, and I guess it\'s your turn next! You\'re in for a treat!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2019_13">Eh? I... What?
Wait, Jelly Bean Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_14">Sorry, Cream Donut Cookie...! You\'re on your own now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2017_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_15">I wholeheartedly and truly wish that you become the greatest circus performer ever! ... For everyone\'s sake!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.Main">The Ultimate Secret?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.01">There has to be a Secret Technique!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.02">Practice When Sleeping &amp; Awake</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.03">Sign Me Out!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.01.Summary">Jelly Bean Cookie, eager to learn First Sprinkle Cookie\'s secrets to performing the perfect acts and tricks, sneaks into her room to see if she has any secrets or hidden techniques. But First Sprinkle Cookie find her sneaking around!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.02.Summary">Surprisingly, First Sprinkle Cookie is more than happy to share her secret. She explains how her bed resembles a stage, which helps her practice when she\'s sleeping. She also claims to spend every waking moment practicing tricks and stunts. As Jelly Bean Cookie listens to First Sprinkle Cookie\'s so-called \"secrets\", her face grows pale...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Title.03.Summary">Unable to handle a life where every single minute involves practicing new tricks, Jelly Bean Cookie makes a run for it. First Sprinkle Cookie searches high and low for her. In a moment of sheer \"luck\", Jelly Bean Cookie comes across Cream Donut Cookie and shoves him forward to become a decoy as she makes her great escape!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Illust.Dialog.01">Eh? Jelly Bean Cookie?
Where\'d you go?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2017.Illust.Dialog.02">Ew, EW, EWWW!
Practice?! All she ever
thinks about is practice?!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017">First Sprinkle Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Story">One night, the moon glowed like a grand circus spotlight. As the night deepened, a Cookie woke up to a dazzling spectacle—hundreds of sprinkles shimmering inside a glass jar bathed in the moonlight.

That night marked First Sprinkle Cookie\'s rise to fame, the one-and-only grand ringmaster of the Sprinkling Circus of Laughs, a performer like no other in all history! With a flick of the wrist and a twirl in midair, she weaves magic and laughter, drawing gasps and cheers from every audience in every performance.

Through every moment, through every hardship, she never fails to bring joy and wonder to all who step into her circus. And so, legend has it that no Cookie, dessert, or critter has ever left her show without bursting into laughter!</string>
