  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Get">The show doesn\'t start until I take the stage!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Random.01">Did you enjoy today\'s show?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Random.02">Well, well!
This seems like fun!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Random.03">Hold onto your popcorn!
The real show\'s just begun!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Random.04">HEEHEE!
My tricks are always a hit!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Random.05">Isn\'t there anything fun
to do around here?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.LifeZero.01">This. Is. NOT. FUN...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2017.Monologue.Greeting">Hey, &lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;!
Today\'s circus show is gonna be AWESOME!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2017">First Sprinkle Cookie\'s Room of Dazzling, Jumbling Colors</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2017.Story">First Sprinkle Cookie\'s room is littered... or adorned... with all sorts of fancy circus props. Everything in this whirlwind of supplies serves a purpose in her pursuit to invent dazzling new tricks, dream up the greatest performances, and choreograph the fanciest of stunts. Any Cookie who steps into her room can\'t help but be captivated by all the fancy, funny toys!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.001">Circus Bed of Unending Laughs</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.002">Circus Bed of Laughs</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.003">Jumbled Box of Surprises</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Ceil.001">Cap and Bells Chandelier</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.001">Sprinkle Shaker</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.002">Arrow Neon Sign</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wallpaper.001">Wall of Sprinkles</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Deck.001">Circus Stage Flooring</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Ceil.002">Confetti-Filled Hat</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.004">Talented Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.003">Risky, Thrilling Dartboard</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Ceil.003">Bouncy Swinging Trapeze</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.005">Jelly Rope Ring</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.006">Perfect Balance Elephant Plush</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.004">Double Arrow Neon Sign</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.005">Sprinkling Prop Gun</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Hanger.001">Circus Garland</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.001.Story">Why would anyone want to sleep in a normal, boring bed? Why not fall asleep with a heart full of fun and joy?! This circus tent-shaped bed, decorated with sprinkles and balloons, is as lively as the circus stage! If you fall asleep here, you just might dream of becoming the star of the circus, basking in the cheers of a delighted audience!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.002.Story">Why would anyone want to sleep in a normal, boring bed? Why not fall asleep with a heart full of fun and joy?! This circus tent-shaped bed, decorated with sprinkles and balloons, reminds you of the circus stage. If you fall asleep here, you just might dream of stepping onto the stage to deliver a dazzling show!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.003.Story">This box is chock-full of props, toys, and supplies. Whenever you need to come up with a new act, look no further! You\'ll always be able to find something useful!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Ceil.001.Story">A clown hat that has become worn down by many fun-filled performances. But whenever it hits the dazzling stage lights, it magically appears to look brand new! It\'s said that every time you see this hat on stage, the joyful memories of your first circus act will come rushing back.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.001.Story">A vessel holding a variety of colorful sprinkles. Are you bored? Then give it a shake! Does your wall seem bland? Then hang it up!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.002.Story">A vibrant sign used to guide crowds to the circus entrance. The twinkling lights seem almost hypnotic and magical as you find yourself walking towards it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wallpaper.001.Story">Bedazzle your guests with this cute and happy wall! The sprinkles will give your walls some extra flair!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Deck.001.Story">The moment you step on this floor, you feel a rush of excitement. And a strong urge to dance!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Ceil.002.Story">A hat that contained a lot of confetti and ribbons. Let\'s put it to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Floor.004.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy with a gift for acrobatics and circus acts. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2017.Wall.003.Story">A breathtaking display of accuracy. Let\'s try not to break the thrower\'s concentration...</string>
