  <string name="$item.Deco.1stAnniversary.Floor.004.Story">From the moment we opened our eyes in the scorching oven to the countless adventures we\'ve had so far exploring every corner of Witch\'s Castle, this candy basket is a gift for all of our dear friends who have been with us for every step! There joyful days, but also some difficult ones... Yet we faced them together as friends! Here\'s to many more adventures and fun days ahead!</string>
