  <string name="$item.Deco.1stAnniversaryPackage.Floor.001.Story">No more tickets left for the circus? Don\'t be sad! A roaming stage awaits, just for you! Watch as the Banana Dolphin juggles with spectacular precision! Before you know it, your feet will start tapping and your hands will clap along to this amazing juggler\'s rhythm!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.1stAnniversaryPackage.Floor.002.Story">No more tickets left for the circus? Don\'t be sad! A roaming stage awaits, just for you! Watch as the Balloon Clown twists and transforms into all sorts of shapes and sizes in the blink of an eye! Before you know it, the frown on your face will change into a beaming smile!</string>
