  <string name="$Saga03_ch1_sq1.Summary">Our friends have discovered the fabled Sprinkling Circus of Laughs, where the legendary First Sprinkle Cookie performs with her troupe! But First Sprinkle Cookie just leaves before they can ask about Cookies of the First Batch! As they watch her vanish into the circus tent, they catch a glimpse of a young, small Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_ch1_sq2.Summary">Ring Candy Cookie tells the group about the Sprinkling Circus. Just hearing about it was enough to spark excitement and curiosity! But, oh dear... All the while, Jelly Bean Cookie and Cream Donut Cookie bicker back and forth.</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_ch1_sq3.Summary">The circus show sounds very fun and exciting, but the group doesn\'t forget their goal! GingerBrave and friends ask about the identity of Giggles, the tiny one who followed First Sprinkle Cookie into the circus tent. During their conversation, they learn that Giggles had once narrowly avoided being kidnapped! How sinister...!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_ch1_sq4.Summary">In order to meet Giggles, there was only one thing to do... Watch the circus! Perhaps they\'d be able to spot Giggles among the audience or after the show? For now... let\'s enjoy the circus!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch2_sq1.Summary">Just as Ring Candy Cookie claimed, the Sprinkle Circus was… SPECTACULAR! Our friends can\'t take their eyes off the amazing stunts and extravagant tricks. All of a sudden, First Sprinkle Cookie looks like she\'s going to faint in mid-air and plummet to her doom...! OH NO!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch2_sq2.Summary">What a performance! First Sprinkle Cookie put on a fantastic show for the Cookies and the audience. Jelly Bean Cookie\'s act is up next, but First Sprinkle Cookie begins heckling her! Erm... the arguing and bickering is all part of the act, right...? Right?</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch2_sq3.Summary">With Jelly Bean Cookie dragged off the stage, First Sprinkle Cookie thrusts Cream Donut Cookie into spotlight! The drummer is suddenly forced to walk the tightrope while doing a one-Cookie band performance! But it\'s all too much for the timid Cookie to handle...!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch2_sq4.Summary">By sheer luck, and with a bit of help from Jelly Bean Cookie\'s conjured balloons, Cream Donut Cookie safely makes it through unscathed. Before he can breathe a sigh of relief, Jelly Bean Cookie\'s balloons turn out to be a whoopee cushion! The noise turns Cream Donut Cookie into the laughingstock of the crowd... Heartbroken, he runs away, wounded in spirit.</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch3_sq1.Summary">Ring Candy Cookie attempts to comfort Cream Donut Cookie, but to no avail. Instead, Cream Donut Cookie runs off once more, disappearing into the distance... GingerBrave and friends decide to find and console him.</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch3_sq2.Summary">Jelly Bean Cookie has been plotting to pull a prank on First Sprinkle Cookie, and it turns out she got some instructions from a mysterious stranger as well... Just then, the still-sniffling Cream Donut Cookie appeared. Eager to set her plot into motion, Jelly Bean Cookie convinces him to take Giggles away and hide somewhere...</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch3_sq3.Summary">The show must continue, but both Giggles and Cream Donut Cookie have gone missing! As the audience waits, Jelly Bean Cookie suddenly appears while holding some strange feathered orbs... But wait! Those aren\'t ordinary orbs...!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_ch4_sq4.Summary">The feathered orbs transform into a swarm of Egg Golems that have been given a mission: KIDNAP GIGGLES! Cream Donut Cookie tries to flee, but is powerless to intervene!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch4_sq1.Summary">One by one, the Egg Golems fall before First Sprinkle Cookie\'s incredible power! Watching in awe, Giggles claps with excited glee, calling it a marvelous act! Giggles turns to Cream Donut Cookie and asks him to play his drums! After all... no performance is complete without the rhythm of Cream Donut Cookie\'s drums!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch4_sq2.Summary">Thanks to Cream Donut Cookie\'s drumming, the chaotic scene turns into a breathtaking performance! As the last golem is destroyed and the dust settles... the audience erupts into a roar of applause, laughs, and cheers!</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch4_sq3.Summary">First Sprinkle Cookie turns to Jelly Bean Cookie, demanding to learn why she caused such a mess. GingerBrave and friends gently suggest to First Sprinkle Cookie that everyone in the circus troupe should be treated with more care and treasured as precious friends, not just a circus crew. First Sprinkle Cookie seems puzzled at the concept...</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch4_sq4.Summary">First Sprinkle Cookie recalls when she was human and how she had to smile and laugh through sadness and hardship—all for the sake of the show. Realizing that she had been repeating history, she makes a promise to her troupe... She vows to create a truly joyful circus by cherishing and treasuring the important friendships made along the way.</string>
  <string name="$Saga03_Ch4_sq5.Summary">First Sprinkle Cookie reveals that the Egg Golems are indeed connected to First Egg Cookie! She warns our heroes that finding other Cookies of the First Batch will be a dangerous task... She bids them to take caution. After taking her advice to heart, GingerBrave and friends set off for the next destination!</string>
