  <string name="$Cookie.2018.Story">When the circus tents sway and twirl to the waltz of the evening winds, a pair of glimmering eyes gazes upon the crowd with a soft smile. Ring Candy Cookie, ever the picture of poise and charm, delivers a graceful performance that bedazzles and enchants the audience without breaking a sweat.

Yet behind the red curtain, tending to troupe members who dream of becoming stars, while also indulging a somewhat excessively whimsical ringmaster, proves no small feat. And so, when the final curtain falls and the last cheers fade into silence, Ring Candy Cookie lets out a hushed sigh... a wishful breeze in the quiet night. He hopes that, one day, the ringmaster will find delight and joy beyond the spotlight.</string>
