  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2018.Story">Ring Candy Cookie\'s room is lined with meticulously managed magical props. Though the spotlight may focus on the stage itself, it\'s the quiet preparation and heartfelt devotion behind the scenes that bring true brilliance to the performance.</string>
