  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Floor.001.Story">Beneath the dazzling lights... POOF! A hat filled with levitating cards and dancing flowers appears from nowhere! As the dreamlike spectacle reaches its climax, a question arises... Ba-dump. Ba-dump. Who will be performing this amazing show?!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Floor.002.Story">A prop inspired by Ring Candy Cookie\'s very own enchanted hat! Reach inside and you\'ll suddenly find cards and flowers tumbling out from nowhere. What secrets lie within this hat? A magician never reveals his secrets! Just watch the performance unfold and let the magic bedazzle you!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Hanger.001.Story">These sparkling balloons are filled with dreams and wonder! They\'ll soar high into the sky, twinkling like stars!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Floor.003.Story">Every performer needs a moment to breathe and relax behind the scenes! Take a short break before your dazzling debut! Just... don\'t get too comfy and miss your own performance!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Floor.004.Story">Which marvelous trick will be performed today? Leave it to the roulette to decide! Give it a good spin!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Ceil.001.Story">This curtain blocks every sliver of light. Once it\'s pulled back, it reveals the mysteries that happen backstage!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Wallpaper.001.Story">The perfect backdrop for any bedazzling performance. It makes every spell and flourish shine as bright as the stars!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2018.Deck.001.Story">A lush green carpet to perform on makes every magic trick and spell sparkle just a bit more!</string>
