  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">Well, well... So this is the Sprinkling Circus\' most affluently decorated room.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">Rumor has it this room harbors the circus\' most prized jewel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_3">I\'d usually case the area first, but even I couldn\'t sit idly by after hearing such information.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">Now then... Where are you hiding, you precious jewel?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Npc.0070_5">See? Shiny and glimmering as always!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Npc.0069_6">Truly the crown jewel of the Sprinkling Circus! Simply amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_7">It sounds like this so-called \"crown jewel\" will be returned to this room soon. Okay, time to be discrete and pretend to be a spectator...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2018_8">Thank you! I hope to see you at the next performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Npc.0069_9">EEEK!
Ring Candy Cookie!!! I\'m your biggest fan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_1_POR1_Cookie.2003_10">My, oh my! That\'s no jewel... The rumor was about a Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">Well, I could always kidnap him. But no, kidnappings are too much work compared to a heist...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_2">*Sigh*
Unfortunately, it seems this lead turned out to be a dead end. I should return home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_3">Huh? I don\'t remember seeing you here before... Where have you come from, wayward parasol?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">There you are, Clemens!
What a mischievous parasol you are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_5">Pardon my intrusion, but I shall be taking my parasol back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_6">Oh! You are...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_7">Ah, yes, I am a merely just a member of the audience and I have simply lost my way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_8">And I am about to depart for home, thank you very much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_9">Did you just... pull a sleight of hand?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_10">Marvelous! You managed to slip that parasol away in the mere blink of an eye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_11">Such astounding talent! You have the perfect qualifications to be a star performer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2003_12">I... Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_13">You said you\'ve come to view the circus and our show.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_14">But have you ever considered performing in a show yourself?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_1">Alas, I am already self-employed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_2">Your talents could really shine on stage.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_3">May we attempt a quick test? Here, take this dagger. No need to worry; it\'s not sharp at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_4">What? No! I refuse to take part in any sort of show! Get this thing away from me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_5">Amazing! A perfect bullseye! Right in the middle of the board!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_6">Oh dear... I just threw it like I usually do. I should have deliberately missed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_7">You were born to perform! You simply must!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_8">Ah, I know! We should pay a visit to First Sprinkle Cookie at once. She will be able to convince you that the circus is your destiny!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_9">Wait... but I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_10">Cream Donut Cookie! Do you perhaps know of First Sprinkle Cookie\'s whereabouts?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2018_11">Ah! There you are, First Sprinkle Cookie! I have discovered a true genius of a performer for our troupe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_12">Crumbs... Is there no escaping this torment...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2018_3_POR1_Cookie.2003_13">This is why one should always case a location before going in for a heist... Suffice it to say, I acted too hastily on mere hearsay.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.Main">Jewel Theft at the Circus?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.01">A Heist Based on Hearsay</string>
