  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.03">Potential to be a Star!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.01.Summary">Sachertorte Cookie has heard a rumor that the Sprinkling Circus of Laughs is home to a glimmering jewel of great renown! But it turns out the subject of the rumor is not about a valuable gemstone... It\'s about Ring Candy Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.02.Summary">The rumor Sachertorte Cookie heard never mentioned the \"crown jewel\" being a Cookie...! She attempts to slip away unnoticed, but Ring Candy Cookie\'s eyes sparkle with excitement, for he has just discovered Sachertorte Cookie\'s hidden talent as a circus performer!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Title.03.Summary">Caught off guard with an impromptu circus audition, Sachertorte Cookie somehow ends up showcasing her impressive skill in dagger-throwing. Unable to escape from Ring Candy Cookie\'s enthusiasm, a simple heist somehow turns into a very long day...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Illust.Dialog.01">I have discovered a true
genius of a performer!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2018.Illust.Dialog.02">Is there no
escaping this
torment...?</string>
