  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Story">This Cookie\'s soft, pillowy dough is filled with heaps of the fluffiest cream imaginable. Whenever the circus is about to begin, you can count on this one-Cookie band\'s cheerful drumbeat to rally the crowd. Maybe it\'s the pride and joy Cream Donut Cookie feels for the circus that makes his rhythm so infectious, because once again, the Sprinkling Circus of Laughs is packed!

Though a circus performer, Cream Donut Cookie can be a bit clumsy, often stumbling mid-beat. And his acrobatic tricks...? Always a spectacular flop. But that won\'t stop him from chasing his dream: to one day dazzle the crowd with flawless jumps, flips, and stunts on stage!

Until then, his drum beats on, just like his dreams—loud and full of hope!</string>
