The circus is in town!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Monologue.Random.02">One day, my show will make
everyone laugh and cheer!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Monologue.Random.03">Today\'s show will feature
an all-new performance!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Monologue.Random.04">Uh-oh! Can someone please
pick up my drumstick?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Monologue.Random.05">I\'m practicing as much
as I can too, hehe!</string>
