Today\'s show is spectacular!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2019">Cream Donut Cookie\'s Room of Abundant Dreams &amp; Cream</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2019.Story">Cream Donut Cookie\'s room is overflowing with all sorts of donut practice props, donut cushions, and donut costumes. Every effort made, no matter how small or soft, is a step toward his sweetest dream!</string>
