  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.001.Story">This small and cozy circus tent, decorated with colorful garlands and donuts, is the perfect hideaway! Toss yourself into the pillowy donut cushions within and all your worries will melt away. As an added bonus, stepping outside makes you feel like a star circus performer emerging from behind the curtains.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.002.Story">This small and cozy circus tent, decorated with colorful donuts, is the perfect hideaway! Toss yourself into the pillowy donut cushions within and let yourself relax for a bit. As an added bonus, stepping outside makes you feel like you\'re ready to become a star circus performer.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.003.Story">Even if you fall from the rope ladder, don\'t worry! You\'ll be just fine as long as you have these soft and fluffy donut cushions below. Their sweet scent and fluffy bounce are enough to lift your spirits after every fall. Just remember to regularly refill them with cream to keep them puffy!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Ceil.002.Story">A piping bag bursting with sweet, fresh cream. Whether it\'s for stage makeup, filling donuts, decorating a room, this handy tool does it all! You can hang up this large one and divide the cream into smaller bags as needed.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Ceil.001.Story">Chocolate-coated donuts were carefully chosen to firmly tie a rope ladder in place. Not vertically, but horizontally. The goal? To practice crossing to the other side with grace and perfect balance!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.004.Story">A donut box nearly filled with practice outfits, cushioned outfits, stage outfits, and even a few drums. Since it\'s well-organized, you can just grab what you need without having to rummage for it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Wallpaper.001.Story">Parchment paper that was used for wrapping donuts has been transformed into wallpaper! Its glossy finish and adorable prints are perfect for any circus performer\'s room. And the walls smell like sweet and scrumptious donuts!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Deck.001.Story">A soft floor decorated with delicate caramel patterns. It\'s been lightly dusted with some powdered sugar to add some extra fluffiness and coziness!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.008.Story">A cheering and smiling audience made of paper. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.005.Story">A rack to hang up your circus hats. It\'s no wonder who this belongs to!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Ceil.003.Story">A mobile made from adorable donut holes. This will look great wherever you put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.006.Story">A simple dresser in the shape of a donut. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.007.Story">A donut drum used to let Cookies know the circus is in town. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Hanger.001.Story">A collection of stamps and ticket stubs. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.009.Story">An obstacle of fire made from paper. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.010.Story">This unicycle is waiting for its rider! Just looking at it makes you feel happy.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Floor.011.Story">A tiny but comfortable stool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.001">Cream Donut Cap</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.002">Makeup Piping Bag</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.003">Practice Socks</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.001.Story">A fluffy donut cap filled with extra cream. Every time Cream Donut Cookie puts on this hat, he looks into the mirror and swells with pride as it reminds him it won\'t be long until he\'s a full-fledged member of the performers in the troupe!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.002.Story">A piping bag containing fresh and long-lasting cream. From filling donuts, and decorating rooms, to getting ready for the stage, this stuff can do everything!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2019.003.Story">A pair of frayed socks. It\'s worn and patched in places, but each stitch tells the story of Cream Donut Cookie running closer towards his dream, one step at a time!</string>
