  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2019.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Cream Donut Cookie. The toy always seems ready to deliver a happy drumbeat.</string>
  <string name="$Season.2019.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the Cream Donut Collection. Clumsy or not, each step forward will be remembered as a chapter in your journey to circus performing greatness!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cream Donut Cookie\'s soul. Holding it makes you feel like you have two left feet, but you can also feel a fiery passion burning within your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2019.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Cream Donut Cookie\'s Room of Abundant Dreams &amp; Cream!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Profile">Cream Donut Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2019.Frame">Cream Donut Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_1">Oh no... I\'ve failed again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_2">Why is tightrope walking so hard...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_3">I followed First Sprinkle Cookie\'s advice and everything... I put sticky honey on my feet and even removed some cream from my drums to make them lighter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_4">First Sprinkle Cookie also said she mastered tightrope walking in only an hour... Maybe I\'m just not good enough?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_5">...
No! I\'m still learning! And it\'s okay to make mistakes when learning...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_6">If I keep practicing, I\'ll definitely get to shine on the stage too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_7">Wooow! That was such a moooving speech!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_8">GAH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_9">The will to keep moooving on, one step at a tiiime! Trying again and agaaain until you succeed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_10">I\'m sooo glad I came to the circus! It bolstered my will to keep training haaard and become strooonger!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_11">Pardon me, but... who are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_12">My name\'s Melted Choco Cookie. I\'m training to become a strooong warrior!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_13">Oh... How do you do? My name\'s Cream Donut Cookie. And, erm, the audiences\' seats are that way... This is just my room.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_14">Cream Donut Cookie! Wooorking hard to make your dreams come truuue!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2016_15">Would you like to traaain with me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_1_Cookie.2019_16">... Eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_1">But... What are you going to train with? You didn\'t bring anything...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_2">I\'m aaalways ready to train, wherever I am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_3">Take this, for example! It looks like a simple maaarshmallow cushion, riiight?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_4">But no! In my haaands, it becomes a tool to traaain our strength!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_5">A... marshmallow... cushion...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_6">Let me shooow you...! You try to make the marshmallow as flaaat as possible...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_7">Then, when the marshmallow wants to expaaand back, you use all your streeength to keep it as flaaat as possible!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_8">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_9">THAT\'S GENIUS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_10">I should also be prepared to practice circus tricks at all times, wherever I am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_11">But... I have no idea where to begin...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_12">Don\'t look too faaar! Your training equipment is riiight under your nose, Cream Donut Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_13">Don\'t thiiink too hard! Just start moving aaand trust your instiiincts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_14">Instinct! Of course!!!
I\'m gonna train with anything and everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_15">Here I go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_16">Huuup...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2016_17">Hyaaah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_2_Cookie.2019_18">I will...!
Become...!
A circus superstar!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_1">*Huff... puff...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_2">*Huuuff... puuuff...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_3">I... I don\'t think I\'ve ever... trained this long before...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_4">Me too... That traaaining session was so intense... I feel like I\'m meeelting...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_5">Weren\'t you... always melting...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_6">But... We caaan\'t get lazy! We need to traaain some mooore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_7">We need to puuush past our limits!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_8">Wait, training too much can lead to injuries and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_9">Hyaaah! Aaaah! Heeeyaaa... urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_10">Erm... Melted Choco Cookie. The marshmallow is pushing you back...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_11">Oh... I\'m so tired... I can\'t feel my arms any mooore...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_12">Watch ooout, Cream Donut Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_13">Nooo! Push back, Melted Choco Cookie! PUSH BACK! Or my room will become a mess and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_14">AAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_15">... And it just became a mess.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_16">Phew... I\'m glaaad you have so many soft cushions in heeere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2019_17">I guess... training time is over and clean-up time has started...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2019_3_Cookie.2016_18">I, erm... I can help you... hehe.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.Main">Pursuing a Sweet Dream</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.01">Let\'s Train Together!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.02">Unbeatable in Effort Alone!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.03">One Step Spells Success or Failure</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.01.Summary">When it comes to performing circus tricks, Cream Donut Cookie is as clumsy as ever. But he\'s not going to give up! As he fires himself up to train even harder, Melted Choco Cookie jumps in to lend some additional motivation and support!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.02.Summary">This pair of Cookies may not be considered the most athletically capable, but nothing will stop them from pursuing their dreams! The two Cookies admire each other\'s efforts and decide to train together.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2019.Title.03.Summary">Just as the duo begins the second round of intense training, they run out of steam and the room ends up in a mess. Working hard to achieve a dream is commendable, but... perhaps a bit of cleaning is needed first.</string>
