  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_1">If I\'m riding a giant balloon puppy, and then it suddenly pops...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_2">And BAM! A million balloon flowers appear as if from thin air!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_3">It\'s perfect! This act will definitely make me the star of the entire circus and... and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_4">Hm... Maybe the act needs something more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_5">I need to come up with an act that\'ll blow First Sprinkle Cookie\'s socks off...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">If I go out on stage with this act, the moment I hop onto the balloon puppy, she\'ll say something like...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">PAH! You call that an ACT?! BOOORING! Show us something better! BETTER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_8">Yeah, that\'s exactly what would happen...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">Ick...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_10">Urgh! I\'ll come up with one tomorrow! I always manage to think better after a good night\'s sleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">Zzz... Just you wait... First Sprinkle Cookie... I\'m cooler... I\'m better... I\'m funnier...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_1_POR1_Cookie.0157_12">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_1">Jelly Bean Cookie! What\'re you doing?! The show\'s about to start!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_2">Huh...? What...? Why am I on stage? I was fast asleep just moments ago?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_3">I have no idea what\'s going on, but... the crowd awaits! I\'ll go out and do everything just like I practiced!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_4">Phew... All done. I didn\'t mess anything up, but the crowd\'s reaction was...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_5">... Amazing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_6">Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_7">AMAZING! AWESOME!
Jelly Bean Cookie! You put on the greatest show this circus has ever seen!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_8">I hate to admit it, but your act was SO MUCH better than my last performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2019_9">You\'re so awesome, Jelly Bean Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2018_10">Simply marvelous! I shall have to make Jelly Bean Cookie\'s act the highlight for every night.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_11">... What\'s with everyone? Why are they acting so differently? Even First Sprinkle Cookie\'s being a bit weird...-er than usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_12">But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_13">AHAHAHA! At least everyone finally recognizes my amazing talent! What a feeling!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2017_14">Jelly Bean Cookie! Teach me how to ride a balloon puppy!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2019_15">Me too! Me too!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_2_POR1_Cookie.2020_16">This isn\'t something anyone can learn! But if you want some pointers, step right up and get in line!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_1">Zzzzzz... Get in line... hehe...
For I am... the greatest... Jelly Bean Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_2">She\'s dreaming so happily...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_3">It was a good idea to decorate CookieLand into a circus stage...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_4">Hehe... I won... Finally won... Zzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_5">I hope this sweet dream of yours doesn\'t just remain a good memory...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_6">You can fulfill your dreams one day, so keep trying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_7">Like the stars, I\'ll be watching over you from far away... sending you my best wishes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_8">Zzz... Yes, more applause... More... I am the great Jelly Bean Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.2020_9">First Sprinkle Cookie... You need to train harder... to be like me... Hehehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2020_3_POR1_Cookie.0157_10">Hehe... May you have only the sweetest dreams.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.Main">Dream Circus</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.01">Victory Will Be Mine!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.02">VICTORY AT LAST!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.03">Sweet Dreams, Jelly Bean Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.01.Summary">Jelly Bean Cookie dreams of becoming the greatest circus performer... even greater than First Sprinkle Cookie! But no matter how hard she tries, the aspiring star is unable to come up with that one big act that will help her gain the recognition she craves. With a huff and a pout, Jelly Bean Cookie eventually drifts off into sleep...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.02.Summary">When Jelly Bean Cookie opened her eyes, she suddenly found herself standing center stage in the circus tent! Though confused and flustered at first, the professional performer gathers her courage and puts on a performance just like she practiced, but isn\'t very satisfied with the outcome. But it turns out that everyone loved her act! Even First Sprinkle Cookie gave her heartfelt praise! Jelly Bean Cookie can hardly believe it and is overjoyed!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Title.03.Summary">It turns out that Cream Unicorn Cookie had invited Jelly Bean Cookie into the dreamworld of CookieLand. Watching the young performer smile in her sleep, Cream Unicorn Cookie quietly wishes that, one day, Jelly Bean Cookie\'s dreams come true.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Illust.Dialog.01">Hehe... I won...
Finally won... Zzz...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2020.Illust.Dialog.02">I hope this sweet dream
of yours doesn\'t just
remain a good memory...</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_001">Calamity has struck! The kitchen is in ruins, and the reviews have hit rock bottom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_002">Alas! Should Cheesehaven fail to earn two stars tonight, we are doomed to be shuttered!</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_003">Erm... Can I help?</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_004">Strawberry Cookie! The fires have gone cold, and the utensils lie in disarray!</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_005">I think we\'ll be okay... We can take it one step at a time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_006">Very well! Let there be no more despair! To the ingredients, we march!</string>
  <string name="$Script_Mergegame_CutOG_007">Come, onwards to the kitchen! It is time to reclaim Cheesehaven\'s glory!</string>
