  <string name="$Cookie.2020.Story">A performer to the very core of her dough, this Cookie has an ambitious, and very bouncy, dream... to one day become the brightest, most beloved star of the circus!

Together with her charming balloon puppies, Jelly Bean Cookie twirls and tumbles across the stage. As the audience\'s anticipation swells like an inflating balloon... POP! BANG! Her playful antics make the crowd roar with laughter and applause!

With her talents, Jelly Bean Cookie is capable of delivering a stellar performance every night. But her lofty dreams often stir a tinge of envy, leading her to occasionally pull mischievous pranks on the troupe instead of practicing for her next act.

Even so... who could ever stay made at Jelly Bean Cookie? One glance at her cheeky, oh-so-adorable smile is enough to melt anyone\'s heart!</string>
