  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Floor.001.Story">A balloon pup with a tail full of balloons in all shapes and sizes! Plus, it also acts as a sofa! One touch of its glossy and squishy surface will fill you with a desire to pop down onto its back! Cookies who sit here feel like they\'re about to float all the way to the clouds. Up, up, and away!</string>
