  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Floor.003.Story">A candy machine brimming with colorful sweets! No one knows which shape or flavor of candy will tumble and roll out next... But that\'s what makes it such a pleasant surprise!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Floor.004.Story">A carousel with swings, adorned with a beaming Bear Jelly! Settle into these cushy swings and go whirling and twirling through the air—you\'ll feel like you\'re soaring high above the clouds! What\'re you waiting for? Hop on board!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Wall.001.Story">A balloon stand built by none other than Jelly Bean Cookie herself! As a lover of pranks and surprises, there\'s no chance of boredom with this in your room! The balloons made here can either burst open with confetti, fill the air with sparkles, or might even pop to give you a snack of jelly beans!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Ceil.001.Story">Is that a yellow balloon moving on its own? Oh, wait...! It\'s a Cheesebird?! Nestled among a bunch of bouncy balloons, this little birdie looks like its ready for an adventure in the skies without having to flap its wings!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Wallpaper.001.Story">A lovely wallpaper decked out with balloons, stars, and garlands! A true star-in-the-making knows every wall must shine as bright as they do!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Deck.001.Story">A floor patterned after the sparkly star painted on Jelly Bean Cookie\'s cheek! One day, everyone will want a floor that reminds them of the future star of the circus!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Hanger.001.Story">What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Ceil.002.Story">Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Floor.005.Story">Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2020.Wall.002.Story">Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
