  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2020">Jelly Bean Cookie\'s Boingy, Bouncy, Starry Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2020.Story">A room jam-packed with fun rides and cute balloons. The audience might mistake Jelly Bean Cookie\'s room for the circus stage! And if a crowd really does stay here for a show, they\'ll be clapping nonstop at Jelly Bean Cookie\'s stellar performance!</string>
