  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2020.001.Story">A color-popping, ultra-cutesy balloon hairband! It\'s perfect for grabbing everyone\'s attention. No wonder it\'s one of Jelly Bean Cookie\'s favorite accessories!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2020.002.Story">Place any balloon here and... POOF!! Balloons puff up so quickly, you\'d think they might burst! Jelly Bean Cookie pretends this gadget is no big deal, but this is absolutely her favorite and most treasured item!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2020.003.Story">A star must always be ready to shine! This pouch, stuffed with balloons galore, is always at the ready for Jelly Bean Cookie\'s next dazzling moment!</string>
