  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_1">Looks like we\'re done moving everything... So, that\'s that. Sharing a room is just temporary, understand?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_3">Didn\'t I tell you I don\'t like it when you stare at me like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_4">You\'re the one who decided to make a giant plushie of Master Shadow Milk Cookie. You dropped it, and now your room\'s a wreck. But, somehow, it\'s become my problem.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_5">... Why is my half of the room smaller?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_6">Because this is my room... and it\'s called sharing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_7">Siiigh... This place is waaay too tiny!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_8">Throwing a fit won\'t fix anything... Wait. No. Fine. Whatever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_9">Let me split the space evenly, and don\'t move. It will be less messy than whatever you were about to do... So please, no more chaos.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_10">AHA HA! Works for me! Then I\'m gonna get to work on the light- Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_11">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_12">What\'s wrong?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_13">The light\'s broken! It won\'t turn on... Did it break during the move?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_14">Oh? So fix it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_15">*Shrugs*
But I dunno how!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_16">This is why Master Shadow Milk Cookie trusts me over you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_17">Nuh-uh! Shadow Milk Cookie is MINE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_18">Mmhmm, sure. Just stand there and do nothing, for once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_19">I will let you know when I\'m done. Wait there. And quietly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_1_POR1_20">... Hmpf!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_1">You really don\'t know anything, do you, Black Sapphire Cookie? Shadow Milk Cookie LOVES me the most!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_2">I know! I\'ll draw a picture to remind him just how much Shadow Milk Cookie adores me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_3">All I need is some paper! Okay, so paper... paper... Where\'s the paper? AH-HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_4">If I draw it like thiiis, and thiiis, and theeere... Heehee! Yeee- NOOO! This isn\'t even close to how perfect Shadow Milk Cookie is!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_5">I can fix this...! If I do thaaat, then thaaat, and... ARGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_6">... What is the little brat doing now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_7">*Hum, hum, hum*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_8">... This can\'t be good.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_9">Every time Candy Apple Cookie goes quiet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_10">Some ridiculous disaster is not far away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_11">KYA HA HA! Perfect!!! ♡♡</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_12">But you don\'t have to take my word for it. Just watch. Here it comes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_13">Ahem. Candy Apple Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_14">Black Sapphire Cookie! Did you fix the light? And what about my half of the room?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_15">The light has been fixed, and the room has been split exactly in half.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_16">AHA HA!!! Faaantastic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_17">Mhmmm, sure, sure. Now tell me, what exactly am I looking at here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_18">It seems the scripts on top of my dressing table have decided to grow legs and run amok on their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_19">Oooh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_20">My notes have become an absolute masterpiece of destruction. Which begs the question...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_2_POR1_21">Flip over that drawing of yours.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_1">Here ya go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_2">... Why am I not surprised.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_3">I leave you alone for a few minutes... and you\'ve somehow evolved from a tiny nuisance to a natural disaster!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_4">KYA HA HA! But it looks sooo good, right?! It\'s me and Shadow Milk Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_6">Oh, and I drew you too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_7">...
*Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_8">(Don\'t lose it here. You totally saw this coming...)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_9">(But even so, just letting this slide doesn\'t sit right either. Hm... What\'s the move here?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_10">You know what? It\'s actually quite an impressive drawing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_11">Buuut... Master Shadow Milk Cookie is looking a bit off, don\'t you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_12">Whaaat?! TAKE THAT BACK!!! There\'s nothing wrong with my Shadow Milk Cookie drawing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_13">This does not even capture half of Master Shadow Milk Cookie\'s grandeur. Especially here... What is going on with the eyes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_14">It looks like someone\'s heart isn\'t in the right place... for Master Shadow Milk Cookie. Is that really all the love and devotion you can muster?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_15">You\'re wrong! Super wrong!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_16">Sure, sure. Whatever helps you sleep at night.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_17">You always ruin EVERYTHING!!! You\'re gonna regret this!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0621_3_POR1_18">(Balance has been restored, haha. All in a day\'s work!)</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.Main">Apples &amp; Grapes Go Round and Round</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.01">The Light\'s Broken!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.02">Not Enough Paper!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.03">Squabbling &amp; Satisfaction</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.01.Summary">Candy Apple Cookie and Black Sapphire Cookie end up having to share a room. A squabble breaks out as Candy Apple Cookie is not satisfied with her side of the room. The commotion fades when she discovers her light is not working...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.02.Summary">While waiting for Black Sapphire Cookie to fix the light, Candy Apple Cookie gets bored and decides to draw a picture, but there\'s no paper! Just then, atop Black Sapphire Cookie\'s dressing table, something that looks like a stack of blank paper catches her eye...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Title.03.Summary">Black Sapphire Cookie discovers that Candy Apple Cookie has scribbled and doodled all over his precious script! What now...?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Illust.Dialog.01">You always ruin
EVERYTHING!!!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0621.Illust.Dialog.02">All in a
day\'s work!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Story">What was the first lie ever told? No one knows for sure, but one Cookie claims to have been born from it—Candy Apple Cookie! Her syrup is so sticky it can seal lips shut and so glossy it leaves everyone staring in awe.

Candy Apple Cookie believes she was crafted by the Master of Deceit himself, Shadow Milk Cookie. From the moment she opened her eyes, her loyalty has been unwavering, dedicating herself to earning his love and trust.

Though indifferent to most things, Candy Apple Cookie has a flair for mischief and a passion for dressing up. She delights in tricking other Cookies, giggling with sinister glee as they fall for her schemes, only to dash off in search of Shadow Milk Cookie\'s approval.

Beware—the first bite of the apple of lies is always the sweetest!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Skill.Name">Apple of My Eye! ♡</string>
