they\'re quite refined!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0622.Monologue.Random.02">All good as long 
as we have fun!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0622.Monologue.Random.03">Can I fly? The most
important is what
YOU believe, he he.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0622.Monologue.Random.04">Is my microphone heavy?
Not at all!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0622.Monologue.Random.05">We\'ll be right back!
Don\'t change the channel!</string>
