  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.001.Story">A grand platform raised high, seats for the host and the guest, and monitors flickering with the mesmerizing energy of lies and deceit. Welcome to the set of the most-watched show in the Witch\'s Castle, where everything\'s made up and the truth doesn\'t matter! Who cares, as long as it\'s fun?!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.002.Story">A cozy platform, seats for the host and guest, and neon signs signaling the start of the show. Welcome to the set of the most-watched show in the Witch\'s Castle! And we\'re live in 5, 4, 3, 2... 1!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.003.Story">Candy Apple Cookie\'s cozy retreat: a plush sofa perfect for sweet naps in between capers of trickery. The cushions, baked from the crunchiest apples, release a tangy and fruity scent that lingers in the air. When you catch Candy Apple Cookie snoozing on sofa, with a plushie of Shadow Milk Cookie close by, be sure to bring her a blanket... or you might be her next target!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.004.Story">The dressing table where Black Sapphire Cookie spends hours preparing for the broadcast. Only after a thorough once-over, when every wrinkle on his clothes are smoothed, when every strand of hair has been set and checked does the final read of the script begin.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.001.Story">Pay attention! Here, okay? Look here, please! Remember to look here. Just keep looking here. Alright? Eyes on the arrow. No no, eyes on where the arrow is pointing, not the arrow itself! Right... On air in 5, 4, 3, 2... 1!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Ceil.001.Story">A hanging light made from sugar-glazed, beautifully sliced apple peels. As it glows, it emits an alluring sugary, fruity scent that attracts fruit bats from nearby. But don\'t let too many of them near it, because it might break!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wallpaper.001.Story">A curtain dyed deep red by using ripe apple peels. It\'s been glazed with an even layer of sugar to add a bit of a sparkle! Be careful though... it\'s rather sticky! Very, very sticky!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Deck.001.Story">A carpet dyed deep purple by using ripe grape skins. A rich sugary aroma rises with every step. It\'s so sweet, it just might make your head spin!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.002.Story">An entryway used by stars, and only stars! What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.003.Story">A pair of neon signs. Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.004.Story">Posters showcasing the Lies &amp; Deceit Show. Try decorating the wall with these.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.005.Story">A collection of doodles and snapshots. Just looking at it lifts your spirits.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Hanger.001.Story">A sash curtain. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.005.Story">A purple stool. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Floor.006.Story">A red stool. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Rug.001.Story">A crimson carpet. Let put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Wall.006.Story">A neon arrow sign. Again, a reminder to look here.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0621">Candy Apple Cookie &amp; Black Sapphire Cookie\'s Room of Lies and Deceit</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.0621.Story">A little bickering and squabbling here, a dash of caring and tenderness there. One lies on the sofa humming, the other sits at the dressing table reading and gossiping. Candy Apple Cookie and Black Sapphire Cookie are like opposite sides of the same coin, but they have somehow managed to share a space together. Was it always a shared space? Or did someone just decide to never leave...? Who knows!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.001">Crunchy Candy Apple</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.002">Shadow Milk Cookie Plushie</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.003">Glossy &amp; Shiny Doll Shoes</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.001.Story">What happens when you take a perfectly round apple and glaze it with a layer of the sweetest syrup? Crunch! Munch! Yum! Ahem, what was the question? Ah! Candy Apple Cookie\'s signature hair accessory is said to made with the ultimate, perfect apple... but is that really true?</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.002.Story">Candy Apple Cookie’s most treasured possession! This plushie is a faithful recreation of the Master of Deceit. Black Sapphire Cookie often teases her that it looks nothing like Shadow Milk Cookie. Every time, Candy Apple Cookie fires back with an unhinged yet adorable \"IT’S PERFECT!\" as if on cue.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0621.003.Story">These shoes, a gift from Black Sapphire Cookie, are always polished to a mirror shine. High-quality grape skins were used to make the outer layer, and soft apple peels make up the lining inside. With each step, they release a sweet, fruity scent into the air.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0621.TeddyBear">Candy Apple Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Season.0621.Complete.Profile">Completed Candy Apple &amp; Black Sapphire Collection</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Soulstone">Candy Apple Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Ceil.999">Candy Apple Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0621.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Candy Apple Cookie. It\'s like the toy is infused with everything that makes her who she is. This toy claims the sun rises at night, the moon is a square, and the sky is actually green. Whisper enough lies near it and you just might hear a sinister giggle...</string>
  <string name="$Season.0621.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the Candy Apple &amp; Black Sapphire Collection. From playful bickering, bursting laughter, to causing utmost chaos... Don\'t take your eyes off these two troublemakers!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Candy Apple Cookie\'s soul Shiny and sweet at first glance, it is so incredibly sticky, you will never be able to part with it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0621.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Candy Apple Cookie\'s Room of Lies and Deceit!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Profile">Candy Apple Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0621.Frame">Candy Apple Cookie &amp; Black Sapphire Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.001">Scandalous Rumor Cue Sheet</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.002">Black Sapphire Brooch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.003">Eau de Grapevine &amp; Hearsay</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.001.Story">A cue sheet packed with only the juiciest, most outrageous rumors and gossip in existence! These scandalous claims are so secretive, only Black Sapphire Cookie has read the entire thing. Seriously, it\'s kept sealed tighter than a stuck peanut butter jar!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.002.Story">A glimmering brooch made from only the finest of grapes. The deep alluring hue has been known to capture the gaze of many Cookies. It\'s a true scene stealer in every sense!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie0622.003.Story">A perfume distilled from the sweetest lies and juiciest scandals. Its scent is so mesmerizing, you\'ll be sniffing the air mid-scene just to catch a whiff. But since it\'s made from falsities and rumors, the scent fades faster than a failed soufflé can collapse.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0622.TeddyBear">Black Sapphire Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.0622.Soulstone">Black Sapphire Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie0622.Ceil.999">Black Sapphire Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie0622.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Black Sapphire Cookie. If you lean in close, the toy will spill the beans on all sorts of secrets, rumors, and hearsay with a mischievous grin.</string>
