  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_1">Thanks for letting me stay for a bit, Werewolf Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_2">I thought I was going to be in big trouble, being lost and stuck in that massive blizzard...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0044_3">... You\'re the one who spotted me first... But how did you know I was watching...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_4">Oh! Snow King told me there was someone nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0044_5">Snow King... Was that the giant creature walking alongside you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_6">Yeah! Snow King and Snow Cone are my best friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0044_7">Oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_8">Hm...? Werewolf Cookie looks... lonely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_9">Hey, Werewolf Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_10">Do you... erm, do you not have many friends...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0044_11">What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_1_Cookie0030_12">I didn\'t mean it in a bad way, really! I\'m sorry if I offended you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_1">It\'s just... I never had any friends either...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_2">I was alone for a very long time... wandering by myself through the snow. So I know what it feels like to be lonely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_3">But then I got to meet my best friends, and even more...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_4">It\'s nice to have good friends around!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_5">... Sure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_6">When the blizzard stops, do you want to go find some new friends together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_7">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_8">Huh? But... why? I... I didn\'t mean to hurt your feelings...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_9">No... It\'s not that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_10">Everyone near me... ends up getting hurt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_11">It\'s better for me to be alone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_12">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0030_13">Then I\'ll be your newest best friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_2_Cookie0044_14">... What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0044_1">I... I don\'t think you understand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_2">No, I understand perfectly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_3">You\'re a very warmhearted Cookie who cares about your friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_4">And it\'ll be okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_5">Because my friend, Snow King, is really, really tough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_6">I know you won\'t hurt me or my friends, Werewolf Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_7">And I promise we\'ll be okay and won\'t get hurt! So... let\'s be friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0044_8">Jeez...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0044_9">The blizzard isn\'t letting up any time soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0044_10">You can sleep in the furry bed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0044_11">I can sleep in my leather hammock tonight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_12">Okay! And tomorrow, after the blizzard is over...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_13">Let\'s go out and play in the snow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie0044_3_Cookie0030_14">It\'ll be fun!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.Main">Did We Just Become Best Friends?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.01">You Don\'t Have Any Friends...?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.02">Being Lonely is Awful!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.03">Let\'s Be Best Friends!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.01.Summary">Werewolf Cookie provides shelter for Snow Sugar Cookie from a massive blizzard. While talking, Snow Sugar Cookie suspects Werewolf Cookie is lonely. Does Werewolf Cookie not have any friends...?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.02.Summary">Snow Sugar Cookie tries to connect with Werewolf Cookie by telling him a story about their own experience with loneliness. They hope Werewolf Cookie can make some new friends, but...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Title.03.Summary">Werewolf Cookie doesn\'t want to make any new friends, in fear of putting them in danger. But Snow Sugar Cookie offers to be his newest best friend! Will Werewolf Cookie accept this sudden declaration of friendship...?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Illust.Dialog.01">Let\'s be friends!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0044.Illust.Dialog.02">Jeez...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Title.Main">The Voices are Scary</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Illust.Dialog.01">Do not worry, 
everything will be okay.
You are safe here.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.0058.Illust.Dialog.02">*Sob, sniffle*
Thank you,
Blackberry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_1">Hello...? I, erm, heard that First Milk Cookie is here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_2">Is anyone here? First Milk Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_3">Oh, a visitor... Why have you sought me out?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_4">Haha! I\'m in the right place! I\'m so glad you\'re here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_5">I came here because I have a Cookie who I think you should really, really meet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_6">Over here, Zombie Cookie! It\'s okay! Come on in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_7">Uuugh... Grah...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_8">Oh my goodness...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_9">Your dough is in very bad shape...! You are pale all over, brittle, and... your eyes are cloudy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_10">Dough... me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_11">Your condition is very serious and concerning. We must begin treatment immediately...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_12">Oh, I see!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_13">I was always worried because Zombie Cookie is absolutely terrified of plants.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_14">I thought this fear of plants might be connected to an illness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_15">Plants... scaaary...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_16">Ah-ha...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_17">Please! Please help Zombie Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_18">I... I have never heard of such a symptom. This may need a more in-depth diagnosis before treatment can begin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_19">If it is alright with both of you... Zombie Cookie, may I take a moment to examine your condition a bit further...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_20">Cookie... take care of... Zombie Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_21">Of course! I\'ll be heading back now, so please help Zombie Cookie get better!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_1_POR1_22">I shall... I shall give this patient my full attention...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_1">Your temperature is very low...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_2">And... I can barely feel the flow of Life Powder within your dough... How can this be?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_3">Graaah... Hungry... Me hungry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_4">You have an appetite...! That\'s a good sign...! Then... yes, there is still hope.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_5">Grah...? Hope...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_6">Treatment will not be easy as I am unfamiliar with your symptoms...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_7">But I will not give up...! You are my patient, and I will do my very best to ensure you never crumble...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_8">...
Oh dear... I cannot make a proper diagnosis...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_9">Me... crumble...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_10">Me... crumble... Not bad thing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_11">You are... fine with your condition?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_12">Me... crumble... then just get up... Grahaha.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_13">But crumbling and... losing all of your Life Powder... You are not afraid of such things?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_14">Grah...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_15">Me... Scared... Plants...
Plants scary...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_16">Plants... are the only thing you fear...? You are not afraid of crumbling apart...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_2_POR1_17">I see...! I did not know there are Cookies who are capable of living in such a manner...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_1">Hello, First Milk Cookie! I\'m back! How is Zombie Cookie doing...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_2">Ah... Herb Cookie, you have returned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_3">Hungry... Want... Jellies...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_4">*Chuckle*
Herb Cookie. Zombie Cookie was not ill...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_5">Zombie Cookie was, in fact, baked this way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_6">Oh...! So... the fear of plants was always there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_7">Gahlramurlgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_8">Zombie Cookie is merely fond of lying down... and, well, plants just make them a little nervous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_9">Still, I believe they are in perfect health... Just living life in their own very special way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_10">Me... okay... Hahagraah...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_11">Haha! That\'s wonderful to hear! I guess I was worried about nothing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_12">No, it was your warm heart and kindness that brought Zombie Cookie here... You helped me realize something too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_13">The world is full of all kinds of Cookies, each finding their own way to live...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_14">And thanks to you, I have been reflecting on myself too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_15">First Milk Cookie...
Kind... and nice...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2021_3_POR1_16">Thank you, Zombie Cookie...
I am so glad to have met you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_1">Oh? Something\'s blocking our way!
We can\'t get in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_2">I\'m unfamiliar with this sort of magic. The spell itself seems to form a barrier and radiates an aroma like... milk?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_3">I know what this calls for! This is the perfect time for-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_4">Wait, GingerBright! I don\'t think that\'s a-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_5">GingerBright! Hang on! It looks like someone\'s over there! We can just ask them how-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_6">If something\'s blocking our way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_7">Are you even listening?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_8">It\'s time to give it some love! HEEHEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_9">CLANG!!!
CLANG!!!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_10">GingerBright! You need to stop!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_11">I got a bad feeling about this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_12">AAAGGGHHH!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_13">Ow, ow... My arm feels a bit crumbly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_14">Ouch... *GASP*
GingerBrave! Are you alright...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_15">Hup...!
Yeah! I think I\'m okay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_16">But... There are crumbs falling from your dough?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_17">The patients within the sanctum require absolute peace for stable recovery. Who is causing such a disturbance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_18">It\'s the Cookie I saw moments ago! Hello, hi there! Sorry about that, but we were just looking for a way inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_19">Apologies, but the Sanctum of Healing only accepts those who are sick or injured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_20">We simply cannot accept every visitor... Caring for our patients keeps us more than busy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_21">And- Oh! You are injured...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_22">Oh dear... There are signs of crumbs falling and cracks in your dough. You will need immediate care. My name is First Milk Cookie, Keeper of the Sanctum of Healing. Now, please, come in.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_23">The barrier just disappeared!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ1_POR1_24">In the end, it seems GingerBright\'s strategy actually worked...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_1">Please follow me, everyone...
Skim Milk Cookie will tend to you from here. And with that... I shall take my leave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_2">Oh? First Milk Cookie isn\'t the one who\'ll be helping us...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_3">*Sigh*
First Milk Cookie is currently attending to patients in intensive care.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_4">Intensive care...? Are there critically ill patients here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_5">Yes... Those in an incubator, for instance...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_6">Oh... It sounds like there are many sick Cookies here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_7">But I digress... Okay, disinfection complete. Everything seems to be in order.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_8">Please refrain from any strenuous activities... And even if the crumbs start to itch, be careful not to scratch at the area.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_9">Look at you! What a trooper! You didn\'t even flinch during the treatment! You\'re very brave! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_10">Haha! I guess I am! My name is GingerBrave after all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_11">GingerBrave! What a perfect name, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_12">Ah, Cottage Cheese Cookie. It seems you\'ve finally returned from yet another ill-advised excursion. It\'s best to avoid any outdoor activities for the moment...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_13">Hehe, I\'m fine! Cut me some slack!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_14">Pardon the intrusion, but this place is impeccably clean! It\'s also very quiet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_15">Yes, all thanks to Cottage Cheese Cookie. She always keeps the sanctum spotless for the patients\' peace of mind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_16">Oooh! So being clean makes you feel better quicker?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_17">Of course! Cleanliness is the most fundamental requirement for speedy recoveries. Think back on Mount St. Crème and how everyone suffered from illness and mold...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_18">Mold?! Don\'t even mention mold! No, absolutely not in our Sanctum of Healing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_19">By the way...! Is there a Cookie of the First Batch here? It kinda just feels like a hospital for sick Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_20">...?!
I see there are others who are familiar with the Cookies of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_21">Yeah! A friend of ours asked us to look for the First Batchers! Is one of them here? What\'s their name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_22">Oooh! How interesting! The Cookie of the First Batch who lives here is called Toughie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_23">Will we get a chance to meet Toughie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_24">Unfortunately... That may be difficult.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_25">Oh? How come?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_26">The First Batcher... Toughie is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ2_POR1_27">the one who is within the incubator and in critical condition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_1">Resting here made my dough all crispy again! And I feel so bright too, heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_2">If everyone gets this kind of care... patients who visit here are sure to feel better in no time...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_3">I guess the seriously ill patients can\'t recover as quickly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_4">I didn\'t know Cookies of the First Batch could get sick... I hope Toughie lives up to their name and gets better soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_5">I really, really hope Toughie gets better! First Milk Cookie is always so busy taking care of the little patient.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_6">And Skim Milk Cookie\'s suuuper busy with all the other patients, like really!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_7">Skim Milk Cookie... You should take care of yourself too...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_8">Wait, something is not adding up. Even though everyone here seems to make a quick recovery, you make it sound like the patient count never really drops.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_9">And it doesn\'t seem like the sanctum gets a steady flow of new arrivals. Odd, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_10">Indeed. Statistically speaking, the relapse rate is unusually high...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_11">Relapse? What\'s that mean?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_12">I know! It means they weren\'t perfectly cured and got sick again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_13">We have been working days and nights to find perfect cures... But we still do not even know the cause of their illnesses.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_14">It\'s true! *Sniffle* Skim Milk Cookie doesn\'t sleep at night! He\'s always reading and researching things! </string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_15">I am more than confident that a perfect cure can be found for any ailment... One of these days, the research will bear fruit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_16">However, my skills will never quite reach the level of First Milk Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ3_POR1_17">You got this, Skim Milk Cookie! I\'m sure you\'ll find a way! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_1">You seem to have made a
full recovery for now, but
I would prefer to wait a few
days to confirm your condition.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_2">Really?
So they\'re staying?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_3">To be frank,
I do not think your wounds will
lead to any long-term ailments...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_4">But... First Milk Cookie
will want to make completely sure
that you\'ve made a full recovery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_5">That sounds great!
I like it here, so I don\'t mind
staying for a few extra days!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_6">Me too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_7">And we could help with taking care
of the patients while we\'re here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_8">Oh! And maybe
we can find a way
to help Toughie too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_9">I... am unsure
if First Milk Cookie will permit it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_10">*Sniffle*
That sounds like a wonderful idea!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_11">*Sniffle!* Don\'t worry about
keeping the place clean!
I can handle that easily!
Really!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_12">Perfect timing!
First Milk Cookie\'s here!
We\'d love to help out while we stay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_13">We\'ll help you take care of your patients!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_14">You...?
Treating the patients...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_15">If you don\'t mind, would
you allow us to examine
and diagnose Toughie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_16">You will... try to help...
Toughie...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_17">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_18">Hm...
Very well. You are welcome to try.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_19">Your lively and energetic voices
could potentially aid in
Toughie\'s recovery...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_20">Leave it to us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_21">You really do not have to
contribute... but, I mean, 
if you really want to help...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH1_SQ4_POR1_22">Ha... Just, please do not
cause a racket or fuss.
The other patients must rest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_1">Doc...! What is this? Why is this happening to me...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_2">I can\'t breathe...! And it feels like my dough is being burnt to a crisp...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_3">Mhr merth ers sterck...! Er crn\'t trk...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_4">Errr... I feel a headache coming on...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_5">There\'s so many patient records to organize and file! There\'s so, so much!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_6">So many Cookies were sick and treated, but they keep coming back...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_7">We can\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_8">...... As non-medical personnel, I think you\'re allowed to give up in moments like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_9">\"Can\'t give up\"?
But GingerBrave. You\'re not a doctor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_10">Erm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_11">When it comes to helping First Milk Cookie and Skim Milk Cookie, we can\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_12">He\'s right! Not giving up is really super important! The Sanctum of Healing doesn\'t know the meaning of the word! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_13">The Sanctum of Healing is open to patients with any illness, even those that are deemed incurable...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_14">After all, that is the oath First Milk Cookie swore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_15">Wow! An oath!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ1_POR1_16">Swearing an oath to heal everyone... That\'s so awesome, but it also sounds hard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_1">Hey! I was organizing the patient files, and I found one with your name on it, Cottage Cheese Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_2">Oh... Erm, were you a patient here in the sanctum too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_3">Yup! I guess the cat\'s out of the bag, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_4">I used to be a patient here. But I\'m all better now! Really!!! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_5">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_6">Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s prognosis is still in progress... But she adamantly claims she is fine and insists on cleaning the sanctum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_7">Oh...! I see!
But, erm, Cottage Cheese Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_8">Is it just me or... Well, you seem a lot smaller than the first time we met.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_9">You\'re almost as short as Wizard Cookie now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_10">..............</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_11">What? No I\'m not! I\'m really fine, really!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_12">As expected... You are not completely cured of your ailment. Like I said before, you are in no condition to be freely running around the sanctum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_13">But I\'m hydrating myself with lots of water every day! I really am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_14">Cottage Cheese Cookie. Are tears flowing from your eyes again, even if you aren\'t sad?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_15">Yeah... But I\'m hydrating with more moisture than I\'m losing! I really, really am trying! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_16">Hydrating with... moisture?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_17">It is a special treatment regimen I have prescribed specifically for her. She becomes smaller and lighter as the water content leaves her dough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_18">Ah... now I see. The reason why your condition seemed stable wasn\'t the treatment, but the milk bottles you\'ve been carrying on your back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_19">But I\'m really okay...! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ2_POR1_20">So what if I shrunk a bit and became a bit lighter... *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_1">*Roaring water... SPLASH*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_2">What was that???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_3">!!!
I think someone just fell from the top of that milkfall! C\'mon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_4">What? Really?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_5">We need to help this Cookie before everything gets soggy! And it looks like there\'s a serious injury too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_6">Then this is an emergency patient! Let me take a look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_7">...
I need everyone to help bring this Cookie out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_8">Is everything going to be alright?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_9">Cottage Cheese Cookie! Find First Milk Cookie and ask her to come at once!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_10">Okay! I\'m already gone!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_11">(Rushes off)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_12">Wake up! Do not be alarmed! Can you hear me? Can you open your eyes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_13">Where... am... I...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_14">Hooray! Thank goodness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_15">You\'re in the Sanctum of Healing! You just fell from the top of that milkfall...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_16">Emergency first aid has been completed. Responsive and awake, and upon first glance, I don\'t see any broken bones...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_17">I\'ll have to perform a thorough examination to make sure... But I must ask, do you remember why or how you fell into the milk?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_18">I... I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_19">Hm... Perhaps the Milk Veil is weakening...? I will have to inspect its integrity once I\'m done with diagnosing our newest patient.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_20">Why or how I fell? Does he suspect something...? Maybe this calls for a little... extra effort.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_21">*SOB!* 
I was attacked...! By a Cookie... A Cookie who reminded me... of eggs...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_22">*GASP*
Eggs? Could it be... First Egg Cookie...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_23">With what we know about First Egg Cookie so far, I wouldn\'t put anything past her. Someone like her could have easily pushed this Cookie into the milk...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_24">Ah, the sweet taste of success...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_25">If not that... First Egg Cookie might be trying to break through the Milk Veil... And she\'s definitely capable...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_26">Over here, First Milk Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_27">Where is the patient...?
Are you feeling well? Does it hurt anywhere?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_28">So...! This is the one called First Milk Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_29">It hurts...! It hurts so much! Please, make it stop...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_30">No, oh no...! I will heal you, just remain calm...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_31">Crumbs... It\'s been a while since we\'ve had a patient in such severe pain. First Milk Cookie must remain her composure or...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_32">Aaagh...! Save me! Make it stop, I\'m begging you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_33">P-P-Please remain calm! I\'m here... to help...! I can... I can... I can heal you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_34">Oh no... This seems bad...! What do we do???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_35">First Milk Cookie...! I will administer a potion to alleviate the patient\'s immediate symptoms! You must compose yourself! Take a deep breath, please...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_36">I... I... Very well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ3_POR1_37">I\'m... I\'m so sorry... Please forgive me... You are in pain, but I will... I will make sure to help you find relief from your pain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_1">So this is the heart of the sanctum,
where the unawakened Cookie of
the First Batch resides... Interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_2">What\'s so special about
that sorry lump of dough?
Why go to all this length
to protect them...? Tch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_3">Hm... How about these for rumors?
The Healer Who Can\'t Heal.
The Sanctum of Frauds and Shams...
Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_4">These might fit perfectly, heh... 
By the time the whispers spread,
oh... things are going to get
VERY interesting...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_5">Is it true...?
Crumbs...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_6">I knew it! For some reason,
I keep getting sick even
after being treated...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_7">Oh no... I\'m doomed...
Getting treated here
was a mistake...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_8">Hey! What\'s going on here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_9">The air in here seems...
ominous. Let\'s listen
quietly to ascertain what-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_10">Hey, folks!
What\'re you doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_11">................
I can\'t even...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_12">*Sniffle, sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_13">What\'s wrong,
Cottage Cheese Cookie?
Stay calm...!
You\'re not supposed to cry...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_14">The patients are...
*Sob* that First Milk Cookie is...
*Sob*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_15">Erm....
What?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_16">The patients are saying that
First Milk Cookie is a fraud...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_17">They\'re saying she hasn\'t
really healed anyone, ever...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_18">What has she done?
Has she ever cured anyone here?!
I keep taking the potions and
medicine, but I\'m still sick!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_19">First Milk Cookie is
the Healer Who Can\'t Heal!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_20">This place isn\'t a place of healing!
It\'s a Sanctum of Frauds and Shams!
They\'re only pretending to help us!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_21">Why... Why is this happening...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH2_SQ4_POR1_22">The entire sanctum
has been plunged into turmoil
because of these ridiculous rumors...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_1">I\'m sick of getting treated with no real results! I\'m leaving to find another doctor! I\'m going to someone who actually knows what they\'re doing!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_2">Does First Milk Cookie even have healing powers? What is she doing all day?! I can\'t trust her anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_3">Everyone\'s really angry... How did all these rumors start in the first place...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_4">N-N-No...! You mustn\'t! You must remain here and... you must heal and recover...! You cannot leave...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_5">First Milk Cookie! We understand how you feel, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_6">No... no...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_7">You must recover... You must rest... Please.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_8">Rest?! Is that the only advice you can give us?! We\'ve done as you said, but how come we aren\'t getting any better???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_9">Maybe she\'s keeping us here on purpose! She\'s probably making us sicker so we can\'t leave!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_10">REALLY? Are you hearing yourselves...? *Sniffle* Don\'t listen to them, First Milk Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_11">No... I... But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_12">Bzzzt... bzzzt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_13">Wait... That sound was...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_14">Look! There\'re holes forming in the Milk Veil...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_15">An astute observation. The Milk Veil is losing integrity...! We need to calm First Milk Cookie down, immediately!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_16">Huh? The barrier is breaking apart, but... we have to help First Milk Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_17">The Sanctum of Healing responds to First Milk Cookie\'s mind and spirit...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_18">Crackle... bzzzt...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_19">I\'m sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_20">I\'m sorry... I\'m so sorry... I\'m... sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_21">AHAHAHAHAAA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_22">Gah... My side...! The pain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_23">Hey! She\'s the one we saved a while back! Why\'s she laughing maniacally?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_24">It\'s no use seeking treatment at the Sanctum of Healing... First Milk Cookie\'s a fraud who can\'t heal anyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_25">Who knew the Cookies getting treated here would eat up these stories so easily! After all that fine treatment and medicine, they\'re being SO ungrateful, don\'t you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_26">But allow me to formally introduce myself. Hello, world! My name is Net Cookie! And I... am just getting STARTED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_27">What...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_28">Agh... My back hurts too...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_29">The one who\'s been disturbing the patients and spreading these absurd rumors about First Milk Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ1_POR1_30">Was you?! Why would you do this, Net Cookie?! WHY?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_1">Unbelievable. To think the cause of all this trouble is a patient who\'s been receiving treatment from us... I cannot in good conscience continue your treatment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_2">You have no right to remain here! Please leave at once...! You are upsetting the other patients and, what\'s more, you are interfering with their recovery...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_3">The right to remain here? Oh, come now. Was there such a thing to begin with?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_4">Isn\'t the whole point of this so-called Sanctum of Healing to welcome, take in, and embrace all Cookies or dessert creatures in need of treatment?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_5">Ouch, ow, oh nooo...! I\'m sooo injured and hurt. Owieee...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_6">Gah...! My side...! Curse this pain...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_7">We... we really do welcome all patients... but... *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_8">Erm... She really does look like she\'s in pain though!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_9">... Argh! You\'re not here in the sanctum to seek healing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_10">What does it matter why I came here? All that matters is that I\'m a patient right now, isn\'t it? I need healing, oh so desperately...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_11">Go on, say it yourself, First Milk Cookie! Didn\'t you swear to provide perfect and devoted treatment to any and all Cookies in need, no matter the circumstances?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_12">I... Yes... That is my oath... So I have to... cure...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_13">First Milk Cookie, stop! You can\'t! If that disruptive nuisance stays in the sanctum, it will only make things more difficult for the patients who genuinely need our care...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_14">Skim Milk Cookie has a good point...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_15">Though I do not disagree... Why must I hesitate...? Why must I delay treating someone who is standing right before me, and is in pain...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_16">Brrrzzzttt, CRACKLE...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_17">Ahahahaha! HAHAHA!!! I heard you were an indecisive fool, even back in your days as a witch! It looks like I heard right!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_18">....!!!!!!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_19">Back when you were still a witch, you decided to let all those poor, sick souls suffer because you were too scared they\'d find out the truth about you, didn\'t you? How cowardly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_20">I want to hear it straight from your lips, First Milk Cookie. Are you going to toss me aside like some worthless scraps and hide behind the excuse that it\'s for the sake of the other poor, poor patients?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_21">...!
First Milk Cookie, do not falter, madam!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_22">I\'m in sooo much pain! I need help too...! Why aren\'t you saying anything? Cat got your tongue?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_23">Wait... \"When she was still a witch\"? What did you mean by that? What do you know about First Milk Cookie...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_24">Oh, I don\'t know much! Or do I? If I said that First Egg Cookie sent me, that should tell you exactly how much I know!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ2_POR1_25">*GASP*
WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_1">F-F-First Egg Cookie sent you here? Then... that means Toughie is in danger...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_2">HAHAHAHA! You lot are smarter than you look!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_3">No... Stop... Stop...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_4">Please... No more...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_5">Crackle...! CRACKLE...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_6">*BEEP BEEP BEEP*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_7">The alarm...?! It\'s the incubator! It means Toughie\'s vital signs are dropping at an alarming rate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_8">No...! Toughie...! Please!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_9">BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEEEEEEEEPPP!!!!!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_10">BZZZT...!!! CRACKLE...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_11">NO! First the incubator, now the Milk Veil?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_12">Skim Milk Cookie! I don\'t think it\'s just the Milk Veil reacting to First Milk Cookie\'s mind...! I think the incubator is linked to her as well!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_13">That alarm started blaring the moment First Milk Cookie was shaken! This can\'t be a coincidence!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_14">All this fuss and chaos over a lump of dough and a few Cookies with sniffles and boo-boos...? Seriously... You\'re all just too easy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_15">No hard feelings! I\'m just following orders, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_16">Look at you! PAH! All fragile and falling apart, worse off than your own patients, but the only thing you really care about is that useless batter ball. That\'s some next-level hypocrisy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_17">Wait... First Milk Cookie seems worse off than the patients...? Come to think of it... she does seem to be really on edge...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ3_POR1_18">Y-Y-You guys...! Maybe the Sanctum of Healing falling apart... is a sign! It\'s a warning that First Milk Cookie\'s spirit is crumbling...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_1">Why are you taking orders from
a nefarious villain like
First Egg Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_2">Heheheee...
Sounds like you know exactly
what First Egg Cookie is capable of!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_3">I won\'t bother hiding it then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_4">I exist to serve!
To bring joy to First Egg Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_5">I was baked by her
for one purpose:
to obey her every order!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_6">...?
A Cookie... baked a Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_7">My creator,
First Egg Cookie,
gave me a purpose...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_8">I\'m here to collect the
Cookie of the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_9">What does First Egg Cookie
want to accomplish...?!
Why is she doing this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_10">Collect?!
Toughie\'s a Cookie,
not some object!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_11">I thought the Milk Veil
was the obstacle that
would make or break
my plans...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_12">But the oh-so-fragile
First Milk Cookie
softened up a bit too easily!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_13">The problem practically
solved itself!
HAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_14">Now it\'s time for
the coup de grâce!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_15">Target confirmed!
Entry to Sanctum of Healing:
secured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_16">Begin acquisition sequence:
Cookie of the First Batch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_17">AAAHAHAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_18">What is that...?
WHAT IS THAT?!?!?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH3_SQ4_POR1_19">EEEK! EGG GOLEMS!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_1">... I appear to be in worse shape... than the patients... who need my help...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_2">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_3">First Milk Cookie, I know we haven\'t stayed here in the sanctum for very long... but... you always seem to be uneasy and... anxious...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_4">I... I did not realize... *Sob*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_5">It\'s obvious now. First Egg Cookie knew exactly what would hurt First Milk Cookie the most. Sending in Net Cookie, sowing chaos within the Sanctum of Healing... it\'s clear this was all by design.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_6">... First Milk Cookie, are you really okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_7">I... I am... I don\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_8">Commence retrieval. Commence retrieval.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_9">Target signature detected. Commencing trace protocol.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_10">BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP!BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEP!BEEP! BEEP! BEEEEEEEEEPPP!!!!!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_11">Nooo...! Toughie...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_12">I thought... if I became a more perfect healer, all would be well...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_13">I thought... if I devoted myself to caring for every soul in need, help them recover... Maybe even those I failed to heal long ago... would forgive me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_14">I... I never really stopped to think... if I was okay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_15">........ It felt too selfish to even ask myself that. It felt... undeserved...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_16">How come...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_17">Because... I have never been a perfect healer... Not back then, not now... There are... far too many... I failed to save... *Sob*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_18">......</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_19">You don\'t really think that, do you, First Milk Cookie? Look at me!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_20">I\'m not a perfect Cookie either! Every time I cry... my body gets lighter and smaller... But that doesn\'t matter! I carry my milk bottle and keep cleaning and scrubbing away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_21">And even if I\'m not perfect, I like myself just as I am! Really! And when my dough feels too light... I rehydrate just like I was prescribed and everything\'s back to normal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_22">Cottage Cheese Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_23">First Milk Cookie. If anyone can diagnose what causes your pain, and what kind of treatment you need...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_24">Wouldn\'t it be you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_25">If your broken heart can be healed, then the sanctum will also restore itself!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_26">I... Could it be...? I have never attempted a self-diagnosis... But I shall try...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_27">... The required remedy and prescription is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_28">&lt;A Loving Hug.&gt;</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_29">First Milk Cookie! Here\'s a really, really loving hug!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_30">First Milk Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_31">Make room! Big group hug for First Milk Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_32">...?
What are you doing?! WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_33">Clack... clack... clack...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ1_POR1_34">Look! The Milk Veil is rebuilding itself!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_1">ALERT! ALERT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_2">Escape route compromised. Detecting obstruction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_3">Abort acquisition sequence. Abort.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_4">Clack... clack... clack...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_5">The Egg Golems are running away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_6">It\'s because the Milk Veil is restoring itself! They need to leave before the barrier is fully functional!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_7">Scan operative: condition and status.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_8">Operative status: injured.
Expedited extraction: compromised.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_9">Operative extraction not viable. Target marked for disposal. Beep. Beep.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_10">WHAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_11">Are you kidding me?! You clanking, brainless scraps...!!! We were this close to succeeding!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_12">How could you leave that doughy brat behind?! Useless, useless steaming piles of rotten eggs!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_13">Clack... clack... clack...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_14">The Milk Veil\'s totally fixed now...! And I don\'t hear the incubator alarm going off anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_15">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_16">What a relief... Ahem, now... Net Cookie. Please leave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_17">Wait...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_18">\???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_19">Net Cookie. I cannot allow you to remain in the Sanctum of Healing... But I can help heal your wounds and ease your pain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_20">...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_21">Let me soothe the pain in your side, that doughy welt... And the swollen knot at the back of your head, it throbs with pain when you cry or shout, does it not?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_22">The pain will fade. Everything will be okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_23">The pain... is gone?
She... cured me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_24">But beyond your physical injuries, I sense that you carry a deeper wound within your heart... Are you okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_25">Shut up! I\'ve no such thing! ... Why would I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_26">She was baked and forged for a single purpose. Now that it has failed, she has been cast aside and abandoned. It is only natural for her to feel anger... isolation... grief...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_27">It was not until I saw the warmth in these Cookies\' eyes as they hoped for Toughie\'s recovery... that I realized just how much emptiness and sorrow was in my own heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_28">... This is the treatment I recommend. But if it means nothing to you, then you are free to leave it behind...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ2_POR1_29">&lt;Time must pass. Tears must be shed. Receive closure with a warm embrace.&gt;</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_1">Haaaaaahhh.........!!!  HOW PATHETIC!
This is rich... Time? Tears?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_2">A hug?! A HUG?!?!?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_3">Don\'t you dare look down on me with your pity!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_4">I won\'t stand for this... Not from you, First Milk Cookie... Not from any of you... And especially that worthless doughball you all coddle and treat like royalty!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_5">Why are you so angry, Net Cookie? If you want your prescribed hug right now... I can give you one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_6">AAARGH...!!! This is infuriating! I\'ve had ENOUGH!!! This whole place is disgusting and nauseating!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_7">(Dashes off)</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_8">She\'s... gone... Just like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_9">Oh dear...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_10">Don\'t worry, First Milk Cookie! You gave her a really good remedy! Even if it\'s not here, she\'ll get better some day! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_11">... I hope so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_12">She\'ll get better! I\'m sure of it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_13">Toughie\'s vital signs have stabilized...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_14">Would you... like to pay a visit?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_15">So this little Cookie is Toughie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_16">I wonder when Toughie will wake up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_17">When you open your eyes... someday... somehow... We hope to see you smiling...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_18">Indeed! I am also optimistic that Toughie will wake up...! We\'ll meet again soon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_19">Though we don\'t know when that day will be, under First Milk Cookie\'s care and supervision... Toughie will make it through and wake up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_20">Haha! Let us know when that day comes! We\'ll come running right over!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ3_POR1_21">Yes... I will let you know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ4_POR1_1">... I\'m sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ4_POR1_2">When I first baked you...
I was so overjoyed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ4_POR1_3">But my fear, my broken heart...
All that pain I held inside...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA04_CH4_SQ4_POR1_4">I did not know it would
be passed on
