to help you recovery...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Monologue.Random.03">Are you feeling any
discomfort or pain...?
Do not hesitate to tell me.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Monologue.Random.04">Are you injured...?
I will treat you right away!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Monologue.Random.05">The sanctum is a safe haven
for the weary and injured...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Monologue.LifeZero.01">I\'m sorry...
I\'m so sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Monologue.Greeting">&lt;color=#E2501D&gt;{0}&lt;/color&gt;... I shall heal and treat you...</string>
