  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.001.Story">A radiant pavilion with a fountain of healing milk nestled within. Its golden pillars and roof gleam with divine brilliance. Here, just like warm milk soothes the soul, this sacred space gently cradles the severely injured, providing them with the much-needed peace and quiet they need to recover.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.002.Story">A tranquil pavilion with a fountain of healing milk nestled within. Here, just like warm milk soothes the soul, this quiet space gently cradles the severely injured, providing them with the much-needed peace they need to recover.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Wall.001.Story">A golden window that shimmers like a miracle. Many say that standing before this window\'s radiant glow will melt away all your pain, as if being in the presence of a healer who works miracles.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Wall.002.Story">Crafted with brilliant golden wings, this ornate window catches light in a way that seems to gently shine upon the injured. The sunlight pouring through feels like a soft embrace for all weary souls.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.003.Story">Meticulously arranged with medicinal herbs and medical tools, this desk always has a potion or two brewing inside glass flasks. Healing experiments and research carry on without rest... It\'s as if the owner of the desk dreams of a future where all are free from pain and illness.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.004.Story">Line with scrolls on various diagnoses and treatment logs, this shelf tells a story of tireless and compassionate care. It is clear that no trace of pain is overlooked, as every page is an indication of the healer\'s unwavering devotion.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Deck.001.Story">A blend of blue and white tiles, embroidered with elegant gold patterns. Each step fills you with a sense of tranquil resolve.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Wallpaper.001.Story">This wallpaper adds a sense of quiet dignity to the Sanctum of Healing\'s walls. Elegant and composed, it reflects the healer\'s solemn oath to comfort all who enter.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Ceil.001.Story">A gauze canopy adorned with a single gemstone. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Ceil.002.Story">A teacup fashioned into a hanging lamp. Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Wall.003.Story">A wall decorated with various memorabilia. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Wall.004.Story">A ship\'s helm with a heartbreaking story. Let\'s place it somewhere worthy.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.005.Story">A veil that perhaps has a story. It\'s no wonder who this belongs to.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Ceil.003.Story">A hammock made from a surgical mask and feathers. It\'s simple but comfortable.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.006.Story">A medicinal herb growing in a milk can. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Hanger.001.Story">A simple curtain to help patient recovery. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2021.Floor.007.Story">A first-aid kit. Always handy to have one nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2021">First Milk Cookie\'s Room of Compassionate Healing</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2021.Story">First Milk Cookie\'s room is filled with the comforting aroma of warm milk. Here, even the tiniest sensations of pain or a heart burdened with despair can recover in peaceful comfort.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.001">Bottle of a Night Best Forgotten</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.002">Heartbroken Healer\'s Staff</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.003">Crystallized Tear Brooch</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.001.Story">Inside this delicate glass bottle lies a model ship caught in a furious storm and moments from vanishing beneath the waves. This is a memory sealed away, too painful to relive, but also too haunting to let go.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.002.Story">The staff of a healer who wished to embrace the injured and weary and soothe their pain. However, this staff now bears the scars of its wielder\'s remorse. Etched with the weight of every failure, it still glows with a glimmer of hope.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2021.003.Story">This pale brooch cradles a single crystallized tear, which was formed while reminiscing about the pain of the past. The crystal\'s light never seems to fade, making it a constant, quiet reminder of a sorrow left unspoken.</string>
