  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2021.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Milk Cookie. It looks delicate, but the eyes contain a strong sense of determination.</string>
  <string name="$Season.2021.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the First Milk Collection! With a bright smile and a warm heart that embraces sorrow, you can melt away any pain and illuminate anyone\'s path with hope!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2021.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Milk Cookie\'s soul. Holding it seems to bring a warm sense of comfort, much like a warm cup of milk after a rough day.</string>
