  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2021.Title.01.Summary">One day, Herb Cookie arrived at the Sanctum of Healing with an unusual request. He brought along Zombie Cookie, and asks First Milk Cookie to cure Zombie Cookie\'s unnatural fear of plants. The Keeper of the Sanctum is unfamiliar with such a symptom, but promises to try her best.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2021.Title.02.Summary">First Milk Cookie attempts to diagnose Zombie Cookie\'s condition, but is bewildered to find the Cookie\'s condition is unlike anything she had treated before. Though hesitant, she resolves to continue the diagnosis and find a treatment.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2021.Title.03.Summary">First Milk Cookie has reached a realization: Zombie Cookie is not sick. This is simply who they are! And, at that moment, she realizes there are many Cookies in the world, each living in their own way.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2021.Illust.Dialog.01">First Milk Cookie...
Kind... and nice...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2021.Illust.Dialog.02">Zombie Cookie...
I am so glad to
have met you...!</string>
