  <string name="$Saga04_Ch1_sq1.Summary">GingerBrave and friends attempt to enter the Sanctum of Healing, but they are blocked by an unseen magical barrier! GingerBright, cheerfully reckless as always, tries to break through, only for the attempt to lead to a few injuries. Only then does the barrier lift.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch1_sq2.Summary">After receiving treatment, our adventuring friends learn from Skim Milk Cookie that there is indeed a Cookie of the First Batch within the Sanctum of Healing. Known as Toughie, the small Cookie is currently a critical patient placed within an incubator.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch1_sq3.Summary">The patients of the sanctum, who have received the best possible care, do not seem to be fully recovering. As a result, the sanctum\'s patient count has rarely dropped. With First Milk Cookie focused on the critically ill, Skim Milk Cookie has become overworked with the remainder of the patients. Nevertheless, he continues his sleepless research to find the cause of the patients\' illnesses.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch1_sq4.Summary">Concerned about a potential relapse, the Cookies are encouraged to stay in the sanctum for further observation. With First Milk Cookie\'s hesitant approval, GingerBrave and friends decide to help care for the patients and keep a watchful eye on Toughie.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch2_sq1.Summary">The Sanctum of Healing is overflowing with patient records. First Milk Cookie\'s vow to heal all patients has filled the halls with hopeful Cookies, but the relapse rate is a major problem that must be addressed. The Cookies decide to do everything they can to help support the healers.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch2_sq2.Summary">It turns out that Cottage Cheese Cookie, a former patient of the sanctum, has relapsed as well. Though she happily claims she is fine, silent tears betray the truth...</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch2_sq3.Summary">A mysterious Cookie is rescued from the nearby Milk Falls. After receiving first aid, the patient comes to and claims to have been attacked by a Cookie who resembled an egg...! Our friends immediately come to a shared conclusion: First Egg Cookie must be nearby!</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch2_sq4.Summary">In the dead of night, Net Cookie devises a scheme to twist the truth and spread devastating rumors about the Sanctum of Healing. Before long, whispers of doubt echo through the halls, and confusion and chaos begin to take hold.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch3_sq1.Summary">The patients, now consumed with distrust and suspicion, prepare to leave the sanctum. Taken aback at the news, First Milk Cookie\'s emotions begin to unravel and the Milk Veil also responds, slowly weakening and dissipating. Net Cookie then steps forward, revealing herself as the source of the chaos.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch3_sq2.Summary">Skim Milk Cookie demands Net Cookie leave, declaring her unfit to receive treatment at the Sanctum of Healing. But Net Cookie mocks First Milk Cookie\'s solemn oath to heal all Cookies, no matter who they are, ridiculing her indecision and emotional instability.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch3_sq3.Summary">Shaken by Net Cookie\'s taunts, First Milk Cookie breaks down. The Cookies realize the Milk Veil, and even Toughie\'s incubator, are tied to her emotions.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch3_sq4.Summary">Our heroes confront Net Cookie, who finally reveals the truth! She was baked by none other than First Egg Cookie and was sent to retrieve the Cookie of the First batch. All of a sudden, the Milk Veil completely shatters and Egg Golems swarm into the Sanctum of Healing.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch4_sq1.Summary">Tormented by the thought that her own emotional scars have made Toughie suffer as well, First Milk Cookie finally chooses to address her own pain. Encouraged by the Cookies, she resolves to begin looking inward to heal herself.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch4_sq2.Summary">Sensing the Milk Veil regenerating to full strength, the Egg Golems make a hasty retreat and abandon Net Cookie! First Milk Cookie, keeping true to her oath, treats Net Cookie\'s wounds and offers a remedy for her own heartache as well.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch4_sq3.Summary">Net Cookie sneers and curses the sanctum on her way out, but the Cookies firmly believe that she will make a full recovery with time. They are invited to view Toughie\'s now peaceful incubator and are eager to meet the First Batcher when they wake up.</string>
  <string name="$Saga04_Ch4_sq4.Summary">First Milk Cookie gently embraces Toughie, confessing that her own pain had been passed on, causing the little one to suffer. As she gently whispers about how precious they are, even if they are not tough all the time, the little Cookie stirs for the first time.</string>
