  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_1">... The medical records filed by First Milk Cookie are flawless as always. Well, now that sterilization is completed, I should find the next patient\'s file...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_2">*Rustle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_3">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_4">What\'s that sound? At this hour...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_5">Creeeak... Tap, tap... THUD!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_6">Oh dear... Could that be a patient? Hm, I should go check on them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_7">Crumbs! An injured Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_8">First, I need to check if they are conscious and responsive.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_9">Excuse me! Hello? Hello?! Can you hear me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_10">Ugh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_11">I must begin emergency treatment immediately. Don\'t worry, I\'m a doctor! You\'re in good hands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_12">I... made it to... the right place...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_1_POR1_13">Do not fret! Don\'t try to talk, just remain calm! Everything will be fine soon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_1">Just collapsing without warning... This is quite concerning.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_2">How peculiar... I have never encountered such unusual scarring before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_3">There are signs of infection too... Bacterial? Viral? Hm, it doesn\'t seem overly severe at the moment, but I can\'t be certain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_4">What happened to this Cookie...? Could this be some form of... contagion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_5">Am I... qualified to treat such an illness?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_6">... No, this isn\'t the time for doubt. I must do everything to the best of my ability. I hope this patient wakes up soon...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_7">Urgh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_8">Ah. He\'s coming to. Thank goodness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_9">How are you feeling?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_10">Ugh... Nngh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_11">Does it hurt anywhere? Can you hear me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_12">... I can... hear you clearly. Thank you for... healing my wounds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_13">Thank goodness. May I ask... who are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_14">My name is... Onyx Cream Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_15">I hail from Mount St. Crème. I am currently traveling... and I appear to be far away from home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_16">These scars are quite concerning. I have never seen an infection leave marks quite like these before... *Sigh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_17">Would you mind explaining where they came from?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_18">... Mount St. Crème has always been a cool and arid place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_19">But when the Temperature Controller broke down, the fungal monstrosities appeared... And now, many in my homeland are infected like I am.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_20">I see... Well, it appears the treatment appears to be working. There are definitely signs of improvement.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_21">As you are acclimated to a colder and dryer environment, it appears your illness was exacerbated by traveling through areas with different climates...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_2_POR1_22">...!!!
I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_1">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_2">It looks like both of us have a high percentage of dairy in our dough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_3">I believe my dough is safe from such maladies, but yours is an entirely different story.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_4">You seem to be very sensitive to any changes in the environment. I believe it is due to the sensitive nature of the heavy cream within your dough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_5">Hm... Sensitive cream within my body... I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_6">For now, I\'ve finished treating your injuries. You should be well enough to return to your travels.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_7">... Much obliged.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_8">Now that you know what caused your condition to worsen, please be mindful of your surroundings as you move forward.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_9">Yes, I shall do so. And I appreciate your concern. I will make sure to travel with caution, just as you advised.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_10">Perhaps, the next time we meet, I will return as a guest, not a patient.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_11">Sounds grand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_12">I get the feeling this may happen in the future again. Not all who seek the Sanctum of Healing will be injured. Some may be seeking aid to help manage the conditions of their unique dough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_13">Yes... I need to conduct more research on this matter.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_14">Research Log, Day 1: A New Case</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2023_3_POR1_15">Beyond treating physical injuries, further research is required to understand how a Cookie\'s unique characteristics and dough composition affects their overall health.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.Main">Skim Milk Cookie\'s Research</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.01">An Injured Guest</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.02">Traces of an Unknown Infection</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.03">New Research, New Commitment</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.01.Summary">While reviewing past medical records, Skim Milk Cookie hears someone collapse outside. Upon investigating, he discovers an almost unconscious Onyx Cream Cookie. Initially startled by the unexpected patient, Skim Milk Cookie immediate begins emergency treatment. Meanwhile, Onyx Cream Cookie reassures himself that he has finally come to the right place.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.02.Summary">Skim Milk Cookie discovers traces of an unfamiliar infection on Onyx Cream Cookie\'s body. When Onyx Cream Cookie comes to, he explains that the scars are from encountering the fungal monstrosities that appeared in Mount St. Crème when the temperature controller malfunctions. After a more thorough diagnosis, Skim Milk Cookie is certain Onyx Cream Cookie\'s health deteriorates due to environmental changes.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Title.03.Summary">Skim Milk Cookie realizes there is a stark difference between Onyx Cream Cookie\'s and his own dough. The two share a large of portion of dairy, but Onyx Cream Cookie\'s heavy cream is much more susceptible to changes in the weather. As Onyx Cream Cookie bids him farewell, he promises to return as a visitor rather than a patient. Skim Milk Cookie makes a personal commitment to begin researching the diverse physiological makeup of different Cookies and their dough.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Illust.Dialog.01">Perhaps, the next time
we meet, I will return as
a guest, not a patient.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2023.Illust.Dialog.02">Sounds grand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_1">Wow... this must be it! My gut feeling was right all along...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_2">According to this treasure map... the lost treasure is hidden around here somewhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_3">Hm...? What\'s this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_4">THUD!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_5">Wh-what? Who\'s there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_6">Huh? A Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_7">Wait...! You\'re the Guardian of the Treasure, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_8">... What nonsense is this Cookie babbling about...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_9">Hm... Might as well have some fun to pass to time! No one ever comes around here anyway.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_10">So... You are aware of the fabled treasure. Identify yourself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_11">Amazing! Just as I thought!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_12">From the moment I opened that door, I knew an awesome adventure would be waiting for me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_13">Oh great Guardian of the Treasure. What trials must I undertake?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_1_POR1_14">T-Trials...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_1">Hehe... Let\'s see where this takes us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_2">Ahaha! I admire your initiative! Let us see if you are truly worthy of being called an adventurer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_3">Alright! I\'ll ace anything you throw at me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_4">Very well! Listen carefully, for this shall be your first test.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_5">Though it holds the most precious treasures in the world, it that cannot hold anything else.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_6">It is always empty, yet full at the same time. Can you discover what it is? Hahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_7">Hm... A vessel for storing the most precious things...? But it\'s empty? And it can\'t hold anything else?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_8">Foolish Cookie! You\'ll never guess it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_9">OH! I got it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_10">The answer... is that thing right there! The Light-Salvaging Net hanging in this very room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_11">The net is so loosely woven that everything slips right through it when you try to hold anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_12">It can only hold light that has lost its way. The net makes them shine bright and clear with newfound purpose, which is one of the greatest treasures to possess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_13">HAHA! Haha... You\'re quite the clever one, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_14">How amusing...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_15">You are rather extraordinary... Well then, how about another?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_16">Very well! Listen carefully, for this is your second test!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_17">What is the most deceptive item within this chamber?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_18">This place is full of wonderful treasures! What\'s deceptive here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_19">Lemme see here... Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_20">Could it be...? AH-HA! The couch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_21">It looks fancy on the outside, but when you take a closer look, there\'s all sorts of abandoned junk stuck to it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_22">It looks luxurious and comfy, but it\'s anything but!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_23">AHAHA! Got it right again! Not bad, not bad.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_2_POR1_24">Okay... One last test...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_1">This is your final test! What is the most treasured of treasures held in this chamber?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_2">The most treasured can also be the most perilous...! Can you pass this test as well, lone adventurer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_3">The most treasured of treasures...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_4">Honestly, everything here seems to be valuable and important...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_5">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_6">Hm...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_7">Of course you can\'t find it, because it doesn\'t exist! How could you possible find a treasure that isn\'t even in here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_8">Oh?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_9">Could it be... Maybe...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_10">Could this diary be the most precious of treasures? I should take a look inside to see if it is. Let\'s see here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_11">AAAGH! Don\'t touch that! I\'m begging you!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_12">\?!?!?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_13">NOT THE DIARY! DON\'T!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_14">I knew it! The diary is the most treasured of treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_15">... This Cookie is too much trouble. I need to get rid of him, NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_16">You are indeed a great adventurer! You have passed all the trials.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_17">As the Guardian of the Treasure, I shall show you where the true treasure lies, waiting to be discovered by one such as you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_18">Really?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_19">You must run away from here, in that direction, until you are out of breath. Once you pass a small brick, take three steps up, spin around counter-clockwise three times, and then go left...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2022_3_POR1_20">Thank you so much! This is awesome...! A brand new adventure, given to me by a Guardian of the Treasure! Goodbye, and thanks again!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.Main">Net Cookie: Guardian of the Treasure?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.01">An Adventurer Seeks Lost Treasure</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.02">Net Cookie\'s \"Trials\"</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.03">The Most Treasured of Treasures</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.01.Summary">After following an ancient treasure map, Adventurer Cookie bursts into Net Cookie\'s room! He mistakes Net Cookie as a \"Guardian of Treasure\". The overly excited adventurer declares his determination to overcome any test or trial to obtain the lost treasaure.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.02.Summary">Intrigued by Adventurer Cookie\'s enthusiasm, Net Cookie decides to play along and \"test\" him. To her surprise, Adventurer Cookie passes every concocted test of hers with flying colors.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Title.03.Summary">For the final test, Net Cookie asks Adventurer Cookie to find the most treasured of treasures. After searching the room, he points to Net Cookie\'s diary. Flustered by this, Net Cookie hastily gives him false information to send him away on a wild goose chase. Overjoyed at the thought of passing the final test, Adventurer Cookie sets off for yet another adventure.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Illust.Dialog.01">Could this diary
be the most
precious of treasures?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2022.Illust.Dialog.02">AAAGH!
Don\'t touch that!
I\'m begging you!!!</string>
