  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.001.Story">A bin filled to the brim with autumn grains! What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.002.Story">A decor to give any room a touch of autumn! This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.003.Story">A lovely ornament pumpkin, bathed in the moonlight. Let\'s put it somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.004.Story">On a silent moonlit night, after gathering ripened grains and harvesting lush fruits from the trees, the warehouses overflow with abundance, bringing peace to everyone\'s hearts. When looking out the window and reminiscing about the past year, you see a shooting star falling from the sky! You say a silent, heartfelt prayer... \"May the next harvest, and the harvest after that be oh-so rewarding as this year.\" Surely, your wish will come true!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.005.Story">The full moon is so delighted to see countless Cookies gazing up and smiling at it. Wishing to share the joy with everyone every single day, the moon scattered tiny moon shards all across the Witch\'s Castle! When pieces together, these shards form a full moon decoration that captures the abundant spirit of the harvest for all to enjoy throughout the year.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.006.Story">Wallpaper that captures the essence of autumn, when the lush greenery changes into a shade of rubies and gold, and the Rice Cake Squirrels are busily gathering acorns to prepare for winter.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.2025MoonEvent.007.Story">Flooring that captures the essence of autumn, when the vast meadows of green change into a shade of golden sun. This flooring helps you feel the energy of nature\'s most colorful and bountiful season.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Frame.EventMoonLight">Moonlight Shard</string>
  <string name="$Item.Profile.EventMoonLight">Moonlight Shard</string>
  <string name="$Item.TowerPalace.Room.2025MoonEvent">Moonlit Autumn Night of Abundance</string>
  <string name="$Item.TowerPalace.Room.2025MoonEvent.Story">After a long year of hard work comes the time to reap the rewards! As Cookies make their wishes to the full moon hanging silently above their bountiful warehouses, the moon itself decided to make a wish too... to shrink down, join the festivities, and share laughter with the Cookies! Perhaps the wish came true, for shards of the moon were found throughout the castle. Now, in this room as abundant as the fall harvest, you can meet the moon whenever you wish!</string>
