  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Story">Honeyed words that roll of the tongue are woven from the stickiest of lies. Net Cookie, ever the master of weaving rumors, twists the truth to exploit weaknesses with unsettling ease and ruthless efficiency. The moment a victim falls for her tall tales, she bursts into maniacal laughter. But is she laughing from true joy, or is it just another lie?

Made only to follow orders and with no other purpose, this Cookie\'s web of deceit hides a hollow core that no amount of sugar-coated lies can ever truly fill...</string>
