  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Get">Ahahaha! Now THIS is
getting interesting.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Random.01">Hey! I just heard some juicy
gossip for your ears only...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Random.02">Deceiving everyone is
like child\'s play...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Random.03">Everything is going
according to plan, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Random.04">What?! This wasn\'t
part of the plan at all!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Random.05">HA! You really
believed that?!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.LifeZero.01">URGH!
This is so annoying...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2022.Monologue.Greeting">AHAHA! What would you
