  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.001">Deceptive Couch of False Comfort</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.002">Couch of Sticky Cobwebs</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.003">Lamp of Reflection</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.001">Tangled Net Chandelier</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Hanger.001">Light-Salvaging Net</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.001">Window of Emptiness</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wallpaper.001">Tightly Woven Plaid Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Deck.001">Damp Stone Floor</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.002">Tattered and Worn Curtains</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.002">Secret Plan Blueprint</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.004">Sharp Harpoon and Sticky Net</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.5">Empty Diaries</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Hanger.002">Sticky Prey</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.003">Soft-Glowing Harpoon Light</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.003">Stained Glass</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Rug.001">Sticky Spider Web Rug</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.006">Sparkling Deceptive Fence</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.001.Story">What a luxurious couch! It\'s adorned with deep turquoise velvet upholstery and golden frames! And... what are those things...? It looks like some abandoned or forgotten trasures from a bygone memory are hanging in sticky webs, decorating the couch in an eerie light...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.002.Story">A simple turquoise, metal-framed couch adorned with various trinkets caught in sticky webbing. Whether these once-cherished items were abandoned or lost remains a mystery, but they\'ve become an unintentional part of the couch itself.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.003.Story">A delicate, egg-shaped lamp adorned with a thin net. Every time the light flickers on, Net Cookie reflects on the very purpose of her creation.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.001.Story">A chandelier woven like a delicate web of glass strands. Light and shadows seep through the gaps, creating a mesmerizing sparkle that captivates everyone\'s gaze.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Hanger.001.Story">A lamp that collects lost rays of light, giving them a chance to sparkle with newfound hope and purpose. Its glow may not fill the emptiness in someone\'s heart completely, but it offers a sliver of gentle comfort to those who need it...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.001.Story">Beneath the tranquil waves visible through the window, forgotten relics aimlessly like bygone feelings floating in the depths of an empty heart. What thoughts cross Net Cookie\'s mind as she gazes out this window?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wallpaper.001.Story">The intricate weave pattern is so soothing to look at. It looks much sturdier than a loose net, bringing you a sense of security that calms any anxious thoughts.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Deck.001.Story">The surface appears smooth at first glance, but upon closer inspection, moisture appears to be seeping through countless hidden cracks. Like an anxious heart, this floor is riddled with gaps and fissures that fail to stay concealed.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.002.Story">A tattered curtain. It\'s tattered. Very tattered. What an interesting find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.002.Story">A blueprint detailing some sort of secret plan. Just looking at it fills you with anticipation.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.004.Story">These tools look dangerous. Let\'s... keep them somewhere safe.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.5.Story">A set of empty diaries... Perfect for filling with untold stories!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Hanger.002.Story">Captured prey. It serves as a good reminder.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Ceil.003.Story">A harpoon-shaped lamp. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Wall.003.Story">A beautiful stained-glass window! What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Rug.001.Story">A sticky rug. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2022.Floor.006.Story">A glittering fence that plays tricks on the eyes. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2022">Net Cookie\'s Room of Forgotten Treasures</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2022.Story">Net Cookie\'s room is filled with abandoned treasures and forgotten trinkets. Perhaps she sees a reflection of herself among these discarded items that have lost their purpose...</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.001">Frigid, Hollow Harpoon</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.002">Egg Golem Pendant</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.003">Jewelry Box of Treasured Tokens</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.001.Story">Instead of warmth and comfort, Net Cookie\'s earliest memory involves nothing but a cold, piercing harpoon. Like someone desperately trying to fill a hollow, empty void within, the pointed edge is always directed at something... or someone.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.002.Story">A pendant shaped like an obedient, mindless Egg Golem. Perhaps it symbolizes a silent wish to become the perfect minion, unquestioning and flawless.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2022.003.Story">A gleaming hairpiece bestowed by none other than First Egg Cookie herself. Each time Net Cookie gazes into this box, her hollow heart blooms with false hopes and empty dreams...</string>
