  <string name="$Cookie.2023.Story">You\'d be mistaken to call this Cookie bland and basic, skimmed of fat and flavorless. What truly defines Skim Milk Cookie is not a physical ingredient. His steadfast commitment to healing others, condensed into a solid core of purpose, by far outweighs anything else in his dough.

With every weary sigh, he jots something down in his medical journal. In his eyes, no ailment is without a remedy and no condition is deemed incurable. His calm, clinical resolve provides his patients with a sense of reassurance within the Sanctum of Healing.</string>
