  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.001.Story">For a thorough diagnosis, this medical scanner is absolutely essential! The holographic lights emanating from it also helps young patients stay calm during their examinations, making the scanning process much less intimidating.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.002.Story">For a flawless diagnosis, precise examination equipment is absolutely essential! This scanner might look intimidating at first glance, but rest assured, you\'re in very good hands!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.003.Story">A cot tucked away in the corner of Skim Milk Cookie\'s office and room. The rolled-up blanket and stacks of medical files scattered across it suggest he\'s never used it for its intended purpose, even when he\'s resting...</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.004.Story">Empty milk bottles sit beside freshly opened ones, while mountains of medical records tower nearby. This scene perfectly captures Skim Milk Cookie\'s daily dedication to his patients\' recovery. Every item on this desk represents his tireless pursuit to find the perfect cure for any case before him.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Wall.001.Story">A reliable robotic assistant installed by the overworked Skim Milk Cookie to monitor critical patients. This remarkable device continuously transmits the status of severely ill patients, ensuring not a single moment goes unobserved!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.005.Story">A high-tech screen that reveals every detail of a patient\'s condition. From simple injuries to microscopic dough fractures, it displays everything! An essential tool for Skim Milk Cookie to accurately diagnose and understand the patient\'s condition.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Deck.001.Story">A thoughtfully designed floor that reflects Skim Milk Cookie\'s concern for patient safety. The checkered pattern provides stable footing, while the soft lighting helps prevent any unfortunate falls. Every detail has been carefully considered to keep patients secure as they walk about!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Wallpaper.001.Story">This isn\'t just any ordinary wallpaper! It\'s a special one with first-aid kits installed for emergencies. Skimmed Milk Cookie personally selected and installed it himself.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.006.Story">A chair for patients to sit in during their examination. It\'s comfier than it looks!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Ceil.001.Story">A window that tells the tale of late-night research sessions. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Wall.002.Story">A versatile medical tray used for various procedures. It\'s very useful!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Wall.003.Story">A surgical lamp that provides bright, focused light. Perfect for any room that needs precise illumination!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.007.Story">A chart to test your eyesight. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.008.Story">A device that Skim Milk Cookie glances at almost every other second. Let\'s put it to good use!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Floor.009.Story">A simple stool for patients. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Ceil.002.Story">A lamp made from a milk bottle and a straw. Thrifty, yet stylish!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2023.Hanger.001.Story">A light that is never turned off. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2023">Skim Milk Cookie\'s Room of Late Night Research</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2023.Story">Piles of medical records and patient files adorn this weary doctor\'s room. Despite there being a first aid cot at his disposable, it\'s barely shown any signs of use! The ever-burning light in this room stands as a testament to his unwavering sense of duty to his patients.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.001">Weary Doctor\'s Glasses</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.002">Cherished Fountain Pen</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.003">Comfy Acupressure Slippers</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.001.Story">A symbol of Skim Milk Cookie\'s tireless dedication as he pores over medical records, research books, and a patient files throughout the night. Even when setting aside the glasses for a brief moment of rest, they never stray far from the weight of responsibility.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.002.Story">A gift from a revered healer. This exquisite and well-crafted pen has never been used. Skim Milk Cookie keeps it tucked away, perhaps saving it for a day that truly matters.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2023.003.Story">Medical personnel can potentially spend the entire day on their feet. As he rushes from patient to patient, these slippers soothe his weary soles after countless laps around the Sanctum of Healing.</string>
