  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Story">Baked with dollops of soft, unripened cottage cheesed nestled into her dough, Cottage Cheese Cookie is as fluffy and light as her bubbly personality. She\'s gentle, caring, and oh-so-cute! It\'s no wonder everyone adores her!

This Cookie does, however, need to carry a heavy jug of milk on her back just to stay grounded... But the concerned glances of those nearby doesn\'t phase her at all.

\"No matter what I look like, I love who I am,\" she exclaims with joy! 

And just like that, every worry in sight seems to melt away. Cottage Cheese Cookie is perhaps the softest soul in the Sanctum of Healing, but she is also the one with the strongest heart.</string>
