Nah, I\'m fine, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Monologue.Random.04">I\'ll clean the floors
if you clean the walls!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Monologue.Random.05">Hm, where\'d Skim Milk Cookie go?</string>
