  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.001.Story">A special milk bottle bed made just for young Cookies. Crafted with the finest dairy, the bed is always surrounded by the sweet and gentle scent of milk and cheese. Whether your eyes or closed or you\'re just waking up, it feels like you\'re still in a starry, twinkling dream. May every Cookie who rests here, young or old, sleep peacefully and dream happily.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.002.Story">A milk bottle bed made just for young Cookies. Adorned with the softest cottage cheese pillows and a cute mobile, it provides the perfect opportunity to sleep peacefully and dream happily.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Wall.001.Story">Everyone deserves to find happiness in their dreams, especially the ill. This full moon mood light features two baby Bear Jellies holding shards of starlight wishing for everyone to become strong and healthy. Offering a silent prayer to the full moon fills you with a warm feeling of reassurance.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.003.Story">Long-term treatments and frequent visits to the hospital can make any toddler afraid of shots...! That\'s why this syringe was filled with sparkling starlight and made to look more friendly. Ever since receiving this night light, a certain little Cookie has not been afraid of injections anymore.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Wall.002.Story">Germs, begone! Worry no more! If you\'re looking to create a clean environment, this is the tool for the job! But don\'t overdo it and try to avoid every germ imaginable. Sometimes, if your body can overcome the sniffles, it could probably overcome a lot more later down the line.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.004.Story">A sturdy frame carved from a block of hardened cheese, topped with light and cream cottage cheese cushions. The rainbow decorations are made from all-natural colored cheese blocks, making them not only cute but also super healthy.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Wallpaper.001.Story">A wall representing what dreams might look like to a baby Cookie. It\'s said to depict what a certain patient of the Sanctum of Healing saw while dreaming. It\'s such a cozy and relaxing design, you almost feel yourself drifting into a dream as well.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Deck.001.Story">A floor representing what dreams might look like to a baby Cookie. Made from the freshest and springiest of cottage cheese, it\'s incredibly fun to just walk, jump, and run on it. Almost feels like walking on real clouds!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Rug.001.Story">A cozy rug depicting the night sky. Where should we put this?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.005.Story">A fluffy table that\'s safe for children to use. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.006.Story">It\'s important to take your medicine and sleep when feeling sick!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Ceil.001.Story">A decorative cloud with stars and moons. Let\'s place it here it and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.007.Story">A cozy and squishy couch! It\'s perfect for short naps!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Hanger.001.Story">A simple mood light that looks like clouds. Just looking at it is very relaxing.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Floor.008.Story">A stool made from a pacifier. This will look great wherever you decide to put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Hanger.002.Story">A garland with moons and stars. Let\'s hang it up somewhere nice!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Wall.003.Story">A collection of small posters. Let\'s put them to good use.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2024">Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s Cozy Wozy Room</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2024.Story">Cottage Cheese Cookie has called this room her own ever since she was little. Ever since she was a patient in the Sanctum of Healing, she diligently filled her room with cozy, fluffy things that reflects her bright and cheerful personality. A homely, gentle aroma of fresh milk and cheese lingers in the air, making you want to stay and chat with Cottage Cheese Cookie about anything and everything.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.001">Cottage Cheese Cap</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.002">High-Calcium Milk Pack</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.003">Curdled Duster</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.001.Story">This is the beloved little hat that Cottage Cheese Cookie wears every day and everywhere! She wears it so much that it has two holes on each side. But not to worry! By adding some cottage cheese fluff, it\'s become even more adorable than before.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.002.Story">To keep from floating away, Cottage Cheese Cookie always carries this custom-made milk jug pack. It\'s filled with rich, creamy milk for anyone who gets thirsty. But drink too much, and Cottage Cheese Cookie might just drift off into the sky...! Careful now!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2024.003.Story">Bundle up some fresh cottage cheese on a stick and what do you get? A fluffy duster that can clean anything! This piece of cleaning equipment can sweep and swipe away every last germ in its path. It\'s all thanks to Cottage Cheese Cookie that the Sanctum of Healing is always so squeaky clean!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2024.TeddyBear">Cottage Cheese Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Season.2024.Complete.Profile">Completed Cottage Cheese Collection</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Soulstone">Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Ceil.999">Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2024.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Cottage Cheese Cookie. It\'s so fluffy and light. Er... in fact, it seems a bit too light...?</string>
  <string name="$Season.2024.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the Cottage Cheese Collection. A cheerful smile and a kind heart will always help you brighten up everyone\'s day!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s soul. When you hold it up to your ear, you can hear a small and squeaky sniffle coming from within. Really!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2024.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Cottage Cheese Cookie\'s Cozy Wozy Room!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Profile">Cottage Cheese Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2024.Frame">Cottage Cheese Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_1">Here we go... Hup! Without this milk bottle on my back, I might float up, up, and away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_2">My body\'s been feeling a bit too light recently... *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_3">But I\'m not worried about being sick... It\'s the concerned looks on everyone\'s faces. I\'m really okay! I really am, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_4">Oh! I can make a wish to the moon! Everyone says the moon grants wishes. I can\'t see the moon from inside, so maybe this full moon mood light will do.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_5">Hello moon! I wish to be healthier than ever. That\'s all, really! I just want to be healthy enough to turn off this environment regulator in my room.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_6">Okay... I guess that\'s it. Now, I just open my eyes and...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_7">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_1_POR1_8">AN ANGEL?!?!?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_1">*Sniffle* Are you... are you really a real angel???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_2">Yes... I am.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_3">Are you to here to grant me my wish?! Really? Like, really???</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_4">Then... I, erm... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_5">You...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_6">Wait! I changed my mind! I wish for everyone in the Sanctum of Healing to be cured and healthy!!! REALLY!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_7">You... don\'t want to cure your own illness... of getting lighter and lighter...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_8">Well... It\'s really sad to see everyone worrying about me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_9">But... I like myself just the way I am! And sometimes, it\'s really fun to float around, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_10">Yes... I like flying around places too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_11">It\'s the best, isn\'t it?! Like, when I get really, really light, I can float up all the way up to the ceiling!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_12">You have such a kind heart... I wish to share my blessings with everyone here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_13">Wow! That\'s really great! Wait, I should find Skim Milk Cookie! I need to tell him that an angel has appeared! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_14">She\'s gone... I think it\'s safe for you to reveal yourself now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_2_POR1_15">... Very well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_1">Thank you. Cottage Cheese Cookie has never left the sanctum because of her treatment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_2">I thought... she would enjoy meeting you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_3">Don\'t mention it... Meeting her actually made me feel happy too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_4">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_5">Skim Milk Cookie! Where are you?! There\'s a real angel in the sanctum! Really, really!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_6">It has been a long time since I\'ve seen a Cookie with such a pure and warm heart...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_7">Ah... She is indeed one of the most warmhearted and kindest Cookies here. Her cheerful mood always manages to bring a smile to everyone\'s faces.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_8">I can see that... I wish to share my blessing with you. May the Sanctum of Healing be filled with warmth and laughter...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2024_3_POR1_9">And may Cottage Cheese Cookie never lose the warmth in her heart...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.Main">A Blessing for a Special Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.01">A Wish to the Moon</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.02">Angels are Light Too!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.03">The Truth...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.01.Summary">Cottage Cheese Cookie isn\'t concerned about her sickness of becoming too light. It\'s the worried look of those around her that saddens her. She makes a wish regarding this predicament...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.02.Summary">Angel Cookie suddenly appears before Cottage Cheese Cookie, who becomes ecstatic! Cottage Cheese Cookie changes her wish at the last moment... She wishes for everyone in the Sanctum of Healing to be healed!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Title.03.Summary">It is revealed that this entire meeting with Angel Cookie was set up by none other than Skim Milk Cookie. Even though it was a ruse, Cottage Cheese Cookie seems more excited to share her cheerful bright smile with everyone in the sanctum.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Illust.Dialog.01">I like myself just the
way I am! And it\'s really
fun to float around, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2024.Illust.Dialog.02">Yes... I like flying
around places too...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CGPCRO.MissionPage.Move">Go Now</string>
  <string name="$item.Badge.Dalgona3nd">Cottage Cheese Cookie Badge</string>
  <string name="$item.CRO9th.Eventitem">Dream Orb</string>
  <string name="$item.CRO9th.Eventitem.txt">Dream Orbs, a collection of happy memories from CookieRun: OvenBreak. They are essential for claiming special rewards from the event.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name1">Bear Jellies\' Dreamy Slide</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name2">Frozen Bear Jelly Plushie</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name3">Yellow Bear Jelly Plushie</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name4">Pink Bear Jelly Plushie</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name5">Vacay Jelly Palm Tree</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name6">Caramel Horsie</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name7">Rainbow Window</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name8">World of Dreams Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name9">Dreamlit Floor</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name1.Story">Want to peek into other Cookies\' dreams? Take a ride down this delightful slide! As you glide down, you\'ll catch glimpses of dreams from every Cookie who\'s ever slid before you. Once you\'ve had a taste, you won\'t be able to resist coming back for more!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name2.Story">When a Cookie frolics freely and catches their reflection, their expression is as refreshing as having tasted a soda jelly! This Ice Bear Jelly Plushie welcomes every Cookie with a warm smile, no matter when they visit.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name3.Story">When a Cookie frolics freely and catches their reflection, their expression is as refreshing as having tasted a lemon jelly! The Yellow Bear Jelly Plushie welcomes every Cookie with a warm smile, no matter when they visit.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name4.Story">When a Cookie frolics freely and catches their reflection, their expression is as refreshing as having tasted a strawberry jelly! The Pink Bear Jelly Plushie welcomes every Cookie with a warm smile, no matter when they visit.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name5.Story">A Cookie once dreamed of hanging a hammock between palm trees at a resort, hoping for a long vacation someday. They say when that dream comes true, every leaf will turn into golden honey.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name6.Story">A Caramel Horsie born from a Cookie\'s endless dream of horseback riding. Its glossy caramel coat tells the tale of how preciously that dream was cherished. But beware—ride too long on a scorching day, and this sweet steed might slowly melt away!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name7.Story">A window that allows you to glimpse the ever-changing dreamscape of the Cookies\' dreams. Perhaps the dream unfolding beyond the window right now is the dream of a Cookie who really wants to run with the Bear Jellies.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name8.Story">This wallpaper depicts someone\'s dream of always being in BONUS TIME. Just looking at it makes you feel like you\'ve eaten heaps of Jellies to your heart\'s content.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CRO9th.name9.Story">This floor boasts a vibrant spectrum of colors, like a palette squeezed from every paint in existence. While Cookies can\'t seem to agree on what treats were used to create these mysterious tiles, there\'s no wrong answer—after all, they appear differently in everyone\'s dreams!</string>
  <string name="$Item.Frame.BlackFriday">Black Friday</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_1">... And, we\'re back here again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_2">I think we\'re walking around in circles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_3">Let\'s try heading in that direction this time! I got a good feeling about that way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_4">Absolutely not! You said that last time! And we\'ve already been down that way before.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_5">I... I think it\'s best if we tried going in an entirely different direction...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_6">But I swear we haven\'t gone that way! It definitely has to be the right path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_7">NO, IT IS NOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_8">He\'s right, you know. That way doesn\'t lead to Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_9">Yes! Thank you! Now let\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_10">... WHO ARE YOU?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_11">Hehe, I\'ve never seen Wizard Cookie jump that high before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_12">Sorry, I didn\'t mean to startle you like that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_13">My name is Mistletoe Cookie. This is your first time here, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_14">The forest around here was made to be confusing on purpose. Anyone coming through for the first time is bound to get lost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_15">Wow! It sounds like you know this place really well! Are you from Berrygalia House, Mistletoe Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_16">Well, erm... Not really.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_17">Oh! So you used to live there before then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_18">No, well... That\'s not exactly wrong, but I can\'t say it\'s right either. Depending on how you look at it, it might be true. But then again, it\'s also not true too? Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_19">... Please tell me someone understood what she\'s trying to say.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_20">Not me... I feel even more lost now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_21">Hehe, I didn\'t catch any of that, but everyone\'s faces were really funny just now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_22">Sorry, I didn\'t mean to make that sound so confusing. It\'s just... I really don\'t know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_23">Huh? What do you mean...? What don\'t you know?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_24">I lost my memories. I don\'t know where I\'m from or who my friends are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_25">That is why I am traveling to Berrygalia House. I\'ve heard there are so many memories stored there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_26">Just being in this forest has faintly rekindled a memory, because I think I recognize the way to get there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_27">Realistically, it might be a case of déjà vu that you are experiencing after wandering around in this forest like us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_28">Wizard Cookie... Ssshhh...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_29">No, it\'s okay, I know that it sounds unlikely, but I\'m pretty sure I know the way there. Would you like to go together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_30">That sounds great! We need to get to Berrygalia House to find a Cookie of the First Batch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ1_POR1_31">It\'s always so nice to meet a new friend! Let\'s get going!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_1">Let me see... Yes, I think it\'s this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_2">She\'s right...! I can see Berrygalia House now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_3">It\'s lucky we ran into Mistletoe Cookie! Without her, we\'d still be wandering through the forest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_4">I imagine we would\'ve ended up wandering through it for more than a week...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_5">An entire week in a forest? Sounds fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_6">It absolutely does not!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_7">You\'re such a lively group. You must be really close friends, huhu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_8">Hey, Mistletoe Cookie? You said you lost your memories... Does that mean you\'ve been alone all this time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_9">Hm? Oh, not at all. There were Cookies who helped me get my bearings after losing my memory, and we soon became good friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_10">They are the ones who told me about Berrygalia House and suggested I go there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_11">My friends told me, \"You may not remember them, but there might be Cookies who are worried about you\". They\'re so thoughtful.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_12">It\'s thanks to them, who believed in me even when I didn\'t, that I made it this far.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_13">Those are some amazing friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_14">They really are! And look! We\'re already here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_16">This place looks awesome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_17">It does, but why are there so many sacks and boxes here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_18">There\'s a lot more than \"many.\" It\'s so packed, there\'s barely even room to walk! Honestly, if you told me we\'re in a warehouse, I\'d believe you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_19">I\'m quite sure we\'re in the right place...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_20">HALT! Who goes th- AGH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_21">Ouch! Rolling down the stairs like that must\'ve hurt...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_22">Maybe that\'s how you\'re supposed to say hello here! Like some sort of greeting dance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_23">Erm... I don\'t think so...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_24">Urgh... ow, ow, ow! Seriously, we need to get rid of some of this junk!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_25">Or MAYBE you should actually watch where you step. Silly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_26">There\'s no choice BUT to watch where I step, ALL THE TIME! Could we just, in the very least, clean up this spot here for once? You never listen to me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_27">I am hardly at fault here, you simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_28">I know! I know, I know! Okay?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_29">They\'re... arguing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_30">It seems like a childish argument, but they seem to be good friends? I think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_31">I refuse to admit that I am on friendly terms with this... Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_32">Oh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_33">Wait! You! You\'re...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_34">Mistletoe Cookie! Is it really you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_35">I think these two know who Mistletoe Cookie is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_36">Do you... really know who I am...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ2_POR1_37">Of course we do! You\'re...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_1">You\'re...! You\'re...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_2">Cat got your tongue? Or have you forgotten how to speak entirely? I can\'t tell with you anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_3">But I digress. Mistletoe Cookie, the last time we saw you, you mentioned going for a brief stroll... only to disappear for ages.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_4">We assumed that we would never be able to meet you again, but here you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_5">Where have you been, you-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_6">No, my mistake. Mistletoe Cookie, you are not a simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_7">So... you do know who I am...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_8">What\'re you talkin about? Of course we know you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_9">I\'m sorry. But my memories are not entirely intact...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_10">Yeah! That\'s why we came to Berrygalia House! We heard this place can help find your lost memories.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_11">No, don\'t generalize it like that. We\'re here because we heard there are many memories stored here, and we wanted to ask if you could help.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_12">Your friend has the same ambiance as Bramble Bat Cookie. You must have your hands full with that one...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_13">Thank you for noticing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_14">Who are you two? Maybe your names will help Mistletoe Cookie remember something!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_15">You can call me Smarty. I am a resident of Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_16">Smarty...? Does that mean... you\'re a Cookie of the First Batch?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_17">You sound different than the other First Batchers! You\'re using all sorts of fancy words!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_18">I\'m Bramble Bat Cookie! I\'m the jack-of-all-trades here in Berrygalia House! I go wherever I\'m needed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_19">He is, in fact, the complete opposite.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_20">Oh, c\'mon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_21">Is our conversation stirring anything within your memories? Does anything feel familiar at all?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_22">Hm... I\'m sorry. I don\'t think my memories are returning just yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_23">Lost memories are unlikely to return so easily. And...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_24">Mistletoe Cookie. I would like to hear your story, or at least what you remember up until this point. In addition, I am curious about this group you are traveling with.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_25">Yes... I will try to tell you everything I know...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_26">That is... Everything I remember up until meeting these kind travelers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_27">Come on then. Let\'s find a more suitable place for a meaningful conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_29">So to sum it all up... Mistletoe Cookie managed to return without her memories intact. And you came here at the request of First Cream Cookie to take me to her.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_30">Hm... I refuse. I am not leaving.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_31">Now that you have your answer, you should continue your journey before you catch First Berry Cookie\'s eyes and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_32">Smarty? Bramble Bat Cookie? Have you two managed to find the holiday ornaments?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_33">Uh-oh... Too late now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_34">Who are you sharing a lively conversation with? Do we have new guests? It\'s been ages since we\'ve had-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_35">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ3_POR1_36">... Mistletoe... Cookie? Is that... is that really you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_1">You know me too,
don\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_2">The look on your face...
Were you a close friend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_3">I\'ve lost my memories.
That\'s why I came
here for help.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_4">You... don\'t remember...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_5">If you don\'t remember...
Then... Oh no...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_6">Happiness, sadness...
Everything has been erased?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_7">But... No, it\'s not...
That won\'t do... It\'s not...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_8">Calm down, calm down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_9">Everything\'ll be fine.
Berrygalia House still
has memories of her.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_10">Leave this lot to us! We found
the ornaments, so you can start
decorating right away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_11">... Yes, yes.
Our winter festival...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_12">And I\'m sure we can
help Mistletoe Cookie\'s
memories come back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_13">In the meantime,
would everyone
like to join us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_14">Please, join us for
our quaint but lovely
winter festival.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_15">A festival?!
That sounds like so much fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_16">Yes. It will be
held right here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_17">WOW!
What a pretty tree!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_18">It\'s so... shiny...
And sparkly...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_19">Hm... There\'s barely any
room to set foot here as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_20">These are all precious
pieces of memorabilia
and sentimental regalia.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_21">... Even this raggedy doll?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_22">Ah, that was the very
first gift I received
from a squirrel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_23">What about these
melting candies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_24">Those were Smarty\'s favorite
snacks. I made them into a
decoration. Lovely, aren\'t they?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_25">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_26">We\'re in the company
of guests. Stop scowling,
you weirdo.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_27">It\'s nothing, okay...?!
Sheesh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_28">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_29">They\'ll hear you,
you loudmouth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_30">Today is a wondrous day.
Here, have some berry jam.
Eat up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_31">Wow!
This tastes awesome!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_32">They\'re gonna wish
they never came here,
aren\'t they?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_33">I bet Mistletoe Cookie is
gonna regret coming back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_34">Let them have their moment.
They\'ll find out on their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH1_SQ4_CUT1_35">... Simpletons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_1">This is the best festival ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_2">It is quite enjoyable, isn\'t it? This tree was planted during Berrygalia House\'s very first winter.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_3">It contains all of the memories of th-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_4">GWUH...?! Where\'d this come from?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_5">Heehee! It looks like Bramble Bat Cookie\'s a bit of a clumsy one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_6">Grrr...! I can\'t take it anymore! First Berry Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_8">This has gone on for too long! Just throw all this stuff away! Why is this dirty thing here? It looks scary enough to be nightmare fuel!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_9">No, I need to keep that. It was Smarty\'s very first toy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_10">If I throw that away, I\'ll forget all the happy moments that were created from it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_11">Good times are simply too fleeting... and someday, they\'ll all disappear and fade away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_12">Keeping things filled with memories close by might bring me a little comfort when I need it... Sorry, it\'s a bit selfish of me, isn\'t it? But I\'m sure I will need it someday...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_13">And... I\'m hanging onto everything because... I don\'t want to forget the time we have spent together... I don\'t ever, ever want to forget anything...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_15">You\'re not just hanging onto everything... You\'re hanging onto everyone too, and they have no choice but to stay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_16">HMPH! And here I thought Mistletoe Cookie coming back would knock some sense into you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_17">But... these are all... precious memories... with everyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_18">That\'s IT! I don\'t know what to think anymore! Do you really think of us as your friends...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_19">Because you\'re treating us exactly like all this messy and useless junk!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_20">Bramble Bat Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_21">I\'ve had it with this place! I don\'t care anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_22">He\'s... he\'s gone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_23">It... it sounded like a pretty bad argument... Are you okay, First Berry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_24">Huhu... I\'ll be okay. He can be a bit hot-headed sometimes is all. He\'s just worried about me, I\'m sure of it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_25">Why would he be worried?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_26">Everyone who calls Berrygalia House their home are sweet and caring. Even with all the memories being stored here, they never complain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_27">He\'s not upset because of the mess. He\'s upset because he\'s concerned for me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_28">Erm... is it okay to ask... why do you keep all of this stuff here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_29">I have to remember them. I have to remember everything... Because they are all precious moments that could vanish... forever...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_30">A single flower picked in autumn. A neatly folded, handwritten note. Treasured feelings are attached to each and every single memory within these walls. I can\'t bear to throw them away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_31">I apologize for the abrupt nature of this question, but... We came here for Smarty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_32">Yeah! First Cream Cookie is waiting for us to return with Smarty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_33">Would it be okay for Smarty to come with us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_34">Ohoho...? Very well. We all have to go our separate ways at some point... It\'s a shame, but I guess it\'s bound to happen...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_35">Oh, but I just remembered. The next batch of berry jam will be ready next week! It will have aged perfectly. Perhaps we can wait until then?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_36">You simply must have a taste of it before you go. I insist...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_37">I guess... being apart from Smarty would be really sad... You\'ll probably need some time to say goodbye...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ1_POR1_38">Sure! We can wait for a bit more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_1">Sure! We can wait for a bit more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_2">... I feel like... You\'ve said that so many times already.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_3">The first time was about trying some berry jam. Then it was about writing letters for us made from dried berry leaves...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_4">Then she wanted to make a storybook for Smarty with all the letters and pictures she received so far...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_5">Then we couldn\'t leave unless we had a grand feast as a goodbye party.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_6">And then she said she ran out of the most important ingredient for the tastiest berry pie we\'d ever eat... and asked us to wait one more time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_7">Heehee, we\'ve been here for quite a while, haven\'t we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_8">This is no laughing matter! At this point, it feels like she\'s actively trying to stop us from leaving.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_9">Finally catching on, are we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_10">I told you from the beginning. You should have left before you caught First Berry Cookie\'s eyes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_11">... Simpletons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_12">Wait, are you saying that First Berry Cookie really is keeping us from leaving? On purpose?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_13">But the door\'s open! We can just try sneaking out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_14">But we\'re not the only ones who need to leave... And we should listen to what Smarty has to say too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_15">I have already made my decision quite clear. I am not leaving.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_16">If I were to disappear with you, First Berry Cookie would be devastated. And I do not approve of such a decision.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_17">Yeah... I think she\'d be really sad...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_18">Bramble Bat Cookie, myself, and everyone who resides here... We all think the same.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_19">Everyone knows how gentle and kind First Berry Cookie is. But she\'s just as fragile... That\'s why, even when an altercation occurs, no one can find the heart to just leave her behind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_20">If we depart, First Berry Cookie\'s heart would be shattered to pieces. In the end, her desire to cling onto every piece of memorabilia, paraphernalia, and regalia would grow exponentially stronger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_21">... And I refuse to see that happen.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_22">It sounds like you really care for First Berry Cookie, Smarty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_23">... There\'s no reason to dislike her!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_24">First Berry Cookie is extremely kind. Everyone knows it and loves her for who she is, not just me. Simpletons...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_25">Hm... We could find out why First Berry Cookie has such a hard time with throwing things away! Maybe if we knew why, we could figure out a way to help her?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_26">That\'s-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_27">This way, Mistletoe Cookie. I am certain your memories will return once you lay your eyes upon it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_28">You seem rather excited. You\'re almost running, huhu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_29">Hey, over there! It\'s First Berry Cookie and Mistletoe Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_30">I wonder where they\'re going!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_31">... That way leads to...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_32">This conversation is over. I need to follow First Berry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_33">We\'ll go too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ2_POR1_34">Hehe! Off we go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_1">We are here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_2">This is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_3">Do you recognize it? The tree has grown much bigger while you were gone. It used to be much smaller, remember?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_4">And look over here. This is where I keep all the memories I made with you, Mistletoe Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_6">But first, drink this. It will help restore your memories, huhu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_7">Huhu, thank you for taking the time to help me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_9">Is it just me, or is it hard to tell who\'s talking from here? They sound so similar.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_10">She changed how she talks ever since Mistletoe Cookie disappeared. She refused to forget what Mistletoe Cookie sounded like.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_11">... There was no need to go to such lengths just to remember her though...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_12">Mistletoe Cookie finished drinking that potion...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_13">Well...? How do you feel, Mistletoe Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_14">Hm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_15">Do you... remember anything...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_16">... I don\'t... know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_17">You don\'t... know?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_18">I... see something like memories. But it feels like I\'m reading a book.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_19">I see myself talking and laughing with everyone here, and yet... it doesn\'t feel like me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_20">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_21">I know you were so eager to help, but... I\'m sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_22">No, this can\'t be happening. This wasn\'t supposed to happen...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_23">I knew it... Disappointment once more. It\'s going to be a disaster if she continues to spiral into grief like that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_24">You can\'t remember...? This wasn\'t supposed to happen... You forgot... everything...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_25">It\'s okay. It will be okay. I appreciate your concern, but-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_26">No, this is not supposed to happen... It\'s not okay at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_27">I have no choice. I need to intervene.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_28">How can you say it will be okay? Your memories... your feelings... They\'re all gone. Gone... forever...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_29">First Berry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_30">Listen to me. I\'ll be fine. Truly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_31">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ3_POR1_32">Huh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_1">I appreciate your concern,
really. And I\'ve learned how
much you care about me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_2">But you are making it sound
like my memory loss means
there\'s something deeply
flawed with me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_3">Yes, losing my memories is sad,
and I do often feel hollow inside.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_4">But you\'ve shown me that
I have friends who cherish
me for who I am, back then
and even now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_5">I have made many new warm
and fond memories ever since
I have arrived here. So please...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_6">I do not want you
to worry too much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_7">But... you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_8">I will be okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_9">Mistletoe Cookie\'s tougher
than she looks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_10">I don\'t know about that in her
current state, but... Yes, she was
quite the strict, no-nonsense Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_11">Maybe she just lost
her memories, not who
she really is inside...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_12">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_13">Hm... I\'ve been wondering.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_14">First Berry Cookie, are you
afraid of forgetting things?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_15">Saying goodbye, keeping
everything around, even
Mistletoe Cookie\'s memories!
You seem scared to lose anything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_16">It\'s like... you\'re afraid of
letting things go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_17">That\'s... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_18">*Sigh*
It all started a long,
long time ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_1">Longer than you\'ve been at Berrygalia House?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_2">Huhu... much, much longer than that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_3">It feels like an eternity ago... It was a time when everyone cared for me, loved me, almost worshiped me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_4">Then, everything changed when the soldiers attacked. They came to capture me for being a witch. We had no choice but to drop everything and flee...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_5">The soldiers did not leave, and we were sealed in the dark, trapped in the one place we thought to be safe.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_6">Before... We tossed out bread because it merely cooled down. Bottles of medicine were wasted just because the lid wouldn\'t close. I never realized how desperately we\'d need the very things we squandered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_7">I hated myself for having to watch everyone, one by one, accept their fate in the cold dark. I desperately wanted to help them, but I was powerless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_8">Some cried out in anguish. Some whispered with their last breath. But they all had the same wish: \"We don\'t want to be forgotten like this...\" I heard it all, but could not do anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_9">From then on, I promised to remember everything. The good times, the bad times, the happiness and sorrow... Every memory made and shared.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_10">Oh... That\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_11">That\'s so sad...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_12">That\'s when I made this, the Memory Tree, to collect all of my memories so that I can look at them every day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_13">Since it has grown quite large, it is becoming rather difficult to look at everything every day, huhu...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_14">That sounds pretty hard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_15">On the contrary, I still enjoy it very much. It\'s fun to see the memories we\'ve made together, and to look back at the items that hold them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_16">But if you\'re looking at this tree every day, you won\'t have the time to enjoy all sorts of tasty Jellies and make new friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_17">... Yes, but this takes precedence over everything else. These are all precious memories, and I am their keeper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_18">It is taking almost all of my power to maintain the Memory Tree.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_19">Oh. I\'m not an expert on stuff like this, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_20">I\'ve made a lot of new friends here! And yeah, it\'s nice to remember the past and talk about stuff that happened...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_21">But the happiest moments are always when I get to see my friends with me right now, smiling and laughing with me there and then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_22">I suppose it\'s hard for you to understand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_23">I know the present is just as important, but sometimes, there are some things that you just can\'t let go.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_24">By the way... Has anyone seen Bramble Bat Cookie? I haven\'t seen him all day.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_25">We haven\'t seen him since your, erm, argument... Maybe he just wants to be alone?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_26">Oh dear...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_27">He seems like a tough Cookie who can take care of himself. I\'m sure he\'s just cooling off somewhere. It\'ll be fine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_28">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ1_POR1_29">Where have you run off to, Bramble Bat Cookie? You blockhead...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_1">No matter how much we\'d argue, we\'d usually be talking again by now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_2">He always writes me a note saying he\'s sorry for getting angry... Look here, I have every single one of them stored right here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_3">... You could write an entire book or two with all those notes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_4">How odd... He has such a big heart. It\'s not like him to stay unseen for this long.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_5">Did... something happen to him...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_6">We should start looking for him!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_7">He might be writing a note right now? Huhu, something longer than usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_8">It\'s plausible, but if you\'re so concerned, we can start searching for his whereabouts right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_9">... Yes, let us go find him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_11">FINALLY! I thought they\'d never leave. Hiding like that really put a strain on my wings...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_12">Now then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_14">It\'s time to use this magic flame...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_15">The Cookie who gave it to me was a bit shady though...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_18">ARGH! First Berry Cookie is so stupid! I\'m trying to look out for her and she JUST. WON\'T. LISTEN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_19">I don\'t care anymore! I\'m gone. I\'m outta here! I\'m gonna take a page from Mistletoe Cookie\'s book and leave! And there\'ll be no regrets!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_20">Aw, poor thing... Tch, tch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_21">Eh? Who\'s there?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_22">What a shame... Such a big, selfless heart, so devoted to a friend. And yet that friend does not even care to notice your genuine concern... Tch, tch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_23">Who... Who are you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_24">Let\'s just say I know a few things about First Berry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_25">Are you a friend of hers or something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_26">Let\'s say I am. And as a fellow friend of First Berry Cookie, I know exactly how you feel and what you\'re going through.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_27">I know how frustrated and worried you are. The same thing happened to me, and we shared quite a fair share of barbed words about it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_28">So much so that I am no longer welcome to meet with her anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_29">Which brings me to my question... How would you like to help First Berry Cookie? All you have to do is use this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_30">... What is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_31">It\'s merely a simple spell, a tiny magical flame. Just enough to burn a single Memory Berry from that cherished tree of hers...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_32">And don\'t worry, it\'s perfectly safe. It\'s not dangerous at all. With this, we can show First Berry Cookie an important truth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_33">So one little thing has been lost, but it\'s not the end of the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_34">Maybe then, instead of clinging to old trinkets, First Berry Cookie will start spending her time in a more meaningful manner... Actually caring for her friends, for instance. Wouldn\'t that be nice?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_35">Do you really think so...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_36">Trust me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_39">A friend of First Berry Cookie, eh...? For some reason, I don\'t think that Cookie was lying.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_40">Okay! I\'m gonna take that Cookie\'s advice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_41">Just wait, First Berry Cookie. You\'ll finally understand that you don\'t need any of this stuff!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_42">And then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ2_POR1_43">We\'ll finally be able to have all sorts of fun, just like we always used to!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_1">Hm... I couldn\'t find any trace of Bramble Bat Cookie at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_2">No luck here either. Where did he go...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_3">I have also combed through every logical location... Where did you go, Bramble Bat Cookie? You sugarbrain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_4">Oh dear... I am starting to get very concerned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_5">I know it\'s a bit premature to jump to conclusions, but he may have left the grounds of Berrygalia House entirely.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_6">Improbable. Bramble Bat Cookie would never.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_7">He may stir trouble and be a blockhead, but he\'s a blockhead who cares for his friends too much to just leave like that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_8">He\'s not the type to disappear without a word.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_9">I agree. I don\'t remember things about him too clearly, but somehow... I know he made me smile on more than one occasion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_10">I know he\'s a kindhearted Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_11">I think we should look around one more time. Smarty, can you think of any other places where he might want to be alone?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_12">Lost memories or not, you\'re still the same Cookie, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_13">Very well. Let\'s search one more time. Bramble Bat Cookie\'s a simpleton of the highest degree, so finding him shouldn\'t be too difficult.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_14">And it smells like it\'s almost time for dinner too! If he\'s hungry, he might show up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_15">Pardon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_16">Dinner! Can\'t you smell that? It smells something like First Berry Cookie\'s jam is being made right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_17">... Wait, that\'s not it. Something smells like it\'s burning?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_18">He\'s right! Look over there! There\'s smoke coming that way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_19">That\'s... where the Memory Tree is.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ3_POR1_20">Let\'s go check it out! Something must\'ve happened!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_1">There\'s so much- *Cough!*
Where did all this
smoke come from?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_2">This is bad!
It\'s a huge inferno!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_3">Hey, someone\'s over there...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_4">Bramble Bat Cookie...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_5">Bramble Bat Cookie!
There you are!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_6">Get away from there!
It\'s too dangerous!
What are you doing?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_7">Mistletoe Cookie... Smarty...
First Berry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_8">I had no idea things would
turn out this way...! I just...
I thought I was helping...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_9">What is it...?
What are you trying to tell us...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_10">I-I-I just...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_11">Gah?!
The fire\'s spreading!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_12">Urgh! It\'s getting
too hot in here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_13">W-W-We need to get out of here!
It\'s too dangerous...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_1">The fire has spread all this way...? Already?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_2">Everything\'s burning...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_3">Did you see the tree though? Everything but the Memory Tree was burning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_4">That\'s because the Memory Tree is being protected by First Berry Cookie\'s magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_5">But let\'s return to the urgent matter at hand. Explain yourself, Bramble Bat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_6">I met a Cookie in the forest who said she was a friend of First Berry Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_7">She said if I started a small fire, just a small one, that everything would solve itself. That everything would be okay...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_8">But the fire just kept growing. I tried to put it out but it just grew out of control...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_9">I didn\'t mean for things to happen this way. I swear!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_10">I really thought this would make things could go back to the way they were. Me, First Berry Cookie, and the others... just like old times.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_12">I\'m sorry I put everyone in danger... I\'m really, really sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_13">A friend of mine...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_14">Yeah. She was dressed in white and yellow...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_15">First Egg Cookie...
So... You\'ve finally made your move.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_16">I can\'t do this on my own...! Help, First Berry Cookie! Your powers can put out the fires in the blink of an eye...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_17">We\'ll help too! We can extinguish that fire together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_18">Wait! That\'s not an ordinary fire. It\'s going to be extremely difficult to extinguish it without some powerful magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_19">You never know until you try! And besides, First Berry Cookie is with us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_20">He\'s right. If we work together, we can put out the fire and save what\'s left. Right, First Berry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_21">... I can\'t.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_22">...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_23">I can\'t... I can\'t do it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ1_POR1_24">W-What do you mean...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_1">Most of my strength is being used to keep the Memory Tree safe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_2">There are memories on that tree... ones that should never be forgotten...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_3">To extinguish this fire, I would have to cut off the spell that sustains the Memory Tree. And if I do that, the entire tree could succumb to the inferno...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_4">I can\'t do it... How can I? How can I ever let them go?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_5">If the fire can\'t get contained... then everyone in Berrygalia House will be in danger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_6">... The past can never come back. It\'s up to me alone to remember the friends who have been lost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_7">Unless you take action, then Berrygalia House and everyone living here will ALSO become a thing of the past.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_8">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_9">First Berry Cookie, what\'s the most important thing in your life?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_10">I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_11">Every Cookie cherishes something different. All those things you keep here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_12">Yeah, they\'re old, but they\'re all super clean and well-cared for! That means they matter so much to you. A lot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_13">But here\'s what we need to know. First Berry Cookie, are memories the most important thing to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_14">More important than the friends standing in front of you right now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_15">I... But I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_16">We can\'t waste any more time! We need to put out that fire before it\'s too late!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_17">I\'ll try to cast a spell to keep it from spreading any further!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_18">... I\'m sorry, First Berry Cookie. I didn\'t mean to break your heart like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_19">I\'m... I\'m gonna do everything I can to put out that fire! You can just wait here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_20">No... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_21">Well... It looks like everyone has gone to put out the fire. I am going to help them too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_22">Are you going to stay here, First Berry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_23">... I don\'t... I\'m...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_24">I can\'t choose...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_25">They didn\'t want to be forgotten, and I didn\'t want to forget... But if I were to lose those memories and trinkets, it\'s almost like the friends tied to them will vanish too... forever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_26">What will happen when time keeps passing, when everyone is gone? What if one day... there\'s no one left by my side?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_27">How could I live with myself if I don\'t have anything to remember you by...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_28">How could I even think of casting aside something so precious...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_29">... First Berry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ2_POR1_30">Listen to me carefully.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_1">Right now, I am going to go help our friends put out that fire.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_2">The fire is spreading and growing so intense, I may end up being scorched and burn down into a pile of ashes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_3">But I\'m okay with that. I\'m willing to face the danger. Even if I don\'t remember anything, my heart tells me it\'s the right thing to do for my friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_4">... Mistletoe Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_5">My lost memories will return someday... But if they don\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_6">... I can just make new ones.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_7">The future does not come back either, you know. It\'s something we build ourselves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_8">If the friends who can build that future with us are lost today... then the past would no longer be a beautiful memory. It would be a heartbreaking reminder of regret.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_9">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_11">And still...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_12">Even if I were to end up a charred and scorched Cookie today, I don\'t think I would blame you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_13">But I would not want you to spend your days in pain, thinking of me all the time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_14">If you could remember me and think, \"Those were good times. She was a good friend\". Every now and then, just once in a while... That would be enough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_15">You do not have to remember everything and every day. No Cookie who truly cherishes their friends would ever wish for such things.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_16">Time keeps moving on, even when you decide to stay in the past. But the longer you stand still, the more those moments turn into sorrow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_17">I do not want that for you. And neither does anyone who ever cared about you, really.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_18">Whatever choice you make, it will be okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_19">Just promise me one thing... Think about what truly matters to you, what belongs in your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_20">I... I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_21">Huhu, I did not expect an answer right away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_23">I am going to help our friends now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_24">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ3_POR1_25">What matters... to me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_1">IT\'S TOO HOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_2">Is this what burnt toast feels like? Heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_3">This isn\'t the time for such speculation! Especially with a smile on your face!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_4">What are you doing over there, Bramble Bat Cookie?! Get out of there, you fool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_5">Just one more... I need to save at least one more of... First Berry Cookie\'s memories...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_6">RUN, YOU FOOL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_7">!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_8">Bramble Bat Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_9">...? A fireball fell on top of me but I\'m alive? And I\'m not burning?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_10">Are you okay, Bramble Bat Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_11">First Berry Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_12">Huhu... I\'m sorry I\'m late. And I\'m sorry I\'ve caused you so much trouble.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_13">Everything will be okay now, because now I know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_14">I realize that I cherish the friends who are by my side, here and now, not just the memories of them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_15">And my friends from ages past would not want me to go on this way... trapped in the past, a prison of my own making.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_16">I finally understand what everyone has been trying to tell me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_17">Even if I\'m not holding onto something, the feelings I\'ve had about those memories will remain in my heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_18">If you use your powers... you\'ll break your connection with the Memory Tree. It\'ll burn down to nothing. And you\'re okay with that? Really...? You said those things were precious to you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_19">I will be okay, Bramble Bat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_20">Because you\'ll still be by my side, right? And besides...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_21">I\'ve spent too long trapped in yesterday!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_23">The... the fire\'s out. In just a flash...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_24">Nothing remains of the Memory Tree...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_25">Still... In the end, it\'s fortuitous that everyone is safe and unharmed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_26">Haha! I\'ve never seen Smarty laugh like that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_27">Aw, what a cute laugh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_28">Okay, the moment\'s over. You simpletons...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_29">Thanks, everyone... This is... all my fault.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_30">No, it is not.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_31">You encountered none other than First Egg Cookie. She is exceptionally clever, but she only uses her cleverness to deceive and betray others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_32">Had I broken free from my obsession with the past, I would have warned you of her much sooner.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_33">I am sorry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_34">And... Gingerbrave. You have come to take Smarty to First Cream Cookie, yes? Then you must do so with haste. Smarty will be safer in her presence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_35">Absolute nonsense.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_36">\?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_37">If I am the subject in question, then I am entitled to voice my opinion! Silly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_38">I refuse to leave. And that\'s my final decision!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ4_POR1_39">... But I must...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_1">You must be protected
from First Egg Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_2">When Mistletoe Cookie disappeared,
I realized First Egg Cookie could
target those precious to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_3">So... I intentionally kept
everyone from leaving.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_4">But... the events that
have unfolded have
taught me a lesson.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_5">It was I myself who put everyone
in danger. The past blinded me so
much I could not see what was
happening right before my eyes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_6">Nope!
Not the way I see it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_7">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_8">You were just trying to the
best you could the only way
you knew how! And I...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_9">I may have left, but I
know now. I really want
to be here with everyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_10">I cannot believe this, but I agree
with him. Besides... Look at the
state of Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_11">You will need my assistance
to get things cleaned up,
rebuilt, and organized.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_12">He has a point, huhu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_13">Of course, I will be staying as well.
I still feel there are some memories
left to be recovered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_14">My friends...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_15">It\'s a real happy ending,
isn\'t it? Haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_16">We\'ll tell First Cream Cookie what
happened here, and that her meeting
with Smarty will take some time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_17">Thank you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_18">Hehe, what a happy memory
to make before leaving
Berrygalia House!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_19">A memory...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_20">Yeah! Today\'s a new beginning
for a new day filled with memories!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_21">That is a fun way to
look at things, huhu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_22">Then, for me as well, today is
the first day of creating new
memories with everyone.
Happy ones that I will not forget.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_23">Thank you again,
GingerBrave.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_24">Were it not for you and
Mistletoe Cookie, I would still
be lost in my own ignorance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_25">In return,
I promise you one thing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_26">If and when you require aid,
I shall answer the call.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_27">Awesome! That\'s great!
Thanks so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_28">Take care on your travels, you lot!
And if you get to come back,
we\'ll have some real fun next time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_29">And perhaps, next time,
Bramble Bat Cookie will
no longer be a foolish simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_30">Heehee! You really do
talk funny, Smarty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_31">I made no attempt
to be funny just now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_32">It has been too long
since laughter has echoed
throughout these grounds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_33">I hope such laughter and
smiles can continue far
into our futures.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_34">Now then, everyone...
Shall we begin rebuilding
Berrygalia House just the
way it should be?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_CH4_SQ5_CUT1_35">A house where everyone
can laugh and be merry as
they create new memories.</string>
