  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_1">Greetings, Rosemary Cookie. Your journey here must have been quite difficult.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_2">It is a pleasure to meet you, First Berry Cookie. You said there was a tree that needed tending to. Where is... Ah, I assume this is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_3">It has grown nicely, but there are definitely branches that are overgrown. Some will need to be pruned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_4">... Oh... I see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_5">I shall begin right away. First, I will start with this area over here-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_6">WAIT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_7">Hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_8">Where are my manners! You must be exhausted from your journey. How about a snack of berries and tea first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_1_POR1_9">Very well. I have heard the berries harvested at Berrygalia House are exceptionally sweet and fragrant.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_1">Thank you for such a fulfilling snack. Now, I shall begin pruning the tree and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_2">... WAIT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_3">Yes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_4">I have recently completed a batch of berry jam. Would you like to have a quick taste before you start?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_5">Thank you, but I must decline. I am quite full from the snack you just provided.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_6">Oh... Then how about we take a quick, relaxing stroll? It would give me a chance to show you some of Berrygalia House\'s Memory Berries.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_7">Ah, no thank you. Seeing these colorful and shining Memory Berries from afar will suffice. And the break I just took has helped me replenish my dough quite well already.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_8">Then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_9">If I may, First Berry Cookie? It seems... you do not wish to see this tree\'s overgrown branches be pruned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_10">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_11">Am I right? I am only curious.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_12">... Yes, you are correct. Even though I am trying, I still find it very difficult to discard my possessions. I do not wish to lose anything...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_13">Saying goodbye is too difficult.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_14">I see... I understand how you feel, First Berry Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_15">But there is a time and place for everything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_2_POR1_16">A time and place?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_1">Yes. Failing to prune in time can actually become harmful to the tree, so much that the tree will fail to absorb the nutrients it needs. In the end, the tree may wither and fall.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_2">Letting go is an art form. You need to know how to let go, what to let go, when to let it go. Not too much, but not too little.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_3">We cannot always get what we want, nor can we always do things the way we want. Having something or someone close by can be happy, and it can be sad too. But we endure it all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_4">And we endure it because, in the end, things tend to work out for the better.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_5">It\'s the same with trees. You can nourish them daily, but they\'ll only rot at the roots and their leaves will wither if they are not properly pruned.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_6">... Thank you, Rosemary Cookie. You have taught me an important lesson.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_7">Now then... I shall begin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_8">... Okay.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_9">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_10">There we are. The pruning is complete and the tree looks much healthier already. I shall dispose of these branches on my way back home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_11">No, do not throw those away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_12">Pardon...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_13">I think... having these pruned branches nearby will remind me of your wisdom. Every day for years to come. I will not be so sad if I keep them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_14">Perhaps I should write down today\'s date on them as well. I should show my friends the lesson I\'ve learned today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2025_3_POR1_15">... Wait, that\'s not... First Berry Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.Main">Sometimes, Just Let it Go</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.01">A Tree Needs Pruning</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.02">Does It Really Need Pruning?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.03">The Importance of Pruning</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.01.Summary">Rosemary Cookie has been invited to Berrygalia House by First Berry Cookie, who has asked the expert gardener to prune a small berry tree, but...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.02.Summary">First Berry Cookie is having a hard time realizing that pruning and discarding branches is a necessity. Rosemary Cookie carefully speaks up...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Title.03.Summary">Rosemary Cookie\'s words of wisdom have granted First Berry Cookie a valuable lesson. If you truly care about someone, it\'s not always about what you want for them... Sometimes, it\'s about they need from you.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Illust.Dialog.01">Having these pruned
branches nearby will
remind me of your wisdom.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2025.Illust.Dialog.02">... Wait, that\'s not...
First Berry Cookie!</string>
