  <string name="$SAGA.05.CinematicOpeningTitle">Berrygalia House</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening01">Everything is fading... and slipping away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening02">There was a time I was accepted as a god,
a time where nothing lacked...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening03">When food was discarded half-eaten...
Things were tossed out on a whim
and medicine was never scarce...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening04">Until that fateful day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening05">Violence. Fire.
The thundering of hooves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening06">Soldiers swarmed in to take me away...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening07">Would it have been wiser
to submit myself to fate...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening08">The way out was sealed
by those who brought death...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening09">I yearned for everything we took for granted....
The squandered water, the neglected medicine...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening10">They cried out as they drew their last breath...
They did not want to be forgotten...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening11">My child.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening12">Come. Take my hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening13">I will not lose anything. I will not forget.
Never again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA05_Opening14">At least not here, in Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Saga.05.Ch01">A Cookie with No Memories</string>
