  <string name="$Saga05_Ch1_sq1.Summary">In their search for First Berry Cookie, GingerBrave and his friends have been wandering through a maze of a forest for quite some time. As they are about to admit they are lost, a strange Cookie approaches them...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch1_sq2.Summary">The stranger who approached them, Mistletoe Cookie, has lost her memories. Our friends and Mistletoe Cookie travel together and arrive at Berrygalia House, where a pair of Cookies seem to recognize her...!</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch1_sq3.Summary">Bramble Bat Cookie and Smarty both claim to know who Mistletoe Cookie is. Just what happened to her in the past? Everyone listens to Mistletoe Cookie\'s story in earnest.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch1_sq4.Summary">Bramble Bat Cookie is not quite happy about First Berry Cookie meeting the newcomers. Unaware of what\'s to come, the group decides to join and enjoy Berrygalia House\'s winter festival.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch2_sq1.Summary">First Berry Cookie grants permission to GingerBrave and friends to take Smarty to First Cream Cookie. But first, she asks for some time to prepare for a proper goodbye. The Cookies decide to delay their departure until First Berry Cookie is ready.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch2_sq2.Summary">So much time has passed, yet the promised farewell hasn\'t come! Or... was this First Berry Cookie\'s plan all along? Their surprise doesn\'t last long, as they witness First Berry Cookie and Mistletoe Cookie heading off somewhere together...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch2_sq3.Summary">First Berry Cookie attempts to restore Mistletoe Cookie\'s memories. But even with a potion made from a berry from the Memory Tree, her memories fail to fully return. First Berry Cookie, more anxious than ever, is brought back to her senses by...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch2_sq4.Summary">It seems First Berry Cookie is afraid of forgetting and losing something, anything. Not just afraid, but almost terrified at the notion. The group listens to her story...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch3_sq1.Summary">First Berry Cookie opens up about what happened to her long ago. She explains that she stores every memory as berries of the Memory Tree, because she never wants to lose or forget anything ever again.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch3_sq2.Summary">The Cookies realize that Bramble Bat Cookie hasn\'t been seen for quite some time. It turns out he was hiding nearby and watching them... When the coast is clear, he throws a strange spark at the Memory Tree, in hopes of freeing First Berry Cookie from the burden of clinging onto past memories.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch3_sq3.Summary">After searching for Bramble Bat Cookie, GingerBrave and his friends are unable to find any trace of Bramble Bat Cookie. But then, they notice the smell of smoke and something burning...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch3_sq4.Summary">Fire! FIRE!!! Our friends find Bramble Bat Cookie panicking near the blazing inferno. What is going on?!</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch4_sq1.Summary">Bramble Bat Cookie confesses everything, about how he genuinely wished to help First Berry Cookie, and using a magical fire given to him by a mysterious stranger. But he never imagined his good intentions would lead to such chaos. In the end, he turns to First Berry Cookie for help...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch4_sq2.Summary">With her powers, First Berry Cookie could extinguish the magical fire. But doing so would mean giving up the Memory Tree and all the Memory Berries growing with it. She hesitates... insisting she cannot bring herself to let go of everything she holds dear.</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch4_sq3.Summary">Our heroes head off to put out the fire! Mistletoe Cookie, left behind with First Berry Cookie, has something to say...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch4_sq4.Summary">At last, First Berry Cookie gathers her strength and extinguishes the magical fire. The Memory Tree is completely burned away... but in the end, she has protected those who are most precious to her...</string>
  <string name="$Saga05_Ch4_sq5.Summary">Although the fire has been extinguished, Berrygalia House now lies in ruins. Everyone who calls Berrygalia House their home decides to pitch in with the rebuilding effort. As for our friends and heroes, they set off on their next journey.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026">Mistletoe Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027">Bramble Bat Cookie</string>
