  <string name="$Cookie.2025">First Berry Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2025.Story">In the heart of a labyrinthine forest, bathed in warm sunlight by day and gentle moonlight by night, a Cookie awakened beneath a towering berry tree, its branches heavy with thousands of fruits. 

Many Cookies were drawn to her kindhearted nature and gentle smile, like sheep to a shepherd. They came to know her as First Berry Cookie, and her presence was so comforting that not a single Cookie ever left her side. Or perhaps... none could. 

Whether First Berry Cookie is aware of the whispers and rumors that surround her, no one can say. But even now, nestled among her treasured keepsakes, memorabilia, and regalia, she quietly stirs a pot of fresh berry jam. For the Cookies, for her friends. To keep everyone close, always.</string>
