  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.001.Story">A carefully pruned branch of the lovingly nurtured Memory Tree was used to create this magnificent snow globe. The tree encased within the globe also bears memory berries, filled to the brim with the cherished memories of many Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.002.Story">A miniature portion of the Memory Tree was delicately sealed within this snow globe. Its tiny shape is undeniably adorable and mesmerizing, but take care not to let it grow too big. If left unchecked, the orb might crack under the weight.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Ceil.001.Story">Even an old giant ribbon can find a second breath of life as a shelf in First Berry Cookie\'s room. But with all those berries stacked to the brink of tumbling down, you might want to watch your head when passing under it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Wall.001.Story">A frame that captures the silhouette of the Memory Tree. When it lights up, a soft glow flickers throughout the area. Its warm, berry hue has a way of bringing long buried memories back to life.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.003.Story">A collection of jars filled with various memories sparkling with a warm glow. Big or small, recent or ancient, every Cookie\'s memory shines in their own special way. Joyful and sorrowful memories alike are what makes you who you are today, so take care of those memories!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.004.Story">They say you need to use golden syrup to grow the plumpest, sweetest berries. But for some reason, First Berry Cookie\'s watering can is filled with... more berries? I guess she couldn\'t bring herself to throw away the previous harvest and just kept them here.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Wallpaper.001.Story">After searching far and wide for yet another place to store her jars of Memory Berries, First Berry Cookie has settled on a decent location: the walls of her room. The lush brambles covering the walls has become a sparkling display of countless memories.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Deck.001.Story">One day, First Berry Cookie discovered a batch of fertile soil—perfect for growing a Memory Tree. It\'s become common knowledge that no memory is cast aside within Berrygalia House\'s walls. In First Berry Cookie\'s room, such memories can grow and take root with no concerns.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Wall.002.Story">A cabinet filled with jars of Memory Berries. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Hanger.001.Story">A collection of sun-dried berries. It adds a homely vibe to wherever you put it.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.005.Story">A bramble shaped into a shrub. The berries are ripe!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Ceil.002.Story">A collection of berries used to make a festive ornament. Let\'s put this to good use.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Ceil.003.Story">A branch of the Memory Tree. It\'s holding several jars of memories.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Hanger.002.Story">A decorative berry flower. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Rug.001.Story">A rug made from brambles. Any room would look cozier with it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Floor.006.Story">A basket filled with plump, sweet berries. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Hanger.003.Story">A wreath perfect for the holidays. Where should we put it?</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2025">First Berry Cookie\'s Room of Cherished Memories</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2025.Story">First Berry Cookie\'s room is filled with luscious Memory Berries scattered here and there. The aroma of fresh berries and wistful nostalgia swim through the air as if enveloping the room in a warm, scented quilt. They say this room is open to everyone who wishes to reflect on the past and dream of the future. Here, where the winter holidays seem to last throughout the year, may everyone find the space to reminisce about the past and prepare for the future. Surely... that\'s what First Berry Cookie wishes too, right?</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.001">Wooden Teaspoon Staff</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.002">Berrycap Mushroom Hat</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.003">Vial of Fondest Memories</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.001.Story">A staff that has stayed by First Berry Cookie\'s side for countless ages. Many have forgotten its true nature as it is often used by her to just stir berry jam... But this is no ordinary staff! It\'s an unbelievably, tremendously powerful magic wand!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.002.Story">This hat was created from a mushroom found growing on the Memory Tree. After gently removing it from the tree\'s bark, First Berry Cookie crafted it into a hat. Her friends added a few ornaments to give it a charming touch!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2025.003.Story">A vial that is said to hold one of First Berry Cookie\'s most precious memories. Afraid it might break, she secretly hides it away, keeping it safe and sound at all times. On the rare days she takes it out, First Berry Cookie stares down at it with a wistful gaze. A warm, gentle smile comes forth the longer she looks... What kind of memory could be inside?</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2025.TeddyBear">First Berry Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Season.2025.Complete.Profile">Completed First Berry Collection</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2025.Soulstone">First Berry Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Ceil.999">First Berry Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2025.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Berry Cookie. It looks so beautiful and grand... This should be kept safe forever. And ever. And never thrown away.</string>
  <string name="$Season.2025.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the First Berry Collection. Sure, it\'s hard to let go of things, but sometimes, the past must remain in the past.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2025.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Berry Cookie\'s soul. It gives off a familiar yet nostalgic aura of countless emotions and memories.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2025.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to First Berry Cookie\'s Room of Cherished Memories!</string>
