  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Story">Mistletoe Cookie was baked with a small sprig of mistletoe, which only bear pearly berries during the winter. Her snowy, mystical nature and calm, tender smile are her unmistakable trademarks. 

There was a time she lived alone, having lost all memory of her past. Yet even then, she endured fears as harsh as the coldest winter and found a way to nurture quiet strength within. Step by steady step, guided by a resolute heart, she pressed onward until she found her way back to the friends and home she once knew. 

Now, with those bonds restored at last, there is no reason for Mistletoe Cookie\'s smile to ever fade again.</string>
