  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Get">Do you know
who I am too...?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Random.01">Berrygalia House is home to
many slumbering memories.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Random.02">It\'s okay if my past is forgotten.
Because I\'m happy in the present.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Random.03">I will make new memories,
one by one.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Random.04">Huhu, I have made so
many wonderful friends.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Random.05">Sometimes, what comes to you arrives
only after you have let something go.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.LifeZero.01">I can do it again...
I know I can...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2026.Monologue.Greeting">{0}, let us make
some good memories today.</string>
