  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Wall.001.Story">In a room once belonging to a Cookie who lost her memories, the window still holds onto her favorite view from the past. She would often read with a blanket at the nook, and one night, lifted her gaze to see a shimmering aurora. Wanting to share that beauty, the Cookie invited her friends to gather. Such a scene must have made a lasting impression on the window itself, as the sparkling aurora still brings equally sparkling smiles to anyone who sits and enjoys the view.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Wall.002.Story">Pause midway through a book and take a glance outside. What do you see? A frigid winter night, snowflakes fluttering in the air, and an aurora gently dancing across the sky. It\'s so beautiful, you simply cannot look away.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.001.Story">Gather mistletoe leaves one by one, tie them together with a ribbon, flip it upright, and voilà! You now have a tree perfect for winter\'s final stretch. Add a sprinkle of snow and the winter mood really comes alive.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.002.Story">Soft moss, grown in pure white snowfields, was gathered and piled high into a cozy bed. When you slip into the giant knitted mitten-blanket, suddenly, winter does not feel cold at all. The ultimate bed for freezing winter nights!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.003.Story">An old-fashioned, wood-burning stove adorned with mistletoe. Once lit, it warms the entire room in no time. Just imagine how cozy it must feel when you\'re sitting next to it with a warm cup of tea... Mmmm!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Ceil.001.Story">Snow-white mistletoe branches gathered and hung together. The puffy snow and round little berries come together to create the perfect, snug winter atmosphere.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Wallpaper.001.Story">Wallpaper made from white logs fitted together. Those little snowy bits peeking through? They\'re actually crushed mistletoe berries to help keep the logs together and serve as insulation. A bit sticky, perhaps, but charming all the same!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Deck.001.Story">Flooring made from blue logs fitted together. It gives off a clean, serene feeling, just like a quiet winter night.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Hanger.001.Story">Curtains that mirror the winter night\'s calm ambience. Looking at it puts your mind at ease.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Hanger.002.Story">A wreath made from sprigs of mistletoe. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Hanger.003.Story">We know what you\'re thinking, and no, they are not antlers. Just a charming wooden decoration. These will look great wherever you decide to put them.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Hanger.004.Story">A twinkling mistletoe ornament. Anyone would like this!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.004.Story">A chair made for winter comfort. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.005.Story">A basket filled with mistletoe berries. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.006.Story">A neat pile of firewood for the stove. Perfect for placing wherever warmth is needed.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Floor.007.Story">A side table adorned with a white mushroom. Anyone would love to have one of these.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2026.Rug.001.Story">A carpet patterned with mistletoe. Simply putting it in a room makes it look more elegant.</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2026">Mistletoe Cookie\'s Room of Greatest Winter Memories</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2026.Story">Mistletoe Cookie\'s room is filled to the brim with snow, mistletoe, and berries. At first glance, her room makes you feel like you\'re outside and surrounded by powdery white snow, but somehow it never feels cold. What is the secret behind such a warm and inviting space? When asked, Mistletoe Cookie simply smiles and replies that she carefully decorated the room with her closest friends in mind.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.001">Mistletoe Jelly Basket</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.002">Fluttering Mistletoe Cloak</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.003">Mistletoe Sprig</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.001.Story">A basket of Mistletoe Jellies, snowy white and adorable. Unlike real mistletoe berries, these are complete non-toxic! Feel free to enjoy them without concern!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.002.Story">Mistletoe Cookie never goes anywhere without her favorite cloak. The cute berries were carefully sewn on by her own two hands.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2026.003.Story">A sprig that Mistletoe Cookie always keeps close. On the day her memories were lost, she slipped down a mountainside and instinctively grabbed onto this very sprig. Thanks to it, she survived at the edge of the cliff, safe and sound.</string>
