  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.Main">A Surprisingly Strict Friend</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.01">Mistletoe Cookie: The Feared?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.02">Mistletoe Cookie: The Kindhearted?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.03">Mistletoe Cookie: The Just!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.01.Summary">Mistletoe Cookie is chatting with Bramble Bat Cookie and Smarty. Before long, stories from Mistletoe Cookie\'s distant past, one hard to imagine today, begin to unfold...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.02.Summary">After helping tidy up Mistletoe Cookie\'s room, Bramble Bat Cookie and Smarty are rewarded with snack time! But true to form, the mischievous Bramble Bat Cookie tries to sneak the first bite...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Title.03.Summary">As always, there\'s only one reason Mistletoe Cookie ever gets mad. Back then or now, the reason never changes.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Illust.Dialog.01">There, see? Isn\'t it nice
when everyone gets along?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2026.Illust.Dialog.02">Ah... right. Mistletoe Cookie never
minded taking the loss herself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_1">Wow...! Your room is always so white and snowy. It looks just like you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_2">It is a fine room for spending a cozy winter.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_3">Huhu, thank you. You have no idea how many days it took to make that bed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_4">You were always fond of winter and its ambience.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_5">Your personality was wintry too! You once scolded me for pulling a little harmless prank... Ugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_6">She was never cold like that. Just a bit strict, you simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_7">Was I really like that? Hearing it now feels strange.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_8">Long ago, Bramble Bat Cookie ate everyone else\'s snacks...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_9">Once you heard what he\'d done, you made a truly terrifying face. Your stern countenance must have made a lasting impression... Bramble Bat Cookie screamed in terror every time snacks were served for quite a while.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_10">When did I ever do that?! I didn\'t do anything like-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_11">Hey...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_12">Uh-oh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_13">Th-The bed just broke... Mistletoe Cookie...! I\'m really sorry, I didn\'t mean to!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_14">It\'s okay. I was just a little startled. You do not need to apologize that much, Bramble Bat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_1_POR1_15">Huhu... Instead of repeated apologies, could you help tidy things up? If the three of us work together, it should be done in no time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_1">Just like Mistletoe Cookie said, with the three of us working together, cleaning Bramble Bat Cookie\'s mess was over in no time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_2">Huhu, thank you both for helping.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_3">And... Smarty, can you tell me more about the past? I want to know more about the kind of Cookie I used to be.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_4">Hm... You were strict, but never truly frightening. The reason Bramble Bat Cookie made such an unneeded fuss earlier is simply because... Well, it\'s him. He\'s dramatic by nature.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_5">AM NOT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_6">You said it took days to make that bed, Mistletoe Cookie! I felt bad because I broke something you worked so hard on...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_7">See what I mean? That\'s just how he reacts to things, with a flair for the theatrical. Not because you are scary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_8">Huhu, you two really are close friends, aren\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_9">Spending a great deal of time together does not necessarily equate to close friendship.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_10">Oh, would you like some snacks? I made some Mistletoe Jellies myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_11">Thank y-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_12">LET\'S DIG IN!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_13">Ow! Hey, that hurts... I was just about to eat that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_14">Too bad! Too slow, haha! It\'s mine now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_15">Honestly...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_2_POR1_16">... What do you think you\'re doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_1">Huh? What? Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_2">Smarty was about to eat that Jelly first. You should not take something your friend was going to eat, Bramble Bat Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_3">Er... It was an accident! Yeah, an accident! Haha...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_4">Even so, you should apologize. Go on. Say sorry to Smarty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_5">... Erm, Mistletoe Cookie? You\'re making... that weird, scary face again... What\'s with you all of a sudden? Haha... ha...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_6">... Are you not going to apologize? I will not ask again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_7">EEK! S-S-Smarty, I\'m sorry for grabbing that snack that you were going to take and eat! I didn\'t know, and I\'m really sorry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_8">There, see? Isn\'t it nice when everyone gets along?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_9">Ah... right. Mistletoe Cookie never minded taking the loss herself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_10">But when it came to her friends being hurt, or fighting among themselves, she was relentlessly strict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2026_3_POR1_11">Despite how much time has passed, even with her memories gone... some things never change, do they?</string>
