  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue1">TA-DA!
The star of the show has arrived!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue2_1">Think!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue2_2">What if all your life is a lie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue3_1">Welcome, folks!
Ready for some giggles?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue3_2">Why the loooong face?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue1_1">Ah, destruction.
It makes me feel... alive!
Ha ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue1_2">What should I wreck next?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue2_1">Oh, the thrill of the chase!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue2_2">You can run, but you\'ll
never escape me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue3_1">Cookies clinging to
their little possessions...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue3_2">Pathetic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue1">The world reveals itself to
those who stop and look.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue2_1">Wake up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue2_2">And you shall see the truth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue3_1">Everything will be in vain</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue3_2">and turn to hollow tears.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue1">Allow yourself a little
moment of laziness~</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue2_1">Some might call escaping</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue2_2">the dull and dreary truth...
indolent.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue3_1">Come now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue3_2">Let us live in
eternal Happiness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0604_dialogue1">Would you trust
a traitor\'s words?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0604_dialogue2">I have no words for you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0604_dialogue3">PROVE YOUR WORTH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0506_dialogue1">Is anything troubling you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0506_dialogue2">I still have a few
tricks up my sleeve!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0506_dialogue3">Ascending...
One step at a time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue1">Nothing shinier?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue2">Hearken to me!
I require new treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue3_1">Greed shines brightest
when it\'s boundless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue3_2">And mine will grow to
shine brighter than ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0508_dialogue1">Always beware 
of the Darkness...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0508_dialogue2">A warrior must not
bend to paltry affairs.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0508_dialogue3">A warrior must not
feel complacent...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0510_dialogue1">I\'m celebrating tonight,
so don\'t even try to stop me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0510_dialogue2_1">Prepare a feast!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0510_dialogue2_2">It\'s time we had some fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0510_dialogue3_1">A joyful day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0510_dialogue3_2">Bring on the berry juice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0509_dialogue1">For Freedom...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0509_dialogue2_1">The answers I seek...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0509_dialogue2_2">are within my grasp.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0509_dialogue3">My friends taught me
how to move on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue1_1">I am the fire!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue2">Don\'t burn your eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue3_1">MY FLAME IS
THE STRONGEST!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue3_2">Hope it doesn\'t rain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue1">Witness the powerful wind...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue2_1">The wind of life that
blows within me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue2_2">The Forest keeps
no secrets from me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue3">The wind is blowing
gently today...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue1">I feel the warmth
of your heart...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue2_1">Just as the sea
cradles countless lives,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue2_2">so too does this kingdom
shelter its own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue3">I grant the blessing of
the deep. A sword tempered
in the fathomless sea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue1">I feel like I am dreaming.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue2_1">The moon will always
shine upon you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue3_1">Are we dreaming
this moment together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue3_2">May the stars bless you
with a peaceful dream.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0125_dialogue1">I am in every season.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0125_dialogue2_1">Such odd behavior!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0125_dialogue2_2">Are you a Cookie too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0125_dialogue3_1">What a delightful place!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0125_dialogue3_2">The end brings forth
another beginning.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0530_dialogue1">This, too, is the will of Nature.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0530_dialogue2">Such dedication to a
mere fleeting moment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0530_dialogue3">Have you ever felt a cold
that pierces your very soul?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue1_1">Hello there, little playthings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue1_2">Are you ready to
become soggy trash?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue2_1">Cookies are small, sweet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue2_2">repulsive abominations!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue3_1">H-h-help me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue3_2">I\'m so scared...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568_dialogue3_3">HA HA!
Fooled ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568s02_dialogue1">I wonder... can I treasure
this moment forever?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568s02_dialogue2_1">... Almighty Sea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568s02_dialogue2_2">Do you hear me?
Do you feel my true heart?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568s02_dialogue3_1">Once you have
accomplished all your goals,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0568s02_dialogue3_2">come back to meet me again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0167_dialogue1">Speak your destination!
The past? The future?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0167_dialogue2_1">Why change time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0167_dialogue2_2">Because I can and it is fun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0167_dialogue3_1">I see your future. I know it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0167_dialogue3_2">Are you not curious as to
what I have seen and learned?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue1">I am the sky,
and the sky is me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue2_1">You dare call upon me?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue2_2">Remain humble when asking
a favor of the heavens!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue3_1">Speak your wishes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue3_2">I may be moved into action.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109_dialogue1">I shall become more
terrifying than any Witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109_dialogue2_1">The Night of the Witches...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109_dialogue2_2">I have seen the truth
at that banquet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109_dialogue3_1">REJECT YOUR
PITIFUL FATES</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109_dialogue3_2">LIKE I HAVE
REJECTED MINE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0138_dialogue1_1">I. Am. The. RED
DRAGON OF LEGENDS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0138_dialogue2_1">Cookies are so sssmall
and insignificant...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0138_dialogue2_2">Yet persistent!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0138_dialogue3">You ssstand before the
dragon of legendsss...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue1_1">Everything is quite dull...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue1_2">At least I have my mandolin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue2_1">The lotus in full bloom
beckons me to venture</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue2_2">beyond the palace walls.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue3_1">Though I may wear
this appearance,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue3_2">my splendor is incomparable
to that of Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue1">Bask in my glory.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue2">Kneel before me.
KNEEL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue3_1">You dare to compare
me to a Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue3_2">Dragons are the greatest
force to grace the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue1">Everything will be restored
into order, as it should.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue2">I am all seeing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue3_1">Survive, or perish...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue3_2">Destiny is waiting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue1">You\'ll end up falling
in love with me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue2_1">You know you love me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue2_2">No need to tell me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue3_1">Heh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue3_2">Heehee... You really think
that\'s my true form?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2001_dialogue1">I will not stop.
I will do anything for...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2001_dialogue2_1">The pain of loss begets</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2001_dialogue2_2">a strong will...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2001_dialogue3">This world has such
potential for beauty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2011_dialogue1">For a prosperous harvest...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2011_dialogue2_1">My goodness!
Such a bountiful harvest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2011_dialogue2_2">Come, let us enjoy
this autumn\'s harvest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2011_dialogue3">As long as I am present,
no one shall go hungry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2015_dialogue1">The strong do not know
the meaning of defeat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2015_dialogue2">Never give up.
Never surrender.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2015_dialogue3">Do you have something
you wish to protect
with all your heart?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2021_dialogue1">I will mend your wounds
and tend to your pain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2021_dialogue2">I will do everything I can...
to help you recovery...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2021_dialogue3">The Sanctum of Healing is
a safe place...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2017_dialogue1">The show doesn\'t start
until I take the stage!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2017_dialogue2_1">Hold onto your popcorn!
The real show\'s just begun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2017_dialogue2_2">Isn\'t there anything fun
to do around here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2017_dialogue3">Did you enjoy today\'s show?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2025_dialogue1">All things must be
remembered and cherished...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2025_dialogue2">I can handle this...
I\'ve endured worse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2025_dialogue3">You aren\'t leaving...
Are you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0238_dialogue1">Yay!
The bathhouse is open!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0238_dialogue2">Two banana milks, please!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0238_dialogue3_1">After breakfast,
off to the bathhouse,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0238_dialogue3_2">then lunch and snack time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0222_dialogue1_1">Hoho! The field is
looking great this year!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0222_dialogue1_2">Want some potatoes?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0222_dialogue2">Ah...
The smell of fresh soil...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0222_dialogue3">Come on!
Let\'s go dig up some potatoes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0082_dialogue1">You don\'t think potatoes
aren\'t vegetables, do you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0082_dialogue2">Alpacas liking veggies is
just an urban myth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0082_dialogue3">Take this and add some
healthy vibes to your home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503_dialogue1">It\'s unwise to get in my way...
Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503_dialogue2">What do you want?!
I\'m busy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503_dialogue3">Yes, I\'ll get them...
NEXT TIME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503s02_dialogue1_1">♫ Say ma name ♫</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503s02_dialogue1_2">(ZZ Skull!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503s02_dialogue2">♫ Gettin\' this power
wasn\'t a breeze ♫</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0503s02_dialogue3">♫ Wrote a diary
with my own tears ♫</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0569_dialogue1">●●●!! ◀◎○???</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0569_dialogue2">◀◀◀!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0569_dialogue3">◆○!! □◎□◇~</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591_dialogue1">Hello! My friend!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591_dialogue2">Have you ever seen the snow?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591_dialogue3">A freezing winter wind
follows me wherever I go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591s01_dialogue1">Let\'s walk arm in arm!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591s01_dialogue2">He he he!
I\'m pretty cool, right?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0591s01_dialogue3">RAWR! How was that?
Super scary, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0165_dialogue1">Mine! Mine!
Gimme! ALL MINE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0165_dialogue2">No touchy!
It\'s mine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0165_dialogue3">I dunno what this is,
but it\'s mine now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507s01_dialogue1">Be grateful to stand 
in the presence of
the Golden Sovereign!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507s01_dialogue2">All that shines 
belongs to my Kingdom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507s01_dialogue3">Bask in my golden glory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0008_dialogue1">Oh, hi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0008_dialogue2">I demand adventure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0008_dialogue3">Prepare the carriage.
We\'re going to a ball!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142_dialogue1">Only I can see your true worth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142_dialogue2">You may call me Phantom Bleu.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142_dialogue3">There\'s no jewel
out of my grasp.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142z03_dialogue1">Need a hint?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142z03_dialogue2">One logical answer?
Sounds rather... dull.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0142z03_dialogue3">Only true jewels
will shine eternal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0005_dialogue1">How about a trip
above the clouds?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0005_dialogue2">Wanna play together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0005_dialogue3">Let\'s DANCE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0611_dialogue1">I\'ll have you know, I\'m from
a fine lineage of Haetae!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0611_dialogue2">The Ivory Pagoda is my
old stomping grounds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0611_dialogue3">*CHOMP*
This Haetae bites!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0024_dialogue1">Ready to fall for me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0024_dialogue2">Marshmallow aroma...?
Don\'t be silly, honey!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0024_dialogue3">Have you fallen
in love with me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0175_dialogue1_1">You\'re here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0175_dialogue1_2">(Why...?)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0175_dialogue2">(Do you know how
hot it is in stage...?!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0175_dialogue3_1">Our circus is the best.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0175_dialogue3_2">(Because of me.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0239_dialogue1_1">Hello! Welcome!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0239_dialogue1_2">Am I doing it right?
I feel a bit shy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0239_dialogue2_1">Welcome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0239_dialogue2_2">Which bath can
I guide you to today?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0239_dialogue3">Time to clean and
scrub the tubs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1018_dialogue1">Hmm hmm~♪
Oh, y-you were listening?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1018_dialogue2">I want to sing in front
of everyone someday.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1018_dialogue3">A song for you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0620_dialogue1">Nice and easy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0620_dialogue2_1">"If you want something,
go get it yourself."</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0620_dialogue2_2">That\'s our family motto.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0620_dialogue3">Friendly advice.
You\'d rather get
on my softer side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0015_dialogue1">Feelin\' PUMPED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0015_dialogue2">One thousand push-ups!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0015_dialogue3">Time to warm up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0015z04_dialogue1">This sword isn\'t...
very heavy! *Huff*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0015z04_dialogue2">I\'m going to learn
dumbbell workouts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0015z04_dialogue3">If I get big muscles,
can I be a warrior?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0229_dialogue1">How about a relaxing
nap until sundown?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0229_dialogue2">Sometimes, all I want
to be is a rock on
the side of a road...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0229_dialogue3">Whatever you might hear,
don\'t come out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1002_dialogue1">Send some Star Coal my way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1002_dialogue2">Train repairs? 
Give me a day and it\'ll be done!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1002_dialogue3">I wonder where we\'ll end up
if  we follow our hearts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue1_1">Where imagination
blooms into reality!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue1_2">Dreams as wild
as you like, tee-hee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue2_1">Nightmares aren\'t so scary,
you know?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue2_2">They\'re just making
your heart stronger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue3_1">One sheep...
Two sheep...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0258_dialogue3_2">I wonder how many
until dreamland calls?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0278_dialogue1">I love you!
Sooo so so much!
I mean it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0278_dialogue2">Even this moment is
a precious memory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0278_dialogue3">I\'ll wait for you, no matter
how long it takes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0209_dialogue1">You must let me know if
you see anyone suspicious...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0209_dialogue2">What happened now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0209_dialogue3">Let me know if
you need anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0615_dialogue1">Where\'s your leader?!
Show yourself!
I challenge you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0615_dialogue2">Wild Spices show no mercy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0615_dialogue3">Have you ever weathered
the storm of the badlands?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2022_dialogue1">Hey! I just heard some juicy
gossip for your ears only...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2022_dialogue2">Deceiving everyone is
like child\'s play...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2022_dialogue3">Everything is going
according to plan, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2008_dialogue1">You called?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2008_dialogue2">The cold never bothered me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2008_dialogue3">I don\'t like commotions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0030_dialogue1">Oh, hello there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0030_dialogue2">You\'re gonna be my friend?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0030_dialogue3">I\'ve been waiting for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0030s02_dialogue1">Let\'s have a big
snowball fight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0030s02_dialogue2">I wish it snowed every day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0030s02_dialogue3">Why does looking
at the falling snow 
feel so warm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0007_dialogue1">Swift as the wind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0007_dialogue2">Has the time come
to test my skills?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0007_dialogue3">Training brings
endless results!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0064_dialogue1">Hey, what\'s your
favorite dinosaur?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0064_dialogue2">Dinosaur extinction?
Impossible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0064_dialogue3">Let\'s set out for
a new adventure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0103_dialogue1">You called?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0103_dialogue2">Mind yourself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0103_dialogue3">I do miss the sunlight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0195_dialogue1">Always remember!
Health is a top priority!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0195_dialogue2_1">E-Emergency!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0195_dialogue2_2">You have Soggy Syndrome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0195_dialogue3">Just take my advice and
it\'s all going tibia-kay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0107_dialogue1">Genius! I\'m a genius!
Heh-he-he!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0107_dialogue2">Side effects?
What side effects? Heh-he!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0107_dialogue3">Ha!
Official science is NO FUN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0061_dialogue1">Dashing through the snow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0061_dialogue2">Let\'s go fishing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0061_dialogue3">My penguins are
the fastest on ice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0071_dialogue1">Got any wice cake?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0071_dialogue2">Wanna wice cake?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0071_dialogue3">Oh, ya like wice cakes too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0132_dialogue1">Ever wondered who
grows your veggies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0132_dialogue2">So much work to do!
Clock\'s ticking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0132_dialogue3">No no no! 
That\'s not how
you plant seeds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0272_dialogue1">I hope to make a
loving environment
for all the little ones!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0272_dialogue2">Childhood memories are
decisive in how a Cookie
grows up...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0272_dialogue3">I know you want to do well,
but are you enjoying yourself?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0057_dialogue1">My loyalty shall never waver.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0057_dialogue2">Distance means
nothing to my horse.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0057_dialogue3">I shall lead.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0158_dialogue1">I am heir to the Leek Clan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0158_dialogue2">My blade can cut
down entire forests.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0158_dialogue3">Haha!
Put the tea on my tab!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0182_dialogue1">I want to help as many
Cookies as I can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0182_dialogue2">Where did my medicine go?
I\'m sure I put it here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0182_dialogue3_1">I heard there are rare herbs</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0182_dialogue3_2">at the top of the mountains!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0633_dialogue1">So many Cookies...
blissfully unaware of
what awaits beyond.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0633_dialogue2">Can you hear it?
Can you hear the Call?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0633_dialogue3_1">Book of the Oven, 8:16.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0633_dialogue3_2">"... Thy sacred plates are not
for those of soggy dough..."</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502_dialogue1">Why is everything... violet...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502_dialogue2">Let\'s munch on some \'shrooms!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502_dialogue3">It\'s time for a \'shroomie party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502s04_dialogue1_1">♬ Have some
shroomies ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502s04_dialogue1_2">♬ Why won\'t y\'all try
some shroomies ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502s04_dialogue2_1">♬ The crew hated
on shroomies ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502s04_dialogue2_2">♬ now they be lovin\'
the shroomies ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0502s04_dialogue3">♬ HAPPY SPORE
DANCE! ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1015_dialogue1">Too cold?
Keep your distance then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1015_dialogue2">Closing my eyes...
Calms me down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1015_dialogue3">I do not take someone\'s
heat without good reason.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue1_1">My name...? It\'s...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue1_2">It\'s Dragon Eye Cookie.
Hehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue2_1">Don\'t touch water...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue2_2">But why can we
drink juice...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue3_1">Hmph! You bring me,
or you accompany me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie0271_dialogue3_2">There is no other path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0127_dialogue1">Put your hands up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0127_dialogue2">I say KOO!
You say KEE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0127_dialogue3">Everybody dance now!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0002_dialogue1">Er... Can I help you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0002_dialogue2">Sometimes I do things
I don\'t usually do...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0002_dialogue3">Shh, I\'m playing a game...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0506_dialogue1">Um, I\'d love some privacy...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0506_dialogue2">Guess I\'m not that fun...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0506_dialogue3">Do we really have to go there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0235_dialogue1">I want to spread happiness, too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0235_dialogue2">... I\'ll try my best.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0235_dialogue3">It\'s the thought that counts
when it comes to presents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0072_dialogue1">Hi~! How are you~?
Do you like to run~? WOOF!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0072_dialogue2">Let\'s go for a walk~!
A WAAALK~! Woof, woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0072_dialogue3">I like getting cuddled!
And pats! And boops!
SOOO MUCH! Woof, woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1017_dialogue1">You should always
keep your heart pure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1017_dialogue2">Try making a wish to
the Mochi Fox God!
They might grant it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1017_dialogue3">Whatever happens,
I\'ll never give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0248_dialogue1">Nothing beats drumming while
looking out at the sea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0248_dialogue2">Every cloud has a silver lining!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0248_dialogue3">I\'m late, but the view on
the way was amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0518_dialogue1">*YAWN*
Hey you, I\'m bored!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0518_dialogue2">Why are there so
many Cookies here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0518_dialogue3">Do YOU know
how Cookies are made?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0518s01_dialogue1_1">How curious!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0518s01_dialogue1_2">Can I disassemble that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0518s01_dialogue2">Let me inspect
your circuitry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0518s01_dialogue3">Stop poking me!
I hate it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516_dialogue1">Add a spoonful of milk
and voila! A latte!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516_dialogue2">Sooner or later, 
you\'ll find the answer you need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516_dialogue3">Did someone say \"latte\"?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516s01_dialogue1">Hm... What magic glyph
should I draw today?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516s01_dialogue2">Writing a thesis was fun!
But I\'m not eager
to write another!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0516s01_dialogue3">Milk is key for a delicious
cup of coffee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0522_dialogue1">... What is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0522_dialogue2">Why I am here?
I cannot tell you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0522_dialogue3">Shh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0054_dialogue1">You aren\'t playing with
other Cookies, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0054_dialogue2">You want me to rap?
Um, it\'s \"Lime\" Cookie,
not \"Rhyme\"!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0054_dialogue3">The secret to my
perfect bangs?
Lime pudding!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0150_dialogue1">My family\'s history lives
within this sword!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0150_dialogue2">I\'m but a budding knight
compared to full blooms...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0150_dialogue3">Winning or losing?
The duel itself matters!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0524_dialogue1">My sword for
House Raspberry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0524_dialogue2">My sword carries 
my family\'s legacy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0524_dialogue3">House Raspberry!
Remember this name.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0027_dialogue1">I\'m the living
legend of ROCK, baby!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0027_dialogue2">You want my autograph?
Oh, maybe a picture together?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0027_dialogue3">Rock stars are
forever young, yeah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0197_dialogue1">I\'m always happy to help!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0197_dialogue2">I got this spear
on my birthday!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0197_dialogue3">I\'ll do anything to
protect my tribe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0161_dialogue1">One punch from my
claw is all that\'s needed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0161_dialogue2">I have long forgotten
my life before Sugarteara.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0161_dialogue3">My Crystal Claw is a
part of this city\'s legacy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0226_dialogue1">I\'ll lead your way to justice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0226_dialogue2">Judicial Training Academy
was only the beginning.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0226_dialogue3">If you need a lawyer,
you have my number
on this card.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2004_dialogue1">Together, we can do anything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2004_dialogue2">Nothin like a mug of syrup
after a hard day\'s work, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2004_dialogue3">Somethin need fixin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0252_dialogue1">For the sake of the Sugar Swan,
I fear nothing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0252_dialogue2">Did you know nature has
its own intricate rules?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0252_dialogue3">Let\'s finish our work
before we rest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0052_dialogue1">Mess with me
and get electrified.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0052_dialogue2">Careful...
You\'ll get zapped.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0052_dialogue3">I like listening to
electronic music.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1006_dialogue1">This will be quite the shock.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1006_dialogue2">Is there nothing
interesting around?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1006_dialogue3">If I\'m not around,
don\'t go looking for me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0578_dialogue1">Heh, first time seeing 
a Dragon Rider?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0578_dialogue2">My butter knife has
several uses, heh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0578_dialogue3">Not only more handsome,
but stronger too?
How great is this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2005_dialogue1">If you need an ear,
I\'m here to talk...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2005_dialogue2">I need rest...
Alone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2005_dialogue3">*Sigh*
Is she up to something again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0210_dialogue1">I know EVERYTHING about
our shop\'s toys, so you can
always ask me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0210_dialogue2">Heh heh! You thought I was
a doll too, didn\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0210_dialogue3">Our shop is the funnest
place in the WHOLE world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0067_dialogue1">Hammer down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0067_dialogue2">Who wants to be smashed?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0067_dialogue3">Squish! Squash! 
Squoosh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0592_dialogue1">You want me to sign your copy?
Heh, with pleasure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0592_dialogue2">... Hm? My apologies. 
I was deeply
absorbed in my work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0592_dialogue3">There\'s a pianist
in my next work.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0511_dialogue1">The Divine smiles upon me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0511_dialogue2">Honored to fight alongside you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0511_dialogue3">How dull...
Should I go on patrol?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0143_dialogue1">Ain\'t no Cookie
spicier than me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0143_dialogue2">HURAGH!
Too spicy for ya!?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0143_dialogue3">Ya know, the legends of our
tribe have dragons in them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0025_dialogue1">Interested in the arcane arts?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0025_dialogue2">Wanna see real magic?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0025_dialogue3">A magical challenge?
Bring it on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0508_dialogue1">*Mumbling*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0508_dialogue2">Shh, I\'m thinking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0508_dialogue3">Our world is full of
magical secrets...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2002_dialogue1">Have we been
previously acquainted?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2002_dialogue2">I have truly missed this place.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2002_dialogue3">Much has changed here,
though it\'s well warranted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1016_dialogue1">Please do not interfere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1016_dialogue2">No errors detected in
current instance.
Monitoring resumed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1016_dialogue3">Hmm... Seems like I have
the night patrol shift today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0243_dialogue1">The vacuum is full...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0243_dialogue2">Nothing is ever easy...
Everyone\'s busy...
working hard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0243_dialogue3">Can\'t believe I\'m cleaning
at work when I don\'t even
clean my own room...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0130_dialogue1">Forward... hut!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0130_dialogue2">Trumpet is a must 
in every march!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0130_dialogue3">Mark time... hut!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0059_dialogue1">Ooh, let\'s go marching
one by one, hurrah, hurrah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0059_dialogue2">Da-dum... dum...
Ta-ta-ta!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0059_dialogue3">One, two, three!
Listen closely, okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0635_dialogue1">Every item we carry
holds a story.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0635_dialogue2">Knowledge is power!
Our guild knows that
better than others.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0635_dialogue3">We\'ve Cookies of great
renown among our clients.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0110_dialogue1">I\'m busy...
Big time... Heh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0110_dialogue2">Hmpf!
I\'ll show you...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0110_dialogue3">He heh...
They will see,
they will all see...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0086_dialogue1">Do I count as a bit cute?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0086_dialogue2">Someone keeps yelling out to
me saying, \"manggae~tteok~!\"
Am I missing something...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0086_dialogue3">Don\'t treat me like a kid!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154_dialogue1">This place is just as
beautiful as our islands!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154_dialogue2">I come from beautiful
tropical islands!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154_dialogue3">My home is an island, 
far away across the ocean.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154s01_dialogue1">I know a place 
you\'d love to visit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154s01_dialogue2">Oh, shall I take you
to the archipelago
where my home is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0154s01_dialogue3">I know the seas
like my own dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0207_dialogue1">A festival is all about
dancing and eating Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0207_dialogue2">Are ya ready for
another delightful tale?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0207_dialogue3">Another day full of sunshine!
It\'s time to play!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0108_dialogue1">My taste is none
of your business!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0108_dialogue2">Not all Cookies
have to be sweet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0108_dialogue3">I want to be free from
society\'s expectations!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0164_dialogue1">Pickaxe at the ready.
Stones need breaking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0164_dialogue2">Work hard, dream big!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0164_dialogue3">Gotta stay fit to
work long hours!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3001_dialogue1">Hehe!
Time to make it BURST!
Nice and cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3001_dialogue2">Hey!
Don\'t move or I\'ll shoot!
Pew! Pew!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3001_dialogue3">Don\'t forget to
like and subscribe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2012_dialogue1">If there is anything you need,
let me know... But only me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2012_dialogue2">I\'ll make sure that nuisance
Chickp... Wh-what?!
Stop eavesdropping!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2012_dialogue3">Oh... Hoo hoo?
No, that\'s a weird way to laugh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0637_dialogue1">I will deliver Their word
here  in this kingdom.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0637_dialogue2">... By Thy Grace shall
I guide Cookies to Paradise.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0637_dialogue3">Divine Will dwells within
order  and structure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0075_dialogue1">I just looove traveling
to new places!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0075_dialogue2">I keep all my stuff
in my Bunny Tunnels!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0075_dialogue3">What fun happenings
await us today?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2016_dialogue1">Do you think I can
get strooonger...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2016_dialogue2">The Chocosseum
is awesome...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2016_dialogue3">It\'s such a nice daaay!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0003_dialogue1">Happy mind, happy life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0003_dialogue2">Hey!
Let\'s party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0003_dialogue3">I am feeling good today!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589_dialogue1">How about a bet?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589_dialogue2">Oh? Did you call for me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589_dialogue3">Safe choices are BORING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589s01_dialogue1">I have a feeling things are
about to get interesting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589s01_dialogue2">He he, let\'s up the ante!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0589s01_dialogue3">Aww... Crispy?
Where\'s the fun in that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0162_dialogue1">The Sacred Pearl
will protect us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0162_dialogue2">The stingrays help me
protect the temple.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0162_dialogue3">I will protect the
Sacred Pearl\'s light.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0529_dialogue1">This is the farthest
I\'ve been from home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0529_dialogue2">Winter or summer,
day or night: our village is
always covered in snow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0529_dialogue3">You\'d be surprised how
one small light can light
up so many roads.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2009_dialogue1">A fresh new day is here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2009_dialogue2">Everything feels so fresh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2009_dialogue3">You can call me for anything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131_dialogue1">Runnin\' is great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131_dialogue2">How \'bout a tale? 
Hi hi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131_dialogue3">I wanna show you
my for\'st home!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131s01_dialogue1">Hop on my back!
Hi hi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131s01_dialogue2">C\'mon! Let\'s play!
I wanna play!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0131s01_dialogue3">Every land tells
its own story!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0249_dialogue1">May the songs of
our youth spread
far and wide...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0249_dialogue2">I want to write lyrics
that capture the vibe
of our town\'s sea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0249_dialogue3">I get the best ideas when
I take walks on the beach.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0046_dialogue1">Shall I play
a piece for you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0046_dialogue2">What piece shall
I play for you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0046_dialogue3">Let the melody
flow through you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0193_dialogue1">Why do I have to
leave the Witch\'s house?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0193_dialogue2">I only need Treasures
in this world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0193_dialogue3">No! Don\'t touch the Treasure!
Ptooey!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0573_dialogue1">Yawn... So where did
I park my train...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0573_dialogue2">Am I still dreaming...?
Nope, definitely not!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0573_dialogue3">Let\'s see... what did the
Conductor\'s Manual say
about reality?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0573s02_dialogue1">Sigh... Maybe YOU could
drive the train today?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0573s02_dialogue2">Let\'s go...!
Somewhere no one
has ever gone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0573s02_dialogue3">Milky Way Cookie,
your conductor made
of delightful starshine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0213_dialogue1">Time records do not pick sides.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0213_dialogue2">As a Cookie of the TBD,
being on time is the
bare minimum.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0213_dialogue3">Start with focusing
on the basics.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1021_dialogue1">There\'s no cutting corners
when it comes to safety!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1021_dialogue2">H-Hey!
Hands off the ears!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1021_dialogue3">*Beep!* If you cut in line
you\'re not allowed to
get on the ride!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0068_dialogue1">Are you ready?
This is the greatest show!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0068_dialogue2">This trick\'ll blow your mind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0068_dialogue3">It\'s showtime!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0081_dialogue1">The three flowers bloom
once more today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0081_dialogue2">Let me guide you... to a place
where there\'s no more pain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0081_dialogue3">There\'s a Cookie waiting
for you on the other side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0587_dialogue1">State your business.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0587_dialogue2">Are there no jackals here?
Then who protects these lands?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0587_dialogue3">Halt!
Who goes there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1012_dialogue1">I\'ll show ya the best cooking
this side of the tower!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1012_dialogue2">Well-fed and ready
for adventure, I hope?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1012_dialogue3">If there\'s anything ya wanna eat,
just let me know! WAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0270_dialogue1_1">Sometimes you gotta laugh
through the worst times!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0270_dialogue1_2">You know why I like egg jokes?
Because they crack me up!
HAHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0270_dialogue2">The moment you give into
the fear, you\'ve already lost!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0270_dialogue3">Haha, this arm? You could
say it\'s a souvenir from
a fight for survival.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0055_dialogue1">Have you heard the story of
the Sea that loved the Moon?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0055_dialogue2">Have you heard of the
pearl that sank away?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0055_dialogue3">I like to dip my 
feet in seawater.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0146_dialogue1">I\'m going on an
adventure one day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0146_dialogue2">Breaking news!
Extra, extra!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0146_dialogue3">Newspaper deliveries for
every house, rain or shine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0263_dialogue1">Any sticky gossip lately?
No? Mm, we\'ll see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0263_dialogue2">I don\'t know how you\'d do
it without me, young master!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0263_dialogue3">Tell \'em everything and
they\'ll never think you\'re
hiding something!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0084_dialogue1">I am devoted to the
ordained teachings...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0084_dialogue2">In flowing white robes
and a folded cap,
softly we take flight...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0084_dialogue3">Are you seeking
peace and solace?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0274_dialogue1">Oh? Oops! Did I just throw
a dagger without warning?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0274_dialogue2">Justice, honor, friendship...
I\'ve never lost to fools
who believe in that.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0274_dialogue3">When you stand before
true power... there\'s
nothing left but to kneel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0035_dialogue1">Why so serious?
Let me pour you some juice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0035_dialogue2">Can\'t you make some 
juice with your alchemy?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0035_dialogue3">Stop worrying
about everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0050_dialogue1">I hate dullness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0050_dialogue2">The world is my canvas!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0050_dialogue3">I\'m gonna create the
greatest masterpiece!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0597_dialogue1">Kneading technique
alone can change
the Cookie drastically!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0597_dialogue2">Working with a research
partner could be helpful!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0597_dialogue3">Life Powder, magic, and
a recipe! The three essentials
for Cookie research!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1022_dialogue1">Do not be led astray
by what glitters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1022_dialogue2">I determine my own fate.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1022_dialogue3">Wherever light goes,
darkness follows.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0211_dialogue1">Young Cookies are always
deserving of presents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0211_dialogue2">What are your holiday
wishes this year?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0211_dialogue3">Tell me, what kind of
toys do you like?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0241_dialogue1">I am my own genre!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0241_dialogue2">Ehem! No director out 
there can do it like me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0241_dialogue3">Art is the medium
which connects
Cookies to the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0006_dialogue1">I wish no Cookies
would starve...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0006_dialogue2">Every Jelly you can
think of passes through
our company.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0006_dialogue3">I can\'t wait to get home
and see my family!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0180_dialogue1">My paintings will
captivate the world!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0180_dialogue2">One look, and you\'ll remember
my paintings forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0180_dialogue3">If you have to ask,
you can\'t afford my paintings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0051_dialogue1">Ah, aren\'t cherry
blossoms pretty?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0051_dialogue2">Nothing better than a
cup of fragrant tea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0051_dialogue3">This lunch box took me
only three hours!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3004_dialogue1">Kya-ha!
Want a taste of my
Bacon Roll Hammer?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3004_dialogue2">Now this is the
kind of hammer
that\'s worth swinging!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3004_dialogue3">Hehe!
Did I just get even cuter?
Kya-ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521_dialogue1">You will speak only
when spoken to!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521_dialogue2">Am I a Cake? Hah!
Are you sure you can
handle the truth?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521_dialogue3">Ah, if only you could
understand the Cakes!
They are the cutest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521s02_dialogue1">♬ Ya ain\'t never seen
a Cookie like me ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521s02_dialogue2">♬ Am I Cake Monster
or Cookie? Naw! ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0521s02_dialogue3">♬ Sweet like Cake
and slick like Velvet ♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0614_dialogue1">Our lighthouse guides
sailors in darkness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0614_dialogue2">Come visit the
Lunar Lighthouse!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0614_dialogue3">Wanna hear a story?
It\'s the one my Grams
once told me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0011_dialogue1">Bored?
Let\'s have some fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0011_dialogue2">Let me show you some tricks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0011_dialogue3">Yo, dude!
Whassup?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0080_dialogue1">I will never bow to injustice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0080_dialogue2">Are you trying to steal barley?
Let\'s see you try.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0080_dialogue3">A roasted scent from
my wings, you say...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2018_dialogue1">Haha, anyone can shine!
Yes, even you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2018_dialogue2">As expected. The ringmaster\'s
performance is perfect as usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2018_dialogue3">Together, we shall bedazzle
the audience once more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0612_dialogue1">Sate your hunger
in my garden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0612_dialogue2">No, that\'s not an
actual peach on my head.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0612_dialogue3">Peach baos will be
abundant this season.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0056_dialogue1">Hyaah!
Was that it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0056_dialogue2">You? Against me? Ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0056_dialogue3">Watahhh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0246_dialogue1">To soar higher, you must
also learn how to fall.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0246_dialogue2">Newly hatched cabbage
pterosaurs are truly gentle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0246_dialogue3">Throwing a tantrum doesn\'t
always work. Some things
just can\'t be done.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3007_dialogue1">Darling... Are you really curious
whether I can pull the trigger?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3007_dialogue2">The Lactose family will rise
to even greater heights...
All thanks to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3007_dialogue3">Mm, a rare day off, and yet
I am just as busy as ever.
How tiresome.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0254_dialogue1">Code name, please!
Did someone order
Jjajang noodles?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0254_dialogue2">That\'s a memory wiper.
Trust me, you don\'t
wanna mess with it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0254_dialogue3">Just because it\'s a delivery
carrier doesn\'t mean
there\'s food inside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0581_dialogue1">... So many Cookies
I\'ve never met before...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0581_dialogue2">Huh? I\'m not angry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0581_dialogue3">I like following my own style.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519_dialogue1">INTRUDER, stop right there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519_dialogue2">Raisin buns: yes or no?
Choose wisely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519_dialogue3">This eye can see 
in the darkest dark.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519s02_dialogue1">Every Cookie matters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519s02_dialogue2">I will survive,
come what may!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0519s02_dialogue3">This eye can see 
in the darkest dark.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0042_dialogue1">Do you require
my assistance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0042_dialogue2">Is there anything
I can do for you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0042_dialogue3">I was informed my employer
came this way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0622_dialogue1">My show covers all
the lies and gossip
of the Cookie World!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0622_dialogue2">Do you like my earrings?
Oh yes, they\'re quite refined!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0622_dialogue3">Can I fly?
The most important is
what YOU believe, he he.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0255_dialogue1">You can count
on me, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0255_dialogue2">I\'d say I\'m a Cookie
of all trades!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0255_dialogue3">The best reward is
the experience we gain!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWC_cookie2007_dialogue1">I shall heed your command.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWC_cookie2007_dialogue2">How may I aid you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWC_cookie2007_dialogue3">I shall protect
these sacred lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0219_dialogue1">Wa ha ha!
You can trust me
with any request!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0219_dialogue2">Peppercorns everywhere!
Wa ha ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0219_dialogue3">My dough is starting to feel stiff!
Time to have some fun!
Wa ha ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3005_dialogue1">I go where the blade leads...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3005_dialogue2">My conviction...
will never waver.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3005_dialogue3">The blade\'s edge has
grown sharper. Good.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0230_dialogue1">I\'m the future Dessert Guardian!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0230_dialogue2">Wanna see my
perfect flying skills?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0230_dialogue3">You know what they say!
Dream big and sweet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0148_dialogue1">Do not touch the
tomes willy-nilly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0148_dialogue2">I have been alone
for quite some time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0148_dialogue3">All tomes and books
have their own worth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0133_dialogue1">Got a spot I can
set up my tent?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0133_dialogue2">Gotta find something to eat...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0133_dialogue3">There is no storm 
I can\'t weather...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0186_dialogue1">There\'s no fashion without fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0186_dialogue2">Where\'d I buy this?
I made this myself, silly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0186_dialogue3">I\'ve been designing ever
since I could use scissors.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0137_dialogue1">Cookie or Robot?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0137_dialogue2">Out of the way, or get zapped!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0137_dialogue3">The age of Cyborg is here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0004_dialogue1">Where\'s Rudolph?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0004_dialogue2">Houses these days
don\'t have chimneys...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0004_dialogue3">You better not cry,
and better not pout!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0153_dialogue1">School? NO!
SANDWICHES...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0153_dialogue2">I have an idea for
a new sandwich!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0153_dialogue3">My recipe diary is
my greatest treasure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0144_dialogue1">Hey there!
Let\'s plan a party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0144_dialogue2">Happy guests
make me happy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0144_dialogue3">Every day is a party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613_dialogue1">There\'re many kinds
of Cream Critters,
not only ferrets!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613_dialogue2">I\'m much faster
when I transform!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613_dialogue3">Cream Critters make
the best babysitters!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613s01_dialogue1">My hugs are warm and fluffy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613s01_dialogue2">Heh, not everyone
gets to have a fluffy
tail like mine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0613s01_dialogue3">Look!
My coat\'s become fluffier!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0598_dialogue1">How can I help you?
Oh wait, this isn\'t
the Town Square!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0598_dialogue2">My hat?
I never leave home without it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0598_dialogue3">Getting out of the office
to work is so much fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160_dialogue1">0Ooo0ooOo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160_dialogue2">0oOoo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160_dialogue3">oO0o0oOOo0o?
o0ooO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160s01_dialogue1">o0Ooo0O!
0o0oo0!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160s01_dialogue2">O0ooOO0o!
Oo0oo0oO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0160s01_dialogue3">0O0o0ooo0oo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0169_dialogue1">Hey! Wanna hear 
one of my songs?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0169_dialogue2">Oh, this outfit?
I put it together myself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0169_dialogue3">I\'m always ready 
for a new challenge!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0223_dialogue1">I shine the most
when I\'m acting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0223_dialogue2">Shying down for a new
role is unprofessional.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0223_dialogue3">I\'m always striving to
work beyond my limits.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0634_dialogue1">If you\'re looking for an
honest deal, come to me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0634_dialogue2">No buttery promises,
only solid wares.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0634_dialogue3">Pirates?
Those no-good crummy batch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0126_dialogue1">Shall I reveal your fate...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0126_dialogue2">I see Darkness in you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0126_dialogue3">My mirror shows 
many reflections.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1020_dialogue1">Ah, there aren\'t enough hours
in a day to fit all this fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1020_dialogue2">Nothing beats hearing the
joyful laughter of Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1020_dialogue3">Fireworks are the perfect
finale to amusement park fun!
Hehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0231_dialogue1">Do you wish to
know how it all began?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0231_dialogue2">One world is akin
to a single sugar egg...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0231_dialogue3">May one live on
with sweet glimmer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0253_dialogue1">I am the most beautiful
swan in all the land!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0253_dialogue2">I shall gracefully fly
higher than any
who came before me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0253_dialogue3">Oh Sugar Mirror,
who is the most beautiful
of them all?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0599_dialogue1">*chew chew*
... Gum?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0599_dialogue2">What? 
Relax, I\'m not gonna mug ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0599_dialogue3">Whoa whoa!
Stay where you are or
my spikes will sting ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0238_dialogue1">Have I been here before...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0238_dialogue2">I hope the scent of lilies
isn\'t too strong...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0238_dialogue3">I wondered why
Cookies are so fragile...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0218_dialogue1">Ohh ho ho! Who dares
to stand in my way?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0218_dialogue2">Don\'t you dare
mess with my clan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0218_dialogue3">I will never forgive
the traitors who
betrayed the clan.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0123_dialogue1">Life is tough.
But it\'s worth living!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0123_dialogue2">I barely made it out alive...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0123_dialogue3">My life is sweet.
Sometimes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1019_dialogue1">This is the perfect timing
for an epic entrance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1019_dialogue2">I hear you\'ve been
looking for me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1019_dialogue3">I\'ve never seen anyone
faster than me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0039_dialogue1">Got this chill surfboard
from the Witch\'s freezer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0039_dialogue2">Don\'t be afraid of waves!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0039_dialogue3">The waves are callin\'!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0136_dialogue1">I can hear the wind
blustering across
a snowy field...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0136_dialogue2">Think of me when
the first snowflake
tickles your nose.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0136_dialogue3">Snow eventually melts...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0571_dialogue1">Each of my footsteps
turn to frost...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0571_dialogue2">The cabin in the snow
will always lie deep
inside my heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0571_dialogue3">I\'ll travel the world
to my heart\'s content!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0572_dialogue1">It\'s my first time
outside the forest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0572_dialogue2">Are you a Cookie too?
You look kinda strange!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0572_dialogue3">I may be small
but I\'m the fastest
in this forest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0639_dialogue1">Wield your sword
for the downtrodden.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0639_dialogue2">Regrets, resentment...
All crumble before time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0639_dialogue3">I, too, was once forgotten...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0066_dialogue1">All my Jellies are yours...
No, no, no!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0066_dialogue2">Your voice is as
sweet as syrup... Um.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0066_dialogue3">Oh, I\'m so in love...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0187_dialogue1">Fashion is in the details.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0187_dialogue2">Classic is timeless.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0187_dialogue3">Some of our clientele
refuse to wear anything
but our brand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0184_dialogue1">I just want to
take things easy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0184_dialogue2">Why work so hard?
Just go with the flow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0184_dialogue3">Flowers bloom and
wilt all the time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0595_dialogue1">I command the
Silver Tree Knights.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0595_dialogue2">I see there is not
a single silver tree...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0595_dialogue3">Be careful:
my glaive is sharp.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0079_dialogue1">Victory belongs to the
one who does not waver.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0079_dialogue2">Today, I am better
than I was yesterday.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0079_dialogue3">To follow proper form is,
in the end, to trust oneself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0189_dialogue1">My heart breaks whenever
a flower withers...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0189_dialogue2">The only thing I remember is
the same colors, everywhere...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0189_dialogue3">Can the greenhouse be
fixed when they return?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1013_dialogue1">Happiness is different
for everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1013_dialogue2">I will bring you the
warmest happiness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1013_dialogue3">Happiness exists for everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0632_dialogue1">Forget about all your troubles.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0632_dialogue2">This place is unlike anything
I\'ve seen in Beast-Yeast...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0632_dialogue3">Have you heard the
Sugar Angel choir sing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0242_dialogue1">A relic is a clock without hands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0242_dialogue2">We are like detectives
of archaeology.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0242_dialogue3">Now, I\'m being honest,
but there\'s no better Cookie
in the division than me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048_dialogue1">I think I\'m getting 
the hang of magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048_dialogue2">Have I finally become
a real wizard?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048_dialogue3">Jellius Extremus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s01_dialogue1">I\'ll give it my best shot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s01_dialogue2">We can do anything as long
as we have each other!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s01_dialogue3">I\'m a bit nervous...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s02_dialogue1">This place is so 
different from school!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s02_dialogue2">The world is so much larger
than described in books!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0048s02_dialogue3">Can\'t study when
you\'re hungry!
Want a cream puff?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0234_dialogue1">I\'m a veteran engineer
in my household!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0234_dialogue2">My family told me
they\'d buy me a train
if I become an engineer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0234_dialogue3">If I become a gift delivery
Cookie, will others be
happy to see me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580_dialogue1">Buu ba ba!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580_dialogue2">Abababwah bwah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580_dialogue3">Whaanya buu ba!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580s01_dialogue1">Snabdragger!
E he he!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580s01_dialogue2">Buu baa kyahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0580s01_dialogue3">Ehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0204_dialogue1">Opportunity comess
to thosse who wait.
Hehehe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0204_dialogue2">Under an outsstanding
general gather 
outsstanding troopss.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0204_dialogue3">My era iss approaching...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0233_dialogue1">Trying things on your
own will help you see
the joy of camping!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0233_dialogue2">Don\'t worry. If we get lost,
there will be another path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0233_dialogue3">There is no right or
wrong in camping!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0616_dialogue1">Mm? Do you require 
my powers?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0616_dialogue2">\"A funny smell\"?
Ah, that\'s probably
my smoke.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0616_dialogue3">There was a time
when the whole kingdom
looked up to me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2023_dialogue1">*Sigh* Okay, what seems
to be troubling you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2023_dialogue2">Further research is required
to develop better treatments.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2023_dialogue3">Always take a moment
to get some relaxation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0574_dialogue1">My voyage... goes on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0574_dialogue2">Traveling through the
vast emptiness of space
is not for everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0574_dialogue3">Think of me when you
see a falling star.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0574s01_dialogue1">What is the name
of this star?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0574s01_dialogue2">Will I, too, find a star
to call my own?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0574s01_dialogue3">In the eyes of the cosmos,
we are but tiny specks...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0176_dialogue1">Do you have a
question for the stars?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0176_dialogue2">What messages will
the stars have tonight?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0176_dialogue3">Stars, please light my path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0264_dialogue1">Find peace within
lush green blessings...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0264_dialogue2">Pray for none other
than yourselves...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0264_dialogue3">You are not alone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0275_dialogue1">This harsh, wild world?
I\'ve survived it with
only a knife at my side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0275_dialogue2">When I swing my knife,
I forget everything else
and leave it to instinct!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0275_dialogue3">The bigger the outlaw,
the greater the danger.
So bring it on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0192_dialogue1">Which timeline are you from?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0192_dialogue2">There are more important
things here than myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0192_dialogue3">No one messes with the
timeline on my watch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3008_dialogue1">Mansion, cleared.
Grounds, cleared.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3008_dialogue2">A proper maid must
be proficient with
the Macheese Gun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3008_dialogue3">Lactose belongs to the Boss.
As it should.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1008_dialogue1">Durian Bombs, AWAY!
DURHURHUR!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1008_dialogue2">Hwah? Sh-shake hands?
For real?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1008_dialogue3">Smell me, and you\'ll turn
your head away for sure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0111_dialogue1">Have a glass!
It\'s on me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0111_dialogue2">Feel like trying
something new tonight?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0111_dialogue3">Perhaps another glass...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0152_dialogue1">Vegetables are the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0152_dialogue2">Eat veggies to
become healthy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0152_dialogue3">Need a snack?
Have some veggies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0060_dialogue1">Cinnamon Cookie,
the Great and Terrible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0060_dialogue2">This hat is
completely empty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0060_dialogue3">Watch closely!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0078_dialogue1">Snacks are great,
but winning tastes the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0078_dialogue2">Stirring up chaos
on the board is...
SO MUCH FUN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0078_dialogue3">Playing strictly by the book?
Where\'s the fun in that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0532_dialogue1">Have you heard of
the Tea Leaf Knights?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0532_dialogue2">Ah, the tea parties we used to
throw after a glorious battle...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0532_dialogue3">Beneath this armor, 
this old-timer\'s got 
a soft spot for tea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225_dialogue1">Have you ever witnessed
pure darkness...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225_dialogue2">The unrestrained power is
akin to a dire curse...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225_dialogue3">Light and darkness differ
by a mere grain of flour...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0619_dialogue1">Detection mode on!
Oh, this place is
filled with sweetness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0619_dialogue2">All sweets will be MINE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0619_dialogue3">If words don\'t work,
firepower will!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0517_dialogue1">Detective Almond Cookie, 
Magical Emergency Handling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0517_dialogue2">I\'m on my break... 
What\'s up?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0517_dialogue3">Another incident? 
Welp, I\'m heading out.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0113_dialogue1">I\'m a tough Cookie!
Ha ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0113_dialogue2">Puns are my 
res-PUN-sibility! LOL</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0113_dialogue3">Be sure to bring
some water \'cause
I\'m on fire!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1023_dialogue1">The heart is like a calm lake.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1023_dialogue2">Do you have what it takes
to pass through a
roaring waterfall?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1023_dialogue3">I will strike before even a
single droplet can descend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1014_dialogue1">No track\'s too rough
for my board!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1014_dialogue2">Bet I can outrun the
train with my board!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1014_dialogue3">I mean, if you fall,
just get back up again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0112_dialogue1">We are a team!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0112_dialogue2">We can do it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0112_dialogue3">Train hard,
play hard!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3002_dialogue1">I\'ve swung this Ice Bat
thousands of times.
What\'s one more?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3002_dialogue2">I\'ve got good memories of
playing catch with my family.
... That was a long time ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3002_dialogue3">Just a bat?
Hmph, you\'re in
for a surprise then.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0533_dialogue1">The best medicine...
tastes sweet in your mouth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0533_dialogue2">I\'m blessed 
to have a formidable 
ally in you. He he...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0533_dialogue3">Yes, listen to what I say.
Only I speak the truth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0023_dialogue1">Don\'t worry, I won\'t
hurt you... Or will I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0023_dialogue2">May luck be
on MY side!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0023_dialogue3">Mhe he...
I like my cola
extra carbonated!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0179_dialogue1">Science is fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0179_dialogue2">I\'ve succeeded in
developing a new CookieBot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0179_dialogue3">Oh? Are you interested
in CookieBots?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1011_dialogue1">One cannot reach
true understanding
without experience.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1011_dialogue2">One must always
maintain serenity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1011_dialogue3">The more one learns,
the less one knows.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0188_dialogue1">I work better alone.
It\'s TRUE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0188_dialogue2">Let\'s search for
the perfect home!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0188_dialogue3">I will find the best
memories for building!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0199_dialogue1">Our team is gonna be
the best of the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0199_dialogue2">Why... Why did we
lose this match...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0199_dialogue3">Practice is the only way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0058_dialogue1">There aren\'t 
any ghosts here...
are there?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0058_dialogue2">Don\'t go...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0058_dialogue3">I don\'t want to be alone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0171_dialogue1">May I be of assistance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0171_dialogue2">My glasses are...
Ah, on my head.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0171_dialogue3">*Tsk* A crease.
I must fetch an iron.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0190_dialogue1">All young Cookies deserve love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0190_dialogue2">Love warms up the
coldest winter day! AHAHA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0190_dialogue3">I can deliver everything
without gettin\' caught!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWAR_cookie0401_dialogue1">Khhhhh... Prhhh... Not bad.
You\'re a pretty tough Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWAR_cookie0401_dialogue2">*Cough, cough*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CWAR_cookie0401_dialogue3">You\'re looking for a lab?
... There\'s one still intact in L.J.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0265_dialogue1">Nut-nut!
Nut-nut-nut?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0265_dialogue2">Nuut? Nut-nut?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0265_dialogue3">Nut-nut...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0513_dialogue1">Yes, I\'m here. 
What now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0513_dialogue2">What is it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0513_dialogue3">You, too, like
the aroma?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0106_dialogue1">Kyou-kya! Kyou-kya?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0106_dialogue2">Dooooo! 
Dooo DA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0106_dialogue3">Dooooooon Dooogh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531_dialogue1">Oh no no no, wouldn\'t
recommend wandering
the museum after dark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531_dialogue2">... A leftover Jelly
does NOT qualify
as a relic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531_dialogue3">Ancient artifacts
require utmost caution
and care!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531s01_dialogue1">Ah, history...!
Makes me lose
track of time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531s01_dialogue2">Now, where are
my spectacles?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0531s01_dialogue3">I am a scholar.
I am a Cookie of class!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0260_dialogue1">It is my duty
to study the stars.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0260_dialogue2">Astronomy is more than
just simply looking
at the stars.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0260_dialogue3">The stars existed long
before any form of magic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0034_dialogue1">Magic?! Hah!
Only alchemy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0034_dialogue2">Alchemy is
a SERIOUS science!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0034_dialogue3">We might even
discover a new
element today!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0032_dialogue1">You wish to know
the future?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0032_dialogue2">Although, my wisdom
is too great to believe...
Believe it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0032_dialogue3">Set your eyes
on your goal.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0053_dialogue1">I\'ll show you my
tennis skills!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0053_dialogue2">Hi! I\'m Orange Cookie!
What\'s your name?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0053_dialogue3">I\'ve got sun-cream
in my dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0077_dialogue1">Cucumbers are great for
quenching your thirst!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0077_dialogue2">What do you mean
I\'m too young for fishing?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0077_dialogue3">The most important
thing to bring fishing?
Knowing how to relax.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0539_dialogue1">Oyster Cookie.
I believe that no further
introduction is required.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0539_dialogue2">Words are weapons.
Use them wisely.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0539_dialogue3">The road to peace
is long and arduous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0250_dialogue1">Nanny!
Tell me that story again, please?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0250_dialogue2">I like the story of
the pretty mermaid.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0250_dialogue3">Tell it again, please?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0124_dialogue1">I\'m... Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0124_dialogue2">I\'m starving...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0124_dialogue3">Into... water...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0228_dialogue1">Pleased to meet you.
I am Okchun Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0228_dialogue2">The world is so much
greater than our village!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0228_dialogue3">I will do everything in my
power to help those in need!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225z01_dialogue1">Have you ever witnessed
pure radiance...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225z01_dialogue2">Coral Staff...
Illuminate our paths!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0225z01_dialogue3">With the radiant light of coral,
I shall purify the sea...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0590_dialogue1">I bet there\'s a lot
to be found beneath
this soil!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0590_dialogue2">Do I see... a fellow
archaeologist?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0590_dialogue3">The most exciting
part is when your
shovel hits something!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535_dialogue1">If you need something,
keep it brief.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535_dialogue2">What?
No, I am not angry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535_dialogue3">For the glory of the
Hollyberry Kingdom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535s01_dialogue1">Never once have
I questioned my path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535s01_dialogue2">Strength alone does
not bring victory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0535s01_dialogue3">Juice and parties
are not my thing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0104_dialogue1">Yoga heals the mind,
body, and soul!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0104_dialogue2">Close your eyes 
and listen to your body.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0104_dialogue3">Yoga is the restriction
of the fluctuations
of consciousness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0140_dialogue1">I need something... unique!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0140_dialogue2">Bear Jellies again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0140_dialogue3">Tired? Here, you can
ride my flying carpet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0026_dialogue1">Nature will protect us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0026_dialogue2">Ah... The feeling of
warm sunlight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0026_dialogue3">Let\'s take care of 
nature together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0596_dialogue1">You have my
attention.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0596_dialogue2">I do not spread my
wings without need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0596_dialogue3">It is by Witches\' grace
that I have my duty
and my kingdom.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0001_dialogue1">Bravery comes
naturally!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0001_dialogue2">Star Jellies?!
YUM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0001_dialogue3">Adventures?!
AWESOME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0001s01_dialogue1">Hope we won\'t
meet the Witch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0001s01_dialogue2">I\'m no ordinary 
cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0001s01_dialogue3">Cookies!
Follow my lead!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0001z10_dialogue1">Of course,
