  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Story">Born from the lush energy of a leafy summer forest, this Cookie carries the lively flutter and rhythm of forest bat wings deep within his dough. The playful essence of those wings gifted him a mischievous, troublemaking nature, while the gentle shade of summer bestowed a surprisingly soft and tender heart.

He usually spends his days grumbling and whining about Berrygalia House being so packed with junk there\'s barely room to walk. Still, whenever he gets chance, you can find him pulling pranks on his friends as part of his daily routine. And yet, once the mischief is done, he always makes sure to write a letter of apology to those very same friends.

Maybe that\'s why it\'s impossible to truly dislike Bramble Bat Cookie after all!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Get">If you get stuck here,
don\'t say I didn\'t warn ya!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Random.01">Don\'t just blurt things
out at me like that!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Random.02">Careful. You can\'t just walk
into Berrygalia House...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Random.03">ARRRGH!
Smarty called me a simpleton again!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Random.04">If you meet First Berry Cookie,
remember to be nice!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Random.05">SSSHHH!
Don\'t make Mistletoe Cookie angry...!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Ugh...
I just slipped, okay?!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Monologue.Greeting">Where have you been,
{0}?!</string>
