  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.001.Story">A tent where Bramble Bat Cookie and his forest bat friends spend countless hours playing together. As the bats grew up, the tent\'s colors changed and the glow of its leaves shifted, but the cheerful stories and pure laughter remain within it as timeless memories.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.002.Story">Lay down the biggest, sturdiest leaves, raise the canopy, and voila! A verdant and sturdy secret hangout where Bramble Bat Cookie and his forest bat friends can play to their hearts\' content!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Wallpaper.001.Story">A sturdy wall made from sun-soaked summer tree trunks. Lean against it to enjoy the cooling shade and hear the soft whispers of the summer wind weaving through the trees.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Deck.001.Story">A floor crafted from only the freshest summer leaves. Soft underfoot and filled with a gentle, refreshing scent, it delivers comfort with every step!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.001.Story">Leafy vines bearing round lantern fruits. Their soft, gentle green glow seems to soothe the soul.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.003.Story">A full-length mirror shaped like a forest bat. It used to look different, but Bramble Bat Cookie insisted on reshaping it. It cracked a little in the process, but he\'s still perfectly satisfied with admiring the mirror, and himself, every morning.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.002.Story">The way to Berrygalia House is always dim! To avoid getting lost, befriending the fireflies is a must! This firefly-friendly cage helps illuminate the forest path. It\'s also filled with fresh, moist soil that the fireflies love.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Wall.001.Story">A lovingly handmade plush of a forest bat. Bramble Bat Cookie used to carry it everywhere, so it\'s burst at the seams more than once... Even now, the stuffing sometimes pokes out, but each time, someone takes the time and effort to quietly stitch it back together.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.004.Story">A window made from sturdy wood. This window also serves as an entrance for flying critters! The sky peeks through the lush foliage of the forest, filling anyone who looks out the window with a sense of peace.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Wall.002.Story">A dartboard adorned with a leaf shaped like a bat. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.003.Story">A swing made with wood and vines. Everyone loves to swing on it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.005.Story">A place to hang clothes, adorned with some berries. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.006.Story">A table made from a berry tree\'s stump. A great choice for decorating any room.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Floor.007.Story">An old toy box that\'s been used for many years. Just looking at it brings good memories back.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.004.Story">A vine for forest bats to rest. Let\'s put it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Wall.003.Story">A leaf with a map drawn on it. Where does it lead to?</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Rug.001.Story">A rug made from leaves used to hide a sneaky trap. Watch your step!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2027">Bramble Bat Cookie\'s Room of Verdant Cheeriness</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2027.Story">Bramble Bat Cookie\'s room stays fresh, lively, and verdant all year round. But upon entering, it seems like the room is hiding a hidden agenda: a map leading out from Berrygalia House, a trap meant to prank unsuspecting visitors... But in truth, this is a secret hideout where Bramble Bat Cookies plays with his forest bat friends. It\'s packed with cherished dolls, toys, and stacks of leafy stationery for writing letters after arguing with friends. Never judge a Cookie, or his room, by appearance alone!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.001">Berry Bow Tie</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.002">Worn Forest Bat Doll</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.003">Forest Bat Hand Mirror</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.001.Story">A bow tie adorned with a ripe and plump berry grown in the soil of Berrygalia House. It\'s woven with fresh grass and vines, adding a verdant and lively touch.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.002.Story">A forest bat plush carefully mended with intricate stitches. It was the very first gift Bramble Bat Cookie ever received from First Berry Cookie. It\'s said to be Bramble Bat Cookie\'s most treasured possession.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2027.003.Story">At some point, this mirror became a must-have for Bramble Bat Cookie. He often checked his appearance wherever he went. After seeing this, the sharp-eyed Smarty muttered, \"Must be that age,\" and walked away.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2027.TeddyBear">Bramble Bat Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Season.2027.Complete.Profile">Completed Bramble Bat Collection</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Soulstone">Bramble Bat Cookie\'s Souldrop</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.999">Bramble Bat Cookie\'s Room Sign</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2027.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles Bramble Bat Cookie. Despite wearing a mischievous grin, there\'s a hint of gentle warmth and kindness shining through.</string>
  <string name="$Season.2027.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the Bramble Bat Collection. A caring heart for the friends you\'re concerned with is commendable, but the courage to take responsibility is truly impressive!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of Bramble Bat Cookie\'s soul. You can hear a mischievous chuckle and the light flapping of wings coming from it.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2027.Ceil.999.Story">Welcome to Bramble Bat Cookie\'s Room of Verdant Cheeriness!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Profile">Bramble Bat Cookie</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2027.Frame">Bramble Bat Cookie</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.Main">The Rascal and the Devil</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.01">A Chance for Mischief</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.02">It\'s a Trap?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.03">Not Such a Rascal After All?</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.01.Summary">Devil Cookie accidentally stumbles into Bramble Bat Cookie\'s room. With leaves everywhere, it looks like the perfect place to hide and pull a prank. It\'s the perfect chance for a little mischief!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.02.Summary">Though he\'s yet to appear, Bramble Bat Cookie proves he isn\'t an easy target. Hiding amongst the leaves was a trap! Why would anyone set up a trap in their own room?!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Title.03.Summary">An unexpected side of Bramble Bat Cookie comes to light. Devil Cookie can\'t handle what follows...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Illust.Dialog.01">I\'m sorry for always
whining and saying
mean things...</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2027.Illust.Dialog.02">YUCK! I can feel the
niceness crawling
under my dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_1">Hmmm...? What is this place? I was heading back to my room and... I guess I made a wrong turn?! I need to get out of here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_2">Wait a second! Before I leave... Hehehe! This room\'s full of leaves and grass. Perfect for hiding and scaring whoever lives here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_3">Hehehe...! Where should I hide? Here? Over there...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_4">Alright, this spot\'ll do! Now I just stay put and wait for whoever owns this room to show up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_5">... Hold on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_1_POR1_6">WHAT IS THIS?!?!?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_1">These leaves under the mirror... They\'re hiding a TRAP! Yikes! I almost fell in.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_2">What kind of Cookie rigs their room with traps?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_3">And what\'s with this weird map? Is this Cookie planning an escape or something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_4">Ugh... Today\'s been the WORST!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_5">Eeek! I need to hide!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_6">Wait... Why am I hiding again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_7">Why won\'t First Berry Cookie ever listen to me?! I ended up getting angry and snapped at her again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_8">Haaah...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_9">Ack...! He\'s coming this way?! I should move and—No, wait! I can just scare him now! Hehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_10">Huh... This thing is... Hm, First Berry Cookie gave it to me awhile back. I thought I threw this old, tattered thing away?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_11">Huh? He went the other way? What\'s he looking at...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_2_POR1_12">A doll...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_1">It\'s been stitched up... And pretty well too. I can tell it\'s First Berry Cookie\'s handiwork. Oh, there\'s a note attached?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_2">"Dear Bramble Bat Cookie. I made this doll to remember the day we first met. I\'m always sorry, and forever thankful."</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_3">... Wow. I didn\'t even stop to think how she felt, or what she was thinking. All I ever do is snap and complain... and think about leaving Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_4">Huh? This Cookie is...? What\'s with the sudden warm and fuzzy feelgood vibes...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_5">That settles it. I\'ve gotta write a letter back and apologize for being such a bad friend!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_6">Ghrrrk...! Th-This Cookie is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_7">He\'s got the horns, the attitude...! He looks like trouble...! BUT HE\'S ACTUALLY NICE?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_8">Dear... First... Berry... Cookie... It\'s me... Bramble Bat... Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_9">I\'m sorry for... always whining... and saying mean things... From now on... I\'ll try to...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_10">YUCK! I can feel the niceness crawling under my dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2027_3_POR1_11">I\'m never coming near this room again!!! FOREVER!</string>
  <string name="Key"></string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0584_dialogue1">So much new stuff to see!
This place is GREAT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0584_dialogue2">What\'s the shiniest thing
you\'ve got around here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0584_dialogue3">I just let my hair
flow when I\'m
underwater!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0073_dialogue1">Don\'t you just
want to dance?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0073_dialogue2">Just a hint of rose...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0073_dialogue3">Have you ever
danced under 
bright moonlight?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0583_dialogue1">Deep or shallow,
plants can be found
in any waters!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0583_dialogue2">Watching the
swaying seaweed
soothes the mind.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0583_dialogue3">You\'d love to see
the Berry Anemones
in the seas depths!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8001_dialogue1">I just love
the scent of flowers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8001_dialogue2">Each and every scent
is unique in its own way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8001_dialogue3">Let\'s sit and
chat for a while!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0158_dialogue1_1">The Crème Republic\'s power</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0158_dialogue1_2">surpasses that of any
kingdom in history.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0158_dialogue2">... Hm?
Have you business with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0158_dialogue3">ARGH!
All this stress is making
my dough brittle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3009_dialogue1">One day... I\'ll stand at
the pinnacle of Lactose.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3009_dialogue2">I will change everything...
with these two fists.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3009_dialogue3">Tch... Fools.
How pathetic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0133_dialogue1">Urrrrgh...!
I hate stupid, sunny weather!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0133_dialogue2">I CAN\'T TAKE IT ANYMORE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0133_dialogue3">Finally!
It\'s GO TIME!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0005_dialogue1_1">Never let a Cookie\'s
smile fool you...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0005_dialogue1_2">I\'m a prime example. Ha.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0005_dialogue2">You\'re not so lacking
in talent. Try approaching
it from a different angle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0005_dialogue3">Hmm... This appears
most suitable for your
current capabilities.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8003_dialogue1">You won\'t find a
better pipa player in
the whole Flower City!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8003_dialogue2">Pretty ornaments
will highlight
your best features!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8003_dialogue3">You\'re asking me
to keep playing?
Hm, maybe...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8002_dialogue1">I wonder what kind of
news the pigeons
will bring this time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8002_dialogue2">Have you seen a...
grumpy, blue Cookie
by any chance?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie8002_dialogue3">I prefer staying
home to any adventures.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0381_dialogue1">NOBODY MOVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0381_dialogue2">Sweet Jelly of mine!
There\'s jam everywhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0381_dialogue3">We will begin with
checking your alibis!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0640_dialogue1">Beware of mold.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0640_dialogue2">There is no life
without suffering.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0640_dialogue3">We don\'t 
deserve freedom.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0221_dialogue1">Muh muh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0221_dialogue2">Agoo... Oooh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0221_dialogue3">Dadada! Dada!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0585_dialogue1">Cookies are everywhere,
even in the deep,
dark void of the sea.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0585_dialogue2">Even a small 
splash of a fin can
cause a tsunami!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0585_dialogue3">The way of the
water is unstoppable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2026_dialogue1">Do you know
who I am too...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2026_dialogue2">I will make new memories,
one by one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2026_dialogue3">Sometimes, what comes to you
arrives only after you have
let something go.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0641_dialogue1">... What is it now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0641_dialogue2">Is there life...
beyond orders?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0641_dialogue3">The locals are
sluggish beings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_pet0139_dialogue1">Hrru pruuu hrr...
(I shall confirm how strong
you have become.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_pet0139_dialogue2">Hrru hrrp pruuu... Hrru hrrp...
(You rarely look this weary...
Come, take a sip of tea.)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_pet0139_dialogue3">Hrrrp prrruuu! Hrru hrrp!
(Those two...! How admirable,
how very admirable...!)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0436_dialogue1_1">Huh...? No!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0436_dialogue1_2">My hand, it\'s turned
to flour already...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0436_dialogue2">Am I... disappearing?
Just like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0436_dialogue3">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0435_dialogue1">But how come... I suddenly feel at peace knowing I no longer have anything to protect...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0435_dialogue2">I am sorry that I have
failed to remain by
your side until the end...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0435_dialogue3">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0017_dialogue1">It is a piece to express how
happy I am to meet all of you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0017_dialogue2">This is a piece that
expresses the sound of
waves with drums!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0017_dialogue3_1">It was short, but it
was so much fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0017_dialogue3_2">(Dumm dumm rat-a-tat-tat)</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s01_dialogue1">Have you heard
about the Banquet
of the Witches?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s01_dialogue2">Truth can change
anyone... Ha ha.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s01_dialogue3">Darkness shall pass,
leaving Freedom in
its wake!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s02_dialogue1">I\'ve always wondered why we, Cookies, are so weak.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s02_dialogue2">Even Dark Moon Magic has its uses...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0109s02_dialogue3">Everyone has limits.
But I can set us free.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookienew0109_dialogue1">I have seen the truth
at the Banquet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookienew0109_dialogue2">Soon, we, Cookies,
will rule this world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookienew0109_dialogue3">Tell me, child.
Are you afraid?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0282_dialogue1">My blade shall never
rust so long as evil
remains in this world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0282_dialogue2">Who am I, you ask?
Hmm... Just a passing
Cookie, that\'s all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0282_dialogue3">Have the flexibility to be
shaken, but the fortitude
to never be broken.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0388_dialogue1">I, Carameleon Cookie, am the Master of Survival in the land of Beast-Yeast,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0388_dialogue2">Hey, listen to what I\'m saying!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0388_dialogue3">My SIZE?!
I\'m almost as big as you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0074_dialogue1">It\'s not the crown,
but the adventure
I crave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0074_dialogue2">I wonder what lies
beyond the palace walls...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0074_dialogue3">If only I could
decide my fate...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0617_dialogue1">The outside world is...
SO COOL, fi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0617_dialogue2">I brought lassi
from my village, fi!
Lassi party, cool!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0617_dialogue3">Would you like
a cup of lassi, fi?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593_dialogue1">Each ivory key 
should be played 
with purpose.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593_dialogue2">What do I like other 
than playing the piano?
... Mystery novels.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593_dialogue3">A pre-performance
ritual? I have one,
but it\'s a secret.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593s01_dialogue1">I used to play in 
juice bars. A different
one every night.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593s01_dialogue2">I never stop
practicing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0593s01_dialogue3">A crispy outer layer of technique with a delicate, creamy filling of emotion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0194_dialogue1">Crow or Cookie...
Does it really even matter?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0194_dialogue2">I get tingles inside
whenever I see shiny things.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0194_dialogue3">Do I need a reason for
liking shiny things?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0166_dialogue1">Optical protection is a
requirement for time travel.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0166_dialogue2">Ever seen a
time rift?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0166_dialogue3">I will become the
greatest time engineer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0166z01_dialogue1">I\'ll do anything to put
time back on its tracks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0166z01_dialogue2">This is all possible thanks
to everyone at the TBD!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0166z01_dialogue3">The Director has to be
the first to make a move!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157_dialogue1">Do you like
merry-go-rounds?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157_dialogue2">Thank you
for coming...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157_dialogue3">Will you play
with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157s01_dialogue1">What is your
unforgettable
memory?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157s01_dialogue2">Memories light the way ahead...
Just like the stars.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0157s01_dialogue3">Would you know the stars shine if you didn\'t look at the night sky?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2019_dialogue1">One day, my show will make
everyone laugh and cheer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2019_dialogue2">Uh-oh! Can someone please
pick up my drumstick?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2019_dialogue3">Today\'s show will feature
an all-new performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie1004_dialogue1">See something
sparkling?
That\'s my blade!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie1004_dialogue2">I wanna be a
Cookie everyone
can rely on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie1004_dialogue3">I should always 
lead by example!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0582_dialogue1">... A two-legged Cookie?
Don\'t come near.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0582_dialogue2">First time seeing
a Gem Mermaid?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0582_dialogue3">I have left the
Duskgloom sea... 
and come here, far away.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0512_dialogue1">Shall I sing a
song for you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0512_dialogue2">"They followed the wind, 
they followed the river..."</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0512_dialogue3">This very moment
deserves a ballad!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0536_dialogue1">My name is Clotted Cream
Cookie, elected Consul of
the Crème Republic.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0536_dialogue2">A day is not properly
finished without dessert
with soft cream on top.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0536_dialogue3">Much of my work involves
oratory, hence the need to
take care of my voice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0043_dialogue1">I follow my road!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0043_dialogue2">The whole world
is my home!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0043_dialogue3">This helmet saved
my life many times.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0257_dialogue1">Anythin\' with a crust is a
pie if you want it to be!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0257_dialogue2">The best pies come
from the heart,
not a silly recipe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0257_dialogue3">Weird\'s a compliment!
It\'s just another way
people say you\'re special!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0579_dialogue1">There\'s no retirement
for dragon hunters
like myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0579_dialogue2">My scar? 
Well that\'s a long story.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0579_dialogue3_1">Remember.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0579_dialogue3_2">If you don\'t hunt the dragons, 
they\'ll hunt you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0636_dialogue1">I thank the
Godly Creators
for the gift of life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0636_dialogue2">The Godly Creators
await you with open arms!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0636_dialogue3">May my dough 
become an instrument 
of Divine Will...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0038_dialogue1">A whole new world
to explore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0038_dialogue2">A brand-new map!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0038_dialogue3">Shh! You didn\'t see me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0038z01_dialogue1">I got all my stuff!
Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0038z01_dialogue2">Cookies say there\'s a
lion inside this cave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0038z01_dialogue3">I practiced rope
tossing a lot!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0163_dialogue1">My, my.
It\'s time to feed
my spiders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0163_dialogue2">Please do not look
under the bed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0163_dialogue3">Would you like to
rest up in my manor
until the rain stops?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527_dialogue1_1">I\'m Twizzly Gummy Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527_dialogue1_2">And you ain\'t
seen nothin\' yet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527_dialogue2">Life\'s a game...
A game of survival!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527_dialogue3">Peace?
More like... PIECES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527s01_dialogue1">Charged, primed,
and ready for crime!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527s01_dialogue2">I\'M FROM THE FUTURE!
Don\'t you forget it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0527s01_dialogue3">Which world should I
port over to next?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0021_dialogue1">It is our duty to
protect Cookies,
no matter what!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0021_dialogue2">From formation
to frontline,
we move as one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0021_dialogue3">We endure with or
without special oil!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0191_dialogue1">It\'s Reindeer Delivery,
fast and reliable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0191_dialogue2">Punctuality is key to
successful delivery.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0191_dialogue3">No time to fool around.
Gifts won\'t deliver 
themselves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0083_dialogue1">I will cut down every
trace of wickedness...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0083_dialogue2">Aigoo... There\'s a foul
energy spread thick
across this place...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0083_dialogue3">You...
You\'re not alone, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0523_dialogue1_1">Pretty toppings,
sweet and lovely!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0523_dialogue1_2">I\'m Parfait Cookie,
and don\'t you forget it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0523_dialogue2">I\'ll play some colorful
melodies for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0523_dialogue3">Be careful, or I might
get stuck in your head!☆</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0631_dialogue1">Wherever there\'s love,
that\'s where I\'ll be!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0631_dialogue2">Heh, I just LOVE the
tragic kinds of love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0631_dialogue3">No hate, only love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0216_dialogue1">I can\'t imagine a world
without fluttery lace...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0216_dialogue2">If it\'s not cute,
what\'s the point?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0216_dialogue3">The origin of my inspiration
is the loveliness of Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0105_dialogue1">Come on!
Let\'s roll out and
see what\'s out there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0105_dialogue2">The world is full
of beauty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0105_dialogue3">Don\'t follow your dreams, 
chase them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0178_dialogue1">I\'ll become the
greatest scientist ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0178_dialogue2">My bag is no
ordinary bag!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0178_dialogue3">Prepare to
be peppered!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0101_dialogue1">Movies + Popcorn 
= LOVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0101_dialogue2">Like your popcorn
salty or sweet?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0101_dialogue3">Mmm, freshly popped
popcorn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0168_dialogue1">The love of our fans
gives us energy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0168_dialogue2">I hope our fans dig
the next album...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0168_dialogue3_1">Always a sweet smile,
just for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0168_dialogue3_2">We\'re the CAKE POPs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069_dialogue1">He he!
I\'m the cutest Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069_dialogue2">Acorn Jellies
are the best!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069_dialogue3">Look! I\'m flying!
*Whoosh*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069s02_dialogue1">Am I cute?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069s02_dialogue2">Hey, check out
my flight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0069s02_dialogue3">Now gimme lots
of Acorn Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2010_dialogue1">You\'ll regret this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2010_dialogue2">Find... Find...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2010_dialogue3">Find the Cookie of the First Batch—the one who possesses ancient strength...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0528_dialogue1">Oh hello! 
Pompon is excited 
to see you as well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0528_dialogue2">Spooky and cute.
Just the way I like it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0528_dialogue3">I\'m not lonely: 
Pompon is always
with me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0520_dialogue1">I am Pastry Cookie,
your judge and executioner!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0520_dialogue2">In the eyes of the Godly
Makers, we are but the
butter and dough...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0520_dialogue3">You are not allowed
to the Monastery!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0588_dialogue1">Woo... 
I\'m... a mummy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0588_dialogue2">Pasta...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0588_dialogue3">I\'m... a mummy...?
A... Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0259_dialogue1">It\'s so fun picking gifts to
make young Cookies happy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0259_dialogue2">Pretty wrapping paper puts
everyone in the holiday spirit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0259_dialogue3">Wow, Gift Artistry is
so much fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0201_dialogue1">Don\'t mind... me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0201_dialogue2">I\'m used to... heat...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0201_dialogue3">Loneliness...
No time for it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0247_dialogue1">I\'m a sorcerer of the
White Stock Tribe!
What spells do you need?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0247_dialogue2">W-What\'s that?!
Can\'t... can\'t you see it, too?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0247_dialogue3">Confidence is more
important than your
inherent magical power.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0628_dialogue1">For Them...
I shall do anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0628_dialogue2">All this...
Is Their design.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0628_dialogue3">My heart...
shall not waver!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2014_dialogue1">I hope... that my singing can
make the world a better place...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2014_dialogue2">AH! Nooo, you\'re not supposed
to hear my song yet...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2014_dialogue3">Gifts...? I think I like
warm, kindhearted
words more than gifts...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0145_dialogue1">Here a POW! There a POW!
Everywhere a POWPOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0145_dialogue2">Ain\'t a party without
some firecrackers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0145_dialogue3">You can never have
enough firecrackers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0642_dialogue1">All these Cookies...
they aren\'t hurting?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0642_dialogue2">All I\'ve ever known was PAIN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0642_dialogue3">... I don\'t want to crumble...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0147_dialogue1">I wanna become
Ginger Claus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0147_dialogue2">Let\'s sing carols!
*Giggle giggle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0147_dialogue3">Jingle, jingle!
JINGLE BELLS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0576_dialogue1">Am I not the best
potion maker of all time?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0576_dialogue2">The reason potions
are so bitter? Well...
Try and guess.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0576_dialogue3">The preservation
of your crispy crunch
is most important, hm?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0036_dialogue1">Let\'s do something!
What do you wanna do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0036_dialogue2">Gimme Jellies!
Lots and lots!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0036_dialogue3">Let\'s play
with bubbles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0239_dialogue1">Whoah! 
White Lily Cookie is the
top of the class, AGAIN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0239_dialogue2">I think we have similar
interests in magic!
Am I right?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0239_dialogue3">The truth always prevails!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0586_dialogue1">My jellyfish told me
a new story.
Would you like to hear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0586_dialogue2">Yes, I can talk to the jellyfish!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0586_dialogue3">Doesn\'t the rippling moonlight
remind you of a shiny pearl?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1001_dialogue1">I will become the
strongest Banana Warrior!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1001_dialogue2">My Bananarang isn\'t heavy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1001_dialogue3">The Bana Bana tribe
is the greatest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0018_dialogue1">Time for an
amazing performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0018_dialogue2">Even the Witch will be
astonished by
my performance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0018_dialogue3">Practice makes perfect!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0033_dialogue1">It is my sacred duty
to protect the Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0033_dialogue2">The shield to protect
what I love, and the
spear to bring justice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0033_dialogue3">May the divine light
guide me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0196_dialogue1">Hey, got your pizza right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0196_dialogue2">So many pizza orders today...
What\'s the occasion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0196_dialogue3">It\'s tough, but I do it
so I can do the things
I totally wanna do later.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0031_dialogue1">In the name of
Justice and Love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0031_dialogue2">Beam of Love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0031_dialogue3">Who\'ll hold me
when I\'m lonely...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0298_dialogue1">Ha ha ha!
What do you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0298_dialogue2">It\'s an alias from
my monster hunter days!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0298_dialogue3">Call me by this name
while we\'re here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0214_dialogue1">Heh heh! I\'m the strongest
Cookie in the WORLD!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0214_dialogue2">Heh heh!
I have my ways!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0214_dialogue3">Trust me!
I\'m a survival expert!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1010_dialogue1">Who I am?
That\'s none of your business.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1010_dialogue2">I\'ve always done
things my way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1010_dialogue3">I have no intention
to hide forever.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0016_dialogue1">I left my sweet jelly
at the sea bottom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0016_dialogue2">I\'m afraid of nothing!
Not even death!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0016_dialogue3">The ocean awaits!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1007_dialogue1">That was tasty...
But now I\'m sooo sleepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1007_dialogue2">Hey loook!
My belly is all rooound!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CTA_cookie1007_dialogue3">This... this is
my last snack...
I can\'t share it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0063_dialogue1">Hello, Mr. Sunshine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0063_dialogue2">Let\'s go for
a walk!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0063_dialogue3">Today is going to be
a bright, sunny day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0141_dialogue1">Genius detective,
at your service!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0141_dialogue2">Pardon me. May I case
the scene, please?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0141_dialogue3">The culprit is...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0515_dialogue1">I bite hard and
never let go.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0515_dialogue2">Any spicy, red-haired 
Cookies in there!? 
Git on out here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0515_dialogue3">Bounty huntin makes
me some Coin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0047_dialogue1">Hot fists and steel kicks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0047_dialogue2">The oven was just 
a part of my training!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0047_dialogue3">My sister?
I don\'t know where she is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0281_dialogue1">No one\'s better than
Capsaicin Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0281_dialogue2">The air here
smells like... nothing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0281_dialogue3">No more running away...!
These are my true powers, and I\'m not afraid of them anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0206_dialogue1">You think of me
as a Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0206_dialogue2">Only one Cookie
recognized me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0206_dialogue3">Did I startle you?
I am practicing how
to scare Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0062_dialogue1">Timed to perfection.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0062_dialogue2">En garde.
Prêt.
Allez!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0062_dialogue3">Victory is a matter of a moment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0261_dialogue1">*Yaaawn*
... Sooo sleepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0261_dialogue2">Ohhh... I\'m suuure...
it\'ll beeeee fiiiine...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0261_dialogue3">I\'m... hungry...
agaaain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3003_dialogue1">The best cafe on Bluefizz Beach!
Come over to Cafe Fruit Bomber!
Bwahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3003_dialogue2">My cafe crew ran off again?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3003_dialogue3">Cafe Fruit Bomber is
THE place to visit
in Bluefizz Beach!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10425_dialogue1">Whoever enters the laboratory
without permission shall be
PUNISHED!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10425_dialogue2">The student\'s curiosity
against the academy\'s safety...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10425_dialogue3">THE LATTER HAS BEEN
DEEMED A MATTER OF
GREATER IMPORTANCE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538_dialogue1">Financier Cookie,
at your service.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538_dialogue2">House Financier 
will stand by my side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538_dialogue3">I am here on a mission,
not on holiday.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s01_dialogue1">The Light beckons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s01_dialogue2">As a knight, I am bound
by the will of the Light.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s01_dialogue3">The blessing of Light
comes with great
responsibility.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s02_dialogue1">I will follow the radiant Light!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s02_dialogue2">The divine Light
guides my way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0538s02_dialogue3">My oath remains unbroken.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0116_dialogue1">Swans are the most
graceful beings!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0116_dialogue2">Dancing in these sunbeams
is such a delight...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0116_dialogue3">I want to
dance forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534_dialogue1">First Watcher 
Caramel Arrow Cookie.
Awaiting your orders.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534_dialogue2">Protecting the good
Cookies of our kingdom
is my duty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534_dialogue3">A warrior\'s instincts must be
as sharp as an arrow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534s01_dialogue1">The skies are clear today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534s01_dialogue2">My bow represents the
harmony of opposites.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0534s01_dialogue3">I will follow you,
no matter how rough
your path is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0273_dialogue1">Despair in chaos!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0273_dialogue2">I don\'t recall giving you
permission to speak.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0273_dialogue3_1">You cannot comprehend
the power I wield...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0273_dialogue3_2">Simply kneel in despair.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0205_dialogue1">I am Black Garlic Cookie,
ghost professor! </string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0205_dialogue2">As a professor on ghosts,
I have to sound professional
during streams! Ehem!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0205_dialogue3">A sub to my channel
would be... Heavenly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0019_dialogue1">Caramel Syrup Suit ready!
Time to escape!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0019_dialogue2">Heroes aren\'t born,
they\'re made!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0019_dialogue3">Hmm... Gotta find a way
to cut the charging time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3011_dialogue1">
Hey there!
I\'m Platter City\'s star, DJ Miya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3011_dialogue2">Miyaow! ☆</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_COS_cookie3011_dialogue3">BOOM!
Surprised? That\'s how we
say hello in Platter City!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0264_dialogue1">Where is Doughnut No.325?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0264_dialogue2">Step aside, flatster.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0264_dialogue3">Let the Doughnut and
the Doughnut Ball...
CONVERGE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0022_dialogue1">In the past, many a student
came to our city.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0022_dialogue2">Whatever I eat,
falls right through!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0022_dialogue3">Do you wish to hear
a rib-tickling joke?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10435_dialogue1">YOU THERE!
ARE YOU ONE OF
THE INTRUDERS?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10435_dialogue2">The forbidden dimensional portal has been opened and vile spirits let into our world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10435_dialogue3">It is my duty to protect the acedemy and its students from these intruders!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10432_dialogue1">KNOW YOUR ENEMY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10432_dialogue2">Ah, the intruders
everyone is
talking about.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10432_dialogue3">Let us test your
tactical prowess!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10418_dialogue1">THIS IS THE LIBRARY!
SILENCE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10418_dialogue2">WHO IS TALKING? WHO IS
WANDERING IN THE
RESTRICTED SECTION?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10418_dialogue3">I SHALL TEACH YOU
A LESSON!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0380_dialogue1">Well, well! I even have a
special compartment for
my coat! How marvelous.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0380_dialogue2">Then it\'s settled!
Now it\'s about time
to start detecting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0380_dialogue3">NOBODY MOVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0014_dialogue1">I feel like my luck will turn
around from now on! Yes, YES!
I can feel it in my dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0014_dialogue2">Elder? Elder?!
Oh no, the Elder fell asleep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0014_dialogue3">Academics is a
lifelong commitment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0076_dialogue1">You will be called into the courtroom shortly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0076_dialogue2">Order! Everyone, please be quiet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0076_dialogue3">Everyone, step back! The defendant is being escorted!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m50006_dialogue1">Crumbs...!
We\'ve been made!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m50006_dialogue2">Mission failed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m50006_dialogue3">Taste this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0309_dialogue1">Are there... *GULP*
Dragons here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0309_dialogue2">......?!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0309_dialogue3">GAH!
Don\'t scare me like that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40315_dialogue1">I am the Meat Dumpling
King of the East!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40315_dialogue2">I bless good Cookies
and punish the bad!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40315_dialogue3">How dare you attempt to enter
the temple, while so tainted
with convictions of the beyond?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40613_dialogue1">Yess...!
Bring it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40613_dialogue2">You lot get into
fightssss all the time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40613_dialogue3">Why do you all
look like a messss?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0361_dialogue1">Enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0361_dialogue2">Welcome, folks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0361_dialogue3">What was that? I couldn\'t hear it!
We\'re going to need a louder
round of applause!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0002_dialogue1">A match, you say? Count me in!
I wouldn’t miss this for the world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0002_dialogue2">Is there a Gold Honey
Pudding somewhere?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0002_dialogue3">You\'ve got to work that brain of
yours! The same way I work the
sturdy dough of these guns!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0426_dialogue1">Whoops...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0426_dialogue2">Clouds move with the wind,
becoming one,
then becoming two!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0426_dialogue3">Alright! The cloud path is open!
C\'mon, let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0170_dialogue1">Make yourselves at home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0170_dialogue2">If your conviction and
determination are strong, then
you must do what you think is right.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0170_dialogue3">Your instinct is pure and you have
every right to be your own Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0004_dialogue1">He heh heh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0004_dialogue2">Come on in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0004_dialogue3">What can I do for ya?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0009_dialogue1">Interesting.
You are far too...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0009_dialogue2">I hope you are
at least tasty,
stale one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0009_dialogue3">Ah, there you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0059_dialogue1">The hands of greatness, headdress of wisdom, and mountainous shadow will grace us all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0059_dialogue2">Providence smiles upon you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0059_dialogue3">Our secret must not be unveiled...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0002_dialogue1">Weee are the cute and
hap-hap-haaaaaappy
Bear Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0002_dialogue2">Weee make Beeeear Jellies
in our village!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0002_dialogue3">Oh noooo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0003_dialogue1">Order! Order!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0003_dialogue2">Order! ORDER!!!
Stay focused!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0003_dialogue3">If you have evidence,
please present it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_dialogue1">Today shall NEVER
be forgotten! </string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_dialogue2">Tomorrow will also
be NEVER forgotten...
Right?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_dialogue3">Yesterday will NEVER
be forgotten!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0034_dialogue1">Um... Crunchy Cookies!
Can you help me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0034_dialogue2">Could you convince one of the
local ghosts to share some
ice cream with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0034_dialogue3">Thank you!
YUM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0003_dialogue1">HEEHEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0003_dialogue2">Are we playing
hide-and-seek?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0003_dialogue3">We\'re running now!
WHEEE!
TEEHEEHEE!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0011_dialogue1">He he he...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0011_dialogue2">Ow, ow...
My back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0011_dialogue3">Hmph...
Feels like rain today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0002_dialogue1">Whr wu goin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0002_dialogue2">Hrmrmr...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0002_dialogue3">*Nom nom... nom?*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0290_dialogue1">Pling plong! ♪ ♫</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0290_dialogue2">O, nameless land of fire ♪ ♫ ♪</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0290_dialogue3">Where the dragon\'s roar
echoed for three days
and three nights ♪ ♫ ♪</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_1_dialogue1">We\'re made of
finely-spun sugar...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_1_dialogue2">Oh-so-delicate,
four-star sugar...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_1_dialogue3">And if we should happen to,
you know, STRESS OUT?!
We melt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0003_dialogue1">Haha, come on in!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0003_dialogue2">I was just taking a break.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0003_dialogue3">I had my own fair share of
adventures before I 
set up shop in this Square.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0377_dialogue1">If it\'s a final goodbye...
I don\'t want it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0377_dialogue2">I always felt safe and at
peace with you by my side...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0377_dialogue3">Frost Cookie!
Frost Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0431_dialogue1">I request His Majesty\'s council.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0431_dialogue2">Greetings, Your Majesty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0431_dialogue3">Take this. It\'s a cacao tablet
made by the Healer Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0432_dialogue1">Sometimes, you must
take the road you\'ve
already traveled.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0432_dialogue2">Long ago, a vessel was built
specifically to cross the dark
waters of the Licorice Sea...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0432_dialogue3">We must plan for
what lies ahead.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0433_dialogue1">Remember to avoid the
areas marked red on the
map at all costs.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0433_dialogue2">I had faith that you
would return safely...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0433_dialogue3">And now...
Where do you intend to go?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0174_dialogue1">I er... I... Well... How is he?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0174_dialogue2">I would like to meet him,
to see him after so long would-</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0174_dialogue3">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0328_dialogue1">Will you... tell me your story?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0328_dialogue2">The soft current washing over
my dough, the gentle waves...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0328_dialogue3">... Little Moon.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0114_dialogue1">Perhaps... it is a good omen.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0114_dialogue2">Know that no matter what happens,
I shall be there for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0114_dialogue3">Why, a few days ago,
albeit shortly, I felt as if the
Light was strong once again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0005_dialogue1">Hiii!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0005_dialogue2">I\'m huuungry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0005_dialogue3">Do you liiike myyy ribbon???</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0274_dialogue1">Psh! Cut it out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0274_dialogue2">OBVIOUSLY,
Scovillia is the BEST!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0274_dialogue3">Show them the
meaning of SPICE!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0172_dialogue1">Come and sit!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0172_dialogue2">Let auntie make
you a full meal!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0172_dialogue3">Oh, Divines!
How could such a
dreadful thing happen?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0173_dialogue1">You could\'ve at least
written us of your arrival...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0173_dialogue2">You must be so
tired and hungry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0173_dialogue3">You know what they say.
A well-fed stomach is a stomach
well-suited for great deeds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0171_dialogue1">How could they just send off a
young and delicate Cookie
to travel across the world?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0171_dialogue2">You know, I\'ve been receiving
dancing lessons recently!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0171_dialogue3">We\'ve more food to come
and plenty to go around!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m51070_dialogue1">Shacka shacka shacka
shacka shacka shacka!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m51070_dialogue2">HEAR THIS SOUND?
IT GOES SHACKA SHACKA  ♪ ♫</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m51070_dialogue3">OVERLORD OF THE MARACAS!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0033_dialogue1">Allow me to introduce myself!
My name is
Maestro Sugar Gnome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0033_dialogue2">I shall truly endeavor to use all
my superb craftsmanship to erect
a bee-you-ti-ful castle just for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0033_dialogue3">So, so happy to see you again,
dear Cookies! Dippiti-do!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0357_dialogue1">Warning! Warning!
Public offense detected!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0357_dialogue2">You will receive
twenty penalty points!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0357_dialogue3">Alert. Alert.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0358_dialogue1">Deploying a clean-up unit.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0358_dialogue2">Targets captured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0358_dialogue3">Please specify destination.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0359_dialogue1">Crime reported.
Crime reported.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0359_dialogue2">Your Radiance\'s order shall
be carried out immediately.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0359_dialogue3">Evacuate. Evacuate. 
Deploying the evacuation unit...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0360_dialogue1">Safety protocol: in action.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0360_dialogue2">Move. Move.
Securing path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0360_dialogue3">Protect. Protect.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40316_dialogue1">I am the Spicy Dumpling
King of the South!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40316_dialogue2">My armor is impenetrable,
and I bring all things to life!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40316_dialogue3">You must wash yourself clean
of all worldly concerns!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0129_dialogue1">HA HA HA HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0129_dialogue2">Taste spicy steel!
HYAAA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0129_dialogue3">GLORY TO THE MALA TRIBE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0188_dialogue1">What with this mud today?
It\'s not as chunky or as silty as usual!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0188_dialogue2">Who\'s that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0188_dialogue3">OI! What do you think
you\'re doing, messin\' up
our operation and everything?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0189_dialogue1">If we smell anything fishy...
we\'re gonna tell everyone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0189_dialogue2">*Scoff*
Gettin\' mighty tired of living off
scraps and leftover sugar...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0189_dialogue3">This is a legitimate business!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0008_dialogue1">Hey there!
C\'mon in, we\'ve been waiting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0008_dialogue2">Relics are sometimes more
beautiful when they\'re unknown.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0008_dialogue3">Don\'t worry about it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0564_dialogue1">Our Commander cherishes
you all too much! Hmph!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0564_dialogue2">Lord Commander is
a very busy Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0564_dialogue3">Ha ha ha!
Lord Commander and his
dreadful sense of humor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0009_dialogue1">Chirp...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0009_dialogue2">Chirp, chirp?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0009_dialogue3">Chirp! Chirp! Chirp!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0135_dialogue1">Welcome, welcome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0135_dialogue2">You\'re in the right place if
you\'ve come for clothes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0135_dialogue3">Please visit the Mont Blanc
Boutique again for any of
your stylish needs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0019_dialogue1">You have avoided our traps.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0019_dialogue2">A bad sign!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0019_dialogue3">The Sacred Tree will decide.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0020_dialogue1">There was a Cookie who
caused a terrible tragedy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0020_dialogue2">I can hardly bear to remember
that dreadful nightmare.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0020_dialogue3">I sense a curse of
tremendous potency.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0024_dialogue1">I\'m the Gatekeeper.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0024_dialogue2">I can\'t let you pass.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0024_dialogue3">Bye!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0440_dialogue1">HO HO HO HO HO HO!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0440_dialogue2">I\'ve spent at least a
thousand years playing Go,
you think I\'d lose to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0440_dialogue3">A lost youngster?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0175_dialogue1">Well, well, well...!
Look who\'s back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0175_dialogue2">We may have differences in
our dough, but in the end,
we all become crumbs.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0175_dialogue3">That\'s true of everyone,
everywhere. You, me, us, them...
We\'re all heading the same direction.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0118_dialogue1">Pfft, you don\'t have to thank me,
I did what every Cookie of an
esteemed berry house would do.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0118_dialogue2">Hey! Watch it there!
More debris falling from above!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0118_dialogue3">Hmm, that one\'s got some
pretty good moves...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0157_dialogue1">A pleasure to meet you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0157_dialogue2">I came to pray for those less fortunate; the Cookies who are suffering in pain and sadness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0157_dialogue3">I shall do everything
I can to aid you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0159_dialogue1">Who are these Cookies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0159_dialogue2">It is only natural we have a
say in the Ancient Heroes\'
usage of Soul Jam!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0159_dialogue3">To share this prayer
with the two of you...
It brings a tear to my eyes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0056_dialogue1">Terrible news!
Such HORRID, awful news!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0056_dialogue2">We need to hurry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0056_dialogue3">There\'s an airship
waiting under the castle!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0425_dialogue1">Enough of your insolence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0425_dialogue2">The sky god
knows all and sees all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0425_dialogue3">Land-dweller Cookies always
think that praying to the sky will
make all their wishes come true...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0162_dialogue1">How may I help you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0162_dialogue2">Are you injured? I can treat
your wounds if you wish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0162_dialogue3">There are many more patients
that need tending than usual...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0459_dialogue1">Did you know the Land of Little
Big Dreams is actually the
Land of Big Little Dreams?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0459_dialogue2">The Sugar Swan is actually
made of honey, not sugar!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0459_dialogue3">Say, did you know there
are actually no wizards 
in the City of Wizards?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0161_dialogue1">A perfect opportunity
for our Republic to
prove its supremacy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0161_dialogue2_1">By applying enough pressure,
even compressed sugar can</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0161_dialogue2_2">become one of the hardest
materials known to Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0161_dialogue3">MY passion is to create
something new!
Something... from nothing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0046_dialogue1">Oh, wow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0046_dialogue2">Here in the Vanilla Kingdom,
we have plenty of Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0046_dialogue3">Now we can conjure
spells too! They\'re basic
and simple, but still!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0047_dialogue1">The usual?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0047_dialogue2">We have plenty of beds to spare!
Just pick one and take a
nap anytime you\'d like!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0047_dialogue3">I brought more Raisin Jellies!
Where should I put them?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0048_dialogue1">Take this!
And that! AND THAT!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0048_dialogue2">I never realized
how fun studying is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0048_dialogue3">Don\'t forget to bring gifts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0049_dialogue1">Our houses don\'t fall
apart in the middle of
the day anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0049_dialogue2">All thanks to
Pure Vanilla Cookie!
He\'s been very kind to us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0049_dialogue3">Ta-da!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0050_dialogue1">Let\'s just keep doing our part!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0050_dialogue2">One by one!
Let\'s not rush things!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0050_dialogue3">Tell us what it\'s like
flying on an airship!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0568_dialogue1">He he...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0568_dialogue2">Commander!
Here, Commander!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0568_dialogue3">...! Who are you?
I\'ve never seen
you around before...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0326_dialogue1">Hey! Black Lemonade Cookie!
Wait up!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0326_dialogue2">MY PICK IS GONE!!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0326_dialogue3">My lucky lemon pick is GONE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0221_dialogue1">Why don\'t we all calm down
and count the sheep...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0221_dialogue2">Have you heard?
Someone defeated a
notorious space villain!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0221_dialogue3">He he... I\'m so thankful
for an opportunity to travel!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40314_dialogue1">I am the Chives Dumpling
King of the North!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40314_dialogue2">I became a light for Cookies
wandering in the dark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40314_dialogue3">Put aside the anguish
that troubles your mind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0117_dialogue1">I used my new overnight yogurt
mask—which is, like the totally
hottest beauty trend these days.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0117_dialogue2">I need... to...
show off my cuteness!
And YOU\'RE IN MY WAY!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0117_dialogue3">YOU THERE!
WHATCHA STARING AT?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0424_dialogue1">Heh... Gladly! Dousing the earth
with rain is my sworn duty!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0424_dialogue2">Thank you.
I do enjoy my work very much.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0424_dialogue3">Ah ha ha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0160_dialogue1">Welcome.
I am Sablé Cookie,
Elder of the Arts.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0160_dialogue2">The Cookies of the Crème
Republic spend their days
with happiness and delight.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0160_dialogue3">We are the only nation for such
a sophisticated yet elegant and
dignified culture to call home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40313_dialogue1">I am the Shrimp Dumpling
King of the West!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40313_dialogue2">My breath becomes the wind
and blows away all evil spirits!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40313_dialogue3">Far I have seen, but never
one with such a heavy heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0438_dialogue1">I can tell you\'re a beginner at Go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0438_dialogue2">Ho ho! 
I can\'t wait to steam in the
waters of the Hot Springs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0438_dialogue3">You must return in
300 years time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0468_dialogue1">HA HA!
AHA HA HA HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0468_dialogue2">I shall deliver you at my master\'s
feet, and he will shower
me with glory and praise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0468_dialogue3">YOU WON\'T GET AWAY!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0376_dialogue1">Ah... this is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0376_dialogue2">My body is only getting
colder and colder...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0376_dialogue3">I must walk further into
the icy wasteland...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0217_dialogue1">This is gonna be
the best trip ever!
But... did I overpack?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0217_dialogue2">WAAAAAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0217_dialogue3">WAAAAAAAAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0138_dialogue1">Granny Cotton Cookie!
Do you know the
lantern story too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0138_dialogue2">Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0138_dialogue3">Hurry up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0137_dialogue1">Alright, where should
we hang this lantern...
How about... here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0137_dialogue2">The first Cookie to hang a lantern
onto this tree used to say that...
Do you want to hear the story?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0137_dialogue3">Hey, it\'s almost time
to make the wishes!
Let\'s hurry!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_2_dialogue1">So many Cookies in one place!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_2_dialogue2">We Sugar Gnomes waited.
And waited. And waited...
WAITED SO LONG WE HAVE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0032_2_dialogue3">What does it feel like to
not have a giant to-build list
hovering over your head...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0017_dialogue1">Hur hur hur!
Nice inn you have here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0017_dialogue2">...*Snore*.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0017_dialogue3">Mhh... Oh? Ah!
I must\'ve fallen asleep.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0441_dialogue1">True, true!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0441_dialogue2">Let us go to the
Dumpling Hot Springs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0441_dialogue3">OHO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0310_dialogue1">WELL, WELL, WELL!
CRUMBLE ME DOWN!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0310_dialogue2">Frankly, the folks here in
Dragon City are... scared.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0310_dialogue3">Heh! The city will perish
without my stew!
Without my fireade!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0307_dialogue1">Dangerous dragons?
Of course they must be slain!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0307_dialogue2">Is there a dragon
in these lands?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0307_dialogue3">Just because dragons can fly,
doesn\'t mean they\'re untouchable!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0004_dialogue1">Sooo fuuullllll...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0004_dialogue2">Sooo sleeeepy...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0004_dialogue3">Hiii theeere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0003_dialogue1">NOOOOOOOO WAY!
WOW! COOKIES??!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0003_dialogue2">It is soooooo nice to
finally meeeeeet you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0003_dialogue3">Cooome, and have some
Bear Jellies with uuuus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0058_dialogue1">It may be difficult, but
time indeed can heal the
worst wounds on our souls.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0058_dialogue2">My dear... A true believer will
always face a moment of doubt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0058_dialogue3">Truly, your soul of
pure butter bears not
an iota of foul margarine...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0312_dialogue1">One fireade. Enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0312_dialogue2">Two fireades. Enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0312_dialogue3">You ready to order?
Fireade?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0311_dialogue1">One stew. Enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0311_dialogue2">Two stews. Enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0311_dialogue3">You ready to order?
Stew?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0113_dialogue1">Shush... Lower your voice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0113_dialogue2">I knew the minute our princess
set foot on these lands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0113_dialogue3">The heart of our great
kingdom holds the spirit
of unwavering solidarity.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0012_dialogue1">I haven\'t seen
these Cookies before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0012_dialogue2">Eh?
Who\'re you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0012_dialogue3">Hm, how did I get here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0015_dialogue1">A shallenger... gers...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0015_dialogue2">Hey! What\'re you...
URP... looking at?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0015_dialogue3">Wait... Why am I...
HIC... here again...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0439_dialogue1">Oh! I think we have a guest!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0439_dialogue2">HA HA HA HA HA HA HA!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0439_dialogue3">You need to open your
mind to see further!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0437_dialogue1">... Take a deep breath
and look around you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0437_dialogue2">WA HA HA HA HA HA!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0437_dialogue3">What you seek lies at the
end of an arduous path.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40515_dialogue1">Hey, you!
The Pepper Pangolins have arrived.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40515_dialogue2">We got into a brawl
on our way here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m40515_dialogue3">WHAT?
Got a problem with that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0565_dialogue1">Look! I\'ve become a
Knight of Kala Namak!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0565_dialogue2">No matter the circumstances,
violence will not be tolerated!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0565_dialogue3">There are Cookies
in need of our help...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0001_dialogue1">Yaaawn...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0001_dialogue2">Hi! I missed you,
everyone. HUH?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0001_dialogue3">YOU\'RE BACK!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0469_dialogue1">We only wish to survive...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0469_dialogue2">A thick blanket of dust is
shrouding the land...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0469_dialogue3">Even the mildest of Spices
are turning savage, and the
winds are blowing hot air...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0116_dialogue1">The seamstress added an extra
layer of whipped cream to make
my dress more fluffy! </string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0116_dialogue2">Dance, is the
art of communication.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0116_dialogue3">Do you not realize how
strained that posture is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2032_dialogue1">QUIET!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2032_dialogue2">Anyone who dares make a scene will be charged with contempt of court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2032_dialogue3">Order! Order!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2030_dialogue1">My dear Cookies, is our crispiness truly eternal?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2030_dialogue2">Can our fragile, doughy forms last forever?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2030_dialogue3">Empty yourself, and set out toward the primordial affection and warmth.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2031_dialogue1">... Objection.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2031_dialogue2">Assign these sturdy-looking outsiders as my temporary assistants.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2031_dialogue3">... We\'re already short-staffed as it is!</string>
  <string name="$item.Badge.Dalgona.Leafbat">Bramble Bat Cookie Badge</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0088_dialogue1">You want to pass through here?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0088_dialogue2">I sense something strange...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0088_dialogue3">I shall remain
ever vigilant!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0001_dialogue1">We\'re sorry for the lacking
reception. Due to the lack
of sunlight these days,</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0001_dialogue2">both fruits and Bear Jelly
harvests have been less
fruitful than usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0001_dialogue3">How are the fruits
around these parts?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0004_dialogue1">Huh?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0004_dialogue2">I could sense you coming!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0004_dialogue3">I can hear something...
from over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0005_dialogue1">You can call me Smarty.
I am a resident of
Berrygalia House.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0005_dialogue2">I refuse to admit that
I am on friendly terms
with simpletons...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0005_dialogue3">Perhaps, next time,
Bramble Bat Cookie
won\'t be a foolish simpleton.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0006_dialogue1">Thank you for coming
all this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0006_dialogue2">O Dragons, watch over us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0006_dialogue3">Aren\'t you hungry?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0007_dialogue1">Looking for me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0007_dialogue2">That\'s right! I\'m completely
innocent! Hehe... Ahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0007_dialogue3">You must really like me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0087_dialogue1">I have slept for ages,
within soil carrying the
fragrance of seasons.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0087_dialogue2">The world may be harsh,
but don\'t lose sight
of who you are.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0087_dialogue3">If you endure the dough-biting
cold, you will gain an
even deeper flavor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0010_dialogue1">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0010_dialogue2">... You wanted to see me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0010_dialogue3">If you need help,
just let me know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0011_dialogue1">Starfruit Cookie!
There is something you
must come check at once!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0011_dialogue2">That was excellent,
Starfruit Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0011_dialogue3">Starfruit Cookie!
Starfruit Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2013_dialogue1">GAH!
You startled me...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2013_dialogue2">My name is Chickpea Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2013_dialogue3">I am attempting to preserve
the soil\'s last traces of moisture.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0003_dialogue1">Mrawr, what\'s all this racket...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0003_dialogue2">Looks like the
Meowstress is
very, very upset...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0003_dialogue3">Perhaps the Meowstress\'
research isn\'t coming along?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0013_dialogue1">Everyone, turn to page 125 of
your Introduction to History! </string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0013_dialogue2">Today\'s class is all about the
Frozen Age and the history
of the gift-giving era!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0013_dialogue3">Now, what was holiday
Cookie\'s first virtue? </string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0275_dialogue1">♪♬♩♪♪~♬</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0275_dialogue2">What is all this nonsense
that I hear?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0275_dialogue3">Where is your flaming
Scovillian spirit?! Did it all
waft into the local clean air?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0014_dialogue1">We were worried.
Legit worried!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0014_dialogue2">That was SO epic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0014_dialogue3">That\'s AMAZING!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0015_dialogue1">Hmm... you\'re
one interesting
Cookie indeed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0015_dialogue2">If you are curious about
who we are, I can tell you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0015_dialogue3">We are the Sneaky Sands Clan
who can steal anything we want.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0016_dialogue1">Usually we treat our guests to
Bear Jellies in different colors,
split into 5 meals a day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0016_dialogue2">Humid days like these really
call for some refreshing
Mango Jelly Ice Cream!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0016_dialogue3">What kind of fruit are all those?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0362_dialogue1">May your splendid hands
multiply our riches and wealth
forever more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0362_dialogue2">Was your hand massage to your
liking, o Golden Sovereign?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0362_dialogue3">May you rest well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0363_dialogue1">Your brilliance truly knows
no bounds, my Queen...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0363_dialogue2">Your magnificent dough shines,
as though freshly-baked!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0363_dialogue3">Your Radiance, may I humbly offer you some refreshments? We have prepared a charcuterie board.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0344_dialogue1">Chirp! I waz wondering where
my golden anklet had gone,
but I see it\'z right here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0344_dialogue2">Forgive me, but I muzt tend
to my Cheesebird flock.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0344_dialogue3">It\'z like they say, \"the greedier
the bird, the wider it\'ll spread
it\'z wingz!\"</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s60_cakehound_dialogue1">Woof woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s60_cakehound_dialogue2">WOOF! Bark bark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s60_cakehound_dialogue3">*Whimper*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0134_dialogue1">You call that steel? Hah!
THIS IS STEEL!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0134_dialogue2">I HATE JOKES!
I\'ll make minced crumbs outta ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0134_dialogue3">.....</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0023_dialogue1">Hello? Want some ice cream?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0023_dialogue2">Why yes, the students
would come to our city for
ice cream all the time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0023_dialogue3">This ice cream will chill
you to the bones!
It\'s a taste to die for!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0085_dialogue1">Give it your all, and you\'ll prevail.
Hold back, and you shall fall!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0085_dialogue2">I will get back up,
no matter how
many times I fall!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRC_cookie0085_dialogue3">Do not announce my fall...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0130_dialogue1">GLORY TO THE MALA TRIBE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0130_dialogue2">Eh?
Who\'re you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0130_dialogue3">COME! Join us in a toast
to our new leader!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0013_dialogue1">Hey-hey, do you know?
Every Cookie was happy in
the great Vanilla Kingdom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0013_dialogue2">Tell me a story!
I want to hear a story!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0013_dialogue3">There seems to be a lot of
interesting places here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0280_dialogue1">Let\'s see what you sweetlings
are made of!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0280_dialogue2">WE WANT CAPSAICIN COOKIE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0280_dialogue3">THE KING OF FLAMES!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0042_dialogue1">I have been awaiting
your arrival, Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0042_dialogue2">One of great power awaits you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0042_dialogue3">If you would, please... This way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0018_dialogue1_1">The pressure of creation!
The struggle against obscurity!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0018_dialogue1_2">Your initiative to step into
the world of art!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0018_dialogue2">It\'s as if my own heart
was shredded by the seams!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0018_dialogue3">Is there no way to stop these
tears of sorrow and pain!
OH, cruel world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0019_dialogue1">Don\'t worry! We\'re all gonna
be okay as long as we stay
nice and crispy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0019_dialogue2">If ya knew how to swim,
I would\'ve taught you
how to dive underwater!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0019_dialogue3">Everyone! Let\'s go fish some Jellies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0229_dialogue1">Aurora speaking. Sugarcloud Express, report. Has there been a malfunction?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0229_dialogue2">Please take measures to
return to normal parameters.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0229_dialogue3">Rules! Law! Is what
keeps this disorderly
world from falling apart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0251_dialogue1">Oh my! How come
our little lady likes the
mermaid story so much?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0251_dialogue2">Once upon a time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0251_dialogue3">And now it\'s time for bed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0164_dialogue1">Halt, state your purpo—</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0164_dialogue2">Please, this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0164_dialogue3">Pardon the intrusion, madam.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0020_dialogue1">Open the storage and provide
the Cookies with Jellies
and umbrellas!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0020_dialogue2">I will have them prepare you a
rice cake quilted duvet, and an
assortment of yakgwa snacks.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0020_dialogue3">I will do my best to become a
magistrate worthy of the Cookies
who live in this village.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0132_dialogue1">We gonna clean this
place out or what?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0132_dialogue2">Pfft...
Enough with the drama.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0132_dialogue3">Psh... Puh-lease.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10134_dialogue1">Bark! Bark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10134_dialogue2">Bark! Bark! Bark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10134_dialogue3">*snarling* ... Bark! BARK!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0392_dialogue1">O, green wanderer</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0392_dialogue2">O, almighty Silver
Watch over us from above</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0392_dialogue3">For your journey has yet to end</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0394_dialogue1">Although you lack a pair of wings
Like a Faerie your floral scent sings</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0394_dialogue2">And protect the peace
and balance of this world of chaos</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0394_dialogue3">sealing the Great Shadow
in the deepest depths</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0145_dialogue1">Hrrrrmmm... Put some milk
on the fire, lad.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0145_dialogue2">Hold on, you\'re not from the
Dark Cacao Kingdom, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0145_dialogue3">Cookies should help Cookies, no?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0144_dialogue1">Grandpappy! Look over there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0144_dialogue2">Now, now, Grandpappy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0144_dialogue3">We talked about this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0021_dialogue1">The Sunblade cannot be
obtained by strength alone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0021_dialogue2">Good luck to all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0021_dialogue3">Let it be a splendid and
honorable match between
all contestants!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s49_cakehound_dialogue1">*Sniff!* *Sniff!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s49_cakehound_dialogue2">Woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s49_cakehound_dialogue3">*whimper...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0022_dialogue1">Leave it to me-Q! Begin scan-Q!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0022_dialogue2">Let me show you to your room-Q.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0022_dialogue3">Competing to see who\'s loudest-Q?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0329_dialogue1">Just one of these creatures is
enough to make us a fortune!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0329_dialogue2">So whadd\'ya say? Ready to
seize the opportunity of
a lifetime? HA HA HA!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0329_dialogue3">Tonight, we FEAST!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0494_dialogue1">.....</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0494_dialogue2">Turn back before it is too late.
Turn back before the cold flames
of doubt consume you whole.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0494_dialogue3">Are you sure you won\'t regret
your choice, come what may?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0077_dialogue1">*Cough... cough...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0077_dialogue2">Hya hyem! I attended one of that Cookie\'s big speeches out of curiosity!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0077_dialogue3">The missing Cookies must\'ve walked straight into the oven on their own two feet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0537_dialogue1">oOoOh! New faces!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0537_dialogue2_1">I\'m Jelly Cup CoOoOokie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0537_dialogue2_2">I love to frolic in this paradise
with my lovely Jelly Cups!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0537_dialogue3">It\'s sOoOoO convenient having Jelly Cups do all the work for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0279_dialogue1">Looks like everybody has gathered!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0279_dialogue2">Let\'s go, or they\'ll leave without us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0279_dialogue3">*sniff sniff* Huh...? Do you smell something sweet?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0219_dialogue1">Um... Uh... H-h-h-h-hello!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0219_dialogue2">T-t-the train is ab-b-bout to d-d-depart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0219_dialogue3">W-w-w-we wish you a p-p-p-pleasant t-trip!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0187_dialogue1">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0187_dialogue2">I await your command.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0187_dialogue3">Give me your order.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0023_dialogue1">Tsk, tsk... Be careful!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0023_dialogue2">Ah, these young Cookies
can be so bothersome...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0023_dialogue3">Are you lost?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0024_dialogue1">Shining Glitter Cookie
is amazing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0024_dialogue2">We\'re so hyped to cover
one of Shining Glitter
Cookie\'s songs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0024_dialogue3">I never thought she
would give you a lift
all the way here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0068_dialogue1">The next training session
will commence soon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0068_dialogue2">It\'s safer now, all thanks to
First Choco Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0068_dialogue3">This is happening much more often of late, little Cookies trying to get into the Chocosseum...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0025_dialogue1">Our special show is only days away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0025_dialogue2">We\'ll finally get to choose
a new member for our circus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0025_dialogue3">It\'s important to take a break
and have some fun while rehearsing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0026_dialogue1">We\'ve finally chosen a
new member of our circus!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0026_dialogue2">Do your best in using
your talents.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0026_dialogue3">Oh, ho ho... You should
sleep inside the dorm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0131_dialogue1">This heat\'s killin\' my vibe...
Even my hair gel\'s meltin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0131_dialogue2">Don\'t get too close!
You\'re blocking the breeze!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0131_dialogue3">So there are multiple worlds,
and we are in other ones too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0027_dialogue1">Welcome to the campsite!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0027_dialogue2">Don\'t forget to pick up the
camping notebook and
pamphlet at the entrance!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0027_dialogue3">Make sure you read the rules
written on the back of
your camping notes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0166_dialogue1">Our city will soon become the force that will decide the fate of all Earthbread!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0166_dialogue2">There is no path to success without sacrifice. Our family will stand behind you with every step.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0166_dialogue3">Our family has deep roots, boy... Deep roots, dating back to the days of the Vanilla Kingdom itself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0501_dialogue1">Where is Pure Vanilla Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0501_dialogue2">Hush, hush...
There, there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0501_dialogue3">Be patient, my dear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0028_dialogue1">We\'re all in this together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0028_dialogue2">After all, we\'re a team!
Nah, we\'re a family!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0028_dialogue3">Shining Glitter Cookie came over
to our rehearsal and brought
us a bunch of snacks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10111_dialogue1">Grrr... Woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10111_dialogue2">Woof, woof woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_m10111_dialogue3">Bark! Bark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0516_dialogue1">I FEEL CLOSER TO THEM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0516_dialogue2">YES, IT COULDN\'T FEEL BETTER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0516_dialogue3">I HAVE NO OTHER CHOICE...
BUT I WILL RETURN, ONE DAY...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0029_dialogue1">C\'mon, Popping Candy Cookie.
Take a break once in a while.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0029_dialogue2">He\'s been rehearsing... a LOT.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0029_dialogue3">Do you know any
nice cafés nearby?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0002_dialogue1">Welcome!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0002_dialogue2">We have a mountain of orders
piled up and the materials are
on the verge of dwindling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0002_dialogue3">Do you have
a style in mind?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0067_dialogue1">C\'mon!
Walk faster, you slowpoke!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0067_dialogue2">Shh! Keep your voice down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0067_dialogue3">I\'m going to scout the area.
Stay here until I get back.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0005_dialogue1">Cuckoo!
Another lively day in the square!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0005_dialogue2">COO, Caramel Choux COOkie,
COO! My favorite employee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_square_npc0005_dialogue3">I\'ll have you know I\'m in
the market for a new
top hat and shoes! Coo!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0030_dialogue1">Coo...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0030_dialogue2">Coo... Cookiecu..tter...
Sha... rk Coo...kie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0030_dialogue3">Coo... What this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0276_dialogue1">Hmm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0276_dialogue2">This is our chance to
demonstrate the superiority
of our values and beliefs!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0276_dialogue3">A Paladin never walks
a well-trodden path!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0004_dialogue1">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0004_dialogue2">Honk...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_event0004_dialogue3">Mimimimimi....</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0277_dialogue1">\"Never turn away from good will,\"
they say.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0277_dialogue2">Is there a problem?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0277_dialogue3">I only hope that you achieve
all your goals at the end of
this trial...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0176_dialogue1">Cookies tainted by sea and mud...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0176_dialogue2">Hearken to me. Hear me.
Accept the words of providence and you may find deliverance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0176_dialogue3">We bring the prospect of a promised land, rich in sunlight and firm soil...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0228_dialogue1">Snacks! Getcha snacks!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0228_dialogue2">We even have packs
of Starflour Crisps!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0228_dialogue3">Would you like a snack?
We have everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0538_dialogue1">Hmm... I simply have no idea
what you\'re talking about!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0538_dialogue2">HA HA HA HA HA!
You two must be enjoying
each other\'s company!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0538_dialogue3">Obsessive love can be
oh-so stifling!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s35_cakehound_dialogue1">Woof! Woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s35_cakehound_dialogue2">Bark! Bark! Bark!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_arenareward_s35_cakehound_dialogue3">Woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0031_dialogue1_1">I will do anything
for our Yogurt Family</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0031_dialogue1_2">even until the day I crumble
and the cream sours...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0031_dialogue2">I can already see our
proud father\'s beaming
and satisfied smile!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_npc0031_dialogue3">While you are \"biding your time\"
my foolish brother will inherit
my father\'s entire fortune!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0427_dialogue1">Hungry... So hungry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0427_dialogue2">I want to eat it. Could I...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0427_dialogue3">Does devouring the sky mean
it will grant me its powers?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0547_dialogue1">Grawr!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0547_dialogue2">Who knows, though.
Perhaps your greatest strength
will become your weakness...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0547_dialogue3">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2027_dialogue1">If you get stuck here,
don\'t say I didn\'t warn ya!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2027_dialogue2">I\'m Bramble Bat Cookie!
I\'m the jack-of-all-trades
here in Berrygalia House!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2027_dialogue3">ARRRGH!
Smarty called me
a simpleton again!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2028_dialogue1">Don\'t think about running.
It\'s time to weigh your sins.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2028_dialogue2">Sometimes, silence is the most honest of testimonies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2028_dialogue3">My verdict stands.
Let your sins dissolve on your tongue, like salt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2029_dialogue1">Hello! Ready to prove you\'ve got a good heart?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2029_dialogue2">If you\'ve abandoned all goodwill, I see no reason to show you mercy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2029_dialogue3">Give me a reason to forgive you. I\'m all ears!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue1">That\'s just life.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue2">Is this icing real,
or is it a toupée?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue3">This... this isn\'t just
my imagination, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_WolfsbaneCookie_dialogue1">I am Wolfsbane Cookie,
an incense sorcerer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_WolfsbaneCookie_dialogue2">What do you think is apropos?
Should I turn all of you
into my puppets?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_WolfsbaneCookie_dialogue3">The Great One truly
knows everything...
All things, everywhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_HaliteGauntletCookie_dialogue1">So... Visitors approach.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_HaliteGauntletCookie_dialogue2">I will defend... this domain...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_HaliteGauntletCookie_dialogue3">I will... hold on...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0078_dialogue1">The culprit... this way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0078_dialogue2">Stop... talking.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_npc0078_dialogue3">... I command you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0285_dialogue1">If someone\'s going to
stay behind, it always
has to be me, got it?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0285_dialogue2">Emergency Neutralization
Division, prepare for
gravitational inversion!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0285_dialogue3">The mission isn\'t a
success unless
everyone gets back alive!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0283_dialogue1">Where did you go...
my dearest...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0283_dialogue2">Where is...
my palanquin...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0283_dialogue3">Today is... the happiest day...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0276_dialogue1">What fun is a cruise
without daily parties?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0276_dialogue2">We are all simply
passengers upon the
cruise of life, darling.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0276_dialogue3">A few small secrets
makes a Cookie\'s life
far more extravagant.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0240_dialogue1">You won\'t even notice that
it\'s me doing the stunts!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0240_dialogue2">There\'s nothing I do better than
jumping, flying, and rolling!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CRO_cookie0240_dialogue3">Action scenes are
all about teamwork,
you know?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0529_dialogue1">Wait, did the light
just get... brighter?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0529_dialogue2">Twinkle twinkle... Sparkle away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_npc0529_dialogue3">I hope this light will
reach all corners
of this land...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0605_dialogue_ready">Hope is nothing
else but a cheap
trick of the mind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0605_dialogue_clear">Show\'s over!
But we will be back, mhm!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0601_dialogue_ready">I shall show you
the true meaning
of enlightenment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0601_dialogue_clear">Yes...
This is true futility.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0602_dialogue_ready">I wonder...
What will it take
to destroy me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0602_dialogue_clear">Heh... I commend
their recklessness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0603_dialogue_ready">Let us forget all
pains and sorrows!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0603_dialogue_clear">They... will get what
they deserve!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0604_dialogue_ready">Prove your
worth to me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0604_dialogue_clear">I cannot
stop here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0138_dialogue_ready">Grrr... You dare
challenge me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0138_dialogue_clear">I lossst...
But it was fun!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue_ready">Witness the
power of Dragons!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0155_dialogue_clear">Hrrrmph...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue_ready">Ahaha!
You\'ll end up on
your knees before me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0198_dialogue_clear">So annoying...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue_ready">These lands are
my paradise.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0185_dialogue_clear">Everything is
quite dull...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue_ready">I am all seeing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CRO_cookie0203_dialogue_clear">We will meet again...
I can see it...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0568_dialogue_ready">Hello there, little playthings.
Are you ready to
become soggy trash?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0568_dialogue_clear">I\'ll make you
regret this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0109_dialogue_ready">I shall crush this
world built on
sweet lies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CK_cookie0109_dialogue_clear">The Darkness is
always near.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2001_dialogue_ready">This world has such
potential for beauty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2001_dialogue_clear">I shall not be defeated.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2011_dialogue_ready">As long as I am present,
no one shall go hungry.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2011_dialogue_clear">Winter shall pass and
the crops will grow
once more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2015_dialogue_ready">What time is it...?
Ah, time for the
next training session.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2015_dialogue_clear">The strong do not
know the meaning
of defeat.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2021_dialogue_ready">Are you injured...?
I will treat you right away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2021_dialogue_clear">I\'m sorry...
I\'m so sorry...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2017_dialogue_ready">Welcome!
You\'re in for a
dazzling show!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2017_dialogue_clear">This. Is.
NOT. FUN...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2025_dialogue_ready">You aren\'t leaving...
Are you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2025_dialogue_clear">I don\'t want to lose anything...
I will never forget anyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_TrialLevel_CWC_cookie2028_dialogue_ready">... Let the trial commence.</string>
