  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.001_1">Ginger... Brave... Now that\'s a name I\'ve not heard in a long time. A long time...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.001_2">It\'s nice being called a hero, but it feels good to be called by that name again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.001_3">May you never lose the courage within your dough, my friend. Not now, not ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.002_1">Uh-oh...! The logout button just disappeared...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.002_2">I\'m... I\'m not going to hide under this hood anymore...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.002_3">My friends are trapped in a game world...! And they\'re waiting for me! It\'s time... for a new adventure!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.003_1">Yes, I am Langue de Chat Cookie. Would you like me to review a case?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.003_2">Wait...? A street talk show? Thank you for the invitation, but I must respectfully decline once again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.003_3">An undefeated lawyer such as myself should be in court, not in front of a camera.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.004_1">I\'m not lonely anymore...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.004_2">Everyone agreed to stay by my side... As brilliant ice that never melts...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.004_3">You\'ll be my friend too, in this eternal winter, won\'t you? Don\'t worry... you won\'t be cold.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.005_1">Having my name become synonymous with a genre in itself? A truly exquisite experience.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.005_2">And now, the final deduction of \"Miss Waffle, Master Detective\" is complete. The title shall be...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.005_3">Hm... Yes. Heh, that\'s the one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.006_1">Always remember! What\'s written on the chalkboard will never be as important as the sunset outside!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.006_2">Now then... That\'s all from me for today! From here on our, take the magic that you are and stir it into the great big world out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.006_3">Thanks for being the last students of your ever-so-tardy professor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.007_1">I can\'t believe it! Instead of my usual delivery route, I finally get to go on a real adventure!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.007_2">I\'m gonna go anywhere my bicycle\'s wheels can take me...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.007_3">And when I get back, I\'m gonna tell Pudding Cookie everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.008_1">Many ailments have their roots in troubled, burdened hearts. More than you\'d think.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.008_2">I\'ve spent so many years brewing remedies and tonics... I\'m nearly the age as my teacher when I first met him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.008_3">And I finally understand... The greatest medicine of all is a sincere heart that stays by your side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.009_1">I always knew this day would come... The day I finally restore the Leek Clan\'s name to its former glory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.009_2">Once more, the spirit of the Leek Clan shall rise over this verdant bamboo grove...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.009_3">And the art of the Leek Blade shall shine brighter than ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.010_1">I still walk along the beach when the sun sets.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.010_2">The silly lyrics I scribbled back then have become songs the whole world knows now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.010_3">But my heart still feels like it belongs in the music room at school!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.011_1">Do I still look like a Dragon Rider with nothing but a beautiful smile and empty words to you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.011_2">These days, I can read the paths beyond the clouds just from the way Buttercream breathes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.011_3">Now then, hold on tight, cutie! We\'re flying off to the most romantic spot in the sky!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.012_1">So everyone keeps saying my jokes leave them feeling empty, eh?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.012_2">Well, I told them I\'d really reflect on myself, and you know what happened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.012_3">I tried a new joke in front of my mirror, and it literally cracked up! Hahaha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.013_1">In the depths of the darkness, I\'m the only one who shines! Gorgeous, don\'t you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.013_2">The Sneaky Sands Clan worked incredibly hard to build a grand fortress this deep underground.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.013_3">The traitors will never find us now, no matter how hard they try! Ohh ho ho!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.014_1">H-Hey, hold on! All of you can\'t just come rushing at me at once...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.014_2">Your noses are, without a doubt, the most dangerously accurate detectors in the world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.014_3">Now then... Once you\'ve all finished your snacks, it\'s nap time for everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.015_1">If I\'m ever written into the history books someday...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.015_2">I hope the phrase \"everyone was happy and laughed\" appears more than my own name!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.015_3">After all, a king must live for his subjects! Now then... let the coronation begin!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.016_1">That dream I had... Embarking on a journey to try coffee from all a round the world? I\'ve already gone around seven times!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.016_2">But honestly... the best cup is still the one I make at home! Freshly brewed, right by my sun-soaked window!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.017_1">In honor of finally hitting 100 million subscribers, I\'ll be hosting a live AMA, Q&amp;A, and FAQ!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.017_2">Let\'s have a look at some questions... Ah, here\'s one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.017_3">\"Is it true that your garlicky aroma chases away real ghosts?\"... Not anymore, it doesn\'t!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.018_1">Pheh... mhe he heh... Look at this...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.018_2">I have loyal followers now...! Loads of them...! Heh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.018_3">If only Dark Enchantress Cookie can see me now... She\'d definitely... definitely... Tch...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.019_1">The debut single\'s release is just around the corner. Just what do you think you\'re doing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.019_2">Hey, you! D.A.K!!! Stop right there! I said STOP!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.019_3">Walk out that door and I will have you dropped from Darkness Entertainment before you ever make it on stage!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.020_1">Showing you my own future? Boooring!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.020_2">Go back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.021_1">Hm? What\'s my secret to being a Giant Veggie Contest judge ten years running?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.021_2">Hoho! You\'re making me blush! There\'s no real secret, you know. I just tend to my fields with everything I\'ve got!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.021_3">Vegetables and Cookies alike, you give\'em love, and they\'ll grow up strong and healthy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.022_1">Ngh... NGH...!!! Phew!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.022_2">I finally blocked off the entrance! Now, nobody can find this place anymore!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.022_3">This Cheese Stone cave is MINE now! Mine, all mine!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.023_1">Hiyaaah! If it\'s to protect our kingdom, I\'ll toughen myself up and train all day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.023_2">Knight Cookie! Don\'t run away! C\'mon, one more round of sparring!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.023_3">Huh? What? My coronation? That was TODAY?! I need to get back to the palace! Let\'s go!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.024_1">Phew...! It\'s been a long journey, turning the Simmering Syrup Sauna from a simple bathhouse into a full-blown hot spring resort.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.024_2">The new steamer open-air bath and the syrup wave pool have both been a hit with guests! What a relief...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.024_3">Now all that\'s left is the grand opening of the full sauna experience tour... I\'d better ask Tangerine Tanghulu Cookie to help out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.025_1">Apprentices. Listen well.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.025_2">First... A true ninja must know humility. Be humble above all else. Second, never neglect your training.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.025_3">Feel the wind, then surrender your dough to it... one step at a time. Focus your mind!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.026_1">Ah, you\'re the new intern, aren\'t you? Regarding that incident report the Relic Management Division was supposed to submit...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.026_2">Oh? You sent Maple Taffy Cookie a reminder every single day?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.026_3">And the follow-up procedures...? Ah. I see you\'ve handled everything without a single loose end. Haha, I admire such thoroughness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.027_1">Ahem! Check, check, mic test! One, two, one, two...! How\'s everyone doing out there?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.027_2">Thanks for inviting me to this year\'s Summer Soda Rock Festa! Wow, has it already been my tenth time here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.027_3">Taking the stage as the headliner never gets old! Let\'s get this started! LET\'S ROCK N\' ROLL, EVERYONE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.028_1">Alrighty, penguins! Try following along. Lie flat on your bellies and push off the snow with your flippers. Yeah! Just like that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.028_2">I built some sleds for the penguins, hehe! Everyone seems to be having a blast too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.028_3">We may not get very far, but at least we can all zip around together with our sleds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.029_1">Wow, I can\'t believe I\'m running a brand-new toy shop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.029_2">I learned so much from Butterbear Cookie, so there\'s nothing to be nervous about... Wait, is it time to open the shop already?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.029_3">... W-Welcome to the Lollibear Toy Shop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.030_1">WHAM! WHAM! Outta my way before I flatten you all! C\'mon, folks! This is a construction site!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.030_2">Everyone calling me the Road Roller Master isn\'t half bad, ya know!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.030_3">And I\'m gonna prove I\'m the real Road Roller Master too by making this site look absolutely incredible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.031_1">So this is the Jellyfish Ocean!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.031_2">And I\'m here all thanks to Artichoke Cookie covering for me as the Tropical Soda Islands guide while I\'m away, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.031_3">The stories this beautiful sea must hold...! I\'ll make sure to share every last one with everyone someday!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.032_1">Wait, there\'s a timeline where I become the Director of the TBD? What\'s going on here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.032_2">I\'m... sure the Director\'s gonna sort things out on their end... In the meantime, maybe I\'ll take a look at some of the relics from this timeline!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.033_1">Whaaat? You\'re scared of this cute little thing? You think it\'s haunted???</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.033_2">How could you throw away this adorable little, moldy Bear Jelly Toy? Can I have it? I wanna add it to my Bright &amp; Cheerful Collectible Shop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.033_3">Though... I really can\'t figure out why I never get any customers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.034_1">Hello there, lil\' Cookies! Welcome to the For\'st Kindergarten, hihi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.034_2">This is a place where ever\'one who loves nature can run around an\' play to their heart\'s content!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.034_3">How \'bout we start by readin\' a book with our for\'st friends? One about a very brave hero, hihi!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.035_1">Hello! I\'m Mint Wafer Cookie, and I\'ll be your music teacher for today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.035_2">Haha, I can\'t believe I\'m here, back at the school where I started our band as a guest teacher...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.035_3">Before we start class, will you share a few stories about yourselves first? Let\'s turn it into a song together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.036_1">One, two, one, two! Hold on just a sec, new monkey recruits!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.036_2">That\'s not how you handle a hula hoop! It\'s a lot more delicate than it looks, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.036_3">Now watch closely! Choco the Monkey and I will show you how it\'s done!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.037_1">The moon... It is an unknown realm, one where no Cookie has ever been permitted to reach...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.037_2">And yet, I continue... plotting a course towards it, sailing through a sea of crashing zeroes and ones.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.037_3">Perhaps, one day, I may truly touch the moonlight itself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.038_1">Hm? The cherry blossom tea is already sold out?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.038_2">Well, it looks like opening this picnic shop was worth it after all! But it looks like I won\'t be able to make it to this year\'s spring picnic myself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.038_3">But knowing that my cherry blossom tea gets to be a part of everyone else\'s picnics...! That\'s all I need to be happy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.039_1">Ahhh... Even lazing around and doing nothing is starting to get boring...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.039_2">Hm... Oh, I know! Maybe I\'ll start a vineyard and start growing my own grapevines! That way, I\'ll have all the grape juice I could ever want!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.039_3">But first... Maybe just one more day of lying here and taking it easy... I\'ll start tomorrow... Probably.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.040_1">One... two... three... Wow, there\'s so many baby peppermint whales! The pod keeps growing and growing...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.040_2">Promise me one thing, baby whales...! Grow up big and strong! And when you do... will you share your stories about the ocean with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.041_1">Ahem! As your guest professor for the day, here\'s what I want you to take away from today\'s lecture.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.041_2">The world may never recognize you or your art. When that happens, stop feeling upset with yourself. You\'ve got to start believing in yourself more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.041_3">I know for certain... there will always be someone out there who will call your work the greatest masterpiece in the world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.042_1">Alright! You have one more test to pass before becoming a true Dessert Guardian. Let me give you one piece of advice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.042_2">Even when the trials ahead are as harsh as winter, you can pull through if everyone remembers to work together.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.042_3">And once you make it past the trials, you can stand tall and proud as a true Dessert Guardian! Just like me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.043_1">It\'s finally sinking in that I\'m leaving this lab.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.043_2">Bell Pepper Cookie! When did you grow up so fast and open a joint research center with Aloe Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.043_3">Looking at you is the only way I can tell how much time has actually passed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.044_1">Alrighty! This should be more than enough to keep A.C.i.D. running smoothly while I\'m gone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.044_2">The next collab collection? Ha, everything on the road will be inspiration!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.044_3">With Chocolate Bonbon Cookie by my side, the whole world will be our runway! See you when I\'m back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.045_1">This is it...! This\'ll be the one millionth party I plan!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.045_2">Thanks for trusting me with it... Oops! The confetti cannon wasn\'t supposed to go off yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.045_3">Well, since it\'s already done... Decorating the floor with confetti is never a bad idea!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.046_1">I\'m so happy to finally throw the shipboard party I\'ve always dreamed of!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.046_2">Hehe, and thanks to everyone teaching me, land language is getting easier every OoO! Huh...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.046_3">I meant to say, OoO, no, wait, oOoOoOOoooOoO! OoOOoOoOooOo?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.047_1">Oh, oh my! Really? I have mail?! All of these letters are for me???</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.047_2">They\'re all from the Cookies I wrote letters to...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.047_3">They wanted to write back to me?! My goodness! My heart is pounding with excitement!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.048_1">The Great Dragon is looking for me? My, my... They really ask me for every little chore, don\'t they?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.048_2">We have plenty of Cookies who can assist now, so I\'d like to relax just a little longer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.048_3">After all, it\'s the very first vacation the Dragon has ever given me. I shall be making the most of it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.049_1">Little bird. Why are you crying?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.049_2">You were teased for the color of your features? Do not let such words bother you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.049_3">You shall become more beautiful than anyone, just like I.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.050_1">How did I become such a great holiday train engineer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.050_2">Hm... There weren\'t any shortcuts! But one thing\'s for certain...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.050_3">The bond you share with your partner Holiday Cookie makes all the difference!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.051_1">Khahaha! Everyone\'s clearing the way for me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.051_2">Of course they would. Even lost souls can recognize the greatness of me, the Super Devil!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.051_3">I think I\'ll celebrate by stirring up some trouble, khehehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.052_1">Hello... Why are you crying? You lost your way and ended up here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.052_2">Don\'t cry... Here, hold this doll. It will make you feel better and braver.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.052_3">I used to cry a lot too, just like you. But thanks to this doll, I don\'t cry anymore...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.053_1">Listen up! The golden rule of alchemy is to attempt new experiments without fearing failure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.053_2">But even an overheated flask is bound to shatter. If you want to reach the absolute truth, sometimes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.053_3">... a quick nap can help open the path to new research!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.054_1">Greetings. I am Okchun Cookie, the newly appointed magistrate. We all know each other quite well by now, don\'t we?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.054_2">Following in my father\'s footsteps, I shall strive to give my all to serve our village.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.054_3">I shall do my part to ensure that your days are bright, just like the full moon\'s light.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.055_1">Phew... I can barely catch my breath. Not even a moment for a quick nap!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.055_2">But for the sake of every Cookie who works for our family...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.055_3">The busier I am, the more everyone else gets to relax and live comfortably!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.056_1">A crowd like this... still feels unfamiliar. But I won\'t run anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.056_2">Next up is my new original song... \"The Monster Within\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.056_3">Are you ready to awaken the wild side inside your hearts? All together then... AWOOOOOO!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.057_1">Hear me well, ministers.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.057_2">This kingdom does not belong to me, nor to you. It belongs to its Cookies. The corrupt will never escape justice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.057_3">No matter how small the matter, you must always lend an ear to our Cookies\' troubles!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.058_1">Commander Knight Cookie, at your service!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.058_2">I pledge upon my sword to defend this kingdom and its Cookies until I crumble.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.058_3">The honor of knighthood will always be deeply engraved into my very dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.059_1">Aurora. Amazing. Glittering lights. Spectacular spectacle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.059_2">Cookie World = Wide, vast. Ion Cookie Robot will continue exploring.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.059_3">Self-Directive: Meet many new friends. Share stories upon return. Alert: Upgrading memory chip to incorporate latest memories...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.060_1">Hello there. You must be the little fawn the trees told me about.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.060_2">I heard you got into a fight with your friends and wandered all the way out here. You know, they\'re all very worried about you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.060_3">Why not come back with me? I will tell you a story on the way... about a Cookie who was just like you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.061_1">We won the World Cheerleading Championships! I still can\'t believe it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.061_2">Wow...! Are all those Cookies here to cheer for us?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.061_3">Being on the receiving end of a cheer feels a bit strange, but I love it so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.062_1">HAHAHA! FINALLY! I got my hands all ten of the world\'s greatest treasures!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.062_2">Do you hear me, world?! No matter how well you hide them, they\'ll always end up back in my hands!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.062_3">From this day on, every treasure will end up belonging to me, the Bandit King!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.063_1">Despite my many shortcomings, I, Yugwa Cookie, humbly accept the role of Chief State Councillor.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.063_2">I shall harbor no selfish ambitions, only devotion to the king and the Cookies of the land.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.063_3">I shall be the whip that drives out corruption in the court and set things straight!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.064_1">After blessing every single Cookie in the world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.064_2">I can now finally fly high up above the clouds...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.064_3">The warm sunlight feels amazing up here... What a beautiful day...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.065_1">Huff... puff... I finally made it! The Great Dough Peak!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.065_2">Wow... From a tent in my room to the top of the world...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.065_3">Haha! My bucket list is finally complete!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.066_1">Ahh... It\'s finally here. A world where justice can exist without laws.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.066_2">The breeze is just right... What perfect timing! Maybe I\'ll go surfing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.066_3">Standing before these perfect waves... It\'s a crime to let them go to waste!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.067_1">I still can\'t believe I\'ve been granted the Doughbel Prize.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.067_2">I never knew the log I kept during my adventures would turn out to become so much more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.067_3">Never forget! Every great discovery begins with a small step forward!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.068_1">I\'ve raced in more competitions than I can count...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.068_2">But this circuit always gets my strawberry jam boiling, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.068_3">Until I\'ve claimed victory in every last race, my wheels will never stop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.069_1">Alright! It\'ll be starting from right over there! Careful, watch your step!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.069_2">Incredible, isn\'t it?! It\'s a meteor shower that shows up once every one hundred years...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.069_3">I wanted you to see this right as it happened. So... what do you think, Blackberry Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.070_1">The new Delivery Train line needs to run this way!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.070_2">This route may look easier, but there\'s heavy snow every winter. It\'ll slow down the trains to a crawl.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.070_3">As the chief engineer, delays are simply unacceptable!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.071_1">*Giggle, giggle!*
Happy holidays, heehee!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.071_2">Since you were a very kind and well-behaved Cookie all year long, this gift is for you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.071_3">This is my very first year as a Holiday Cookie, so I\'ll even sing you a carol! What\'s your favorite holiday song?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.072_1">Welcome, little friends! My name\'s Apple Cookie, and I\'ll be your guide to this newly opened CookieLand!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.072_2">I designed those rides over there! The apple-shaped ferris wheel and the giant jellyworm coaster!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.072_3">And over here! Meet Cream Unicorn Cookie, who helped me build CookieLand into what it is today!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.073_1">I came, I saw, and I conquered!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.073_2">I, Pistachio Cookie, have fought to banish the forces of evil and bring peace to the land with every crumb of my being...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.073_3">And finally, victory is achieved! I shall raise a toast of triump with every Cookie who stood by my side!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.074_1">I\'m so happy to be building Fairy Village together with everyone...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.074_2">Everyone calls me the queen, but... I\'m just an ordinary, peace-loving Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.074_3">Let\'s all live in peace and harmony here...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.075_1">Freeze! Don\'t move, you criminal robot! This is the police!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.075_2">Darn! Suspect is running! Launch the Pepper Rope Missile!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.075_3">Haha! I knew this\'d come in handy! I developed it specifically for catching runaway criminals!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.076_1">Wahoo! My screenplay is actually being made into a movie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.076_2">And the Cookie directing it is the onle and only Butter Squid Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.076_3">If my life was a movie, this would definitely be the highlight reel!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.077_1">I\'m all grown up now, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.077_2">Like a proper adult, I\'ll start my mornings with coffee and eat my vegetables!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.077_3">... Wait! Acorn Jellies are on sale?! WHERE?! I need to buy as much as I can!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.078_1">Thanks for coming to the signing session. Oh, you\'re my number one fan? Haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.078_2">I\'m truly honored that my unsolved case files became a published book.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.078_3">There\'s still one Cookie who is on the loose, and I\'ll never give up the chase... Wait, that cheesy scent... Are you...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.079_1">Finally! After one million experiments... I\'ve succeeded!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.079_2">The Candy Engine can now run infinitely! No more charging module needed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.079_3">My research paper is going to shake the whole world, isn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.080_1">A new dragon showed up? And blocking the valley\'s bridge?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.080_2">Haha! No worries. I\'m very familiar with the Dragon\'s Valley.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.080_3">I\'ll head out personally give that dragon a taste of something really spicy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.081_1">The Cherry Fireworks Festival is here! What a perfect name, hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.081_2">A festival named after me, held right in town?! I love it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.081_3">It\'s time to load up the red, blue, and yellow cherry bombs and light up the sky! Boom! BOOM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.082_1">This is awesome! I played my icicle keyboard and sang a song as usual, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.082_2">This time... some icicle friends showed up! Everyone\'s following along, dancing and singing with me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.082_3">Now I\'ve got friends wherever I go, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.083_1">I left the Cookie Kingdom behind... and I have no regrets!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.083_2">I may be a tiny Sugar Gnome, but I\'ll help Cookies in need and defeat the scary swamp monsters too!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.083_3">The hero of the next great story will be me!!! A Sugar Gnome!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.084_1">Hahaha! Being the boss feel pretty great!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.084_2">Carrot Bots! Listen to your leader, me, Peeled Carrot Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.084_3">You\'re gonna plow up these useless fields all over the planet and set up our secret base!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.085_1">Yay! I don\'t need to wun awound to find wice cakes anymoa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.085_2">Now, I can just make as many wice cakes as I want! And mine taste the BEST!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.085_3">If anyone wants wice cakes, you\'d better get in line early in the mowning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.086_1">B.A.D 4\'s hiatus went on way too long...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.086_2">So... I came back to the stage with a solo track!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.086_3">Because I\'m the best, coolest rapper than anyone there is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.087_1">Awesome! The Wafflebots and I finally built an entire city!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.087_2">And get this! There\'re no requirements to move into Wafflebot City! My blueprints don\'t call for anything boring like that!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.087_3">And i-it\'s... not like I made all these houses and rooms for wandering Cookies from abandoned villages or anything, okay?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.088_1">Only after the grimoire was sealed did the curse keeping my contained in the Archives finally break...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.088_2">After all those years of guarding this place... Seeing it gone leaves me feeling strangely... hollow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.088_3">But now, I can finally go see the moon glowing in the open night sky. Just the thought of it makes me truly... happy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.089_1">You came all the way here looking for the Sneaky Sands Clan? What\'s your business...? Ah, stealing Yogurca\'s fabled treasures?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.089_2">You\'re too late. The Sneaky Sands Clan is no longer playing that game. We are the Lilac Clan now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.089_3">And we deal with criminals like you. You\'ll be feeling very sleepy soon, so close your eyes and sleep quietly. Sweet dreams.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.090_1">Pudding hair, check! Bouncy beach ball, check! All set!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.090_2">I\'m way more nervous than the World Beachball Championships...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.090_3">Because today is... the historic day I debut in a sports ad alongside Orange Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.091_1">It\'s truly an honor to be hosting the wedding of two Cookies whose love came true through my magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.091_2">Now, behold! A hat that holds nothing... and TA-DA! An endless stream of roses!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.091_3">Just like these roses, your love will go on forever and ever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.092_1">I thought life in the Vanilla Kingdom would be peaceful...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.092_2">But I didn\'t expect it to be this peaceful. It\'s stirring up a strange hunger within me... An appetite for a new magical research project.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.092_3">Since the coffee at Crow\'s Nest Inn is quite exceptional, I shall begin jotting down some ideas there.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.093_1">My fellow knights! Trust in your commander! I shall lead the way, my friends!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.093_2">With courage and faith, there is no enemy we cannot overcome! OH! When did it get so late?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.093_3">Training ends here for today, my good friends. Sir Dark Choco Cookie has requested my presence for a cup of tea. Farewell!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.094_1">Have you been abandoned by those you trusted and wandering day and night... Welcome to Apricot Jam Village.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.094_2">Here, none will betray you, and no one has to be alone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.094_3">But... if you ever decide to betray us... Hehe, well, I\'m sure you won\'t come to such a foolish decision.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.095_1">One... Two... HUP! Wow! Did you see that?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.095_2">I can stand on the ground with my own two feet now! Even without the Sterile Environment Regulator!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.095_3">Every Cookie in the Sanctum of Healing is healthy again...! It\'s a miracle!!! *Sniffle*</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.096_1">Now then, these are the essentials for pathfinding in Beast-Yeast.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.096_2">First, a caramel blade that stretches to any length. Second, a tent that shifts to match its surroundings in a pinch!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.096_3">First-time customers get a discount! Oh, and the Brave Hero\'s autograph is not for sale!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.097_1">The sea breeze... feels comforting. I never thought I\'d play the piano somewhere other than a concert hall...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.097_2">I think I\'m finally learning to enjoy playing without being bound by a pre-performance ritual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.097_3">As for today, maybe I\'ll play something soft by the shore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.098_1">The applause is still ringing... So many Cookies are here to see me lead the show...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.098_2">I\'m glad I managed to pull off today\'s show...! Another flawless performance with no mistakes...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.098_3">What matters isn\'t worrying about the stage. It\'s trusting the audience and delivering on their expectations!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.099_1">Pompon... Today\'s guest has candy button eyes...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.099_2">I matched the dress to their color of the eyecing... What do you think? What\'s that? It suits them perfectly?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.099_3">Hehe, ever since opening this shop, it feels like Pompon and I have made so many new friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.100_1">... Cookies, Cream Roll Birds, and Snow Spirits...! H-H-Hello, everyone!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.100_2">Thank you for coming to the Poinsettia Choir\'s holiday performance...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Future.Dialogue.100_3">I\'m... a bit nervous, but everyone in the choir practiced hard for today. We hope you enjoy...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.001_1">Rawr! You want to meet my Master?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.001_2">If you want to see Mystical Flour Cookie, you need to stand in line! It ends waaay back there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.001_3">Who am I? Why, I\'m Cloud Haetae Cookie, and I\'m destined to be just as magnificent as my mom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.002_1">The wicked goblin was driven away, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.002_2">Some of the villagers seem to fear me more than they did the goblin...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.002_3">Hm... Maybe they\'d all feel a littler better... if I wasn\'t in the village.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.003_1">Hehe. A crispy body and a fragrant aroma... So that\'s what a Cookie looks like.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.003_2">This feeling... It\'s the first time I\'ve felt this way...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.003_3">The old fox granny said if I survive on flour and butter for 999 days... I could shapeshift into a Cookie myself. Hmmm...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.004_1">Heh-heh! Just as I thought! There\'s more than one world out there!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.004_2">If I write this up as my master\'s thesis, it\'ll turn everything we know upside down!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.004_3">Geniuses are always ahead of their time, heh heh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.005_1">Woof, woof! Puppy Star is so warm and filled with treats!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.005_2">But there\'s a scent in the air that smells so familiar! The soft doughy aroma of my best friend...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.005_3">I\'m going to make another wish! I want to see my best friend Cookie again, woof woof!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.006_1">For the city that took me in... I\'d give up both my claws without a second thought!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.006_2">Even without the title of Chief Protector, my love for Sugarteara will never change.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.006_3">This place and only this place, is my true home.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.007_1">Hello! I\'m the new designer, reporting for my first day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.007_2">I was taught that perfect measurements are the foundation of designing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.007_3">For a style with true refinement, I\'ll work with precision! Not a single millimeter off!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.008_1">Yo! I work up this morning and saw that Ginger Claus left a skateboard for me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.008_2">The bandages on my legs and arms keep piling up, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.008_3">That trick I failed yesterday? I know I\'ll land it today! I just know it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.009_1">Waaah! Scrubbing towels are so scratchy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.009_2">Grandma, you liar! You said it\'d feel refreshing...! But it\'s not even close, waaah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.009_3">Just let me stay in the syrup bath!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.010_1">Even the great Red Dragon makes mistakes from time to time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.010_2">But talking back at every turn, that\'s really no way to hold a conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.010_3">Shall we have a little chat about communicating without hurting each other\'s feelings? It\'s been a while since we\'ve had such a conversation.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.011_1">How long has it been since all the Cookies left? We Sugar Gnomes are the only ones left here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.011_2">The Cookies will come back someday, right...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.011_3">When that day comes... maybe we can finally build the Cookie Kingdom we\'ve all been dreaming of!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.012_1">Ugh, tons of formulas and calculations to memorize today...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.012_2">Is this really what school life is like...? I thought it\'d be different...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.012_3">The break before my next class is a bit long, so I might as well check out that new sandwich shop around the corner!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.013_1">Just as tea leaves steep in hot water, so too shall my resolve grow stronger with every trial.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.013_2">Until the day my crumbs return to the dust of the earth... I will overcome every hardship alongside my comrades.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.013_3">I, a member of the Tea Leaf Knights, swear this upon my shining armor!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.014_1">My friends say foraging for Jelly Berries are fun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.014_2">But me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.014_3">I like finding old stories written on worn-out paper! It\'s the most fun thing in the whole world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.015_1">Wooo...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.015_2">Look at the sky! It\'s turning completely black...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.015_3">Wh-What\'s happening...?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.016_1">Hyah! Heeeyaaah!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.016_2">One day, I\'m gonna build some big muscles and lift every dumbbell I can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.016_3">Today... I\'ll warm up with some sit-ups! Haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.017_1">Hmph! That wizard refused to take me as an apprentice?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.017_2">Just you wait...! I\'m a Cookie who means business! And when I mean business, I really, really mean it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.017_3">One day, you\'ll regret not taking me in as an apprentice! You had your chance!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.018_1">Hehe... You... You\'re the Cookie... who made me...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.018_2">... W-Why are you... glaring at me? Why are you saying... I\'m useless...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.018_3">I... I... never asked to... be made... in the first place...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.019_1">The time is nigh... Almost...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.019_2">The day this cursed village is swallowed in flames.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.019_3">The day this village that fed on my divine power... The forsaken Sacred Pomegranate Tree... All will burn!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.020_1">Huh? Who are... Ah, I see. Timekeeper Cookie sent you here, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.020_2">Do me a favor. If you ever run into someone called String Gummy Cookie, tell him I said thank you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.020_3">Deliver the message myself? Haha, I wish I could. But you probably already know... I\'m not supposed to exist anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.021_1">Now then... Where\'s my next class...? Huh? Why is my locker stuffed with chocolates?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.021_2">There\'s a note! \"For the Cookie who stole my heart\"...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.021_3">Ha! There\'s no way I can carry all this stuff in one trip.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.022_1">I finally chased off those outsiders lurking near the forest...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.022_2">I\'m most comfortable by myself. These fireflies are the only ones who truly understand me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.022_3">Making friends with other Cookies... Hm, I can\'t even picture it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.023_1">Ugh! My hair\'s fine already, sis! I just put sour cream mousse in it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.023_2">Huh? You made me an outfit? Ew, no way I\'m wearing something like th-</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.023_3">Wait... Is that a dinosaur on the front? Fine, hand it over. I\'ll at least try it on!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.024_1">Dear... Ginger... Claus...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.024_2">This year, I didn\'t cry. And I listened to my teacher. Please don\'t forget the stethoscope I asked for.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.024_3">I want to become a doctor who fixes sick Cookies before they get really, really sick!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.025_1">Mom! I finished my homework! What\'re we having for snacks today? Macarons?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.025_2">Awesome! Look at\'em go \'round and \'round! Oh, I just thought of a cool new beat!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.026_1">Get it together, Raspberry Mousse Cookie! In your current state, you\'ll only disgrace the family name!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.026_2">I need to practice harder... Day and night, without rest...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.026_3">Wait... Drifting on the wind from somewhere... What is this aroma...? Roses?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.027_1">To think I\'d become a Dessert Guardian... I\'ll carry out every duty flawlessly, without fail!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.027_2">Even as Sugar Swan Cookie departs on a great journey...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.027_3">... I will make sure that the cold of winter will never set foot in Dessert Paradise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.028_1">Ugh... Why do I have to go to school?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.028_2">I\'ll admit, the cafeteria\'s food at Scovillia is pretty good and spicy, but getting out of the bed is too hard...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.028_3">And why does the chieftain always say, \"I expect great things from you\"? I\'m tired of hearing it every single day... Ugh.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.029_1">Nnngh... I need to find a way out of this oven before it\'s too late.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.029_2">Wait, what\'s that? Is that a candy wand? It looks like it could cast some pretty serious magic!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.029_3">Alright... While the witch is looking away, I\'ll make a run for it and grab it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.030_1">Boom, boom, ba-dum, ba-dum! Oh... Why does my drum sound so quiet?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.030_2">I just wish I could march with a big, bold, booming drumbeat like the others...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.030_3">Wait... Did that Macaron Animal just... move to the rhythm of my drum?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.031_1">Mother, father! The treasure of Sugarteara is truly wondrous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.031_2">A teardrop shed when a celestial saw the moon reflected on the night sky...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.031_3">As a member of the Rays, I will do everything I can protect this divine treasure.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.032_1">I\'ve been performing on the streets for so long now...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.032_2">But no one stops to listen... And everyone just mocks me for smelling like toothpaste...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.032_3">Okay... haha! Fine then! Starting today, I will live a new life under a new name so sharp and distinguished, none shall ever forget it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.033_1">Hm... Are those Cookies trying to leave the house???</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.033_2">There\'s all sorts of dangerous things out there! Should... I go too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.033_3">WAIT! What\'s that shiny thing over there?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.034_1">Where is it I am heading now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.034_2">I wandered without direction... until I have been brought here, deep in the forest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.034_3">Yes... The verdant call from this small plant has led me here... </string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.035_1">Though built from the hands of mere Cookies, this palace is quite the spectacle.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.035_2">Now, I must begin gathering the strength I\'ve lost when I was bound to this frail Cookie form.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.035_3">Hydrangea Cookie. Spread word to the Cookies of this land. Tell them of a mystical festival where their wishes can be granted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.036_1">Area locked down! Alien Cookie apprehended in approximately one minute of deployment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.036_2">Did you really think slapping a bread bag over your head would keep us from recognizing you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.037_1">Starting next year, I\'ll be an official Holiday Cookie too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.037_2">For the sake of every child\'s happy smile... from the Tropical Soda Islands to the Dragon\'s Valley...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.037_3">Wherever there are young Cookies, I\'ll do my best to deliver gifts to every single one of them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.038_1">Hmph... Even if I can\'t summon a single spark right now, I\'m gonna become a great wizard someday!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.038_2">But... I can\'t use magic yet. How am I supposed to prove how incredible I really I am?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.038_3">I have an idea...! If I bring back a scale from the Red Dragon of Dragon\'s Valley, everyone will start believing me!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.039_1">Pardon me? The young master said he wants to become a royal inspector one day?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.039_2">Haha, I\'m sure he\'s just joking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.039_3">Have you ever seen a royal inspector who can\'t do anything himself? Haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.040_1">Huff... huff... Just a little bit further, and I\'ll...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.040_2">If I practice with the bo staff every single day... Maybe my family will finally recognize my skills...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.040_3">I can become like Peach Cookie, maybe even better! I know I can!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.041_1">Ha, that\'s right. Earning Coins is important, but sharing them matters more.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.041_2">The Cookies we help today may be the ones who help us tomorrow.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.041_3">Do you understand, Cheesecake Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.042_1">Wait, wait! The key to this scene is right here in front of our noses...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.042_2">Tch... Rejected again. The investors, the critics... Why can\'t anyone see the brilliance of my screenplay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.042_3">No, I can\'t give up now! My own vision... my own cinematic universe... I\'ll bring it to life no matter the odds!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.043_1">Ugh! The wind, rain, and waves are rocking the boat all at once...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.043_2">There\'s no way I can haul in the nets like this...! Maybe I\'ll... ARGH! The catch broke through the net and swam away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.043_3">I\'ll catch you one day, Kingfish! Just you wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.044_1">So you wish to hear the story of the day I came into being, riding the thread of sugar through chaos.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.044_2">Where should I begin...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.044_3">Yes, let\'s start with that day... when the earth itself breathed with every beat of my wings, and the mountains and seas turned sweet.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.045_1">They ssay it\'ss better to be the head of the sserpent than the tail of a dragon... Only those lacking vision sspeak in ssuch a manner.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.045_2">Opportunity findss those who wait... When I become a dragon, the era of SSnake Fruit Cookie shall open!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.045_3">And when it doess, those who dared mock me and call me a mere ssnake will have no choice but to bow!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.046_1">Huh? Why isn\'t the camper moving? Did it get stuck in the mud?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.046_2">Oh... it\'s out of gas. I thought I checked before I left... I\'ll have to ask someone nearby for help.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.046_3">Wait a second... These aren\'t the camping grounds at all! It\'s too dark to tell where I am. What- AGH! My flashlight...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.047_1">High Oracle, look at this! I drew it myself!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.047_2">This is the Nebula Chalice! And that\'s me, all grown up, serving as an Oracle in the Pantheon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.047_3">I want to read the stars one day too, just like you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.048_1">Urgh... Is this the end? I don\'t have... the strength to hold on much longer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.048_2">The time rift is... slowly consuming me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.048_3">I guess... this is really how it ends... Huh? Wh-What...? Who\'re you?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.049_1">Oh, excuse me? I didn\'t order this. Hm? It\'s on the house?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.049_2">Interesting. A glass of juice with a hint of aromatic, sweet flowers...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.049_3">Haha, you know, one day... I\'d love to open my own juice bar. Thank you for the words of encouragement.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.050_1">Ah, thank you for your concern, but everything\'s alright. Yes, we named her Walnut Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.050_2">Did someone report an incident? It\'s okay, it\'s fine. Of course we should respond.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.050_3">I need to build a world where my daughter can live in peace, as soon as possible!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.051_1">Earl Grey Cookie, at your service.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.051_2">It is an honor to welcome you to... our hotel...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.051_3">Sigh... No matter how many times I say it... It\'s still just me, alone in this empty hotel with no guests...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.052_1">Oops... I failed the exam again?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.052_2">I had no idea becoming a Holiday Cookie would be this difficult... But I won\'t give up!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.052_3">Every young Cookie deserves to be happy! I\'ll keep trying, for them! I\'ll try as many times as it takes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.053_1">Yaaawn... I\'m so sleepy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.053_2">Why do I get so sleepy whenever I try to meditate...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.053_3">And even when if I manage to stay awake, my mind keeps wandering! Argh, meditation is so hard!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.054_1">Mini Orange Mouse! Little mousy! Where did you go?! I looked away for a split second...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.054_2">Oh! I heard something in those bushes! Alrighty then... I\'ll sneak up and... HYAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.054_3">Ow! Oops, I\'m so sorry! I thought you were my friend, hehe... What\'s your name? Nice to meet you, Lemon Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.055_1">Why is our world filled with conflict and evil... If only it was filled with nothing but love and peace...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.055_2">Yes... Perhaps, even in a world torn by chaos, music can still reach the hearts and minds of Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.055_3">I have determined my path! I will wander this world and sing the songs of love and peace!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.056_1">Hm? OH! Is this ginseng...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.056_2">What\'s this?! You\'re not ginseng! You\'re just a balloon flower root!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.056_3">Hm? You want to know how to become ginseng? Ho ho ho, very well. Follow me, little root.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.057_1">The teacher told me the same thing again.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.057_2">My swordsmanship is dangerous, and I need to keep my emotions in check.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.057_3">My fears and feelings need to be hidden away... I need to endure and carry on. As long as I\'m careful, everything should be fine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.058_1">Three scholarships in a row...? Thank you so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.058_2">I\'m gonna keep going all out! Water, land, or sky, it doesn\'t matter!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.058_3">I\'ll become the best stunt performer and make this school proud!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.059_1">Here I go! Take this...! Shoot, and goal- WHAT?! You blocked me again?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.059_2">So you\'re not gonna take it easy on me, huh? Fine! Just watch me, sis!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.059_3">I might lose now, but just you wait! I\'m gonna be a famous soccer player one day, haha!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.060_1">Chieftain. Why does everyone in our village pour chocolate over their heads?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.060_2">Oh? So... if I want to be a true warrior, I need to do this ritual too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.060_3">Hehe, when I grow up, I want to do the ritual too! I\'ll pour chocolate and come a strong warrior!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.061_1">Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.061_2">I learned how to support others from someone I really admire. So... where should I begin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.061_3">Hm, maybe I\'ll start by looking into some promising, up-and-coming artists!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.062_1">That guy\'s been muttering strange things lately... Treasure this, dark seas that...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.062_2">I\'d hate to seem him throw away his pride for the navy to chase riches... Maybe I\'ll bring him a glass of rum juice and talk some sense into him.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.062_3">Wait... He just hopped into a lifeboat! Hold it right there, Pirate Cookie!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.063_1">My goodness! It\'s an invitation to the royal palace\'s year-end ball!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.063_2">All I did was offer a cup of cocoa to a Cookie on the street... He looked like he needed it, but he was a prince...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.063_3">I wonder if there\'ll be cocoa at the ball? Hehe!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.064_1">What is this feeling...? I finally have a tower to call my own, and yet my heart feels empty...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.064_2">I hear the laughter of Cookies in the village below, all the way from up here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.064_3">Hm, maybe I\'ll start a hobby. I can start by collecting things that shine... just like those twinkling village lights.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.065_1">Look, little spiders. This is our new home. Look around to your hearts\' content, my friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.065_2">Since it\'s moving day, I think I\'ll take out the tea set I\'ve been saving for a day like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.065_3">And you there, the one listening to me from out there. Would you like to join me for a cup of tea as well?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.066_1">Excuse me. You, the gentleman in the pink icing. Would you care to dance with me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.066_2">You don\'t know how to dance? Nonsense. Let the music course through you, carry you into a state of flowing movement. Dancing comes from the heart!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.066_3">Here, take my hand. Like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.067_1">So these creatures are called... Cookies? Not one of them can even lift their heads to even peek up towards me.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.067_2">Hm, I suppose they are far too small to bear the presence of a great dragon such as myself.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.067_3">Their offerings are laughably crude. But I will accept them as a special favor... Consider yourselves honored, little Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.068_1">The Hollyberry Magazine... Tch, nothing but dull news as usual.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.068_2">Where\'s the one who called me a big lizard? Hasn\'t she come back yet?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.068_3">Grrr...! Where am I supposed to find a Cookie who can actually keep me entertained?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.069_1">Your dough... is soft...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.069_2">You\'re... stubborn like me. Born with that look... of not listening to anyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.069_3">Something sweet has... come into my life at last. After all these... spicy years...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.070_1">Whoa! What was that?! It\'s like the stars are exploding in the night sky!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.070_2">Huh? They\'re called firecrackers? Hehe, everyone looks like they\'re having so much looking at them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.070_3">Oh, I get it! As long as there are firecrackers, everyone can feel like they\'re at a fun and happy party!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.071_1">Strange. Every moment I dream, I see a world teeming with insignificant critters...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.071_2">The time when my powers shall be lost draws near... Until then, I shall sleep a long and deep sleep.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.071_3">Hmph... Such trivial creatures could never change this world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.072_1">Ahaha! Even that haughty Blue Dragon ended up on their knees before me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.072_2">Now, there\'s no dragon left who hasn\'t knelt to my glorious- Wait...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.072_3">The Ivory Dragon is still standing! Hehe, I wonder just how that prideful, arrogant one can last against me...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.073_1">Those Cookies\' uniforms... It looks like they\'re students from Cheese Dough Academy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.073_2">If I went to school, I could study whatever I wanted to, right? But... I can\'t afford the tuition...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.073_3">Gah! What\'s this flyer...? Now Hiring: Pizza Deliveries? Bonus Coins based on the number of deliveries made in a day?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.074_1">Welcome, Cookies. I am glad to see you again...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.074_2">The sound of your laughter filling CookieLand feels like the Song of Happiness itself...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.074_3">I wish CookieLand could always be filled with such pure, joyful laughter for generations...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.075_1">I still remember the day I winded up this box\'s key for the first time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.075_2">The swan on top of the music box started to spin, slowly, gracefully...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.075_3">It feels like a fleeting dream once lived inside this very box... I wonder who it belonged to?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.076_1">Haharrr! I\'ve finally mapped the exact spot of the very legends themselves! The riches of the entire world are hidden just beyond this point!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.076_2">I\'d throw my very soul into the depths of the sea to claim the legendary treasures of the deep!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.076_3">Oh, Great Master of the Depths! Let me live until I\'ve claimed every last treasure in this world! Hahaaa!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.077_1">Hi there! Did I startle you? I\'ve been here the whole time...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.077_2">That ghost drawing. Did you make it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.077_3">Oh, you\'re not scared of ghosts, are you? Can I join the ghost club too?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.078_1">Ugh... it\'s hot, so hot! But this is exactly the kind of heat that makes training feel real!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.078_2">I won\'t escape this oven until my training is complete!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.078_3">My dough is still too soft to leave!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.079_1">At first, I thought my beard was trembling from the cold...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.079_2">But then the fates before my eyes began pouring out as written words!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.079_3">That\'s when I first realized my beard holds an extraordinary power!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.080_1">Huh?! That voice...! Who is it???</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.080_2">Rising star... Shining Glitter Cookie\'s... debut? Is this really a new singer?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.080_3">Her voice...! It feels like I\'ve been struck by lightning!!! One day, I will share the stage with that amazing Cookie! I simply must!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.081_1">Sigh, why am I even at an archery competition? The sun\'s so nice... I\'d rather be watching the clouds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.081_2">Oops! I forgot to miss on purpose... Ugh, and I accidentally hit every target?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.081_3">I need to run before my brother tells me to enter a bigger tournament!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.082_1">... Why are you crying, child?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.082_2">I can tell your heart must be hurting because you\'re crying without saying a single word...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.082_3">Here, these are herbs I grew myself. Take a deep breath of their gentle scents, and your heart will start to settle. There, are you feeling better?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.083_1">Whoa...! Ack...! This legendary white sugar stallion refuses to let me ride upon it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.083_2">But there\'s no such thing as giving up for someone destined to be Knight Commander!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.083_3">Once more unto the breach! Come, noble stallion! We shall ride to grand adventures together, just you wait!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.084_1">There is no corner of the Witch\'s cupboard untouched by the glory of House Danish.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.084_2">I swear upon this sword today... the honor and majesty of our family will stretch on into eternity!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.085_1">I never imagined I\'d wear the title of maestro!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.085_2">To lead our Sugar Gnomes in the right direction, I will need to carry myself with dignity!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.085_3">But how...? AH! A beard! I will grow a glorious and dignified beard with the longest, fullest sugar whiskers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.086_1">The world is full of mysteries, and there are truly so many fun places in it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.086_2">I\'m gonna visit every continent there is! I\'ve hopped to other villages through my Bunny Tunnel before, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.086_3">I wonder if I can reach even the farthest away places! Ehe he, I\'m gonna try! Time to hoppity hop hop!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.087_1">My, my! Looks like something interesting has popped up.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.087_2">The ever-pungent Smoked Cheese Cookie is carrying a puppy on his back!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.087_3">I wonder just how long those two will stay on good terms... Care to place a bet, Golden Cheese Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.088_1">Mmm...? Smo... Chee... Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.088_2">Smo...ke Cheese Coo...kie! I want to play...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.089_1">Many members of our troupe have been tearing up over the ringmaster\'s outbursts lately...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.089_2">Someday, there will come a day when the ringmaster and the troupe can laugh together, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.089_3">But until then... the show must go on and the stage must keep shining! I will share a few words of encouragement with everyone today.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.090_1">Ugh, I can\'t stand being cooped up in this stuffy classroom. Riding my Black Tiger Bike is the only time I feel really alive!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.090_2">Yesss! This is the freedom I\'ve been after!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.090_3">It\'s time to cut through the wind and ride like our dough\'s about to burst!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.091_1">What? The aisle\'s decorations are ruined? Hm, let me see...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.091_2">Oh dear...! We were supposed to get summery cream flowers, not the wintry ones...! I\'ll find some replacements, right away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.091_3">I\'ll do everything to make your special day perfect! And besides, I can\'t ruin my very first job as a wedding planner!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.092_1">Mmm...! Candy... Hehe, so many candies... in this garden...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.092_2">Cookie? I missed you... too... First Cr... ZZZzzz...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.093_1">Ha. Everyone thought I was deep in anguishing thoughts before the match.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.093_2">Truth is, I was just daydreaming about cold sikhye! Then that one move popped into my head like a grain of rice! Before I knew it, I won!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.093_3">Guess there was no need to be so nervous about my first match, heh!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.095_1">Why do Cookies crumble so easily...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.095_2">One who was full of dreams just yesterday... Another who went adventuring with hopes of becoming a hero...</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.095_3">What is it that you intend, O Almighty?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.096_1">Huh? That sound... Is something wrong with the syrup pump again?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.096_2">I\'d better take apart the entire faucet and fix it in one go before... AGH?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.096_3">S-S-Stop! N-No! The whole garden is gonna get flooded in syrup! I need to fix this!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.097_1">What\'s that? Art isn\'t art unless it\'s refined and proper? BAH!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.097_2">I define my own art and my own world!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.097_3">So long, boring and old-fashioned art school! It\'s time for the world to embrace some color! POW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.098_1">I heard everything, Mozzarella Cookie. You made a bet with Golden Cheese Cookie, did you not?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.098_2">Like spoiled cheese, your expectations are off.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.098_3">There\'s no way the puppy I have raised and cared for would not get along with me!</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.100_1">A newcomer won the tournament?</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.100_2">Hm, a move that popped into the train of thought like a grain of rice? Not bad, but one cannot rely on luck every time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_OneMillionDoors.Timekeeper.Past.Dialogue.100_3">The proper strategy in the game of Go is building your own path, steadily, stone by stone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening01">Sugar &amp; Salt: Why does no one believe us?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening02">Sugar: We didn\'t do anything wrong. All we wanted was a life of happiness.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening03">Salt: We did nothing. They were the one who committed sin.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening04">Sugar: Why harm us when we did nothing wrong?
Salt: Why did our mother have to disappear?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening05">Sugar &amp; Salt: Why?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening06">Salt: Why are you swayed by the tears of the guilty?
Sugar: How can a single tear wash away wrongdoing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening07">Salt: Then... the guilty sinner came back for us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening08">Sugar: An unknown power merely protected us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening09">Sugar: But it ended up becoming our crime?
Salt: Ah... I see.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening10">Sugar &amp; Salt: They simply refused to hear anything from a witch.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening11">Sugar &amp; Salt: Even with no wrongdoing, hatred alone can create a crime.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening12">Salt: Had the savior not appeared...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening13">Sugar: We would have vanished... Just like our mother.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening14">Salt: But not anymore.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening15">Sugar: In the Court of Judgment, none shall suffer injustice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_Opening16">Sugar &amp; Salt: All will be judged by the Scales.</string>
  <string name="$SAGA.06.CinematicOpeningTitle">Court of Judgment</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch01">Who is the Sinner?</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch01.SQ1">The Trial Begins!</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch01.SQ2">The Scale of Good and Evil</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch01.SQ3">Assistants to the Supervisor of Records</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch01.SQ4">Conspiracy of the Persecuted</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch02">In the Face of Absolute Truth</string>
  <string name="$Saga.06.Ch02.SQ1">Is Saffron Cookie Guilty?</string>
