  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_1">My dear Cookies, is our crispiness truly eternal? Can our fragile, doughy forms last forever?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_2">Whoa! There\'s a huge crowd in here! I wonder what\'s going on?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_3">Hm? You don\'t know? That\'s Saffron Cookie! She\'s been summoned to court today just for sharing the truth! The Cookies who hear her words find the courage to leave for a haven of peace!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_4">Ah... Saffron Cookie... I feel like my dough\'s gone staler than yesterday... In the end, I will crumble someday, won\'t I?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_5">Poor soul... that is the law of this world. Of our existence. But fear not, my friend.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_6">For when you are returned to the First Dough in the warm embrace of the Absolute... there will be nothing left to fear.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_7">The First Dough...? The Absolute...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_8">Empty yourself, and set out toward the primordial affection and warmth. Toward a haven where you will never go stale...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_9">Saffron Cookie, please stand by! You will be called into the courtroom shortly!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_10">Of course. I await your summons. My friends... I am afraid the rest of my story will have to wait for another time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_11">Madam Saffron Cookie...! Just a moment! Those who never came back... Salvation has truly found them, hasn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_12">... I believe so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_13">I-It\'s time to deliver the verdict on Choco Gold Cookie and Roasted Salt Cookie\'s cases...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_14">Order! Everyone, please be quiet!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_15">Haha! I never once stepped outside the law, so how could I possibly be guilty? This is all just jealousy over my gold dust, I\'m telling you.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_16">Pipe down, you slimy loan shark! Even if you walk free, I\'ll never forgive you!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_17">I apologize. If only I... *Sigh* Maybe that Cookie would not have crumbled...if I still had my medical license...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_18">No, doctor! Treatment was the right thing to do, and it was perfectly fine! Licensed or not, you were the only one who helped us! You are our doctor!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_19">Yikes...! Everything\'s so complicated and... overwhelming! How are we supposed to find the Cookie of the First Batch in a place like this?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_20">We haven\'t even started looking yet, but... my head is already spinning...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_21">ORDER! Anyone who dares make a scene before the Scale of Good and Evil will be charged with contempt of court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_22">Eeep...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_23">... First Salt Cookie, First Sugar Cookie. Please resume the trial.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_24">Very well. Now... the verdict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_25">Alright! First up... Choco Gold Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_27">GUILTY! The terms of the contract were honored to the letter, yes, but the suffering inflicted upon so many Cookies weighs heavily! The scales have spoken!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_28">Wh-WHAT?! The scales can weigh something like THAT?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_29">Next. Roasted Salt Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_31">Nothing changes the fact that you are practicing medicine without a license. But considering the urgent action required to save a life... This court sentences you to pay a fine and serve three days of community service.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_32">Oh...! Thank you, thank you so much!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_33">So that\'s the Scale of Good and Evil! Incredible...! It weighs not just the law, but everything involved in any case!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_34">Shh, Wizard Cookie! We\'re gonna get thrown out if you keep talking...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_35">Alrighty...! So then, who\'s next?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_36">Next is the trial of Saffron Cookie...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_38">What a beautiful scale... But can that little toy truly measure the weight of truth?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_39">... Let us begin. The trial on the charges of causing numerous Cookies to go missing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_1">Defendant: Saffron Cookie. Dozens of Cookies have gone missing in recent times. Every one of them was last seen attending the defendant\'s gatherings before they vanished.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_2">It has been alleged that the defendant has confined them or abducted them to an undisclosed location.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_3">I see. Shall we hear from the accused herself about these allegations?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_4">Confinement? Abduction? I have never once laid a hand on any of them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_5">I did nothing more than guide them toward the truth, and a place of peaceful rest...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_6">... Guide? Are you saying you admit to having a hand in these Cookies\' disappearances?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_7">I am merely saying their disappearances were of their own volition and free will.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_8">Souls who have faced and seen the truth can no longer endure the soggy weight of reality... Thus, they seek out the flame on their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_9">How could leading them there be counted as a sin? If anything, guiding their souls to salvation should be rewarded.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_10">I mean, when you put it that way... If she didn\'t drag anyone by force, is it really a crime?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_11">But they all vanished without a trace and no one knows if they\'re alive! Her behavior... It\'s equal to incitement.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_12">......</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_13">See here. Even the great scale hesitates. It has not tipped to either side.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_14">How much does the will drawn forth from a pure heart weigh? Can the scales truly measure the worth and weight of goodwill aimed at saving a soul?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_15">Defendant. Are you seriously standing in this sacred courtroom and daring to challenge the authority of the sacred scales?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_16">If anything, I wish to learn... to know. I am positing a question. I have only spoken the truth, and yet this court still seeks to condemn me. Is this truly a fair trial?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_17">Forcing judgment upon matters the scale itself cannot weigh... Your arrogance is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_18">Has it never occurred to you that such arrogance only makes the world, and we who live in it, grow more stale...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_19">Defendant! One more word and this court may charge you with contempt!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_20">Hold on... Do you see that shadow on the other side of the glass?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_21">Hm? What...? I don\'t see anything.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_22">Could that be the Cookie of the First Batch? Oh... W-W-Wait...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_23">S-Stop pushing...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_24">Ow, ow, ow! Wizard Cookie...! We fell flat on our faces...! Why did you keep shoving us?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_25">Whoops, sorry. I was just trying to get a better look at the shadow reflected onto the glass up there...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_26">Silence! How dare anyone cause a commotion in this sacred courtroom!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_27">My, my... Quite the rowdy guests. Have they lost their way, I wonder?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_28">Hm? What\'s with all the commotion?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ2_POR1_29">For now... This trial is suspended.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_1">Your Honors! I demand these
outsiders be charged with
contempt of court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_2">I\'ll have them dragged
to the Sugar Glass Dome
this instant!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_3">Wait, wait!
We\'re not trying to
stir up any trouble!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_4">That\'s right...!
We\'re just... trying to find
a Cookie of the First-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_5">Disrupting this court is a
crime most serious, and
you will serve your sentence!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_6">... Objection.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_7">If they had no ill intent,
perhaps a different
sentence instead?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_8">Candy Chain Cookie!
Managing order in
this court is MY job!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_9">It is a waste of time and
resources to detain Cookies
unrelated to this trial!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_10">... And we\'re already
short-staffed as it is!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_11">The recent string of
cases has pushed the
Records Department
to the breaking point.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_12">Please consider assigning
these Cookies as temporary
assistants. I\'m begging you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_13">Well... it did look like they
just tripped and fell...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_14">It does seem
excessive to lock them
up for being clumsy.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_15">Alrighty! You there!
The disruptive
clumsy ones!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_16">You shall be given the
chance to repay the court
for the... minor disturbance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_17">Until the conclusion of
this trial, you are to serve
as temporary assistants!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_18">With that settled...!
This trial will resume
tomorrow at the same time!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_19">Tread carefully during
your investigations. The truth runs
far hotter than one might expect.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_20">Saffron Cookie! You are to
remain in the Sugar Glass Dome
until the trial resumes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_21">PHEW!
That was close...
Thanks for saving us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_22">Do not celebrate just yet. By the
time you\'re done, you just may
beg to get sent to the dome.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_23">Don\'t worry! Research and
investigation are just up my alley.
So... Where do we start?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_24">We must first look into the
list of Cookies who attended
her public speeches and
trace their every step.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_25">Just hearing that makes it sound like...
an enormous amount of work...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_26">That gathering we saw earlier...
The way it looked, it kinda sounds
like everyone would just
say they left on their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_27">Exactly. Most of the missing
Cookies disappeared of their
own accord after the gatherings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_28">Does it not strike you as strange?
Vanishing without a single word,
not even a note, to family or friends?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_29">So we need to uncover
the truth buried underneath all this.
Saffron Cookie\'s so-called \"truth\"!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_30">Indeed. You must find out
what kind of \"truth\" she
used to reel them all in.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_31">Very well! Let\'s dig in, crack
this puzzle, and prove ourselves!
And then...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_32">We can go straight to First Salt
Cookie and First Sugar Cookie
and ask them about the First Batcher!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_1">Madam Saffron Cookie... forced to stay in the Sugar Glass Dome? But... she didn\'t do anything wrong...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_2">Everyone, step back! The defendant is being escorted!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_3">Persecuted for just speaking the truth... This is so unfair...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_4">There\'s no reason to wait for some sham of a trial! Let\'s get her out of here, NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_5">Try it. I dare you. All of you will be next!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_6">Please, my friends. That\'s enough.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_7">Rock Candy Cookie. Would you please give us a brief moment alone? I shall calm their nerves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_8">One moment. Just one. Anything suspicious and I\'m arresting the lot of you!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_9">*Sob sob*
Madam Saffron Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_10">Settle down, my friends. There is nothing to grieve. If the Absolute is watching... this injustice will not go unanswered.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_11">Listen closely. The Absolute holds a power far greater than this broken courtroom could ever hope to wield.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_12">Ah-ha...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_13">With your devotion, the injustice committed against me, to all of us, can yet be undone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_14">True salvation does not come to those who simply wait in silence... Be prepared.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_15">To undo this injustice... we must raise our voices and cry out. I understand...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_16">It\'s time to deliver a true verdict to the court that falsely imprisoned you and turned its back on the one real truth!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_17">We have much to do.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_18">Until we meet again, please take good care of yourself, Madam Saffron Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_19">Walk with the Absolute, my friends.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_20">Done chatting? Good. Time to move!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_21">... And now, we shall see how long the scales can hold before something far beyond its meager power arrives.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_22">Huh? Did you say something?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_CUT1_23">Heh... It was merely a thought spoken out loud.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_1">What do you think, First Sugar Cookie? Do you believe those Cookies will manage to bring us any proper, infallible evidence?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_2">Who knows! But there\'s a spark of genuine purpose in them that I find pretty interesting!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_3">Say... Do you feel like something about this trial feels different from everything we\'ve handled before? Or is it just me?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_4">No, it does feel different. Whatever is hidden here, it runs along a different path than the good and evil we are familiar with weighing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_5">You know... I wonder! Could it be connected to something from... long ago?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_6">... Hm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_7">Your Honors. First Salt Cookie, First Sugar Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_8">The defendant, witnesses, the Supervisor of Records and his \"assistants\", and the Overseer of the Isolation Ward are all seated and ready...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_9">Oh? The overseer is present as well? Were they not currently undergoing repairs?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_10">Clarification. In the event the trial concludes with a guilty verdict... Directive: immediate escort of the convicted to the Sugar Glass Dome. Optional? No, required.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_11">Yes, yes, we know! Alrighty, please take a seat in the gallery for now, overseer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_12">Acknowledged. Proceeding to... gallery, empty seat. Initiating movement.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_13">Let\'s get this trial back on track!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_14">The defendant\'s argument concluded before we adjourned, so the next order of business shall be cross-examination.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_15">Candy Chain Cookie. Are you ready to proceed?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_16">Yes, Your Honors. The temporary assistants you have assigned to me have managed to secure witness testimonies. I shall have them present their findings directly.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_17">We tracked down someone who attended one of Saffron Cookie\'s speeches before the trial! The witness is here with us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_18">Allow me to introduce... Zero Sugar Cookie! He\'ll explain everything!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_19">Hya hyem! I attended one of that Cookie\'s big speeches out of curiosity! I\'m telling ya, she said some really remarkable stuff.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_20">She spoke of sweet, eternal rest and told everyone to seek out the hottest place they could find!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_21">The way she described this \"haven\"... it sounded exactly like the oven. You know the one, right? The one everyone whispers about! Ain\'t that scary?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_22">*GASP!*
So Saffron Cookie... really sent everyone to their...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_23">The Cookies who never came back must have walked straight into the oven on their own two feet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_24">Hold it! Did he just say \"Must have\"? Without solid evidence, he\'s essentially just guessing!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_25">I recognize him! He was once convicted of fraud in this very courtroom!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_26">Wh-What? Is that true, Zero Sugar Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_27">Hyahem...! Well, that\'s practically ancient history at this point!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_28">What Saffron Cookie was preaching is still suspicious either way! The oven does exist! We\'ve seen it for ourselves before!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_29">The very witness they brought forward was convicted of fraud before? Here?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_30">Wait... so Zero Sugar Cookie is a con artist? A professional liar? How could they bring in someone like THAT to testify...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_31">Silence! Be quiet! Keep it down! There will be no disruptions to this trial!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_32">The point is... Wherever Saffron Cookie is sending them, it has to be somewhere dangerous! And-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_33">My, my. Do you truly believe I mean to harm those who listen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_34">I simply could not bear to watch our fellow Cookies suffer through a soggy, painful existence any longer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_35">But... everyone who left after listening to you... None of them have come back...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_36">They have not failed to return. They have gone somewhere they have no reason to return from.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_37">You claim to have seen and know the oven. Then surely you understand the fate that awaits us... trembling atop a great dining table...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ1_POR1_38">...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_1">Alas, our lives are not eternal. But the fear born from our own fragile, doughy limits...? That FEAR is what lasts forever!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_2">The truth I have shared is a simple one. Every Cookie must return to the state in which they were most complete... most perfect.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_3">... To trace back through the First Oven, and return to the First Dough, when all was one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_4">The First... Oven...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_6">Look upon this scale! This so-called instrument of absolute truth. It weighs the depth of malice and the gravity of sin beyond what the mortal eye can see!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_7">If there was even a trace of malice or ill intent behind my words, even the faintest desire to harm my fellow Cookies, would not the scales have tipped already?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_9">Candy Chain Cookie... Are there any traces of evidence to prove malicious intent?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_10">...... My team of temporary assistants and I have traced the movements and remaining records of the missing Cookies.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_11">We examined Saffron Cookie\'s statements, actions, and the testimonies of those who were swayed by her influence...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_12">However, there appears to be no desire to deceive, and no desire to harm. Not a single grain of malicious intent could be confirmed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_13">Saffron Cookie\'s actions are rooted entirely in this so-called \"truth\" she genuinely believes and upholds.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_14">Her conviction runs so deep, there\'s no intent to deceive at all. There\'s essentially nothing to place on the scales...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_15">The law has always hinged on the concept of intent. If the intent is pure and from the heart, how can it be labeled a crime?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_16">I did nothing more than show lost souls the way back home...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_17">They will not return, and have no need to, for they have found eternal rest.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_18">By my flour and salt...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_19">We worked so hard sifting through all that paperwork to find something... Is the trial just going to end like this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_20">By the sugars in the stars... Look at Saffron Cookie\'s face. Not even a flicker of doubt... Maybe she really means it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_21">Cross-referencing records... Anomalous egg on file. Eyewitness testimony, placing it with Saffron Cookie. Validity confirmed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_22">Huh...? A winged egg...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_23">Tell us more!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_24">Saffron Cookie. Pre-gathering record: clean. No prior criminal record or investigative history. However...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_25">Scanning reports... Witnessed: defendant, Saffron Cookie, acquiring a winged egg. Post-acquisition: sudden onset of speeches and public gatherings.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_26">Hypothesis: Gatherings and winged egg, possible correlation. Probability: significant. Awaiting assessment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_27">What do you think you\'re doing? Chattering away in the middle of a trial?! I\'ll have you thrown in-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_28">We\'re not chattering! It\'s about the trial!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_29">Saffron Cookie. You said there wasn\'t a single shred of deceptive or ill intent, correct?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_30">Then answer me this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_31">This truth you preach... Did someone preach it to you? Was that individual... First Egg Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_32">...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_33">What is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_34">Ah, so you know of her too? She is the one soul who holds knowledge of every truth there is.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_35">Yes, First Egg Cookie reached out to me. She showed me the truth, through her own hand and grace.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_1">First Egg Cookie... was the one who taught you this...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_2">NO! Wake up and smell the frosting! First Egg Cookie is dangerous!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_3">She\'s been trying to kidnap Cookies of the First Batch from the other First Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_4">And while we\'re on the topic... First Salt Cookie! First Sugar Cookie! We don\'t have time for this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_5">If Saffron Cookie is serving First Egg Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_6">This whole thing could be a conspiracy to target the Cookie of the First Batch under your protection!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_7">... First Salt Cookie. If she\'s targeting the Cookies of the First Batch... could Sweety be in danger?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_8">Sweety is inside the Sugar Glass Dome... She should be safe for now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_9">Let us proceed with the trial for the moment, First Sugar Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_10">Okay... But the moment this trial is over, we go straight over to check on Sweety.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_11">A conspiracy...? Are you suggesting Saffron Cookie has somehow deceived the scales?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_12">The scales are absolute! There has never been a Cookie, not a single one, who has ever managed to deceive it! NOT ONCE!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_13">What if... Saffron Cookie is being tricked by First Egg Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_14">She might be under a spell? Or being controlled by her...? Or maybe she doesn\'t have a choice...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_15">Hm? Then that means Saffron Cookie could be a victim herself...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_16">And it could also mean First Egg Cookie is the only one who\'s guilty for pulling the strings here...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_17">If the defendant is under coercive control, sentencing her would go against everything the law stands for...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_18">Defendant. Please answer this question. Did First Egg Cookie coerce you into any of this? Are you acting under duress?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_19">Victim... Manipulation... How you cling to such pitiable words.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_20">I have never been forced. Not for a single moment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_21">The first time I heard her voice... I understood the true reason my dough was ever shaped at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_22">Call it manipulation if you wish. I accept it as the moment my soul finally understood the true meaning of devotion and servitude.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_23">Are you stating, for the record, that you are willingly serving First Egg Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_24">You\'re admitting you, and no one else, pushed those Cookies straight into the hands of evil?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_25">I shared with them the same joy I was allowed to experience. It is not evil. It is absolute, unconditional goodwill.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_26">You don\'t know what First Egg Cookie is really like! She\'s definitely up to no good! Something big and evil!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ3_POR1_27">Enough of this! This case is only becoming muddled by dragging it deeper into the unknown! My head is going to crack clean in half...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_1">Is this willing devotion?
Or a quiet erosion of the
mind by a hidden hand...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_2">... Can the Scale of Good and Evil
truly cut through such
a tangled mess of this nature?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_3">An act with no malice, and yet
the harm is undeniable.
Arguments for or against it will
never be able to see it the same way...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_4">Where does this leave
the trial? Are the scales
really going to stay still?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_5">Hm, the scales really
are holding at
perfect equilibrium.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_6">The scale\'s logic may be
incapable of weighing the
gravity of her deeply
rooted beliefs...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_7">The scales may not
be moving, but that
doesn\'t make her innocent!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_8">There might be Cookies
walking away right now because
they believed every word she said!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_9">Come to think of it...
Have you guys noticed none
of her followers are in the
courtroom anymore?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_10">Did they leave already...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_11">... Silence, everyone.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_12">The scales may not be able to
render judgment, but we also can\'t
just ignore the problem at hand.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_13">Ah. Then are you
stepping in personally?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_14">Surely your boundless wisdom
can weigh something as meager
as my humble honesty.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_15">Whether your will was eroded
or freely given... We\'ll set that
aside for now. But...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_16">The consequences of your
\"truth\" are a clear and present
threat to this court and to the
safety of every Cookie here.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_17">Do you have anything
to say to that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_18">Heh... What you call a threat...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_19">... is nothing more than the
first tremors of something
far greater in the making.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_20">Until the scale is able to
render a verdict, the defendant
is to be held in confinement-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_21">Did you hear that?
And... the ground is shaking...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_22">The entire courtroom is shaking!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_1">What\'s happening?! The ground is shaking like crazy! Is it an earthquake?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_2">It sounds like the sky is falling...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_3">What is...?! Rock Candy Cookie, Glass Cannon Cookie! Can either of you see what\'s going on outside?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_4">Wh-What... is that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_5">Report. Unidentified dark mass. Approaching Sugar Glass Dome. Probability of aggression: guaranteed. Warning. Danger. Warning. Danger.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_6">Ahhh. At long last, the reckoning has come! A force more absolute than any verdict this court could ever render...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_7">Warning! WARNING! Sugar Glass Dome integrity, compromised! Critical destruction risk! Danger, danger, DANGER!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_8">...!
Everyone get down!!! NOW!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_9">The Sugar Glass Dome is falling!!!
WE\'RE DOOMED!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_11">No...! Sweety is still inside the Sugar Glass Dome...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_12">A massive hand... is shattering the dome!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_13">GAAAH! Everything is spinning...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_14">What is that THING...?! It\'s enormous! It just grabbed a Cookie with its giant branches...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_15">No. Those are not branches...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_16">It\'s... It\'s a witch\'s hand!!! And she\'s taking Sweety...!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_17">NGH...! What?! My head... it\'s...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_19">What is this...? Something is... pushing itself into my mind...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_20">I... This... It\'s a... strange memory... resurfacing...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_22">Are you alright, First Salt Cookie?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_23">Stay with us, First Sugar Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_1">These Cookies are sweet... but so terribly weak..</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_2">One wrong bump and they crumble to pieces.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_3">Yes... These little ones need something powerful to protect them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_4">Like we have......... our hero.........</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_5">If we concentrate all that power into a single vessel... we can forge a true, powerful hero...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_6">Of course, each......... will have their own idea of..........</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_7">......... is already baking......... one after the other, trying to make the......... always wanted.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_8">I just hope......... doesn\'t bake a Cookie who hides the exact same way, too afraid to trust anyone, hehe...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_9">Hm... Even so......... didn\'t say they wouldn\'t stop any Cookie who wanted to become a hero... And yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_10">We know the truth... for the happiness of the good... a power to hold back evil is necessary...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_11">Yes... What\'s needed is a hero who stands with the vulnerable and delivers justice to the oppressed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_12">So... Let\'s make a hero, beautiful and eternal...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_13">Yes... Only then will the world of Cookies grow safer, and stronger...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_15">Your Honors...! Wake up...! First Salt Cookie, First Sugar Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_16">Ngh...! Wh-Where are we...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_17">... What happened? Eugh...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_18">They\'re awake! Are you both okay?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_19">Both of you blacked out when you saw the witch\'s hand! You really gave us a fright...!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_20">Eugh... Is everyone... in one piece? What about... Sweety...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_21">Glass Cannon Cookie went to check, but...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_22">Re-Report-t-t-t-t. Sugar Glass Dome: 87% destroyed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_23">Priority Search Target: Sweety.
... Status: Missing.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_24">......</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_25">We lost... someone again...? Like mother... and now Sweety too...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_26">I\'m so sorry... If only we\'d been just a little faster...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_27">That wasn\'t First Egg Cookie\'s doing...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_28">It was a real witch. With a human body.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_29">What\'s going on...? Why did this happen...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_30">Saffron Cookie! MADAM SAFFRON COOKIE! You\'re alive!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_31">We did it! The Absolute was watching over us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_32">Huh? What do you mean? Did you guys have something to do with this???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ2_POR1_33">What...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_1">Ah! You have witnessed the full force of the Absolute\'s power with your very own eyes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_2">You have made this miracle happen, my friends! Truly a magnificent achievement!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_3">Wh-What have you done?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_4">After you spoke of the Absolute, we all decided to head to the oven together!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_5">Ahhh... the First Oven... It was every bit as vast and scorching as described, hot enough to scorch you to the core!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_6">Just like the Cookies who had gone before, others in our group willingly stepped into the oven.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_7">I will never forget the rich, sweet scent that poured from the oven as its flames embraced their dough...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_8">It was that very scent that drew the Absolute\'s gaze down upon us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_9">All we had to do next was run! We ran and guided its shadow here!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_10">We kept running, from the oven to this very courtroom! We led the Absolute\'s gaze here ourselves!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_11">And the Absolute understood what we wished for! That is surely why the dome was destroyed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_12">No! How could you believe that\'s what happened here, you simpletons!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_13">The Witch sensed a Cookie with tremendous power nearby... a Cookie of the First Batch. That\'s why the Sugar Glass Dome was destroyed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_14">Your plan didn\'t work! That witch didn\'t come to save Saffron Cookie at all!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_15">I see no signs of failure. Could there be any greater success than this?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_16">This court\'s false sense of justice, riddled with contradictions and hypocrisy, has been shattered! Only the power of the Absolute remains to shine in its place!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_17">You put other Cookies in danger just to save Saffron Cookie?! How could you do such a thing?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_18">It is precisely through their noble sacrifice that the Absolute claimed the one with tremendous power!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_19">And that Cookie, snatched away from this forsaken court, will pass through the Absolute\'s hands and reach First Egg Cookie at last!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_20">She was right all along... First Egg Cookie will redeliver the First Salvation!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_21">Are you hearing yourself right now? This isn\'t salvation at all!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_22">You only survived by chance! First Egg Cookie didn\'t protect you at all, not even for a second!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_23">You still refuse to understand. There was no reason for me to be saved.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_24">I am nothing more than a guide for this great return... a humble contribution to a journey of everlasting glory!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_25">... I\'ve heard enough. To think this courtroom was destroyed over such senseless delusion.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_26">Glass Cannon Cookie! Rock Candy Cookie! Salt Crystal Cookie! Detain every last one of these zealots!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_27">With this, we have all taken one step closer to the truth! One step closer to returning to our Haven, the First Dough!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_28">You are all hereby under arrest for contempt of court! No... for the destruction of this court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ3_POR1_29">Ahaha... hahaha... HAHA... HA HA HA HA HA!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_1">Are you okay, First Salt Cookie?
How about you, First Sugar Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_2">Our Sugar Glass Dome.
Our court. Our order.
All is lost and in ruins...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_3">The trial and the scales...
Everything was made
a mockery of...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_4">No, the trial isn\'t over yet...
We can still do this!
... Right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_5">Saffron Cookie\'s crimes have
evolved into something
entirely new. What do we do?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_6">Even... if a verdict is decided...
Saffron Cookie can\'t be held anywhere...
The Sugar Glass Dome is destroyed...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_7">Does this mean...
Saffron Cookie\'s trial is over?
Just like that?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_8">... No.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_9">Neither good nor evil
crumble so easily.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_10">... And we will not allow it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_11">Saffron Cookie... There is no malice
in your words or intent, that much
is clear. Even if the outcome is
nothing short of devastating.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_12">And in attempting to weigh that...
this court must acknowledge that
it was not equipped to bear the
full weight of your contradictions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_13">Your Honors...! Surely you
cannot be considering
abandoning the trial...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_14">No. This trial...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_15">... is hereby suspended
pending further deliberation!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_16">Suspended???</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_17">Until we\'re sure that we can
reach the right decision,
the trial is suspended.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_18">That said, Saffron Cookie and
her followers have caused
considerable damage to this
court by luring a witch here...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_19">That\'ll have to be handled
as an entirely separate trial!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_20">Until the trial resumes... confine them
to whatever remains of the
Sugar Glass Dome\'s isolation ward!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_21">Confirmed. Isolation ward,
or equivalent, shall be secured.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_22">So... This is your choice.
Do you truly believe this sham
of a trial can be reopened?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_23">Do you honestly believe
you can resolve this so-called
conundrum before you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_24">... You may be right.
This may be beyond
our power to resolve.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_25">Because at the very
foundation of this world,
there is no single answer...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_26">But unlike the scale,
we possess will.
And will grants the
power of choice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_27">Because... until this trial is reopened,
and perhaps for far longer than that,
you WILL remain locked in that
isolation ward until justice is served!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_28">... You...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_29">Transfer Saffron Cookie,
NOW!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_30">Executing orders.
Detain and transfer
Saffron Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_1">Thanks for everything you did to help with the trial! Even... if it ended up like this...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_2">Thanks to your efforts, we have a much clearer picture of what is actually transpiring.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_3">The court is our responsibility, and it is we who shall see this to the end. Your services are no longer-</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_4">No! We can\'t just walk away from this!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_5">We\'re on this journey to specifically to stop First Egg Cookie!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_6">That\'s right. We knew the Cookies of the First Batch were in danger of being taken, so we\'re out to find them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_7">First Cream Cookie asked us personally to find and rescue the First Batchers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_8">First Cream Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_9">So you\'re... Ha, once again, we are in her debt.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_10">We let our guard down this time as well. We never imagined First Egg Cookie could\'ve prepared something like this so far in advance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_11">Nobody could have seen her using the witch as part of her plan...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_12">We\'re not gonna give up! We\'re gonna keep pushing forward!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_13">We\'ll stop First Egg Cookie! And we WILL bring Sweety back. We promise!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_14">... Yes. Please, take good care of Sweety. Once we\'ve sorted things out here, we\'ll do everything we can to find her too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_15">... And we will also get to the bottom of whatever First Egg Cookie is plotting.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_16">First Salt Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_17">First Sugar Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_18">So... what happens to us now?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_19">While the courtroom is being put back together...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_20">... Each one of you has worked diligently to keep this court running. More than you know.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_21">All of you should take this chance to relax and enjoy a proper vacation!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_22">... Later... whether the courtroom opens again... or it doesn\'t...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_23">Will you... please let us know...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_24">... Of course! Always!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ1_POR1_25">Yes. We promise, no matter what.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_1">The courtroom hasn\'t been this empty in a long, long time.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_2">... Indeed.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_3">First Salt Cookie... That memory from earlier, you saw it too... didn\'t you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_4">The one where we were shaping light with our big hands...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_5">... No matter how hard I try to forget, it\'s a feeling that just cannot be forgotten... Back when our hands... were a different shape.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_6">Those days when we were so eager... to give the little ones a hero of their own.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_8">We were creators once. Standing before the oven, dreaming of a sweeter, more perfect world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_9">A world free of the threats born from greed, absent of cold steel blades.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_10">A world absent of unjust trials, free of the grief born from losing those you love.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_11">A world where none would ever dare dream of revenge... It felt so possible back then, didn\'t it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_12">It did. We were certain it would be a world where the innocent are never punished as unjustly as we were.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_13">Because the one who saved us, ......, told us so.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_14">... That Cookies would live in nothing but happiness. Free from the conflict and pain so familiar to us...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_15">We were shown a small, sweet vision of that perfect world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_16">The other...... lashed out, angrily... said that wasn\'t what mattered right now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_17">But ...... loved Cookies deeply... hoping they would never carry the same sorrows we did.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_18">To preserve that ideal, we poured our power into the creation of a world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_19">And like...... we agreed a hero was necessary.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_20">And so we made up our minds. We would pool our strength together and forge a light... worthy of a hero.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_21">But were we wrong in our thinking? The world of Cookies is not so different from our own after all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_22">Envy, jealousy, deception, conflict, strife... All of it still exists...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_23">It isn\'t a world of beautiful happiness alone... Ugliness and suffering lives here too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_25">Perhaps the ideal world we dreamed of... is simply impossible in reality.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_26">And the standards we believed to be the measure of good and evil... were perhaps nothing but measures of our arrogance.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_27">This world... filled with those who live with free will... It seems good and evil aren\'t always easy to define. And not easy to separate either.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_28">What we\'ve been doing all this time with the Scale of Good and Evil... Has it actually helped the world of Cookies?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_29">We may have rendered fair verdicts and isolated the guilty, all in hopes of building a world for good Cookies to thrive in. And yet...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_30">We still could not bring that ideal world into being. This approach—OUR approach... it wasn\'t the answer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_31">You\'re right. We kept going because we firmly believed it was the only answer....</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_32">Now we truly know. Isolating those who do wrong is not enough to make an ideal world.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_33">To face that truth and still insist on isolation anyway...? That would be nothing but cowardice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_34">... Picking out the guilty and sealing them inside the Sugar Glass Dome put our minds at ease, yes...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_35">But the world outside that dome was still soaked in despair... Is that what you\'re saying?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ2_POR1_36">I think I understand now... I refuse to be a coward!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_1">For far too long, we sat perched high above on the scales... and turned our eyes away from the reality below.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_2">When you think about it... maybe this courtroom falling apart was exactly what we needed to happen?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_3">... Yes.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_4">The world of Cookies has turned out to become so different from what we had hoped... What are we to do? Where do we even begin?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_5">What we\'ve been doing all this time... What if it wasn\'t truly for the sake of this world...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_6">Hmmm... Okay, yes! That\'s it! First Salt Cookie... let\'s go outside!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_7">Outside? You mean, outside the courtroom?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_8">Yes! We still want this world of Cookies to be crisp and sweet, right?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_9">Wouldn\'t it be better to leave these crumbled walls behind and tackle the problems head-on ourselves?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_10">You mean we should become part of the Cookie world ourselves?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_11">Yes! Experiencing this world as Cookies, not as its creators. It might reveal to us the truest path forward for Cookies everywhere!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_12">What do you think, First Salt Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_13">... Could we... ask the scales first?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_14">The scales?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_15">For so long... we\'ve placed the lives of other Cookies on the scale and weighed them.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_16">But whether the very act of building the scales and handing down verdicts was ever truly for the good of this world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_17">We never questioned our motives... never once asked.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_18">Not even once.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_19">Alrighty then! Let\'s find out what verdict the scales have for us!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_21">Weigh the burden of our goodwill!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_22">Weigh the hope we have for setting the rules for a better world, our desire for protecting the weak!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_24">Weigh the burden of what we chose to look away from.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_25">The branding of Cookies as guilty, the arrogance of passing judgment without ever understanding what it means to live as one of them...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_26">Weigh the burden of that irresponsibility.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_30">It\'s... not moving...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_31">... Perhaps that means we were right, First Sugar Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_32">We are complex beings. Even within what is sweet, salty and savory flavors can lurk underneath and seep out...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_33">Even the softest dough can carry a hard layer of icing on top.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_34">As long as a soul lives in even the smallest of Cookies, countless contradictions and complex flavors will be woven together within.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_35">Yes. Life... Living... The world itself... Perhaps complexity is simply inevitable.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_36">The forces of good and evil are intertwined everywhere... In our own hearts, in this world...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ3_POR1_37">What is truly guilty? What is truly innocent? Perhaps that is something we were never able to separate at all.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_1">The scale... It has stopped
at perfect equilibrium.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_2">That is... the most
complete answer it
could have given us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_3">I guess the answer
we\'ve been given is...
\"Our guilt cannot be determined\".</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_4">The most precise and
elaborate essence of order
we have built... has just ruled
against its own creators.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_5">... Pffft!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_6">Are you laughing,
First Sugar Cookie?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_7">It\'s so funny! Hahaha!
We put ourselves on trial
and we couldn\'t get an answer!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_8">Ahahahaha!
We really are a mess,
aren\'t we?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_9">Hehe... I guess we really are.
Honestly, we\'re something else.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_10">Hahahaha! Haha... ha...
Somehow though, now that
it\'s come to this... I actually
feel so much better.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_11">I know what you mean.
Because, in the end, even a
non-answer is still an answer.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_12">The desire we carried as creators,
that urge to control... It was
holding this world back...
Suffocating, stagnating...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_13">If we kept weighing good
against evil forever, this world
may have never been able to move
forward. Or worse, moved backward.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_14">Yes.
Just like the scale.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_15">Yes, indeed.
Just like the scale.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_16">... Shall we depart then?
And leave the scale exactly as it is?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_17">And not interfere in the
lives of Cookies anymore?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_18">It will be their laws, their lives,
their world... their fate.
Let\'s leave all of it in their hands.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_19">Then it is settled.
We will live our lives
properly... as Cookies!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_20">Though we may not be
able to leave this castle
entirely... and Sweety is
still out there too.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_21">Even so... Just stepping
outside the courtroom will
change our lives completely!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_22">Ah...
What must we do
about the courtroom?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_23">We can leave a letter before
we go. Candy Chain Cookie and
the others are sure to find it.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_24">Rock Candy Cookie,
Glass Cannon Cookie,
Salt Crystal Cookie,
Gummy Tape Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_25">If anyone can build
a new court for
the Cookies... it\'s them!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_26">A court made by Cookies
for the Cookies! Let\'s leave it
in their hands and see this
world for ourselves.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_27">And when we\'re 
ready to meet them,
truly Cookie to Cookie...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_28">We\'ll come back and
see what kind of court
they\'ve built.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_29">... I like that plan.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_30">Then let\'s go. Let us
give the Cookies the
power to shape their
own world and order.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_31">And we\'ll leave the
door open! So that every
Cookie has a chance to
find their own happiness,</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_32">to run far beyond any path
we could\'ve ever laid out
for them! Free in ways
even we never imagined!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_33">... Cookies.
Your destiny
belongs to you now.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH4_SQ4_CUT1_34">Good luck.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.Main">The Scent of Roses in a Salt Shaker</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.01">In Need of a Little Comfort</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.02">The Pickiest Judges</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.03">Finally, A Sign of Approval</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.01.Summary">First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie want their room to feel a little cozier. They decide to call on Herb Cookie to find just the right plant to set the mood!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.02.Summary">Herb Cookies returns with carefully chosen plant after plant... after plant... Each one is promptly turned down for one reason or the other.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Title.03.Summary">After much deliberation, Herb Cookie arrives with black and pink roses. For once, both First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie are completely won over. Each bouquet of roses finds a perfect spot in their room, and all is right in the world!</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Illust.Dialog.01">Your roses have more than
earned their place here.</string>
  <string name="$UX.CPC.cookie.2028.Illust.Dialog.02">Woohoo! I just knew
today was going to
be a wonderful day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_1">Hello! Is this... the room of First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_2">Hello there, Herb Cookie! Can I interest you in a piece of sugar candy?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_3">Greetings. You are not here because of a trial, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_4">Hehe, thanks for the candy! I heard you two were looking for some plants... So, here I am!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_5">Yes. We would like to make this room feel a little... cozier. A plant seemed like a good place to start.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_6">Exactly! Some trials are just absolutely dreadful... When we come back, it feels like something\'s been hollowed right out of us.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_7">Having something living and green nearby really does put the heart at ease...! You\'ve made the right choice!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_8">So, Herb Cookie! Do you think you can find a plant that suits both of our rooms?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_9">Of course! Leave it to me! I\'ll turn this room into a cozy little garden both of you can enjoy!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_10">Take note. Nothing too chaotic, please. Like weighing sin, the plant must carry a precise and balanced presence.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_11">And good intentions will always be taken into account! But if it ends up ruining the room instead... Well, that\'s another matter entirely. Got it?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_1_POR1_12">Not to worry! I\'ve got some absolutely stunning ideas already!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_1">First up...! Meet my absolute best friend, the Cookievorous Plant! Isn\'t it just the most adorable thing ever?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_2">A Cookievorous Plant...? Shouldn\'t this thing be summoned to court to be placed on trial...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_3">Hold on, let me go grab the scales and-</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_4">Oh no, no! This plant just lives the way it always has and will! Erm, I\'ll recommend another friend then!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_5">How about this one? A bouquet of colorful, Rainbow Jelly Flowers!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_6">This one... looks too similar to a certain defendant from a recent trial.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_7">It was only a misdemeanor, a petty argument and some lies. But the defendant was really loud. So loud, I\'ll never forget that case. Motion for plant adoption is rejected!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_8">Oh... It\'s sad that it has to be rejected for resembling a defendant... Then, how about a potted Vanilla Flower? It has the softest, creamiest aroma!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_9">... It smells like... nostalgia.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_10">The scent is lovely... Don\'t be too sad, but I think this flower makes the heart go too soft.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_11">If that scent drifted through the courtroom, it would be impossible to concentrate. Only what is deserved must remain... Your proposal is rejected.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_12">Oh... Finding the right plant isn\'t easy at all...</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_13">No need to get upset!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_14">Take your choices with a grain of salt and think them over. There must be a suitable alternative.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_2_POR1_15">Oh! Wait just a moment! There\'s one more plant I thought of!
Some flowers bloomed just this morning!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_1">I\'m really confident about these! They\'re definitely the ones that will make your room shine!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_2">Wow! Pink roses in silver teacups! Just look at that radiant shine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_3">Yes! The shining silver complements your room very well! And the scent...! It\'s very gentle, right? I\'m sure it\'ll help you relax.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_4">A rose like this could make the memories of even the most dreadful of trials fade away completely! I love it!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_5">... Black roses for the nightstand. Steadfast and unwavering.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_6">Both have bloomed into strong and healthy flowers! They suit the room\'s darker tones nicely, don\'t you think?</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_7">This shade of black will cast the most honest of shadows.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_8">The verdict is in... Herb Cookie, your roses have more than earned their place in this room.</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_9">Does this mean they\'ve passed? Woohoo! I just knew today was going to be a wonderful day!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_10">Passed? That\'s an understatement! We\'ll give these roses the most radiant spots in the entire room!</string>
  <string name="$Script_PuzzleChallenge_Cookie2028_3_POR1_11">The roses seem pleased too. What a relief!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.001">Luxurious Salt &amp; Sugar Fireplace</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.002">Luminous Salt &amp; Sugar Fireplace</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wall.001">Scales of Justice Stained Glass</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.003">Goddess of Justice Statue</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Ceil.001">Salt Shaker Crystal Chandelier</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.004">Pink Roses in Silver Teacups</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wallpaper.001">Iridescent Wallpaper</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Deck.001">Sleek Matte Stripe Flooring</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.005">Sturdy Black Sofa</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.006">Plush Pink Sofa</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wall.002">Salt &amp; Sugar Lamp</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.007">Colorful Sugar Shaker Table</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Hanger.001">Shimmering Verdicts</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.008">Simple Black Footstool</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.009">Cute Pink Footstool</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Hanger.002">Black &amp; White Stamps</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.010">Black Rose Ornament</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.001.Story">The fireplace where First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie sit side by side to rest after a long day of announcing verdicts. Glistening crystals shimmering within the flames cast a jewel-like brilliance across their entire room. The warmth of the fire fills the room with an air of comfort, providing a cozy opportunity for a well-earned rest.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.002.Story">The fireplace where First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie sit side by side to rest after a long day of announcing verdicts. The balanced symmetry of black and pink emits a calm, inviting charm. The warmth of the fire fills the room with an air of comfort, providing a cozy opportunity for a well-earned rest.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wall.001.Story">A grand window that drinks in the light and scatters it into a brilliant cascade of color. The scales rendered in the window seems to remind all who enter this room that this is a sacred space where justice is upheld and served.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.003.Story">An elegant statue holding a sharp blade in one hand and a balanced scale in the other. A symbol of the absolute justice First Salt Cookie and First Sugar Cookie both uphold, it commands the center of the room with a dignified and noble presence.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Ceil.001.Story">A grand, one-of-a-kind chandelier modeled after an enormous salt shaker. Crystals cascade down like falling salt, scattering light across the room in a dazzling, radiant sea of color.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.004.Story">These carefully tended roses blooming in a set of shining silver teacups add a touch of elegance to the room\'s already brilliant atmosphere. A gentle, floral fragrance swims through the room, quietly soothing any heart from the nerves of presiding in court all day.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wallpaper.001.Story">This wallpaper shifts between luminous shades of black and pink depending on the angle you view it. It seems to emit a glow that makes you feel like you\'re inside a gemstone, making the room feel larger, deeper, and alive.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Deck.001.Story">A matte-finish floor designed with black and pink stripes. Its calm and grounded appearance lets the room\'s ornate furniture take center stage, contributing to a flawless and perfectly balanced symmetrical aesthetic.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.005.Story">A firm and sturdy sofa chair, perfect for resting in any room you place it in.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.006.Story">A soft and plush sofa chair, perfect for resting in any room you place it in.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Wall.002.Story">A pair of lamps to light up the room. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.007.Story">A table fashioned from a sugar shaker. Let\'s find a good spot for it!</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Hanger.001.Story">Memories of past verdicts. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.008.Story">A typical black footstool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.009.Story">A typical pink footstool. It serves its purpose.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Hanger.002.Story">A collection of black and white stamps, framed up and displayed. Let\'s place it here and there.</string>
  <string name="$item.Deco.CookieRoom.cookie2028_2029.Floor.010.Story">Black roses displayed on a nightstand. What a lucky find!</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2028_2029">First Salt Cookie &amp; First Sugar Cookie\'s Room of Firm Justice and Graceful Mercy</string>
  <string name="$Room.Cookie.2028_2029.Story">Tucked cozily beside the Court of Judgment, this room is where the silence after the verdict settles in. Beneath a shimmering salt shaker chandelier, the weight of every ruling gives way to a well-earned rest. With honored judgments and a gleaming set of scales looking on, the two Cookies dream of another fair and just tomorrow.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.001">Chained Salt Shaker Hat</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.002">Black Rose Veil</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.003">Key of Sharp Judgment</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.001">Rainbow Gavel</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.002">Sugared Lace Veil</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.003">Glimmering Comb</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.001.Story">A sleek brimmed hat crafted from a black salt shaker. Rigid metal chains along the brim complete its austere, judicial air. When pulled down low over the eyes, it serves as a signal that court is about to be called to order, and the weight of every sin will be measured.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.002.Story">A short lace veil adorned with black roses. When draped across the judge\'s face, her expression remains still, unreadable, unmoved as she tries to avoid being swayed by emotions. For First Salt Cookie, who holds silence as the most honest form of testimony, this veil is more than just an accessory!</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2028.003.Story">A cold black key fitted with a razor-edged ornament. What it unlocks, only First Salt Cookie knows. Just what buried injustice could this key be waiting to reveal?</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.001.Story">A gavel fashioned from a sugar shaker fitted with a handle. Don\'t let the charming appearance and colors fool you... When swung, the crack it makes in the courtroom is dead serious. It\'s said to be hammered down without hesitation the moment a criminal betrays the goodwill they were shown.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.002.Story">A short white lace veil brightened with a pink rose. It makes First Sugar Cookie\'s radiant smile shine even brighter. When a merciful verdict is handed down, it sways gently with her sunlit smile.</string>
  <string name="$Item.CookieItem.cookie2029.003.Story">A small comb etched with a delicate rose pattern. Each gentle stroke through the hair stirs a fond, distant memory kept close to First Sugar Cookie\'s heart. It is a treasured keepsake she reaches for whenever her faith in goodwill begins to waver.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2028.TeddyBear">First Salt Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2029.TeddyBear">First Sugar Cookie Bear Jelly Toy</string>
