  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2028.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Salt Cookie. Its steady, unwavering eyes stare back at you with intense honesty. The longer you look, the more you feel every secret you\'ve ever kept rising to the surface.</string>
  <string name="$Item.Deco.cookie2029.TeddyBear.Story">A Bear Jelly Toy that greatly resembles First Sugar Cookie. Its warm, sweet smile makes you want to embrace it close... but something about it keeps you just alert enough to stay on your best behavior.</string>
  <string name="$Season.2028_2029.Complete.Profile.Story">Proof of completing the First Salt &amp; First Sugar Collection. One day, none shall ever shed tears over an unjust fate.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Salt Cookie\'s soul. Briny and unyielding, the weight of hardened justice seeps quietly into your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Soulstone.Tooltip">This mysterious drop holds a piece of First Sugar Cookie\'s soul. Behind its sweet aroma lies an unshakable sense of sincerity that seems to be reaching out to your heart.</string>
