  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0605_dialogue3">\"Lying is bad\"?
Oh?! I\'m so sorry?!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0602_dialogue1">Your destruction
shall be my
greatest pleasure!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue1_1">As the master of
the Ivory Pagoda...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue1_2">Everything shall
return to flour...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0601_dialogue2">... The Seeker of Volition.
Once, that name was mine.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue1_1">Sing far and wide!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue1_2">The Bringer of
Happiness
has returned!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0603_dialogue2">True Happiness begins
when once accepts
their Sloth~</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0604_dialogue2_1">\"Divine Emissary\"?
That title was laid
to rest long ago.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0604_dialogue2_2">Tainted power
holds no pride.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0506_dialogue2_1">Truth, Deceit...
Nothing can
bring me down.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0506_dialogue2_2">The more you
understand, the more
there is to love!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue2_1">True greed means
protecting what is yours...
No matter the cost.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0507_dialogue2_2">Witness my
boundless greed!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0508_dialogue3_1">Great power must
be used for the
greater good.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0508_dialogue3_2">I became a king
to protect the
unfortunate!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue1_2">Eternal flames!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue2_1">I burn hotter than
the Red Dragon!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue2_2">No one can
stop my fire!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0041_dialogue3">You won\'t stop
the fire!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue1_1">The Forest keeps
no secrets from me...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue1_2">My arrow shall
purify the Darkness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue2">I once roamed
the woods in
a different form...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue3_1">My arrow will pierce
the Darkness and
rejuvenate your soul.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0070_dialogue3_2">I live to protect the
forest from
the Darkness!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue3_1">Not all wishes
come true...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0065_dialogue3_2">I am prepared to face
my fate. We must not
be afraid to move on.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue1_1">Magic is like an
endless night sky...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue1_2">I have seen
your dreams...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0049_dialogue2_2">Do not be afraid!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0530_dialogue3_1">All life will 
fade eventually.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0530_dialogue3_2">Have no fear.
All shall follow the
will of Nature...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0600_dialogue2">Bow down to
your sky god!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CK_cookie0138_dialogue1_2">MORTALSSS!
BOW BEFORE
THE RED DRAGON!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2025_dialogue3_1">I don\'t want to lose
anything... I will never
forget anyone...</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie2025_dialogue3_2">You aren\'t leaving...
Are you...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0025_dialogue1_1">Which spell
should I
practice today...?</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_cookie0025_dialogue1_2">Abra-Cookie-Dabra!</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue1_1">There will come a time
when you must make
a difficult choice.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue1_2">Don\'t ever forget
the spark of courage
that lies in your heart.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue3_1">There\'s a chance we
may not lay eyes
on tomorrow\'s sun.</string>
  <string name="$Script_MillionDoors_Meet_CC_cookie4012_dialogue3_2">But our friendship
will last forever.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Story">When the moonlight of the first frost faded over a jar of snow-white salt, a Cookie stirred awake among the hardest crystals. First Salt Cookie has earned a reputation of being an unflinching arbiter of right and wrong. Wielding a scale that tolerates not a single grain of error, her fairness is so absolute that every plea and excuse dissolves before her. When all else fails, wronged Cookies find their way to her court as a final refuge.

Standing beneath the unwavering scale, her expression carries the chill of a cold wind sealed inside a jar of salt. Day after day, she adjusts them in silence and with intense concentration, so that not a single injustice goes unanswered.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Get">Don\'t think about running.
It\'s time to weigh your sins.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Random.01">You think it\'s unfair?
Hm, the scales never lie.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Random.02">Sometimes, silence is the
most honest of testimonies.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Random.03">Proper judgment and
punishment makes the
world a better place.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Random.04">There is no mercy... 
Only what is deserved.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Random.05">My verdict stands.
Let your sins dissolve on
your tongue, like salt.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.LifeZero.01">Do not allow your
emotions to get
the better of you.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2028.Monologue.Greeting">{0}...
You\'re not on trial, are you?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Story">As the rising sunlight poured over a gleaming jar of sugar, a Cookie stirred awake among the sparkling crystals. First Sugar Cookie, always wearing a bright smile, is known as a warmhearted mediator who weighs the goodwill in others. She believes a measure of mercy is essential when delivering justice, having never forgotten a certain cruel trial from long ago. However, when a criminal has truly abandoned all goodness, she flings open the isolation ward\'s doors without a moment\'s hesitation, faster than her sister.

Both sweet and unyielding, much like sugar itself, she never fails to put every Cookie in her courtroom just a little on edge... Seeing this, she flashes her signature sunlit smile as she prepares for a new day. And in that smile, Cookies in the court find the same quiet reassurance: no good deed goes forgotten.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Get">Hello! Ready to prove
you\'ve got a good heart?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Random.01">Give me a reason to
forgive you. I\'m all ears!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Random.02">Do you want a tour
of the isolation ward?
It\'s quiet and peaceful.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Random.03">Some trials are awful...
We don\'t want you to
end up like that, do we?</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Random.04">Don\'t be sad...
Good intentions will
be taken into account.</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Random.05">If you\'ve abandoned all
goodwill, I see no reason
to show you mercy!</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.LifeZero.01">It\'s time for Cookies to
stop doing bad things...</string>
  <string name="$Cookie.2029.Monologue.Greeting">{0}!
I\'ve been waiting!
Wanna piece of candy?</string>
