  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_50">Wow...! So this is where crimes are put on trial... The Court of Judgment!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_51">I\'ve read there is a special scale here that weighs the gravity of every crime and always gives a fair verdict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_52">Sounds like fun! Let\'s go inside and check it out!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_53">Hey, look over there...! There\'s a crowd of Cookies in front of the courthouse... I wonder what\'s going on?</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_54">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_55">Choco Gold Cookie. You\'ve been lending gold coins to Cookies in need.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_56">However, these loans charged excessive interest. Predatory contracts, each and every one.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_57">Every last one of those was agreed upon in writing! I have never broken a single law! Not a single one!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_58">The defendant shall remain silent! We are in the middle of the final verdict! This is a fair and just ruling, and everything has already been taken into account!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_59">Yes, yes... Every contract was carried out exactly as written. That part is beyond dispute!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_60">However, those contracts were signed by Cookies in extreme, dire circumstances who had no choice but to accept the terms. Your terms... which were excessive and deeply unfair.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_61">The contracts were deliberately written with terms and language to trap Cookies in perpetual hardship, while ensuring that you, the lender, walked away with unjust gain.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_62">What?! No, no! I was helping them with GOOD intentions! There are plenty of Cookies who escaped their circumstances and succeeded because I lent them my gold coins!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_63">SILENCE! Any further disruption and you will be held in contempt of court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_64">Your Honors! This is a smear campaign born from... from jealousy! I am innocent! If I am acquitted, I swear to make a generous donation to this court!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_65">Aw, how nice. But there\'s no need for that, so don\'t you worry! In the Court of Judgment, none shall suffer injustice! No one walks away with a sentence they don\'t deserve.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_66">The Scale of Good and Evil will weigh everything, every right and wrong, and the true gravity of your crimes!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_67">Bias, misplaced emotions, lies, manipulation... Such trivial factors do not hold any sway in this courtroom.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_68">All will be judged by the Scales...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_69">And the verdict is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_70">Right! Bailiff! Take the convicted to the Sugar Glass Dome for confinement!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_71">Right away!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_72">Your Honors. Let us please proceed with the next verdict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_73">...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_74">Roasted Salt Cookie. You are practicing medicine without a license, and caused injury in the process.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_75">But the Cookie in question was in a critical state, weren\'t they? Had Roasted Salt Cookie not stepped in and taken action, the patient\'s life would\'ve been at risk.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_76">Even so, there may have been a Cookie better suited to provide care. Had they been taken to a proper clinic, the unfortunate incident may never have happened.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_77">No matter how urgent the situation, an ill-fitted intervention can give rise to an even greater degree of harm.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_78">And yet...! The Cookies who have received treatment before are all grateful to Roasted Salt Cookie.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_79">In a case like this... we need to weigh the ripple effects the verdict itself may have on Cookies everywhere.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_80">With all of that taken into account, the Scale of Good and Evil will render its judgment.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_81">All will be judged by the Scales... And the verdict is...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ1_POR1_82">Innocent. However, there are some conditions.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH1_SQ3_POR1_33">But it is also their
clumsiness that has
disrupted an important trial.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_36">Warning! Anomalous energy reading detected from defendant. Initiate search protocols. Proceeding with precision scan...</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ2_POR1_37">Anomaly detected. Item of unknown origins among belongings. Scanning... Description: Winged egg with active magical energy signature.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_23">WHAM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH2_SQ4_CUT1_24">WHAM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_30">WHAM!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_31">WHAM!
*CRACK*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_32">WHAAAM!
*CRACK, CRACK...*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_33">WHAAAAAAM!
*CRSSHHH!!!*</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ1_POR1_24">Urgh... Mine too...! Everything is... spinning!!!</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_31">... only the endless process
of finding our way forward
through eternal conflict.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_32">The scale is a tool built to
find one correct answer...
But it\'s powerless before
a problem like this.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_33">We choose to no longer
permit you to drive
Cookies into harm\'s way.</string>
  <string name="$Script_SAGA06_CH3_SQ4_CUT1_34">For until this trial reconvenes,
perhaps even an eternity later,
you will be locked away.</string>
